NK060(i)001:1: // dpal gsang ba snying po'i rgyud don gsal byed me long zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK060(i)001:2: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i rgyud kyi 'grel bshad/
NK060(i)001:3: rgyud don gsal bar byed pa'i me long zhes bya ba/
NK060(i)001:4: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bor
NK060(i)001:5: gyur pa dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams dang
NK060(i)001:6: rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs la gus pas phyag 'tshal
NK060(i)001:8: gang dag rnam gsum srid pa la gnas lus can
NK060(i)001:9: rnams dang mtshungs par ldan yang rang bzhin rnam par
NK060(i)001:10: dag /dag dang ma dag sems can kun gyi khams
NK060(i)001:11: dang bsam pa rab tu mkhyen yang gzung dang 'dzin
NK060(i)001:12: pa med // med par lta sogs log sred can
NK060(i)001:13: la brtse ba'i thugs rje rgyun mi gcod kyang bdag
NK060(i)001:15: dmigs med mkha' ltar khyab pa ma lus mdzad pa'i
NK060(i)001:16: phrin las yongs su rdzogs kyang 'gro ba'i don la
NK060(i)001:17: brtson // 'jig tshogs lta sogs lta ngan lnga yi
NK060(i)001:18: d+r+wa ba gcod pa mtshon phyir zur gyi gdung du
NK060(i)001:19: brtson // sku bltams nas // ma rigs 'khrul pa'i
NK060(i)001:20: sems can rnams la bu gcig pa yi ma bzhin
NK060(i)001:21: byams pa'i thugs rjes skyob mdzad cing //
NK060(i)001:22: mu stegs theg dman ri dwags tshogs rnams zil gyis
NK060(i)001:23: gnon mdzad smra ba'i seng ge rtsol bral gsang 'dzin
NK060(i)001:24: pa // mi yi khyu mchog chos kyi rgyal po
NK060(i)001:25: gsang bdag gnyis pa de yi zhabs la rtag tu
NK060(i)001:26: pa // gus pas 'dud // lam gyi nang nas
NK060(i)001:27: nye lam dam pa 'jig 'das dngos grub kun gyis
NK060(i)001:28: 'byung gnas gsang ba snying po'i rgyud //
NK060(i)001:29: 'chad par 'dod kyang blo gros stobs zhan yid ma
NK060(i)001:30: gzhungs dang rnam g.yeng dbang gyur 'ga' yi don ched
NK060(i)001:31: du // chos kyi spyan ldan sgro phug pa yi
NK060(i)001:32: bshad srol rim brgyud ma 'ongs sangs rgyas mtshan can
NK060(i)001:33: du // las rnyed pa // mi nub bya phyir
NK060(i)001:34: brtse ba'i sems kyis blun ngag bzhin du bsnyad pa'i
NK060(i)001:35: gsung sgros yi ger dgod par bya //
NK060(i)001:36: 'dir rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po/
NK060(i)001:37: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse/
NK060(i)001:38: bstan pa thams cad kyi 'byung gnas/
NK060(i)001:40: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i zhe phugs/
NK060(i)001:42: sngar 'das pa'i rgyal ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi gshegs shul/
NK060(i)001:43: ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi lam dam par gyur pa/
NK060(i)001:44: che ba'i yon tan brgyad dang ldan pa/
NK060(i)001:45: sems dang ye shes rang snang ston pa sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i rgyud/
NK060(i)001:46: dpal gsang ba'i snying po 'di bshad pa'i dbang du bgyis na/
NK060(i)001:48: kho gzhung gsal ba'i sgron med las/
NK060(i)001:49: mtshon bya rang bzhin gzhi yi rgyud //
NK060(i)001:50: sgro skur med par bstan pa ni //
NK060(i)001:51: mtshon byed sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste //
NK060(i)001:52: mdzub mos ri bong can bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:54: mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud ni sems can thams cad kyi sems kyi chos nyid/
NK060(i)001:55: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:56: de mtshon byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud kyi bshad thabs/
NK060(i)001:57: spyi don rnam pa gsum gyi sgo nas ston te/
NK060(i)001:58: spyir na rgyal ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK060(i)001:59: rgyas rnams kyis gdul bya sems can rnams kyi don
NK060(i)001:60: du bstan pa dang theg pa ji ltar gsungs pa'i
NK060(i)001:61: tshul dang / de dag gi nang nas bstan pa
NK060(i)001:62: dang theg pa gang yin par bsdus te ngos bzung
NK060(i)001:63: tshul dang / ba dang / de bshad pa'i thabs so //
NK060(i)001:64: dang po ni rgyal ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:65: sangs rgyas thugs rje che la thabs mkhas pa rnam
NK060(i)001:66: pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi dgongs pa
NK060(i)001:67: dang ldan pa rnams kyis gdul bya sems can khams
NK060(i)001:68: gsum du 'khor zhing rgyud drug tu 'khyams pa rnams
NK060(i)001:69: kyi don du bstan pa dang theg pa ji ltar
NK060(i)001:70: gsungs she na/ gsung pa'i tshul gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:73: thabs sam gnyen po la dgongs te gsungs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:74: dang po ni 'di nyid kyi gsum pa las/
NK060(i)001:75: ma rig pa'i rnam par rtog pa nyon mongs pa
NK060(i)001:76: stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i gnyen por chos stong
NK060(i)001:77: phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:80: zhes pas gdul bya sems can rnams kyi rgyud la/
NK060(i)001:81: nyon mongs pa stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi la sogs te bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig yod pas/
NK060(i)001:82: de dag 'dul ba'i gnyen por dam pa'i chos kyang
NK060(i)001:83: stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi la sogs pa bsam
NK060(i)001:84: gyis mi khyab pa zhig gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:85: de dag kyang mdor bsdu na/
NK060(i)001:86: nyon mongs pa 'dod chags kyi cha las gyur pa
NK060(i)001:87: nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen por dam pa'i chos
NK060(i)001:88: 'dul pa'i/ nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gi cha las
NK060(i)001:89: gyur pa nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen por dam
NK060(i)001:90: 'dul pa'i/ pa'i chos mdo sde'i/ nyon mongs pa gti
NK060(i)001:91: mug gi cha las gyur pa nyi khri chig stong
NK060(i)001:92: gi gnyen por dam pa'i chos mngon pa'i/
NK060(i)001:93: nyon mongs pa dug gsum mam lnga la sogs pa
NK060(i)001:94: mtha' dag gi gnyen por rig pa 'dzin pa sngags
NK060(i)001:95: kyi sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs te/
NK060(i)001:96: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud las/
NK060(i)001:97: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK060(i)001:98: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK060(i)001:99: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK060(i)001:100: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK060(i)001:101: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK060(i)001:102: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK060(i)001:103: thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK060(i)001:104: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK060(i)001:105: mdor na brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa yang //
NK060(i)001:106: nyon mongs 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs par zad //
NK060(i)001:108: de yang sngar 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:109: da ltar gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:110: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang gsung bar 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:111: gnyis pa theg pa'i rkang grangs la dgongs te gsungs pa ni/
NK060(i)001:112: 'di nyid kyi le'u gsum pa las/
NK060(i)001:114: 'dul ba'i dbang gis lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:115: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:116: rang byang chub kyi theg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:117: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:118: bla na med pa'i theg pas/
NK060(i)001:120: theg pa lnga ru 'dus par yang gsungs/
NK060(i)001:122: lang ka'i bdag po gzhan yang gang //
NK060(i)001:123: don dam nges pa'i theg pa ni //
NK060(i)001:124: gsum du nges par bstan pa ste //
NK060(i)001:125: kun 'byung 'dren dang dka' thub rig /dbang sgyur thabs kyi theg pa'o //
NK060(i)001:126: zhes theg pa gsum du 'dus par yang gsungs/
NK060(i)001:128: theg pa rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK060(i)001:129: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa dang //
NK060(i)001:132: theg pa gnyis su 'dus par yang gsungs/
NK060(i)001:134: ji srid 'du shes med kyi bar //
NK060(i)001:135: theg pa'i sgo yang de las med //
NK060(i)001:136: ji srid 'du shes gnas ma thag /theg pa'i sgo yang bsam mi khyab //
NK060(i)001:138: theg pa bsam gyis mi khyab par yang gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:139: gsum pa thabs sam gnyen po la dgongs te gsungs pa ni/
NK060(i)001:141: de dag thams cad kyang gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i
NK060(i)001:142: phyi nang gi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba 'dzin
NK060(i)001:144: las dang las kyi 'bras bu chud mi za ba dang /
NK060(i)001:145: las dang las kyi 'bras bus mi gos/
NK060(i)001:147: gos su med par ston pa'i mthar thug go //
NK060(i)001:149: gnyen por yang theg pa chung ngu la nyon mongs pa spong 'gegs dang /
NK060(i)001:150: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa la spyod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:151: sngags kyi phyi rgyud la lhar bsgyur ba dang /
NK060(i)001:152: nang pa gnyis la dbang du byed pa dang /
NK060(i)001:153: a ti la spang gnyen ro gcig pa'i tshul gyis te/
NK060(i)001:154: mdor na nyon mongs pa rang kha ma'i rtog pa
NK060(i)001:155: 'joms par byed pa'i gnyen po yang lnga'am drug tu
NK060(i)001:157: spyi don gnyis pa de dag gi nang nas bstan
NK060(i)001:158: pa dang theg pa gang yin pa bsdus te ngos
NK060(i)001:159: bzung ba ni/ theg pa'i rkang grangs mang du gsungs kyang /
NK060(i)001:160: yongs su grags pa'i dbang du theg pa rim pa dgur 'dus te/
NK060(i)001:162: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK060(i)001:163: dam tshig bsgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK060(i)001:164: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK060(i)001:165: ces pas theg pa rim pa dgu las/
NK060(i)001:167: mtshan nyid sde gsum yang ma yin/
NK060(i)001:168: phyi rgyud sde gsum yang ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:169: nang rgyud du ngos gzung ngo //
NK060(i)001:171: bskyed pa sku'i rgyud da byings che bar ston pa
NK060(i)001:172: ma h+aa yo ga /rdzogs pa gsung gi rgyud zhal
NK060(i)001:173: gsal bar ston pa a nu yo ga /bskyed rdzogs
NK060(i)001:174: gnyis su med pa'i don ston pa a ti yo
NK060(i)001:175: ga las/ 'dir ma h+aa yo gar ngos gzung ngo //
NK060(i)001:176: 'di la rgya gar na tran+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad du yod pa las/
NK060(i)001:177: bod du 'gyur ba la sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad/
NK060(i)001:179: de dag gi man ngag phra mo drug cu rtsa bzhi dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:180: pan+di ta chen po bi la ma la mi tra'i zhal snga nas/
NK060(i)001:181: zhus chen gyi lo ts+aa ba rma rin chen mchog gis bsgyur ba las/
NK060(i)001:183: sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad kyi nang nas kyang rtsa ba'i
NK060(i)001:184: rgyud du gyur pa gsang ba'i snying po de kho
NK060(i)001:185: na nyid nges pa'i rgyud ces bya bar ngos gzung
NK060(i)001:186: ngo // gsung pa de ltar ngos gzung ba'i rgyud
NK060(i)001:187: gzhung 'di nyid bshad thabs kyi yan lag rang du
NK060(i)001:188: ngo // zhe na/ khog gzhung gsal ba'i sgron me las/
NK060(i)001:189: phal gyi lan gdab 'bru bsnan dang //
NK060(i)001:190: khog dbub sa bcad bzhi ru gsungs //
NK060(i)001:192: kho dbub pa stong thun gyi/
NK060(i)001:195: gnas skabs brgal lan gyi don dang sbyar te bshad pa dang bzhi'o //
NK060(i)001:196: dang po khog dbub pa ni/
NK060(i)001:197: spyi don rnam pa lnga'i sgo nas ston par byed de/
NK060(i)001:200: sa bcad pa dkyus kyi don dang /
NK060(i)001:201: 'bru bsnan pa'i tshig gi don ni thun mong gi du ston la/
NK060(i)001:202: brgal lan ni gnas skabs khre'u ru ston pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:203: de yang sa bcad pa dkyus kyii dbang du byas na gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:207: klad kyi don la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:208: bgrang bgrang zhes pa 'di rnams ni sa dmigs bgrang ba yin te/
NK060(i)001:209: mtshal la ma sleb kyi bar gyi ser rnams bgrang ngo //
NK060(i)001:211: drang drang zhes pa 'di rnams ni byang 'dren pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:212: ser 'og ma la ma sleb kyi bar gyi mtshal rnams bklag go //
NK060(i)001:213: mtshan bstan pa 'di la sa nang tshegs su bcad na/
NK060(i)001:214: ji skad du rnam bshad las/
NK060(i)001:216: man ngag cung zad sbyin par bya //
NK060(i)001:217: dgos pa bsdus pa'i don bcas dang //
NK060(i)001:218: tshig don bcas dang brgal lan bcas //
NK060(i)001:219: mtshams sbyar bsnyad de bshad par bya //
NK060(i)001:226: bye brag tu mtshan klad du smros pa'i/
NK060(i)001:227: rgya skad du mi smros par bod skad smros pa'i dgos pa'o //
NK060(i)001:228: dang po mtshan smos pa'i dgos pa ni/
NK060(i)001:229: bstan pa la mtshan nges pas glegs bam bshad bde ba'i dgos pa yod/
NK060(i)001:230: gnyis pa mtshan klad du smos pa'i dgos pa ni/
NK060(i)001:231: blo dbang po yang rab mchog tu gyur pa rnams
NK060(i)001:232: kyis ni mtshan mthong ba tsam gyis rgyud dbu zhabs
NK060(i)001:233: kyi don khong du chud par 'gyur zhing /
NK060(i)001:236: mtshan mthong ba tsam gyis 'di ni gsang ba snying
NK060(i)001:237: po de kho na nyid nges pa'i rgyud bya ba
NK060(i)001:238: yin par 'dug snyam du myur du ngos zin pa'i
NK060(i)001:239: dgos pa yod/ gsum pa rgya skad mi smos par bod skad smos pa'i dgos pa ni/
NK060(i)001:240: lo ts+aa ba 'ga' zhig rgya gar du bgrod pa'i dka' ba spyad pas bod 'bangs la drin bzhag pa'am/
NK060(i)001:241: bstan pa'i byung khungs rgya gar yin pas khung btsun pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:242: rgya skad dang bod skad gnyis smos kyi/
NK060(i)001:244: pan+di ta bi ma la mi tra bod yul du byon nas/
NK060(i)001:245: lo ts+aa ba rma rin chen mchog la dka' ba spyad ma dgos shing /
NK060(i)001:246: tshig spros pa'ang mi spro bas skad gnyis smos kyang don gzhan ma mthong pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:247: bod du skad zhes dmigs kyis bkar nas bod skad
NK060(i)001:248: rkyang pa smos pa tshig nyung la don myur du
NK060(i)001:249: ngos zin pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK060(i)001:250: ga nyis pa bsdus pa'i don la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:255: gsang ba'i zhes pas rgyud kyi rang bzhin/
NK060(i)001:256: snying pos rgyud kyi che ba/
NK060(i)001:257: de kho na nyid kyis rgyud kyi mtshan nyid/
NK060(i)001:258: nges pas rgyud kyi nges don/
NK060(i)001:259: 'o zhes pas rgyud don yongs su rdzogs par ston pa'o //
NK060(i)001:261: gsang ba'i zhes pas rtogs dka' bar/
NK060(i)001:263: de kho na nyid kyis gzhan sel bar/
NK060(i)001:264: nges pas nges don the tshom dang bral bar/
NK060(i)001:266: de dag la rgyud don yongs su rdzogs par go ba'o //
NK060(i)001:268: ston tshul dang rjes su mthun par rtogs pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:269: gsang ba'i zhes pas rgyud kyi rang bzhin/
NK060(i)001:270: snying pos rgyud kyi che ba/
NK060(i)001:271: de kho na nyid kyis rgyud kyi mtshan nyid/
NK060(i)001:272: nges pas nges don the tshom dang bral bar/
NK060(i)001:273: 'o zhes pas rgyud don yongs su rdzogs par rtogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:274: gsum pa tshig gi don la/
NK060(i)001:275: 'grel pa spar khab kyis phyi ltar kho na las ma bshad kyang /
NK060(i)001:276: bla ma brgyud pa'i gdams ngag ltar bshad na/
NK060(i)001:277: phyi nang gsang ba gsum las/
NK060(i)001:278: dang po mtshan phyi ltar bshad pa la yang bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:284: dang po gsang ba'i zhes pa la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:288: rang bzhin gyis gsang ba la yang bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:292: dgos ched ci'i phyir gsang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:295: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po/
NK060(i)001:297: gdul bya blo 'khrul pa rnams la/
NK060(i)001:299: rang gsang thabs kyis chod pa'i tshul du ste/
NK060(i)001:300: 'di nyid kyi le'u gnyis pa las/
NK060(i)001:301: e ma ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK060(i)001:302: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK060(i)001:303: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang //
NK060(i)001:304: gzhan du min las shin tu gsang //
NK060(i)001:308: don dam pa'i bden pa dkor bdun ngo bo nyid
NK060(i)001:309: du lhun gyis grub pa rang chas su yod kyang
NK060(i)001:310: rang ngo rang gi ma shes te/
NK060(i)001:312: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas rang rig la nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes pas so //
NK060(i)001:314: gnyis su med pa'i rang byung gi ye shes yon
NK060(i)001:315: tan ril lhun gyis grub pa de rang chas su
NK060(i)001:316: yod kyang ngo ma shes pa kho na la bya'o
NK060(i)001:317: zhes gsungs so // rang bzhin gyi gsang ba ni/
NK060(i)001:318: kun rdzob kyi bden pa ye nas sku dang ye
NK060(i)001:319: shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang bzhin gyis gnas kyang
NK060(i)001:320: rang ngo rang gis ma shes pa ste/
NK060(i)001:321: gang gis ma shes na kun tu brtags pa'i ma
NK060(i)001:322: rig pas rang snang la mtshan mar bzung bas ma
NK060(i)001:323: shes so // de yang spar khab las/
NK060(i)001:324: de nyid rang snang ba'i dngos po ril mi zad
NK060(i)001:325: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo rang rgyud du gnas pa
NK060(i)001:326: btags pas bsgribs pa'i zhes gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:327: ngo bo nyid kyi gsang ba ni/
NK060(i)001:328: dbyer med kyi bden pa ye nas rang chas su gnas kyang ngo ma shes te/
NK060(i)001:329: gang gis ma shes na snang stong tha dad du bzung bas ma shes so //
NK060(i)001:331: rang bzhin gyi rgyud kyi ngo bo nyid yul sems
NK060(i)001:332: rgyu 'bras dang bden pa gnyis po las grol ba
NK060(i)001:333: de rang snang ba'i phyir rang gi ngo bo nyid
NK060(i)001:334: yul du byar ma dmigs pa kho na'o zhes gsungs
NK060(i)001:335: so // shin tu gsang ba ni/
NK060(i)001:336: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba'i don ye nas rang chas su gnas kyang ngo ma shes te/
NK060(i)001:337: gang gis ma shes na yul dang yul can du bzung bas ma shes so //
NK060(i)001:339: 'bras bu'i rgyud bsgrub par bya ba de gud nas med kyang nyon mongs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:340: shes bya dang lta ba'i sgrib pas gzhan du tshol
NK060(i)001:341: yang rang rig pa las snang ba kho na'o zhes
NK060(i)001:342: gsungs so // des na gsang tshul bzhis chod pa'i tshul du gsang ngo //
NK060(i)001:343: dgos ched ci'i phyir gsang na/
NK060(i)001:344: phal gyi yul ma yin pa'i phyir gsang ngo //
NK060(i)001:345: gnyis pa gab pa'i gsang ba ni drug ste/
NK060(i)001:353: yi ge'i rgyud kyi don de/
NK060(i)001:355: mtshon byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud du/
NK060(i)001:357: gdul bya ras chod can la/
NK060(i)001:359: rgyud dkrugs lung gcus man ngag gab pa'i tshul du/
NK060(i)001:360: dgos ched gang gi phyir na/
NK060(i)001:361: bka' sel med par bya ba'i phyir gab/
NK060(i)001:363: tshad ma gnyis kyi bdag pos 'byin no //
NK060(i)001:364: gsum pa sbas pa'i gsang ba la yang lnga/
NK060(i)001:371: spyod pa'i khyad par lnga gsum bco lnga la sogs pa sngags kyi spyod pa rnams/
NK060(i)001:375: gsang sngags sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa rnams la/
NK060(i)001:378: ma rtogs pa yis spyad gyur na //
NK060(i)001:379: yi dwags srin po'i gnas su skyes //
NK060(i)001:380: zhes sgra ji bzhin par spyad na skyon 'dug pa'i phyir sbas/
NK060(i)001:382: sngags kyi man ngag dang ldan pas 'byin no //
NK060(i)001:383: snying po zhes pa'i don la yang gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:386: bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po'o //
NK060(i)001:388: rgyud 'di nyid bstan pa'i byin rlabs kyis go phye nas bstan pa thams cad 'byung bas na rgyu'o //
NK060(i)001:389: de yang 'di nyid kyi gsum pa las/
NK060(i)001:390: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK060(i)001:391: dam tshig bsgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK060(i)001:392: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK060(i)001:393: phyogs bcu rnams su rab grags pa //
NK060(i)001:394: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK060(i)001:397: theg pa kun nas bsgrubs pa'i mthar gsang pa'i snying po 'di nyid mngon du byed dgos pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:399: sa rnams khyad par bkod par yang //
NK060(i)001:400: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK060(i)001:403: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK060(i)001:404: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK060(i)001:406: bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po ni/
NK060(i)001:407: gtan tshigs kyi sgo gang nas kyang /
NK060(i)001:411: smal/ gzhigs/ brtags/ gtan la phab kyang /
NK060(i)001:412: mthar thug de bzhin gshegs pa'i dgongs pa'i spyod yul ni/
NK060(i)001:413: snang spyod dang rtog tshogs thams cad sku dang ye
NK060(i)001:414: shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs
NK060(i)001:415: rgyas pa yin te/ rgyas pa las/
NK060(i)001:416: don bsdus gsung rab bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK060(i)001:417: de bas lhag pa'i don smra ba //
NK060(i)001:418: de ni rnam dag lam min te //
NK060(i)001:419: rang blo bsam pa 'khrul pa yin //
NK060(i)001:421: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK060(i)001:422: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK060(i)001:424: de kho na nyid ces pa'i don la yang gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:427: gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK060(i)001:428: de yang sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las/
NK060(i)001:429: rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa la //
NK060(i)001:430: de nyid ngo bo skabs kyis gsum //
NK060(i)001:433: rtog tshogs thams cad rang rig las mi gzhan pa'i
NK060(i)001:434: phyir snang stong gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi
NK060(i)001:435: dkyil 'khor la blo ma bcos par bzhag pa ni/
NK060(i)001:436: ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK060(i)001:437: de la skabs kyi rgyu'i de kho na nyid ces kyang tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK060(i)001:439: sku dang ye shes de nyid phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:440: mang por snang ba mngon du byung ba ni ma
NK060(i)001:441: nor ba ste/ de la skabs kyi 'bras bu'i de kho na nyid ces tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK060(i)001:443: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med kyi ye shes las shes bya'am bsgrub bya gzhan med pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:445: ji snyed brjod pa'i kha brgyud kyang //
NK060(i)001:446: yang dag don gyi snying po 'di //
NK060(i)001:447: gzhan nas btsal kyang mi rnyed de //
NK060(i)001:448: rang rig sgrib med dag pa yin //
NK060(i)001:451: dus bzhi'i phyogs bcu gang nas kyang //
NK060(i)001:452: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas brnyes mi 'gyur //
NK060(i)001:453: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK060(i)001:454: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma 'tshol zhig /ces pas gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK060(i)001:455: de la skabs kyi rgyu 'bras ro gcig pa'i de
NK060(i)001:456: kho na nyid ces kyang tha snyad du 'dogs so
NK060(i)001:457: // nges pa zhes pa'i don la yang gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:461: de yang 'grel pa spar khab las/
NK060(i)001:462: gzhi dang lam dang ngo bo yi //
NK060(i)001:463: nges pa rnam pa gsum du bshad //
NK060(i)001:466: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ste/
NK060(i)001:467: rang bzhin gyis nges pas gzhir nges pa zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:469: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK060(i)001:470: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK060(i)001:473: rgyud 'di ni nyid kyi lugs kyi 'bras bu la lam du byed pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:475: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK060(i)001:476: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK060(i)001:479: 'bras bu lam du gyur nas dus gcig mnyam par sbyor //
NK060(i)001:482: rgyud 'di nyid kyis rgyal ba'i dgongs pa mngon du ston pa'i phyir te/
NK060(i)001:484: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK060(i)001:485: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK060(i)001:487: gnyis pa nang ltar bshad pa la yang bzhi/
NK060(i)001:491: nges pa zhes pa'i don no //
NK060(i)001:492: gsang ba la yang dbye na gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:500: dgos ched ci'i phyir gsang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:502: rang bzhin bde ba'i ye shes de/
NK060(i)001:504: gdul bya blo 'khrul pa rnams la/
NK060(i)001:506: rang gsang thabs kyis chod pa'i tshul gyis gsang ste/
NK060(i)001:508: e ma ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK060(i)001:509: zhes pa la sogs pa sngar bzhin te/
NK060(i)001:511: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo na/
NK060(i)001:512: rtsa 'dab ma brgyad la rtsa ba'i 'dab ma bzhi ni/
NK060(i)001:513: g.yas na chos nyid kyi rtsa dbyibs zlum po/
NK060(i)001:517: lha min gyi sa bon yi ge su dang tri/
NK060(i)001:518: sbyong byed de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku'i snying po yi ge +amo gis mnan nas gnas so //
NK060(i)001:519: rgyab na ye shes kyi rtsa dbyibs gru bzhi/
NK060(i)001:522: sbyang bya lha dang mi'i sa bon yi ge a dang n+ri/
NK060(i)001:523: sbyong byed de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs kyi snying po yi ge h'u gis mnan nas gnas so //
NK060(i)001:524: g.yon na yon tan gyi rtsa dbyibs zla gam/
NK060(i)001:526: shes pa na nyon mongs pa can gyi yid/
NK060(i)001:527: sbyang bya yi dwags dang dmyal ba'i sa bon yi
NK060(i)001:528: ge pre dang duh sbyong byed de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK060(i)001:529: gsung gi snying po yi ge +aam gis mnan nas
NK060(i)001:530: so // mdun na las rang rgyud kyi rtsa dbyibs gru gsum/
NK060(i)001:532: de na sbyang bya dang sbyong byed kyi yi ge ni med de/
NK060(i)001:534: dmar nag mdog la lkog shol dbyibs //
NK060(i)001:535: de ni blun smug snod yin no //
NK060(i)001:537: de rnams kyi nang na rtsa'i dwangs ma dar dkar
NK060(i)001:538: gyi skud pa tsam gnas te 'byung ba sa'i khams
NK060(i)001:539: so // rtsa de'i nang na khrag gi dwangs ma
NK060(i)001:540: mtshal cog la ma bcag pa'i khu ba tsam gnas
NK060(i)001:542: de na dbugs kyi dwangs ma gser sa 'og tu
NK060(i)001:543: bcug pa'i rlangs tsam gnas te 'byung ba rlung gi
NK060(i)001:544: khams so // de na drod kyi dwangs ma me
NK060(i)001:545: long nyi ma la bzhag pa'i ngad tsam gnas te
NK060(i)001:547: de na 'od kyi dwangs ma kha dog sna tshogs
NK060(i)001:548: pa zhig gnas te 'byung ba nam mkha'i khams so
NK060(i)001:549: // de ltar dwangs ma lnga 'dus kyi dbus na
NK060(i)001:550: ye shes snying po'i thig le ye nas gnas kyang
NK060(i)001:551: // / ngo ma shes pas na ye nas gsang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:552: de dag sku dang ye shes su ma 'gags par
NK060(i)001:553: snang yang rang gi rang bsgribs te ngo ma shes
NK060(i)001:554: pa ni rang bzhin gyi gsang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:555: de nyid gnyis su med pa'i bde ba'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:556: nyams su myong dka' ba ni ngo bo nyid kyi
NK060(i)001:557: gsang ba'o // de rang gi rgyud la snang yang thabs lam gyi brtul zhugs kyis gzhan du tshol la/
NK060(i)001:558: btsal kyang gzhan nas mi rnyed pa ni shin tu gsang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:559: dgos ched ci'i phyir gsang na/
NK060(i)001:560: rang bzhin bde ba'i ye shes de spyod yul dang bral zhing rtogs dka' ba'i phyir gsang ngo //
NK060(i)001:561: gnyis pa gab pa'i gsang ba la yang /
NK060(i)001:565: dgos ched ci'i phyir gab pa dang bzhi las/
NK060(i)001:567: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes rgyu dang bcas pa de/
NK060(i)001:569: gzu lum can dang ras chod can la/
NK060(i)001:571: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes man ngag
NK060(i)001:572: dang lung du mi ldan pa rnams kyis ngos ma
NK060(i)001:573: zin pas nyams su myong dka' ba'i tshul du/
NK060(i)001:575: gzu lum can dang ras chod can dgag pa'i phyir du gab bo //
NK060(i)001:576: gsum pa sbas pa'i gsang ba la yang /
NK060(i)001:581: gang gis 'byin pa dang lnga las/
NK060(i)001:583: spyod pa'i khyad par lnga gsum bco lnga la sogs pa/
NK060(i)001:585: sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa rnams la/
NK060(i)001:586: tshul ni barda'am sgra'i tshul du/
NK060(i)001:588: sgra ji bzhin par spyad na ltung ba dang bcas par 'gyur ba'i phyir sbas so //
NK060(i)001:590: thabs lam steng sgo'i man ngag dang ldan pa'i bla mas 'byin no //
NK060(i)001:591: snying po zhes pa'i don la yang gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:594: bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po'o //
NK060(i)001:596: rtsa dang thig le de nyid bde ba'i ye shes skye ba'i rgyud yin pa'o //
NK060(i)001:598: thabs kyis bsgoms pas 'bras bu'i ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis mngon du byed pas so //
NK060(i)001:599: bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po ni/
NK060(i)001:600: thabs kyis bsgom pa las byung ba ltar snang yang
NK060(i)001:601: rang gi rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes su ye
NK060(i)001:602: nas gnas shing gsal bas so //
NK060(i)001:603: de kho na nyid ces pa la don gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:606: gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK060(i)001:607: ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid ni rtsa dang thig le bde ba dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:608: ye nas ma bcos par rang chas su gnas pa la blos ma bcos par 'jog pa'o //
NK060(i)001:609: de la skabs kyi rgyu'i de kho na nyid ces kyang tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK060(i)001:610: ma nor ba'i de kho na nyid ni de ka bsgrub bya'i don kho nar 'dug pas so //
NK060(i)001:611: de la 'bras bu'i de kho na nyid tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK060(i)001:612: gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid ni don
NK060(i)001:613: de dag kyang zhen pa'i stobs kyis gzhan du rtog
NK060(i)001:614: kyang rang las byung bas so //
NK060(i)001:615: de la rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa'i de kho na nyid ces kyang tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK060(i)001:616: nges pa zhes pa'i don la yang gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:621: bde ba'i ye shes don gyis gnas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:623: thabs kyis spyod pa'i dus de nyid kho na la lam du byed pa'o //
NK060(i)001:625: lhan skyes kyi ye shes ngos zin pa de las bsgrub bya logs na med pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:626: gsum pa mtshan gsang ba ltar bshad na/
NK060(i)001:630: nges ba zhes pa'i don dang bzhi las/
NK060(i)001:631: dang po gsang ba la yang gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:635: rang bzhin gyi gsang ba la bzhi/
NK060(i)001:639: dgos ched ci'i phyir gsang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:641: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes de/
NK060(i)001:643: gdul bya chags pa rang dga' mar spyod pa rnams la/
NK060(i)001:645: e ma ye nas gsang ba'i zhes pa la sogs pa gsang tshul bzhi'i sgo nas te/
NK060(i)001:646: de yang yab yum gyi thig le bde ba'i ro
NK060(i)001:647: dang bcas pa rang chas su yod pa ngo ma
NK060(i)001:649: de nyid la yab kyi rdo rje sku/
NK060(i)001:651: gsang ba'i rnam shes thugs su gnas kyang rtog pas bsgribs nas ngo ma shes pas na/
NK060(i)001:653: de gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo 'di 'drar bstan dka' bas na/
NK060(i)001:655: de nyid 'bras bu yin yang gzhan du tshol bas bsgribs te ngo ma shes pas na/
NK060(i)001:658: sgro skur can la phan gdags pa'i phyir gsang ngo //
NK060(i)001:659: gnyis pa gab pa'i gsang ba la yang /
NK060(i)001:663: dgos ched ci'i phyir gab pa dang bzhi las/
NK060(i)001:665: rang bzhin bde ba'i ye shes de/
NK060(i)001:667: gdul bya blo chung ba rnams la/
NK060(i)001:669: rang gsang thabs kyis chod pa'i tshul du/
NK060(i)001:671: phal pa rnams kyis yul ma yin pa'i phyir gab bo //
NK060(i)001:672: gsum pa sbas pa'i gsang ba la yang /
NK060(i)001:677: gang gis 'byin pa dang lnga las/
NK060(i)001:679: gsang sngags thabs kyis spyod pa rnams la/
NK060(i)001:681: blo chung sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa rnams la/
NK060(i)001:684: ga na la sogs pa'i barda'am sgra'i tshul du/
NK060(i)001:686: thabs lam rtogs dka' bas 'khrul pa 'byung ba'i skyon 'dug pa'i phyir sbas/
NK060(i)001:688: bla ma dam pa thabs lam gyi man ngag tshad dang ldan pas 'byin no //
NK060(i)001:689: snying po zhes pa la yang gsum/
NK060(i)001:694: yab yum gyi thig le rang byung gi ye shes
NK060(i)001:695: bcud dang ldan pa zhig 'byung zhing gnas pas na
NK060(i)001:697: byed pa sgom pa'i rlung thabs kyis bsgrubs shing nyams
NK060(i)001:698: su blangs pas lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes rtsal
NK060(i)001:699: rdzogs par rang la mnga' zhing 'char ba ni 'bras
NK060(i)001:700: bu'o // bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po ni/
NK060(i)001:701: yab yum gyi thig le bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes su bcud 'dus pa'o //
NK060(i)001:702: de kho na nyid ces pa'i don la'ang gsum/
NK060(i)001:705: gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK060(i)001:706: ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid ni/
NK060(i)001:707: rtsa dang thig le bde ba'i ro dang bcas pa
NK060(i)001:708: la blos ma bcos par rang bzhin gyis gnas pa
NK060(i)001:710: de ka la skabs kyi rgyu'i de kho na nyid ces kyang 'dogs so //
NK060(i)001:711: ma nor ba'i de kho na nyid ni/
NK060(i)001:712: de nyid thabs kyi lam gyis lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK060(i)001:713: ye shes mngon sum du gsal bas na ma nor
NK060(i)001:714: ba ste/ de la skabs kyi 'bras bu'i de kho na nyid ces kyang 'dogs so //
NK060(i)001:715: gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid ni/
NK060(i)001:716: de dag zhes pa'i skabs kyis bsgom pa las byung
NK060(i)001:717: ba ltar snang yang gzhan nas 'ongs pa ma yin
NK060(i)001:718: pas na gzhan ma yin pa ste/
NK060(i)001:719: de la skabs kyi rgyu 'bras ro gcig pa'i de kho na nyid ces kyang 'dogs so //
NK060(i)001:720: nges pa zhes pa'i don la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:725: rtsa dang thig le bde ba'i ro dang bcas pa ni rang bzhin nam gazhi'o //
NK060(i)001:727: thabs kyi rgyud kyi ngo bo de nyid lam du byed pas na lam mam thabs so //
NK060(i)001:729: lam des bskyed pa'i de kho na nyid kyi ye
NK060(i)001:730: shes de bzhin gshegs pa'i dgongs pa mngon du snang
NK060(i)001:732: 'o zhes pas bshad thabs phyi nang gsang ba gsum
NK060(i)001:733: po des gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i don lhag
NK060(i)001:734: ma ma lus par mtshan bstan pa tsam gyis yongs
NK060(i)001:736: bzhi pa mtshan gyi brgal lan la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:737: mtshan rgyud don yin min gyi/
NK060(i)001:738: mtshan du rgyud don 'dus ma 'dus kyi/
NK060(i)001:739: rgya skad mi smos par bod skad smos pa'i brgal lan no //
NK060(i)001:741: mtshan rgyud don yin nam min/
NK060(i)001:742: yin na gleng gzhi gleng bslang dgos med du thal/
NK060(i)001:743: gleng gzhi gleng bslang gi gong du rgyud don byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:744: mtshan rgyud don ma yin na/
NK060(i)001:745: dbang po yang rab kyis mtshan mthong ba la brten
NK060(i)001:746: nas rgyud don ji lta ba bzhin mi rtogs par
NK060(i)001:750: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK060(i)001:753: sgyu 'phrul snying po lung gi spyi //
NK060(i)001:754: lag gi rtsa bzhin dbu zhabs rtogs //
NK060(i)001:757: rab kyi don du mtshan bshad pa yang zhes pas gsal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:759: rje dri ngas pa nye'u ston chos kyi seng ge'i zhal nas/
NK060(i)001:761: gleng bslang nas rgyud don gsungs kyang /
NK060(i)001:762: mi'i yul du gsang ba'i bdag pos/
NK060(i)001:763: tshig dang yi ger 'god pa'i tshe/
NK060(i)001:764: blo rab 'bring gsum la dgongs nas mtshan klad du smos pas/
NK060(i)001:766: gleng gzhi gleng bslang dgos med du mi 'gyur gsung /
NK060(i)001:767: yang khyed na re mtshan rgyud don yin nam ma yin zer na/
NK060(i)001:768: mtshan gleng gzhi gleng bslang dgos 'brel gdams gtad kyang yin nam ma yin zhes mgo bsgre gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:769: rgya gab gong pa na re/
NK060(i)001:770: mtshan gleng gzhi gleng bslang rgyud don dgos 'brel gdams gtad kun gyi don yin pas/
NK060(i)001:771: rgyud don yin min gyi rtsod gzhi rang mi dgos gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:772: kho bo ni 'di ltar sems te/
NK060(i)001:773: ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs kyi mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud don ni/
NK060(i)001:774: sems can thams cad kyi sems kyi chos nyid rang
NK060(i)001:775: bzhin bde pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen
NK060(i)001:776: por ye nas sangs rgyas pa de yin la/
NK060(i)001:777: mtshon byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud don ni/
NK060(i)001:778: yi ge dang ming dang tshig gi tshogs glegs bam
NK060(i)001:779: du bris pa'i rgyud dbu zhabs thams cad kyang yin
NK060(i)001:780: no // de gnyis ka'i mtshan don ldan thun mong du btags pa ni/
NK060(i)001:781: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'o zhes pa ste/
NK060(i)001:782: mdor na rgyud kyi don ni rtog dka' ba dang /
NK060(i)001:785: the tshom dang bral ba dang /
NK060(i)001:786: de dag las don gzhan lhag ma med pa'o //
NK060(i)001:791: nges pa'i don mtshon par byed pa'i ming yin gyis/
NK060(i)001:792: ming gi don mtshon par nus pa tsam gyis ming de/
NK060(i)001:793: don rang gi ngo bo yin pa'i khyab pa med do //
NK060(i)001:795: mtshan du rgyud don 'dus sam ma 'dus/
NK060(i)001:796: 'dus na rgyud don la bcu yod pas sbyor dang /
NK060(i)001:797: ma 'dus na blo yang rab kyis kyang mtshan thos
NK060(i)001:798: pas rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don mi rtogs par 'gyur
NK060(i)001:800: rgyud don yongs su shes byed kyi dngos po bcu
NK060(i)001:801: po bye brag tu phye la mtshan dang dngos su
NK060(i)001:802: brang sprad la sbyar rgyud med kyang mtshan gyi don
NK060(i)001:803: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du gnas pas der rgyud
NK060(i)001:804: don 'dus so // dngos su gsal bar ma byung
NK060(i)001:805: ba ni dbang po yang rab kyi don gtso che
NK060(i)001:806: don 'dus so // ba yin no // zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:807: rgya gab gong pa na re/
NK060(i)001:808: tshod ma la tsh+wa blta na 'thung ma zin pa'i gong rol du blta ba yin/
NK060(i)001:809: tshod ma 'thung zin na tsh+wa blta rgyud med pa bzhin mtshan rgyud don yin par grub zin nas/
NK060(i)001:810: mtshan yang rgyud don 'dus ma 'dus kyi rtsod pa mi dgos gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:812: rgyud gzhung 'di la rgya skad ma byung bas bod mar 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:817: sdud pa po tshig gi gnyer/
NK060(i)001:818: sgra sgyur pa'i lo ts+aa ba'i gnyer dang bzhi yin pa las/
NK060(i)001:819: 'dir lo ts+aa ba rma rin chen mchog gis tshig
NK060(i)001:820: nyung bar bya ba'i phyir rgya skad klad du ma
NK060(i)001:821: bkod la/ don myur du ngos zin par bya ba'i
NK060(i)001:822: phyir bod skad bod pas bod mar 'gyur ba'i khyab
NK060(i)001:823: bkod la/ med la/ tshig spros la dga' ba 'ga'
NK060(i)001:824: zhig gis sa bod du brtsams pa'i bstan bcos rnams
NK060(i)001:825: bkod la/ med la/ la'ang / rgya skad klad du
NK060(i)001:826: bkod pa du ma yod de des rgya gar mar
NK060(i)001:828: mdor na rtogs ldan chos kyi rjes su 'jug pa rnams ni/
NK060(i)001:829: rton pa bzhi'i rjes su 'brang bar rigs kyis/
NK060(i)001:830: gyi na'i brgal lan don chung bar rig par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:833: de yang byed pa'i mu dang sbyar te bshad na/
NK060(i)001:837: dgos ched gang gi phyir btsal ba dang bzhi las/
NK060(i)001:838: dang po phyag gang gis btsal zhe na/
NK060(i)001:840: sdud pa pos tshig gnyer ba de'i tshe/
NK060(i)001:841: rang gi ston pa la mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK060(i)001:843: phyag sdud pa pos btsal bar bzhed mod kyis/
NK060(i)001:844: kho bo ni rgyud gzhung spyi dang bstun na sdud
NK060(i)001:845: pa po'i tshig /e bam ma ya zhes pa man
NK060(i)001:847: yi ge pas rgyud gzhung yi ger 'dri ba'i tshe
NK060(i)001:848: rang gi 'dod pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal pa'i tshig
NK060(i)001:850: des na yi ge pa'i rkyen gyis nang pa'i gzhung
NK060(i)001:851: 'ga' zhig tu lha dbang phyug chen po la sogs
NK060(i)001:853: phyi rol pa'i gzhung 'ga' zhig tu 'jam dpal gzhon
NK060(i)001:854: nu la sogs pa la btsal ba la yang snang
NK060(i)001:855: ngo // mdor na rgyud gzhung spyi'i lugs kyi phyag
NK060(i)001:856: 'tshal pa'i tshig yi ge pas gzhung don yi ger
NK060(i)001:858: mtshan klad du lo ts+aa bas sgra bsgyur ba'i tshe 'god pa yin par sems so //
NK060(i)001:860: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la ste/
NK060(i)001:861: de'i don rgyas par bshad na bcom zhes pas phrin las kyi mtshan te/
NK060(i)001:862: de yang sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i le'u don gnyis pa las/
NK060(i)001:863: bdud sde tshar gcod ces bya ba'i dam tshig ni/
NK060(i)001:864: nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par dag /phung po lnga nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NK060(i)001:865: bdag nyid lha yi dkyil 'khor te //
NK060(i)001:866: skyi shi med pa'i g.yung drung gnas //
NK060(i)001:868: nyon mongs pa lnga nyid ma spangs ye shes lnga'i ngo bor mngon du gyur pa ni/
NK060(i)001:869: nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom pa ste/
NK060(i)001:870: phrin las dang sbyar na zhi ba'i phung po lnga
NK060(i)001:871: nyid ma spangs rigs lnga'i ngo bor mngon du gyur
NK060(i)001:872: pa ni/ phung po'i bdud bcom pa ste/
NK060(i)001:873: phrin las dang sbyar na rgyas pa'i/
NK060(i)001:874: sems nyid skye 'chi med pa'i don mngon du gyur pa ni/
NK060(i)001:875: 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom pa ste/
NK060(i)001:876: phrin las dang sbyar na dbang gi/
NK060(i)001:877: lha dang rtog pa gnyis su med pa'i don mngon du gyur pa ni/
NK060(i)001:878: lha'i bu'i bdud bcom pa ste/
NK060(i)001:879: phrin las dang sbyar na drag po'i phrin las so //
NK060(i)001:880: de yang rdo rje las rim las/
NK060(i)001:881: bdud bzhi la sogs rig pa'i gdeng gis bcom //
NK060(i)001:883: ldan zhes pa yon tan gyi mtshan te/
NK060(i)001:884: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'am nyi shu
NK060(i)001:885: rtsa lnga la sogs pa thugs rang rig pa'i ye
NK060(i)001:886: shes la rang bzhin gyis ldan pa ste/
NK060(i)001:888: sku lnga la sogs yon tan brjod las 'das //
NK060(i)001:890: 'das zhes pa mtshan nyid kyi mtshan te/
NK060(i)001:891: gong gi yon tan de thams cad kyang yod med
NK060(i)001:892: rtag chad skye 'gag 'gro 'ong gi mtha' thams cad
NK060(i)001:893: las 'das pas te/ rdo rje las rim las/
NK060(i)001:894: rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med //
NK060(i)001:897: mtshan nyid mtha' rnams kun bral ba //
NK060(i)001:899: dpal zhes pa ni che ba'i mtshan te/
NK060(i)001:900: thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i dpal gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:901: thun mong gi dpal ni 'jig rten na bud med
NK060(i)001:902: khyo nor du 'dzom pa la mo dpal mo che
NK060(i)001:904: 'jig rten gyi dge legs phun sum tshogs pa la bya ste/
NK060(i)001:905: stong 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po la sogs pa thob pa ni thun mong gi dpal yin la/
NK060(i)001:906: thun mong ma yin pa'i dpal ni gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:907: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i/
NK060(i)001:909: thugs rje chen po zhor la 'byung ba'i dpal lo //
NK060(i)001:910: de la rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dpal ni/
NK060(i)001:911: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor bden gsum ris med du lhun gyis grub pa ste/
NK060(i)001:912: chos spyi skad dang bstun na/
NK060(i)001:913: chos kyi dbyings shin tu dri ma med pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po'o //
NK060(i)001:914: rig pa rang snang ba'i dpal ni/
NK060(i)001:915: gzhi chos dbyings shin tu dri med de nyid mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu ni/
NK060(i)001:916: kun tu 'od kyi sa ste rgyud mthun zab pa'i chos sku'o //
NK060(i)001:917: de ka la rtogs pa bdag gi dpal zhes kyang tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK060(i)001:918: thugs rje chen po zhor la 'byung ba'i dpal ni/
NK060(i)001:919: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor zhi
NK060(i)001:920: khro'i mdzad pa cir yang mi 'gag bas gdul bya
NK060(i)001:921: gang la gang 'dul de la der bstan nas 'gro
NK060(i)001:922: ba'i don rgyud chad med par 'byung ba ni/
NK060(i)001:924: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa ste/
NK060(i)001:926: de ka la thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal zhes tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK060(i)001:927: kun tu bzang po zhes pa/
NK060(i)001:928: rang gi ngo bo'i mtshan te 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK060(i)001:929: thams cad de nyid dang gzhan du brjod du med
NK060(i)001:930: pa'i don mngon du byas pas spyod yul yongs su
NK060(i)001:931: dag cing blang dor dang bral ba'o //
NK060(i)001:934: 'ga' zhig gnas gzhi mtshon par 'dod mod kyi/
NK060(i)001:935: kho bo ni sgra'i gnas brgyad las bzhi pa dgos ched kyi sgras mtshams sbyar bar sems so //
NK060(i)001:936: tshul ji lta btsal na phyag 'tshal lo zhes pa ste/
NK060(i)001:940: tha ma mos gus kyi phyag go //
NK060(i)001:943: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag dang //
NK060(i)001:944: ji ltar mar la mar bzhag bzhin //
NK060(i)001:945: rang gis rang gi ye shes gang //
NK060(i)001:948: sgom pa goms pa'i phyag ni/
NK060(i)001:949: lus zhing gi rdul snyed du sprul nas/
NK060(i)001:950: rdul gcig gi steng na rdul snyed kyi sangs rgyas
NK060(i)001:951: bsam gyis mi khyab pa brjod kyis mi lang ba
NK060(i)001:952: rnams la dus gcig tu 'tshal na ni ting nge
NK060(i)001:955: ming gzhan 'phrul dag'i phyag ces kyang grags so //
NK060(i)001:957: lus kyi sgo nas gnas lnga sa la gtugs/
NK060(i)001:958: ngag gi sgo nas dbyangs dang bstod par bcas/
NK060(i)001:959: yid kyi sgo nas mos gus gdung sems dang ldan pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:960: skabs 'dir phyag 'tshal ba po sdud pa po yin na ni lta ba mjal ba'i phyag tu rigs te/
NK060(i)001:961: ston sdud dgongs pa dbyer med du bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:962: gzhan du na ji ltar rigs so //
NK060(i)001:964: ston pa gzhan las khyad par du gyur pa la ngam pa'i phyir dang /
NK060(i)001:967: yi ger 'bri ba la sogs pa'i tshe ya rabs
NK060(i)001:968: kyi tshul mi nyams par bya ba'i phyir 'tshal lo
NK060(i)001:969: // gzhung gi don la bka' rang lugs kyis sa bcad na/
NK060(i)001:970: le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod pa las/
NK060(i)001:972: slob dpon 'grel pa gdams ngag mkhan gyis sa bcad na/
NK060(i)001:979: de ltar gleng gzhi ston par byed pa'i le'u dang po 'di la/
NK060(i)001:980: 'chad mkhan rig pa'i sgros kyis sa bcad na gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:984: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gazhi'am gleng gzhi mdor bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:985: rgyud khyad par gyi gleng gazhi'am gleng gzhi rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK060(i)001:989: 'di la 'grel pa spar khab kyis gsang ba ltar
NK060(i)001:990: kho na las ma bshad kyang bla ma brgyud pa'i
NK060(i)001:991: gsung sgros kyi rjes su 'brangs nas phyi nang gsang
NK060(i)001:993: de yang phyir ltar gzhung rgyas pa dang sbyar te bshad pa ni/
NK060(i)001:994: 'di zhes pas gnas phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:995: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med ces pa nas/
NK060(i)001:996: pad+ma rin po che'i gdan la zhes pa'i bar dang sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:997: skad ces pas ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:998: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:999: rang bzhin te zhes pa'i bar gyis ston pa'i rang bzhin dang /
NK060(i)001:1000: sku mdun dang zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:1001: dbu gsum dang ldan pa zhes pa'i bar gyis ston pa'i ngo bo dang sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:1002: bshad ces pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1003: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:1004: gnyis su med par bzhugs so zhes pa'i bar dang sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:1006: bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1007: ston pa'i thugs la rgyud don yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1008: dus na zhes pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1009: ston 'khor gnas gsum nam 'dzom pa'i dus de nyid gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:1010: ye shes rdzogs pa'i rgyud las/
NK060(i)001:1011: gnas dang ston pa 'khor tshogs ni //
NK060(i)001:1012: dus dang sdud pa shugs las 'byung //
NK060(i)001:1014: nang ltar thabs lam steng sgo dang sbyar te/
NK060(i)001:1016: 'di zhes pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1019: 'od gzhi e sogs dbyibs su gnas //
NK060(i)001:1021: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab brgyad de/
NK060(i)001:1022: g.yas chos nyid kyi rtsa dbyibs zlum po 'od dkar po zhi ba'i gnas/
NK060(i)001:1023: rgyab ye shes kyi rtsa gru bzhi ser po rgyas pa'i gnas/
NK060(i)001:1024: g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa zla gam dmar po dbang gi gnas/
NK060(i)001:1025: mdun las rang rgyud kyi rtsa dbyibs gru gsum 'od dmar nag drag po'i gnas so //
NK060(i)001:1026: skad ces pas ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1028: mi shigs thig le wam dbyibs can //
NK060(i)001:1029: rang la bde ba gsal byed dag /ces pas/
NK060(i)001:1030: srog mi shigs pa'i thig le dwangs ma lnga 'dus
NK060(i)001:1031: kyi ngo bo thig le zlum po yi ge wam
NK060(i)001:1032: gyi dbyibs can de rang la bde ba gsal bar
NK060(i)001:1034: bshad ces pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1036: ma nu rnam shes yid sogs bzhi //
NK060(i)001:1037: ye shes myong bas sdus par bshad //
NK060(i)001:1039: yid la sogs pa'i sems rnam par shes pa tshogs
NK060(i)001:1040: brgyad ye shes lngar gsal bar nyams su myong bas
NK060(i)001:1041: bshad pa dang 'dra bas na 'khor ro //
NK060(i)001:1042: pa'i zhes pa bston pa phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1044: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pa //
NK060(i)001:1045: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK060(i)001:1047: pa p+aa ra mi ta'i sgra las drangs na/
NK060(i)001:1048: don dam pa byang chub kyi sems/
NK060(i)001:1049: ma ma h+aa yan theg pa chen po ste/
NK060(i)001:1050: de nyams su blangs pas ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs can skyes pa ni bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1051: dus na zhes pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1053: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK060(i)001:1054: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK060(i)001:1056: ye shes skyes pa'i dus su gsum du 'dzin pa
NK060(i)001:1057: med pa ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus te
NK060(i)001:1058: dus so // gsang ba ltar rdzogs rim 'og sgo dang sbyar te bshad na/
NK060(i)001:1059: 'di zhes pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1061: 'di zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni //
NK060(i)001:1062: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyibs can gnas //
NK060(i)001:1064: yum gyi mkha' phyi khyams gru gsum drag po'i gnas/
NK060(i)001:1065: bar khyabs gru bzhi rgyas pa'i gnas/
NK060(i)001:1066: skye gnas zla gam dbang gi gnas/
NK060(i)001:1067: dbyings phyug gi sna rtse zlum po zhi ba'i gnas so //
NK060(i)001:1069: khyams dang sgo dang bya'i gdong dang za ma tog rnams/
NK060(i)001:1070: drag rgyas zhi dbang du gnas pa ni sangs rgyas ril gyi bzhugs gnas su gsungs so zhes so //
NK060(i)001:1071: skad ces pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1073: skad ces gsal byed las ming can //
NK060(i)001:1074: bam dbyibs thig ler bcas ston pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1076: yab kyi gsang ba rdo rje'i dbul kun rdzob ye
NK060(i)001:1077: shes kyi thig le yi ge bam gyi dbyibs su
NK060(i)001:1078: rdzogs pas/ rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis
NK060(i)001:1079: 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i byed pa po yin pa dang
NK060(i)001:1080: rdzogs pas/ / thig le de nyid kyis bde ba gsal bar byed pas na ston pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1082: gu h+ya badz+ra dbur rdzogs pa'i thig le dang bcas
NK060(i)001:1083: pa ni ma lus pa'i byed pa po'i phyir ston
NK060(i)001:1084: pa'o zhes so // bshad ces pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1086: ma da ma nu sdom byed yid //
NK060(i)001:1087: las can rnam shes de dag la //
NK060(i)001:1088: gsal bar go bas bshad par 'dod //
NK060(i)001:1091: ma/ ma ta na sdom pa/
NK060(i)001:1093: ma/ ma nu na yid de/
NK060(i)001:1094: bde ba sdom par byed pa/
NK060(i)001:1095: yid la sogs pa'i rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ni 'khor ro //
NK060(i)001:1097: ma nu ma da na sdom byed de/
NK060(i)001:1098: sems lngas gleng bslang ba'i las kyis/
NK060(i)001:1100: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK060(i)001:1101: rdo rje mthong ba la sogs pa phyin ci ma log par go ba ni/
NK060(i)001:1102: brjod pa dang 'dra ba'i phyir 'khor la bshad do bar tha snyad 'dogs so //
NK060(i)001:1103: pa'i zhes pa bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1105: pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK060(i)001:1106: ya na theg chen 'dir yin te //
NK060(i)001:1109: pa/ pa ra m+aar+tha don dam pa/
NK060(i)001:1110: ya na na theg pa chen po dga' ba bcu
NK060(i)001:1111: drug gi mtha' mar rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK060(i)001:1112: bde ba'i ye shes lhangs kyis nyams su myong ba
NK060(i)001:1113: ni/ rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don yin te de ni bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1116: pa/ p+aa ta ma ta na don dam pa byang chub
NK060(i)001:1117: kyi sems te sems lnga'i mtha' ma skad cig ma
NK060(i)001:1118: bcu drug gi byang chub sems mtha' ma reg pa
NK060(i)001:1119: ni/ ma h+aa ya na theg pa chen po ste rgyud 'adi'o zhes so //
NK060(i)001:1120: dus na zhes pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1122: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab dus //
NK060(i)001:1123: n+aa ma de ming zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:1125: mkha' gsang la bde ba skyes pa'i tshe na dus
NK060(i)001:1126: phyogs gcig tu brjod du mi btub ste snga phyi
NK060(i)001:1127: 'dzin pa'i rtog pa dang bral bas bsam gyis mi
NK060(i)001:1129: n+aa ma de ming zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:1131: dus de la bab pa'i ming can nam/
NK060(i)001:1132: yang na kun la 'jug pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1139: de'i dus ni gcig tu brjod du med pas bsam
NK060(i)001:1140: gyis mi khyab pa'i dus zhes tha snyad du 'dogs
NK060(i)001:1142: 'di dag thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhir 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ni/
NK060(i)001:1143: mthar lam pa dang gdul bya chags pa can gyi dbang du gsungs pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:1145: de ni gdul bya las tha ma pa rnams kyi
NK060(i)001:1146: don gyi phyir thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gazhi'o
NK060(i)001:1147: zhes gsungs so // de ltar bshad pa'i thun mong
NK060(i)001:1148: ma yin pa'i gleng gazhi'am gleng gzhi mdor bstan pa'i
NK060(i)001:1149: zhes gsungs so // skabs 'dir/ kha cig na re/
NK060(i)001:1150: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud 'di la log pa'i ston bzhi yod de/
NK060(i)001:1151: rgyud gzhan na 'di skad thos bya ba yod pa la/
NK060(i)001:1152: 'dir 'di skad bshad bya ba byung bas gleng gzhi log /gzhan na dus gsum du yod pa las/
NK060(i)001:1153: 'dir dus bzhi byung ba dus log /
NK060(i)001:1154: rgyud kyi bdag po kun tu bzang po yin pa
NK060(i)001:1155: la dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bor rdo rje sems dpa'
NK060(i)001:1156: byung bas dkyil 'khor log /sgrub pa'i zhag dang tshes
NK060(i)001:1157: grangs ni // rgyud las smos pa bzhin du bshad //
NK060(i)001:1158: ces kha 'phangs pas rgyud log go zhe na/
NK060(i)001:1159: skabs 'dir gleng gzhi log pa'i skyon spang ba ni/
NK060(i)001:1160: glan chab bar pa na re/
NK060(i)001:1161: pho re ba dang spyang slong ba //
NK060(i)001:1162: tshig la mi mthun don la mthun //
NK060(i)001:1164: byi'u gson po la rten byas nas slong ba dang /
NK060(i)001:1165: spyang ki shi ba'i gsob la brten nas slong ba gnyis/
NK060(i)001:1166: gnas skabs rten dang brten bshad gnyis ka mi mthun yang /
NK060(i)001:1167: don slong ba la mthun pa bzhin bshad pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1168: thos pa gnyis tshig mi mthun kyang ston pas 'khor la bshad pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1169: 'khor gyis ston pa la thos pa don mthun gsung /
NK060(i)001:1170: mda' tig chos sh+aaka na re/
NK060(i)001:1171: thos bya ba 'khor gyi tshig yin te/
NK060(i)001:1172: ma rtogs log rtogs the tshom gsum dang bcas pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:1173: bshad bya ba ston pa'i tshig yin pas ma rtogs
NK060(i)001:1174: log rtogs the tshom gsum dang bral bas rgyud 'di
NK060(i)001:1175: gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa yin gsungs/
NK060(i)001:1176: rje sgro phug pa na re/
NK060(i)001:1177: sku gnyis kyis bstan pa'i khyad par yin te/
NK060(i)001:1178: longs sku'i tshig tu mi gsung bas rna bas thos
NK060(i)001:1179: su med pa'i phyir bshad bya bar 'ong ba yin
NK060(i)001:1180: la/ sprul skus tshig tu gsungs pas rna bas thos
NK060(i)001:1181: su yod pa'i phyir thos zhes bya bar 'ong ba
NK060(i)001:1182: la/ yin te/ spar khab las/
NK060(i)001:1183: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK060(i)001:1184: rdo rje mthong ba la sogs pas phyin ci ma
NK060(i)001:1185: log par go ba ni brjod pa dang 'dra ba'i
NK060(i)001:1186: phyir 'khor la bshad do bar tha snyad du 'dogs
NK060(i)001:1188: nye'u ston chos kyi seng ge na re/
NK060(i)001:1190: dgongs pa brda'i bshad pa sdud pa pos ma phri ma bsnan bar mi yul du bshad pas/
NK060(i)001:1191: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhir gsungs pa yin pas/
NK060(i)001:1192: bshad ces pa la gleng gzhi log pa'i skyon med gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:1193: kho bo'i bla ma zur thams cad mkhyen pa ni 'di ltar du bzhed de/
NK060(i)001:1194: ston pa longs skus gsungs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK060(i)001:1195: sprul skus gsungs pa'i bka' du ma na/
NK060(i)001:1196: la la na 'di skad bshad pa'i dus na zhes pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1197: la la na 'di skad bstan pa'i dus na zhes pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1198: la la ni 'di skad bsgo ba bdag gis thos pa'i dus na zhes pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1199: phal cher na 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus
NK060(i)001:1200: gcig na zhes pa la sogs pa du ma snang
NK060(i)001:1201: yang / rgyud gzhung thams cad kyi legs par sbyar ba'i skad la e wam ma ya bya ba las/
NK060(i)001:1202: bshad dang thos la sogs pa'i rnam dbye 'di ni mthun pa med do //
NK060(i)001:1203: 'on kyang de'i don lo ts+aa bas bod skad du bsgyur ba'i dus su/
NK060(i)001:1204: rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don la brtags pas/
NK060(i)001:1205: rgyud gzhung de'i lugs kyis ston sdud kyi dgongs pa
NK060(i)001:1206: la khyad par med par bstan pa'i gzhung lugs su
NK060(i)001:1207: 'dug na/ bshad la sogs pa ra bsgyur ba dang /
NK060(i)001:1208: ston sdud kyi dgongs pa la khyad par yod par
NK060(i)001:1209: bstan pa'i gzhung lugs su 'dug na thos pa la
NK060(i)001:1210: sogs par bsgyur bar mngon te/
NK060(i)001:1211: de'i khyad kyis thog ma ni thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:1212: phyi ma ni thun mong gi gleng gzhi yin no //
NK060(i)001:1213: de yang thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi ltar na/
NK060(i)001:1214: 'di skad bshad la sogs pa bsgyur ba'i dgos ched ni/
NK060(i)001:1215: sdud pa pos ston pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1216: dgongs pa tha dad med par khas blangs nas nyid
NK060(i)001:1217: las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor la bshad pa mtshon pa'o
NK060(i)001:1218: // de la yang nyid dgos gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:1219: ston pas 'khor la rgyud 'chad pa'i sngon du dbang bskur bas/
NK060(i)001:1220: ston 'khor dgongs pa gnyis su med par gyur pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:1221: bstan pa 'di dgongs pa'i zhe phugs yin par mtshon pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1222: bstan pa thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1224: sdud pa po dbang thob pa drug pa nyid dang
NK060(i)001:1225: gnyis su med par gyur ba'i phyir thos pa la
NK060(i)001:1226: ma ltos par mtshon pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1227: sdud pa po thun mongs ma yin pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1228: dus na zhes dus gcig kho nar ma smos pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:1229: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid mtshon pa ste dus thun mong ma yin pa'i che ba'i mtshon pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1230: de las gzhan pa thun mong gi gleng gzhi ltar na/
NK060(i)001:1231: 'di skad thos bya ba la sogs par bsgyur ba'i
NK060(i)001:1232: dgos ched ni sdud pa pos ston pa'i dgongs pa
NK060(i)001:1233: dang khyad par yod par khas blangs nas lhan cig
NK060(i)001:1234: pa dang go phye ba'i 'khor gyi don du ston
NK060(i)001:1235: pa nyid la thos pa mtshon pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1236: de la nying dgos bdun te/
NK060(i)001:1237: 'di skad thos zhes bka'i don sgro skur dang bral bar mtshon pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1238: yang bdag gis thos zhes sdud pa po ston pa ma yin par mtshon pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1239: yang bdag gis thos zhes gzhan la ma brgyud par
NK060(i)001:1240: sdud pa po bdag rang gis thos pas sdud pa
NK060(i)001:1241: po tshad ma nyid du mtshon pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1242: yang dus gcig na thos zhes dus thams cad du
NK060(i)001:1243: ma smos pas bka'i don 'byung bar dka' bar mtshon
NK060(i)001:1244: pa dang / yang dus gcig na zhes 'dir 'di thos la/
NK060(i)001:1245: gzhan du gzhan kyang thos pas sdud pa po thos pa che bar mtshon pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1246: yang dus gcig nas zhes ma yengs par thos pas
NK060(i)001:1247: sdud pa po dgongs pa dang ldan par mtshon pa
NK060(i)001:1248: dang / yang dus gcig na zhes yang dang yang
NK060(i)001:1249: du ma smos par dus gcig gis chud pas sdud
NK060(i)001:1250: pa po shes rab mtshon pa'i dgos pa yod do
NK060(i)001:1251: dang / // rgyu mtshan de dag gi phyir tshul 'di dag khong du chud par byas la/
NK060(i)001:1252: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' dri ma med pa la the tshom dang som nyi mi bya'o //
NK060(i)001:1253: yang la la dag na re/
NK060(i)001:1254: mdor bstan gyi rjes su rgyas bshad 'jug gam mi 'jug /mi 'jug na/
NK060(i)001:1255: mdor bstan don med du thal lo //
NK060(i)001:1256: 'jug na gleng gzhi mdor bstan pa lnga byung la/
NK060(i)001:1257: rgyas bshad la gsum las ma byung ba gang lags zer na/
NK060(i)001:1258: mdor bstan gyi rjes su rgyas bshad 'jug go //
NK060(i)001:1259: gong gi skyon mi yong ngam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:1260: bstan pa ni ston pa'i thugs la rdzogs shing /
NK060(i)001:1261: dus ni ston 'khor gnas gsum nam 'dzom pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1262: sngar bshad pa'i ye shes rdzogs pa'i lung gis gsal lo //
NK060(i)001:1263: gnyis pa rgyud khyad par gyi gleng gazhi'am gleng gzhi rgyas par bstan pa la spyi don gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:1264: gang gis gsungs pa'i ston pa/
NK060(i)001:1266: gang la gsungs pa'i 'khor phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1267: spyi don dang po la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:1269: ston pa'i rang bzhin bdun bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:1271: 'di la 'grel pa spar khab kyi lugs kyis/
NK060(i)001:1272: rgyal ba drug pa'i yon tan mtha' yas pa yang mdor bdun du 'du ste/
NK060(i)001:1274: ston pa'i rang bzhin bdun du bshad/
NK060(i)001:1275: khog gzhung gsal ba'i sgron me las/
NK060(i)001:1276: ston pa'i rang bzhin brgyad dang ldan/
NK060(i)001:1277: byed pa rdo rje de bzhin te //
NK060(i)001:1279: ston pa'i rang bzhin brgyad du bshad/
NK060(i)001:1280: 'grel chung pin tar tha ltar na/
NK060(i)001:1281: byang chub mchog gi ngo bo dang //
NK060(i)001:1282: chos rnams rol pa'i longs spyod dang //
NK060(i)001:1283: phyogs dus bde gshegs bdag po dang //
NK060(i)001:1284: chos so cog dang dbyer med pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1286: ston pa'i rang bzhin bzhir bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:1287: bla ma brgyud pa'i gdams ngag ltar na/
NK060(i)001:1288: ston pa mya ngan las 'das pa dang dbyer mi phyed pa'i rang bzhin dang /
NK060(i)001:1289: ston pa 'khor dang dbyer mi phyed pa'i rang bzhin gnyis su bzhed do //
NK060(i)001:1290: de la gzhung gi steng du 'bru bsnan na/
NK060(i)001:1291: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes bya ba'i de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1292: de zhes pa snyeg pa'i tshig /gang la snyeg na
NK060(i)001:1293: gzhi shes bya gshis kyi gnas lugs ji lta ba
NK060(i)001:1294: bzhin du'o // gang zhe na ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid skye med kyi gshis/
NK060(i)001:1295: ma nor ba'i de bzhin nyid 'gag med kyi gdangs/
NK060(i)001:1296: gnyis su med pa'i de bzhin nyid dbyer med kyi ngang /
NK060(i)001:1297: lhun gyis grub pa'i de bzhin nyid blo'i spyod yul
NK060(i)001:1298: las 'das pa de nyid nar son zhing de'i ngo
NK060(i)001:1299: bor gyur bas na gshegs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1300: de ka la 'grel pa spar khab ltar ston pa'i rang bzhin bdun gyi dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:1301: de bzhin nyid du nar son pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:1302: yang dag par rdzogs pa zhes pa ni/
NK060(i)001:1303: gnyis med kyi ye shes la spang bya med pas
NK060(i)001:1304: yang dag par 'bras bu lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i don
NK060(i)001:1305: no // de ka yon tan ma btsal bar lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:1307: yang dag pa'i rang bzhin dang /
NK060(i)001:1308: rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin gnyis su bzhed do //
NK060(i)001:1310: sa pa la sogs pa'i lta ba ngan pa sangs
NK060(i)001:1311: nas rang byung gi ye shes kun tu gdal te
NK060(i)001:1312: ye shes bla ma'i sa non pas na rgyas pa
NK060(i)001:1313: ste de ka ye shes mtha' dbus dang bral ba'i
NK060(i)001:1314: rang bzhin no // bcom ldan 'das zhes pa'i 'bru rgyas par phyag gi skabs su bshad zin la/
NK060(i)001:1315: bsdus pa tsam bshad na bdud bzhi bcom/
NK060(i)001:1316: che ba'i yon tan dang ldan/
NK060(i)001:1317: mtshan nyid kyi mtha' kun las 'das pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1318: de ka 'bras bu la mnga' mdzad kyang ngo bor 'di 'drar bstan du med pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:1319: de yan chod ni 'grel chung pin tar tha ltar na/
NK060(i)001:1320: byang chub mchog gi ngo bo dang //
NK060(i)001:1322: longs spyod chen po zhes pa ni/
NK060(i)001:1323: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i dngos po
NK060(i)001:1324: gnyis la longs spyod bzhin du blang dor gyi spyod
NK060(i)001:1325: yul dang bral zhing gzhan las khyad par du gyur
NK060(i)001:1327: de ka mnyam pa nyid du mngon du mdzad kyang spyod yul dang bral ba'i rang bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:1328: 'di ni 'grel chung pin tar tha ltar na/
NK060(i)001:1329: chos rnams rol par longs spyod dang //
NK060(i)001:1331: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK060(i)001:1332: kyi sku dang gsungs dang thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid
NK060(i)001:1333: ces pa ni/ spar khab las/
NK060(i)001:1334: tha snyad gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK060(i)001:1335: ril gyi yon tan brjod pa las 'das pa yang
NK060(i)001:1336: mdor bsdu na nyi shu rtsa lngar 'dus te zhes
NK060(i)001:1337: gsungs pas/ phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i de
NK060(i)001:1338: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rten byed pa'i ngos
NK060(i)001:1340: brda sprod pa'i ngos nas gsung lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:1341: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ngos nas thugs lnga/
NK060(i)001:1342: 'di na med kyis kyang lung gra chad pa nyal ba bslang ba bshad pa mkhan po'i gnyer yin pas/
NK060(i)001:1343: 'dod dgu 'byung ba'i ngos nas yon tan lnga/
NK060(i)001:1344: bya ba byed pa'i ngos nas phrin las lnga/
NK060(i)001:1345: de ltar sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'am
NK060(i)001:1346: nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs pa bsam gyis mi
NK060(i)001:1347: khyab pa thams cad kyang rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed
NK060(i)001:1348: pa rdo rje'i bdag nyid du gcig pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:1349: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po ste/
NK060(i)001:1350: drug pa kun tu bzang po'o //
NK060(i)001:1351: de bzhin du phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i
NK060(i)001:1352: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK060(i)001:1353: yon tan phrin las lnga'am nyi shu rtsa lnga la
NK060(i)001:1354: sogs pa thams cad kyang mtshan nyid skye 'jig dang
NK060(i)001:1355: bral ba rdo rje'i bdag nyid du gcig pa'i phyir
NK060(i)001:1356: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po'o //
NK060(i)001:1357: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i de bzhin gshegs
NK060(i)001:1358: pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang
NK060(i)001:1359: yon tan dang phrin las lnga'am nyi shu rtsa lnga
NK060(i)001:1360: la sogs pa thams cad kyang ngo bo 'dus ma
NK060(i)001:1361: byas pa rdo rje'i bdag nyid du gcig pa'i phyir
NK060(i)001:1362: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po ste/
NK060(i)001:1363: de ka de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bdag nyid
NK060(i)001:1364: gcig dang du ma las grol ba'i rang bzhin no
NK060(i)001:1365: // 'di ni 'grel chung pin tar tha ltar na/
NK060(i)001:1366: phyogs dus bde gshegs bdag po dang /
NK060(i)001:1368: de yan chod la bla ma brgyud pa'i gdams ngag ltar na/
NK060(i)001:1369: ston pa mya ngan las 'das pa dang dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin zhes bzhed do //
NK060(i)001:1370: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa thams cad
NK060(i)001:1371: dang so so ma yin tha mi dad dbyer med
NK060(i)001:1372: pa'i rang bzhin zhes pa ni/
NK060(i)001:1373: khams kyi sgo nas bzhag na ma lus ni 'dod khams/
NK060(i)001:1375: lus pa med ni gzugs med kyi khams te/
NK060(i)001:1376: 'dod khams gzugs khams gzugs med gsum gyis bsdus pa'i
NK060(i)001:1377: sems can dang chos thams cad dang rgyud kyi bdag
NK060(i)001:1378: po drug pa kun tu bzang po rig pa sgyu
NK060(i)001:1379: ma las so so ma yin don dam ma skyes
NK060(i)001:1380: pa las tha mi dad bden pa gsum pa dbyer
NK060(i)001:1382: dus kyi sgo nas bzhag na/
NK060(i)001:1384: mi lus ni da ltar ba/
NK060(i)001:1385: lus pa med pa ni ma 'ongs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1386: 'das da ltar ma 'ongs gsum gyis bsdus pa sems
NK060(i)001:1387: can dang chos thams cad dang rgyud kyi bdag po
NK060(i)001:1388: drug pa kun tu bzang po rig pa sgyu ma
NK060(i)001:1389: la so so ma yin don dam ma skyes pa
NK060(i)001:1390: la tha mi dad bden pa gsum pa dbyer med
NK060(i)001:1392: gnas kyi sgo nas bzhag na/
NK060(i)001:1394: mi lus ni sa 'og /lus pa med pa ni
NK060(i)001:1395: sa steng ste sa bla sa 'og sa steng gsum
NK060(i)001:1396: gyis bsdus pa'i sems can dang chos thams cad dang
NK060(i)001:1397: rgyud kyi bdag po drug pa kun tu bzang po
NK060(i)001:1398: rig pa sgyu ma la so so ma yin don
NK060(i)001:1399: dam ma skyes pa la tha mi dad bden pa
NK060(i)001:1400: gsum pa dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:1401: de ka dus gsum 'du 'bral med pa 'khor ba'i
NK060(i)001:1402: chos dang rgya ma chad par 'brel ba'i rang bzhin
NK060(i)001:1403: no // 'di ni 'grel chung pin tar tha ltar na/
NK060(i)001:1404: chos so cog dang dbyer med pa'i //
NK060(i)001:1406: bla ma brgyud pa'i gdams ngag ltar na/
NK060(i)001:1407: ston pa 'khor ba dang dbyer mi phyed pa'i rang bzhin zhes bzhed do //
NK060(i)001:1408: te zhes pa ni skyon can gyi tshig dang /
NK060(i)001:1409: bstan bya lhag ma can gyi tshig gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:1410: 'di ni lhag ma can gyi tshig ste gang zhe na/
NK060(i)001:1411: sngar bstan pa rnams ni ston pa'i rang bzhin yin la/
NK060(i)001:1412: lhag ma ston pa'i ngo bo 'og nas ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:1414: ras chod can dang gzu lum can dgag pa'i phyir
NK060(i)001:1415: rgyud dkrugs lung gcus man ngag gab pa'i tshul du
NK060(i)001:1416: gnas pa las/ skal ba dang ldan pa la 'chad pa'i tshe/
NK060(i)001:1419: man ngag gab pa mngon tu phyung nas 'chad dgos te/
NK060(i)001:1420: gsang sngags 'chad tshul nyes pa'i skyon brgyad kyi dbang du mi btang ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:1422: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1423: 'bras bu rdo rje'i theg pa khyad par med par bshad na/
NK060(i)001:1424: rdo rje theg pa na babs kyis bshad pa'i skyon/
NK060(i)001:1425: sngags phyi nang gi khyad par med par bshad na/
NK060(i)001:1426: bsnyen sgrub bzhi'o don la gol te/
NK060(i)001:1428: 'brel tshul gnyis dang ma 'brel bar bshad na/
NK060(i)001:1430: spyi dang khyad par gyi dgos ched med par bshad na/
NK060(i)001:1432: rtog ge dang the tshom gyi gegs sel ma shes na/
NK060(i)001:1434: mi mthun pa'i tshig don sdebs ma shes na/
NK060(i)001:1435: long ba'i long thug lta bu'i/
NK060(i)001:1436: mngon par rtogs pa'i go rim sdebs ma shes na/
NK060(i)001:1437: bdud rtsi ro nyams lta bu'i/
NK060(i)001:1438: gong 'og gi 'khrugs sdeb ma shes na/
NK060(i)001:1439: rin po che rtsar 'chol ba lta bu'i bshad pa'i skyon no //
NK060(i)001:1440: de'i phyir gong 'og gi 'khrugs sdeb nas ston pa'i rang bzhin dang /
NK060(i)001:1441: ston pa'i ngo bo gnyis bar ma chad par 'chad par byed don/
NK060(i)001:1442: ston pa'i ngo bo dang 'chad pa'i skyes bu mtshan thun mong du bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1445: ston pa chos kyi sku'am sku dang zhal gyi don bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:1447: ston pa drug pa'i ngo bo dang 'chad pa'i skyes bu'i mtshan nyid ni/
NK060(i)001:1448: rang byung ye shes kho na'i phyir sku mdun dang rgyab kyi tha snyad grub pa med pa la/
NK060(i)001:1449: gdul bya'i snang ba la thams cad du yang zhal thal le bar gsal zhing snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:1451: 'di mi mthun pa'i tshig don byung ste/
NK060(i)001:1452: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa dang thams cad du zhal thal le par gsal ba 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:1453: don du mi 'gal rtags su mi 'gal snang ba gnyis nas cha phye nas mi 'gal te/
NK060(i)001:1454: dbyings la thug pa med pa ni don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1455: rtags de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la mdun rang rgyud pa med/
NK060(i)001:1456: ye shes la 'gags pa med pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1457: rtags de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la rgyab rang rgyud pa med/
NK060(i)001:1458: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa cis kyang mi bsgribs par gsal ba don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1459: rtags thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal ba yin pas mi 'gal/
NK060(i)001:1460: snang ba gnyis su cha phye na sku mdun dang
NK060(i)001:1461: rgyab med pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba yin
NK060(i)001:1462: la/ thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal ba gdul bya'i snang ba yin pas mi 'gal lo //
NK060(i)001:1463: gtsang ba byis ston na re/
NK060(i)001:1464: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa kas thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:1465: mdun dang rgyab gnyis yod na/
NK060(i)001:1466: thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal bar mi 'ong gsung /
NK060(i)001:1467: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'am rgyan gyi/
NK060(i)001:1469: spyir thun mong gi mtshan dpe dang /
NK060(i)001:1470: thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan dpe gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:1471: thun mong gi mtshan dpe sum cu rtsa gnyis ni/
NK060(i)001:1472: phyag zhabs 'khor lo'i mtshan dang rus sbal zhabs //
NK060(i)001:1473: phyag dang zhabs sor d+r+wa bas 'brel ba dang //
NK060(i)001:1474: phyag ni zhabs bcas 'jam zhing gzhon sha chags //
NK060(i)001:1475: 'di yi sku ni bdun dag mtho ba dang //
NK060(i)001:1476: sor mo ring yang rting yangs sku che drang //
NK060(i)001:1477: zhabs 'bur mi mthong spu ni gyen du phyogs //
NK060(i)001:1478: byin pa e na ya 'dra phyag ring mdzes //
NK060(i)001:1479: 'doms kyi lba ba sbubs su nub pa'i mchog /pags pa gser mdog pags pa srab pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1480: spu ni re re nas kyang g.yas legs 'khrungs //
NK060(i)001:1481: zhal mdzod spus brgyan ro stod seng ge 'dra //
NK060(i)001:1482: 'di yi dpung pa'i mgo zlum thal gong rgyas //
NK060(i)001:1484: sku ni nya gro ta ltar chu zheng gab //
NK060(i)001:1485: gtsug tor dbur ldan ljags ring mdzes pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1486: tshangs dbyangs 'gram pa seng ge 'dra dang tshems //
NK060(i)001:1487: shin tu dkar dang tshad mnyam thags bzang dang //
NK060(i)001:1488: grangs ni bzhi bcu tham pa tshang ba dang //
NK060(i)001:1489: spyan ni mthon mthing spyan rdzi ba mchog gi //
NK060(i)001:1490: 'dra ba 'di dag sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan //
NK060(i)001:1492: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu ni //
NK060(i)001:1493: thub pa'i sen mo zangs mdog dang //
NK060(i)001:1494: mdog snum mtho dang sen mo rnams //
NK060(i)001:1495: zlum rgyas byin gyis phra ba dang //
NK060(i)001:1496: rtsa mi mngon dang mdud pa med //
NK060(i)001:1497: long bu mi mngon zhabs mnyam dang //
NK060(i)001:1498: seng ge glang chen bya dang ni //
NK060(i)001:1499: khyu mchog stabs gshegs g.yas phyogs dang //
NK060(i)001:1500: mdzes gshegs drang dang 'khril bag chags //
NK060(i)001:1502: gtsang dang 'jam dang dag pa'i sku //
NK060(i)001:1503: sku yi kho lag yangs shing bzang //
NK060(i)001:1504: goms snyoms pa dang spyan gnyis ni //
NK060(i)001:1505: dag dang gzhon sha can nyid dang //
NK060(i)001:1506: sku zhum med dang rgyas pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1507: shin tu grims pa'i sku nyid dang //
NK060(i)001:1508: yan lag shin tu rnam 'byes dang //
NK060(i)001:1509: gzigs pa sgrib med dag pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1510: sku zlum skabs phyin ma rnyongs dang //
NK060(i)001:1511: phyang nge ba dang lte ba dang //
NK060(i)001:1512: zab dang g.yas phyogs 'khyil ba dang //
NK060(i)001:1513: kun nas lta na sdug pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1514: kun spyod gtsang dang sku la ni //
NK060(i)001:1515: sme ba gnag bag med pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1516: phyag ni shing bal ltar 'a jam dang //
NK060(i)001:1517: phyag rim mdangs yod zab ring dang //
NK060(i)001:1518: zhal ni ha chang mi ring dang //
NK060(i)001:1519: mchu ni bim pa ltar dmar dang //
NK060(i)001:1520: ljags mnyen pa dang srab pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1521: dmar dang 'brug gi sgra nyid dang //
NK060(i)001:1522: gsung snyan 'jam dang mche ba zlum //
NK060(i)001:1523: rno dang dkar dang mnyam pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1524: byin gyis phra dang shangs mtho dang //
NK060(i)001:1525: mchog tu dag pa dag dang ni //
NK060(i)001:1526: spyan yangs pa dang rdzi ma stug /pad ma'i 'dab ma 'dra ba dang //
NK060(i)001:1527: smin tshugs ring dang 'jam pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1528: snum dang spu ni mnyam pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1529: phyag ring rgyas dang snyan 'jam dang //
NK060(i)001:1530: nyams pa rnam par spangs pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1531: dpral ba legs par 'byed pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1532: dbyes che ba dang dbu rgyas dang //
NK060(i)001:1533: dbu skra bung ba ltar gnag dang //
NK060(i)001:1535: mi gshor dri zhim skyes bu yi //
NK060(i)001:1536: yid ni 'phrog par byed pa dang //
NK060(i)001:1537: dpal gyi be'u bkra shis ni //
NK060(i)001:1538: g.yung drung 'khyil bas brgyan pa ste //
NK060(i)001:1539: sangs rgyas dpe byad bzang por bzhed //
NK060(i)001:1541: 'di rnams la thun mong gi mtshan dper 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ni/
NK060(i)001:1542: ston pa sprul pa'i sku dang /
NK060(i)001:1543: stong 'khor los sgyur rgyas po la'ang yod la/
NK060(i)001:1544: tha mal pa'i sems can rnams la'ang snang tsam yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:1545: thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan dpe ni gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:1546: phyi'i mtshan dpe ni drug pa kun tu bzang po
NK060(i)001:1547: yab yum gyi thugs rig pa rang byung gi ye
NK060(i)001:1548: shes thabs kyi snang cha las sems dpa' bcu drug
NK060(i)001:1549: dbyings rnam par dag pa shes rab kyi snang cha
NK060(i)001:1550: las sems ma bcu drug ste/
NK060(i)001:1551: de ltar sum cu rtsa gnyis ni/
NK060(i)001:1552: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK060(i)001:1553: 'o na sems dpa' brgyas sems ma brgyad de bcu drug tu bshad pa dag 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:1554: de ni rgyu skal bzang gi sems dpa' sems ma bcu drug yin la/
NK060(i)001:1555: 'dir 'bras bu dpe bral gyi sems dpa' yab bcu
NK060(i)001:1556: drug yum bcu drug ste sum cu rtsa gnyis so
NK060(i)001:1557: // de ltar 'bras bu'i sems dpa' yab bcu drug po re re la'ang /
NK060(i)001:1558: dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga lnga ste lha brgyad cu ni dpe byed bzang po brgyad cu'o //
NK060(i)001:1560: mtshan gyi me tog la dpe byad kyi 'bras bus spras pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:1561: sras kyi tshogs kyis kun nas brgyan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1563: 'di nyid kyi le'u drug pa las/
NK060(i)001:1564: mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs //
NK060(i)001:1565: spyod yul kun tu ma da la //
NK060(i)001:1567: 'o na de ltar sems dpa' sems ma sum cu
NK060(i)001:1568: rtsa gnyis po de 'khor du 'dug pa la rgyan
NK060(i)001:1570: rgyan gyi don ni mdzes par byed pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:1571: 'dir longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mdzes par byed pa sems dpa'/
NK060(i)001:1572: sems dpa' mdzes par byed pa dbu rgyan te/
NK060(i)001:1573: dper na slob dpon mdzes par byed pa grwa pa/
NK060(i)001:1574: grwa pa mdzes par byed pa thang zhu lta bu yin zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:1576: spyi bo bde ba chen po'i 'khor lo la rtsa 'dab sum cu rtsa gnyis ni/
NK060(i)001:1577: mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK060(i)001:1578: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo la rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi/
NK060(i)001:1579: mgrin pa longs spyod 'khor lo la rtsa 'dab bcu drug ste/
NK060(i)001:1580: brgyad cu ni dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu'o //
NK060(i)001:1582: ston pa yab yum gnyis rol pa'i dus su yab kyi dga' ba bcu drug dang /
NK060(i)001:1583: yum gyi dga' ba bcu drug ste/
NK060(i)001:1584: sum cu rtsa gnyis ni mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK060(i)001:1585: 'o na dga' ba bzhir gsungs pa la bcu drug tu ji ltar 'gyur zhe na/
NK060(i)001:1586: bla ma gong ma rnams ni/
NK060(i)001:1590: dga' ba'i lhan cig skyes dga' zhes pa la sogs pa/
NK060(i)001:1591: dga' ba re re la'ang bzhi bzhi ste bcu drug tu bzhed do //
NK060(i)001:1592: dus kyi 'khor lo'i 'grel pa dri ma med pa'i 'od las/
NK060(i)001:1593: sku gsung thugs ye shes bzhi re re la yang
NK060(i)001:1594: dga' ba bzhi bzhi ste bcu drug tu bshad do
NK060(i)001:1595: // dga' ba bcu drug po re re la'ang ye shes lnga lnga'i ro dang ldan pas/
NK060(i)001:1596: ye shes brgyad cu ni dpe byad brgyad cu'o //
NK060(i)001:1597: 'o na nang dang gsang ba'i mtshan dpe rtsa dang
NK060(i)001:1598: khams kyi rang bzhin du 'dug pa la rgyan du
NK060(i)001:1599: cis 'gyur zhe na/ longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la
NK060(i)001:1600: rtsa khams rnam par dag pa bde ba chen po'i
NK060(i)001:1601: rang bzhin du ro mnyam pa ni/
NK060(i)001:1602: mdzes pa'i nang nas mdzes pa chen po ste/
NK060(i)001:1603: rgyan gyi nang nas mchog yin zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:1604: de ltar phyi nang gsang ba'i mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis gnyis dang /
NK060(i)001:1605: dpe byad brgyad cu brgyad cu ste de dag tu
NK060(i)001:1606: ldan pa ni ston pa drug pa dang 'chad pa'i
NK060(i)001:1607: skyes bu kho na las gzhan la mi mnga' ba'i
NK060(i)001:1608: phyir thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan dape'o //
NK060(i)001:1609: sprul pa'i sprul pa bstan mdzad pa'i/
NK060(i)001:1611: zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad du
NK060(i)001:1612: zhi ba dang khro bo la sogs pa'i sku sna
NK060(i)001:1613: tshogs pa dang / 'gro ba rigs drug so so'i skad du chos ton pa'am/
NK060(i)001:1614: theg pa dgu la sogs pa'i gsung sna tshogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1615: ye shes lnga la sogs pa'i thugs mkhyen pa'i ye
NK060(i)001:1616: shes sna tshogs par mtha' yas pa'i gdal bya'i ngo
NK060(i)001:1618: zhabs dang zhabs gyi bzhugs tshul gyi/
NK060(i)001:1620: thabs yab kyi zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1621: de la shes rab yum gyi zhabs gnyis brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung du bcas pas 'khyud pa ni/
NK060(i)001:1622: rtse sprad pa'i bde ba la rgyu 'bras ril rdzogs pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:1623: bde ba chen po'i ngang las mi 'gyur bar bzhugs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1626: ye shes lnga rang byung gi ye shes dang drug gi don/
NK060(i)001:1627: rgyal ba drug pa nyid la ldan pa'i rtags su phyag drug dang /
NK060(i)001:1628: des gdul bya'i don la 'gags par mdzad pa'i rtags
NK060(i)001:1629: su ye shes rin po che'i phyag rgya ni phyag
NK060(i)001:1630: dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu/
NK060(i)001:1631: bar pa gnyis 'khor lo dang rin po che/
NK060(i)001:1632: mtha' ma gnyis pad+ma dang ral gri rigs kyi kha dog 'od 'bar ba can 'dzin pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1634: ye shes drug phyag gi don du yang byung la
NK060(i)001:1635: phyag mtshan gyi don du yang byung bas ldabs so
NK060(i)001:1636: zhe na/ phyag gi ye shes drug ni ye nas ldan pa'i cha nas bzhag la/
NK060(i)001:1637: phyag mtshan gyi ye shes drug ni des gdul bya'i
NK060(i)001:1638: don mdzad pa'i cha nas bzhag pas ldabs pa'i skyon
NK060(i)001:1639: med do // dbu'i don bstan pa'i/
NK060(i)001:1641: rnam thar gsum chub pa'i rig pa ni sku gsung thugs rang snang ba ste/
NK060(i)001:1642: de'ang sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa'am/
NK060(i)001:1643: nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1644: rtags su g.yas kyi dbu dkar ba yang bsam gyis mi khyab/
NK060(i)001:1645: gsung bsam kyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa'am/
NK060(i)001:1646: gdul bya la chags pa'i don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1647: rtags su g.yon gyi dbu dmar ba yang bsam gyis mi khyab/
NK060(i)001:1648: thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i don dang ldan pa'am/
NK060(i)001:1649: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1650: rtags su dbus kyi dbu mthing kha yang bsam gyis mi khyab pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1651: de ltar dbu gsum dang ldan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1653: dbu bsam gyis mi khyab na dbu gsum du grangs nges pa 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:1656: snang ba gnyis su cha phye nas kyang mi 'gal te/
NK060(i)001:1657: don rtags su mi 'gal ba ni bshad ma thag pa'i 'bru bsnan pas shes la/
NK060(i)001:1658: snang ba gnyis su cha phye na/
NK060(i)001:1659: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:1660: dbu gsum gdul bya'i snang ba yin pas mi 'gal lo gsung /
NK060(i)001:1661: yang bdag gi bla ma mda' sh+aakya 'phel ni/
NK060(i)001:1662: dbu gsum nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa yin gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:1663: de ltar ston pa'i rang bzhin dang /
NK060(i)001:1664: ngo bo gnyis po des gang gis gsungs pa'i ston
NK060(i)001:1665: pa phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bstan pa yin
NK060(i)001:1666: te/ de yang sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho las/
NK060(i)001:1667: ye shes rgya mtsho 'og min gyi //
NK060(i)001:1669: bdag po kun bzang 'khor lo bskor //
