NK060(i)001:1670: bka' sdod skyes bu mdun na gnas //
NK060(i)001:1671: brjod pa med bzhin go bar mdzad //
NK060(i)001:1672: dpag med ye shes yongs rdzogs pas //
NK060(i)001:1673: zhing 'khor longs spyod phun sum ldan //
NK060(i)001:1677: bdag po kun bzang 'khor rnams la //
NK060(i)001:1679: mi bskyod rgyal po mdun na gnas //
NK060(i)001:1681: rgyud kyi ston pa rigs thams cad kyi bdag po drug pa kun tu bzang po yin la/
NK060(i)001:1682: 'chad pa'i skyes bu spyir rigs lnga char yin te/
NK060(i)001:1684: 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga ste //
NK060(i)001:1686: thugs kyi sgyu 'phrul gyi skabs 'dir 'chad pa'i skyes bu rdo rje sems dpa' mdun na gnas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1687: spyi don gnyis pa gang du gsungs pa'i gnas phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bstan pa la lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:1688: gnas kyi rang bzhin nam gzhi'i 'og min gsum gyi/
NK060(i)001:1695: spyir gyi 'og min zhes pa ni gong gzhan gyis mchod pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1696: bye brag tu rang rig pa'i gong gang gis kyang ma chod pa'i rig pa'i/
NK060(i)001:1697: don chos nyid kyi gong gang gis kyang mchod pa ni don gyi/
NK060(i)001:1698: lha rtogs dbyer med kyi gong gang gis kyang mchod pa ni rtogs pa'i/
NK060(i)001:1699: yum gyi mkha'i bde ba gong gang gis kyang ma chod pa ni gsang ba'i/
NK060(i)001:1700: yod min med min gyi skye mched ni bgrangs pa'i/
NK060(i)001:1701: gzugs khams kyi rtse mo ni 'jig rten gnas kyi longs spyod chen po'i 'og min dang bdun las/
NK060(i)001:1702: 'og min gyi gnas 'di ni gzugs khams kyi rtse
NK060(i)001:1703: mo 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min las nyis 'gyur
NK060(i)001:1704: gyis spags pa na ma spangs rgyan tshogs kyi gzhal
NK060(i)001:1705: yas khang ngo // de yang rgyal pa'i thugs rang
NK060(i)001:1706: rig pa'i ye shes mtha' dbus dang bral ba don
NK060(i)001:1707: yas khang ngo // yin la/ rtags gzhal yas khang
NK060(i)001:1708: la mtha' dang dbus ris su chad pa med pa'o
NK060(i)001:1709: yas khang ngo // yin la/ // de nas chos nyid rgya chad dang bral zhing /
NK060(i)001:1710: ngo bo snang stong tha mi dad pa phyogs bcur rang snang ba don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1711: rtags pany+tsa re kh+aa yongs su ma chad pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1712: sna zlum pa ma yin pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1713: phyi gzung ba'i yul dang nang 'dzin pa'i sems gnyis
NK060(i)001:1714: su med par rang rig pa'i ye shes 'ba' zhig
NK060(i)001:1715: las mi gzhan pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1716: rtags kun tu yang nang du gyur pa'i gzhal yas khang de na zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:1717: gnyis pa gnas kyi ngo bo la bdun te/
NK060(i)001:1721: 'og gzhi de blos tshad gzung du med pa'i phyir na gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK060(i)001:1722: de yang ye shes lnga dang ldan pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1723: de mtshon byed kyi rtags kyang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi
NK060(i)001:1724: dbus kyi lte ba dang lnga rang bzhin gyis 'od
NK060(i)001:1725: gsal ba de la yon tan thams cad ma btsal
NK060(i)001:1729: 'o na gzhal yas khang de'i rgyu rang ci snyam na/
NK060(i)001:1730: ye shes nyid dbyibs dang kha dog tu rang snang ba yin te/
NK060(i)001:1731: de yang gdul bya'i dgos 'dod skong ba don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1732: rtags rin po che 'od 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK060(i)001:1735: 'bras bu'i chos la che ba'i yon tan dpag tu
NK060(i)001:1736: med par rgyas pa don yin pa'i phyir na rtags
NK060(i)001:1737: gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs gru bzhir gyur pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1740: ye shes re re yang lhag pa'i ye shes bzhi bzhi dang ldan pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1741: rtags rigs bzhi'i kha dog can gyi rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis te/
NK060(i)001:1742: rtsa rgyud kyi dbang du lha med pa'i khang pa bzhis mdzes pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1745: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK060(i)001:1746: dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad kyi dgongs pa
NK060(i)001:1747: thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes la so so ma
NK060(i)001:1748: yin pas ngo bo nyid du gcig pa'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:1749: las ma g.yos pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1750: rtags gzhal yas khang gi rtse mo spra'am gur lta bur kun tu 'khyil ba'o //
NK060(i)001:1751: rgyan gyi don la nang tshegs gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:1754: thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab
NK060(i)001:1755: pa nyid cir yang mi 'gag pa'i rtsal sna tshogs
NK060(i)001:1757: rtags gdul bya'i snang ngor ye shes rin po che
NK060(i)001:1758: dbyibs dang kha dog sna tshogs pa la sogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:1759: sogs khongs nas 'od zer sprul pa'i 'phro 'du rnam
NK060(i)001:1760: pa tha dad pa'i bye brag du ma dang ldan
NK060(i)001:1761: pa'o // de yang khyad par du gyur pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1763: ye shes rang snang gi rgyan de dag /gang las na/
NK060(i)001:1767: 'jig rten pa'i rgyan ni lta bas ngoms la/
NK060(i)001:1768: ye shes rang snang gi rgyan ni lta bas mi ngoms pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1769: 'jig rten pa'i rgyan ni re re'ang du mar mi 'char la/
NK060(i)001:1770: ye shes rang snang gi rgyan ni re re'ang du mar 'char ba dang /
NK060(i)001:1771: 'jig rten pa'i rgyan ni gcig gis gcig sgrib la/
NK060(i)001:1772: ye shes rang snang gi rgyan gcig gis gcig mi
NK060(i)001:1773: sgrib par gsal bas na khyad par du gyur pa
NK060(i)001:1774: ste/ de'ang ye shes rin po che sna tshogs kyi
NK060(i)001:1775: dbyibs dang kha dog thugs rje dang sprul pa'i 'phro
NK060(i)001:1776: 'du rgyun mi 'chad pa dang ldan pa don yin
NK060(i)001:1777: ste/ la/ rtags rin po che'i phreng ba dang /
NK060(i)001:1778: bden pa gnyis su med pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1779: rtags rin po che'i chun 'phyang dang /
NK060(i)001:1780: thabs ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1781: rtags rin po che shar bu'i rgyan dang ldan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1782: gnyis pa 'dod yon gyi rgyan ni/
NK060(i)001:1784: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ma spangs rnam dag rgyan du rdzogs pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1785: rtags gzugs kyi lha mo dkar mo me long bsnams pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1786: sgra'i lha mo dmar mo pi wang thogs pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1787: dri'i lha mo sngon mo dri'i dung chos thogs pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1788: ro'i lha mo ser mo mkhar gzhong g.yos kyis bkang ba thogs pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1789: reg bya'i lha mo dkar mo lha'i na bza' pany+tsa
NK060(i)001:1790: li ka thogs pa sna tshogs kyis rang bzhin grub
NK060(i)001:1791: pa'i dbang du phyogs bcur 'khrigs pa rgyu rkyen med
NK060(i)001:1792: par rang byung la/ sgom pa'i dbang du ni pany+tsa re kh+aa'i phyi/
NK060(i)001:1795: steng gi bya 'dabs kyi 'og /ka thung bcu drug
NK060(i)001:1796: gi phrag /d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed kyi gseb nas mchod
NK060(i)001:1798: de yang phyi yis nang mi sgrib/
NK060(i)001:1799: nang gis phyi mi sgrib par dper na/
NK060(i)001:1800: rin po che gser gyi sbu gur rin po che ze'u kha bcug pa lta bu'am/
NK060(i)001:1801: rin po che shel gyi sbu gur rin po che
NK060(i)001:1802: sna tshogs pa bcug pa ltar gsal ba'i rgyan mang
NK060(i)001:1803: ba'i tshad ni bsam gyi mi khyab pas klubs pa
NK060(i)001:1807: theg pa gzhan las 'dir bla na med pa'i theg pa 'phags pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1808: rtags su gzhal yas khang gi 'og gzhi rim pa bzhin/
NK060(i)001:1809: rdo rje 'greng bu res spags pa chos kyi dbyings la thug pa med pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1810: rtags su bum pa'i mtho dman tshad dpag tu med pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1811: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gtsug tor lta bu'o //
NK060(i)001:1818: de ltar rnam par thar pa'i ting nge 'dzin bzhi'i
NK060(i)001:1819: sgo nas ma h+aa a tir 'jug pa'i tshul ni
NK060(i)001:1820: don yin la/ rtags gzhal yas khang gi phyogs bzhir sgo bzhi ni thang sgo lta bu ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:1821: sgo khyud sgo rgyan dang ldan pa can no //
NK060(i)001:1823: lam spyi'i 'jug tshal sems lnga ru/
NK060(i)001:1826: khog gzhung rnams kyis bshad pa dang /
NK060(i)001:1827: 'dir rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi nas 'jug par bshad pa 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:1828: thun mong ngam spyi'i 'jug tshul sems lnga yin yang /
NK060(i)001:1829: khyad par ram lta ba rtogs nas 'jug tshul rnam thar bzhi yin pa mi 'gal te/
NK060(i)001:1830: de yang 'di nyid kyi le'u lnga pa las/
NK060(i)001:1831: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pa //
NK060(i)001:1832: rtogs pa'i dbang sgyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK060(i)001:1836: 'khor ba la sa rnam par thar par byed pa'i
NK060(i)001:1837: theg pa brgyad bgrod nas rang sa'i 'bras bu brgyad
NK060(i)001:1838: thob pa ni don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1839: rtags su rgyan gyi rta babs brgyad dang ldan pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1844: rin chen sgrom bu ste bzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:1849: rin chen phreng ba dang bzhi'o //
NK060(i)001:1851: theg pa a nu man chad brgyad bgrod nas/
NK060(i)001:1852: thob bya gsang ba'i snying por 'dod pa 'gal lo zhe na mi 'gal te/
NK060(i)001:1853: lha mi'i theg pa zhes bgrangs pa'i theg pa brgyad kyang yin la/
NK060(i)001:1854: theg pa kun gyi thob bya rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po yin te/
NK060(i)001:1856: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK060(i)001:1857: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK060(i)001:1859: 'khor lo bskor ba de dag gi 'bras bu'i mchog /ces gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:1860: lnga pa gdan khri'i don bstan pa'i/
NK060(i)001:1862: 'di la'ang 'og gzhi chos kyii 'khor lo bskor ba'i/
NK060(i)001:1864: yon tan gyi che bas nyes tshogs bcom pa'i/
NK060(i)001:1866: thugs rig pa rang snang ba'i gdan dang lnga las/
NK060(i)001:1867: dang po 'og gzhi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i gdan ni/
NK060(i)001:1868: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dbus kyi lte ba dang bcas pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:1869: de dag gi steng du smon lam gus pa'i gdan ni/
NK060(i)001:1870: sa mtha'i byang chub sems dpa' smon lam gyi dbang
NK060(i)001:1871: gis seng ge la sogs par sprul pa'i lus gdan
NK060(i)001:1872: du phul nas nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa sbyong /
NK060(i)001:1873: rna bas chos mnyan nas shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyong /
NK060(i)001:1875: byang chub sems dpa'i smon lam dbang //
NK060(i)001:1876: thos pa rgya mtsho bsags pa'i phyir //
NK060(i)001:1877: las ni seng ge'i gdan du phul //
NK060(i)001:1880: seng ge la sogs pa smon lam gyi byang chub sems dpa' gcig kyang brgyad brgyad do //
NK060(i)001:1882: gsum pa yon tan gyi che bas nyes tshogs bcom pa'i gdan ni/
NK060(i)001:1883: nyi zla pad ma'i gdan yin la/
NK060(i)001:1884: bzhi pa sa'i khyad pa bgrod pa'i gnad ni/
NK060(i)001:1885: de rnams kyang rin po che'i khri rkang gis bteg pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1886: de dag ni rgyu'i theg pa'am/
NK060(i)001:1887: rgyu mas sbyangs kyi dbang du yin la/
NK060(i)001:1889: yas sprul gyi dbang du gdan thams cad kyang thugs rig pa rang snang ba'i gdan du gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:1891: byang chub sems dpa' lus gdan du phul nas/
NK060(i)001:1892: chos nyan pa ni 'bras bu'i theg pa'i skabs su 'thad par ma gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:1895: de'i phyir gdan lnga ka yang thugs rig pa rang snang gi gdan gyi dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:1896: bshad ma thag pa'i gzhal yas khang de na rgyal
NK060(i)001:1897: ba drug pa'i thugs la mi 'jigs pa bzhi lhun
NK060(i)001:1898: gyis grub pa ni don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1899: rtags seng ge khyi tshugs pa brgyad mjug ma nang
NK060(i)001:1900: du bsnol nas rin po che'i khri rkang 'degs pa
NK060(i)001:1901: dang / de bzhin du sku stobs bcu lhun gyis grub pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1902: rtags glang po che brgyad kyis btegs pa'i khri dang /
NK060(i)001:1903: yon tan rdzu 'phrul bzhi lhun gyis grub pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1904: rtags su rta brgyad kyis btegs pa'i khri dang /
NK060(i)001:1905: gsung dbang bcu lhun gyis grub pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1906: rtags rma bya brgyad kyis btegs pa'i khri dang /
NK060(i)001:1907: phrin las las bzhi lhun gyis grub pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1908: rtags su thogs pa med pa nam mkha' lding brgyad kyis btegs pa'i khri dang ldan pa ste/
NK060(i)001:1909: de yang dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las/
NK060(i)001:1910: thugs ni mi 'jigs bzhi yis bdud bzhi 'joms //
NK060(i)001:1911: de grub rtags su seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK060(i)001:1912: sku ni stobs bcus mi dge bcu rnams 'dul //
NK060(i)001:1913: de grub rtags su glang chen khri la bzhugs //
NK060(i)001:1914: yon tan rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis chags med sgrol //
NK060(i)001:1915: de grub rtags su rta mchog khri la bzhugs //
NK060(i)001:1916: gsung ni dbang bcu mthar phyin rgyal ba'i gsung //
NK060(i)001:1917: de grub rtags su rma bya'i khri la bzhugs //
NK060(i)001:1918: las ni phrin las bzhi yis thogs med sgrol //
NK060(i)001:1919: de grub rtags su shang shang khri la bzhugs //
NK060(i)001:1921: rgyal ba'i thugs rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba ste/
NK060(i)001:1922: de yang shes rab rang bzhin med pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1924: thabs 'gag pa med pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1926: thugs la nyes pa'i skyon gyis gos pa med pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1927: rtags sna tshogs pad+ma'i gdan dang /
NK060(i)001:1928: dgos 'dod lhun gyis grub pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1929: rtags rin po che'i khri rkang ngo //
NK060(i)001:1930: de yang dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis grub pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:1931: rtags khri rkang re re yang mdzod mig bdun bdun dang ldan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:1932: de la gdan gyi rim pa ni/
NK060(i)001:1933: skyes bu lnga la lnga brtseg ste //
NK060(i)001:1934: sems dpa' la ni gsum brtseg go //
NK060(i)001:1935: nyi rkyang khro la pad rkyang thub //
NK060(i)001:1936: kun bzang yab yum bzhi brtseg go //
NK060(i)001:1937: zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:1938: spyan 'grel gyi sa sgo ba yab yum la nyi
NK060(i)001:1939: ma dang pad ma nyis brtseg /kun bzang yab yum
NK060(i)001:1940: la dkyil 'khor la 'god pa'i tshe gsum brtseg dang
NK060(i)001:1941: / chos 'chad pa'i tshe lnga brtseg tu bshad do //
NK060(i)001:1942: gdan gyi steng du zla ba 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan ni/
NK060(i)001:1944: thig le chen po dang sa bon ni dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:1945: thams cad kyi byed pa po'i phyir bdag po dang
NK060(i)001:1946: rdo rje ste dbus na zla ba blar gnas so
NK060(i)001:1948: thabs lam ltar na snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo na srog mi shigs pa'i thig le dang /
NK060(i)001:1949: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo na kun tu bzang po'i thig le yong pas/
NK060(i)001:1950: thig le gnyis po de thams cad kyi byed pa po'i rgyu ru 'gro la/
NK060(i)001:1951: grol lam ltar na rgyud kyi bdag po drug pa kun tu bzang po dang /
NK060(i)001:1952: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:1953: gdan zla ba steng du 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan yin gsung /
NK060(i)001:1955: gtso bo ni shes rab la spyod pa'i phyir dang /
NK060(i)001:1956: nang gi chu skyes kyi lte ba'i nyi ma la zla ba brten pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:1957: ri bong can steng na gnas so //
NK060(i)001:1958: yum rnams ni de las ldog ces 'chad na yang /
NK060(i)001:1959: 'khril sbyor phyir gcig pa mi 'gal lo //
NK060(i)001:1961: shes rab kyis spyod pa'i dbang du yum gyi pad+ma
NK060(i)001:1962: 'dab ma brgyad pa'i lte ba la nyi ma byang
NK060(i)001:1963: chub kyi sems yod pa de la/
NK060(i)001:1964: yab kyi zla ba byang chub kyi sems brten dgos
NK060(i)001:1965: pa'i phyir zla ba steng du 'ong ba yin gsung
NK060(i)001:1966: ngo // rje dri ngas pa nye'u ston chos kyi seng ge na re/
NK060(i)001:1967: gtso bor thabs snang ba 'gag pa med pas zla ba steng du 'ong ba yin gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:1968: yang zhi ba la lha kun la zla ba steng du 'ong la/
NK060(i)001:1969: khro bo la lha kun la nyi ma steng du
NK060(i)001:1970: 'ong bar yang 'grel pa mngon rtogs ltar rung ngo
NK060(i)001:1971: // yang 'ga' zhig sems can gyi gdan 'di dag sprul pa yin nam/
NK060(i)001:1972: rang rgyud pa yin gyi brgal lan byed mod kyi
NK060(i)001:1973: 'di dag gi rgyu mtshan gong gi 'bru bsnan gyi
NK060(i)001:1974: skabs su rgyas par bshad pa bzhi go bar bya'o
NK060(i)001:1975: // de ltar sa dmigs lnga po des/
NK060(i)001:1976: gang du gsungs pa'i gnas phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bstan pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:1978: dga' bde yang dag rdzogs pa'i gnas //
NK060(i)001:1979: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK060(i)001:1980: ma lus 'dus pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK060(i)001:1981: bdag po rgyan dang bcas pa nyid //
NK060(i)001:1983: nyis 'gyur shin tu spags pa na //
NK060(i)001:1984: ngo bo mtha' gsum las 'das pa //
NK060(i)001:1985: ma spangs rgyan tshogs gzhal yas khang //
NK060(i)001:1986: yon tan lnga yi bdag po ste //
NK060(i)001:1987: grub bzhi spyi bor 'khyil snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:1989: spyi don gsum pa gang la gsungs pa'i 'khor phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bstan pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:1990: rang bzhin nas dgongs pa gnyis su med pa'i 'khor dang /
NK060(i)001:1991: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor ro //
NK060(i)001:1994: rigs kyi yab lnga sku mdog dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:1996: bcom ldan 'das dang de bzhin gshegs pa zhes pa mtshan thun mong ba gnyis ni/
NK060(i)001:1997: thugs rig pa rang snang ba'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:1998: ston pa'i rang bzhin dang 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:1999: rnam shes spyi'i mtshan nyid ni yul rig pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:2000: bye brag tu phye nas tshogs brgyad de/
NK060(i)001:2005: de ltar brgyad kyi tshogs pa ni rnam par shes pa'i phung po'o //
NK060(i)001:2006: de lta bu'i rtog pa la thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis rang dbang sgyur zhing /
NK060(i)001:2007: zag pa med pa'i chos la mnga' brnyes pas bde ba chen por longs spyod pas na rgyal po ste/
NK060(i)001:2008: lha na rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK060(i)001:2009: de bzhin gshegs pa ni 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:2011: gzhig cing gzhom du rung ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:2014: rgyu'i gzugs sa chu me rlung bzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:2015: 'bras bu'i gzugs dbang po lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:2017: rnam par rig byed ma yin pa'i gzugs te so so thar pa'i sdom pa la sogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2018: de ltar gzugs chos bco lnga po rnams kyi rtog
NK060(i)001:2019: pa la gong bzhin du rang dbang sgyur bas na
NK060(i)001:2020: rgyal po ste/ lha na rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK060(i)001:2021: de bzhin gshegs pa ni 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:2022: tshor ba'i spyi'i mtshan nyid ni/
NK060(i)001:2023: nyams su myong ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:2026: bde sdug btang snyoms gsum gyi tshor ba'i rtog pa la rang dbang sgyur pas na rgyal po ste/
NK060(i)001:2027: lha na rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK060(i)001:2028: de bzhin gshegs pa ni 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:2032: rgya che ba chung ba tshad med pa gsum gyi
NK060(i)001:2033: 'du shes kyi rtog pa la rang dbang sgyur bas
NK060(i)001:2034: na rgyal po ste/ lha na snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK060(i)001:2035: de bzhin gshegs pa ni 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:2036: 'du byed spyi'i mtshan nyid ni mngon par 'du byed pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:2038: bshad ma thag pa'i tshor ba dang /
NK060(i)001:2042: sems dpa' dang gsum ste kun 'gro gsum dang /
NK060(i)001:2047: shes rab ste yul so sor nges pa lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:2051: 'dod chags med pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba/
NK060(i)001:2052: zhe sdang med pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba/
NK060(i)001:2053: gti mug med pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba/
NK060(i)001:2057: rnam pa mi 'tshe ba ste dge ba bcu gcig dang /
NK060(i)001:2063: the tshom ste rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa drug dang /
NK060(i)001:2082: shes bzhin ma yin pa ste nye ba'i nyon mongs pa nyi shu dang /
NK060(i)001:2086: dpyod ste gzhan du 'gyur pa bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:2087: de ltar bzhi bcu rtsa dgu 'du byed kyi rtog pa la rang dbang sgyur ba'i rgyal po/
NK060(i)001:2088: lhan don yod grub pa dang lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:2089: de dag kun kyang chos nyid ma 'gyur ba mtshon pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:2090: rtags sku mdog mthing kha bdun dang /
NK060(i)001:2091: nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:2092: rtags sku mdog dkar po lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:2093: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:2094: rtags sku mdog ser po lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:2095: gdul bya la chags pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:2096: rtags sku mdog le brgan bzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:2097: las sna tshogs pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:2098: rtags sku mdog ljang khu'i mdog can gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:2099: de rnams kyi dmigs bsal ni 'chad par 'gyur pa'i le'u drug pa'i skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:2100: sku mdog de dag kyang ma 'dres par rang rang gi kha dog tu 'tsher ba'o //
NK060(i)001:2101: 'o na skabs 'dir rdo rje sems dpa' dang bya ba la sogs pa mi 'ong bar/
NK060(i)001:2102: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang zhes pa la
NK060(i)001:2103: sogs pa rtog pa smos pa la dogs pa ci
NK060(i)001:2104: yod ce na/ spar khab las/
NK060(i)001:2105: kun gzhi la sogs pa'i rtog pa lnga smos pa ni/
NK060(i)001:2107: thun mong ma yin pa'i phyir smos pa ste/
NK060(i)001:2108: de dag kar dag par chud pa la rdo rje
NK060(i)001:2109: 'dzin pa la sogs par rang snang ba'i phyir ro
NK060(i)001:2111: rang bzhin ni shes bya'i gshis la rtog pa rnam pa shes pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2112: 'bras bu rdo rje sems dpa' gnyis snang na snang mnyam/
NK060(i)001:2114: bzang ngan med par mnyam par kyang smos pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:2115: thun mong ma yin pa'i phyir smos pa ni/
NK060(i)001:2116: thun mong gi theg pa'i skabs su lha smos la/
NK060(i)001:2117: thun mong ma yin pa'i rgyud 'di'i skabs su rtog pa smos pa/
NK060(i)001:2118: lha dang rtog pa dbyer med du ngos zin par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK060(i)001:2120: lam nyams su blangs pas 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dus tsam na/
NK060(i)001:2121: rnam par shes pa nyid ma spangs pa bsgyur bar
NK060(i)001:2122: rdo rje sems dpar rang snang ba'i phyir du'ang smos
NK060(i)001:2123: pa'o // de'i phyir rtog pa smos pa thams cad de ltar shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:2124: rigs kyi yum lnga gnyis su med par bzhugs tshul tshad dang bcas pa'i/
NK060(i)001:2126: btsun mo ni bskyed pa'i rgyud gyur pas sam/
NK060(i)001:2127: spyad bya'i yul du gyur pas sam/
NK060(i)001:2128: sras kyi 'byung khungs su gyur pa ste/
NK060(i)001:2129: go rim bzhin 'byung ba lngas phung po lnga bskyed pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2130: shes rab la thabs kyis rol pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2131: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor gyi 'byung khungs su gyur pas so //
NK060(i)001:2132: de yang sems ma las khyad par du gyur pas na dam pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2133: snang ba dbyings ni 'byung ba nam mkha' ste/
NK060(i)001:2134: lha na rdo rje dbyings phyug ma dang /
NK060(i)001:2135: sra ba'i dbyings ni 'byung ba sa ste/
NK060(i)001:2136: lha na sangs rgyas spyan ma dang /
NK060(i)001:2137: mnyes pa'i dbyings ni 'byung ba chu ste/
NK060(i)001:2138: lha na m+aa ma k+ai dang /
NK060(i)001:2139: dro ba'i dbyings ni 'byung ba me ste/
NK060(i)001:2140: lha na na bza' dkar mo dang /
NK060(i)001:2141: bskyod pa'i dbyings ni 'byung ba rlung ste/
NK060(i)001:2142: lha na dam tshig sgrol ma'o //
NK060(i)001:2143: la sogs pa'i sogs khongs nas de dag dang cha
NK060(i)001:2144: lugs mthun pa'i rgyud mas sbyangs kyi btsun mo'i tshogs
NK060(i)001:2145: kyang bsdus ste/ de yang shes rab kyi rgyud ltar
NK060(i)001:2146: na bud med kyi tshogs kyi dbus na yab dang
NK060(i)001:2147: yum gnyis su med par bzhugs shing chos kyi dbyings
NK060(i)001:2148: kun tu mtha' yas par khyab pa'i rang bzhin mngon
NK060(i)001:2149: du byas pa ni don yin la/
NK060(i)001:2150: rtags su khang pa lhas gang ba 'di lta ste/
NK060(i)001:2151: dper na til gyi gang bu la til 'bras kyis khyab la/
NK060(i)001:2152: til 'bras la til mar gyis khyab pa bzhin du
NK060(i)001:2153: gzhal yas khang lhas gang nas kun tu khyab par
NK060(i)001:2154: bzhugs so // gnyis pa rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor/
NK060(i)001:2159: nang sems yab yum brgyad bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:2162: 'brel mtshams sbyar ba'i tshig byang ngang mo'i 'gros ltar du bshad na/
NK060(i)001:2163: rang bzhin nam dgongs pa gnyis su med pa'i 'khor bstan pa la/
NK060(i)001:2164: de rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor ston pas na nas zhes 'brel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:2165: byang chub chen po rdo rje zhes pa la sogs pa la/
NK060(i)001:2167: rgyud mas sbyangs rang rgyud pa ltar du 'bru bsnan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2168: thugs rang snang sprul pa ba ltar du 'bru bsnan pa gnyis gsungs kyang /
NK060(i)001:2169: don la yin tshul dang snang tshul gnyis su go bar bya ste/
NK060(i)001:2170: yin tshul gyi dbang du byas na thun mong ma
NK060(i)001:2171: yin pa'i gleng gzhi'i skabs 'dir byung ba'i 'khor thams
NK060(i)001:2172: cad kyang thugs rig pa rang snang sprul pa ba
NK060(i)001:2173: yin te/ sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho las/
NK060(i)001:2174: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK060(i)001:2175: rang snang rgyal ba sems sogs dang //
NK060(i)001:2178: mtshan thun mong ba gnyis ni sngar thal te/
NK060(i)001:2180: rang rig pa nyid gsum gyi khyad par du snang ba la ngam pa gsum mo //
NK060(i)001:2182: kar dag pa chud pa la rdo rje 'dzin pa la sogs par rang snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:2184: 'on kyang de dang cha lugs mthun pa'i rgyud mas sbyangs kyi 'khor kyang yod de/
NK060(i)001:2186: dang po sangs rgyas sa rgyal ba //
NK060(i)001:2187: sems dpa' che dang 'joms pa che //
NK060(i)001:2188: brjod kyis mi lang tshad med dang //
NK060(i)001:2191: de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK060(i)001:2193: snang tshul gyi dbang du byas nas/
NK060(i)001:2194: sa mtha'i byang chub sems dpa'i tshul du snang ste/
NK060(i)001:2196: gdul bya las mthar thug pa ni/
NK060(i)001:2197: drug pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing du gyur te/
NK060(i)001:2198: de dag sa gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas chen po ste/
NK060(i)001:2199: lta ba'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir las kyi rdo rje'o //
NK060(i)001:2202: mig gi rnam par shes pa la sogs pa tha mal pa'i rtog pa byang nas/
NK060(i)001:2203: sa mthar phyin pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sa'i snying po la sogs par chub pa ste/
NK060(i)001:2204: sa dgu pa man chad las khyad par du gyur pas na chen po/
NK060(i)001:2205: lta ba'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir las kyi rdo rje'o //
NK060(i)001:2206: mthong ba ni mig gi rnam par shes pa ste/
NK060(i)001:2207: lha na byang chub sems dpa' sa'i snying po dang /
NK060(i)001:2208: byang chub chen po rdo rje ni 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:2209: thos pa rna ba'i rnam par shes pa/
NK060(i)001:2210: lha na phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK060(i)001:2211: byang chub chen po rdo rje snom pa'i sna'i rnam shes te/
NK060(i)001:2212: lha na nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK060(i)001:2213: byang chub chen po rdo rje myong ba lce'i rnam shes/
NK060(i)001:2214: lha na spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang /
NK060(i)001:2215: btsun mo zhes bya ba ni sngar bshad pa bzhin las/
NK060(i)001:2216: khyad par du skabs 'dir yul bzhis rnam shes bzhi bskyed pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2217: mthong bar bya ba gzugs te/
NK060(i)001:2218: lha na la s+ye ma dang /
NK060(i)001:2219: mnyan par bya ba sgra ste/
NK060(i)001:2221: snom par bya ba dri ste m+aa le ma dang /
NK060(i)001:2222: myong bar bya ba ro ste n+airti ma'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams so //
NK060(i)001:2223: phyi sems yab yum brgyad bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2225: byang chub chen po rdo rje ni 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:2226: mthong byed mig gi dbang po ste lha na byams pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2227: byang chub chen po rdo rje ni 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:2228: thos byed rna ba'i dbang po ste sgrib sel dang /
NK060(i)001:2229: byang chub chen po rdo rje ni 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:2230: snom byed sna'i dbang po ste kun tu bzang po dang /
NK060(i)001:2231: byang chub chen po rdo rje 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:2232: myong byed lce'i dbang po ste 'jam dpal gzhon nu dang /
NK060(i)001:2233: btsun mo ni sngar bzhin la/
NK060(i)001:2234: khyad par du skabs 'dir dus bzhis dbang po bzhi bskyed pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2235: de yang 'das pa'i dus lha mo d+h+au pe ma dang /
NK060(i)001:2236: da ltar gyi dus push+pe ma dang /
NK060(i)001:2237: 'byung bar ma nges pa'i dus +aa lo ke ma dang /
NK060(i)001:2238: ma byon pa'i dus gan+d+he ma ste de dag dang
NK060(i)001:2239: cha lugs mthun pa'i rgyud mas sbyangs kyi tshogs dang
NK060(i)001:2242: sku gsung thugs kyi mdzad pas bdud dang mu stegs
NK060(i)001:2243: 'joms pa gnod sbyin las khyad par du gyur pas
NK060(i)001:2244: na chen po/ lta ba'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir las kyi rdo rje'o //
NK060(i)001:2245: reg pa ni gsang ba'i yul dang dbang po dang rnam par shes pa ste gsum 'dus so //
NK060(i)001:2246: lus ngag yid gsum spyir 'dzin pa ste lha na bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK060(i)001:2247: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje ni 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:2248: reg byed ni gsang ba'i dbang po pho'i mtshan ma'am ngag ste lha na rta mgrin dang /
NK060(i)001:2249: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg bya ni/
NK060(i)001:2250: gsang ba'i yum mo'i mtshan ma'am lus te/
NK060(i)001:2251: lha na stobs po che dang /
NK060(i)001:2252: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg shes ni gsang
NK060(i)001:2253: ba'i rnam par shes pas dga' ba nyams su myong
NK060(i)001:2254: ba'am yid de/ lha na gshin rje gshed dang /
NK060(i)001:2255: btsun mo ni sngar bshad pa bzhin las/
NK060(i)001:2256: khyad pa ni skabs 'dir rtag chad kyi phyi log
NK060(i)001:2257: bzhis lus te rtog pa bzhi dngos su mi bskyed
NK060(i)001:2258: kyang brgyud nas bskyed gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:2259: rtag par ma yin pa ni/
NK060(i)001:2260: mi rtag pa ste lha na lcags kyu ma dang /
NK060(i)001:2261: chad par ma yin pa ni/
NK060(i)001:2262: sdug bsngal ba ste lha na zhags pa ma dang /
NK060(i)001:2263: bdag tu ma yin pa ni/
NK060(i)001:2264: bdag med pa ste lha na lcags sgrog ma dang /
NK060(i)001:2265: mtshan mar ma yin pa ni/
NK060(i)001:2266: stong pa ste lha na dril bu ma'o //
NK060(i)001:2268: gzhung drang thad dbang btsan du byas pa yin gyi/
NK060(i)001:2269: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la la dag ni/
NK060(i)001:2270: rtag par ma yin pa la rtag par 'dzin pa
NK060(i)001:2271: la sogs pa don dang 'gal ba'i lta ba phyin
NK060(i)001:2272: cig log /rtag chad bdag mtshan bzhis lus kyi rtog
NK060(i)001:2273: pa bzhi bskyed par byed pa yin pas na/
NK060(i)001:2274: rtag pa ma yin par rtag par 'dzin pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2275: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i bar gyi tshig la/
NK060(i)001:2276: rtag par 'dzin pa bya ba la sogs pa mi mngon par bya ba'i lugs yin gyi/
NK060(i)001:2277: gzhung gi tshig sgra ji bzhin par bshad du mi rung ngo //
NK060(i)001:2278: zhes bzhed pa 'di dag brtag par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:2279: 'khor de dag mang ba dang khyab pa'i tshad dang gnyis su med par bzhugs pa'i tshul bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2281: la sogs pa'i sogs khongs nas thugs rang snang sprul
NK060(i)001:2282: pa ba dang cha mthun pas na de lta bu'i
NK060(i)001:2283: rgyud mas sbyangs kyi tshogs dang bcas pa brjod kyis
NK060(i)001:2284: mi lang ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs pa'i
NK060(i)001:2285: tshul ni bzhi ste/ rang bzhin gyis snang ba'i dbang
NK060(i)001:2286: du 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pas bsdus
NK060(i)001:2287: tshul ni bzhi ste/ pa'i chos/ thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi'i dbang du ston 'khor dgongs pa/
NK060(i)001:2288: bdag nyid chen po'i dbang du lha dang rtog pa/
NK060(i)001:2289: gnas kyi dbang du longs spyod chen po'i 'og min dang /
NK060(i)001:2290: zhing khams mtha' yas mu med bsam gyis mi khyab pa gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK060(i)001:2291: 'o na de ltar bshad pa'i 'khor 'di dag la/
NK060(i)001:2292: kha cig sprul pa ba yin nam/
NK060(i)001:2293: rang rgyud pa yin gyi brtag pa dang brgal lan byed de/
NK060(i)001:2294: kho bos 'di dag gi go don gzhung gi 'bru
NK060(i)001:2295: bsnon gyi skabs su gsal bar bkod pa bzhin go
NK060(i)001:2296: bar bya'i/ gyi na'i rtsod spong don chung bar rig par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:2297: gal te spros pa la dga' ba rnams snga rabs
NK060(i)001:2298: pa rnams kyis mdzad pa'i gtar kha la gzigs pas
NK060(i)001:2299: khyab bo // yang kha cig na re/
NK060(i)001:2300: le'u dang po gleng gzhi'i le'u 'dir lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis tshang ngam ma tshang /
NK060(i)001:2301: tshang na kun tu bzang mo dang /
NK060(i)001:2302: thub pa drug mi 'dug pas gsal/
NK060(i)001:2303: ma tshang na gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs par mi 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2304: thabs dang shes rab ces pa las/
NK060(i)001:2305: shes rab la kun tu bzang mo nges 'dzin/
NK060(i)001:2306: sku gsung thugs sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba/
NK060(i)001:2307: zhes pas thub pa drug ngos 'dzin no //
NK060(i)001:2308: des na gleng gzhi ma tshogs pa'i skyon med la/
NK060(i)001:2309: gsal bar mi 'byung ba'i 'thad pa ni/
NK060(i)001:2310: le'u dang po gsang dbang gi skabs min pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2311: thun mong gi gdul bya med pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2312: chos 'chad pa'i skabs yin pas so //
NK060(i)001:2313: le'u gnyis par dbang bskur ba'i don du kun tu bzang mo byung ba yin/
NK060(i)001:2314: le'u gsum par dkyil 'khor du 'khor pa'i 'khor dang /
NK060(i)001:2315: 'gro ba 'dul byed kyi 'khor yin pas thub pa drug byung ba yin no //
NK060(i)001:2316: zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:2317: kho bo'i bla ma zur thams cad mkhyen pa ni/
NK060(i)001:2318: sdud pa po'i tshig dang yi ger 'god pa'i tshe gleng gzhi tshogs tshul le'u dang por bshad/
NK060(i)001:2319: gleng bslangs shing dbang bskur tshul le'u gnyis par bshad kyang /
NK060(i)001:2320: don la thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi nam tshogs pa'i dus de nyid du/
NK060(i)001:2321: gleng bslangs shing dbang bskur nas rgyud gsungs pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:2322: kun tu bzang mo ni yab dang gnyis su med par bzhugs pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:2323: thub pa drug ni sprul sku yin pa'i phyir thun
NK060(i)001:2324: mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi'i skabs su dngos su
NK060(i)001:2325: ma byung ba yang kun tu bzang po'i thugs la
NK060(i)001:2326: rdzogs pas na/ gleng gzhi ma tshogs par mi 'gyur la/
NK060(i)001:2327: thun mong gi gleng gzhi'i skabs su kun tu bzang po'i thugs las thub pa drug sprul nas/
NK060(i)001:2328: go phye ba'i 'khor gyi don nam/
NK060(i)001:2329: rgyud 'di nyid kyi lam stegs thun mong gi bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2330: theg pa ston pa'i phyir le'u gnyis par sprul pa thub pa drug spro bar zhal gyis bzhes nas/
NK060(i)001:2331: le'u gsum par spro ba dngos bstan par bzhed do //
NK060(i)001:2333: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang na/
NK060(i)001:2334: sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bzhugs sam mi bzhugs/
NK060(i)001:2335: bzhugs na thub pa drug gis gdul bya rigs drug
NK060(i)001:2336: gi sems can yin pas gdul bya dang 'dul byed
NK060(i)001:2337: gnas tha dad par 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2338: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang mtha' dbus
NK060(i)001:2339: dang rgya chad med par gnas kyi rang bzhin gyi
NK060(i)001:2340: skabs su bstan zin pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:2341: rigs drug gi sems can gyi gnas khams gsum dang /
NK060(i)001:2342: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang gnyis de nyid dang gzhan du brjod du med pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:2343: rang rig pa rang byung gi ye shes mngon du
NK060(i)001:2344: byas ma byas kyi khyad par yin pa'i phyir ro
NK060(i)001:2345: // de yang sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa las/
NK060(i)001:2346: yang dag shes pa'i rang rig blo med na //
NK060(i)001:2347: bde gshegs zhing yang ngan song gnas su mthong //
NK060(i)001:2349: spyi don gsum pa gleng gzhi bsdus te bstan pa la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:2351: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:2353: de nas zhes pa 'brel mtshams sbyor ba'i tshig ste/
NK060(i)001:2354: gzhung rgyas par bstan pa la de bsdus te ston pas na nas zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:2355: de bzhin gshegs pa rgyal ba drug pa nyid btsun
NK060(i)001:2356: mo'i tshogs yum rnams dang thabs lam ltar na thabs
NK060(i)001:2357: shes rab bde ba'i ye shes/
NK060(i)001:2358: grol lam ltar na yab yum dgongs pa gnyis su
NK060(i)001:2359: med pa'i gsang ba'i ye shes rang bzhin lhun grub
NK060(i)001:2360: kyi dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi don nyams su
NK060(i)001:2361: myong dka' ba'i gsang ba 'di nyid rigs thams cad
NK060(i)001:2362: kyi bdag po ston pa drug pa'i sku dang gsung
NK060(i)001:2363: dang thugs dang yon tan dang phrin las lnga'i ngo
NK060(i)001:2364: bo/ 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga'o //
NK060(i)001:2365: de dag kyang gcig dang du ma'i mtha' dang bral ba'i phyir mi phyed pas na rdo rje ste/
NK060(i)001:2366: de nyid las mngon sum du snang bas na phyung ngo zhes tha snyad du btags so //
NK060(i)001:2367: gleng gzhi bsdus pa nges tshig dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:2370: gzhung rgyas pa dang sbyar ba kho na las ma gsungs kyang /
NK060(i)001:2371: bla ma brgyud pa'i gdams ngag ltar na bshad tshul gsum gyis ston no //
NK060(i)001:2372: de yang e ma zhes pa ngam pa'i tshig ste/
NK060(i)001:2373: rangs te yon tan la ngam pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2374: ma rangs te skyon la gam pa gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:2376: de yang spyi dang bye brag gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:2377: spyir ni e zhes pa theg pa rim pa dgu'i don la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2378: e ma zhes pa dkyil 'khor rim pa bdun gyi don la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2379: e ma'o zhes pa gzhung rgyas pa'i don la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2380: bye brag tu theg pa rim pa dgu la sbyar na/
NK060(i)001:2381: e zhes pas rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa gsum la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2382: e ma zhes pas phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa gsum la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2383: e ma'o zhes pas nang pa thabs kyi theg pa gsum la ngam pa ste/
NK060(i)001:2384: de yang 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sems nyid
NK060(i)001:2385: ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid du
NK060(i)001:2386: rtogs pa/ gang du bsdu na 'dir bsdu la/
NK060(i)001:2387: gang sdud na a ti yo ga'i thig pa sdud/
NK060(i)001:2388: chos thams cad sku dang ye shes shes kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang sgyur ba ma h+aa'i theg pa sdud/
NK060(i)001:2389: chos thams cad dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med
NK060(i)001:2390: pa'i dkyil 'khor du ston pa a nu'i theg pa
NK060(i)001:2391: sdud/ theg pa dgu'i nang nas theg pa gong ma
NK060(i)001:2392: ba rnams thugs rje ngang gis skyes ba'i yul nyan
NK060(i)001:2394: don dam mtshan ma med pa'i byin rlabs rdo rje
NK060(i)001:2395: dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba nyid lha
NK060(i)001:2396: so bdun gyi dkyil 'khor la sogs par gsal ba
NK060(i)001:2398: theg pa snga phyi gnyis la ltos pa'i ting nge
NK060(i)001:2399: 'dzin gyis rang sa'i 'bras bu rigs bzhi'i dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:2400: bsgrub pa u pa ya'i theg pa sdud/
NK060(i)001:2401: don dam pa chos kyi dbyings gzugs brnyan rdzob rigs
NK060(i)001:2402: gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du snang ba kri ya'i theg
NK060(i)001:2403: pa sdud/ phyi nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis sgyu
NK060(i)001:2404: ma tsam du rtogs pa rang rgyal gyi theg pa
NK060(i)001:2405: pa sdud/ sdud/ spros pa'i mtha' rnam par dag par dbu ma'i theg pa sdud/
NK060(i)001:2406: sems rang rig rang gsal rtogs pas ni sems tsam gyi theg pa sdud do //
NK060(i)001:2407: sku gsung thugs zhes pa man chad theg pa dgu'i 'bras bu'o //
NK060(i)001:2408: dkyil 'khor bdun dang sbyar te bshad na/
NK060(i)001:2409: e zhes pas rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2410: e ma zhes pas gzhan dkyil 'khor drug la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2411: e ma'o zhes pas rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor la ngam pa ste/
NK060(i)001:2412: de yang ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings te/
NK060(i)001:2413: gang du bsdu na 'dir bsdu la/
NK060(i)001:2414: gang sdud na rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor sdud/
NK060(i)001:2415: mnyam pa nyid des 'khor 'das gnyis ka la dbang sgyur bas rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor sdud/
NK060(i)001:2416: ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor la gzhan don thugs rje
NK060(i)001:2417: ngang ngam shugs kyis 'byung ba rang bzhin 'bras bu
NK060(i)001:2419: sems mi rtog pa'i ngang du rang snang ba nyid de ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor sdud/
NK060(i)001:2420: lha dang gzhal yas khang bsgom pa'i bya bas lhag
NK060(i)001:2421: pas na lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:2422: sdud/ rnam rtog phra rags lha yab yum gyi gzugs brnyan mtshon pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor sdud/
NK060(i)001:2423: rtsa dang thig le rnam par dag pas bde ba'i
NK060(i)001:2424: ye shes su gsal ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil
NK060(i)001:2425: 'khor sdud/ tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa sku gsung
NK060(i)001:2426: thugs dang yon tan phrin las kyi rigs gtso 'khor
NK060(i)001:2427: dang bcas pa tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor sdud/
NK060(i)001:2428: sel med ces pa man chad kyis dkyil 'khor bdun
NK060(i)001:2429: gyi yon tan 'bras bu dang bcas pa ston par
NK060(i)001:2430: byed do // gzhung rgyas pa dang sbyar te bshad na/
NK060(i)001:2431: e zhes pas ston pa phun sum tshogs pa la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2432: e ma zhes pas gnas phun sum tshogs pa la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2433: e ma'o zhes pas 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la ngam pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2435: gang du bsdu na bsdu pa'i gzhung 'dir bsdu la/
NK060(i)001:2436: gang sdud na gzhung rgyas pa sdud de/
NK060(i)001:2437: sdud pa'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan ni/
NK060(i)001:2438: tshig mthun dag don mthun du byung ba'i phyir sdud do //
NK060(i)001:2439: de yang sems nyid lhun gyis grub pa'i de bzhin
NK060(i)001:2440: nyid dang mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings nyid du ye
NK060(i)001:2441: nas gnas pa/ gang du sdud na 'dir sdud la/
NK060(i)001:2442: gang sdud na gnas kyi rang bzhin nam/
NK060(i)001:2444: ya ki na 'og min phyi dang nang /
NK060(i)001:2445: rgya phyogs zhes sogs tshig rkang gsum po de sdud de/
NK060(i)001:2446: sdud pa'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan ni/
NK060(i)001:2447: ya ki na don chos nyid rgya chad dang bral
NK060(i)001:2448: ba phyi nang med pa mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings
NK060(i)001:2449: su 'dug la/ 'di na'ang don de ltar du 'dug
NK060(i)001:2450: pas tshig mthun dang don mthun du byung ba'i phyir
NK060(i)001:2451: su 'dug la/ sdud gsungs mdzod/ de'i 'phros kyis 'og ma rnams la'ang shes par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:2452: don gong ma las mnga' mdzad cing dbang sgyur ba/
NK060(i)001:2454: gang na ston pa'i ngo bo/
NK060(i)001:2455: ya ki na sku mdun zhes pa nas dbu gsum dang ldan pa zhes pa'i bar sdud/
NK060(i)001:2456: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag go //
NK060(i)001:2457: rtogs pa'i rig pa nyid ye shes lngar gsal ba/
NK060(i)001:2458: 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba/
NK060(i)001:2460: gang na ston pa mya ngan las 'das pa dang dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin/
NK060(i)001:2461: ya ki na de bzhin zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:2462: bdag nyid ces pa'i bar sdud/
NK060(i)001:2463: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag /dus gsum gyi chos
NK060(i)001:2464: dang rgya ma chad par thugs rje chen po'i ngang
NK060(i)001:2466: gang na ston pa 'khor ba dang dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin/
NK060(i)001:2467: ya ki na ma lus zhes pa nas rang bzhin te zhes pa'i bar sdud/
NK060(i)001:2468: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag /rtogs pa'i rig pa
NK060(i)001:2469: nyid la 'bras bu sku dang ye shes thams cad
NK060(i)001:2470: rdzogs pa'i rtsa bar 'gyur ba nyid de/
NK060(i)001:2472: gang na gnas kyi ngo bo/
NK060(i)001:2473: ya ki na gzhi tshad med ces pa nas klubs pa zhes pa'i bar sdud/
NK060(i)001:2474: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag /rnam par thar pa bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin te/
NK060(i)001:2477: ya ki na rnam par thar pa zhes pa nas sgo khyud can zhes pa'i bar sdud/
NK060(i)001:2478: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag /theg pa brgyad nas bgrod pa mtshon pa'i gzugs brnyan te/
NK060(i)001:2480: gang na rta babs kyi don/
NK060(i)001:2481: ya ki na rnam par shes pa nas dran pa zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:2482: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag /thams cad rang rig sgyu mar gsal ba/
NK060(i)001:2484: gang na sems can gyi gdan/
NK060(i)001:2485: ya ki na mi 'jigs zhes pa nas khri dang zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:2486: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag /spyad kyang zhes pas skyon gyis ma gos pas rnam par dag pa/
NK060(i)001:2489: ya ki na gos pa med pa pad ma zhes pa de sdud/
NK060(i)001:2490: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag /ma skyes pa'i ye
NK060(i)001:2491: shes nyid thabs dang shes rab tu gsal ba ni
NK060(i)001:2492: cir yang mi 'gag par rang snang ba/
NK060(i)001:2495: ya ki na rang bzhin zhes pa nas 'khor dang zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:2496: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag /sku de bzhin gshegs
NK060(i)001:2497: pa dang gsung pad+ma thugs rdo rje dang yon tan
NK060(i)001:2498: rin po che phrin las las kyi rigs te/
NK060(i)001:2499: phung po dang 'byung ba ye nas kar dag pa/
NK060(i)001:2501: gang na rang bzhin nam dgongs pa gnyis su med pa'i 'khor/
NK060(i)001:2502: ya ki na rigs lnga yab dang yum/
NK060(i)001:2503: bcom ldan 'das zhes pa nas rgyal po dang zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK060(i)001:2504: btsun mo zhes pa nas la sogs pa zhes pa'i bar sdud/
NK060(i)001:2505: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag /rtogs pa sku dang
NK060(i)001:2506: ye shes su gsal ba las gzhan pa'i sel med
NK060(i)001:2508: gang na gnyis su med par bzhugs tshul tshad dang bcas pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2509: 'khor de dag kun mang ba dang khyab pa'i tshad/
NK060(i)001:2510: ya ki na btsun mo zhes pa nas bzhugs so zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK060(i)001:2511: de lta bu'i zhes pa nas bzhugs so zhes pa'i bar sdud/
NK060(i)001:2512: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag /sku mdog dang 'od
NK060(i)001:2513: zer la sogs pa'i yon tan lngas sems can gyi
NK060(i)001:2514: don mdzad pa/ gang du na 'dir gang na sku mdog gi don/
NK060(i)001:2515: ya ki na de dag kyang zhes pa nas 'tsher ba zhes pa'i bar sdud/
NK060(i)001:2516: de'i gnad ka' ma rgyu mtshan brtag /dgos 'dod re ba yid bzhin gyi rin po che ltar skong ba/
NK060(i)001:2518: gang na rin po che'i gdan/
NK060(i)001:2519: ya ki na rin po che'i gdan la zhes pa de sdud/
NK060(i)001:2520: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag /sku gsung thugs mi zad par ldan rgyan gyi 'khor lor rang snang ba/
NK060(i)001:2522: gang na rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor/
NK060(i)001:2523: ya ki na de nas byang chub zhes pa nas sogs pa zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:2524: de'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtag /rdo rje mchog gi
NK060(i)001:2525: gnas nyid do zhes pa gleng gzhi bsdus pa'i nges
NK060(i)001:2526: tshig ste/ ston 'khor gnas gsum tshogs pa'i dus na
NK060(i)001:2527: rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud mchog tu gyur pa bstan
NK060(i)001:2528: pa 'di nyid kyi byung khungs sam gnas nyid do
NK060(i)001:2529: tshig ste/ zhes pa'am/ yang na gzhung bsdu ba'i tshig
NK060(i)001:2530: bzhis mtshon pa'i ting nge 'dzin las gsang sngags rdo
NK060(i)001:2531: rje theg pa mchog gi 'bras bu 'byung pa'i gnas
NK060(i)001:2533: bka' gsang sngags mtshon pa'i tshig go //
NK060(i)001:2535: zhes snang ba gsum mi phyed pas na rdo rje/
NK060(i)001:2536: nyams su lon dka' bas na gsang ba'i don te/
NK060(i)001:2537: de dag mtshon par byed pa'i tshig tu'o zhes pa'am/
NK060(i)001:2538: yang na zhes le'u'i don thams cad bsdu ba'i tshig
NK060(i)001:2539: bzhi ru dril ba 'di ni rdo rje 'dzin pa
NK060(i)001:2540: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje'i tshig tu'o
NK060(i)001:2541: zhes kyang bya'o // de lta bu'i gleng gzhi bsdus pa 'di la/
NK060(i)001:2542: brgal lan du byas na brtag pa lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:2543: ston pas bsdus sam 'khor gyis bsdus/
NK060(i)001:2544: gleng gzhi yin nam rgyud don yin/
NK060(i)001:2545: tshig 'dus nas sdud dam don 'dus nas sdud/
NK060(i)001:2546: bsdus par dgos ches ci yod/
NK060(i)001:2550: drug pa dang bzhi kho nar bsdu ba 'byung la/
NK060(i)001:2551: le'u gzhan la bsdu ba mi 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ci yin brtag par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:2552: brtag pa dang po ni ston pas bsdus so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2553: sdud pa po gsang bdag ma yin par thal/
NK060(i)001:2558: 'khor gyi nang na skal mchog ldan //
NK060(i)001:2559: 'dul ba'i dus bab gsang ba'i bdag /lag na rdo rjes bsdu ba mdzad //
NK060(i)001:2561: yang 'khor gyis bsdus so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2562: ston pas gsungs nas bsdus sam ma gsungs par bsdus/
NK060(i)001:2564: gleng bslang la dgos pa med par 'gyur la/
NK060(i)001:2566: sku gsung thugs rdo rje las byung ngo zhes pas/
NK060(i)001:2567: rigs lnga dbyer mi phyed pa rgyal ba drug pa nyid kyis gsungs pa dang 'gal zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2568: 'di la rje drings pa'i bzhed kyis/
NK060(i)001:2569: bsdu ba gang gis bsdus na 'khor gyis bsdus/
NK060(i)001:2570: de yang gsang bdag gis bsdus so //
NK060(i)001:2571: ston pas gsungs sam ma gsungs na/
NK060(i)001:2573: sngon 'byung 'og min chos kyi dbyings pho brang du gleng gzhi tshogs/
NK060(i)001:2575: gleng bslang la dgos pa med par mi 'gyur la/
NK060(i)001:2576: mi yul du sdud pa po gsang ba'i bdag po
NK060(i)001:2577: phyag na rdo rjes tshig dang yi ger 'god pa'i
NK060(i)001:2578: tshe bsdus pa yin pas mi 'gal lo gsung /
NK060(i)001:2579: rgya gab gong pa na re/
NK060(i)001:2580: ma la ya ru gleng gzhi rgyas pa de dag lo rgyus su gsungs nas/
NK060(i)001:2581: de dag bsdu na 'dir bsdu zhes sdud pa pos gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:2583: ston pa dang 'chad pa'i skyes bu ltar gsal bas 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2585: dbang thob nas ston sdud khyad par med de/
NK060(i)001:2587: dbang rdzogs pa rigs drug pa nyid du sdud pa'i phyir ro zhes pas gsal lo //
NK060(i)001:2588: yang bsdu ba 'di gleng gzhi bsdus pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:2589: de'i don bsdu na 'dir 'dus zhes gsungs kyang /
NK060(i)001:2590: rgyud don du 'gyur ba'i skyon med do //
NK060(i)001:2591: gzhan yang ston pas gsungs pa tsam gyis rgyud don du 'gyur na/
NK060(i)001:2592: e ma bde gshegs snying po las //
NK060(i)001:2593: zhes pa thun mong gi gleng bslang yang rgyud don du 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:2594: tshang tshul nas rgyud don tshang yang yin tshul nas gleng gzhir mi 'gal te/
NK060(i)001:2595: gleng gzhi'i le'u ste zhes pas mngon no zhes gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:2597: bsdu ba 'di gleng gzhi yin nam rgyud don yin/
NK060(i)001:2598: gleng gzhi yin na 'di nyid las de nas de
NK060(i)001:2599: bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang gnyis su med
NK060(i)001:2600: par gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi gsang
NK060(i)001:2601: ba nyid sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon tan
NK060(i)001:2602: dang phrin las rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK060(i)001:2604: rgyal ba kun tu bzang po'i dgos pa las phyung bar bzhad pas 'gal lo //
NK060(i)001:2605: rgyud don yin na gleng bslang ba la dgos pa med par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:2606: cis te na gleng ma bslang bar rgyud don gsungs nas 'dug pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:2608: gleng gzhi le'u ste zhes pas gsal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2610: rgyud don yin kyang gleng bslang la dgos pa med par mi 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:2611: 'og min du ston pa kun tu bzang pos gleng bslang nas gsungs la/
NK060(i)001:2612: ri ma la yar phyag rdor gyis tshig dang yi
NK060(i)001:2613: ger 'god pa'i tshe gsungs pa yin pas gleng bslang
NK060(i)001:2614: ba la dgos pa med par mi 'gyur gsung /
NK060(i)001:2615: g.yung ston chos kyi mgon po na re/
NK060(i)001:2616: bsdu ba 'di 'og min gyi cha nas gleng gzhi bsdus pa ltar snang la/
NK060(i)001:2617: mi yul gyi cha nas mtshan man chad rang rgyud don yin nam bsam mo gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:2620: gnas skabs rang rang gi tshig don gnyis ka 'dus nas sdud de/
NK060(i)001:2621: sngar 'bru bsnan pa'i skabs su bshad zin to //
NK060(i)001:2622: yang bsdu ba rang la dgos ched ci yod ce na/
NK060(i)001:2623: ma zin pa zin par byed pa la dgos/
NK060(i)001:2624: zin pa brtan par byed pa la dgos/
NK060(i)001:2625: chos sgra las su mi 'gyur bar byed pa la dgos zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:2626: yang le'u bzhi kho nar bsdu ba 'byung la gzhan du mi 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2628: le'u dang por chos thams cad kyi bca' gzhi 'cha' bas 'ong ba yin/
NK060(i)001:2629: le'u gsum par lam thams cad kyi sngon du lta
NK060(i)001:2630: ba 'gro bas lam gyi thog mar lta ba gtan
NK060(i)001:2631: la 'bebs pa'i skabs su 'ong ba yin //
NK060(i)001:2632: le'u bzhi par lam ting nge 'dzin 'byung bas 'ong ba yin/
NK060(i)001:2633: le'u drug par 'bras bu 'byung bas 'ong ba yin gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:2634: gtsang pa byi ston gyi bzhed kyis/
NK060(i)001:2636: la lar mi 'ong ba 'di rgyud gzhung rang shugs kyis byung ba yin gsung /
NK060(i)001:2637: rgyud gzhung rang shugs kyis ka la lar 'ong /
NK060(i)001:2638: la lar mi 'ong ba ci yin zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2639: 'o na mi rnams kyis kyang sna 'di byad kyi dkyil kho nar 'ong la/
NK060(i)001:2640: o lko sogs pa gzhan du mi 'ong ba ci yin byas pas/
NK060(i)001:2641: las kyi dbang gis 'ong ba yin zer na/
NK060(i)001:2642: 'dir yang rgyud gzhung rang shugs kyis byung ba yin no byas la mgo basgre'o gsung /
NK060(i)001:2643: kho bo ni drings pa ltar du 'thad par sems te/
NK060(i)001:2644: le'u dang por chos kyi bca' gzhi bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:2647: drug par rgyu shes pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2649: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid rnams kyi bca' gzhi phal cher bstan pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:2652: gsang ba'i zhes pa rgyud kyi rang bzhin snying po
NK060(i)001:2653: rgyud kyi che pa de kho na nyid rgyud kyi
NK060(i)001:2654: mtshan nyid nges pa rgyud kyi nges don las mtshan
NK060(i)001:2655: gyi gzhi ru gda'/ gnas dang /
NK060(i)001:2659: dus phun sum tshogs pas na gleng gzhi bstan pa'i
NK060(i)001:2660: gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas na le'u ste yas bgrangs
NK060(i)001:2661: dang po'i don du gda' 'o////da ni bka' rang gnyer
NK060(i)001:2662: gyis sa bcad na/ le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su yod pa las/
NK060(i)001:2664: slob dpon 'grel ba gdams ngag mkhan gyis sa bcad na/
NK060(i)001:2671: de la yang 'chad mkhan rig pa'i sgros kyis sa bcad na gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:2677: gzhung dngos la spyi don gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:2678: ston pas mdun bsu ste gleng bslang ba'am thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng bslang ba dang /
NK060(i)001:2679: 'khor gyis gus pas zhu ba zhus te gleng bslang ba'am thun mong du gleng bslang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:2680: de dag gi go ba ni/
NK060(i)001:2681: lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyi ched dam/
NK060(i)001:2682: rgyud 'di nyid 'byung ba'i rkyen du gyur pa ni thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng bslang yin la/
NK060(i)001:2683: go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched dam/
NK060(i)001:2684: bstan pa mtha' dag 'byung ba'i rkyen du gyur pa
NK060(i)001:2685: ni thun mong gi gleng bslang ba yin zhes bla
NK060(i)001:2686: ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:2687: de la spyi don dang po thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng ba slang ba la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:2689: dbang gnyis kyi las thun mong du bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2690: dang po gsang dbang bskur ba la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:2692: gsang dbang gi nges tshig go //
NK060(i)001:2693: gleng bslang ba la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:2694: yab kyi gleng bslang ba dang /
NK060(i)001:2698: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:2700: rgyu gleng gzhi bstan pa la de rkyen gleng bslang ba ston pas na nas/
NK060(i)001:2701: bcom ldan 'das ni 'bru lngar bshad zin la/
NK060(i)001:2702: 'khor ba'i byed pa po rtog pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2703: 'das pa'i byed pa po rang rig pa'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:2704: gnyis rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pas na rdo rje
NK060(i)001:2705: yin te/ ngo bo 'dus ma byas shing mtshan nyid skye 'jigs dang bral ba de la/
NK060(i)001:2706: spang bya mi dmigs shing spyod yul yongs su dag pas na kun tu bzang po zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:2707: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pas bsdus pa'i
NK060(i)001:2708: chos thams cad lhag ma ma lus pa'i rang bzhin
NK060(i)001:2709: drug pa nyid kyi bdag nyid du tshul gcig cing
NK060(i)001:2710: mi phyed pas na sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i bdag
NK060(i)001:2711: nyid des/ btsun mo ni spyad par bya ba dang
NK060(i)001:2712: sras kyi 'byung khungs su gyur pa sngar bshad pa
NK060(i)001:2714: khyad par ni chos kyis yid skyed par byed pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2715: bya ba mo ni yul 'dus byas dang 'dus ma
NK060(i)001:2716: byas kyi chos la spang bya mi dmigs pas na
NK060(i)001:2718: sku'i phyag rgya chen po'i gzungs so //
NK060(i)001:2719: de la snyoms par 'jug pa ni gdul bya'i snang ba dang rjes su mthun pa ste/
NK060(i)001:2720: ji ltar 'jug par gyur ba'i tshul ni/
NK060(i)001:2721: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pas rol par gyur to //
NK060(i)001:2722: de ltar zhugs pa la dgos pa ci yod ce na/
NK060(i)001:2723: 'byung bar ma nges pa'i de bzhin gshegs par ni
NK060(i)001:2724: 'gro ba ril kyang 'gyur ba'i phyir phyogs bcu dang
NK060(i)001:2725: dus bzhis bsdus pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa ma lus
NK060(i)001:2726: pa thams cad kyang lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:2727: gcig gi rang bzhin du dbyer med par gsal bas/
NK060(i)001:2728: de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu bzang po nyid/
NK060(i)001:2729: de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu bzang mo nyid la
NK060(i)001:2730: lhan cig pa'i 'khor la dbang bskur ba'i ched du
NK060(i)001:2731: tshig tu brjod pa dang 'dra bar sku nyams su
NK060(i)001:2732: bstar ba'i don 'og nas 'byung ba 'di gsal bar
NK060(i)001:2733: brjod do // sku nyams su bstar ba'i don/
NK060(i)001:2736: thabs lam ltar na chags pa spyad kyang spyod yul yongs su dag pa'am/
NK060(i)001:2737: grol lam ltar na rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes su ye nas sangs rgyas pa la ngam pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2738: rdo rje ni thabs lam ltar na bde stong dbyer mi phyed/
NK060(i)001:2739: grol lam ltar na snang stong dbyer mi phyed pas sam/
NK060(i)001:2740: don rang rig pa'i ye shes la lha rtog dbyer mi phyed pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:2741: phung po ni du ma spungs pa'i phyir te/
NK060(i)001:2742: gzugs la sogs pa lnga'i yan lag ni rtog pa'i rang bzhin brgyad cu ste/
NK060(i)001:2743: de dag ye nas sku gsum du sangs rgyas pa yin kyang /
NK060(i)001:2744: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ni sku lngar lhun gyis grub cing rigs lnga ru grags pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2745: mig rna ba sna lce'i rnam par shes pa dang bzhi/
NK060(i)001:2746: gzugs sgra dri ro dang yul bzhi/
NK060(i)001:2747: mig rna ba sna lce'i dbang po dang bzhi ste skye mched bcu gnyis dang /
NK060(i)001:2748: gsang ba'i rnam shes dang yul dang dbang po ste/
NK060(i)001:2749: gsang ba'i khams gsum rnams kyi khongs nas gsang ba gsum 'dus kyi reg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2750: 'das ma 'ongs da ltar ma nges pa'i dus te bzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:2751: rtag chad bdag mtshan bzhi ma yin pa'i gya phyi log bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:2752: de ltar rtog pa'i bye brag mang po kun kyang byang chub sems dpa' dang sems ma'i tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:2753: khro bo dang khro mo'i dkyil 'khor nyid do //
NK060(i)001:2754: de bzhin du sa sangs rgyas spyan dang /
NK060(i)001:2757: rlung dam tshig sgrol ma ste/
NK060(i)001:2758: gzhan yang byung khungs kyi ming can nam mkha' ni nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'o //
NK060(i)001:2759: de'i phyir 'dod pa dang gzugs dang gzugs med kyi
NK060(i)001:2760: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa thams cad kyang ye
NK060(i)001:2761: nas rang sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi zhing khams yin
NK060(i)001:2762: no // de yang ming las dngos po mtshan ma ste/
NK060(i)001:2763: tha snyad bzhis bsdus pa thams cad dang 'khor ba
NK060(i)001:2764: dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos so cog ma
NK060(i)001:2765: lus ba kun kyang sku dang ye shes su kar
NK060(i)001:2766: dag ste sangs rgyas pa nyid las gzhan pa ni
NK060(i)001:2767: ma yin no // tha snyad bzhi po de dag
NK060(i)001:2768: rang sangs rgyas nyid yin pa de las gzhan pa'i
NK060(i)001:2769: ma yin no // chos/ dngos po rnams kyi ngo
NK060(i)001:2770: bo la btsal kyang sangs rgyas nyid kyi ye shes
NK060(i)001:2771: kyi spyan gyis kyang mi gzigs shing thob par byar
NK060(i)001:2772: med pas na mi brnyes so //
NK060(i)001:2776: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i 'khor gyi de bzhin
NK060(i)001:2777: gshegs pa thams cad ston pas sku nyams su bstar
NK060(i)001:2778: ba'i don ched du brjod pa de la mnyes par
NK060(i)001:2779: gyur to // yum gyi gleng bslang ba la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:2781: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:2783: de nas zhes pa la yi ge snga phyi yod
NK060(i)001:2784: kyang dus mnyam par gsungs pas don 'brel ni mi
NK060(i)001:2785: rtsi la/ tshig 'brel gyi dbang du byas na yab kyi gleng bslang ba bstan pa la de/
NK060(i)001:2786: yum gyi gleng bslang ba ston pas na nas/
NK060(i)001:2787: btsun mo bya ba mo chos kun tu bzang mos/
NK060(i)001:2788: bcom ldan 'das yid kun tu bzang po dang thabs
NK060(i)001:2789: lam ltar na thig le nyi zla gnyis su med
NK060(i)001:2790: pa dang / grol lam ltar na dgongs pa gnyis
NK060(i)001:2791: su med par gyur nas lhan cig pa'i 'khor rnams
NK060(i)001:2792: kyi ched du sku nyams su bstar ba'i don brjod
NK060(i)001:2794: sku nyams su bstar ba'i don dngos so //
NK060(i)001:2796: kye zhes pa ni 'bod pa'i tshig /ma'o zhes pa ni ngam pa'i tshig ste/
NK060(i)001:2798: bdag gi bde ba gzhan la bstan pa'i phyir kye zhes lhan cig pa'i 'khor la bos nas/
NK060(i)001:2799: ma'o zhes sngar ma myong ba'i bde ba'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:2800: thun mong ma yin pa bstan du yod do zhes
NK060(i)001:2801: ngam pa'o // de ji lta bu zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2802: phyogs bcu dang stong gsum dang khams gsum dang snang
NK060(i)001:2803: ba ni rang gi ngo bos stongs pa'i phyir na
NK060(i)001:2804: kun gzhi dri med chos kyi sku ni ye nas
NK060(i)001:2805: stong zhing bdag gnyis kyi sa dben pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2806: de yang spong ba rdo rje las/
NK060(i)001:2807: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK060(i)001:2808: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK060(i)001:2809: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK060(i)001:2811: de bzhin du srid pa gsum po nyid dag pa sku gsum po'i zhing khams yin no //
NK060(i)001:2812: mtha' ma'i phyir na snyigs ma ste grangs ni lnga ru nges pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2818: tshe/ las/ nyon mongs pa'i snyigs ma'o //
NK060(i)001:2819: de yang dus kyi snyigs ma ni rtsod ldan no //
NK060(i)001:2820: sems can gyi snyigs ma ni de'i dus su skyes pa/
NK060(i)001:2821: tshe'i snyigs ma ni tshe lo brgya pa man chad/
NK060(i)001:2822: las kyi snyigs ma ni mi dge ba bcu la spyod pa/
NK060(i)001:2823: nyon mongs pa'i snyigs ma ni gnyen pos mi non pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2824: de dag kyang kun brtags nyid kyi phyir/
NK060(i)001:2825: rang bzhin ma dmigs pas na bde ba chen po dang ldan pa de rol pa'i gnas so //
NK060(i)001:2826: des na phung po lnga nyid yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku lnga'o //
NK060(i)001:2827: de ltar phyogs bcu stong khams/
NK060(i)001:2830: phung po lngar snang ba ste/
NK060(i)001:2831: tha snyad bzhis bsdus pa thams cad yon tan nam 'bras bu'i mchog gi bsgrub bya'i snying po yin pas/
NK060(i)001:2832: de las gzhan du rgyal ba'i chos shig mi btsal te/
NK060(i)001:2833: tha snyad bzhi'i rang bzhin nyid ye nas chos sku
NK060(i)001:2834: yin pa las de las gzhan pa'i 'bras bu chos
NK060(i)001:2835: sku zhes bya ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos
NK060(i)001:2836: shig btsal kyang gud na rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas
NK060(i)001:2837: rgyal ba nyid kyis kyang mi brnyes so //
NK060(i)001:2838: gsang dbang gi nges tshig go //
NK060(i)001:2840: zhes brjod pas ston pa thams cad sku dang ye
NK060(i)001:2841: shes su ye nas sangs rgyas par de bzhin gshegs
NK060(i)001:2842: pa rgyal mchog kun bzang yab yum gnyis kyis mkhyen
NK060(i)001:2843: to // gnyis pa dbang gnyis kyi las thun mong du bstan pa la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:2844: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2845: sems bskyed pa'i rim pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2846: sems bskyed pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:2849: gsang dbang bskur ba bstan pa la de shes rab ye shes dang /
NK060(i)001:2850: dbyer med bde chen gyi dbang gnyis kyi las thun mong bstan pas na nas/
NK060(i)001:2851: thabs lam ltar na ston pa yab yum thig le nyi zla dang /
NK060(i)001:2852: grol lam ltar na yab yum dgongs pa gnyis su
NK060(i)001:2853: med pa'i bde ba'i ye shes la mnga' mdzad pas
NK060(i)001:2854: na bdag nyid chen po des lhan cig pa'i 'khor
NK060(i)001:2855: rnams la ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i dgongs pa'am/
NK060(i)001:2856: sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs de nyid/
NK060(i)001:2857: yas babs zag bcas kyi dga' bzhi dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyis mtshon nas/
NK060(i)001:2858: mas brtan zag med kyi dga' bzhi rang bzhin lhan
NK060(i)001:2859: cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyi sems rnam par shes
NK060(i)001:2860: pa tshogs brgyad ye shes lnga la dngos su bskyed
NK060(i)001:2861: pa'i thabs/ sems rim lnga 'og nas 'byung ba'i 'di dag gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:2862: sems bskyed pa'i rim pa 'di la spar khab kyis gsang ba ltar kho na las ma bkral kyang /
NK060(i)001:2863: rje sgro phug pa'i bzhed kyis/
NK060(i)001:2864: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du 'chad de/
NK060(i)001:2865: bshad thabs dang po phyi ltar man ngag lam rim
NK060(i)001:2866: gyi le'u gsum pas rgyab byas nas spyod lam bzhi
NK060(i)001:2869: spyod lam bzhi ye nas rang spyod yul yongs su dag pa la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2871: spyod lam bzhi spyad kyang de chos nyid du 'char ba la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2873: de ka gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i khyad chos yin pa la ngam pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2874: de nyid tshogs gnyis yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK060(i)001:2875: rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo yin pas kyang
NK060(i)001:2876: gsang / phal pa rnams kyis spyod yul du ma gyur pa'i phyir kyang gsang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:2877: de yang rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba rtog shing /
NK060(i)001:2878: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin lam du byed pa'i rnal 'byor pas/
NK060(i)001:2879: spyod lam bzhi lam du ji ltar 'khyer zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2881: nyal zhing gnyid log pa dang /
NK060(i)001:2883: 'gro zhing 'ong ba'i spyod lam bzhi gang spyod kyang /
NK060(i)001:2889: don dam pa'i bden pa ste dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2893: 'gro 'ong bar snang ba'i ni kun rdzob kyi bden pa ste/
NK060(i)001:2894: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:2895: skyes ba nyid na skye ba med //
NK060(i)001:2897: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK060(i)001:2898: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK060(i)001:2900: dbyer med kyi bden pa ste/
NK060(i)001:2901: kun rdzob sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK060(i)001:2902: rang snang ba nyid don dam dkor bdun ngo bo
NK060(i)001:2903: nyid du lhun gyis grub pa las ma g.yos pa'o
NK060(i)001:2904: // de ltar bden gsum mnyam nyid kyi ngang nas/
NK060(i)001:2905: lam pas spyod lam bzhi mi 'gog pas bsod nams
NK060(i)001:2906: kyi tshogs dang mi 'dzin pas ye shes kyi tshogs
NK060(i)001:2908: bshad thabs gnyis pa nang ltar lam bskyed rdzogs dang sbyar te bshad na/
NK060(i)001:2909: e ma zhes pas snang ba bzhis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad skye ba med pa la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2910: ngo mtshar zhes pas thams cad skyes pa la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2911: rmad kyi chos zhes pas skyes pa nyid na skye ba med pa la ngam pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2912: de dag tshogs gnyis yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK060(i)001:2913: rgyas sku lnga po kun gyi thugs kyi brnag bya
NK060(i)001:2915: skye ba med pa la sogs pa lnga po 'di la bshad tshul gnyis kyis 'chad de/
NK060(i)001:2916: dang po bskyed rim sku lnga rkyang pa ltar du bshad pa'am/
NK060(i)001:2917: grol lam rim gyis pa ltar du bshad na/
NK060(i)001:2918: don dam byang chub kyi sems la snang ba bzhi
NK060(i)001:2919: skye ba med pa las kun rdzob byang chub kyi
NK060(i)001:2920: sems la thams cad skye ba'o //
NK060(i)001:2921: de ltar kun rdzob kyi bden pa la skye bsdo
NK060(i)001:2922: ba'i dus nyid na don dam pa'i bden pa la
NK060(i)001:2923: skyes pa med pa'i phyir bden gnyis dbyer med du
NK060(i)001:2924: la bzla ba'o // de ni sems lnga las g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems/
NK060(i)001:2925: sku lnga las chos kyi sku/
NK060(i)001:2926: ye shes lnga las stong pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK060(i)001:2927: de'i 'gro sa kyis gzhan 'og ma bzhi po yang shes par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:2928: 'gag sogs 'jig 'jug byang chub kyi sems mngon par byang chub pa'i sku/
NK060(i)001:2929: me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK060(i)001:2931: gnas pa byang chub kyi sems longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku/
NK060(i)001:2932: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK060(i)001:2934: smon pa byang chub kyi sems rdo rje'i sku/
NK060(i)001:2935: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NK060(i)001:2937: mthar phyin pa byang chub kyi sems sprul pa'i sku/
NK060(i)001:2938: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK060(i)001:2939: gnyis pa rdzogs rim sku lnga lhun grub tu bshad pa'am/
NK060(i)001:2940: grol lam cig car ba ltar du bshad na/
NK060(i)001:2945: 'gro 'ong med ces pa nga ni don dam pa'i bden pa la/
NK060(i)001:2949: mthar phyin gyi sems lnga dus gcig la rdzogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2953: 'gro dang 'ong zhes pa lnga ni kun rdzob kyi
NK060(i)001:2954: bden pa la sems lnga dus gcig la rdzogs pa'o
NK060(i)001:2955: // skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK060(i)001:2957: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK060(i)001:2958: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK060(i)001:2960: ces pa lnga ni dbyer med kyi bden pa la/
NK060(i)001:2961: sems lnga dus gcig la rdzogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:2963: lam cig car ba sems lnga nas bgrod dam mi bgrod/
NK060(i)001:2966: sems 'di dag sa gcig na tshang ba'i phyir cig car 'jug pa'i lam zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:2972: lam rim gyis pa dang khyad med du thal/
NK060(i)001:2975: 'dod cig car ba yin pa nyams so //
NK060(i)001:2976: cig car bgrod na sems lnga'i tha snyad ma grub par thal/
NK060(i)001:2979: 'dod na khas blangs kyis gsal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2980: rgya gab gong ba na re/
NK060(i)001:2981: sems lnga ngo bo dbyer med du bgrod pa 'thad de/
NK060(i)001:2982: sems rim lnga dang 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:2983: rim gyis pa ltar sems rim lnga yod kyang 'di'i
NK060(i)001:2984: yon tan dus gcig la rdzogs pas mi 'gal lo
NK060(i)001:2986: thabs lam 'og sgo ltar bshad na/
NK060(i)001:2989: g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems/
NK060(i)001:2991: e ma zhes pas 'dod chags kyi spyod pas 'khor bar mi 'ching ba la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2992: ngo mtshar zhes pas de nyid spyod yul dag pa'i 'bras bu sku dang ye shes thob pa la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2993: rmad kyi chos zhes pa de ka sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i khyad chos su 'dug pa la ngam/
NK060(i)001:2994: de nyid tshogs gnyis yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK060(i)001:2995: rgyas sku lnga po kun gyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo'am
NK060(i)001:2996: thugs kyi brnag bya yin pa dang thabs kyi lam
NK060(i)001:2997: 'di khe nyen dang bcas pa'i phyir gsang ngo //
NK060(i)001:2998: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la nyi zla byang chub kyi sems skye ba med pa las/
NK060(i)001:2999: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su
NK060(i)001:3000: blangs pa'i dus su thig le 'gog yos tsam na
NK060(i)001:3001: bden ba 'go ldang ba'i tshul du thams cad skyes
NK060(i)001:3002: pa ni g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems so //
NK060(i)001:3003: de ltar dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:3004: la bden ba skyes pa ltar snang bsngo ba'i dus
NK060(i)001:3005: nyid na rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:3006: la skyes pa dang ma skyes pa dbyer med du
NK060(i)001:3007: la bazla'o // de yang spar khab las/
NK060(i)001:3008: de'i ro yang rang bzhin las ma 'das pa'i phyir zhes gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:3011: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK060(i)001:3012: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK060(i)001:3014: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la nyi zla byang chub sems 'gag pa med pa las/
NK060(i)001:3015: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su
NK060(i)001:3016: blangs pas bde ba snga ma 'jig tsam na phyi
NK060(i)001:3017: ma 'jug cing mthar bde ba thams cad 'gag pa
NK060(i)001:3018: ni 'jig 'jug byang chub kyi sems so //
NK060(i)001:3019: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la 'gag
NK060(i)001:3020: pa ltar snang bsdo ba'i dus nyid na rang bzhin
NK060(i)001:3021: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la 'gag pa dang
NK060(i)001:3022: mi 'gag pa dbyer med du la bazla'o //
NK060(i)001:3024: ye shes kyi ro skad cig ma'i rgyun 'phel ba'i phyir mi 'gal ba kho na'o //
NK060(i)001:3028: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK060(i)001:3029: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK060(i)001:3031: rang bzhin lhan skyes pa'i ye shes la nyi zla byang sems gnas pa med pa las/
NK060(i)001:3032: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su blangs pas/
NK060(i)001:3033: dga' ba thams cad rang sa na gnas pa ni gnas pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK060(i)001:3034: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la dga'
NK060(i)001:3035: ba rang sa na gnas pa ltar snang bsdo ba'i
NK060(i)001:3036: dus nyid na/ rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye
NK060(i)001:3037: shes la gnas pa dang mi gnas pa dbyer med
NK060(i)001:3038: dus nyid na/ du la bazla'o // de yang spar khab las/
NK060(i)001:3039: yul dang bral ba'i gnas bca' ru med de/
NK060(i)001:3040: 'bras bu la lam du byed pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:3044: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK060(i)001:3045: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK060(i)001:3047: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la nyi
NK060(i)001:3048: zla byang sems dmigs pa med pa la dngos po
NK060(i)001:3049: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su blangs pas/
NK060(i)001:3050: snga ma'i bde bas mtshon nas phyi ma'i bde ba
NK060(i)001:3051: la smon pas na thams cad dmigs zhes bya ste
NK060(i)001:3052: smon pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK060(i)001:3053: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la dmigs
NK060(i)001:3054: shing smon pa'i dus nyid na rang bzhin lhan cig
NK060(i)001:3055: skyes pa'i ye shes la dmigs pa dang dmigs pa
NK060(i)001:3058: skyed du thal ba nyid kyang rang rig pa'i phyir
NK060(i)001:3059: rkyen tsam ste gzhan nas thob pa med pa'i phyir
NK060(i)001:3061: mthar phyin pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK060(i)001:3063: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK060(i)001:3064: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK060(i)001:3066: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la nyi
NK060(i)001:3067: zla byang sems 'gro ba dang 'ong ba med pa
NK060(i)001:3068: las dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams
NK060(i)001:3069: su blangs pas/ byang chub kyi sems dka' dmar rdo
NK060(i)001:3070: rje dang pad+ma'i rtser 'gro ba dang 'ong ba 'phrad
NK060(i)001:3071: pa'i rkyen gyis yas babs pa'i dga' ba bzhi rdzogs
NK060(i)001:3072: shing kun rdzob kyi bden pa mngon du byas pa
NK060(i)001:3073: ni shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob pa'o //
NK060(i)001:3074: byang chub kyi sems nyi zla gnyis 'dres de nyid
NK060(i)001:3075: gyen du ldog pa'i thabs kyis mas brtan pa'i dga'
NK060(i)001:3076: ba bzhi rdzogs nas dbyer med kyi bden pa mngon
NK060(i)001:3077: du byas shing / de nyid blo'i spyod yul dang
NK060(i)001:3078: bral ba ni bde ba chen po'i dbang thob pa
NK060(i)001:3079: ste mthar phyin pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK060(i)001:3080: de ltar nyi zla byang chub sems 'gro 'ong du
NK060(i)001:3081: snang bsdo ba'i dus nyid na rang bzhin lhan cig
NK060(i)001:3082: skyes pa'i ye shes la 'gro ba dang 'ong ba
NK060(i)001:3085: sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran pa ni mngon par
NK060(i)001:3086: shes pa'i phyir dang gang du yang phyin pa med
NK060(i)001:3088: 'di dag dbang gnyis kyi las thun mong du 'gro tshul ni/
NK060(i)001:3090: gzhung gcig gi steng du dbang gnyis byung bas sam/
NK060(i)001:3091: yang na dbang gnyis ka'i sngon du sems bskyed dgos pas kyang thun mong yin no gsung /
NK060(i)001:3092: rgya gab gong pa na re/
NK060(i)001:3093: 'grel pa ltar sems bzhi po de dbang gnyis ka'i sngon 'gro thun mong ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:3094: 'gro 'ong byang chub kyi sems ni dngos gzhi thun
NK060(i)001:3095: mong bar 'dug pas dbang gnyis kyi las thun mong
NK060(i)001:3096: du 'gro gsung / kho bo ni phyi ma ltar yin par sems so //
NK060(i)001:3097: yang zab mo'i dbang gsum po'i 'di gleng bslang du ji ltar 'gro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:3098: dbang gsum thob nas ston 'khor dgongs pa khyad med du gyur nas/
NK060(i)001:3099: gzhan don du rgyud zhu ba'i spobs pa dang ldan
NK060(i)001:3100: pas gleng bslang du 'gro zhes bla ma gong ma
NK060(i)001:3101: rnams gsung ngo // yang zab mo'i dbang gsum gleng
NK060(i)001:3102: bslang du 'dug pa la rgyud don gang la ngos
NK060(i)001:3103: 'dzin gleng bslang dang rgyud don mtshon tshul 'dres par
NK060(i)001:3105: rgya gab gong pa na re/
NK060(i)001:3106: dbang gsum bskur ba'i las rim gleng bslang du 'gro la/
NK060(i)001:3107: bden pa gsum rgyud la skyes pa de rgyud don du 'gro gsung /
NK060(i)001:3108: yang mthar lam pa la dbang gsum rim pas bskur ram/
NK060(i)001:3112: dus gcig skyes bar 'gyur pa cig car 'jug pa'i lam zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:3115: dus mtha'i skad cig nyid kyis gshegs //
NK060(i)001:3116: zhes sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'gro ba'i rkyen dbang
NK060(i)001:3117: yin la de bskur ba'i skad cig mar bshad pa
NK060(i)001:3118: dang 'gal lo // cig car du bskur na dbang gsum po dang 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:3120: dbang gsum rim par bskur nas mthar dbyer med bde
NK060(i)001:3121: ba chen po'i dbang thob pas 'tshang rgya ba yang
NK060(i)001:3122: rung la/ yang na dus mtha'i skad cig la dbang gsum dus gcig la thob nas 'tshang rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:3123: 'o na skad cig la dbang bskur gsum gyi dbang thob pa 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:3125: bskur bya thams cad mkhyen pa'i 'go shar ba yin pa dang /
NK060(i)001:3126: skur byed drug pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:3127: lar rim cig car gnyis ka rung yang skabs 'dir
NK060(i)001:3128: cig car du 'thad ces bla ma gong ma rnams
NK060(i)001:3129: gsung ngo // yang skyes ba med ces pas skye med sgrub par byed pa'i rig pa bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:3130: rgyu rkyen las ma skyes pa'i phyir dang /
NK060(i)001:3131: dus glo bur du ma byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK060(i)001:3132: byed pa pos ma byas pa'i phyir dang /
NK060(i)001:3133: skyes pa'i dngos po 'di 'dra ba ma grub pa'i phyir skye med grub pa'o //
NK060(i)001:3135: 'gag med sgrub par byed pa'i rig pa bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:3136: 'khrul pa'i snang ba tsam pa 'di las kyi bgo
NK060(i)001:3137: skal mthun pa'i 'gro ba rnams la mthun snang du
NK060(i)001:3139: snang ba med na don dam shes byed kyang med pa'i skyon du 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK060(i)001:3140: snang ba 'di thams cad mkhyen pa'i phyag gis kyang
NK060(i)001:3141: mi khegs te rang snang zhing 'dug pa'i phyir dang
NK060(i)001:3142: / rang rig pa thams cad du rtsal ma 'gags par rang snang ba'i phyir 'gag med grub bo //
NK060(i)001:3146: ces pas dbyer med sgrub byed kyi rig pa bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:3147: de yang bden pa gnyis po de rang bzhin bzang ngan med pa'i phyir dang /
NK060(i)001:3148: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa'i phyir dang /
NK060(i)001:3149: 'dug pa tha mi dad pa'i phyir dang /
NK060(i)001:3150: dus snga phyi med pa'i phyir dbyer med grub bo //
NK060(i)001:3151: de ltar gtan tshig bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas skye
NK060(i)001:3152: 'gag nas dmigs 'gro 'ong ltar snang ba'i chos thams
NK060(i)001:3153: cad gshis la mi gnas par gtan la phab pas/
NK060(i)001:3154: ma yin dgag gi stong nyid rang bzhin bden pa
NK060(i)001:3155: dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por grub pa
NK060(i)001:3156: ni bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs kyis so //
NK060(i)001:3157: de'i phyir rnal 'byor gyi rgyud man chod du gsungs pa'i rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam dang /
NK060(i)001:3158: yang dag pa'i kun rdzob rnams theg pa 'di'i lugs
NK060(i)001:3159: kyis rnam grangs kyi don dam dag log pa'i kun
NK060(i)001:3161: des na theg pa 'di'i lugs kyis rnam grangs ma
NK060(i)001:3162: yin pa'i don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du
NK060(i)001:3164: yang dag pa'i kun rdzob snod bcud sku dang ye
NK060(i)001:3165: shes kyi dkyil 'khor du ye nas sangs rgyas pa
NK060(i)001:3166: gnyis dgos ches kyi dbang gis mtshon tshul tha dad
NK060(i)001:3167: kyang / don la tha dad med par bshad ma
NK060(i)001:3168: thag pa'i dbyer med sgrub byed kyi rig pa bzhis
NK060(i)001:3169: kyang / grub bo // gsum pa sems bskyed pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:3171: zhes sems bskyed pa'i thabs rim pa lnga po de brjod pas/
NK060(i)001:3172: lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa yab
NK060(i)001:3173: thams cad dang btsun mo'i tshogs yum thams cad kyang
NK060(i)001:3174: ston 'khor dgongs pa khyad med du gyur cing /
NK060(i)001:3175: ma 'ongs pa'i sems can rnams kyang de bzhin gshegs par mngon du byas nas/
NK060(i)001:3176: sku dang ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa lnga mthar phyin
NK060(i)001:3177: par 'gyur pa la mnyes pas khyab par gyur to
NK060(i)001:3178: // spyi don gnyis pa thun mong gi gleng bslang la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:3183: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:3185: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng bslang bstan pa la
NK060(i)001:3186: de thun mong du gleng bslang ba ston pas na
NK060(i)001:3187: nas/ de bzhin gshegs pa yab thams cad kyang btsun
NK060(i)001:3188: mo'i tshogs yum thams cad dang bcas pas 'og nas
NK060(i)001:3189: 'byung ba'i ched du brjod pa gsang ba bzhis chod
NK060(i)001:3191: gsang ba bzhis chod pa rnams kyi ched du bshad par zhus pa'o //
NK060(i)001:3193: e ma'o zhes pa ni dam pa'i tshig ste/
NK060(i)001:3194: skabs 'dir ma rang te skyon la ngam pa'o //
NK060(i)001:3198: go phye ba'i 'khor gyi don du/
NK060(i)001:3200: gsang ba bzhis chod nas ma rtogs pa la ngam mo //
NK060(i)001:3202: 'og nas chos zhes pas 'khor ba dang mya ngan
NK060(i)001:3203: las 'das pa'i bsdus pa'i chos thams cad rang bzhin
NK060(i)001:3204: bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos skur sangs rgyas
NK060(i)001:3205: pa de'o // gang gis ma rtogs na/
NK060(i)001:3206: rang ngo rang gis ma shes so //
NK060(i)001:3208: gsang tshul bzhis chod pa'i tshul gyis te/
NK060(i)001:3209: rgyas par mtshan gyi skabs su bshad zin la/
NK060(i)001:3210: 'dir yang mdo tsam bshad na don dam pa ma rtogs pas ye nas gsang ba'i tshul lo //
NK060(i)001:3211: de bzhin du kun rdzob ma rtogs pas sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang /
NK060(i)001:3212: dbyer med ma rtogs pas ngo bo nyid kyi rab tu gsang /
NK060(i)001:3213: spyod yul dang bral ba ma rtogs pas gzhan du min la shin tu gsang ba ste/
NK060(i)001:3214: rang gsang thabs kyis chod pa'i phyir na go phye
NK060(i)001:3215: ba'i 'khor rnams thugs rje bzung bar rigs so zhes
NK060(i)001:3216: brjod pas so // ston pas lan gnang ba la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:3218: thugs rje skyes nas gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:3220: sku dang ye shes mngon du gyur pa'i de bzhin
