NK060(i)001:3221: gshegs pa rnams kyi mdzad pa 'bras bu chos thams
NK060(i)001:3227: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad ye gdod ma nas rang
NK060(i)001:3228: bzhin bden par dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen
NK060(i)001:3229: por sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo nyid du gcig pa'i
NK060(i)001:3230: mtshan nyid yin pas na dbyer med pa ste/
NK060(i)001:3231: gzhi zhes bya gshis kyi gnas lugs so //
NK060(i)001:3232: na'ang zhes pa lhag ma can gyi tshig ste/
NK060(i)001:3233: gnas lugs rang ngo ma shes pas 'gro ba lnga'i rnam par rtog pa nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:3234: las gsum ste de dag gi rtsa ba ni ma rig pa gnyis kho na las byung bas so //
NK060(i)001:3235: 'gro ba lnga'i rnam grangs ni ngan song gsum dang mi dang lha'o //
NK060(i)001:3236: 'o na 'gro ba rigs drug tu bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:3237: lha ma yin ni stod rigs lhar bsdu la/
NK060(i)001:3238: smad rigs 'ga' zhig yi dwags dang /
NK060(i)001:3240: de dag kyang nang rigs mang ba ste/
NK060(i)001:3241: khams gsum la gnas rigs bzhi bcu zhe gcig go //
NK060(i)001:3242: de yang mas rim gyis bgrangs na dmyal ba la dmyal khams bco brgyad yod kyang /
NK060(i)001:3243: tsha dmyal re dang grang dmyal re thad sor tshe
NK060(i)001:3244: tshad dang lus tshad dang sdug bsngal gyi tshad mnyam
NK060(i)001:3245: pas gnas rigs re rer brtsi la/
NK060(i)001:3246: nyi tshe ba dang nye 'khor ba'i dmyal ba gnyis
NK060(i)001:3247: ni gnas rigs re re na'ang yod cing de dang
NK060(i)001:3248: de'i rigs su gtogs pas na dmyal ba la gnas
NK060(i)001:3249: rigs brgyad dang / yi dwags dang dud 'gro'i gnas rigs gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:3250: de ltar gnas rigs bcu ni ngan song gnas bcu zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:3251: gling bzhi'i mi ni tshe tshad dang /
NK060(i)001:3253: bsod nams kyi tshad mi mnyam pas na gnas rigs so sor bgrang la/
NK060(i)001:3254: rgyal chen rigs bzhi ni tshe lus bsod nams kyi tshad mnyam pas gnas rigs gcig tu brtsi ste/
NK060(i)001:3255: rgyal chen rigs bzhi nas gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi
NK060(i)001:3256: bar gyi 'dod lha rigs drug la gnas rigs re
NK060(i)001:3257: rer brtsis pas/ mi dang lha'i gnas rigs bcu ste mtho ris gnas bcu zhes ba bya'o //
NK060(i)001:3258: de ltar gnas rigs nyi shu ni 'dod pa'i khams yin la/
NK060(i)001:3259: bsam gtan bzhi la lha rigs gsum gsum ste bcu
NK060(i)001:3260: gnyis gtsang rigs kyi lha lnga ni gnas rigs re
NK060(i)001:3261: re ste/ gzugs khams gnas rigs bcu bdun zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:3262: gzugs med kyi khams la skye mched mu bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:3263: gnas rigs gang dang gang du shi ba de dang
NK060(i)001:3264: de'i gnas su skye bas gnas gzhan log pa med
NK060(i)001:3265: kyang tshe dang bsod nams kyi tshad skyes pa'i gnas
NK060(i)001:3266: gang yin de dang yang min pas gnas rigs so
NK060(i)001:3267: sor brtsi ste gzugs med skye mched mu bzhi zhes
NK060(i)001:3268: bya'o // de ltar khams gsum gyi gnas rigs re
NK060(i)001:3269: re'i sems can kyang bsam gyis mi khyab par rnam
NK060(i)001:3270: pa sna tshogs su smin pa ni ma rtogs te
NK060(i)001:3272: de la sangs rgyas kyi ye shes dmigs pa med
NK060(i)001:3273: pa'i thugs rje spros pa dang bral zhing 'gro ba'i
NK060(i)001:3274: ril la mnyam par khyab pa ni sems dang chos
NK060(i)001:3275: la dmigs pa'i thugs rje las khyad par du gyur
NK060(i)001:3277: des khams gsum pa'i 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal yul med rang gsal du gzigs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:3278: thugs rje gzigs pa'i tshul lo //
NK060(i)001:3279: de ltar gzigs nas thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas
NK060(i)001:3280: kyi ye shes de byang chub sems dpa'i thugs rje
NK060(i)001:3281: las kyang khyad par du gyur pas na chen po
NK060(i)001:3282: ste/ rang bzhin shugs kyi thugs rje phyogs ris med
NK060(i)001:3283: cing rtag pa rgyun gyi thugs rje rgyun mi 'chad
NK060(i)001:3284: ste/ kyang / lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyis bskul zhing
NK060(i)001:3285: gsol ba btab pa'i ngor go phye ba'i 'khor sdug
NK060(i)001:3286: bsngal gyi nyam thag pa'i gdul bya rnams la yul
NK060(i)001:3287: dang 'phrad pa'i thugs rje skyes nas zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:3288: thugs rjes gzigs nas skyes pa'i tshul lo //
NK060(i)001:3289: de ltar thugs rje skyes shing de dag gi don
NK060(i)001:3290: mdzad par dgongs nas go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched
NK060(i)001:3291: du sprul pa'i spro ba'i zhal bzhes brjod pa 'di
NK060(i)001:3292: lhan cig pa'i 'khor rnams la brjod do //
NK060(i)001:3293: lhun gyis grub pa'i chos bstan pa'i phyir sprul pa spro ba la zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK060(i)001:3295: e ma'o zhes pa ni gzhi dngos po'i gnas lugs
NK060(i)001:3296: gcig la 'khor 'das gnyis su 'khrul pa ngo mtshar
NK060(i)001:3297: te ma rangs pa'i dam tshig go //
NK060(i)001:3298: de bzhin nyid la spros pa'i zug rngu med pas na bde ba chen po'o //
NK060(i)001:3299: de don nar son bas na gshegs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:3300: de nyid kyi snying po chos kyi dbyings shin tu
NK060(i)001:3301: dri med du gnas kyang nges pa'i shes pa ma
NK060(i)001:3302: skyes pa ni lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa
NK060(i)001:3303: zhes bya ste/ 'khor ba 'phrul ba'i rgyu yin no //
NK060(i)001:3304: de las kyang rang gi sems kyi rnam par rtog
NK060(i)001:3305: pa yul dang yul can du snang ba las gzung
NK060(i)001:3306: 'dzin sna tshogs kyi shes pas glo bur du sprul
NK060(i)001:3307: pa ni kun tu btags pa'i ma rig pa zhes
NK060(i)001:3308: bya ste/ 'khor ba 'khrul ba'i rkyen yin no //
NK060(i)001:3309: sna tshogs pa'i lus bzang ngan dang longs spyod che
NK060(i)001:3310: chung dang gnas mtho dman dang sdug bsngal brgyad dam
NK060(i)001:3311: bcu gcig la sogs pa las dang nyon mongs pas
NK060(i)001:3312: bsdus ba rnams te/ 'khor ba 'khrul pa'i ngo bo yin no //
NK060(i)001:3313: gong gi de tsho la bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin kyang 'khrul ngo tsam du zad kyis/
NK060(i)001:3314: yang dag par na gang zag dang chos kyi bdag gnyis ma grub pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:3315: 'ching bar byed pa'i mkhan po dgra lta bu sus
NK060(i)001:3316: kyang ma bcings shing 'ching byed kyi dngos po zhags
NK060(i)001:3317: pa lta bus kyang bcings pa med de/
NK060(i)001:3318: bcing bar bya ba'ii yul btson lta bu'am yod pa
NK060(i)001:3319: ma yin kyang rang gi nan btags kyis rnam par
NK060(i)001:3320: rtog pas nga dang bdag tu 'dzin pa 'khrul ngor
NK060(i)001:3321: gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang ba yis bcings pa ste/
NK060(i)001:3322: 'khor ba 'khrul pa'i byed pa po yin no //
NK060(i)001:3323: de yang thang phrom pa zos pa'i rgan mo zhig
NK060(i)001:3324: gis rang gi mig rab rib tu gyur pa las
NK060(i)001:3325: skra shad kyi dngos po med bzhin nan btags kyis
NK060(i)001:3326: nam mkha' la skra shad 'dzag pa mthong nas skra
NK060(i)001:3327: shad la mdud pa mang po byas na 'dor ba'i
NK060(i)001:3328: snang ba byung ba bzhin te/
NK060(i)001:3330: de ltar bcings pa ltar snang ba'i dus nyid na
NK060(i)001:3331: bdag 'dzin dang sems can dang sdug bsngal gyi dngos
NK060(i)001:3332: po rnams sems nyid kyi gshis la ma grub pas
NK060(i)001:3333: bcings pa med pa'i phyir rnam par grol ba po
NK060(i)001:3334: yang med pas na/ ye nas rang rig pa nyid
NK060(i)001:3335: sku dang ye shes su lhun gyis rdzogs shing gsal
NK060(i)001:3336: ba ni sangs rgyas kyi thugs su chud pa'i chos
NK060(i)001:3337: sam ngo bo yin pas na 'khor 'das mnyam pa
NK060(i)001:3338: nyid du la bzlas pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:3339: de mtshon par byed pa gsang ba snying po'i rgyud 'di nyid bstan par bya ba'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:3346: dgyes pa tshul drug gi sgo nas lhan gcig pa'i
NK060(i)001:3347: 'khor la dngos su bstan cing go phye ba'i 'khor
NK060(i)001:3348: la rgyud 'di nyid kyi lam stegs theg pa gzhan
NK060(i)001:3349: bstan par bya ba'i phyir sprul pa thub pa drug
NK060(i)001:3350: spro ba la sogs pa sna tshogs pa mdzad do
NK060(i)001:3351: // 'di'i skabs su 'khrul gzhi yod med kyi brtag ni/
NK060(i)001:3356: 'khrul gzhi yod pas 'khrul lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:3359: sgro 'dogs dbang gyur gang zag rnams //
NK060(i)001:3360: sems nyid dmigs su med pa la //
NK060(i)001:3361: dngos po rang rgyud gzhi smra ba //
NK060(i)001:3362: de yi rigs rgyud rtag par lhung //
NK060(i)001:3364: 'khrul pa rang rgyud par rtag par thal ba dang /
NK060(i)001:3365: gzhi 'khor ba'i mthar lhung bar thal ba/
NK060(i)001:3366: thos bsam sgom gsum gyis 'khrul pa mi sel bar thal ba/
NK060(i)001:3367: gzhi gzung 'dzin can du thal ba'i skyon 'ong ste/
NK060(i)001:3370: 'dod par nus pa ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:3371: 'khrul pa rang rgyud par rtag par 'dod na/
NK060(i)001:3373: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin mi dmigs phyir //
NK060(i)001:3375: gzhi 'khor ba'i mthar lhung bar 'dod na/
NK060(i)001:3377: rang bzhin ngang gis dbyer med pa'ang //
NK060(i)001:3379: thos bsam sgom gsum gyis 'khrul pa mi sels bar 'dod na/
NK060(i)001:3381: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK060(i)001:3382: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK060(i)001:3384: gzhi gzung 'dzin can du thal bar 'dod na/
NK060(i)001:3386: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK060(i)001:3388: yang 'ga' zhig 'khrul gzhi med kyang 'khrul lo zhes 'dod na yang mi rigs te/
NK060(i)001:3390: skur ba pa ni lhun grub la //
NK060(i)001:3391: de dang mi mthun so sor rtog /de la de ni mi srid bzhin //
NK060(i)001:3392: gzhi la ye nas med ces smra //
NK060(i)001:3393: zhen blo'i ngo la yod do zhes //
NK060(i)001:3394: skur pa gang yin chad lta ba //
NK060(i)001:3395: de dang de gnyis tha dad cing //
NK060(i)001:3398: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa ma grub par thal ba/
NK060(i)001:3399: gzhi myang 'das kyi mthar lhung bar thal ba/
NK060(i)001:3400: 'khor ba la thog ma 'byung bar thal ba/
NK060(i)001:3401: rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas la yang 'khrul ba 'byung bar thal ba dang bzhi'o //
NK060(i)001:3404: 'dod par nus pa ma yin no //
NK060(i)001:3405: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa ma grub par 'dod na/
NK060(i)001:3407: nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes pa ni lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'o //
NK060(i)001:3409: gzhi myang 'das kyi mthar lhung bar 'dod na/
NK060(i)001:3411: mya ngan 'das pa'ang yod ma yin //
NK060(i)001:3413: 'khor ba la thog ma 'byung bar 'dod na/
NK060(i)001:3415: 'khor ba thog ma tha ma med //
NK060(i)001:3417: rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas la 'khrul pa 'byung bar 'dod na/
NK060(i)001:3419: de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa yang //
NK060(i)001:3420: sna tshogs zhen las grol bar zad //
NK060(i)001:3423: 'khrul gzhi yod med dbyer med la 'khrul lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:3425: gzhi rang bzhin ni ye nas rnam dag yin la/
NK060(i)001:3426: 'khrul ba ni blo bur gyi dri ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:3427: 'o na lan ji ltar gdab ce na/
NK060(i)001:3428: skad yangs par byas la lan gdab pa dang /
NK060(i)001:3429: dog par byas la lan gdab pa gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:3430: yangs par byas na 'khrul gzhi yod med dbyer med gsum ka las kyang 'khrul te/
NK060(i)001:3431: de gsum gang rung cig kho na las 'khrul pa ni ma yin no //
NK060(i)001:3433: 'khrul gzhi yod pa las kyang 'khrul te/
NK060(i)001:3434: dpe thag khra la sbrul 'dzin gyi shes pa zhugs pa lta bu'o //
NK060(i)001:3435: de yang a ro thig le'i skor las/
NK060(i)001:3438: 'khrul gzhi med pa las kyang 'khrul te/
NK060(i)001:3439: dpe thang phrom zos pa'i rgan mo'i mig sngar nam mkha' la skra shad 'dzag pa lta bu'o //
NK060(i)001:3441: nyi ma'i dkyiil na mun med ltar //
NK060(i)001:3444: dper sman ga bur de tshad nad can la sman dang /
NK060(i)001:3445: rlung nad can la dug tu 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:3447: don gcig yod med ris med la //
NK060(i)001:3448: de yi rgyu rkyen rang bzhin bas //
NK060(i)001:3449: sman gyi phan gnod ci bzhin du //
NK060(i)001:3450: thams cad ma lus rgyu gcig pas //
NK060(i)001:3451: mi mthun khyad par so sor snang //
NK060(i)001:3453: mdor na rang bzhin rnam dag ye nas dri ma dang bral bar gnas kyang /
NK060(i)001:3454: nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes pa lhan skyes kyi
NK060(i)001:3455: ma rig pas rgyu byas rang snang la yul du
NK060(i)001:3456: gzung bas/ gzung 'dzin gnyis snang kun btags kyi ma
NK060(i)001:3457: rig pas rkyen byas nas glo bur du 'khrul lo
NK060(i)001:3458: gzung bas/ // skad dog par byas nas lan gdab
NK060(i)001:3459: pa ni gzhi rang bzhin rnam dag yod med dbu
NK060(i)001:3460: ma'i mtha' las grol ba de rang ngo rang gis
NK060(i)001:3463: drug gi 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK060(i)001:3464: sems nyid nor bu rin po che //
NK060(i)001:3465: ji ltar bsams pa snang ba la //
NK060(i)001:3466: 'khrul gzhi yod med sgro skur med //
NK060(i)001:3468: 'o na de la 'khrul gzhi zhes bya ba de/
NK060(i)001:3469: bde gshegs snying po la 'dod dam/
NK060(i)001:3470: ma rig pa rgyu dang bcas pa la 'dod/
NK060(i)001:3472: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mi rnyed par 'gyur/
NK060(i)001:3474: 'khrul pa'i ngo bo mi rnyed par 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:3475: brgyud pa'i rgyu bde gshegs snying po dngos rgyu ma rig pa'o //
NK060(i)001:3477: e ma bde gshegs snying po las //
NK060(i)001:3478: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK060(i)001:3481: bcing med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK060(i)001:3482: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK060(i)001:3484: gzhi ka dag dang lhun grub kyi stong thun brjod par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:3485: de yang ka dag lhun grub re re la'ang /
NK060(i)001:3489: la bzla dang bzhi bzhi las/
NK060(i)001:3491: ka dag gi grub mtha'i lugs kyi gzhi gdod ma nas ka nas dag pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:3492: ma rig pa glo bur gyi dri ma yin pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:3493: gzhi dang ma rig pa tha dad du 'dod de/
NK060(i)001:3494: dper na nor bu rin po che mi gtsang ba'i
NK060(i)001:3495: 'dam gyis bstums pa lta bur 'dod pa ni ka
NK060(i)001:3497: lhun grub kyi grub mtha' lugs kyis gzhi ye nas lhun gyis grub pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:3498: ma rig pa gzhan byung ma yin pa'i phyir gzhi dang ma rig pa dbyer med du 'dod pa ste/
NK060(i)001:3499: dper na gser 'gyur gi gzhi'i lcags de ye nas
NK060(i)001:3500: gser lcags dbyer med du med na gser du bsgyur
NK060(i)001:3501: du mi btub pa lta bur 'dod pa ni lhun
NK060(i)001:3504: ka dag lhun grub gnyis ka la gsum gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:3506: dbyings ka dag /ye shes ka dag /ka dag skyon med dam chen po'o //
NK060(i)001:3507: dang po dbyings ka dag ni/
NK060(i)001:3508: nor bu rin po che la mi gtsang ba'i 'dam gyis sel med pa dper byas nas/
NK060(i)001:3509: gzhi chos dbyings rnam dag yin pas ma rig pa'i gzhi min par 'dod/
NK060(i)001:3510: gnyis pa ye shes ka dag ni/
NK060(i)001:3511: nor bu rin po che la dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i
NK060(i)001:3512: gegs mi gtsang ba'i 'dam gyis bstums pa de skyur
NK060(i)001:3513: po dang lwa bas bkrus shing phyis pas rnam par
NK060(i)001:3514: dag pa la dgos 'dod 'byung ba dper byas nas/
NK060(i)001:3515: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes la ma rig pa glo bur gyi dri ma lam lngas spangs par 'dod/
NK060(i)001:3519: lhun grub skyon med dam chen po'o //
NK060(i)001:3520: dang po chos nyid lhun grub ni/
NK060(i)001:3521: ye nas gser lcags dbyer med du med na gser
NK060(i)001:3522: 'gyur gyi rtsis lcags gser du bsgyur du mi rung
NK060(i)001:3523: ste/ rdza shing la sogs pa bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:3524: zhes pa dper byas nas gzhi ma rig pa dang
NK060(i)001:3525: ye shes dbyer med du yod pa'i gnad kas chos
NK060(i)001:3526: nyid gcig gi rang bzhin las ma 'das pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:3527: chos can so so yang phan tshun gcig la gcig lhun gyis grub par 'dod/
NK060(i)001:3529: lcags gser du gyur pa'i tshe gser la lcags kyi mtshan ma mi snang yang /
NK060(i)001:3530: lcags nyid gser du gyur ba las lcags logs su ma spangs pa dper byas nas/
NK060(i)001:3531: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes thob kyang ma rig pa gtan nas ma spangs te/
NK060(i)001:3532: 'khor 'das gnyis de las mi gzhan par 'dod do //
NK060(i)001:3533: de dag la skyon brjod pa ni/
NK060(i)001:3534: ka dag tu 'dod pa la spyi'i skyon dang /
NK060(i)001:3535: bye brag gi skyon gnyis yod de/
NK060(i)001:3536: spyi skyon ni sngar bshad pa'i 'khrul gzhi med na skyon du 'gyur pa'i lung rig bzhis gnod do //
NK060(i)001:3538: dbyings ka dag pa ltar na/
NK060(i)001:3539: 'khrul pa skye mi srid par thal/
NK060(i)001:3540: gzhi de ma rig pa'i brgyud rgyur yang mi rung ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:3541: 'dod par nus pa ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:3543: ma rig pa glo bur gyi dri ma yin no zhe na/
NK060(i)001:3544: rgyu bkag pa la 'bras bu khegs pa'i khyab pa
NK060(i)001:3545: yod pa'i phyir glo bur gyi dri ma 'byung bar
NK060(i)001:3546: mi rigs te/ rgyu bde gshegs snying po dri bral yin pas so //
NK060(i)001:3547: yang ye shes ka dag pa ltar na/
NK060(i)001:3548: lha dang rtog pa tha dad du thal/
NK060(i)001:3549: sku dang ye shes thob pa'i tshe na 'khrul pa spangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:3551: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK060(i)001:3552: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:3554: rdo rje 'dzin pa la sogs par rang snang ba'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:3555: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pas gsal lo //
NK060(i)001:3556: lhun grub tu 'dod pa la'ang spyi'i skyon dang /
NK060(i)001:3557: bye brag gi skyon gnyis yod de/
NK060(i)001:3558: dang po ni 'khrul gzhi yod na skyon du 'gyur ba'i lung rig bzhis gnod la/
NK060(i)001:3559: bye brag gi skyon ni chos nyid lhun grub pa ltar na/
NK060(i)001:3560: 'khrul pa spang du mi rung bar thal/
NK060(i)001:3561: gzhi dang 'khrul pa dbyer med pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:3563: lam sbyangs pa don med par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:3564: yang chos can lhun grub pa ltar na/
NK060(i)001:3565: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob kyang dgos pa med par thal/
NK060(i)001:3566: ma rig pa'i rang bzhin las ma 'das pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:3567: mdor na gang la skyon can gnyis la lhun grub kyi grub mthas gnod la/
NK060(i)001:3568: lhun grub skyon can gnyis la ka dag gi grub mthas gnod pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:3569: grub mtha' bzhi po de thams cad kyang skyon can 'ba' zhig yin no //
NK060(i)001:3571: lhun grub skyon med gnyis ni gzhi 'bras la ma
NK060(i)001:3572: rig pa mi ldan pa'i cha nas ka dag tu
NK060(i)001:3573: btags la/ gzhi 'bras kyi ma rig pa ma spangs
NK060(i)001:3574: pa'i cha nas lhun grub tu btags par zad kyis
NK060(i)001:3576: ma rig pa ma spang la mi ldan par lta ba gong mthun te/
NK060(i)001:3577: dper rgyal bu dmangs su 'khyams pa'i stong thun bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:3578: 'on kyang lta ba 'di ni mchog yin la/
NK060(i)001:3579: gzhan ni gti mug go snyam du sems na yang
NK060(i)001:3580: rang lta mchog tu 'dzin pa'i lta ba zhes bya
NK060(i)001:3581: ste/ dri ma'i rang bzhin las ma 'das so //
NK060(i)001:3583: shes bya gshis kyi gnas lugs rang bzhin bden pa
NK060(i)001:3584: dbyer med de blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa'i phyir
NK060(i)001:3589: tshul khrims dang ting nge 'dzin mchog tu 'dzin pa dang /
NK060(i)001:3590: rang lta mchog tu 'dzin pa'i dri ma ma dag pa de srid du/
NK060(i)001:3591: ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes thob pa'i skabs med do //
NK060(i)001:3592: bla ma gong ma phal cher ka dag gi grub mtha' 'dzin la/
NK060(i)001:3593: lha rje zur chung shes rab grags pa ni lhun grub kyi grub mtha' ltar 'thad gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:3596: zhes dbang rdzogs pa drug pa nyid dang khyad par med pas na/
NK060(i)001:3597: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid de bzhin gshegs pa nyid
NK060(i)001:3598: la go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched du gleng ngo
NK060(i)001:3601: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las zhes pa 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:3602: skye ba med la zhes pa la sogs pa lnga ni don dam pa byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK060(i)001:3603: thams cad skyes zhes pa la sogs pa lnga ni kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK060(i)001:3604: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK060(i)001:3605: ces pa la sogs pa lnga ni dbyer med byang
NK060(i)001:3606: chub kyi sems te de nyid dbyer med spyod yul
NK060(i)001:3607: dang bral ba rang rig pa'i ye shes su bskyed
NK060(i)001:3608: pa'am/ yang na gsang dbang dang shes rab ye shes
NK060(i)001:3609: kyi dbang thob pa ni kun rdzob byang chub kyi
NK060(i)001:3610: pa'am/ sems yin la/ dbyer med bde ba chen po'i
NK060(i)001:3611: dbang thob pa ni don dam pa byang chub kyi
NK060(i)001:3612: pa'am/ sems yin la/ sems yin te/ de dag kyang
NK060(i)001:3613: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba rang rig pa'i
NK060(i)001:3614: ye shes su bskyed pa'i gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas
NK060(i)001:3615: na le'u ste yas bgrangs gnyis pa'i don du gada'o
NK060(i)001:3616: pa'am/ sems yin la/ sems yin te/ // 'o na don dam pa dang /
NK060(i)001:3617: kun rdzob ces pa de gnyis kyi go don rang gang yin snyam na/
NK060(i)001:3619: rang gi ngo bo thams cad du mi phyed pa ni don dam pa ste ces pas/
NK060(i)001:3620: skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong dang bral ba'i chos
NK060(i)001:3621: nyid ni gang dang yang mi phyed pas na don
NK060(i)001:3622: dam pa'o // kun rdzob kyi rgyu rkyen la ltos pas snang ba ste/
NK060(i)001:3623: zhes pas skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong ltar snang
NK060(i)001:3624: ba'i chos can ni rgyu rkyen la ltos shing rag
NK060(i)001:3625: lus pas na kun rdzob ces bya'o //
NK060(i)001:3626: de'i phyir skye ba la sogs par snang bsdo ba'i
NK060(i)001:3627: dus na skye ba la sogs pa yod ma myong
NK060(i)001:3628: ste tho yor mir snang ba la sogs pa bzhin
NK060(i)001:3629: no // yang thun mong gleng bslang mtshan du ma 'dus so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:3630: thun min gleng bslang gi shugs la 'dus so zhes
NK060(i)001:3631: bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo ////da ni bka'
NK060(i)001:3632: rang gnyer gyis sa bcad na/
NK060(i)001:3633: le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis yod pa las/
NK060(i)001:3635: slob dpon 'grel pa gdams ngag mkhan gyis sa bcad na/
NK060(i)001:3641: 'dir stod nas bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:3642: smad nas rgyud don ston par byed pa'i le'u 'di la/
NK060(i)001:3643: chos tshoms kyi dbang du blo rab 'bring gsum dang sbyar te bshad na/
NK060(i)001:3644: blo rab kyi chos tshogs gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las/
NK060(i)001:3648: spar khab kyi thub pa drug la/
NK060(i)001:3649: thabs lam zur tsam bshad mos kyis lta ba grol lam ston/
NK060(i)001:3650: mtshan nyid gsum las rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK060(i)001:3651: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid ston/
NK060(i)001:3652: snang ba bzhi las bzhi ka ston/
NK060(i)001:3653: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa gtso che/
NK060(i)001:3654: bsdu ba'i skabs nas cig car ba zur tsam ston/
NK060(i)001:3655: blo 'bring gi chos tshoms gleng gzhi gleng bslang rgyud don dgos 'brel gdams gtad dang lnga las/
NK060(i)001:3656: le'u'i stod kyi thub drug gi gleng gzhi ston/
NK060(i)001:3658: rgyud don la yongs su shes par byed pa'i dngos po bcu yod pa las lta ba ston/
NK060(i)001:3659: bcu po yang brgya'i bdag nyid du byas na lta
NK060(i)001:3660: ba'i zhor la thub pa drug gis gzhan don mdzad
NK060(i)001:3661: pa'i spyod pa ston/ dkyil 'khor dang phrin las zur tsam ston/
NK060(i)001:3662: blo tha ma'i chos tshoms la bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu yod pa las rang bzhin lta ba ston/
NK060(i)001:3665: gzhan yang spyi 'phro gsum gyis ston te/
NK060(i)001:3668: rang rkyen gnyer rnams ston no //
NK060(i)001:3669: de ltar ston pa'i le'u gsum pa 'di la 'chad
NK060(i)001:3670: mkhan rig pa'i sgros kyis sa bcad na le'u'i gzhung
NK060(i)001:3671: dang mtshan no // dang po la gnyis/
NK060(i)001:3674: rgyas pa la spyi don gnyis/
NK060(i)001:3675: bstan pa byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:3676: yongs su shes par bya ba'i lta ba'o //
NK060(i)001:3677: spyi don dang po la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:3684: yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po rgyud kyi don bya ba yin nam ma yin/
NK060(i)001:3685: yin na de nas zhes bya ba la 'brel ji ltar sbyor zhe na/
NK060(i)001:3687: rgyud dum bur gyur kyang rim pa ma nor ba kho na'i phyir de nas zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:3689: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:3690: thun mong bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi gnyis/
NK060(i)001:3691: bar gleng bslang gis chod pas rgyud dum bur gyur
NK060(i)001:3692: kyang rim pa ma nor ba ni lhan cig pa'i
NK060(i)001:3693: 'khor la zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur nas/
NK060(i)001:3694: rtogs tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sku dang ye shes
NK060(i)001:3695: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su mngon du byas pas rdo
NK060(i)001:3697: ston 'khor dgongs pa khyad med par gyur bas rgyud zhu ba'i spobs pa dang ldan te/
NK060(i)001:3698: go phye ba'i 'khor gsang ba bzhis chod pa rnams kyi don du'ang bshad du gsol zhes zhus pas/
NK060(i)001:3699: 'di nyid nyan pa'i skal ba dang ldan pa rnams la dgyes pa'i tshul drug gis dngos su gsungs la/
NK060(i)001:3700: skal ba dang mi ldan pa rnams la lam stegs
NK060(i)001:3701: kyi bstan pa ston pa'i ston pa thub pa drug
NK060(i)001:3702: spros nas gsung bar zhal gyis bzhes pa la/
NK060(i)001:3703: deng spro ba dngos ston pas na nas zhes 'grel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:3705: de ltar na gleng gzhi'i rgyu gleng bslang yin par 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:3706: rgyud 'di nyid kyi dbang du rgyu gleng gzhi tshogs nas/
NK060(i)001:3707: rkyen gleng bslang ba yin yang /
NK060(i)001:3708: de nyid thun mong gi bstan pa 'byung ba'i gleng
NK060(i)001:3709: gzhi'i rgyu ru song ba la skyon lta ga la
NK060(i)001:3710: yod de/ de'i rgyu mtshan nam gnad ka ni rgyud
NK060(i)001:3711: 'di nyid gsung pa'i byin rlabs las bstan pa mtha'
NK060(i)001:3713: de bzhin gshegs pa drug pa spyi'i gzugs can rigs
NK060(i)001:3714: thams cad kyi bdag po'i thugs spros bral gyi ye
NK060(i)001:3715: shes las/ thugs rje dngos po ril la khyab pa'i
NK060(i)001:3716: brtse ba chen po thams cad rang byung gi ye
NK060(i)001:3717: shes su lhun gyis grub pa'i byin gyis brlabs gdul
NK060(i)001:3718: bya la cir yang mi 'gag pa zhes bya ba'i
NK060(i)001:3721: rig pa'i gnas bco brgyad dam/
NK060(i)001:3722: sku gsung thugs las kyang mi 'dod pa ma yin no zhes gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:3723: rig pa'i gnas bco brgyad ni/
NK060(i)001:3742: zhes dka' spyad dang po big p+aa ta chen mo nas bshad do //
NK060(i)001:3743: thub pa zhes pa ni sku thub ste stag dang spre'u ltar mi mdzad/
NK060(i)001:3744: gsung thub ste ca co dang ga zha mi smra/
NK060(i)001:3745: thugs thub ste mnyam par ma bzhag pa mi mnga' ba'o //
NK060(i)001:3746: gdul bya 'gro ba rigs drug tu grangs nges pa'i phyir ston pa yang thub pa drug tu byung ste/
NK060(i)001:3747: gang las na de bzhin gshegs pa drug pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs thabs yab dang /
NK060(i)001:3748: shes rab yum gnyis su med pa thig le byang
NK060(i)001:3749: chub kyi sems dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las
NK060(i)001:3751: zla ba dang nyi ma las ma g.yos bzhin chu
NK060(i)001:3752: skyogs tha dad ni nang du gzugs brnyan snang ba
NK060(i)001:3753: ltar 'gro ba rigs drug gi gnas so sor snang
NK060(i)001:3754: bar gyur to // gleng gzhi rang gi ngo bo'o //
NK060(i)001:3759: de ltar thub pa drug 'thon nas kyang gdul bya'i
NK060(i)001:3760: las kyi rtog pa mi mthun pa'i dbang gis phyogs
NK060(i)001:3761: sam logs te s+n+rel gzhi dang steng 'og gnyis te
NK060(i)001:3762: yan man gyi snod 'jig pa la bcud 'jig pa
NK060(i)001:3763: rten pa/ chags lugs sam ljid 'dor lugs mi 'dra
NK060(i)001:3764: ba drug gi rang bzhin can gyis phyogs bcu mtha'
NK060(i)001:3765: yas par kun tu khyab pa ni mu med pa
NK060(i)001:3766: zhes bya ste chos sku'i zhing khams so //
NK060(i)001:3767: de'i khongs su 'og nas 'chad pa'i stong gsum gyi
NK060(i)001:3768: stong chen po gcig grangs kyi gzhi ru byas nas
NK060(i)001:3769: gcig nas gnyis su bgrangs pa'i stong rgyu bkod dang
NK060(i)001:3770: po/ de grangs kyis gzhi ru byas nas gcig nas
NK060(i)001:3771: gnyis su bgrangs pa'i stong la stong rgyu bkod gnyis
NK060(i)001:3772: po/ pa/ de'ang grangs kyi gzhi ma gcig tu byas
NK060(i)001:3773: pa'i gcig nas gnyis su bgrangs pa'i stong la stong
NK060(i)001:3774: mtshams sbyor yongs su 'das pa zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:3775: longs sku nyag gcig gi zhing khams so //
NK060(i)001:3776: stong gsum gyi stong chen po ni/
NK060(i)001:3778: gling bzhi dang ni nyi zla dang //
NK060(i)001:3779: ri rab dang ni 'dod lhar bcas //
NK060(i)001:3780: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten stong la ni //
NK060(i)001:3781: stong ni spyi phud yin par 'dod //
NK060(i)001:3782: de stong la ni stong gnyis pa //
NK060(i)001:3783: bar ma'i 'jig rten khams yin no //
NK060(i)001:3784: de stong la ni stong gsum ste //
NK060(i)001:3786: zhes pas gling bzhi nyi zla ri rab dang bcas
NK060(i)001:3787: pa bye ba phrag brgya la stong gsum gyi stong
NK060(i)001:3789: sprul sku nyag gcig gi zhing khams so //
NK060(i)001:3790: de ni gnas phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:3791: 'o na 'di na sprul sku'i gleng gzhi gnas 'chad pa la/
NK060(i)001:3792: chos sku dang longs sku'i gleng gzhi smos pas skabs 'chol ba'i skyon du 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:3794: ma ga d+ha rdo rje'i gdan dmigs kyis bkar nas mtshon pa la/
NK060(i)001:3796: rgya gar gyi yul ma ga d+ha rdo rje'i gdan zhes smos pa bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:3797: sprul sku'i zhing khams stong gsum gyi stong chen po
NK060(i)001:3798: re rer sprul sku thub pa chen po bcom ldan
NK060(i)001:3799: 'das re rer snang nas don mdzad pa ni ston
NK060(i)001:3801: sku dang thugs dang bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang
NK060(i)001:3802: gsum gyi mdzad pa'i 'dul ba rnam pa bzhis gdul
NK060(i)001:3803: ba ni bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:3804: 'gro ba rigs drug la lha ma yin stod rigs lha dang /
NK060(i)001:3805: smad rigs byol song du bsdus pas 'gro ba lnga'i sems can rnams ni 'khor phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:3806: de ltar gnas dang ston pa bstan pa 'khor rnams
NK060(i)001:3807: 'dzom pa'i dus su don mdzad pa ni dus phun
NK060(i)001:3808: sum tshogs pa'o // gleng gzhi bye brag tu bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:3813: de yang 'dir bltams pa la sogs pa'i mdzad pa brgyad dkyus nas ston la/
NK060(i)001:3814: 'og nas la sogs pa ston pa'i thub pas zhes pas sogs khongs nas/
NK060(i)001:3815: dga' ldan nas babs pa la sogs pa bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:3816: mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas don mdzad pa
NK060(i)001:3817: ni theg pa thun mong ba rnams kyi snang ba
NK060(i)001:3818: yin te/ de yang theg pa chung ngu ba rnams
NK060(i)001:3819: kyi snang ngo la rgyal bu don grub tu skye
NK060(i)001:3820: ba bzhes pa'i dus na sogs so'i skye bo 'ching
NK060(i)001:3821: ba mtha' dag gis bcings pa cig yin pa la/
NK060(i)001:3822: skye rga na 'chi'i sdug bsngal bzhi gzigs pa'i rkyen gyis nges par 'byung ba'i dad pa skyes nas/
NK060(i)001:3823: rgyal srid mchil ma'i thal ba bzhin du bor zhing
NK060(i)001:3824: khyim nas khyim med par rab tu byung nas lo
NK060(i)001:3825: drug dka' ba spyad nas nyan thos rnams kyi ngo
NK060(i)001:3826: la dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu dang /
NK060(i)001:3827: rang sangs rgyas kyi ngo la yid bzhin bde ba
NK060(i)001:3828: mchog gi 'bras bu bse ru'am ne tso lta bu
NK060(i)001:3830: sngags phyi rgyud pa rnams kyi snang ngor lha'i bu
NK060(i)001:3831: dam pa tog dkar po de byang chub sems dpa'
NK060(i)001:3832: sa mthar phyin pa srid pa tha ma ba skye
NK060(i)001:3833: ba gcig gis thogs pa can zhig yin la/
NK060(i)001:3834: de mi'i bu rgyal bu don grub tu skye ba
NK060(i)001:3835: bzhes nas khyim nas khyim med par rab tu byung
NK060(i)001:3836: zhing chu bo nee rany+dza na'i 'gram na dka' thub
NK060(i)001:3837: mdzad cing byang chub snying por bzhugs pa la/
NK060(i)001:3838: sangs rgyas rnams kyis bskul bas mi g.yo ba'i ting
NK060(i)001:3839: nge 'dzin las bzhengs nas rnam smin gyi lus nee
NK060(i)001:3841: yid kyi lus 'og min gyi gnas su phyin te
NK060(i)001:3842: don dam pa byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed
NK060(i)001:3843: pa la sangs rgyas rnams kyis dbang bskur nas/
NK060(i)001:3844: dpal kun rig rnam par snang mdzad du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas/
NK060(i)001:3845: de nas sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas su babs nas lha yul gyi gdul bya rnams smin par mdzad/
NK060(i)001:3846: de nas mi yul gyi gdul bya rnams 'dul ba'i
NK060(i)001:3847: don du slar dka' thub kyi khong par zhugs nas
NK060(i)001:3848: byang chub kyi shing drung du sangs rgyas pa la
NK060(i)001:3849: sogs pa'i tshul bstan par snang ngo //
NK060(i)001:3850: de yang 'di nyid kyi le'u drug pa las/
NK060(i)001:3851: nyan thos rnams la dgra bcom gzugs //
NK060(i)001:3852: rang rgyal rnams la bse ru'i tshul //
NK060(i)001:3853: gzhan yang theg mchog rim pa bzhin //
NK060(i)001:3854: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK060(i)001:3855: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK060(i)001:3857: de ltar yin yang mthun snang du grags pa byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ltar bshad na/
NK060(i)001:3858: bcom ldan 'das thub pa'i dbang po 'di shes rab
NK060(i)001:3859: dang snying rje'i sa bon phun sum tshogs pa'i mthus
NK060(i)001:3860: bsod nams cha mthun gyi dge ba'i rtsa ba rgya
NK060(i)001:3861: chen po du ma bsags pa cig yin pa la
NK060(i)001:3862: re zhig na las 'ga' zhig gis sems can dmyal
NK060(i)001:3863: ba'i gnas su lcags bsregs kyi sa gzhi'i steng na
NK060(i)001:3864: shing rta 'dren pa'i gyad zhig tu skyes par gyur
NK060(i)001:3865: pa las/ de sdug bsngal gyi tshor bas bdag gi
NK060(i)001:3866: lus la gnod par gyur pas rang gi sdug bsngal
NK060(i)001:3867: pa las/ la dpags nas/ shing rta chen po 'dren
NK060(i)001:3868: pa'i grogs byed pa'i gyad gcig la mnyam pa med
NK060(i)001:3869: pa'i snying rje skyes nas gshin rje'i skyes bu la'
NK060(i)001:3870: di'i khur bdag gis 'khur ba'i ci gnang zhes zhus
NK060(i)001:3871: pa las/ la dpags nas/ pas/ de rab tu khros
NK060(i)001:3872: nas rang gi las kyi 'bras bu la longs spyod
NK060(i)001:3873: pa la khyod kyis ci byar yod ces zer nas
NK060(i)001:3874: mgo la lcags kyi thu lum gyis bsnun to //
NK060(i)001:3875: de de nyid du shi nas lhar skyes so //
NK060(i)001:3876: der lo mang po lha'i bde ba nyams su myong
NK060(i)001:3877: zhing shi 'phos nas mi'i nang du rdza mkhan spad
NK060(i)001:3878: pa 'od kyi bu khye'u snang byed ces bya bar
NK060(i)001:3879: gyur to // de'i tshe sangs rgyas thub pa chen
NK060(i)001:3880: po la byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed pa
NK060(i)001:3881: de nas brtsams nas bskal pa chen po grangs med
NK060(i)001:3882: pa gsum gyi bar du tshogs bsags sgrib pa sbyangs
NK060(i)001:3883: gyur to // nas/ sa bcu pa'i byang chub sems
NK060(i)001:3884: dpa' lha'i bu dam pa tog dkar po zhes bya
NK060(i)001:3886: dga' ldan gyi gnas na lha rnams kyi ston pa mdzad la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis/
NK060(i)001:3887: bsod nams rgya chen tshogs mang dran rtogs shing //
NK060(i)001:3888: blo gros mtha' yas shes rab 'od mdzad pa'i //
NK060(i)001:3889: mtshungs med stobs mnga' sgyu rtsal rgya che ba //
NK060(i)001:3890: mar me mdzad kyi lung bstan dgongs par mdzod //
NK060(i)001:3892: byang chub sems dpa'i dgongs pa la bdag gi bya ba 'di tsam du ma zad de/
NK060(i)001:3893: thams cad mkhyen par sangs rgyas nas sems can gyi
NK060(i)001:3894: don mdzad par smon lam btab pa dran nas mdzad
NK060(i)001:3895: pa bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad
NK060(i)001:3896: par dgongs te/ mi pham mgon po la dbu rgyan bskon nas rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur zhing /
NK060(i)001:3897: 'dzam bu'i gling du rgya che rol pa ltar gzigs
NK060(i)001:3898: pa bzhi ru bshad kyang mdo sde mngon par 'byung
NK060(i)001:3899: ba dang / 'dul ba lung nas gzigs pa rnam pa lngar bshad pa bzhin/
NK060(i)001:3900: gling bzhi las 'dzam bu'i gling la gzigs/
NK060(i)001:3904: rigs sh+aakya'i rigs la gzigs te/
NK060(i)001:3905: glang po che thal kar mche ba drug pa zhig
NK060(i)001:3906: tu sprul nas yum sgyu ma lha mdzes gso sbyong
NK060(i)001:3907: la gnas pa'i lhums su zhugs nas/
NK060(i)001:3908: yum gyi lhums rgyal sras kyi nye bar spyad pa
NK060(i)001:3909: rin po che bkod pa zhes bya bar byin gyis
NK060(i)001:3910: brlabs nas zla ba dgu ngo bcu ru zag med
NK060(i)001:3911: kyi bde ba la longs spyod do //
NK060(i)001:3912: de'i tshe dpal lha las babs pa'i mchod rten rang byung du byon no //
NK060(i)001:3913: gnyis pa bltams pa dang zhes pa ni/
NK060(i)001:3914: shing pho byi ba'i lo'i dbyar zla ba'i nya'i nang
NK060(i)001:3915: par skya rengs shar tsam na lum+bi'i tshal du blag
NK060(i)001:3916: sha'i shing la sku brten nas bshad pa'i gnas spangs
NK060(i)001:3917: pa'i phyir rtsib ma'i go bar g.yas pa na bza'
NK060(i)001:3919: phyogs bzhir gom par bdun bdun por zhing dam bca'
NK060(i)001:3920: re mdzad pa'i rjes la yum byang chub kyi yan
NK060(i)001:3921: lag bdun dang ldan pa'i rtags su zhabs rjes la
NK060(i)001:3923: de'i dus su dpal pad+ma spungs pa'i mchod rten rang byung du byon no //
NK060(i)001:3926: klu'i rgyal po 'jog pos sku khrus gsol na/
NK060(i)001:3927: bram ze mtshan mkhan la mtshan brtags pas bram ze brgyal bar gyur nas/
NK060(i)001:3928: de sangs pa dang 'khor ba'i kha lo chos la sgyur ba'i ston pa gcig 'ong ste/
NK060(i)001:3929: ston pa 'byon khar bram ze rgas zhes smre sngags 'don no //
NK060(i)001:3930: de nas zhag bdun nas ma 'das par gyur nas byang chub sems dpa'i rim gro ba/
NK060(i)001:3934: dri ma 'phyi ba'i ma ma brgyad brgyad de sum
NK060(i)001:3935: cu so gnyis kyis bsrel bas sku cher brtas par
NK060(i)001:3936: gyur to // gzhon nu rol rtsed mdzad pa dang /
NK060(i)001:3937: khab dang rgyal srid bzhes pa'i mdzad pa gnyis ni thun mong du 'chad de/
NK060(i)001:3938: rol rtsed kun gyi thog mar yig dpon kun gyi
NK060(i)001:3939: bshes gnyen la yi ge slob pa'i phyir khye'u dang
NK060(i)001:3940: bu mo stong phrag bcu bcu'i 'khor dang bcas te
NK060(i)001:3941: phyin pa las/ rgyal bus yig dpon la dris pa/
NK060(i)001:3942: tshangs pa'i yi ge'am kha ro ti'i yi ge zhes
NK060(i)001:3943: sogs yig rigs yi ge'i gnas drug cu rtsa bzhi
NK060(i)001:3944: gang la bslab ces dris pas/
NK060(i)001:3945: slob dpon kun gyi bshes gnyen ngo mtshar du gyur nas bzhin gyi mdangs phyung nas/
NK060(i)001:3946: sems can dag pa ngo mtshar che //
NK060(i)001:3947: bstan bcos kun la bslabs gyur kyang //
NK060(i)001:3949: yi ge'i gral ni byon par gyur //
NK060(i)001:3950: zhes pa la sogs pa smras pas/
NK060(i)001:3951: de'i rkyen gyis byis pa sum khri nyis stong byang chub du smin par byas so //
NK060(i)001:3952: de nas zhing las kyi mtha'i skyed mos tshal du
NK060(i)001:3953: shing 'dzam bu'i grib ma la bsam gtan gzhi la
NK060(i)001:3954: mnyam par bzhag pas phyi rol pa'i drang srong rdzu
NK060(i)001:3955: 'phrul can mngon par shes pa dang ldan pa lnga'i
NK060(i)001:3957: byang chub sems dpa' la tshigs su bcad pa du mas kyang bstod do //
NK060(i)001:3958: de'i tshe shing gzhan gyi grib ma yol yang shing
NK060(i)001:3959: 'dzam bu'i grib ma ma yol ba la skye bo
NK060(i)001:3960: thams cad ya mtshan du gyur pa na sh+aakya rgan
NK060(i)001:3961: rabs pa rnam kyis rgyal po la gsol pa/
NK060(i)001:3962: gzhon nu 'di ni rab tu byung na de bzhin
NK060(i)001:3963: gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:3965: khyim nas ma byung na ni mtha' bzhi las rnam
NK060(i)001:3966: par rgyal ba 'khor lo sgyur ba'i rgyal por 'gyur
NK060(i)001:3967: bas/ de'i slad du btsun mo blang bar bagyi'o zhes bskul nas/
NK060(i)001:3968: yab rgyal pos rgyal bu la khab bzhes par zhu ba phul bas/
NK060(i)001:3969: byang chub sems dpa' 'di snyam du sems te/
NK060(i)001:3970: 'dod pa'i skyon ni bdag gis mtha' yas rigs //
NK060(i)001:3971: 'thab mo mkhon bcas mya ngan sdug bsngal rtsa //
NK060(i)001:3972: 'dzin byed dug gi lo ma 'dra ba ste //
NK060(i)001:3973: me dang 'dra zhing ral gri'i so dang 'dra //
NK060(i)001:3974: 'dod pa'i yon tan bdag 'dod ma yin te //
NK060(i)001:3975: bdag gi bud med tshogs dang mdzes ma yin //
NK060(i)001:3976: bsam gtan ting 'dzin de bas zhi sems su //
NK060(i)001:3977: bdag ni mi smra nags tshal gnas par bya //
NK060(i)001:3978: snyam du thugs kyis dgongs kyang sngon gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyis btsun mo'i tshogs spangs nas/
NK060(i)001:3979: rab tu byung ba'i rnam par thar pa la bslab pa'i phyir khab bzhes par dgongs nas/
NK060(i)001:3980: tshigs su bcad pa 'di dag smras so //
NK060(i)001:3981: 'dam dang ljan ljin khrod nas pad ma rnam par 'phel //
NK060(i)001:3982: mi rnams gang ba'i gnas nas rgyal pos mchod pa 'thob //
NK060(i)001:3983: gang tshe byang chub sems dpa' 'khor mchog thob gyur la //
NK060(i)001:3984: de tshe sems can bye ba khrag khrig 'ching byed 'dul //
NK060(i)001:3985: sngon gyi byang chub sems dpa' mkhas mang gang byung ba //
NK060(i)001:3986: de dag kun gyis btsun mo sras dang slas kyang bsten //
NK060(i)001:3987: 'on kyang 'dod pas chags med bsam gtan bde ma nyams //
NK060(i)001:3988: bdag kyang de dag yon tan rjes su bslab par bya //
NK060(i)001:3989: gang la spyod lam yon tan bden ba'i tshig med pa //
NK060(i)001:3990: bud med phal pa gang yang bdag gi tshul mthun min //
NK060(i)001:3991: gang zhig bdag gi sems ni mngon par dga' byed cing //
NK060(i)001:3992: bag yod gzugs dang na tshod rus rigs dag pa 'os //
NK060(i)001:3993: des na yon tan tshigs su bcad de yi ger bri //
NK060(i)001:3994: 'di 'dra'i bu mo mchis na bdag la bka' stsol
NK060(i)001:3995: cig /skyes bo phal pa ma bsdams bdag la mkho
NK060(i)001:3996: ma lags // yon tan brjod pa'i 'di ldan mchis
NK060(i)001:3997: na bdag stsol cig /dar cing gzugs bzang ldan yang
NK060(i)001:3999: phu nu ma la byams ltar byams pa'i sems ldan zhing //
NK060(i)001:4000: gtong la dga' ste dge sbyong bram ze'i sbyin tshul can //
NK060(i)001:4001: de 'dra'i bu mo mchis na yab kyis bdag stsol
NK060(i)001:4002: cig /gang la nga rgyal khengs dang zhe sdang ma
NK060(i)001:4003: mchis shing // g.yo dang phrag dog sgyu spangs drang ba'i ngang tshul can //
NK060(i)001:4004: rmi lam na yang skyes pa gzhan la chags dang bral //
NK060(i)001:4005: bdag gi khyos ni chog 'tshal rtag sdom bag mchis la //
NK060(i)001:4006: rgyags pa ma mchis mi g.yem zung thub tshul 'chang zhing //
NK060(i)001:4007: nga rgyal ma mchis 'gying dang bral bas bran mo bzhin //
NK060(i)001:4008: sgra dri ro la ma chags chang la'ang ma chags te //
NK060(i)001:4009: 'dod bral brnab sems ma mchis rang gi nor gyis 'tshal //
NK060(i)001:4010: bden la gnas shing mi 'phyar g.yem pa ma lags pa //
NK060(i)001:4011: ngo tsha'i gos 'tshal rgod dang khengs pa ma mchis gnas //
NK060(i)001:4012: lha dang bkra shis ma chags rtag tu chos la brtson //
NK060(i)001:4013: lus dang ngag dang yid kyi dngos po rab dag pa //
NK060(i)001:4014: gnyid dang rmugs pa mi mnga' nga rgyal glen bral zhing //
NK060(i)001:4015: rtog dang ldan la legs pa'i las rnams rtag spyod de //
NK060(i)001:4016: gyos sgyugs gnyis la'ang ston pa bzhin gyi rim gror ldan //
NK060(i)001:4017: bran dang bran mo kun la'ang bdag bzhin byams bsrel ba //
NK060(i)001:4018: smad 'tshong bzhin du bstan bcos cho ga 'tshal zhing mkhas //
NK060(i)001:4019: slad kyis nyal zhing sngon du mal nas ldang bgyid pa //
NK060(i)001:4020: byams pas rjes bsnyegs bzhin du tshul 'chos ma mchis pa //
NK060(i)001:4021: de 'dra'i bu mo mchis na yab kyis bdag stsol cig /ces yab la zhus pas/
NK060(i)001:4022: yab kyis de dag yi ger bris nas mdun na 'don rnams la bskur te/
NK060(i)001:4023: gong gi yon tan rnams dang ldan pa'i bu mo
NK060(i)001:4024: tshol du btang bas sh+aakya lag na be con gyi
NK060(i)001:4025: bu mo rnyed nas/ rgyas pos pho nya ba btang ste bslangs pas/
NK060(i)001:4026: sh+aakya lag na be con can na re/
NK060(i)001:4027: gzhon nu de ni pho brang na skyid par 'khrungs pa lags na/
NK060(i)001:4028: bdag gi rigs ni sgyu rtsal shes pa la bu
NK060(i)001:4029: mo gtong gis gzhan la ni ma yin no zer
NK060(i)001:4030: ro // der rgyal bu byang chub sems dpa' des sa 'tsho ma rgyal ba'i ru mtshon du bzhag ste/
NK060(i)001:4031: sh+aakya'i gzhon nu lnga brgya dang sgyu rtsal 'gran pas
NK060(i)001:4032: sgyu rtsal drug cu rtsa bzhi la sogs pa thams
NK060(i)001:4033: cad la'ang byang chub sems dpa' 'ba' zhig khyad par
NK060(i)001:4035: de nas sh+aakya lag na be con can gyis bu mo byang chub sems dpa' la phul te/
NK060(i)001:4036: byang chub sems dpas sa 'tsho ma btsun mo brgyad
NK060(i)001:4037: khri bzhi stong gi nang nas mchog tu dbang bskur
NK060(i)001:4038: nas/ byang chub sems dpa' btsun mo'i tshogs dang rol
NK060(i)001:4039: zhing dgung lo nyi shu rtsa dgu'i bar du dga'
NK060(i)001:4040: nas/ mgur spyad do // rab tu byung ba dang /
NK060(i)001:4041: zhes pa de'i tshe phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang
NK060(i)001:4042: chub sems dpa' rnams kyis bskul ba'i tshig sil snyan
NK060(i)001:4043: gyi sgra las byung ba'i tshigs su bcad pa du
NK060(i)001:4045: grong khyer gyi phyi rol tu sku 'chag tu byon pas/
NK060(i)001:4046: skye rga na 'chi'i sdug bsngal gyis mnar ba rnams dang /
NK060(i)001:4047: dge slong zhi ba 'dul ba la sogs pa dge
NK060(i)001:4048: slong gi chos rnams dang ldan pa zhig mthong ba'i
NK060(i)001:4049: rkyen gyis khyim nas khyim med par rab tu 'byung
NK060(i)001:4050: bar 'tshal te/ yab rgyal po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NK060(i)001:4051: lha gcig bdag ni mngon par 'byung ba'i dus bab
NK060(i)001:4052: rig /gegs kyang ma mdzad mi dgyes pa yang ma
NK060(i)001:4053: mdzad cig /rgyal po gnyen bcas yul 'khor bcas te
NK060(i)001:4054: bzod par mdzod // ces gsol pas/
NK060(i)001:4055: rgyal po mchi mas mig gang bzhin pas/
NK060(i)001:4056: byang chub sems dpa' la 'di skad ces smras pa/
NK060(i)001:4058: yid la 'dod pa gang yin pa smros shing sbyin par bya'o zhes smras pas/
NK060(i)001:4059: byang chub sems dpas yab la gsol ba/
NK060(i)001:4060: lha gcig dam pa bzhi 'tshal de ni bdag la stsol //
NK060(i)001:4061: gal te stsal bar spyod na mnga' ni khyod la mchis //
NK060(i)001:4062: 'on kyang rtag tu khyim na gzims shing 'byung mi 'gyur //
NK060(i)001:4063: lha gcig bdag la rgas pas tshugs par mi 'gyur zhing //
NK060(i)001:4064: rtag tu mdog bzang dar la bab par gnas pa dang //
NK060(i)001:4065: nad ma mchis pa thob cing nad kyis mi btab dang //
NK060(i)001:4066: tshe dpag ma mchis pa dang rgud par mi 'gyur 'tshal //
NK060(i)001:4068: rgyal po nyam thag bzhin pas gzhon nu gnas ma
NK060(i)001:4069: yin pa de lta bu ster ba'i mthu bdag la
NK060(i)001:4071: byang chub sems dpas yang gsol pa/
NK060(i)001:4072: lha gcig gal te mchog bzhi 'di dag mi stsal na //
NK060(i)001:4073: gzhan yang mchog gcig gsol gyi rgyal po gsan du gsol //
NK060(i)001:4074: 'di nas shi 'phos nying mtshams sbyor bar mi 'gyur mdzod //
NK060(i)001:4075: ces smras pas rgyal po thugs kho thag chod de gnang ba byin no //
NK060(i)001:4076: dkar phyogs kyi lha rnams kyis kyang btsun mo'i tshogs
NK060(i)001:4077: dang gzhon nu srung bar byed pa'i sh+aakya'i tshogs dang
NK060(i)001:4078: / mdun na 'don rnams kyang gnyid kyis myos par byas so //
NK060(i)001:4079: de'i tshe byang chub sems dpas srod kyi cha la btsun mo grags 'dzin ma'i lhums su sras bzhag nas/
NK060(i)001:4080: nam gyi gung la rgyal po chen po bzhi 'khor dang bcas pas bar snang la gdan drangs nas/
NK060(i)001:4081: mchod rten rnam dag gi drung du rang byung gis bsnyen par rdzogs par mdzad do //
NK060(i)001:4082: de'i tshe bkra shis brtsegs pa'i mchod rten rang byung du byon no //
NK060(i)001:4083: dka' thub mdzad pa dang zhes pas/
NK060(i)001:4084: drang srong ring 'phur dang lhag spyod gnyis la ci yang med pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4085: srid rtse'i sems dag mngon du mdzad nas chu bo
NK060(i)001:4086: nee rany+dza na'i 'gram du byon nas mkha' khyab kyi
NK060(i)001:4089: la brten nas lo drug tu dka' ba spyad de
NK060(i)001:4090: dbugs 'gyu ba gcad nas bzhugs so //
NK060(i)001:4091: de'i dus su dpal ka ni ka'i mchod rten rang byung du byon no //
NK060(i)001:4092: byang chub snying por gshegs pa'i mdzad pa ni/
NK060(i)001:4093: grong pa'i bu mo legs skyes mas 'o thug drangs pa gsol nas/
NK060(i)001:4094: bdud gzhom pa'i phyir r+ts+wa 'tshor bkra shis la r+ts+wa
NK060(i)001:4095: blangs te khyer nas byang chub kyi shing la lan
NK060(i)001:4096: bdun bskor nas r+ts+wa'i rtse mo nang du bstan rtsa
NK060(i)001:4097: ba phyir bstan pa'i steng du zhal shar du phyogs
NK060(i)001:4098: pas bzhugs nas byang chub ma thob kyi bar du
NK060(i)001:4099: skyil krung mi bshig pa'i dam bca' mdzad do //
NK060(i)001:4100: bdud btul ba dang zhes pas/
NK060(i)001:4101: thog mar bdud bskul ba'i phyir smin mtshams nas 'od zer bkye ste/
NK060(i)001:4102: byang chub sems dpa' mang po 'khor du bsdus nas bdud kyi gnas mog mog por byas pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4103: bdud sdig can gyis bdud kyi dpung mi 'khrugs phrag gcig bsdus te/
NK060(i)001:4104: cho 'phrul sna tshogs bstan cing mtshon cha sna tshogs
NK060(i)001:4105: 'phangs pa rnams me tog gi char du gyur cing
NK060(i)001:4106: / bdud rnams kyis rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs la skur pa btab pa'i tshe/
NK060(i)001:4107: sa'i lha mo la dpang gsol te sa'i lha mos
NK060(i)001:4108: dpang po byas pas bdud rnams skyengs nas byer bar
NK060(i)001:4109: gyur cing bdud kyi bu mo rnams kyi g.yo sgyus
NK060(i)001:4110: kyang bslur ma tshugs par bdud kyi dpung rnams 'thor
NK060(i)001:4111: nas zhag bdun du 'phrad par ma gyur to //
NK060(i)001:4112: de'i tshe dpal gser gyi 'od can gyi mchod rten rang byung du byon no //
NK060(i)001:4113: sangs rgyas pa dang zhes pas/
NK060(i)001:4114: sa pho khyi'i lo sa ga'i zla ba'i nam gyi
NK060(i)001:4115: cha smad skya rengs shar ba rnga brdung ba'i tshod
NK060(i)001:4116: tsam na byang chub sems dpas rten 'brel bcu gnyis
NK060(i)001:4117: dang / bden pa bzhi'i don khong du chud cing
NK060(i)001:4118: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu mngon
NK060(i)001:4119: dang / du byas nas/ skad cig dang ldan pa'i
NK060(i)001:4120: shes rab kyi mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas so
NK060(i)001:4121: dang / du byas nas/ // de'i dus su byang
NK060(i)001:4122: chub chen po'i mchod rten rang byung du byon no
NK060(i)001:4123: dang / du byas nas/ // // zla ba yang
NK060(i)001:4124: gzas zin zhing btsun mo grags 'dzin ma'i sras kyang
NK060(i)001:4125: bltams nas mtshan kyang sgra can 'dzin du btags so
NK060(i)001:4126: dang / du byas nas/ // // // cho 'phrul chen po ston pa dang zhes pa ni/
NK060(i)001:4127: de nas sangs rgyas kyis shing ta la bdun srid du 'phags te/
NK060(i)001:4128: lam gyi rgyud ni chad do zhes pa la sogs pa ched du brjod pa brjod do //
NK060(i)001:4129: lha rnams kyis kyang me tog pus nub tsam gtong te mchod cing 'jig rten snang bar byas/
NK060(i)001:4130: sa chen po rnam pa drug tu g.yos/
NK060(i)001:4131: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis chos nyid dga' bas dbang bskur/
NK060(i)001:4133: bdag cag ji ltar byang chub thob ltar khyod sangs rgyas //
NK060(i)001:4134: dper na mar dang mar gyi nying khu mtshungs 'dra zhing //
NK060(i)001:4135: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs shing lung bstan pas kyang ched du brjod pa mdzad do //
NK060(i)001:4136: de'i tshe cho 'phrul chen po'i mchod rten rang byung du byon no //
NK060(i)001:4137: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang zhes pas/
NK060(i)001:4138: sangs rgyas nas zhag bdun dang po la skyil mo krung ma bzhigs par byang chub kyi shing la gzigs/
NK060(i)001:4139: gnyis pa la stong gsum rgyang ring du 'chag /gsum
NK060(i)001:4140: pa la byang chub kyi snying por spyan mi 'dzum
NK060(i)001:4141: par gzigs/ bzhi pa la shar nub tu rgyang mi
NK060(i)001:4142: ring bar 'chag /lnga pa la klu btang bzung gi
NK060(i)001:4143: par gzigs/ gnas su bzhugs/ drug pa la shing nya gro d+ha skyong du bzhud/
NK060(i)001:4144: bdun pa la shi sgrol rgyu'i drung du bzhugs te/
NK060(i)001:4145: tshong pa ga gon dang bzang pos sbrang rtsi la
NK060(i)001:4146: sogs pa phul ba rgyal chen rigs bzhis phul ba'i
NK060(i)001:4147: rdo'i lhung bzed bzhi gcig tu byin gyis brlabs par
NK060(i)001:4148: bzhes te/ de gnyis kyi bsod snyoms kyang gsol nas shis pa brjod de/
NK060(i)001:4149: sbrang rtsi 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i rgyal por lung bstan no //
NK060(i)001:4150: de nas ston pa thugs las chung ngur bzhugs te/
NK060(i)001:4151: zab cing rdul bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK060(i)001:4152: bdud rtsi'i chos ni bdag gis thob par gyur //
NK060(i)001:4153: bdag gis bstan kyang gzhan gyis mi shes te //
NK060(i)001:4154: mi smra nags 'dab gnas par bya'o snyam //
NK060(i)001:4156: tshangs pa gtsug phud can gyis 'di skad du/
NK060(i)001:4157: ye shes chen po mchog gi dkyil 'khor bsgrub nas ni //
NK060(i)001:4158: phyogs bcu dag tu 'od zer rnam par bkye mdzad de //
NK060(i)001:4159: ye shes zer gyis mi yi pad ma kha 'byed pa //
NK060(i)001:4160: smra ba'i nyi ma de ring ci slang btang snyoms bzhugs //
NK060(i)001:4161: zhes pa la sogs pas bskul bas cang mi gsung bar snang zhing /
NK060(i)001:4162: yang thugs las chung ba la gzhol bas/
NK060(i)001:4163: brgya byin dang tshangs par nan tan du bskul bas zhal gyis bzhes te/
NK060(i)001:4164: b+aa ra n+aa s+air byon pa dang lnga sdes nang khrims bcas pa rang zhig tu gyur te/
NK060(i)001:4165: 'khor lnga sde bzang po dang lha yi 'khor rnams
NK060(i)001:4166: la chos bden pa bzhi lan gsum du bzlas pas
NK060(i)001:4167: rnams pa bcu gnyis kyis bskor te/
NK060(i)001:4169: lnga sdes dgra bcom pa thob cing brgyud nas gdul
NK060(i)001:4170: bya rnams kyis gang zag tu 'dzin pa bzlog pa'o
NK060(i)001:4171: // de ni bka' dang po bden pa bzhi'i rnams pas bstan pa'i chos kyis 'khor lo bskor ba'o //
NK060(i)001:4172: de nas gnas bya rgod phung po'i ri la sogs
NK060(i)001:4173: par 'khor theg pa chen po la yang dag par
NK060(i)001:4174: bzhugs pa rnams la bka' bar pa mtshan nyid med
NK060(i)001:4175: pa'i rnam pas bstan pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo dang
NK060(i)001:4176: / gnas ri ma la ya la sogs par 'khor
NK060(i)001:4177: nges pa don gyi theg pa la yang dag par
NK060(i)001:4178: bzhugs pa rnams la bka' mtha' ma legs par rnams
NK060(i)001:4179: par phye ba dang ldan pa nges pa don gyi
NK060(i)001:4180: rnam pas bstan pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ro
NK060(i)001:4181: / // de ltar 'khor lo gsum du bzhag pa
NK060(i)001:4182: ni phyogs gcig nas mtshon pa'am gtso che ba tsam
NK060(i)001:4183: yin gyi rnam pa thams cad du de'i nges pa
NK060(i)001:4185: de'i dus su dpal 'khor lo brtsegs pa'i mchod rten rang byung du byon no //
NK060(i)001:4186: mya ngan las 'das pa zhes pa ni/
NK060(i)001:4187: snyigs ma lnga dang ldan pa'i sems can rnams la
NK060(i)001:4188: thams cad mkhyen pa'i sku mngon du snang ba'i skal
NK060(i)001:4190: gdul bya rtag par 'dzin pa'i gnyen po'am thabs dam
NK060(i)001:4191: pa mi rtag pa'i tshul bstan par bya ba'i phyir
NK060(i)001:4192: dang / skyes pa'i mtha' 'chi bas mi gtong ba
NK060(i)001:4193: mtshon pa'i brdar bcom ldan 'das dgung lo brgyad cu
NK060(i)001:4194: bzhes pa'i tshe chu mo lug gi lo dpyid zla
NK060(i)001:4195: 'bring po'i tshes bco lnga'i nyin yongs su mya ngan
NK060(i)001:4197: grong khyer r+ts+wa mchog tu 'khor rnams la gdams ngag
NK060(i)001:4198: bzhag pa'i rjes su shing s+aa la zung gcig gi
NK060(i)001:4199: drung du seng ge'i nyal thabs kyis gzims shing sku
NK060(i)001:4200: yongs su mya ngan las 'das so //
NK060(i)001:4201: de'i tshe 'od srungs chen po 'od ma'i tshal na
NK060(i)001:4202: yod pa la sa g.yos par gyur pas de bzhin
NK060(i)001:4203: gshegs pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i rtags su mkhyen
NK060(i)001:4204: nas/ grong khyer r+ts+wa mchog tu byon nas bcom ldan 'das kyi pur sbyangs so //
NK060(i)001:4205: de'i tshe sku gdung chen po'i mchod rten rang byung du byon no //
NK060(i)001:4206: sku gdung ring bsrel dang tshems mche ba rnams lha
NK060(i)001:4207: dang mi la sogs pa'i gdul bya rnams kyis mchod
NK060(i)001:4208: rten du gdan drangs pa'i tshul ni/
NK060(i)001:4210: bcom ldan sku gdung brel bo brgyad dag las //
NK060(i)001:4211: bdun ni 'dzam bu gling pas mchod par 'thob //
NK060(i)001:4212: skyes bu mchog de'i bre bo gang zhig ni //
NK060(i)001:4213: grong khyer sgra sgrogs klu yi rgyal pos ma chod //
NK060(i)001:4214: skyes mchog de'i mche ba bzhi dag las //
NK060(i)001:4215: mche ba gcig ni rtsa gsum 'jig rten mchod //
NK060(i)001:4216: gnyis pa tshig 'dzin grong khyer yid 'ong na //
NK060(i)001:4217: gsum pa ka li rgyal po'i yul na ste //
NK060(i)001:4218: skyes mchog de yi mche ba bzhi pa ni //
NK060(i)001:4219: grong khyer sgra sgrogs klu yi rgyal pos mchod //
NK060(i)001:4221: bcom ldan 'das sku bltams pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4223: mya ngan las 'das pa rnams kyi lo gang yin
NK060(i)001:4224: gyi gsal kha mdo rnams na gsal bar gsungs pa
NK060(i)001:4225: kho bos ma mthong mod kyi dus kyi 'khor lo
NK060(i)001:4226: nas bcom ldan 'das thun mong ba'i 'khor gyi snang
NK060(i)001:4227: ngor mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul bstan pa de'i
NK060(i)001:4228: tshe/ thun mong ma yin pa'i 'khor rgyal po zla
NK060(i)001:4229: ba bzang po la sogs pa dang dpal ldan 'bras
NK060(i)001:4230: spungs su dus kyi 'khor lo'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK060(i)001:4231: dam pa dang po'i rgyud bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:4232: de nas lo drug brgya nas rgyal po grags pa 'byung bar lung bstan/
NK060(i)001:4233: grags pas lo brgya'i bar du rtsa rgyud gsungs shing bsdus rgyud sdud par lung bstan/
NK060(i)001:4234: de nas lo brgya nas ma ga d+har kla klo 'byung bar lung bstan/
NK060(i)001:4235: de nas lo brgya dang brgyad cu gya gnyis nas
NK060(i)001:4236: rigs ldan rgyal ba dang dus mtshungs su nyung ngu'i
NK060(i)001:4238: de nas lo nyis brgya nyi shu rtsa gcig nas
NK060(i)001:4239: rab byung gi lo la ma ga d+ha'i yul du
NK060(i)001:4240: nyung ngu'i rtsis dar bar lung bstan/
NK060(i)001:4241: de nas drug cu bskor lnga dang de nas chu
NK060(i)001:4242: mo lug gi bar la lo bcu drug 'das pa
NK060(i)001:4245: nyi skar la sogs pa thams cad ma 'phyugs par 'grig gi 'dug pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4246: snga rabs pa rnams kyi gtan rtsis la mi mthun
NK060(i)001:4247: pa du ma snang ba rnams la brtags shing dpyad
NK060(i)001:4248: nas/ rgyu mtshan dang ldan pa rnams la rjes su dpags pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:4250: sku yi mdzad pa 'di dag dang gong du sku
NK060(i)001:4251: gsung thugs rdo rje las 'thon par bshad pa 'gal
NK060(i)001:4254: drang ba po dag dga' ldan nas babs par zhes zer ba ni bden mod kyi/
NK060(i)001:4255: byang chub sems dpas dbang thob pa mthar phyin pa'i phyir 'gal ba med de/
NK060(i)001:4256: le'u'i klad nas byung khungs smos pa'o //
NK060(i)001:4258: nges don du rgyal ba drug pa'i thugs rig pa
NK060(i)001:4259: rang snang las 'thon pa yin kyang gdul bya drang
NK060(i)001:4260: ba'i don du mdzad pa bcu gnyis ltar snang nas
NK060(i)001:4262: yang skabs 'dir sku'i mdzad pa ston pa la chos
NK060(i)001:4263: kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang zhes pa skabs 'chol
NK060(i)001:4264: ba'i skyon du 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4266: mdzad pa'i sgra gzhi ma dang gtso che ba gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:4267: skabs 'dir gtso che la btags pa ste/
NK060(i)001:4268: dper na rta zhon mang po'i gseb na dre'u zhon
NK060(i)001:4269: pa re re tsam yod kyang rta pa mang po
NK060(i)001:4273: 'das da ltar ma 'ongs 'byung bar ma nges pa'i dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pas te/
NK060(i)001:4274: sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran pa'i mngon par shes pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4275: 'chi 'pho dang skye ba shes pa'i mngon shes gnyis so //
NK060(i)001:4277: dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa dang bya ba 'dug pas dus bzhi thad kar rim par mkhyen nam/
NK060(i)001:4278: btsal bas rang gi ngo bos stong pa'i mnyam nyid du mkhyen/
NK060(i)001:4280: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes de sems can gyi rtog pa dang khyad med par thal/
NK060(i)001:4281: dus bzhi thad ka thad dkar mkhyen tsam las mi 'dug pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:4283: dus bzhir 'dod kyang dus bzhi rang ma yin par thal/
NK060(i)001:4284: dus mnyam pa nyid dam stong pa nyid pa'i phyir ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4285: kun rdzob kyi bden pa'i cha nas dus bzhir snang la/
NK060(i)001:4286: don dam gyi bden pa'i cha nas dus bzhir ma dmigs/
NK060(i)001:4287: dbyer med kyi bden pa'i cha nas de nyid dang
NK060(i)001:4288: gzhan du brjod du med pas dus bzhi mnyam pa
NK060(i)001:4289: nyid ces bya'o // mkhyen tshul ni/
NK060(i)001:4290: spyir gyis gnas lugs dus las 'das pa/
NK060(i)001:4292: ye shes dus la dbang sgyur ba yin pa la/
NK060(i)001:4293: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gnas lugs dus las 'das pa yang mkhyen/
NK060(i)001:4294: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams blo dus ltar 'khrul par yang mkhyen te/
NK060(i)001:4295: de yang 'das pa la ma thogs ma chags pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4296: da ltar la ma thogs ma chags pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4297: ma 'ongs pa la ma thogs ma chags pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4298: 'byung bar ma nges pa la ma thogs ma chags
NK060(i)001:4299: pa'i ye shes kyis dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid du
NK060(i)001:4300: rang gsal 'dzin pa med par mkhyen no //
NK060(i)001:4301: 'o na gzhan thams cad na dus gsum las med
NK060(i)001:4302: pa la 'dir dus bzhir bshad pa'i dus log pa'i
NK060(i)001:4305: 'dir lha rtog sbyar ba'i dbang du dus bzhir grangs dang go rim nges so //
NK060(i)001:4306: de yang grangs nges pa ni dus ring ba dper byas na/
NK060(i)001:4307: bskal pa gcig la chags gnas 'jig stongs bzhir grangs nges/
NK060(i)001:4308: dus thung ba dper byas na lo gcig la dbyar dgun ston dpyid bzhir grangs nges pa bzhin te/
NK060(i)001:4309: des mtshon nas rgya cher spros pas chog go //
NK060(i)001:4310: go rim nges pa ni bskal pa lta bu dper byas nas/
NK060(i)001:4311: da lta bskal pa gnas pa'i dus la ltos na bskal pa chags pa ni 'das pa/
NK060(i)001:4313: stongs pa ni 'das ma 'ongs gang du 'ang ma nges pa'i dus so //
NK060(i)001:4314: de la kha cig na re/
NK060(i)001:4315: de ltar yin yang bskal pa sngar stongs pa ni 'das pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:4316: phyis stongs par 'gyur pa ni ma 'ongs pa yin pas dus gsum du kha tshon chod de zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4317: stongs pa'i dus de nyid gzhir byas pa la 'das
NK060(i)001:4318: ma 'ongs gnyis gang rung gcig tu kha tshon ma
NK060(i)001:4319: chod pas ma nges pa'i dus su ci'i phyir mi
NK060(i)001:4320: 'gyur/ rgyu mtshan de'i phyir dus bzhir grangs dang go rim nges pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:4321: de yang bskal pa 'jig pa'i dus na gnas pa 'das pa/
NK060(i)001:4323: 'chags pa ma nges pa'i dus so //
NK060(i)001:4324: de bzhin du stongs pa'i dus na 'jig pa 'das pa/
NK060(i)001:4326: gnas pa ma nges pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:4327: 'chags pa'i dus na stongs pa 'das pa/
NK060(i)001:4329: 'jig pa ma nges pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:4330: de'i phyir na blo dus ltar du 'khrul pa'i 'khrul rtog dus bzhir snang ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:4331: de dag lha dang sbyar na phyi'i sems ma bzhi yin te/
NK060(i)001:4332: 'di nyid kyi le'u bzhi pa las/
NK060(i)001:4333: ya ni skye ba rnam par dag /wa ni gnas pa dag pas te //
NK060(i)001:4334: ra ni 'jig pa dag pa yin //
NK060(i)001:4335: la ni stong pa bdag med pa'o //
NK060(i)001:4337: 'di ltar ma go ba 'ga' zhig /spar khab nas/
NK060(i)001:4338: ngo bo nyid 'di 'drar bstan du med pa zhes
NK060(i)001:4339: pas 'khrul gzhi byas nas dus gsum mnyam pa nyid
NK060(i)001:4340: kyi dus dang bzhir 'dod pa ni ches 'khrul te
NK060(i)001:4341: mnyam pa nyid rtog pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro
NK060(i)001:4343: ngo bo nyid 'di 'drar bstan du med ces pa'i don ni ma nges pa'i dus de ni/
NK060(i)001:4344: 'das ma 'ongs da ltar gyi dus gsum gang rung
NK060(i)001:4345: gi ngo bo 'di 'drar bstan du med ces bya
NK060(i)001:4346: ba yin no // gzhan yang gdul bya sems can
NK060(i)001:4347: thams cad kyi sems kyi rgyud nyon mongs pa shas
NK060(i)001:4348: che chung la sogs pa nyid las mi gzhan pa'am/
NK060(i)001:4349: yul med rang gsal gyi tshul gyis kun tu mkhyen
NK060(i)001:4350: pa gzhan gyi sems shes pa'i mngon shes dang gsum
NK060(i)001:4351: mo // rdzu 'phrul gyi lha'i spyan gyis mngon shes
NK060(i)001:4352: kyi gzugs thams cad nye ring med par kun tu
NK060(i)001:4353: mo // gzigs pa dang / rdzu 'phrul gyi lha'i
NK060(i)001:4354: snyan gyis mngon shes sgra thams cad nye ring med
NK060(i)001:4355: par kun tu gson pa la sogs te dbang po'i
NK060(i)001:4357: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho gas stod nas me 'bar ba dang /
NK060(i)001:4359: me yis mi tshig /chu yis mi gsher/
NK060(i)001:4363: sa la 'dzul ba la sogs pas kun tu sems
NK060(i)001:4364: can gyi don spyod pa rdzu 'phrul gyi mngon shes
NK060(i)001:4365: dang lnga'o // 'o na lus kyi rdzu 'phrul 'di dag mngon shes su ci 'gro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4366: 'di yang mtshan gtso che la btags zhes bla ma rnams gsung mod kyi/
NK060(i)001:4367: sems can gyi don byed tshul gyi cha nas lus
NK060(i)001:4368: kyi bkod pa ltar snang la yang thugs kyi rnam
NK060(i)001:4369: par 'khrul pa yin pas rdzu 'phrul gyi mngon shes
NK060(i)001:4370: zhes bya'o // de lta bu'i tshul ji ltar spyod
NK060(i)001:4371: kyang gzung 'dzin mi mnga' bas zag pa med pa
NK060(i)001:4372: zhes bya'o // ste/ spyod yul yongs su dag pa
NK060(i)001:4373: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa yi 'gro ba'i bsam
NK060(i)001:4374: pa mkhyen cing don rdzogs pa'i phyir zag pa med
NK060(i)001:4375: pa'i mngon par shes pa ste de ltar drug dang
NK060(i)001:4376: zhes bya'o // ste/ ldan pa'o // bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdzad pa/
NK060(i)001:4378: kun tu gdul bya la zhi khro la sogs pa'i sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4379: dus kun tu thugs mkhyen pa'i ye shes tshad med pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4380: dus kun tu phra men la sogs pa'i zhal bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4381: dus kun tu gdul bya'i ngo la gsung bstan pa
NK060(i)001:4382: dang theg pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan
NK060(i)001:4383: pa ste/ de ltar bsam gyis mi khyab pa grangs med pa gdul bya'i snang ba dang /
NK060(i)001:4384: lhun gyis grub pa'i rol pa mi 'gag pa'i phyir phyogs bcur snang bar gyur to //
NK060(i)001:4386: kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4388: stag dang spre'u ltar mi mdzad/
NK060(i)001:4390: ca co dang ga zha mi mi mdzad/
NK060(i)001:4392: mnyam par ma bzhag pa mi mnga' bar bshad pa 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4394: gong ma ni gdul bya'i don du mi 'gyur ba'i phyir thub pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:4395: 'di ni gdul bya'i don du 'gyur na sku gsung
NK060(i)001:4396: thugs kyi mdzad pa cir yang mdzad pa la dgongs
NK060(i)001:4397: pa yin no // yang sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4398: zhal bsam gyis mi khyab pa la khyad par ci yod ce na/
NK060(i)001:4399: snga ma ni dbu lus mthun pa'i sgo nas smos la/
NK060(i)001:4400: phyi ma ni dbu lus mi mthun pas te/
NK060(i)001:4401: phra men gyi sgo nas don mdzad pa'i phyir smos so //
NK060(i)001:4402: yang bsam gyis mi khyab pa grangs med pa phyogs bcur snang bar gyur to zhes pa la/
NK060(i)001:4404: sprul pa'i sku gcig las gcig sprul na thugs pa med par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:4407: yang sprul du zhes zer ba ni kha gam pa'o //
NK060(i)001:4408: zhes pas gsal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4409: 'di la rgya gab gong pa na re/
NK060(i)001:4410: rgyal ba lhun grub kyi mdzad pa go mi 'gag pa nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK060(i)001:4411: 'khor gdul bya'i snang ba chu dwangs pa lta bu dang /
NK060(i)001:4412: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan cing thugs rje chen
NK060(i)001:4413: po'i 'brel pa yod pa bar snang sgrib g.yogs med
NK060(i)001:4414: pa lta bu'i ngos nas bzhag pa'o //
NK060(i)001:4415: de'i phyir yang sprul du mi 'gyur gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:4421: spyir theg pa'i go ba ni/
NK060(i)001:4422: 'og nas gong du 'degs par byed pa'i don gyis na theg pa zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:4430: gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad kyang bsdu na 'og nas 'byung ba'i 'di lta ste/
NK060(i)001:4431: gdul bya 'dul ba'i dbang gis lngar snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:4432: de yang lha zhes pa dang mi zhes pa'i ming ni 'dod rgyal te/
NK060(i)001:4433: gang zhig mi dge bcu spong ba'i sgor zhugs nas/
NK060(i)001:4434: las rgyu 'bras la yid ches pa'i lta ba dge ba bcu spyod cing /
NK060(i)001:4437: mi g.yo pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgoms pas lha dang
NK060(i)001:4438: mi'i gnas rigs stod rigs su 'degs par byed pa'i
NK060(i)001:4439: don gyis na theg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4440: thos sgrogs gzhan brten zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:4441: slob dpon la brten dgos pas sam/
NK060(i)001:4442: phal cher nyan cing thos pa'i phyir nyan thos kyi ste/
NK060(i)001:4443: bden pa bzhi'i sgor zhugs nas gang zag gi bdag
NK060(i)001:4444: rang bzhin med par rtogs pas khrims nyis brgya lnga
NK060(i)001:4445: bcu rang don du spyod cing /
NK060(i)001:4446: ye shes bcu drug bsgoms pas gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rgyun zhugs dang /
NK060(i)001:4449: mthar thug gi 'bras bu dgra bcom pa'i gnas su 'degs par byed pas na theg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4450: sbyor lam bzod pa'i 'bring po nas rigs phye ste/
NK060(i)001:4451: rang gi 'bras bu ma thob kyi bar du rkyen
NK060(i)001:4452: slob dpon la mi ltos par rang gi shes rab
NK060(i)001:4453: kyis dur khrod kyi bam ro la brtags nas ma
NK060(i)001:4454: rig pas bkag pas rang byang chub kyi sa thob
NK060(i)001:4455: par 'dod de/ rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas
NK060(i)001:4456: zhugs shing bdag phyed dang gnyis rang bzhin med par
NK060(i)001:4457: rtogs pas khrims nyis brgya lnga bcu rang don du
NK060(i)001:4458: spyod pa nyan thos dang mthun pa la/
NK060(i)001:4459: rdzu 'phrul ya ma zung gi sgo nas gzhan don shas 'ga' spyod cing /
NK060(i)001:4460: rten 'brel lugs 'byung bkag nas lugs ldog stong pa bcu gnyis khrims chags su bsgoms pas/
NK060(i)001:4461: 'bras bu bse ru'am ne tso lta bu'i yid bde
NK060(i)001:4462: ba mchog gi sar 'degs par byed pa'i don gyis
NK060(i)001:4464: bdag don du byang chub pa gzhan don la sems pas na byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ste/
NK060(i)001:4465: smon 'jug gnyis kyi sgo nas zhugs nas gang zag
NK060(i)001:4466: dang chos kyi bdag gnyis ka rang bzhin med par
NK060(i)001:4467: rtogs pas pha rol tu phyin pa drug gam bcu
NK060(i)001:4468: gzhan don 'ba' zhig tu spyod cing /
NK060(i)001:4469: sa bcu rim gyis spros bral du bsgoms pas 'bras
NK060(i)001:4470: bu bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sar 'degs par
NK060(i)001:4471: byed pa'i don gyis na theg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4472: theg pa de dag las kyang lta sgom spyod 'bras
NK060(i)001:4473: mchog tu gyur pas na bla na med pa'i theg
NK060(i)001:4474: pa ste/ de la yang phye na phyi nang gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:4475: phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa gsum la/
NK060(i)001:4476: dang po bya ba'i rgyud ni/
NK060(i)001:4477: khrus dang gtsang sbra'i sgo nas zhugs nas don dam
NK060(i)001:4478: pa dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma dang bral bar
NK060(i)001:4479: rtogs pas mchod rdzas dkar gsum mngar gsum la spyod
NK060(i)001:4480: cing / sgom pa mtshan bcas lha ye shes sems dpa' rje bo dang /
NK060(i)001:4481: bdag dam tshig sems dpas khol gyi tshul gyis mchod
NK060(i)001:4482: pa phar 'bul zhing dngos grub tshur zhu ba dang
NK060(i)001:4483: / mtshan med bden gnyis re mos su bsgoms pas
NK060(i)001:4484: 'bras bu rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sar 'degs
NK060(i)001:4487: 'jug sgo dang spyod pa bya ba'i rgyu dang mthun/
NK060(i)001:4488: lta ba dang sgom pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud dang
NK060(i)001:4489: mthun pa la 'bras bu rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang
NK060(i)001:4490: gi sar 'degs par byed pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4491: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud ting nge 'a dzin gyi sgo nas zhugs nas/
NK060(i)001:4492: sems rang rig rang gsal dag pa rnam snang chen
NK060(i)001:4493: por rtogs pas dam rdzas kha yar ba longs spyod
NK060(i)001:4494: cing / bdag dam tshig sems dpa' dang /
NK060(i)001:4495: lha ye shes sems dpa' grogs po mnyam po'i tshul du bsgoms pas/
NK060(i)001:4496: skyes dang skyes lan gyi tshul du phan tshun mchod
NK060(i)001:4497: pa mnyam por phul bas 'bras bu rigs lnga stug
NK060(i)001:4498: po bkod pa'i sar 'degs par byed pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4499: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud rnal 'byor chen po ba ni/
NK060(i)001:4500: thabs dang shes rab kyi sgo nas zhugs nas bden
NK060(i)001:4501: pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por rtogs
NK060(i)001:4502: pas dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga la 'jol nyog du
NK060(i)001:4503: spyod cing / lha dang rtog pa dbyer med du
NK060(i)001:4504: bsgoms pas 'bras bu ma chags pad ma can gyi
NK060(i)001:4505: sar 'degs par byed pa'i don gyis na thig pas
NK060(i)001:4506: spyod cing / zhes bya'o // nyon mongs pa la dgongs te gsungs pa/
NK060(i)001:4508: rtsa ba ma rig pa gnyis kho na las gyur pa'i rnam par rtog pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4509: nyon mongs pa dug gsum cha mnyam pa'ang yang na
NK060(i)001:4510: khong khro ste nyon mongs pa bzhi po re re
NK060(i)001:4511: la'ang nyi khri chig stong ste/
NK060(i)001:4512: stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i gnyen por spong sgyur dbang du byed pa'i chos 'dul ba/
NK060(i)001:4515: rig pa 'dzin pa sngags kyi sde snod dang bzhi po re re la'ang nyi khri chig stong ste/
NK060(i)001:4516: stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi sngar 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:4517: da ltar gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyang gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:4518: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyang gsung par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:4519: thabs sam gnyen po la dgongs te bsdu ba'o //
NK060(i)001:4521: chos kyi sgo de dag thams cad kyang nyon mongs pa'i gnyen por 'gyur tshul ni/
NK060(i)001:4522: theg pa lnga ltar na gnyen po yang lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:4523: sde snod bzhi ltar na gnyen po yang bzhir 'gyur mod kyis/
NK060(i)001:4524: 'di la skyed lung gi yang khyed bla ma ni ral gri'i stong thun dang sbyor/
NK060(i)001:4525: chu bar gyi glan sh+aakya bzang po sprul nag gi stong thun dang sbyor kyang /
NK060(i)001:4526: rje sgro phug pa chen po ni dug sdong gi stong thun dang sbyor te/
NK060(i)001:4528: ldum rar dug gi sdong skyes pa //
NK060(i)001:4529: dug sdong yin par shes ma thag /rtsad nas bcad de dbyung bar bya //
NK060(i)001:4530: ci phyir ldum zas de dag la //
NK060(i)001:4533: dper na rgyal po chen po gcig gi bza' shing
NK060(i)001:4534: gi ra bar dug shing gyi sdong po gcig skyes
NK060(i)001:4535: pa la/ 'bangs blun po rnams dug shing gi ro
NK060(i)001:4536: mngar ba tshor zhing de la chags nas bza' shing
NK060(i)001:4537: pa la/ dor nas/ dug shing yal ga lo 'dab
NK060(i)001:4538: me tog 'bras bu dang bcas pa la longs spyod
NK060(i)001:4539: pas dug nad drag po'i sdug bsngal gyis mnar zhing
NK060(i)001:4541: dpe de bzhin du ma rig pa gnyis kyis bskyed
NK060(i)001:4542: pa'i nyon mongs pa'i sdong po yal 'dab dug lnga'am
NK060(i)001:4543: nye nyon nyi shu la sogs pa la/
NK060(i)001:4544: tha mal pa'i lha mi 'jig rten chos brgyad la
NK060(i)001:4545: mngon par zhen pa rnams kyis dge ba bcu spangs
NK060(i)001:4546: nas/ nyon mongs pa dang mi dge ba'i las la
NK060(i)001:4547: 'jol nyog du spyad pas 'bras bu ngan song gsum
NK060(i)001:4548: gyi sdug bsngal gyis nyam thag cing thar pa'i srog
NK060(i)001:4550: 'bangs de rnams kyi nang nas dug shing gi nyes dmigs shes pa kha cig ni/
NK060(i)001:4551: bza' shing dang dug shing gi khe nyen shes nas/
NK060(i)001:4552: bza' shing la longs spyod par byed kyang dug shing
NK060(i)001:4553: gi khrod nas 'phags par ma nus pa bzhin du
NK060(i)001:4554: lha mi'i nang nas dkar po'i las sad pa kha
NK060(i)001:4555: cig /dge ba'i las kyi 'bras bu mtho ris dang
NK060(i)001:4556: / sdig pa'i las kyi 'bras bu ngan song las
NK060(i)001:4557: mi 'da' zhing mi bslu bas na chud mi za
NK060(i)001:4558: bar yid ches pas mi dge bcu spangs nas dge
NK060(i)001:4559: bcu spyad kyang 'khor ba las nges par 'byung ma
NK060(i)001:4560: nus pa lha mi'i theg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4561: yang 'bangs de rnams kyi nang nas kha cig na re/
NK060(i)001:4562: dug shing gi sdong po 'di rtsa ba khab rtse
NK060(i)001:4563: tsam yang ma lus par bton nas rta dang glang
NK060(i)001:4564: po la bkal te/ la brgal dang chu 'phags su bskyal ba drag go zer ro //
NK060(i)001:4565: dpe de bzhin du phyi gzung ba'i yul rags pa
NK060(i)001:4566: dang nang 'dzin pa'i shes pa rgyun dang bcas pa
NK060(i)001:4567: rang bzhin med par rtogs pas 'khor ba las nges
NK060(i)001:4568: par byung yang / gzung yul rdul phra rab dang
NK060(i)001:4569: 'dzin sems shes pa skad cig ma don dam du
NK060(i)001:4570: 'dod pa nyan thos kyi theg pa la nyon mongs
NK060(i)001:4572: yang 'bangs de bas kyang cung zad thabs che ba gcig na re/
NK060(i)001:4573: dug shing gi sdong po 'di rtsa ba nas 'don mi dgos te/
NK060(i)001:4574: sdong po sngar bzhin bskyal nas bcad mtshams la khro
NK060(i)001:4575: chu khol ma blug pas slar skyes bar mi 'gyur
NK060(i)001:4577: 'dzin rig skad cig ma don dam gyi bden par
NK060(i)001:4578: 'dod pas phyi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung pa bcu
NK060(i)001:4579: gnyis mang nyung gi tshul du 'khor la/
NK060(i)001:4580: nang gi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba bcu gnyis lus med rnams la bag chags dang /
NK060(i)001:4581: lus can rnams la dngos su 'khor bar 'dod pas
NK060(i)001:4582: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa la nyon mongs pa
NK060(i)001:4584: yang 'bangs de rnams kyi nang nas/
NK060(i)001:4585: lha rje mkhas pa cig na re/
NK060(i)001:4586: dug shing gi rtsa ba khab rtse tsam yang ma lus par bru ba dang lta ci smos/
NK060(i)001:4587: dug sdong bcad nas bsgyel pa yang nyes dmigs dang rtsol bar bcas pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:4588: de bas na kho bo ni sman mar sbyor pa
NK060(i)001:4589: la dug shing nyo ba yang ma rnyed do zhes
NK060(i)001:4590: zer nas/ dug shing la sman sbyor byas pas nad
NK060(i)001:4591: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi sel zhing ro rtsa'i mchog tu
NK060(i)001:4593: dpe de bzhin du nang 'dzin pa'i zhes pa rkyen
NK060(i)001:4594: gyis 'khrul pa'i snang ba las don du bden par
NK060(i)001:4595: ma grub kyang phyi yul du 'dogs pa ni kun
NK060(i)001:4596: brtags dang / gzhan dbang yin pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:4597: yongs grub bdag med rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis yul
NK060(i)001:4598: dang shes pa tha dad du ma skyes par shes
NK060(i)001:4599: nas/ zhi ba phyogs gcig pa las/
NK060(i)001:4600: nges par 'byung ba byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa la/
NK060(i)001:4602: rnam par rtog pa chos nyid du sbyong ba'i thabs dang /
NK060(i)001:4603: yang 'bangs pho de rnams kyi nang nas/
NK060(i)001:4605: dung shing 'dul ba la sman gyis 'dul sbyong 'di tsam byed ci dgos/
NK060(i)001:4606: 'di bzhin byed pa yin mod zer nas phyag rgya cig bcas nas sngags btab pa tsam gyis/
NK060(i)001:4607: sngar gyi sman sbyor byas pa de bas kyang ro nus pa mchog tu gyur pa zhig byung skad/
NK060(i)001:4609: sngags dang phyag rgya dang ting nge 'dzin gyi cho 'phrul gyi sgo nas/
NK060(i)001:4610: nyon mongs pa dang rnam par rtog pa lha'i rang
NK060(i)001:4611: bzhin du dbang sgyur bas dge ba'i las dang sdig
NK060(i)001:4612: pa'i las kyi 'bras bu mtho ris dang ngan song
NK060(i)001:4613: gis mi gos pa kri yog sde gsum gyi theg
NK060(i)001:4614: pa la/ nyon mongs pa lha dang ye shes su bsgyur ba'i thabs dang /
NK060(i)001:4615: yang rma bya zhig byung nas dug gi sdong po
NK060(i)001:4616: mthong ba la shin tu dga' ba'i sems kyis gang
NK060(i)001:4617: la'ang ltos med du zos pas/
NK060(i)001:4618: lang tsho rgyas shing spu sdug mdangs dang ldan par gyur lo/
NK060(i)001:4620: las dang las kyi 'bras bu bdag nyid chen po'i rol par rtogs nas/
NK060(i)001:4621: nyon mongs pa spyad kyang mi 'ching zhing ye shes
NK060(i)001:4622: lngar gsal bas na gos par mi 'gyur ba sngags
NK060(i)001:4623: nang pa gnyis kyi theg pa la/
NK060(i)001:4624: nyon mongs pa dbang du byed pa'i thabs dang /
NK060(i)001:4625: de ltar dug gi sdong po skyes pa'i dus nyid
NK060(i)001:4626: na ldum ra'i sa gzhi de la dug skyes pa
NK060(i)001:4630: rma byas zos pa la sogs pa gang la yang spang blangs dang /
NK060(i)001:4631: dga' mi dag'i rtog pa med/
NK060(i)001:4632: dug ma skyes kyang dgag bsgrub dang blang dor med pa bzhin du/
NK060(i)001:4633: chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa
NK060(i)001:4634: rang byung gi ye shes rang shar ba la las
NK060(i)001:4635: dang las kyi 'bras bus gos su med pa a
NK060(i)001:4636: ti rang lugs kyi theg pa ste/
NK060(i)001:4637: spang gnyen gyi tha snyad las 'das pa ni ston
NK060(i)001:4638: pa drug pa'i thugs kyi dgongs pa'i mthar thug go
NK060(i)001:4639: // 'o na ston pa drug pa'i thugs dgongs mthar thug pa a ti yin par 'dug pa la/
NK060(i)001:4640: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud 'di nyid kyi byin gyis rlabs las byung bar bshad pa 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4641: spyir gyi bskyed rdzogs gsum dgos ched kyi dbang gis khyad par yod pa ltar bstan kyang /
NK060(i)001:4642: ston pa drug pa'i dgongs pa'i mthar thug tu gcig la/
NK060(i)001:4643: de dag gi spyi rgyud gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa 'di yin te/
NK060(i)001:4645: lung gi spyi 'di shin tu zab pa'i phyir //
NK060(i)001:4648: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK060(i)001:4651: bla ma gong ma rnams ni 'di'i dper/
NK060(i)001:4652: mnga' bdag rtse sde la 'bangs kyis nor 'gran pa'i gleng gzhi gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:4653: spyi don gnyis pa yongs su shes par bya ba'i lta ba la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:4655: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:4657: bstan pa 'byung ba'i rgyu rkyen bstan pa la de/
NK060(i)001:4658: yongs su shes pa'i lta ba ston pas na nas/
NK060(i)001:4659: de bzhin gshegs pa rigs thams cad kyi bdag po
NK060(i)001:4660: kun tu bzang pos go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched
NK060(i)001:4661: du 'og nas 'byung ba'i don 'di rnams tshig tu
NK060(i)001:4662: brjod pa dang 'dra bar go bar byed pa 'di
NK060(i)001:4663: brjod do // lta ba gtan la dbab pa dngos so //
NK060(i)001:4665: 'khor ba gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4666: mya ngan las 'das pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:4669: brtags zhi 'khor ba'i chos bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:4671: lhan skyes kyi ma rig pas rang ngo rang gis
NK060(i)001:4672: ma shes pa ni 'khor ba 'khrul pa'i rgyu yin
NK060(i)001:4673: no // kun brtags kyi ma rig pas gang zag dang chos kyi bdag tu rtogs pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:4674: phyi gzung ba'i yul dang nang 'dzin pa'i shes pa
NK060(i)001:4675: gnyis snang gi rkyen gyis nyon mongs pa skye zhing
NK060(i)001:4676: / des las gsog pa ni 'khor ba 'khrul pa'i rkyen yin no //
NK060(i)001:4677: las kyi dbang gis 'khor bar 'khyams pa ji snyed/
