NK060(i)001:4678: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten mtha' yas pa la gnas
NK060(i)001:4679: pa'i sems can blo 'khrul pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK060(i)001:4681: 'khor ba 'khrul pa'i ngo bo yin no //
NK060(i)001:4682: 'o na sems can de dag ji ltar 'khor zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4683: phyi rten 'brel bcu gnyis mang nyung gi tshul du 'khor te/
NK060(i)001:4684: dpe shing gi sdong po lta bu la sbyar na/
NK060(i)001:4691: 'bras bu rnams snga ma snga mas phyi ma phyi ma bskyed pa lta bu yin la/
NK060(i)001:4692: nyung ba rdo zlum lta bu gcig la sbyar na/
NK060(i)001:4698: 'bras bu thams cad de rang yin pa lta bu'o //
NK060(i)001:4700: 'byung ba lnga dus kyis 'gyur dang drug go //
NK060(i)001:4701: nang rten 'brel bcu gnyis lus med rnams la bag chags dang /
NK060(i)001:4702: lus can rnams la dngos su 'khor te/
NK060(i)001:4703: de yang ma rig pa'i rkyen gyis 'du byed/
NK060(i)001:4704: 'du byed rkyen gyis rnam par shes pa/
NK060(i)001:4705: de bzhin du ming dang gzugs/
NK060(i)001:4712: rga shi rnams lugs 'byung zo chu'i khyud mo bzhin 'khor ba ni/
NK060(i)001:4714: 'gro ba nang rigs mi mthun pa so so la rang rang gi gnas skabs kyi bde ba/
NK060(i)001:4715: gla bas gla ba rnyed pa lta bu dang /
NK060(i)001:4716: gzhan yang phyi nang gi sdug bsngal brgyad dam khyad
NK060(i)001:4717: par du ngan song gsum la sdug bsngal gyi sdug
NK060(i)001:4718: bsngal mdze la tsh+wa chu bskus pa lta bu ste
NK060(i)001:4719: bcu gcig myong bar 'gyur pa ni 'khor ba 'khrul
NK060(i)001:4723: bde ba nyes par ci 'gro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4725: sangs rgyas kyi bde ba la ltos na/
NK060(i)001:4726: sems can gyi bde ba ji ltar phun sum tshogs kyang sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin las ma 'das te/
NK060(i)001:4727: gla bas gla pa rnyed pa lta bu yin gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:4728: gtsang pa byi ston na re/
NK060(i)001:4729: la la'i bde ba la la'i sdug bsngal du 'gyur te/
NK060(i)001:4730: do bos mi thong po gsod pa lta bu yin gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:4731: de ltar brtag gzhi 'khor ba'i chos de dag gi
NK060(i)001:4732: rang bzhin ni sems nyid sku dang ye shes kyi
NK060(i)001:4733: dkyil 'khor las nyams pa med de/
NK060(i)001:4735: tho yor la mi ru snang yang tho yor las ma g.yos pa bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:4737: 'khor ba la thog mtha' yod med kyi brgal lan ni/
NK060(i)001:4739: 'khor ba la thog mtha' med do zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4740: lam nyams su blangs pa la dgos pa med par thal/
NK060(i)001:4743: 'dod na 'di nyid kyi bcu gsum pa las/
NK060(i)001:4744: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK060(i)001:4745: rang 'byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK060(i)001:4748: thog mtha' yod do zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4750: dong sprugs pa srid par thal/
NK060(i)001:4755: 'khor ba thog mtha' med pa'i khyabs su zhes gsungs pas gsal lo //
NK060(i)001:4756: spyi btsan du thog mtha' med la/
NK060(i)001:4757: bye brag lam nyams su len pa la mtha' ma yod do zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4758: rigs kyi spyis bye brag la ma khyab par thal/
NK060(i)001:4762: khyab pa med na 'khor ba dong sprug par thal/
NK060(i)001:4763: spyis bye brag la khyab la/
NK060(i)001:4764: bye brag lam nyams su len pa la mtha' 'dug pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:4766: spyi mdo'i lung gis gsal lo //
NK060(i)001:4767: de la lan cig ltar gdab ce na/
NK060(i)001:4772: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med //
NK060(i)001:4775: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin mi dmigs phyir //
NK060(i)001:4777: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pas bsdus pa'i
NK060(i)001:4778: chos gnyis de nyid dang gzhan du brjod du med
NK060(i)001:4779: pa'i phyir/ blo'i yul las 'das pa ste thog mtha'
NK060(i)001:4780: yod med kyi tha snyad las grol ba yin no
NK060(i)001:4781: pa'i phyir/ // 'on kyang lan gyi dbang du byas nas/
NK060(i)001:4782: 'gal na 'gog /mtshungs na bsgre bya ba yin pas/
NK060(i)001:4783: 'byung chen ltos kyi nam mkha' la mtha' dbus yod dam med byas pas/
NK060(i)001:4784: kho na re yod zer na/
NK060(i)001:4785: 'khor ba la yang thog mtha'i thob bya med pa'i lung gis gsal zer na/
NK060(i)001:4786: nam mkha' la yang mtha' dbus med par lung rig tshad mas gsal bya'o //
NK060(i)001:4789: 'khor ba la yang thog mtha' med byas pas/
NK060(i)001:4791: lam nyams su blangs pa don med du thal zer na/
NK060(i)001:4792: bu ga'i nam mkha' bkag kyang mi khegs par thal zhes 'go mtshungs basgre'o //
NK060(i)001:4793: gtan tshig bden pa gsum gyis gtan la dbab pa/
NK060(i)001:4795: yang dag don dam pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4796: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i bden pa zhes mdo sde pa
NK060(i)001:4797: dang tshul mthun par bden pa gnyis su phye na
NK060(i)001:4798: bdag tu rig pa'i ngar 'dzin pa rnam par shes
NK060(i)001:4800: bdag gi myong ba'i phung po lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:4801: gzhan 'byung ba yul ltar du snang ba 'di dag chos can/
NK060(i)001:4802: don dam bden ngor bdag gsum po de grub pa med de/
NK060(i)001:4803: sems nyid ye nas skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong dang bral ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:4804: des nas don dam pa spros bral tsam du mnyam la/
NK060(i)001:4805: kun rdzob bden ngor bdag gsum po des bslu ba med de/
NK060(i)001:4806: skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong ltar snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:4807: des na kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du mnyam mo //
NK060(i)001:4808: de ltar mnyam pa gnyis ni theg pa thun mong gi mnyam pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:4809: de las lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis ni yang dag
NK060(i)001:4810: don dam gyis gtan la phab na don dam gsum
NK060(i)001:4811: ste/ bdag ma rig pa'i ngar 'dzin pa rnam shes tshogs brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:4812: bdag gi myong ba'i phung po lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:4813: gzhan 'byung ba yul ltar snang ba 'di dag ye shes lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:4815: rigs kyi yum lnga'i rang bzhin las/
NK060(i)001:4816: ma g.yos pa ni go rim bzhin ye shes don dam/
NK060(i)001:4818: rang bzhin du don dam zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:4819: dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis grub par mnyam la/
NK060(i)001:4820: kun rdzob sgyu mas gtan la phab na sgyu ma rnam pa gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:4821: bdag ma rig pa'i ngar 'dzin pa rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:4822: bdag gi myong ba'i phung po lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:4823: gzhan 'byung ba yul ltar du snang ba 'di dag
NK060(i)001:4824: ye shes lnga dang rigs lnga dang rigs kyi yul
NK060(i)001:4825: lnga kar dag pa thugs su chud pa ni go
NK060(i)001:4826: rim bzhin ye shes sgyu ma/
NK060(i)001:4828: dngos po sgyu ma zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:4829: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du ye nas rdzogs par mnyam mo //
NK060(i)001:4830: de'i phyir bden pa gnyis kyang mthar rnam par dag
NK060(i)001:4831: pa mnyam pa'i dbyings nyid du tha mi dad pas
NK060(i)001:4832: na/ dbyer med kyi ngang du tshul gcig pa ni
NK060(i)001:4833: thun mong ma yin pa'i theg pa 'di'i dgongs pa'i
NK060(i)001:4834: na/ mthar thug go // grub mtha' rtogs pa bzhi
NK060(i)001:4835: dang dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs kyis 'bras bu
NK060(i)001:4836: rdo rje'i theg pa gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK060(i)001:4838: bdag ma rig pa'i ngar 'dzin pa rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:4839: bdag gi myong ba'i phung po lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:4840: gzhan 'byung ba yul ltar du snang ba 'di dag rnams ni chos can/
NK060(i)001:4841: ma rig pa'i dbang gis log par rtog pa'i ngo bo tsam nyid du snang ba las/
NK060(i)001:4842: nyan thos kyi 'dod pa ltar yul phra ba ste rdul phran dang /
NK060(i)001:4843: rang rgyal gyi 'dod pa ltar shes pa zab pa ste skad cig ma'ang yod pa ma yin no //
NK060(i)001:4844: 'o na gzung 'dzin 'di gang nas byung zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4845: log rtog snga ma nyid la phyi ma nyid long
NK060(i)001:4846: brtags nas spyod pa ste de ltar spyod kyang sems
NK060(i)001:4847: nyid las gzhan du g.yo ba bdag gsum dang chos
NK060(i)001:4848: gsum ris su gyur pa ci yang med do //
NK060(i)001:4849: 'o na gzhi log rtog gi dbang du song ngam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4850: log rtog gi sgyu ma rig pa 'bras bu phung
NK060(i)001:4851: po rgyun zhen pa nyid kyang phyi mo nas brten
NK060(i)001:4852: pa'i gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba gnyis med de/
NK060(i)001:4853: 'khor 'das gnyis ka mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings rdul
NK060(i)001:4854: dang skad cig ma las 'das pa'i phyir rgyu gcig
NK060(i)001:4856: log rtog gi rgyun rnam par dag pa skye ba med pa'i dbyings nyid chos can/
NK060(i)001:4857: yig 'bru'i tshul du ma 'gags par snang ba yin te/
NK060(i)001:4858: sems nyid ma skyes pa mtshon pa'i yig 'bru a
NK060(i)001:4859: nyid la snang spyod ye shes su dbang sgyur ba
NK060(i)001:4860: mtshon pa o nyid/ zung 'jug mtha' bral mtshon pa na thas brgyan bas ste/
NK060(i)001:4861: gsung dang sku dang thugs kyi ye shes su spyod
NK060(i)001:4862: pa'i phyir na yig 'bru'i tshul gyi gtan tshigs so
NK060(i)001:4864: mngon sum pa gnyis ni 'og nas/
NK060(i)001:4865: rnam dag bla med theg pa'i mchog /ces pa la ngon 'dzin gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:4866: rgyas par le'u bcu gcig pa'i skabs su 'chad par byed do //
NK060(i)001:4867: dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs ni bdag dang zhes pa ni myong ba'i phung po lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:4868: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su rnam par dag /gzhan dang
NK060(i)001:4869: zhes pa ni 'byung ba yul ltar du snang ba
NK060(i)001:4870: lnga ste/ rigs kyi yum lngar rnam par dag /rtog
NK060(i)001:4871: pa'i rgyun zhes pa ni ngar 'dzin pa rnam shes
NK060(i)001:4872: lnga ste/ tshogs brgyad de/ ye shes lngar rnam par
NK060(i)001:4873: dag pa'i phyir bla na med pa theg pa'i mchog
NK060(i)001:4874: lnga ste/ tshogs brgyad de/ ste/ gzhan mtshan nyid dang
NK060(i)001:4875: phyi rgyud las khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir ro
NK060(i)001:4876: lnga ste/ tshogs brgyad de/ ste/ // 'o na ji
NK060(i)001:4877: snyed 'jig rten zhes pa dang gcig /bdag dang bdag
NK060(i)001:4878: lnga ste/ tshogs brgyad de/ ste/ // gi gzhan med // zhes pa dang gnyis/
NK060(i)001:4879: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan rnams ni //
NK060(i)001:4881: log rtog nyid la nyid spyod de //
NK060(i)001:4883: log rtog rgyu 'bras rgyun nyid kyang //
NK060(i)001:4885: bdag dang gzhan dang rtog pa'i rgyun //
NK060(i)001:4886: zhes pa dang drug po 'di ldabs so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4888: dang po ni gzhal bya spyi'i ngos nas bzhag go //
NK060(i)001:4889: gnyis pa ni gtan tshigs bden pa gsum dang bstun te gzhal bya bsdus pa'i ngos nas bzhag go //
NK060(i)001:4890: gsum pa ni log rtog gi ngor snang yang ngo bo ma grub pa'i ngos nas so //
NK060(i)001:4891: bzhi pa ni log rtog nyid kyang chos nyid las ma g.yos pa'i cha nas so //
NK060(i)001:4892: lnga pa ni rgyu gcig pa'i cha nas so //
NK060(i)001:4893: drug pa ni yig 'bru'i tshul dang dag pa gsum thun mong gi cha nas bzhag pa'o //
NK060(i)001:4894: yang lha dang mi'i theg pa dang zhes pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4895: ma rig pa'i zhes pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4896: de dag thams cad kyang zhes pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4897: theg pa bzhi zhes pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4898: 'dul ba mdo sde zhes pa dang /
NK060(i)001:4899: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK060(i)001:4901: chos rnams ming du zhes pa bdun po ldabs so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4902: ma ldabs pa'i khyad par sa bcad kyi ming gis shes so //
NK060(i)001:4903: gnyis pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i yon tan la lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:4910: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang bzhi yis nges par 'byung la/
NK060(i)001:4914: byang chub sems dpas mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung
NK060(i)001:4915: pa'i mthar thug gsang sngags kyi theg pa gcig kho
NK060(i)001:4916: na yin la/ de dag gi bsgrub bya yang yin
NK060(i)001:4917: pas na theg pa pa kun gyi 'bras bur gnas
NK060(i)001:4918: na yin la/ shing / 'bras bu la lam du
NK060(i)001:4919: byed pa'i phyir na theg pa kun gyi mchog kyang
NK060(i)001:4920: na yin la/ shing / yin no // de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba/
NK060(i)001:4922: don dam gsum mngon du byas pa'i yang dag pa'i
NK060(i)001:4923: don ji lta bar rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis rab
NK060(i)001:4924: tu brtags na/ dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad rang bzhin med pa yin kyang /
NK060(i)001:4925: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i mthu las sems can
NK060(i)001:4926: gyi bsam pa dang mthun par cir yang 'grub pa'o
NK060(i)001:4927: // sangs rgyas dang chos la 'byung 'jug dang dar rgud med par bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:4929: de bzhin nyid mngon du byas pa'i sangs rgyas rnams ni yongs su mya ngan las yongs mi 'da' la/
NK060(i)001:4930: des gsungs pa'i chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te/
NK060(i)001:4931: de bzhin nyid de ngo bo nyid kyis rtag pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:4932: 'o na ston pa mya ngan las 'da' zhing /
NK060(i)001:4933: bstan pa la dar nub 'ong ba ci snyam na/
NK060(i)001:4934: gdul bya 'dul ba'i don du tshul bstan pa tsam yin te/
NK060(i)001:4935: de yang ma rig pa'i gdul bya smin par mdzad pa'am/
NK060(i)001:4936: rtag tu re ba sun dbyung zhing thabs des 'dul ba'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:4937: sangs rgyas 'jig rten du byung nas mya ngan las 'da' bar byed pa'i tshul ston zhing /
NK060(i)001:4938: bstan pa dar nub kyi tshul kyang ston par mdzad do //
NK060(i)001:4940: khyod ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin te //
NK060(i)001:4947: lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa gtso bor ston pa 'dul ba/
NK060(i)001:4948: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi bslab pa gtso bor ston pa mdo sde/
NK060(i)001:4949: lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa gtso bor ston pa chos mngon par dang /
NK060(i)001:4950: sngags kyi bca' gzhi dam tshig gtso bor ston pa kri ya/
NK060(i)001:4951: kri yog gnyis ka la brten nas bsgrub pa u pa ya dang /
NK060(i)001:4952: ting nge 'dzin gtso bor ston zhing don myur du grub pa yo ga dang /
NK060(i)001:4953: bskyed rim gtso bor ston pa sku'i rgyud ma h+aa dang /
NK060(i)001:4954: rdzogs rim gtso bor ston pa gsung gi rgyud a nu dang /
NK060(i)001:4955: bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug tu ston pa thugs kyi rgyud a ti yo ga ste/
NK060(i)001:4956: theg pa dgu la sogs pa phyogs bcu kun tu
NK060(i)001:4957: rab tu grags pa thams cad rang bzhin gsang ba'i
NK060(i)001:4959: de phyir rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di ni
NK060(i)001:4960: sde snod gsum po kun dang rgyud drug po kun
NK060(i)001:4962: de dag gtan la'ang rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di nyid kyis nges par 'bebs par byed do //
NK060(i)001:4963: 'o na bstan pa dang theg pa de dag yang dag par yod dam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4964: gdul bya'i ngo la bstan pa tsam las yang dag
NK060(i)001:4965: par na 'chad par 'gyur ba'i chos rnams ming du
NK060(i)001:4966: btags pa tsam/ zhes pa la sogs pa go bar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:4967: gdul bya dang mthun par gsungs pa las yang dag par na gsung du med par bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:4969: chos rnams rang gi ngo bos stongs pa'i phyir ming du btags pa tsam mo //
NK060(i)001:4970: de la dgos ched ci yod ce na/
NK060(i)001:4971: lha mi'i ston pa thub pa'i dbang pos don bden
NK060(i)001:4972: pa gnyis dbang btsan du byas nas gnas skabs kyi
NK060(i)001:4973: chos nyid dang mthar thug gi chos nyid gnyis ka
NK060(i)001:4975: gdul bya so so'i blo dang yang mthun par bya ba'i dgos ched yod do //
NK060(i)001:4976: 'o na de gdul bya'i blo dang mthun phyogs su ji ltar bstan zhe na/
NK060(i)001:4977: ming dang tshig tu btags nas so //
NK060(i)001:4978: de gang gis na ston pa sprul pa'i sku des so //
NK060(i)001:4979: de ltar bstan kyang ston pa byed pa'i mkhan po
NK060(i)001:4980: dang des bstan pa'i ming tshig la dngos po'am mtshan
NK060(i)001:4982: de dag sgro btags pa yin pa'i phyir ro zhes brjod do //
NK060(i)001:4983: gzhung bsdus te bstan pa la bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:4985: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:4987: gzhung rgyas par bstan pa la/
NK060(i)001:4988: de bsdus te bstan pas na nas/
NK060(i)001:4989: de bzhin gshegs pa yab yum thabs shes rab gnyis
NK060(i)001:4990: su med pa'i dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyis nyams
NK060(i)001:4991: su myong dka' ba'i don gyis na gsang ba 'di
NK060(i)001:4992: nyid sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon tan phrin
NK060(i)001:4993: las rdo rje las 'og nas 'byung ba'i bsdus pa'i
NK060(i)001:4997: 'di la gzhung rgyas pa dang sbyar te bsdu ba dang /
NK060(i)001:4998: 'grel pa spar khab ltar lam cig car ba ltar du bsdus ba gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:5000: bsdu ba'i stod du le'u'i smad bsdu ba dang /
NK060(i)001:5001: bsdus ba'i smad du le'u'i stod bsdu ba gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:5002: de yang a hohzhesa pa ni/
NK060(i)001:5003: dngos po gnyis gtan tshig gsum gyis ngo bo gcig par grub pa la mnyes pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5004: srid pa gsum gyi rtsa ba'i nyes dmigs rgyu lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa ste/
NK060(i)001:5008: ya ki'i gzhung rgyas pa'i skabs na 'khor ba 'khrul pa'i rgyu ma rig pa ces pa de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5009: de ltar sdus pa'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan brtags la bshad pa ni/
NK060(i)001:5010: le'u dang po'i bsdu ba'i skabs ltar 'dir yang shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:5011: gang zag dang chos kyi bdag tu rtog pa de
NK060(i)001:5012: las 'phros pa rkyen kun brtags kyi ma rig pa
NK060(i)001:5015: ya ki na rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin zhes pa de sdus/
NK060(i)001:5016: 'gro ba rgyud drug srog skye 'gag dang lus bzang
NK060(i)001:5017: ngan dang longs spyod che chung dang gnas mtho ba
NK060(i)001:5018: dang dma' ba ru snang ba/
NK060(i)001:5020: gang na 'khor ba 'khrul pa'i ngo bo/
NK060(i)001:5021: ya ki na ji snyed 'jig rten 'khrul pa'i chos zhes pa de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5022: sdug bsngal brgyad dam bcu gcig tu snang ba ste/
NK060(i)001:5024: gang na 'khor ba 'khrul pa'i nyes pa/
NK060(i)001:5025: ya ki na mi mthun bde sdug myong bar 'gyur zhes pa de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5026: phyi nang gi rten cing 'brel la 'khrul 'khor la sogs pa'i tshul du snang ba/
NK060(i)001:5029: ya ki na phyi nang rten 'brel gnyis su 'khor zhes pa de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5030: log par rtog pa'i ngo bo nyid snang ba tsam
NK060(i)001:5031: las gzhan du chos nyid kyi don las ci'ang g.yos
NK060(i)001:5032: pa med pa/ gang du na 'dir/
NK060(i)001:5034: ya ki na rang bzhin nyid las mnyam pa med pa ces pa de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5035: gtan tshigs kyi sgo nas stong pa nyid kyi don bdag med par rtogs pa/
NK060(i)001:5039: dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs kyi don/
NK060(i)001:5040: ya ki na yang dag sgyu ma'i zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5041: theg pa'i mchog ces pa'i bar de rnams sdud/
NK060(i)001:5042: mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings ye nas mkhyen pa rang rig pa'i ye shes su gsal ba'i thugs te/
NK060(i)001:5044: gang na de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba dang sangs
NK060(i)001:5045: rgyas dang chos la 'byung 'jug dang dar rgud med
NK060(i)001:5046: par bstan pa/ ya ki na yang dag rtogs pas zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5047: 'da' bar ston zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5048: dmigs byed gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa ngang gis med pa dran snang ye shes su dbang sgyur ba/
NK060(i)001:5050: gang na theg pa'i khyad par dang /
NK060(i)001:5052: ya ki na theg pa bzhi zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5053: 'bras bur gnas zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK060(i)001:5055: nges par 'bebs zhes pa'i bar sa dmigs gnyis po de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5056: dmigs bya ye shes la ye shes spyod pa/
NK060(i)001:5058: gang na gdul bya dang mthun par gsungs pa la/
NK060(i)001:5059: yang dag par na gsung du med pa/
NK060(i)001:5060: ya ki na chos rnams ming zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5061: ces brjod do zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5062: bsdu ba'i smad du le'u'i stod bsdu ba ni/
NK060(i)001:5063: yon tan lhun gyis grub pa la ngo mtshar ba'i mdzad pa thub pa drug spro ba/
NK060(i)001:5066: ya ki na de nas zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5068: yongs su shes par bya ba lta ba'i gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa de nas zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5069: 'di brjod do zhes pa'i bar sa dmigs gnyis po de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5070: sku mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi don mdzad pa/
NK060(i)001:5073: ya ki na bltams pa dang zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5074: ston pa'i thub pas zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5075: gsung bstan pa dang theg pas don mdzad/
NK060(i)001:5077: gang na gsung gi mdzad pa/
NK060(i)001:5078: ya ki na thams cad kyang zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5079: mthar thug go zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5080: yon tan mngon shes su shar nas don mdzad pa/
NK060(i)001:5082: gang na thugs kyi mdzad pa/
NK060(i)001:5083: ya ki na dus bzhi zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5084: drug dang zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5085: zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab par snang ba/
NK060(i)001:5087: gang na gleng gzhi'i ngo bo spyir bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:5088: ya ki na 'thon nas kyang zhes pas nas/
NK060(i)001:5089: don mdzad de zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5090: gong gi mdzad pa de dag las 'bras bu bsam gyis mi khyab pa/
NK060(i)001:5092: gang na bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdzad pa/
NK060(i)001:5093: ya ki na kun tu zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5094: snang bar gyur to zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5096: gang du bsdu na bsdu ba'i gzhung 'di dag tu/
NK060(i)001:5097: gang bsdu na gzhung rgyas pa'i don rnams sdud de/
NK060(i)001:5098: sdud pa'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan ni gnas skabs rang
NK060(i)001:5099: rang tshig gi don mthun par 'dug pa'i don gyis
NK060(i)001:5101: de'i phyir bsdu ba'i don 'di las gzhan na brjod bya dang rjod byed med de/
NK060(i)001:5102: rang rig pa'i ye shes de nyid gdul bya'i snang
NK060(i)001:5103: ba la gong du brjod pa de ltar du snang
NK060(i)001:5104: ba yin pas snang ba gnyis las ma 'das pa'o
NK060(i)001:5105: // yang bshad lugs gnyis pa cig car ba ltar du bshad na/
NK060(i)001:5107: gzhan du g.yo ba ci yang med ces pa'i bar gyi tshig bzhi po gzhal bya'o //
NK060(i)001:5108: chos thams cad stong nyid bdag med par gtan la 'bebs pa gtan tshigs so //
NK060(i)001:5109: ye nas gnas pa'i don mkhyen te/
NK060(i)001:5110: rang rig pa'i thugs rang gsal bar rtogs pa grub mtha' ste de dag ni lta ba'o //
NK060(i)001:5111: dmigs bya dmigs byed med par gnas pa ni sgom pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5112: dran snang ye shes su dbang sgyur ba ni spyod pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5113: de ltar lta sgom spyod gsum gyis ngo mtshar ba'i
NK060(i)001:5114: sku gsung thugs yon tan dang zhing khams dang phrin
NK060(i)001:5115: las lhun gyis grub pa de mngon du snang ba
NK060(i)001:5116: ni 'bras bu'o // gzhan na med de rang rig
NK060(i)001:5117: de nyid sku dang ye shes su shar ba de
NK060(i)001:5118: dag rgyal ba kun tu bzang po'i thugs rig kyang
NK060(i)001:5120: zhes snang ba gnyis las ma 'das te/
NK060(i)001:5121: mngon du byas pa bde gshegs kyi snang ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:5122: de lta bu'i mdzad pa ni gdul bya'i snang ba yin no //
NK060(i)001:5123: bka' gsang sngags mtshon pa'i tshig /drang /
NK060(i)001:5124: zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o zhes pa'i 'bru le'u dang po'i bsdu bar bshad zin to //
NK060(i)001:5125: gzhung bsdus pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:5127: zhes gzhung bsdus pa'i de dag tshig tu brjod pas/
NK060(i)001:5128: thub pa drug gi sprul pa grangs med pa dang /
NK060(i)001:5129: de bzhin gshegs pa sku lnga po thams cad kyis
NK060(i)001:5130: gsungs pa yang bsdu ba'i tshig de dag tu 'dus
NK060(i)001:5131: par de bzhin gshegs pa drug pa kun tu bzang
NK060(i)001:5135: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las zhes pa 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:5136: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pas bsdus pa'i
NK060(i)001:5137: chos thams cad gtan tshigs gsum gyis gtan la phab
NK060(i)001:5138: pa'i gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pa'i don gyis na le'u
NK060(i)001:5139: ste yas bgrangs gsum pa'i don du gada'o////da ni le'u
NK060(i)001:5140: bzhi pa'i chos tshoms ngos gzung ba'i dbang du byas
NK060(i)001:5141: na/ rab kyis chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las/
NK060(i)001:5142: yi ge la brten nas lam nyams su len pas lam ston/
NK060(i)001:5144: rang bzhin dang 'bras bu'i snang ba zur tsam ston/
NK060(i)001:5146: thabs grol gnyis las gnyis ka /mtshan nyid gsum las/
NK060(i)001:5154: bcu yang brgya'i bdag nyid du byas na/
NK060(i)001:5155: ting nge 'dzin gyi shugs la lta ba zur tsam dang spyod pa dang dkyil 'khor ston no //
NK060(i)001:5156: tha ma'i chos tshoms bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu las/
NK060(i)001:5162: de ltar ston par byed pa'i le'u bzhi pa 'di la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:5163: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:5168: lta ba gtan la phab pa bstan pa la/
NK060(i)001:5169: de yi ge'i don nyams su len pa ston pa na nas/
NK060(i)001:5170: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad du drug pa kun
NK060(i)001:5171: tu bzang po'i dgongs pa gcig dang du ma'i mtha'
NK060(i)001:5172: dang bral ba de nyid gsung lnga lhun gyis grub
NK060(i)001:5173: pa las mi g.yo bas na/
NK060(i)001:5174: dgongs pa gcig tu gyur nas snang stong gnyis med
NK060(i)001:5175: du mnyam pa'i de'i gong na gzhan med pas na
NK060(i)001:5176: chen po'i tshul te/ de nyid kyi ngo bo la 'khor 'das gnyis mi phyed pas na rdo rje'o //
NK060(i)001:5177: sems nyid ma skyes pa'i dbyings su 'khor 'das kyi
NK060(i)001:5178: chos thams cad ye gdod ma nas sku dang ye
NK060(i)001:5179: shes su gsal ba ni drug pa'i ngo bor sangs
NK060(i)001:5180: rgyas pas na/ bsgom bya sgom byed gnyis su med
NK060(i)001:5181: pa'i ting nge 'dzin las mi g.yo bar dngos po'i
NK060(i)001:5182: chos thams cad ngo bo nyid med pa'i phyir ming
NK060(i)001:5183: tsam du gnas pa'i yi ge'i rgyun gsung gi phreng
NK060(i)001:5184: ba'i 'khor lo zhes bya ba 'og nas 'byung ba
NK060(i)001:5185: 'di ni ston pa drug pa yab yum sku dang
NK060(i)001:5186: gsung dang thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las
NK060(i)001:5187: rgyas pas na/ phyung ngo // le'u'i gzhung don la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:5191: yi ge ji ltar byung ba'i tshul lam khungs/
NK060(i)001:5193: lam pa'i dbang du sems sbyang ba/
NK060(i)001:5197: lha dang yi ger sbyar ba ni 'og nas 'chad la/
NK060(i)001:5198: yi ge'i khungs kyi dbang du byas na a ni khong pa nas byung ste/
NK060(i)001:5200: a ni yig 'bru kun gyi mchog /don chen yi ge dam pa ste //
NK060(i)001:5201: khong nas 'byung ba skye ba med //
NK060(i)001:5203: a'i 'od zer gre phugs su 'phros pa las/
NK060(i)001:5204: ka kha ga g+ha nga lnga byung ste/
NK060(i)001:5206: ka la sogs pa dang po lnga //
NK060(i)001:5207: mgur gyi gsang ba'i rang bzhin yin //
NK060(i)001:5208: a yi 'od zer lce sked las 'phros pas //
NK060(i)001:5209: tsa tsha dza dz+ha nya lnga ste //
NK060(i)001:5210: gnyis pa tsa la sogs pa lnga //
NK060(i)001:5211: zla gam ljags kyi rang bzhin yin //
NK060(i)001:5212: a yi 'od zer lce rtse las 'phros pas //
NK060(i)001:5214: ta tha da d+ha na bcu ste //
NK060(i)001:5215: gsum pa ta la sogs pa bcu //
NK060(i)001:5216: ljags kyi rtse mo'i rang bzhin yin //
NK060(i)001:5217: a yi 'od zer mchu la 'phros pas/
NK060(i)001:5218: pa pha ba b+ha ma lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:5219: bzhi pa pa la sogs pa lnga //
NK060(i)001:5220: zhal gyi sgros las byung bar bshad //
NK060(i)001:5221: a yi 'od zer lus spyi la 'phros pas //
NK060(i)001:5222: ya wa ra la sogs bcu bdun te //
NK060(i)001:5223: lnga pa la ya la sogs pa ni //
NK060(i)001:5224: bcu tshan gnyis kyi yi ge dag /sku las 'phros pa rab tu bshad //
NK060(i)001:5225: de yang ya byin pa las 'phros ste/
NK060(i)001:5226: skyes bu chen po'i byin pa las //
NK060(i)001:5229: skyes bu chen po'i dku skabs las //
NK060(i)001:5230: gti mug gsal ba'i yig 'bru wa //
NK060(i)001:5232: skyes bu chen po'i sta zur las //
NK060(i)001:5235: skyes bu chen po'i dpung pa las //
NK060(i)001:5239: cho 'phrul ston pa'i yig 'bru sha /sha thugs ka las/
NK060(i)001:5240: thugs kar 'khyil ba'i dpal be'u las //
NK060(i)001:5241: mtshan ma dag pa'i yig 'bru sha //
NK060(i)001:5243: sku yi khru tshad lte ba las //
NK060(i)001:5247: sgrib pa sel ba'i yig 'bru ha //
NK060(i)001:5249: gsang ba mkha' yi 'od zer las //
NK060(i)001:5252: skyes bu chen po'i spyan gnyis las //
NK060(i)001:5253: rin cen yi ge i gnyis shar //
NK060(i)001:5255: skyes bu chen po'i snyan gnyis las //
NK060(i)001:5256: rin cen yig 'bru u gnyis shar //
NK060(i)001:5258: skyes bu chen po'i shangs gnyis las //
NK060(i)001:5259: rin cen yig 'bru e gnyis shar //
NK060(i)001:5261: skyes bu chen po'i tshems las ni //
NK060(i)001:5262: rang bzhin yi ge o ru shar //
NK060(i)001:5264: skyes bu chen po'i spyi gtsug las //
NK060(i)001:5265: rgyal ba'i sa bon +amo du shar //
NK060(i)001:5267: gnyis pa yi ge byung ba'i mthu/
NK060(i)001:5270: thog mar grol lam ltar bshad na/
NK060(i)001:5271: yi ge 'di dag phyung bas yi ge'i mthus 'jig
NK060(i)001:5272: rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa shar mtho
NK060(i)001:5273: na nub dma' ba la sogs pa rnam pa drug
NK060(i)001:5274: tu g.yos/ tshabs che bas na rab tu g.yos/
NK060(i)001:5275: khyab cing tshabs che bas na kun tu g.yos nas
NK060(i)001:5276: dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ming
NK060(i)001:5277: gi bye brag dang yi ge kho na'i phyir ngo
NK060(i)001:5278: bo nyid bstan du med pa'i mtshan nyid tsam du
NK060(i)001:5279: gyur to // de'i don la hohzhesa pa mnyes pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5280: yang thabs lam ltar bshad na/
NK060(i)001:5281: 'di dag phyung bas lus kyi 'jig rten 'khor lo
NK060(i)001:5282: drug gi gnas dang lus kyi phyogs bcu'i rtsa gnas
NK060(i)001:5283: mtha' yas pa thig le bde ba'i ye shes kyis
NK060(i)001:5284: khyab pas rnam pa drug tu g.yos/
NK060(i)001:5285: tshabs che bas rab tu g.yos/
NK060(i)001:5286: khyab cing tshabs che bas kun tu g.yos nas rtog
NK060(i)001:5287: tshogs dang thig les bsdus pa'i chos thams cad bde
NK060(i)001:5288: ba'i ye shes kyi ming gi mtshan nyid mtshan du
NK060(i)001:5289: gyur to // de la mnyes pas hohzhesa bya'o //
NK060(i)001:5290: gsum pa lam pa'i dbang du sems sbyang ba la yang gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:5292: yi ge a la sems sbyang ba/
NK060(i)001:5296: dkar ba ni byang chub kyi sems so //
NK060(i)001:5298: stong pa nyid kyi ngang la rang gi rig pa'i
NK060(i)001:5299: yi ge a dkar po gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad
NK060(i)001:5300: dang ldan pa cig tu bsgom mo //
NK060(i)001:5301: de yang rab tu brtan pa'i tshad bzhi dang ldan pa ste/
NK060(i)001:5306: cir yang bsgyur du btub pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5307: de ltar rang rig ar snang ba de nyid gzung
NK060(i)001:5308: 'dzin dang bral zhing nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos
NK060(i)001:5309: par dkar ba ste gsal ba'i tshad bzhi dang ldan
NK060(i)001:5315: de las a s+phar na phata ces spros pas/
NK060(i)001:5316: gzhi ma'i a de las shin tu phra ba'i a
NK060(i)001:5317: dpag tu med pa rnams spros pa phyogs bcu thams
NK060(i)001:5318: cad as gang bar gsal bar gyur nas sam ha
NK060(i)001:5319: ra na h+aum zhes bsdus kyang gzhi ma'i a la
NK060(i)001:5320: 'phel ba dang phyogs bcu'i a la 'grib pa med
NK060(i)001:5321: par ting nge 'dzin brtan pa'i tshad ni gsal ba
NK060(i)001:5323: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la sems sbyang ba/
NK060(i)001:5325: a de las ka la sogs pa'i yi ge'i ming
NK060(i)001:5326: gi tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kha dog gsal zhing
NK060(i)001:5327: 'od zer 'bar ba kun kyang s+phar na phata kyis
NK060(i)001:5328: spros zhing / sam ha ra na h+aum gis bsdu
NK060(i)001:5329: ba'ang sngar yi ge a la sems sbyangs pa de
NK060(i)001:5330: spros zhing / bzhin no // de rdo rje dngos grub kyi rgyur bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5331: drang yi ge la sems sbyang ba 'di ni sku
NK060(i)001:5332: dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje'i dngos grub lhun gyis
NK060(i)001:5333: grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin brtan par 'byung bas na/
NK060(i)001:5334: rang rig pa'i ye shes dngos su skye bar byed pa'i rgyud yin no //
NK060(i)001:5336: ye shes brtan par 'byung ba 'di ni rdo rje dngos grub kyi rgyu yin no zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:5337: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu 'bras so //
NK060(i)001:5338: bzhi pa yi ge'i don bshad pa la gnyis/
NK060(i)001:5340: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:5342: sems sbyang ba bstan nas yi ge'i don bshad pa ston pas na de nas zhes 'brel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:5343: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag po drug pa kun tu bzang pos/
NK060(i)001:5344: ched du brjod pa 'og nas 'byung ba'i yi ge'i don bshad pa 'di dag brjod do //
NK060(i)001:5345: yi ge'i don bshad pa dngos so //
NK060(i)001:5346: de la spyi don gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:5350: yi ge sku gsum du sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK060(i)001:5351: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin du bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:5352: yi ge dngos por mi dmigs kyang sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub 'gugs par bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:5355: yi ge sku gsum du sangs rgyas pa dngos dang /
NK060(i)001:5356: yon tan gyi mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK060(i)001:5359: yi ge chos skur sangs rgyas pa/
NK060(i)001:5361: yi ge a de ni mdo sde pa ltar du
NK060(i)001:5362: stong pa don dam dang mi stong pa kun rdzob
NK060(i)001:5363: kyi mtha' gnyis su bral ba'i phyir dbu ma'ang dmigs
NK060(i)001:5364: su yod pa ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:5365: mtha' gsum las 'das pa ni chos kyi sku'o //
NK060(i)001:5366: a'i sgras bsdus ba'i sgra dbyangs kyi yi ge thams cad ming du btags pa tsam las/
NK060(i)001:5367: don snang stong gnyis su med pas na sangs rgyas
NK060(i)001:5368: kun gyi rang bzhin yi ge phreng ba chos kyi
NK060(i)001:5372: yi ge a nyid sna tshogs par snang ba'i tshul gang zhe na/
NK060(i)001:5373: ka la sogs pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su snang la/
NK060(i)001:5374: de'i sgra dang yi ge dang ming tshig gis 'khor
NK060(i)001:5375: 'das kyi chos thams cad bsdus shing de dag kyang
NK060(i)001:5376: zag pa med pa'i bde ba'i ye shes su mnga'
NK060(i)001:5377: mdzad pas na mngon rdzogs rgyal po ste yi ge
NK060(i)001:5379: yang 'di la thabs lam ltar bshad na/
NK060(i)001:5380: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo ni thig le a thung gi dbyibs su gnas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5381: de nyid kyi rtsa la thig le sna tshogs par snang te/
NK060(i)001:5382: thig le'i dbyibs ka kha la sogs pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su snang la/
NK060(i)001:5383: de'i sgra yis thig le thams cad bsdus nas/
NK060(i)001:5384: thig le dang rtog tshogs bde ba'i ye shes su mnga' mdzad pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:5385: mngon rdzogs rgyal por thabs lam gyi ting nge 'dzin de nyid nges so //
NK060(i)001:5386: yi ge sprul sku ru sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5389: yi ge gsung du sangs rgyas pa/
NK060(i)001:5391: e ma'o zhes pa yi ge'i ming la ngam/
NK060(i)001:5392: ngo mtshar zhes pa las la ngam/
NK060(i)001:5393: ya mtshan gyis zhes pa yi ge'i rang bzhin la ngam pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5394: yang na btsun ma mo 'jam dpal 'don pa ltar bshad de/
NK060(i)001:5395: e ma'o zhes pa 'phrul chen yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i ming la ngam/
NK060(i)001:5396: ngo mtshar zhes pa tshig rnams ma lus par 'dzin pa'i gnas la ngam/
NK060(i)001:5397: ya mtshan zhes pa sna tshogs don chen smra zhing ston pa la ngam pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5398: de yang sems nyid yi ger snang ba'i cho 'phrul
NK060(i)001:5399: chen po grangs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi steng du
NK060(i)001:5400: khyab byed thugs gsung sku'i yi ge gsum bsnan pas
NK060(i)001:5401: bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i ming byung la/
NK060(i)001:5403: tshig gis don rnams ma lus par 'dzin pa'i gnas
NK060(i)001:5404: byas nas rnam pa sna tshogs pa'i tshig gis don
NK060(i)001:5405: chen po smra zhing ston par byed pa sprul sku'i
NK060(i)001:5406: gsung yin no // yi ge thugs su/
NK060(i)001:5408: yi ger snang ba de dag kyang dngos po dang mtshan mar grub pa med de/
NK060(i)001:5409: yi ge'i rang bzhin sems nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:5410: sems bde ba chen po la gang zag dang chos kyi bdag gnyis snang ba med cing /
NK060(i)001:5411: de'i phyir dngos po yod med dbu ma'i mtha' gsum
NK060(i)001:5412: dang yang bral zhing de nyid kyang blo'i yul du
NK060(i)001:5413: byar mi dmigs pa ni sprul sku'i thugs so //
NK060(i)001:5414: yi ge sku ru sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5416: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin du snang ba de
NK060(i)001:5417: dag kyang yi ge'i dbyibs dang kha dog dang ming
NK060(i)001:5418: dang tshig gi tshogs kyis rol pa ni phung po/
NK060(i)001:5422: las/ ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa cir yang sprul zhing ston pas na sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK060(i)001:5423: yon tan gyi mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK060(i)001:5425: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i de bzhin gshegs
NK060(i)001:5426: pa'i thugs ye shes sems dpa'i rang bzhin can re
NK060(i)001:5427: re yang sku gsung thugs gsum gsum dang ldan pa'i
NK060(i)001:5428: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i bdag nyid/
NK060(i)001:5429: yi ge'i mgo ber ka ris nas k+shahyana chad la lus kyi yi ge rnams rdzogs la/
NK060(i)001:5430: yan lag gi yi ge i la sogs pa brgyad lus kyi yi ge a la rdzogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5431: gnyis pa sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin du bstan la/
NK060(i)001:5433: sems rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad kyi rang bzhin yi ger gnas pa ste/
NK060(i)001:5434: kun gzhi'i yi ge a'i rang bzhin can gnas sa lte ba na gnas so //
NK060(i)001:5435: de bzhin du yid am gi rang bzhin can mgrin pa/
NK060(i)001:5436: nyon yid h+aum gi rang bzhin can snying ga /sgo
NK060(i)001:5437: lnga ham gi rang bzhin can klad pa na gnas
NK060(i)001:5438: so // yi ge de dag re re'i rtsal du
NK060(i)001:5439: ma snang yang dngos po rdzas grub tu yod pa
NK060(i)001:5441: gsum pa yi ge dngos po mi dmigs kyang sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub 'gugs par bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:5443: yi ge la snang stong gnyis dmigs su med pa
NK060(i)001:5444: de nyid kyang sna tshogs par sku gsung thugs dbyer
NK060(i)001:5445: med kyi ye shes de dkyil 'khor la sogs pa
NK060(i)001:5446: gang du'ang mi 'gag pas na 'khor lo che zhes
NK060(i)001:5447: bya'o // rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid sku gsung
NK060(i)001:5448: thugs su shar ba ni bsam gyis mi khyab pas
NK060(i)001:5449: na ngo mtshar gyi gnas so //
NK060(i)001:5450: de ltar ya mtshan pa yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa
NK060(i)001:5451: lnga'i 'phrul chen pos 'bras bu sku gsung thugs su
NK060(i)001:5452: bcad pa'i sku dang ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK060(i)001:5453: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du rab tu 'gugs pa'o
NK060(i)001:5454: // bzhi pa yi ge'i nges tshig go //
NK060(i)001:5456: mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings la blo mnyam par bzhag pa ni dbyings kyi bris pa ste/
NK060(i)001:5457: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir yi ge zhes ni nges tshig brjod pa'am/
NK060(i)001:5458: ak+sha ra'i sgra las drangs na/
NK060(i)001:5459: ma skyes pa'i chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:5460: yi ge zhes brjod pa ni don gyi mtshan yin no //
NK060(i)001:5461: spyi don gnyis pa yi ge bye brag gi don bshad pa la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:5462: khyab byed yi ge gsum gyi don bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:5463: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi don bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:5464: yi ge'i mjug bsdu'am che ba bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5472: lha dang lnga sbrag tu 'chad de/
NK060(i)001:5473: yi ge na 'go ni ber ka ris sam thig yin te/
NK060(i)001:5474: dpal byin gyis zhus pa'i mdo las/
NK060(i)001:5475: 'go ni thog mar mtshon pa ste //
NK060(i)001:5476: dang la gzugs su gang chags pa //
NK060(i)001:5477: de ni yi ge'i 'go yin phyir //
NK060(i)001:5478: ber ka ris la 'go zhes mtshon //
NK060(i)001:5481: yi ge sbrul lta bus 'go 'dren pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:5484: gzugs can snying pos zhus pa'i mdo las/
NK060(i)001:5485: yi ge 'go ni thig yin pas //
NK060(i)001:5486: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rnams //
NK060(i)001:5487: ma nor dam pa'i thig yin pas //
NK060(i)001:5488: lam mkhan thig nas yi ge zhugs //
NK060(i)001:5490: don ni ma nor ba thabs shes rab gnyis med do //
NK060(i)001:5491: las ni lam yin te yi ge'i 'go 'dren no //
NK060(i)001:5492: rtog pa ni yid du 'dzin pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5493: lha ni thugs kyi lha mi bskyod pa'i lha rang bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:5494: yi ge na tig ni tsheg yin te/
NK060(i)001:5495: rgyal po drag shul can gyis zhus pa'i mdo las/
NK060(i)001:5496: ting ni tsheg tu bsgrub pa ste //
NK060(i)001:5497: yi ge bsdus nas ming du smra //
NK060(i)001:5498: de phyir tsheg ni tig ces bya'o //
NK060(i)001:5500: yo ga rgyan dam pa las/
NK060(i)001:5501: sdud pa'i phyir na tsheg ni tig /'thor ba bsdus nas ming du smra //
NK060(i)001:5503: don ni shes rab rang bzhin med pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5504: las ni ming du smra ba/
NK060(i)001:5505: rtog pa ngag tu 'dzin pa ste gsung gi lha 'od dpag med kyi rang bzhin te/
NK060(i)001:5506: yi ge na shad ni shad yin te/
NK060(i)001:5508: gcod pa mtshon par byed pa'i yi ge la ni/
NK060(i)001:5509: ming dbyug pa zhes bla dwags su btags so //
NK060(i)001:5511: khyim bdag dpal byin gyis zhus pa'i mdo las/
NK060(i)001:5512: tshigs su bcad pa'i las can la //
NK060(i)001:5513: de phyir shad du grags so zhes //
NK060(i)001:5515: don ni thabs snying rje chen po/
NK060(i)001:5516: las ni tshigs su gcod pa/
NK060(i)001:5517: rtog pa lus su 'dzin pa ste sku'i lha rnam par snang mdzad kyi rang bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:5518: gnyis pa yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi don bshad pa la bdun te/
NK060(i)001:5520: kun tu bzang mo dang rigs lnga yab yum bcu'i yi ge bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:5522: 'di na mar bzhi sbrag tu 'chad de/
NK060(i)001:5524: don ni skye ba med pa/
NK060(i)001:5525: rtog pa 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas kyi chos kyi de bzhin nyid ma spangs pa/
NK060(i)001:5526: lha na kun tu bzang mo'o //
NK060(i)001:5528: a yi ge kun gyi 'go bor 'byung ba'ii rgyu mtshan ci yin zhe na/
NK060(i)001:5529: yi ge kun gyi 'byung gnas sam/
NK060(i)001:5531: de yang sgyu 'phrul phyi ma las/
NK060(i)001:5532: a ni stong pa ye nas stong //
NK060(i)001:5533: stong pa nyid na stong pa med //
NK060(i)001:5534: yi ge kun gyi gazhi'am rgyu //
NK060(i)001:5535: yin pa'i phyir na 'go bor bzhag /ces gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:5536: de bzhin du yi ge na tha/
NK060(i)001:5537: don ni sgyu 'phrul te lha yab mtshon pas na thabs kyi cha'o //
NK060(i)001:5538: rtog pa na rnam par shes pa'i phung po/
NK060(i)001:5539: lha rdo rje sems dpa' nyid don //
NK060(i)001:5542: rtog pa na gzugs kyi phung po/
NK060(i)001:5543: lha rnam par snang bar mdzad pa'i sku nyid do //
NK060(i)001:5546: rtog pa na tshor ba'i phung po/
NK060(i)001:5547: lha na yid bzhin te rin chen 'byung ldan nyid do //
NK060(i)001:5551: lha na snang ba rnam par dag pa mtha' yas nyid do //
NK060(i)001:5555: lha don kun tu grub pa nyid do //
NK060(i)001:5556: 'o na spyir gyis sgyu ma mtshon pa lha yum/
NK060(i)001:5558: d+r+wa ba mtshon pa lha yab yum dbyer med yin pa la/
NK060(i)001:5559: 'dir yab la sgyu 'phrul du 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ci yin zhe na/
NK060(i)001:5560: phung po lnga sgyu ma lta bu la rang rig
NK060(i)001:5561: rtogs pa'i thabs kyis ye shes lnga mtshon nas rigs
NK060(i)001:5562: lngar snang ba la 'phrul zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:5563: de yang he ru ka 'dus pa las/
NK060(i)001:5564: rnam par shes pa la sogs pa //
NK060(i)001:5565: phung po lnga nyid dkyil 'khor te //
NK060(i)001:5566: sgyu ma lta bu'i phung po las //
NK060(i)001:5567: rang rig thabs kyis rigs lngar 'phrul //
NK060(i)001:5570: lnga phung sgyu ma'i ye shes la //
NK060(i)001:5571: rang rig thabs kyis rigs lngar 'phrul //
NK060(i)001:5575: chos mtshungs dper byas nas lha yum mtshon pas na shes rab kyi cha'o //
NK060(i)001:5576: de yang mngon rdzogs ni 'byung ba nam mkhar rtog pa/
NK060(i)001:5577: lha nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma nyid do //
NK060(i)001:5579: don ni d+r+wa ba zhes pa 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:5580: brtan pa ni sor rtog pa/
NK060(i)001:5581: lha sangs rgyas spyan nyid do //
NK060(i)001:5583: don ni d+r+wa ba zhes pa 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:5584: lha ma me na mer rtog pa/
NK060(i)001:5585: lha gos dkar mo nyid do //
NK060(i)001:5587: don ni d+r+wa ba zhes pa 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:5588: 'khril ba nyid ni chur rtog pa ste/
NK060(i)001:5589: lha na m+aa ma k+ai nyid do //
NK060(i)001:5591: don ni d+r+wa ba zhes pa 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:5592: kun tu 'gyur ba ni rlung du rtog pa ste/
NK060(i)001:5593: lha dam tshig sgrol ma nyid do //
NK060(i)001:5594: 'o na yum la d+r+wa bar 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan gang yin zhe na/
NK060(i)001:5596: d+r+wa ba ni mdo mdud 'brel pa rdzas kyi dngos
NK060(i)001:5597: po shong zhing sdud pa dang d+r+wa mig zang thal
NK060(i)001:5598: du yod pa dang 'dra ba ste/
NK060(i)001:5599: yum gyi rtsa mdud 'brel ba dang /
NK060(i)001:5600: bde ba shong zhing sdud pa dang mkha' zang thal du yod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:5601: gang nas zhugs kyang gsal bar snang ba dang ldan pas d+r+wa ba zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:5602: de yang rdo rje g.yung drung 'khyil ba'i mdo las/
NK060(i)001:5603: d+r+wa ba cir yang 'gyur ba ste //
NK060(i)001:5604: mdo mdud 'brel zhing zang thal ba //
NK060(i)001:5605: gang nas bltas kyang gsal bar snang //
NK060(i)001:5606: ci yang sdud cing shong ba bzhin //
NK060(i)001:5607: de bzhin yum gyi mkha' dbyings kyang //
NK060(i)001:5608: mdo mdud 'brel cing zang thal ba //
NK060(i)001:5609: gang nas zhugs kyang gsal bar snang //
NK060(i)001:5610: thams cad sdud cing shong ba'i phyir //
NK060(i)001:5611: yum la d+r+wa ba zhes su brjod //
NK060(i)001:5613: nang gi sems dpa' bzhi shar gyi sgo ba dang bcas pa'i/
NK060(i)001:5615: 'di na mar yi ge dang rtog pa dang lha dang gsum sbrag tu 'chad de/
NK060(i)001:5616: yi ge na ka /rtog pa ni spyan gyi thugs te mig gi rnam shes kyi rtog pa/
NK060(i)001:5617: lha mchog byang chub sems dpa' sa'i snying po'o //
NK060(i)001:5618: 'o na rnam par shes pa la thugs su 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na/
NK060(i)001:5621: rig pa kho na'i phyir thugs te/
NK060(i)001:5623: de bzhin du yi ge na kha/
NK060(i)001:5624: rtog pa ni snyan gyi thugs te rna ba'i rnam shes kyi rtog pa/
NK060(i)001:5625: lha mchog phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK060(i)001:5626: yi ge nag /rtog pa ni shangs kyi thugs kyi sna'i rnam shes kyi rtog pa/
NK060(i)001:5627: lha mchog nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK060(i)001:5629: rtog pa ni ljags kyi thugs te lce'i rnam shes kyi rtog pa/
NK060(i)001:5630: lha mchog spyan ras gzigs dang /
NK060(i)001:5632: rtog pa ni thugs kyang 'jigs par byed pa ste
NK060(i)001:5633: gsang ba'i rnam shes kyi khams bde ba nyams su
NK060(i)001:5634: myong ba'i dus na mig la sogs pa'i rnam shes
NK060(i)001:5635: kyi rtog pa mi gnas par byed pa/
NK060(i)001:5637: nang gi sems ma bzhi lho'i sgo ba dang bcas pa'i drang /
NK060(i)001:5640: rtog pa ni spyan gyi sku ste mig yul gzugs kyi rtogs pa/
NK060(i)001:5642: 'o na yul la sku ru 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na/
NK060(i)001:5644: yul bzhis rnam shes brten pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:5648: rnam shes bzhi ni dmigs pa'i yul //
NK060(i)001:5649: mthong bar bya ba la sogs pa //
NK060(i)001:5650: dmigs par bya phyir sa yi mchog /ces gsungs pas mngon no //
NK060(i)001:5651: de bzhin du yi ge na tsha/
NK060(i)001:5652: rtog pa ni snyan gyi sku ste sgra/
NK060(i)001:5655: rtog pa ni shangs kyi sku dri ste/
NK060(i)001:5656: lha'i mchog m+aa le ma dang /
NK060(i)001:5658: rtog pa ni ljags kyi sku ro ste/
NK060(i)001:5659: lha'i mchog ni ra ti ma/
NK060(i)001:5661: rtog pa ni sku yang 'jig par byed pa gsang
NK060(i)001:5662: ba'i yul gyi khams pad+ma dang 'phrad pa'i dus na
NK060(i)001:5663: gzugs la sogs pa yul gyi rtog pa mi gnas
NK060(i)001:5664: par byed pa/ lha na stobs po che'o //
NK060(i)001:5665: phyi'i sems dpa' bzhi nub kyi sgo ba dang bcas pa'i/
NK060(i)001:5668: rtog pa ni spyan gyi gsung gi ste mig gi dbang po/
NK060(i)001:5670: 'o na dbang po la gsung du 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na/
NK060(i)001:5672: dbang po rnams ni yul dang shes pa rnams phyi
NK060(i)001:5673: nang gi tshul gyis brda spros par byed pa na
NK060(i)001:5676: 'khyil zhing gnas pa sku dang thugs //
NK060(i)001:5677: phyir 'byung smra ba gsung gi sgra //
NK060(i)001:5679: de bzhin du yi ge na pha //
NK060(i)001:5680: rtog pa ni snyan gyi gsung gi ste rna ba'i dbang po/
NK060(i)001:5683: rtog pa ni shangs kyi gsung gi ste sna'i dbang po/
NK060(i)001:5684: lha mchog kun tu bzang po dang /
NK060(i)001:5686: rtog pa ni ljags kyi gsung gi ste lce'i dbang po/
NK060(i)001:5689: rtog pa ni gsung yang 'jig par byed pa gsang
NK060(i)001:5690: ba'i dbang po'i khams kyis yul bzhir 'dzin pa yang
NK060(i)001:5694: rtog pa ni gnas pa'am da ltar gyi dus dag pa/
NK060(i)001:5695: lha na push+pe ma yin no //
NK060(i)001:5697: rtog pa ni 'jig pa dag pa ste ma 'ongs pa'i dus/
NK060(i)001:5700: rtog pa ni stong pa'am 'byung bar ma nges pa'i dus dag pa ste/
NK060(i)001:5702: yi ge na sha /rtog pa ni rtag med mi rtag par 'dzin pa dag pa ste/
NK060(i)001:5703: lha na lcags kyu ma dang /
NK060(i)001:5705: rtog pa ni chad pa'ang yod pa ma yin pa ste sdug bsngal bar 'dzin pa dag pa/
NK060(i)001:5706: lha na zhags pa ma dang /
NK060(i)001:5708: rtog pa ni mtha' bral ba med du 'dzin pa dag pa/
NK060(i)001:5709: lha na lcags sgrog ma dang /
NK060(i)001:5711: rtog pa ni mtshan ma med pa ste stong pa nyid du 'dzin pa dag pa/
NK060(i)001:5712: lha na dril bu ma nyid do //
NK060(i)001:5713: kun tu bzang po dang thub pa drug gi/
NK060(i)001:5715: 'di na mar go phye ba'i 'khor gyi don yin pas rtog pa mi sbyor/
NK060(i)001:5716: dag pa sbyor bar gsungs te yi ge na rgyu
NK060(i)001:5717: rkyen mthar zad pa k+shah dag pa ni rnam shes
NK060(i)001:5718: tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar dag pa'i thugs kyi nang
NK060(i)001:5719: nas kyang yul thams cad yid kho nas gcod par
NK060(i)001:5720: byed la/ de yang rnam par dag pa ni thugs rang byung gi ye shes te/
NK060(i)001:5721: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid kun tu bzang po'o //
NK060(i)001:5722: de yang thugs nyis brtseg yod pa'i 'thad pa ni/
NK060(i)001:5723: yo ga rgyan dam pa las/
NK060(i)001:5724: rnam par shes pa kun yid yin //
NK060(i)001:5725: yid kyi rnam shes gcod byed pa //
NK060(i)001:5726: thugs nyid rig pa sna tshogs ldan //
NK060(i)001:5727: de phyir thugs kyi mchog ces bya //
NK060(i)001:5730: rnam shes lnga yi yul ril kyang /
NK060(i)001:5731: yid kho nas gcod pa'i phyir brtsegs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:5733: yang k+sha thub pa drug gi yi ge 'go ru 'byung ba'i 'thad pa ni/
NK060(i)001:5734: kun tu bzang po'i thugs rig las go phye ba'i
NK060(i)001:5735: 'khor gyi don du thub pa drug sprul nas don
NK060(i)001:5736: byed pa'i phyir te/ de yang hri ha ya na'i tan+t+ra las/
NK060(i)001:5737: k+sha ni kun tu bzang po'i mkha' //
NK060(i)001:5738: b+ha ga rgya mtsho'i klong mtha' yas //
NK060(i)001:5739: chos nyid yangs pa'i mkha' klong nas //
NK060(i)001:5740: 'bras bu kun tu bzang mor shar //
NK060(i)001:5741: mkha' dang gnyis med rnam par dag /bde chen rgyal ba kun gyi thugs //
NK060(i)001:5742: de rtog pa la thub drug byung //
NK060(i)001:5745: dag pa ni nga rgyal te/
NK060(i)001:5746: nang rigs grangs las 'das pas na rdul snyed de
NK060(i)001:5747: lha rnams kyi gnas su thub pa brgya byin dang
NK060(i)001:5749: dag pa ni phrag dog ste/
NK060(i)001:5750: rdul snyed lha ma yin rnams kyi thub pa thag bzang rigs dang /
NK060(i)001:5753: rdul snyed mi rnams kyi gnas su thub pa sh+aakya seng ge dang /
NK060(i)001:5755: dag pa ni gti mug ste rdul snyed byol song rnams kyi thub pa seng ge rab brtan dang /
NK060(i)001:5757: dag pa ni ser sna ste rdul snyed yi dwags
NK060(i)001:5758: rnams kyi gnas su thub pa kha 'bar de dang
NK060(i)001:5760: dag pa ni zhe sdang ste rdul snyed dmyal ba rnams kyi thub pa chos kyi rgyal po'o //
NK060(i)001:5761: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i yi ge gnyis bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5764: rtog pa na gsum 'dus kyi reg pa ste/
NK060(i)001:5765: yi ge snga mas ni rtog pa thams cad 'jig par byed la/
NK060(i)001:5766: phyi mas ni thams cad mi gnas par byed pas na zhig pa yin zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:5768: 'o na bdud rtsi 'khil ba la yi ge gnyis 'ong ba ci yin zhe na/
NK060(i)001:5769: o ni gsang ba'i khams gsum gyi rtog pa bde ba 'jig par byed pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:5770: oo ni nges par spyad pa'i dus su bde bas
NK060(i)001:5771: las kyang 'das nas rtog pa thams cad mi gnas
NK060(i)001:5772: par 'dzin bral gyi ye shes su gnas pa yin
NK060(i)001:5773: te/ rgyu 'bras ro gcig pa'i phyir yi ge gnyis rtog pa gcig tu bzhag pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:5774: 'o na sgo ba kun yum dang bcas nas mi 'ong bar rkyang bar 'ong ba dang /
NK060(i)001:5775: sgo ba bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i yi ge kun gyi mjug tu 'ong ba'i 'thad pa ni/
NK060(i)001:5776: yi ge'i rim pa'i dbang gis byung ba shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:5777: yi ge'i mjug bsdu ba'am che ba bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5779: don mtshon par byed pa'i yi ge gsung gi 'khor
NK060(i)001:5780: lo'i tshogs chen po 'dis de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK060(i)001:5781: cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi phreng ba yi ges
NK060(i)001:5783: de ltar yi ge sku gsum du sangs rgyas pa
NK060(i)001:5784: de la dgyes pa'i don gyis na a hohzhesa bya'o
NK060(i)001:5785: // gzhung bsdus te bstan pa la bzhi/
NK060(i)001:5786: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:5789: bsdus te ston pas na de nas zhes 'brel mtshams sbyar nas/
NK060(i)001:5791: btsun mo'i tshogs yum dang gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor de bdag nyid kyi gsang ba/
NK060(i)001:5792: gzhung bsdu ba'i tshig 'di nyid sku gsung thugs yon
NK060(i)001:5793: tan phrin las mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las phyung
NK060(i)001:5796: 'di la grol lam ltar du gzhung rgyas pa dang sbyar te bsdu ba ni/
NK060(i)001:5797: a hohzhesa pa ni bsdu ba'i don 'og nas 'byung ba la mnyes pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5798: thabs yab dang shes rab yum ste/
NK060(i)001:5799: thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa'i don gang du bsdu na 'dir bsdu la/
NK060(i)001:5800: gang bsdu na yi ge chos kyi sku ru sangs rgyas pa'i don/
NK060(i)001:5801: ya ki na a ni zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5802: nyid la gnas zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5803: nyi zla gnyis su med pa'i sbyor ba ni dgyes pa'i sprin te/
NK060(i)001:5804: ya ki na yi ge a la sems sbyang ba/
NK060(i)001:5806: a/ rab tu zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5807: med par bstan zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5808: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems yi ge'i tshogs te/
NK060(i)001:5810: gang na gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:5811: ya ki na de nas zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5812: phyung ngo zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK060(i)001:5813: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la sems sbyang ba de las zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5814: bzhin no zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK060(i)001:5815: yi ge'i don bshad pa'i gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa de nas zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5816: brjod du zhes pa'i bar dang sa dmigs gsum sdud/
NK060(i)001:5817: byang chub kyi sems yongs su rdzogs pa'i rgyu ste/
NK060(i)001:5819: gang na rdo rje dngos grub kyi rgyu ru bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:5820: ya ki na 'di nas zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5821: rgyu yin no zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5824: nga na yi ge ji ltar byung ba'i tshul/
NK060(i)001:5825: ya ki na a zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5827: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya rmad du byung ba'i
NK060(i)001:5828: 'bras bu rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis smin zhing
NK060(i)001:5830: gang na yi ge spyi'i yon tan gyi mjug sdud/
NK060(i)001:5831: ya ki na phyogs bcu zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5832: k+sha la rdzogs zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK060(i)001:5833: yi ge bye brag gi don bshad pa rnams te/
NK060(i)001:5834: 'go ni ma nor zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5835: brjod du a hohzhesa pa'i bar sdud/
NK060(i)001:5836: chos nyid rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal bas na ngo mtshar ba ste/
NK060(i)001:5838: gang na yi ge gsung du sangs rgyas pa/
NK060(i)001:5839: ya ki na e ma'o zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5840: smra zhing ston zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5841: yi ge'i ming gi tshogs te/
NK060(i)001:5843: gang na yi ge byung ba'i mthu //
NK060(i)001:5844: ya ki na 'di dag ces pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5845: gyur te hohzhesa pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5846: a la sogs pa'i yi ge sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi rang bzhin te/
NK060(i)001:5848: gang na yi ge longs sku ru sangs rgyas pa/
NK060(i)001:5849: ya ki na a nyid ces pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5850: de nyid nges zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5851: sems kyi chos nyid ngo bo dus ma byas pa nyid de/
NK060(i)001:5853: gang na yi ge thugs su sangs rgyas pa/
NK060(i)001:5854: ya ki na dngos med ces pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5855: mi dmigs zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK060(i)001:5856: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin du bstan pa sems kyi ces pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5857: ma yin zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK060(i)001:5858: yi ge'i nges tshig dbyings zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5859: brjod ces pa'i bar sa dmigs gsum sdud/
NK060(i)001:5860: lam nyams su len pa'i dus su 'dus byas ltar
NK060(i)001:5861: snang yang de nyid sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bo
NK060(i)001:5862: dus gsum du mi phyed pa'i rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:5863: 'byin pa'i dam tshig las mi 'da' ba/
NK060(i)001:5865: gang na yi ge sku ru sangs rgyas pa'i don/
NK060(i)001:5866: ya ki na kyang zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5867: ston zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:5868: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje las 'da' bar mi
NK060(i)001:5869: mdzad pa'i dam tshig gis rang rig pa'i 'bras bu
NK060(i)001:5870: sku dang ye shes su rang snang ba nyid mi
NK060(i)001:5872: yongs su rjogs pa'i rgyu lta ba dang sgom pa'i
NK060(i)001:5873: las kyi mtshams sbyor ba'i rkyen ting nge 'dzin 'tshogs
NK060(i)001:5874: pa'i mthu chen po rang snang ba yin pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:5876: gang bsdu na yi ge dngos po mi dmigs kyang sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub 'gugs par bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:5877: ya ki na dmigs med ces pa nas/
NK060(i)001:5879: de ltar bsdu ba'i gnad ka'am rgyu mtshan ni/
NK060(i)001:5880: 'di na yang sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob pa las mi 'da' ba 'dug la/
NK060(i)001:5881: ya ki na yang don de ltar 'dug pas tshig mthun don mthun du byung ba'i phyir sdud gsung mdzod/
NK060(i)001:5882: a hohn bsdus ba'i don la mnyes pa'i tshig tu gda'/
NK060(i)001:5883: gnyis pa thabs lam ltar bshad na/
NK060(i)001:5884: thog mar steeng sgo la bslab pa ni/
NK060(i)001:5886: rgyu 'khor lo zhes pas byang chub kyi sems skyed par byed pa'i rgyu 'khor lo bzhi ni/
NK060(i)001:5887: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab drug cu
NK060(i)001:5888: rtsa bzhi'i dbus na thig le a thung gi dbyibs
NK060(i)001:5889: su gnas so // snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo
NK060(i)001:5890: rtsa 'dab brgyad kyi dbus na thig le bam gyi
NK060(i)001:5891: su gnas so // dbyibs su/ mgrin pa longs spyod
NK060(i)001:5892: kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab bcu drug gi dbus na
NK060(i)001:5893: thig le am gi dbyibs su/
NK060(i)001:5894: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab sum
NK060(i)001:5895: cu so gnyis kyi dbus na thig le ham gi
NK060(i)001:5898: sum mdo me'i 'khor lo na ram dang /
NK060(i)001:5899: sgrom mado'am bshang kha rlung gi 'khor lo na yam dang bcas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:5900: de lam pas bsgom pa'i dus na 'og rlung bskyod de rlung gis a thung gi me sbar bas/
NK060(i)001:5901: rtsa a wa d+h+au t+ai'i nang du me sna zhugs te/
NK060(i)001:5902: lte ba'i thig le rtog pas 'khyags pa bzhu/
NK060(i)001:5905: spyi bo'i 'khor lo rnams kyi thig le rtog pas 'khyags pa rnams bzhu nas/
NK060(i)001:5906: thig le'i 'od zer spyi bo nas 'thon te phyogs
NK060(i)001:5907: bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la bde stong gi
NK060(i)001:5908: mchod pa phul bas/ bde bar gshegs pa rnams ma
NK060(i)001:5909: chags thabs kyi sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang chub kyi
NK060(i)001:5910: mchod pa phul bas/ sems tshur 'dus/ spyi bo'i thig
NK060(i)001:5911: le la phog /'od du zhu bas lus kun khyab
NK060(i)001:5912: ste rkyal ba zhos bkang ba bzhin du gyur pa
NK060(i)001:5913: ni steng sgo la sbyang thabs yin no //
NK060(i)001:5914: de nas 'og sgo la bslab pa ni/
NK060(i)001:5918: yab yum gnyis med du rol pas dgyes pa'i sprin
NK060(i)001:5919: nyi zla gnyis med byang chub sems kyi tshogs sku
NK060(i)001:5920: gsung thugs ni phyag rgya rmad du byung ba'i 'bras
NK060(i)001:5921: bus rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi ngo bor
NK060(i)001:5922: smin cing grub pas ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK060(i)001:5923: de dag kyang ming gi tshogs tsam las ngo bo'am mtshan mar ma grub ste/
NK060(i)001:5924: bde ba'i ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po yang
NK060(i)001:5925: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ngo bo
NK060(i)001:5926: 'dus ma byas pa nyid dngos po lhan cig skyes
NK060(i)001:5927: pa'i ye shes 'dus byas ltar snang ste/
NK060(i)001:5928: bde stong dbyer med pa rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor mngon
NK060(i)001:5929: du 'byin pa las byed pa'i las mi 'da' ba
NK060(i)001:5931: de nas dam tshig de las 'da' bar mi mdzad 'da' ba'i dbang med de/
NK060(i)001:5932: rgyu steng sgo las su rung ba dang /
NK060(i)001:5933: rkyen thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med du sbyor
NK060(i)001:5934: ba'i ting nge 'dzin 'tshogs pa'i mthu chen po rang
NK060(i)001:5936: a hohn mnyes pa'i don yin no //
NK060(i)001:5937: bka' gsang sngags mtshon pa'i tshig /drang /
NK060(i)001:5938: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK060(i)001:5939: zhes pa 'bru zhib sngar bshad zin to //
NK060(i)001:5940: gzhung bsdus pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:5943: de bzhin gshegs pa rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)001:5944: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor thams
NK060(i)001:5945: cad yi ge'i rang bzhin bzhi bcu rtsa lngar 'dus
NK060(i)001:5946: shing de dag gi 'khor lor gyur to //
NK060(i)001:5949: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:5950: mtshon par byed pas na yi ge rgyun mi 'chad
NK060(i)001:5951: pas phreng ba'i gsung gi 'khor lo'i rim pa dang
NK060(i)001:5954: mtshan nyid ma nor bar bkod pa'i gcod cing mtshams
NK060(i)001:5955: 'dzin par byed pas na le'u ste yas bgrangs bzhi
NK060(i)001:5956: pa'i don du gada'o////da ni le'u lnga pa 'chad par
NK060(i)001:5957: byed de/ spyir gyis rgyud gzhung rdo rje'i tshig 'di lta bu 'chad par byed pa la/
NK060(i)001:5958: dgongs pa can dang dgongs pa can ma yin pa/
NK060(i)001:5960: sgra ji bzhin ma yin pa/
NK060(i)001:5961: drang ba'i don dang nges pa'i don du bshad pa'i mtha' drug yod mod kyang /
NK060(i)001:5962: de dag gi dgongs don phyin ci ma log par 'chad par byed pa la/
NK060(i)001:5963: 'brel pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i sgo nas 'chad dgos te/
NK060(i)001:5965: sgrub thabs chog khrigs dang 'brel ba/
NK060(i)001:5966: chog khrigs phyag bzhes dang 'brel ba/
NK060(i)001:5967: phyag bzhes bla ma brgyud pa'i gdams gang dang 'brel ba'o //
NK060(i)001:5968: de yang rgyud gzhung gcig dbu zhabs su dril nas/
NK060(i)001:5969: gang zag gcig gis nyams su len par byed pa la/
NK060(i)001:5973: rje sgro phug pa'i gsung sgros rgya che 'grel gyi lugs 'adi'o //
NK060(i)001:5975: spyir gyis rgyud 'grel pas bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:5976: rgyud sgrub thabs kyis bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:5977: rgyud gdams ngag gis bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:5978: rgyud bdag nyid kyis bdag nyid bshad pa dang lugs bzhi yin pa las/
NK060(i)001:5979: 'dir bshad thabs bzhi po skabs dang sbyar nas gang
NK060(i)001:5980: la gang dgos kyi 'chad par byed pa ni rgya
NK060(i)001:5981: che 'grel gyi bshad lugs yin gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:5982: rgyud 'di'i nang nas le'u gcig nyams su len na/
NK060(i)001:5986: mtshan nyid gsum du dril nas so //
NK060(i)001:5987: tshig bzhi tshigs su bcad pa gcig nyams su len na/
NK060(i)001:5989: le'u drug pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor te/
NK060(i)001:5991: lam cig car bar bshad pa ltar ro //
NK060(i)001:5992: tshig gcig nyams su len na/
NK060(i)001:5994: le'u gsum pa'i bsdu ba'i nang nas/
NK060(i)001:5995: stong nyid bdag med ye mkhyen rang rig thugs //
NK060(i)001:5996: zhes pa de tshul ji ltar na/
NK060(i)001:5997: gzhung rgyas pa'i skabs su rtogs pa bzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:5999: mnyam pa gnyis kyi gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab pa ltar ro //
NK060(i)001:6000: yig 'bru gcig nyams su len na/
NK060(i)001:6002: tshul ji ltar na le'u bzhi par a la sems sbyar ba ltar ro //
NK060(i)001:6004: mda' ltar rtse mo nas bzung ste bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:6005: mdung ltar sked pa nas bzung ste bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:6006: ral gri ltar yu ba nas bzung ste bshad pa dang gsum las/
NK060(i)001:6007: rtse mo nas bzung ste bshad pa ni/
NK060(i)001:6008: mtshan gyi skabs su chos thams cad gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du dril nas 'chad/
NK060(i)001:6009: sked pa nas bzung ste bshad pa ni/
NK060(i)001:6010: le'u lnga pa 'dir chos thams cad mtshan nyid gsum du dril nas 'chad/
NK060(i)001:6011: yu ba nas bzung ste bshad pa ni/
NK060(i)001:6012: le'u mtha' mar chos thams cad snang ba bzhir dril nas 'chad pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:6013: de la le'u lnga pa 'chad par byed pa la chos tshoms ngos gzung ba ni/
NK060(i)001:6014: blo rab kyis chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam gtsor ston/
NK060(i)001:6016: lam la thabs grol gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:6018: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa ston/
NK060(i)001:6021: snang ba bzhi las lam snang gtso che gzhi 'bras kyang zur tsam ston/
NK060(i)001:6024: rgyud don yongs su shes par byed pa'i dngos po bcu las/
NK060(i)001:6025: ting nge 'dzin dang sgrub pa ston/
NK060(i)001:6026: bcu yang brgya'i bdag nyid du byas na/
NK060(i)001:6034: bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud 'khrugs gtso cher ston/
NK060(i)001:6035: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:6036: de ltar ston pa'i le'u lnga pa 'di la rnam
NK060(i)001:6037: par dbye ba'i tshig /stag gis mchongs pa ltar du
NK060(i)001:6038: bshad na don chings gsum gyis ston te/
NK060(i)001:6040: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:6042: le'u bzhi par yi ge la sems sbyang ba bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:6043: da ting nge 'dzin gyis dngos grub bsgrub pa ston pas na de nas zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:6044: le'u gong mar yi ge 'khor lo sprin bkod pa'i
NK060(i)001:6045: mthu las sgyu ma mtshon pa lha yum 'phrul pa
NK060(i)001:6046: mtshon pa lha yab/ yab yum gnyis su med pa lha'i dkyil 'khor las/
NK060(i)001:6047: las dang dngos grub la sogs par snang ba rnams rnam par 'phro ba'i 'di ched du brjod do //
NK060(i)001:6052: dang po byang chub bsgrub pa'i rgyu/
NK060(i)001:6055: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK060(i)001:6056: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK060(i)001:6058: zhes pa'i rang bzhin brgyad dang ldan pa'i ston pa
NK060(i)001:6059: rdo rje slob dpon la sgo gsum gus pa'i sgo
NK060(i)001:6060: nas mnyes pa gsum gyis mchod cing phan/
NK060(i)001:6062: nus/ zab mo'i dbang rim par thob par byas nas brtson
NK060(i)001:6063: 'grus kyis rgyud yongs su sbyang ba'i sgo nas lta
NK060(i)001:6064: ba bden pa dbyer med rtogs pa/
NK060(i)001:6067: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gsum gsal ba/
NK060(i)001:6068: bla med mi spang ba la sogs pa rtsa ba lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:6069: mi spang mi dor ba'i yan lag bcu la sogs pa'i dam tshig ma nyams pa/
NK060(i)001:6070: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba/
NK060(i)001:6072: bzlas pa las kyi sngags te/
NK060(i)001:6076: chos/ sku'i phyag rgya chen po dang bzhi po rnams shes shing /
NK060(i)001:6081: +aa li k+aa li'i yo byad dang lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:6082: de tsho dang ldan na byang chub 'grub par 'gyur la/
NK060(i)001:6083: mi ldan na bsgrubs kyang don med pas na brlag ces bya'o //
NK060(i)001:6084: 'di ni tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa yang yin te/
NK060(i)001:6085: lam rim gyi le'u bdun pa bar chad med pa'i lam/
NK060(i)001:6086: tshogs bsgrub pa dang sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:6088: sa bcad nang brtsegs gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:6091: gang skal pa dman zhing bla ma'i man ngag gis
NK060(i)001:6092: ma zin ba zhig gis sems nyid gang du yang
NK060(i)001:6093: dmigs su med pa'i don mi shes pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:6094: de yis chos nyid mnyam pa nyid 'dus ma byas kyi dbyings kyang mi shes so //
NK060(i)001:6095: de'i phyir rigs drug gi sems can rang rang gi zhen dngos/
NK060(i)001:6099: nyan thos pa rdul dang shes pa/
NK060(i)001:6100: rang rgyal 'dzin rigs skad cig ma/
NK060(i)001:6101: sems tsam pa sems rang rig rang gsal/
NK060(i)001:6102: myong ba gnyis med kyi shes pa dngos por lta
NK060(i)001:6103: ba de dag le'u gsum par gtan tshig gyi gtan
NK060(i)001:6104: la phab pa ltar brtags na rang gi ngo bo
NK060(i)001:6105: stongs pa'i phyir/ dngos po thams cad dngos med du 'jig pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6106: mu stegs chad pa ba shes pa snga phyi gtan
NK060(i)001:6107: med lung gi phyogs tsam pa thams cad ci yang
NK060(i)001:6108: ma yin la/ ma yin pa tsam yang ma yin pa/
NK060(i)001:6109: dbu ma ye shes rgyun chad pa mtha' bral stong
NK060(i)001:6110: pa nyid la yul gtan ma grub pas der 'dzin
NK060(i)001:6111: gyi ye shes kyang med par lta ba ste/
NK060(i)001:6112: mdor na dngos med du 'dod pa thams cad du kyang dngos po las ltos pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:6113: sems kyi rang bzhin stong pa nyid kyi ngang du
NK060(i)001:6114: 'jig pas na sems nyid dngos po dang dngos med
NK060(i)001:6115: gang du'ang dmigs du med pa ste/
NK060(i)001:6116: de shes par gyis shig par gdams pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6117: lta ba rang gi ngo bo'o //
NK060(i)001:6119: rten pa'i gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba med pa'i
NK060(i)001:6120: sems nyid ni mtshan gyi sgo nas pho dang mo'ang
NK060(i)001:6121: ma yin la ma ning yang min zhing mtshan med
NK060(i)001:6122: sgo nga lta bu yang ma yin no //
NK060(i)001:6123: rigs kyi sgo nas rgyal rigs la sogs pa lnga dang rgyud 'gro ba drug kyang min zhing /
NK060(i)001:6124: gzugs kyi sgo nas kha dog lnga'am nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs pa yang ma yin/
NK060(i)001:6125: dbyibs kyi zhi rgyas dbang drag la sogs pa yang
NK060(i)001:6126: ma yin gnas rten dang rten med gnyis su grub
NK060(i)001:6127: pa'ang ma yin te/ mdor na dngos po dang dngos
NK060(i)001:6128: med kyi mtha' gang yang min pa ni de bzhin
NK060(i)001:6129: nyid kyi dbyings mu mtha' dang bral zhing chos thams
NK060(i)001:6130: cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa'i phyir gnas lugs
NK060(i)001:6132: de mngon du byed pa'i thabs kyi khyad par ni rang bzhin te/
NK060(i)001:6134: lhag pa'i phyag rgya gsum las mi 'da' ba ni/
NK060(i)001:6135: bden gsum kun gyi ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu'o //
NK060(i)001:6136: de dag ni man ngag lam gyi rim pa dang
NK060(i)001:6137: sbyar nas rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba yin
NK060(i)001:6140: lta ba rang gi ngo bo ni lam rim le'u
NK060(i)001:6141: dang po ye shes rang la gnas pa dang sbyar
NK060(i)001:6142: nas lta ba rtogs par gdams pa ni/
NK060(i)001:6143: lam rim le'u gnyis pa rang gnas mthong ba dang sbyar na 'thad dam sems so //
NK060(i)001:6144: gsum pa bsgoms pa'i dgos ched/
NK060(i)001:6146: dngos po rnams sems nyid kho nar gnas pa'i dus
NK060(i)001:6147: na sems nyid dngos po med par gtan tshigs kyis
NK060(i)001:6149: rtogs pa'i don la ma yengs par dbang sgyur ba
NK060(i)001:6150: ni btang snyoms chen po'i ting nge 'dzin yin no
NK060(i)001:6153: lta ba rtogs pa'i rten gyi gang zag zhig gis
NK060(i)001:6154: dpe glang chen smyon pa rgun 'brum gyi chang gis
NK060(i)001:6155: myos pa la 'dul thabs rgyan 'dul dang khrom 'dul
NK060(i)001:6157: 'khrul rtog sna tshogs kyis myos pa'i sems yul la
NK060(i)001:6158: 'phro ba de 'dul ba'i thabs kyang gnyis yod do
NK060(i)001:6159: // gdams ngag gi stobs kyis bzhag thabs dang /
NK060(i)001:6160: shes rab kyi stobs kyis bzhag thabs gnyis gang rung
NK060(i)001:6161: gi sgo nas sngar gyi lta ba'i rjes su cir
NK060(i)001:6162: yang mi dmigs par mnyam par bzhag pas btul nas/
NK060(i)001:6163: ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa'i ye shes gnyis mngon du byas shing /
NK060(i)001:6164: gzhi ji lta ba klungs su phebs pa ni thul ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6165: de ltar bsgoms pa'i dgos ched dang bsgoms pa'i thabs gnyis ni de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin te/
NK060(i)001:6166: lam rim le'u gsum pa stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor dang sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:6167: lnga pa de nyid thams cad du rang snang ba/
NK060(i)001:6169: rten pa'i gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba med pa'i
NK060(i)001:6170: stong pa nyid kyi dbyings sems nyid 'di ni pho
NK060(i)001:6171: mo la sogs pa mtha' gar yang ma lhung la
NK060(i)001:6172: rgya gar yang ma chad pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:6173: snying rje chen po nam mkha' dang mnyam pa bsgom par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:6174: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin yin no //
NK060(i)001:6175: de nyid lam rim le'u bzhi pa snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor dang sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:6176: 'khor ba mya ngan las 'das pas bsdus pa'i chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba sems nyid yin la/
NK060(i)001:6177: kun gyi rtsa ba sems nyid de ye gdod ma
NK060(i)001:6178: nas ma skyes pa'i phyir na yi ge a'i rang
NK060(i)001:6179: bzhin yin te/ yi ge a de las yi ge'i
NK060(i)001:6180: phreng ba 'byung ba ni dper na yid bzhin gyi
NK060(i)001:6181: nor bu rin chen las ma g.yos par dgos 'dod
NK060(i)001:6182: bzhin yin te/ 'byung ba bzhin/ a s+pha ra na phata ces/
NK060(i)001:6183: a phra mo grangs med pa nam mkha' khyab par spro/
NK060(i)001:6184: sam ha ra h'u zhes tshur bsdus pas/
NK060(i)001:6185: sems nyid gzhi ma nges pa la yi ge'i sprin
NK060(i)001:6186: le'u bzhi par bshad pa bzhin bsgom pa ni phra
NK060(i)001:6188: drug pa de la dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsgom pa/
NK060(i)001:6190: rang rig pa nyid yi ger snang ba rtsa ba'i thabs so //
NK060(i)001:6191: thabs de las gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa
NK060(i)001:6192: gsal ba ni thabs las byung ba gzhi'i thabs so
NK060(i)001:6193: // der lha'i dkyil 'khor bkod nas bsgom pa ni thabs bsam yas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6194: gsum po de dag ni rags pa lha sku la bslab pa ste/
NK060(i)001:6195: sngar bshad pa'i phra ba yig 'bru la bslab pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6196: 'chad par 'gyur pa'i de la 'dris par bsgom pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6197: sa dmigs gsum po de ni phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor te/
NK060(i)001:6198: lam rim le'u lnga pa phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:6199: de ltar thabs gsum po de rang rig pa'i ye shes su gcig pas na/
NK060(i)001:6200: tha dad min pa las blo chung rim gyis pa
NK060(i)001:6201: la tha dad pa ltar re mos su bsgom pa'i
NK060(i)001:6202: tshul ni/ nang lha dang nang gi phyi rol gzhal
NK060(i)001:6203: yas khang gi bkod pa rten dang brten par bcas
NK060(i)001:6204: pa'i dkyil 'khor le'u brgyad par 'chad pa bzhin tshom
NK060(i)001:6205: tshul ni/ bu stong dang / nyi khri bzhi stong
NK060(i)001:6206: dang bsam yas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor lha la
NK060(i)001:6207: lha dang ye shes la ye shes rol pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6208: de lta bu'i lam pa de 'khor ba'i g.yang sa dang /
NK060(i)001:6209: tshogs lam gyi g.yang sa gnyis la 'jigs pa med
NK060(i)001:6210: cing spyod yul yongs su dag pa kun tu bzang
NK060(i)001:6211: po ste sku'i phyag rgya chen po'i ngang las mi
NK060(i)001:6214: nang nyid rnam shes nang gi dbang po dang //
NK060(i)001:6215: phyi rol yul gyi rnam pa thams cad kun //
NK060(i)001:6216: bsam yas dkyil 'khor kun bzang phyag rgyar rol //
NK060(i)001:6218: bdun pa de nyid kar dag pa blang dor dang bral ba dpe yis bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:6220: thabs gsum po de nyid sems nyid rang rig pa'i ye shes su rang snang ba'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:6221: h+aum m+aum la sogs pa'i yi ge'i ming dang /
NK060(i)001:6222: badz+ra d+h+rika la sogs pa bskyed pa'i tshig dang /
NK060(i)001:6223: sku mdog phyag mtshan la sogs pa sku yongs su
NK060(i)001:6224: rdzogs pa'i gzugs bsgom pa la sogs pa'i ting nge
NK060(i)001:6226: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che la dgos 'dod 'byung ba ltar/
NK060(i)001:6227: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsgoms pas 'dod pa'i don thams cad 'grub par 'gyur te/
NK060(i)001:6228: dper na mun khung du sgron me bteg pa'i dus
NK060(i)001:6229: na mun pa gang yang ma spangs pa la snang
NK060(i)001:6230: ba byung ba ji bzhin du/
NK060(i)001:6231: lam pas thabs gsum po bsgom pa'i dus na rtog
NK060(i)001:6232: tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis gang yang ma spangs par
NK060(i)001:6233: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su rang snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6234: yang lcags ma spangs par gser du 'gyur bar byed
NK060(i)001:6235: pa gser 'gyur gyi rtsi lcags la thebs pa bzhin
NK060(i)001:6236: du/ lam pas thabs gsum po bsgom pa'i dus na/
NK060(i)001:6237: phyi 'byung ba yul ltar du snang ba ma spangs
NK060(i)001:6238: par yum lnga'i mkha'i rang bzhin can gyi gzhal yas
NK060(i)001:6239: khang gdan dang bcas pa rang snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6240: gzhan yang rtsi ma g+hi ta'am nus pas dug ma
NK060(i)001:6241: spangs par sman gyi rang bzhin du byed pa'i tshul
NK060(i)001:6242: du/ lam pas thabs gsum po bsgom pa'i dus na
NK060(i)001:6243: ma rig pa'i ngar 'dzin pa rnam par shes pa
NK060(i)001:6244: du/ tshogs brgyad dam/ nyon mongs pa dug lnga ma spangs bzhin du ye shes lngar rang snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6245: 'di la 'ga' zhig dpe gsum po ldabs pa'i 'gal spong byed mod kyi/
NK060(i)001:6247: bshad ma thag pa'i 'bru bsnan pas shes so //
NK060(i)001:6248: brgyad pa de la 'dris par bslab pa/
NK060(i)001:6250: sngags kyi yan lag lnga dang phyag rgya gcig spros
NK060(i)001:6251: kyi ting nge 'dzin gsal ba yul gyis mi 'phrogs
NK060(i)001:6252: pa rab tu brtan par gyur na thun mong dang
NK060(i)001:6253: mchog gi dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'grub par
NK060(i)001:6254: 'gyur te 'og nas ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:6255: dgu pa thun mong gi dngos grub bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:6257: 'di la rgyud dang 'grel pa dang sgrub thabs kyi bshad pa'i dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:6258: zas dug can la yi ge a bkod de/
NK060(i)001:6259: 'ju 'dul byas pa tsam gyis bdud rtsir 'gyur zhing de'i yon tan 'byung ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6261: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel zhing bdud rtsi'i 'od
NK060(i)001:6262: zer las longs spyod 'byung zhing tri pre duhngana song
NK060(i)001:6263: gi sa bon rnams sbyong ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6264: de las gzhan pa ci yang gzhan du ste/
NK060(i)001:6265: bye ma las gser dang sol ba las ljon shing du 'gyur pa la sogs pa 'grub bo //
NK060(i)001:6266: nam mkha' la rdo rje'i skas bsgoms pas sra ba'i
NK060(i)001:6267: skas 'byung zhing lag mthil du yige ram bkod pas
NK060(i)001:6268: de las ye shes kyi me 'bar nas tha mal
NK060(i)001:6269: gyi me yang 'tshig par 'gyur pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6270: kham las chu 'gyur 'bab pa'ang dpe gong ma de
NK060(i)001:6271: bzhin te tha mal gyi chu dag par byed pa
NK060(i)001:6272: dang / yam las ye shes kyi rlung 'byung bas
NK060(i)001:6273: 'jig rten gyi khams kyi tha mal gyi rlung ni
NK060(i)001:6274: dang / 'thor ba dang / yi ge a bkod
NK060(i)001:6275: de 'phro 'du byas pas thams cad stongs par bsams
NK060(i)001:6276: dang / 'thor ba dang / na/ 'jig rten gyi
NK060(i)001:6277: khams stongs shing gzhol phyogs su lhung bar 'gyur pa
NK060(i)001:6278: dang / 'thor ba dang / na/ dang / ting
NK060(i)001:6279: nge 'dzin gyis dgra bgegs dgug pa dang gling khams
NK060(i)001:6281: jag chings kyis bcing ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6282: gzhan gyis byad du bcug pa dgrol pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6283: sri'u dang lo tog dang nad pa la sogs pa gso ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6285: gzhan gyi g.yul 'pham par bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6286: rang gi g.yul rgyal bar bya ba la sogs pa
NK060(i)001:6287: ni phyag rgya gcig spros kyi ting nge 'dzin las
NK060(i)001:6288: su rung ba'i rnal 'byor pa 'di yis byed par
NK060(i)001:6289: 'gyur ro // yang 'di la rgyud gdams ngag ltar du bshad na/
NK060(i)001:6290: thog mar steng sgo dang sbyar te bshad pa ni/
NK060(i)001:6293: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab drug cu
NK060(i)001:6294: rtsa bzhi'i bdag nyid snying po yi ge a thung
NK060(i)001:6295: dang bcas pa bsgoms pas sa'i dwangs ma zin/
NK060(i)001:6298: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab brgyad kyi bdag nyid can/
NK060(i)001:6299: snying po thig le bam dang bcas pa bsgoms pas chu'i dwangs ma zin/
NK060(i)001:6302: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab bcu drug gi bdag nyid can/
NK060(i)001:6303: snying po yi ge am dang bcas pa bsgoms pas me'i dwangs ma zin/
NK060(i)001:6304: thams cad stongs shing zhes pas/
NK060(i)001:6305: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi bdag nyid can/
NK060(i)001:6306: snying po yi ge ham dang bcas pa bsgoms pas
NK060(i)001:6307: nam mkha'i dwangs ma zin pa de la yang mda'
NK060(i)001:6308: gcig gis sha ba gnyis gsod pa'i tshul du byas
NK060(i)001:6309: nas bshad na/ 'bar nas me yang zhes pas/
NK060(i)001:6311: 'jig rten khams ni 'thor ba ces pas/
NK060(i)001:6313: de dag bsgoms pa'i thabs ni/
NK060(i)001:6314: 'og rlung bskyod pas rlung gis me sbar te 'khor lo bzhi'i thig le zhu ste/
NK060(i)001:6315: bde ba'i ye shes rgyud la skyes pa ni rlung gi dwangs ma zin pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6316: de dag ni steng sgo bsgom pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6317: 'og sgo ni nam mkha' ni shes rab/
NK060(i)001:6319: thabs shes rab gnyis su med par phyag rgya bzhi
NK060(i)001:6320: yis rol bas rtsa gnas nas thig le dgug pa
NK060(i)001:6321: dang / rdo rje'i dbu'i bum par thig le bcing ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6322: yum gyi mkhar thig le btang ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6323: rtsa mdud kyi rtog pa thams cad dgrol ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6324: de nas thig le ldog pa'i thabs kyis ldog pas gsang ba'i rdo rje na yar zhugs te/
NK060(i)001:6326: klad pa bde chen khyab gdal chen po'i dgongs pas
NK060(i)001:6327: lus mgo 'jug tu lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:6332: tha mal 'dod chags kyi rtog pa'i bdud de bde
NK060(i)001:6333: ba'i ye shes kyi rtsir 'gyur zhing yon tan thams
NK060(i)001:6335: de ltar spyad pas bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rims sel ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6336: gsang ba'i longs spyod zag pa med pa'i bde ba 'byung zhing /
NK060(i)001:6337: bde ba'i ye shes mngon du gyur tsam na ngan
NK060(i)001:6338: song gsum gyi sa bon thams cad kyang sbyong bar
NK060(i)001:6339: byed do // de la sogs pa ci yang gzhan du 'gyur ba ni thig dbab/
NK060(i)001:6341: bskyil/ ldog /dgram pa la sogs pa 'grub cing /
NK060(i)001:6342: mtha' bral 'jig med nam mkha' lta bu'i bde ba
NK060(i)001:6343: 'bar bas nyams chag dang rtog sgrib thams cad tshig
NK060(i)001:6344: par 'gyur la/ bde ba'i chu rgyun rgyun chad med par 'bab pa'ang de bzhin te/
NK060(i)001:6345: des nyon mongs pa dang rnam par rtog pa 'jig
NK060(i)001:6346: pa la 'jig rten pa dang bcas pa'i khams ni
NK060(i)001:6347: bde ba'i ye shes kyis 'thor ba byed pa dang
NK060(i)001:6348: / bden 'dzin gyi rtog pa thams cad stong zhing ltung bar 'gyur te/
NK060(i)001:6349: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su myong bar byed do //
NK060(i)001:6350: de ltar lam du slongs tsam na bde ba'i ye
NK060(i)001:6351: shes kyis 'dod chags kyi rnam par rtog pa'i dgra
NK060(i)001:6352: bsad pa dang / khams 'dzag med du byas pas 'khor ba'i g.yul 'pham pa dang /
