NK060(i)001:6353: rtog tshogs thams cad sku dang ye shes su byung
NK060(i)001:6354: sa thebs pas mya ngan las 'das pa'i g.yul rgyal
NK060(i)001:6355: ba zhes bya ste/ thabs lam gyi ting nge 'dzin
NK060(i)001:6356: las su rung ba'i 'di yis 'bras bu rtsol med
NK060(i)001:6357: du thob par byed par 'gyur ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6358: de dag ni gdams ngag ltar bshad pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:6360: bdag nyid kyis bdag nyid bshad pa ltar na/
NK060(i)001:6362: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel zhing //
NK060(i)001:6364: mchog gi bdud rtsi sgrub par byed pa ste/
NK060(i)001:6365: sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i le'u bzhi bcu pas rgyas par ston no //
NK060(i)001:6366: de yang mtshams bcad pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6368: sman bkod pa dam pa rigs brgyas sbyang ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6369: btags btsags byas la rigs lngas sbyang ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6370: bum par dril la rigs gcig gis sbyong ba la sogs pa bshad do //
NK060(i)001:6372: ro langs bsgrub pa bstan te/
NK060(i)001:6373: thun mong gi bdud rtsi bsgrub pa yang yin no //
NK060(i)001:6374: longs spyod 'byung zhing ngan song sbyong //
NK060(i)001:6376: le'u zhe gcig pa'i phyogs gcig nas slob pa'i rim pa bsgrub pa ston pa de'o //
NK060(i)001:6379: le'u so brgyad pa nas rkang mgyogs bsgrub pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6380: lus mi snang ba bsgrub pa ston/
NK060(i)001:6381: le'u re bzhi pa nas tshe bsgrub pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6382: re lnga pa nas pra dang /
NK060(i)001:6383: gzhan rdo rje bkod pa kun 'dus kyi rgyud nas/
NK060(i)001:6389: sol ba la ljon shing du bsgrub pa la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6390: yul khams dbang du bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6394: rgyud gzhan dag nas kyang mang du gsungs pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:6395: nam mkha'i rdo rje zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig lnga ni/
NK060(i)001:6396: rdo rje snying po las thams cad pa'i rgyud kyi le'u so brgyad pas ston te/
NK060(i)001:6397: mi gnas nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa //
NK060(i)001:6398: goms par 'dod pas thos pa dang //
NK060(i)001:6399: chu la sa bzhin 'gro ba dang //
NK060(i)001:6400: bsreg bya 'bar ba'i dbus nas dang //
NK060(i)001:6401: tsha ba rlung gis bteg nas kyang //
NK060(i)001:6402: phyogs bcu kun tu phyin par gsungs //
NK060(i)001:6403: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyas par ston no //
NK060(i)001:6405: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i gzungs ma rigs lnga'i yum dgug pa ni/
NK060(i)001:6406: le'u zhe gnyis pa dang zhes gsum pas ston/
NK060(i)001:6407: sems ma dgug pa zhe gnyis pas ston/
NK060(i)001:6408: 'jig rten pa'i gzungs ma dgug pa ni/
NK060(i)001:6409: rgyal po sa 'dzin gyi chung ma dang /
NK060(i)001:6410: lha chen gzhan gyi chung ma dgug pa zhe lnga pas ston/
NK060(i)001:6411: rgyud gzhan dag las lha'i bu mo dang /
NK060(i)001:6413: rigs ngan mo mi'i bu mo dgug pa yang ston no //
NK060(i)001:6415: drag po spyi yi sbyor ba yis //
NK060(i)001:6416: dgra bgegs gling khams gzhan du btang //
NK060(i)001:6418: dgra bgegs gling khams gzhan du 'phangs pa la sogs pa rgyas par bshad do //
NK060(i)001:6419: bcing zhes pa ni ma mo'i jag chings dang /
NK060(i)001:6420: 'byung po kha bcing ba la sogs pa bshad do //
NK060(i)001:6421: dgrol zhes pa ni ma mo'i jag chings la sogs pa dgrol ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6426: klu'i gegs sel lnga pa le'u zhe drug pas ston/
NK060(i)001:6428: ro langs bsgrub pa'i le'u la yang ngos gzung du rung ngo //
NK060(i)001:6432: rgyud gzhan nas dgra bgegs dang /
NK060(i)001:6435: gzhan gyi g.yul 'pham par bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6436: rang gi g.yul rgyal bar bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6437: rgyal po sde bzhi bsgrub pa la sogs pa drug cu re drug pas ston/
NK060(i)001:6438: sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho la sogs pa bshad rgyud gzhan
NK060(i)001:6439: nas kyang ston pas rgya cher sbyar bas chog go
NK060(i)001:6440: // de ltar dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsgom pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6441: de nyid kar dag pa blang dor dang blang bar dpe yis bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6442: bsgom pa'i 'bras bus thun mong gi dngos grub bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6443: sa dmigs gsum po de phyag rgya spros bcas kyi rnal 'byor yin te/
NK060(i)001:6444: lam rim le'u drug pa spros pa'i rnal 'byor la bslab pa dang sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:6445: bcu pa mchog gi dngos grub mdor bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:6447: sgyu ma mtshon pa lha yum dang /
NK060(i)001:6448: 'phrul ba mtshon pa lha yab ste/
NK060(i)001:6449: phung po lnga la sogs pa'i rtog pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su snang ste/
NK060(i)001:6450: yab yum 'brel ba d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal zhing rdzogs pas/
NK060(i)001:6451: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa thams cad khams gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bas na/
NK060(i)001:6452: spyod yul dang bral ba yi ge 'khor lo tshogs
NK060(i)001:6453: chen gyis mngon du rdzogs pa yi 'bras bu ni
NK060(i)001:6454: rgyal ba thams cad gcig dang du ma las grol
NK060(i)001:6455: bas dkyil 'khor lhag ma ma lus pa thams cad
NK060(i)001:6457: 'di ni mthar thug gi 'bras bu yin te/
NK060(i)001:6458: lam rim le'u dgu pa mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu bstan pa dang sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:6459: bcu gcig pa mchog gi dngos grub rgyas par bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6461: dngos po thams cad sku dang ye shes su gsal
NK060(i)001:6462: ba ni dus gsum gyi rgyal bas thugs su chud
NK060(i)001:6464: rnal 'byor pa'i lta ba yang yin pas na dngos grub kyi mchog go //
NK060(i)001:6465: de dag gi bcud 'dus pa snying po'i yon tan ni zad pa'i dus med de/
NK060(i)001:6467: rgyal po'i dkor mdzod lta bu byung yang 'phel ba dang /
NK060(i)001:6468: ma byung yang 'grib pa med par 'byung ba ngo bo nyid kyi rtag pa ste/
NK060(i)001:6469: dngos po'am mtshan mar grub pa med pa las/
NK060(i)001:6470: gdul bya'i ngo la lha dang dkyil 'khor dang ting
NK060(i)001:6471: nge 'dzin la sogs pa dngos po'i sprin sna tshogs
NK060(i)001:6472: pa'i rnam par 'byung zhing ngo bo cir yang 'char
NK060(i)001:6473: ba de nyid rnam pa cir yang 'gyur ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6474: 'di ni gnas skabs lam gyur gyi 'bras bu yin te/
NK060(i)001:6475: lam rim le'u brgyad pa mthar phyin pa'i lam bstan pa dang sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:6476: gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:6478: zhes gzhung gi don de dag brjod pas 'khor gyi
NK060(i)001:6479: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid ting nge 'dzin gyi mthu
NK060(i)001:6480: las dngos grub sna tshogs snang bas na/
NK060(i)001:6481: ma ltas par rang gsal ba'i gzigs mos te bdag nyid chen po'i mchod pas mnyes par gyur to //
NK060(i)001:6484: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las mtshan gyi gzhir du gda'/
NK060(i)001:6485: lha yab yum zung du 'brel ba sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi mthu las/
NK060(i)001:6486: dngos grub ma lus pa bsgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK060(i)001:6487: gyi gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas na le'u ste yas
NK060(i)001:6488: bgrangs lnga pa'i don du gada'o////da ni le'u drug pa
NK060(i)001:6490: chos tshoms kyi dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:6491: rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las/
NK060(i)001:6493: lam la thabs grol gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:6496: lam dang 'bras bu'i snang ba ston/
NK060(i)001:6499: rim cig car gnyis las gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:6502: de la bcu las gzhung hril po sku'i dkyil 'khor ston/
NK060(i)001:6503: bcu yang brgya'i bdag nyid du byas na dkyil 'khor gyi zhor la lta ba zur tsam ston/
NK060(i)001:6508: tha ma'i chos tshoms bcu las/
NK060(i)001:6509: rang bzhin lta ba zur tsam/
NK060(i)001:6514: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:6515: de ltar ston pa'i le'u drug pa 'di la don chings gsum/
NK060(i)001:6517: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:6519: thabs gsum mdo tsam bstan pa la de/
NK060(i)001:6520: ting nge 'dzin gyis nyams su len pa ston pas na nas/
NK060(i)001:6521: de bzhin gshegs pa chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin
NK060(i)001:6522: ni ma 'dres pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir gcig
NK060(i)001:6523: dang du ma'i mtha' med pa'i don mngon du byas
NK060(i)001:6524: pas bdag nyid chen po thams cad kyi ngo bo
NK060(i)001:6525: nyid gcig dang du ma dang bral bar bzhugs pas
NK060(i)001:6526: 'jig rten drug gam khams gsum gyi phyogs bcu ma
NK060(i)001:6527: lus pa thams cad la rig pa rang snang ba
NK060(i)001:6528: nyid kyi che ba ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor du
NK060(i)001:6529: gdal te/ gsal bar ston pa'i dgongs pa mngon du
NK060(i)001:6530: bzhag pa las dbyung bar bzhed nas 'og nas 'byung
NK060(i)001:6531: ba'i don ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK060(i)001:6532: le'u'i gzhung don la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:6535: dang po la spyi don gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:6537: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)001:6541: rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar brtags na/
NK060(i)001:6542: gsal la mi rtog pa me long lta bu/
NK060(i)001:6543: bzang ngan med pa mnyam pa nyid/
NK060(i)001:6544: ma 'dres pa so sor rtog pa/
NK060(i)001:6545: yongs su rdzogs pa bya ba grub pa/
NK060(i)001:6546: mtha' thams cad las 'das pa stong pa nyid de
NK060(i)001:6547: de ltar ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor de nyid kyi
NK060(i)001:6548: ngo bo blos gzhal ba las 'das pa ste/
NK060(i)001:6549: bsam yas shing lhun gyis grub pa ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs so //
NK060(i)001:6550: de rtogs shing mngon du byas pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK060(i)001:6551: yon tan kun 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor chen por spyod
NK060(i)001:6552: cig pa'am sgoms shing ces gdams pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6553: de ni rim gyis pa ltar 'grel pas bshad pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:6554: cig car ba ltar gdams ngag gis bshad na/
NK060(i)001:6555: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK060(i)001:6557: rnal 'byor pa gang zhig gis 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rdzogs pa/
NK060(i)001:6558: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po bden pa dbyer med
NK060(i)001:6559: lhag pa'i chos sku chen por rtogs pa ni lta
NK060(i)001:6560: ba yin no // dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK060(i)001:6562: rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor bsam pa'i yul las 'das pa la/
NK060(i)001:6563: blo ma bcos par lhun grub tu gnas pa ni bsgom pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:6566: lta sgom zung du 'brel ba'i sgo nas snang grags
NK060(i)001:6567: kyi chos thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyiil
NK060(i)001:6568: 'khor chen por longs spyod pa ni spyod pa yin
NK060(i)001:6569: no // ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te //
NK060(i)001:6571: de ltar spyod pa'i 'bras bu ye shes lngar rang snang ba ni 'bras bu yin no //
NK060(i)001:6572: de ltar lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi yang don la
NK060(i)001:6573: dbyer med phyed par nyams su len pa ni 'bras
NK060(i)001:6574: bu lam du byed pa zhes bya ste gsang sngags
NK060(i)001:6575: ma h+aa yo ga'i khyad chos yin no //
NK060(i)001:6576: yang 'di la 'grel chung pin tar+tha ltar na brtags te zhes pa bshad pa'i gzhir byas nas/
NK060(i)001:6578: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa des/
NK060(i)001:6580: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa de/
NK060(i)001:6582: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga'i tshul du/
NK060(i)001:6584: kun 'byung dkyil 'khor chen po spyod pa'i phyir du'o //
NK060(i)001:6585: zhes zur thams cad mkhyen pa gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:6586: spyi don gnyis pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:6592: ngo bo rkyen dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:6594: 'dir lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'i dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:6595: thog mar thos bsam gyi sgo nas lta ba spyi'i rnam par rtogs par byas nas/
NK060(i)001:6596: nyams len dngos gzhi'i dus su le'u gnyis pa nas
NK060(i)001:6597: 'byung ba bzhin byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed
NK060(i)001:6598: cing / le'u bzhi pa nas 'byung ba bzhin yi
NK060(i)001:6599: ge la sems sbyangs nas 'byung ba lnga'i sa bon
NK060(i)001:6600: las 'byung ba rim brtsegs ri rab dang bcas pa
NK060(i)001:6601: cing / bskyed pa'i steng du/ le'u bdun pa nas
NK060(i)001:6602: 'byung ba bzhin b+h+r+aum las ye shes kyi gzhal yas
NK060(i)001:6604: don ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i rtags su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dbus kyi lte ba dang lnga/
NK060(i)001:6605: don chos nyid spros dang bral ba mtshon pa'i rtags su rdo rje rab mu khyud dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:6606: don bden pa bzhi mtshon pa'i rtags su gru chad bzhis mdzes par brgyan pa/
NK060(i)001:6607: don bden pa gnyis su med pa mtshon pa'i rtags su bar khyams dang /
NK060(i)001:6608: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i rtags su kun tu dbyibs gru bzhi pa/
NK060(i)001:6609: don rnam par thar pa bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin nas
NK060(i)001:6610: 'jug pa mtshon pa'i rtags su sgo bzhi 'bur sgo
NK060(i)001:6611: yod pas na mu khyud dang ldan pa/
NK060(i)001:6612: gzhi ma nges pa la thabs kyis sna tshogs su snang nas tshim par byed pas na rol mo ste/
NK060(i)001:6613: le'u dang por bshad pa bzhin gzugs kyi lha mo la sogs pa sna tshogs pa sprin phung bzhin du/
NK060(i)001:6614: rang bzhin grub pa'i dbang du phyogs bcu nas 'khrigs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:6616: tha ma'i 'dab mas kun g.yogs pas //
NK060(i)001:6617: ye shes rtsig steng seng mgos bltams //
NK060(i)001:6618: mi 'jigs kha nas mu tig har //
NK060(i)001:6619: pha gu mdzes pa'i bad dang ldan //
NK060(i)001:6620: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed mgul 'khor ldan //
NK060(i)001:6621: gzugs sogs lha mo 'khrigs pa ste //
NK060(i)001:6622: sna tshogs mchod byed rol mo yis //
NK060(i)001:6623: bar snang khams kun sprin phung bzhin //
NK060(i)001:6625: rnal 'byor pa bsgom pa'i dbang du pany+tsa re kha'i phyi/
NK060(i)001:6628: steng gi bya 'dabs kyi 'og /ka thung bcu drug
NK060(i)001:6629: gi phrag /d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed kyi gseb na sprin
NK060(i)001:6630: phung bzhin du mchod pa 'bul ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6631: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ni/
NK060(i)001:6632: rang bzhin grub pa'i dbang du lha nam grub tsa
NK060(i)001:6633: na gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa yang grub
NK060(i)001:6634: la/ rnal 'byor pa bsgom pa'i dbang du gdan bzhi
NK060(i)001:6635: bcu rtsa gnyis na sprul pa 'od zer gyi 'phro
NK060(i)001:6636: 'du can bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis mdzes par brgyan
NK060(i)001:6639: mi 'jigs pa bzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su
NK060(i)001:6640: gzhal yas khang gi dbus kyi lte ba la seng
NK060(i)001:6641: ge dang / stobs bcu lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su shar gyi rtsibs la glang chen dang /
NK060(i)001:6642: rdzu 'phrul bzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su lho'i rtsibs la rta dang /
NK060(i)001:6643: dbang bcu lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su nub kyi rtsibs la khyung dang /
NK060(i)001:6644: phrin las thogs pa med pa'i rtags su byang gi rtsibs la nam mkha' lding ngo //
NK060(i)001:6645: de dag gi tshul ni sems can re re yang
NK060(i)001:6646: mjug ma nang du bsnol ba brgyad brgyad kyis rin
NK060(i)001:6647: po che'i khri chen po 'degs pa'i tshul du yod
NK060(i)001:6648: pa la/ de'i steng na shes rab rang bzhin med pa'i rtags nyi ma/
NK060(i)001:6649: thabs 'gag pa med pa'i rtags zla ba/
NK060(i)001:6650: gang ltar spang kyang skyon gyis mi gos pa'i rtags pad+ma ste/
NK060(i)001:6651: de dag kyang dgos 'dod lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags
NK060(i)001:6652: su rin po che'i khri rkang gis btegs nas gnas
NK060(i)001:6653: pa'o // de ltar lha so so'i gnas su gdan mtho dman gyi rim pa ni/
NK060(i)001:6654: le'u dang por bshad pa bzhin rigs lnga la lnga
NK060(i)001:6655: brtseg /kun bzang yab yum la bzhi brtseg /sems dpa'
NK060(i)001:6656: la gsum brtseg /sgo ba la nyi ma rkyang pa/
NK060(i)001:6657: thub pa la pad+ma rkyang pa re re bsgom par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:6658: gnyis pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bsgom pa la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:6660: bzhugs tshul bzhugs gnas dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:6662: gdan de dag la rigs kyi yab lnga ni/
NK060(i)001:6663: mdzad pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i rtags su mnyam pa'i skyil mo krung dang /
NK060(i)001:6665: rang don gyi mdzad pa brtul nas gzhan don gyi
NK060(i)001:6666: mdzad pa la zhugs pa'i rtags su brtul zhugs kyi
NK060(i)001:6667: skyil mo krung gis yab la 'khyud pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6668: sems dpa' rnams ni mdzad pa yongs su ma rdzogs pas rta babs pa'i tshul la/
NK060(i)001:6669: sems ma rnams kyis g.yon ngos nas 'khyud pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6670: sgo ba yab yum ni gdug pa can 'dul ba'i
NK060(i)001:6671: phyir gyad kyi dor thabs kyis zhal phyir bstan nas
NK060(i)001:6672: bzhugs pa'o // kun bzang yab yum ni mdzad pa rdzoogs pa'i phyir yab rdo rje'i skyil krung dang /
NK060(i)001:6674: thub pa drug 'gro ba'i don la gshegs pa'i phyir 'greng bur bzhugs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6675: gnas ni 'khor lo la rgyal po yab lnga/
NK060(i)001:6676: rgyal mo yum dang bcas pa gtso bo zhal shar
NK060(i)001:6677: du gzigs pa'i dbang du byas nas rtsibs mchan bzhi
NK060(i)001:6678: la g.yas shar lho'i rtsibs mchan la mthong ba sa'i
NK060(i)001:6679: snying po dang nas kyi sgras go rim bzhin/
NK060(i)001:6680: thos pa phyag na rdo rje lho nub kyi rtsibs la yong bar rigs kyang /
NK060(i)001:6682: rim pa ni yi ge'i dbang du gsungs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:6683: gral ni lugs su mthun pa kho na'o zhes pas/
NK060(i)001:6684: g.yon byang shar gyi rtsibs mchan la thos pa phyag na rdo rje/
NK060(i)001:6685: rgyab phyogs kyi g.yas lho nub kyi rtsibs la snom pa nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK060(i)001:6686: g.yon phyogs byang chub kyi rtsibs la myong ba spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang /
NK060(i)001:6687: btsun mo la s+ye ma la sogs pa'i tshogs su bcas pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6688: gru chad bzhi la ni shar lhor mthong byed byams pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6689: lho nub tu thos byed sgrib sel/
NK060(i)001:6690: nub byang du snom byed kun tu bzang po/
NK060(i)001:6691: byang shar du myong byed 'jam dpal rnams btsun mo
NK060(i)001:6692: d+h+au pe la sogs pa'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas
NK060(i)001:6694: shar lho lha la lho phyogs mi //
NK060(i)001:6695: lho nub nub byang yi dwags byol //
NK060(i)001:6696: byang dang byang shar lha min dmyal //
NK060(i)001:6698: bar gyi khyams la ni thub pa drug dang /
NK060(i)001:6699: mdun shar dang rgyab nub tu byed pa kun tu bzang po dang /
NK060(i)001:6700: bya ba kun tu bzang mo dag ni dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:6701: la 'god pa'i skabs su bar khyams la gnas par
NK060(i)001:6702: bstan no // sgo khyud bzhi la gdug pa can 'joms pa shar du gshin rje gshed/
NK060(i)001:6705: byang du bdud rtsi 'khyil ba rnams ni btsun mo
NK060(i)001:6706: lcags kyu ma la sogs pa'i tshogs dang ldan par
NK060(i)001:6707: gnas so // 'o na 'dir zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:6708: gyi skabs su khro bo 'ong bar mi rigs so
NK060(i)001:6709: gnas so // zhe na/ gtso bo'am gtso che ba'i
NK060(i)001:6710: ngos nas zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor yin kyang sgo skyong
NK060(i)001:6711: khro bor byung ba la 'gal ba med do //
NK060(i)001:6713: ston pa kun tu bzang po rgyud kyi bdag po yin pa la khyams la bton nas/
NK060(i)001:6714: rdo rje sems dpa' 'khor gyi gtso bo dbus kyi
NK060(i)001:6715: lte ba la bkod pas dkyil 'khor log pa'i skyon
NK060(i)001:6717: skyon med de rgyal ba drug pa'i thugs rang rig
NK060(i)001:6718: pa nyid sku dang ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK060(i)001:6719: su rang snang ba'i phyir gtso 'khor la bzang ngan
NK060(i)001:6721: go phye ba'i 'khor gyi don du lam stegs kyi
NK060(i)001:6722: ston pa thub drug thugs las sprul pa'i phyir khyams
NK060(i)001:6723: su bkod kyang gtso 'khor log par mi 'gyur te/
NK060(i)001:6724: rtog pa'i dbang du kun kyi byed pa po yid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:6726: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK060(i)001:6727: rang snang rgyal ba'i sems sogs dang //
NK060(i)001:6730: gtso bo la gnyis yin te/
NK060(i)001:6731: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' yin par yang /
NK060(i)001:6733: rdo rjes sems dpa' dkyil yin te //
NK060(i)001:6734: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo 'khor //
NK060(i)001:6736: chos 'chad pa'i gtso bo kun tu bzang po yin te/
NK060(i)001:6739: bdag po kun bzang 'khor lo bskor //
NK060(i)001:6740: bka' sdod skyes bu mdun na gnas //
NK060(i)001:6742: dper na gnas gzhi'i gnas brtan dang /
NK060(i)001:6743: chos grwa'i ston pa lta bu yin gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:6746: 'dir sgyu 'phrul 'bring po'am bsdus pa ltar lha rnams zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:6747: rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag mtshan rdo rje rtse lnga pa/
NK060(i)001:6748: rnam snang gi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa/
NK060(i)001:6749: rin chen 'byung ldan rin po che zur brgyad pa/
NK060(i)001:6750: snang ba mtha' yas pad+ma dkar po/
NK060(i)001:6751: don yod grub pa ral gri so gnyis pa/
NK060(i)001:6752: kun kyang g.yon dril bus yum la 'khyud pa/
NK060(i)001:6753: yum lnga ka yang g.yas dril bu 'dzin pa ste/
NK060(i)001:6754: g.yon rang rtags kyi phyag mtshan yab dang mthun la thams cad kyang 'od 'bar ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6755: sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa ltar zhal gsum phyag drug pa'i dbang du/
NK060(i)001:6758: dril bu pad+ma rin po che //
NK060(i)001:6760: gzhan gang gnas su rdo rje shes //
NK060(i)001:6761: dang po thugs dang g.yon 'khyud pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6763: sems dpa' sems ma'i phyag mtshan ni/
NK060(i)001:6765: byams pa klu shing 'dzin pa la sogs pa'i sogs khongs nas phyag mtshan gzhan rnams kyang 'byung ste/
NK060(i)001:6766: sa snying rin po che myu gu/
NK060(i)001:6768: spyan ras gzigs pad+ma dkar po/
NK060(i)001:6769: phyag na rdo rje rdo rje/
NK060(i)001:6771: kun bzang rin po che'i snye ma bsnyams pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6772: nang gi sems ma bzhi ni mdzes pa'i tshul 'dzin pa ste/
NK060(i)001:6774: m+aa le rin po che'i phreng ba/
NK060(i)001:6776: n+airti gar gyi phu dung ngo //
NK060(i)001:6777: phyi'i sems ma bzhi ni mnyas pa'i yo byad 'dzin pa ste/
NK060(i)001:6779: push+pe me tog /+aa lo ke mar me/
NK060(i)001:6780: gan+d+he dri'i dung chos bsnams pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6781: gzhan yang 'joms pa bzhi'i phyag mtshan ni/
NK060(i)001:6782: gshin rje gshed n+rir mgo gdengs pa can/
NK060(i)001:6783: stobs po che rdo rje rtse lnga pa/
NK060(i)001:6784: rta mgrin thod pa sbrul gyis dkris pa/
NK060(i)001:6785: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba sna tshogs rdo rje'o //
NK060(i)001:6789: kun tu bzang po ni phyag g.yas pa steng du byas pa'i mnyam gzhag la/
NK060(i)001:6790: kun tu bzang mo ni de las ldog pa'i mnyam gzhag gam/
NK060(i)001:6791: yang na thal mo thugs kar sbyar ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6792: thub pa drug po ni lha'i pi wang /
NK060(i)001:6793: lha ma yin gyi go cha/
NK060(i)001:6796: yi dwags kyi rin chen sgrom bu/
NK060(i)001:6797: dmyal ba'i thub pa me chu bsnams pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6798: sku mdog tshul dang bcas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6800: chos nyid mi 'gyur ba mtshon pa'i sku mdog mthing kha bdun te/
NK060(i)001:6803: phyag na rdo rje yab yum/
NK060(i)001:6804: lha ma yin gyi thub pa rnams so //
NK060(i)001:6805: nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa mtshon pa'i sku mdog dkar po lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:6809: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa mtshon pa'i sku mdog ser po lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:6811: nam mkha'i snying po yab yum/
NK060(i)001:6813: 'gro ba don la chags pa mtshon pa'i sku mdog le brgan bzhi ni/
NK060(i)001:6814: snang ba mtha' yas yab yum gnyis/
NK060(i)001:6815: spyan ras gzigs yab yum gnyis so //
NK060(i)001:6816: phrin las sna tshogs pa mtshon pa'i sku mdog ljang gu gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:6817: don yod grub pa yab yum mo //
NK060(i)001:6818: la sogs pa'i sogs khongs nas sna tshogs 'dres pa'i sku mdog bcu dgu ston te/
NK060(i)001:6819: byams pa yab yum dkar ser/
NK060(i)001:6820: sgrib sel yab yum dmar ser/
NK060(i)001:6821: kun bzang yab yum dmar ljang /
NK060(i)001:6823: gshin rje gshed yab yum smug nag /stobs po che
NK060(i)001:6824: yab yum ser nag /rta mgrin yab yum dmar nag
NK060(i)001:6825: /bdud rtsi 'khyil ba yab yum ljang nag /byol song
NK060(i)001:6826: gi thub pa smug nag /yi dwags kyi thub pa
NK060(i)001:6827: ser nag /dmyal ba'i thub pa dud kha'o //
NK060(i)001:6828: de ltar rigs dang rigs 'dres pa'i sku mdog thams
NK060(i)001:6829: cad kyang re re'ang rang bzhin gyi sku mdog bzhi
NK060(i)001:6833: kun muta ltar snum la 'dril ba/
NK060(i)001:6834: dung ltar nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'o //
NK060(i)001:6835: de lta bu'i lha tshogs thams cad kyang zhi ba'i tshul dgu dgu dang ldan pa ste/
NK060(i)001:6836: nga rgyal ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags su yan lag gser zhun ma ltar mnyen pa/
NK060(i)001:6837: zhe sdang ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags su phyag sor sbrul gyi mjug ma ltar du lcug pa/
NK060(i)001:6838: 'dod chags ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags su
NK060(i)001:6839: thabs shes rab g.yu'i ljang pa ltar du phan tshun
NK060(i)001:6840: 'khril ba/ gti mug ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i
NK060(i)001:6841: rtags su sku sked thang shing lta du drang zhi
NK060(i)001:6842: 'khril ba/ ldem pa/ phrag dog ma spangs gnas su
NK060(i)001:6843: dag pa'i rtags su byis pa lo brgyad pa ltar
NK060(i)001:6844: 'khril ba/ ldem pa/ gzhon tshul can/ thugs la ma
NK060(i)001:6845: rig pa med pa'i rtags su zla ba ltar gsal
NK060(i)001:6846: 'khril ba/ ldem pa/ gzhon tshul can/ ba/ che ba'i
NK060(i)001:6847: yon tan lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su nyi ma
NK060(i)001:6848: 'khril ba/ ldem pa/ gzhon tshul can/ ba/ ltar 'tsher
NK060(i)001:6849: ba/ mtshan dpe yongs su rdzogs pa'i rtags su dbus
NK060(i)001:6850: kyi ri rgyal ltar lhun sdug pa/
NK060(i)001:6851: thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i rtags su seng ge 'bum gzhibs pa ltar gzi byin dang ldan pa/
NK060(i)001:6852: ba spu'i bu ga re re nas kyang gsal la rno ba'i 'od zer dkar/
NK060(i)001:6858: re re yang bye ba phrag drug drug 'phro ba'i tshogs chen po/
NK060(i)001:6859: khyad par du khro bo rnams ni me dpung 'bar
NK060(i)001:6860: ba'i phreng ba rdo rje rtse lnga'i rnam pas 'khrigs
NK060(i)001:6861: pa'i tshul can te zhes pa'am/
NK060(i)001:6862: yang na tshul dgu dang ldan pa zhi ba'i lha rnams 'od zer 'phro ba'i tshogs chen po can/
NK060(i)001:6863: gar dgu dang ldan pa'i khro bo khro mo rnams
NK060(i)001:6864: 'bar ba'i phreng bas 'khrigs pa can zhes kyang bya'o
NK060(i)001:6865: // gsum pa dkyil 'khor gyi che ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6867: chos kyi dbyings mtha' dbus med par ye shes kyis
NK060(i)001:6868: khyab pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni yon
NK060(i)001:6870: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsgoms pa'i
NK060(i)001:6871: mthus rang bzhin 'bras bu lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:6873: spyi don gsum pa rang gzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor la bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:6877: sku'i dkyil 'khor byung ba'i byin rlabs so //
NK060(i)001:6880: 'di la spyir gyi sku zhes pa ni rten byed pa zhig yin la/
NK060(i)001:6881: skabs 'dir 'bras bu'i chos sam yon tan gyi rten byed pa'i ngos nas sku zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:6882: sku'i phyag rgya chen po las mchog tu gyur pa
NK060(i)001:6883: ni zung 'jug sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa drug
NK060(i)001:6884: pa spyi'i gzugs can zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:6885: de ltar sku gcig gis ldog cha la bye brag tu phye na/
NK060(i)001:6886: dbyings gtso che ba'i ngos nas chos kyi sku/
NK060(i)001:6887: de nyid smin pa rgya mtsho'i 'khor gyi ngo la nges pa lnga ldan du snang ba longs sku/
NK060(i)001:6888: mos pa rgya mtsho'i 'khor gyi ngos la ma nges pa lnga ldan du snang ba sprul sku/
NK060(i)001:6889: sku gsum snang cha la ma 'dres pa'i ngos nas mngon byang gi sku/
NK060(i)001:6890: dbyer mi phyed pa'i ngos nas rdo rje'i skur bzhag pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:6891: de yang gnyis su med pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings las ma g.yos pa chos kyi sku'o //
NK060(i)001:6892: de nyid kyang spang bya med pas na yang dag
NK060(i)001:6893: pa ste 'ching ba'i mdud pa gnyis las thar ba
NK060(i)001:6894: thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan dpes brgyan pa'i gzugs
NK060(i)001:6895: can longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK060(i)001:6896: 'gro ba drug ma lus pa 'dul ba'i dgos ched yod pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:6897: gdul bya dang mthun par byas pa'i sku ni bsam
NK060(i)001:6898: gyis mi khyab par rnam pa sna tshogs pa ston
NK060(i)001:6900: sku sna tshogs su ston pa nyid sgyu ma'am mig
NK060(i)001:6901: yor dang 'dra ba'i tshul du snang yang bden par
NK060(i)001:6902: ma grub pa'i dpes mtshon nas/
NK060(i)001:6903: gzugs sku gnyis kyi tshul de nyid kyang chos kyi
NK060(i)001:6904: dbyings las g.yos pa med pas chos sku dang gzugs
NK060(i)001:6905: sku dbyer mi phyed pas na rdo rje'i sku zhes
NK060(i)001:6906: bya'o // de nyid las ma g.yos bzhin du sku
NK060(i)001:6907: lnga ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa nyid gdul
NK060(i)001:6908: bya'i blo'i rim pa dang mthun par sna tshogs su
NK060(i)001:6909: snang ba'i tshul ni mngon par byang ba'i sku'o //
NK060(i)001:6910: de ltar sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa de'i tshe/
NK060(i)001:6911: gdul bya'i las mi mthun pa sna tshogs pa la
NK060(i)001:6912: sku lnga ngo bo so so dang 'dra bar gdul
NK060(i)001:6913: bya la snang ba ni de bzhin nyid kyi ngang
NK060(i)001:6915: ma bcos kyang gdul bya'i las 'phro'i dbang gis sku lnga so sor snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:6918: dper na me long ma g.yos par bzhin gyi gzugs
NK060(i)001:6919: brnyan snang ba dang chu zlas chu skyogs thams cad
NK060(i)001:6920: du khyab par snang ba bzhin du/
NK060(i)001:6921: sems can gyi don mdzad pa de'i tshe gdul bya
NK060(i)001:6922: 'gro ba rigs drug po thams cad la sdig pa
NK060(i)001:6923: spong ba thub pa drug gi gzugs su rnam par
NK060(i)001:6925: de bzhin du dge tshul nyan thos pa rnams la 'phags pa dgra bcom pa'i gzugs dang /
NK060(i)001:6926: rang rgyal rnams la rigs mthun pas don byed pa
NK060(i)001:6927: bse ru'am ne tso lta bu'i tshul du bstan nas
NK060(i)001:6928: don mdzad do // 'o na rang sangs rgyas kyi nges tshig nyams so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:6930: chos bshad sdud kyis don mi byed pas rang rgyal du bzhag kyang /
NK060(i)001:6931: rigs mthun pa'i sgo nas don shugs la grub ste/
NK060(i)001:6932: rigs mthun 'bras bu ne tso'am bse ru lta bu
NK060(i)001:6933: thos pa grogs po gnyis kyi lo rgyus bzhin no
NK060(i)001:6934: // de las gzhan yang theg pa chung ngu las
NK060(i)001:6935: spags pa theg pa mchog la rim pa bzhin du
NK060(i)001:6936: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi ngo la sh+aakya thub
NK060(i)001:6937: // pa/ kri ya la rigs gsum/
NK060(i)001:6939: nang ba gnyis la kun tu bzang por snang nas don mdzad do //
NK060(i)001:6940: gsum pa sku'i 'grub tshul gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:6941: byang chub sems dpa' sgrib pa sbyong zhing 'bras bu 'grub tshul dang /
NK060(i)001:6945: sgrib pa sbyong zhing 'bras bu 'grub tshul/
NK060(i)001:6947: 'og min chen po bla na med pa'i gnas mchog
NK060(i)001:6948: tu sku ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku rnam par
NK060(i)001:6950: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams
NK060(i)001:6951: la chos ston tshul ni sprul sku'i tshig tu gsung
NK060(i)001:6952: ba de bzhin du longs sku ni gsung mchog tshig
NK060(i)001:6953: tu smra ste/ 'o na chos ji ltar ston zhe na/
NK060(i)001:6954: sku'i brda yis chos rnams 'khor gyi blo la 'jal bar ston pa ni/
NK060(i)001:6955: dper na me long bstan pas byad dngos kyi mdog
NK060(i)001:6956: ngan dri ma dang khyem thams cad ngos zhin nas
NK060(i)001:6957: sel bar byed pa'i tshul bzhin du 'khor gyi byang
NK060(i)001:6958: chub sems dpa' rnams kyis de bzhin gshegs pa longs
NK060(i)001:6959: spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la bltas na byang chub sems
NK060(i)001:6960: dpa' la sgrib pa gtig dpag tu med pa zhig
NK060(i)001:6961: 'dug pa de/ me long gi nang du gzugs brnyan
NK060(i)001:6962: shar ba bzhin du ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:6963: 'dug pa de/ sku la bltas pas/ bsgribs par snang
NK060(i)001:6964: nas byang chub sems dpa'i sgrib pa ngos zin no
NK060(i)001:6965: 'dug pa de/ sku la bltas pas/ // de ji ltar zhe na/
NK060(i)001:6966: ngos zin tshul ni bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:6967: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang gcig dang du ma las/
NK060(i)001:6969: byang chub sems dpa' sems can gyi rgyud du 'dug pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6970: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni ye shes sgyu ma'i sku skye 'jig dang bral bar 'dug la/
NK060(i)001:6971: byang chub sems dpa' smon lam gyi lus skye 'jig can du 'dug pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6972: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la mnyam par gzhag 'jog mi mnga' la/
NK060(i)001:6973: byang chub sems dpa'i mnyam par gzhag dgos kyi 'dug pa dang /
NK060(i)001:6974: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku kha sbyor gyi
NK060(i)001:6975: bde ba la gnas kyang nyes skyon gyis mi gos
NK060(i)001:6976: la/ byang chub sems dpa' thabs dang mi ldan na
NK060(i)001:6977: lam la 'khrul pas gos yod pas kyang sgrib pa
NK060(i)001:6978: ngos zin no zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung
NK060(i)001:6979: la/ ngo // yang de nas sa bcu'i rim gyis byang zhes pa 'di la/
NK060(i)001:6981: spar khab mkhan gyis lang ka'i mdo'i lung drangs nas/
NK060(i)001:6982: sa dang po nas bcu pa'i bar gyi sdig pa 'byang bar gsungs pas/
NK060(i)001:6983: de'i rjes su 'brangs nas byang chub sems dpa' sa
NK060(i)001:6984: dang po la sangs rgyas kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK060(i)001:6985: byin gyis brlabs nas/ de ma thag tu byang chub
NK060(i)001:6986: sems dpa' theg pa chen po la rab tu snang
NK060(i)001:6987: ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la 'jug ste/
NK060(i)001:6988: zhugs ma thag tu phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi zhal mthong zhing sgrib pa ngos zin la/
NK060(i)001:6989: de nas sa bcu pa chos kyi sprin gyi bar
NK060(i)001:6990: du sa'i mi mthun phyogs sam sgrib pa rim gyi
NK060(i)001:6991: 'byang ba yin te/ de la de bzhin gshegs pa
NK060(i)001:6992: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i zhal dang phyag gi dbang
NK060(i)001:6993: 'byang ba yin te/ bskur nas/ rdo rje lta bu'i
NK060(i)001:6994: ting nge 'dzin mngon du byas pas shes bya'i sgrib
NK060(i)001:6995: pa bag la nyal 'joms pa bla na med pa'i
NK060(i)001:6996: byang chub yang dag pa kun tu 'od chos kyi
NK060(i)001:6997: 'byang ba yin te/ bskur nas/ sku 'thob bo // kha cig na re/
NK060(i)001:6998: de ltar yin na sa dang po sprul sku'i 'khor dang /
NK060(i)001:6999: sa bcu pa longs sku'i 'khor du bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:7000: sa dang po pa longs sku'i dbang bskur ba'i 'khor min kyang /
NK060(i)001:7001: zhal mthong gi 'khor yin pas mi 'gal te/
NK060(i)001:7003: byung ba'i mun pa sangs nas rdzogs longs spyod pa mngon du snang ngo //
NK060(i)001:7006: 'du byed nyon mongs pa phra rags kyi sgrib pa
NK060(i)001:7007: dag nas 'khor ba'i sa bon dang bral te sa
NK060(i)001:7008: non pas/ longs spyod rdzogs pa'i zhal mthong bar 'gyur ro zhes gsungs pas mngon no //
NK060(i)001:7010: le'u dang por yang gleng gzhi gcig byung /
NK060(i)001:7013: le'u bco lnga par yang byung bas gleng gzhi ba'i bzhi ldabs so zer na/
NK060(i)001:7015: le'u dang por byung ba ni bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi yin la/
NK060(i)001:7016: le'u gsum par thun mong gi ston pa thub drug gi gleng gzhi yin la/
NK060(i)001:7017: 'dir 'bras bu 'grub tshul gyi shugs la gleng bzhi smos pa yin/
NK060(i)001:7018: le'u bco lnga par gdul bya dgos ched kyi gleng gzhi bstan pa yin pas ldabs pa med do //
NK060(i)001:7019: 'bras bu'i ngo bo sku gsum mo //
NK060(i)001:7021: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa glo bur gyi
NK060(i)001:7022: dri ma dang bral ba de 'bras bu'i yon tan
NK060(i)001:7023: thams cad kyi rten du gyur pas na sku ste/
NK060(i)001:7024: blos dpag tu med tshig tu brjod du med pa'i
NK060(i)001:7025: don mngon du gyur pa ni ye shes kyi tshogs
NK060(i)001:7026: rdzogs shing rang don grub pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:7027: gzhan don du gzugs sku gnyis kyi phrin las mi 'gag par 'byung ba na/
NK060(i)001:7028: bsod nams kyi tshogs yongs su rdzogs pa'i mthu las
NK060(i)001:7029: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yon tan zad pa med
NK060(i)001:7030: pa nor bu rin cen gyi gter lta bu dang
NK060(i)001:7031: / sprul pa'i sku bye ba phrag brgya la sogs
NK060(i)001:7032: pa bsam gyis mi khyab par snang nas sems can
NK060(i)001:7034: sngags kyi 'grub tshul la yang gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:7036: sangs rgyas kyi sa gnyis bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:7039: thabs dang shes rab sa yi mchog /ces pa 'dir blangs te/
NK060(i)001:7040: thabs ma 'gag par sku gsung thugs kyi mdzad pas 'gro ba'i don byed pa dang /
NK060(i)001:7041: dmigs pa med pa'i shes rab kyis ji ltar spyad
NK060(i)001:7042: kyang nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pas na sa'i
NK060(i)001:7043: mchog ste ma chags pad+ma can gyi sa'o //
NK060(i)001:7044: thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis
NK060(i)001:7045: dang dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu po thams cad
NK060(i)001:7046: rdzogs shing / snang grags kyi spyod yul ma lus
NK060(i)001:7047: pa kun kyang bdag nyid las mi gzhan pa'i phyir
NK060(i)001:7048: na bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor du shar bas
NK060(i)001:7049: ma da la zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:7050: dkyil 'khor gyi sgras snying po len pa bsod nams
NK060(i)001:7051: dang ye shes kyi tshogs chen gnyis kyang ma btsal
NK060(i)001:7052: bar lhun grub tu rdzogs par rol ba'o //
NK060(i)001:7053: yon tan gsum po de la sogs te sogs khongs
NK060(i)001:7054: nas yon tan bsam yas pa dang ldan pa'i mchog
NK060(i)001:7055: ni yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa'o //
NK060(i)001:7058: sems nyid ye nas skye shi med pa'i phyir skad
NK060(i)001:7059: cig ma'i skye 'jig las 'das pas na ngo bo
NK060(i)001:7061: 'gyur ba med pa g.yung drung chos kyi sku'o //
NK060(i)001:7062: sdug bsngal gyi nyam thag cing nyon mongs pa'i gdul
NK060(i)001:7063: bya kun gyi tshogs gnyis bsags pa'i zhing du gyur
NK060(i)001:7064: pa sprul pa'i sku'i 'byung gnas de nyid zag pa
NK060(i)001:7065: med pa'i longs spyod zad mi shes pa 'byung ba'i
NK060(i)001:7066: gter du 'gyur pa ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o
NK060(i)001:7067: // sku gsum dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje rang
NK060(i)001:7068: rig pa'i ngang du mi 'bral bar 'dzin pa ste
NK060(i)001:7070: sku gsum la sogs pa thams cad rig pa rang
NK060(i)001:7071: snang ba'i cha nas dbyer med kyang snang cha ma
NK060(i)001:7072: 'dres pa'i cha nas sku dang ye shes du mar
NK060(i)001:7073: snang zhing bzang ngan med par mnyam pa mngon par
NK060(i)001:7077: 'dul ba'i thabs la sogs pa thams cad ji snyed
NK060(i)001:7078: pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gang la gang 'dul
NK060(i)001:7079: de la der bstan nas don mdzad pa sprul pa'i
NK060(i)001:7080: sku'o // des na ma chags pad+ma can dang yi
NK060(i)001:7081: ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa gnyis thob pa
NK060(i)001:7082: de'i tshe sku lnga po kun kyang dus gcig la
NK060(i)001:7085: sku'i bshad pa lan gsum byung bas ldabs so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:7087: sku yi phyag rgya che mchog ni //
NK060(i)001:7088: zhes pa la sogs pa ni/
NK060(i)001:7089: 'bras bu sngags kyi sku'i mtshan nyid ma 'dres pa'i
NK060(i)001:7090: sgo nas bzhag /chos sku dpag med brjod du med
NK060(i)001:7091: // ces pa la sogs pa ni/
NK060(i)001:7092: mtshan nyid kyi sku gsum gyi sgo nas bzhag /skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung sku //
NK060(i)001:7094: mthar thug 'bras bu sku lnga yongs su rdzogs pa'i sgo nas bzhag pa'o //
NK060(i)001:7095: 'o na rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i sku gsum dang /
NK060(i)001:7096: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg pa'i sku gsum la khyad par ci yod ce na/
NK060(i)001:7099: chos sku'i khyad par la'ang gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:7102: byin rlabs kyi khyad par dang gsum las/
NK060(i)001:7103: dang po rgyu mtshan nyid kyi chos sku ni stong nyid spros dang bral ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:7104: sngags kyi chos sku snang stong zung 'jug yin te/
NK060(i)001:7106: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK060(i)001:7107: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK060(i)001:7108: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK060(i)001:7110: gnyis pa ni rgyu'i chos sku stong pa'i mar lhung la/
NK060(i)001:7111: sngags kyi chos sku snang stong gnyis su med pas mthar ma lhung ngo //
NK060(i)001:7112: gsum pa ni rgyu'i chos sku la byin rlabs gzugs sku gnyis las mi 'char la/
NK060(i)001:7113: sngags kyi chos sku snang stong dbyer med kyi byin
NK060(i)001:7114: rlabs sku lnga la sogs pa cir yang 'char ro
NK060(i)001:7115: // gzugs sku gnyis kyi khyad par yang gsum las/
NK060(i)001:7116: dang po rgyu mtshan nyid kyi gzugs sku gnyis rgyu rkyen las byung la/
NK060(i)001:7117: sngags kyi gzugs sku rgyu rkyen gyis bskyed pa ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:7119: rgyu rkyen rag lus med pa'i phyir //
NK060(i)001:7121: gnyis pa ni rgyu'i gzugs sku skye 'jig can yin la/
NK060(i)001:7122: sngags kyi gzugs sku skye 'jig dang bral ba yin te/
NK060(i)001:7124: sgyu ma rdo rje btsan po mchog /ces gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:7125: gsum pa la yang gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:7128: longs sku'i khyad par la'ang gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:7129: longs spyod bya yul gyi khyad par ni/
NK060(i)001:7130: mtshan nyid kyi dkar po'i phyogs la longs spyod pa las/
NK060(i)001:7131: nag po'i phyogs la longs mi spyod la/
NK060(i)001:7132: sngags kyi gnyis ka la longs spyod do //
NK060(i)001:7133: longs spyod byed thabs kyi khyad par ni/
NK060(i)001:7134: mtshan nyid la nag po'i phyogs la spyod pa'i thabs med la/
NK060(i)001:7135: sngags la dkar nag gnyis ka la spyod pa'i thabs yod pas so //
NK060(i)001:7136: sprul sku gnyis kyi khyad par la yang gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:7137: gdul bya yul gyi khyad par ni/
NK060(i)001:7138: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi sprul skus dkar phyogs kyi gdul bya las/
NK060(i)001:7139: nag phyogs kyi gdul bya mi 'dul lo //
NK060(i)001:7140: sngags kyi sprul skus gdul bya la phyogs ris med pas so //
NK060(i)001:7141: 'dul byed thabs kyi khyad par ni/
NK060(i)001:7142: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi sprul sku la nag phyogs 'dul ba'i thabs med la/
NK060(i)001:7143: sngags kyi sprul skus dkar phyogs dang nag phyogs gnyis ka 'dul ba'i thabs dang ldan pas so //
NK060(i)001:7144: de'i phyir dbyer med rdo rje dang mngon par byang
NK060(i)001:7145: chub pa'i sku gnyis kyis kyang 'phags par shes par
NK060(i)001:7146: bya'o // zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:7148: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung sku //
NK060(i)001:7149: zhes pa la sogs pa sngags kyi lam ma byung bar 'bras bu 'byung ba ci zhe na/
NK060(i)001:7150: rim gyis 'jug pa'i dbang du rgyu'i theg pa la sbyangs nas 'bras bu'i theg par 'jug pas sam/
NK060(i)001:7151: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin sku'i dkyil 'khor dang rjes
NK060(i)001:7152: su mthun pa'i phyir byung ba yang yin no zhes
NK060(i)001:7153: gsung ngo // bzhi pa sku'i dkyil 'khor byung ba'i byin rlabs so //
NK060(i)001:7155: zhes rang bzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor gyi don de dag
NK060(i)001:7156: brjod pas 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i gdul bya'i
NK060(i)001:7157: gnas mtha' yas par mu med pa thams cad du
NK060(i)001:7158: sku'i dkyil 'khor gyi rol pa brjod kyis mi lang
NK060(i)001:7159: ba zhing gi rdul snyed du rang bzhin sku'i dkyil
NK060(i)001:7160: 'khor rang rig pa la gsal bar gyur to //
NK060(i)001:7161: gzhung bsdus pa la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:7162: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:7164: gzhung rgyas par bstan pas na de/
NK060(i)001:7165: bsdus te bstan pas na nas/
NK060(i)001:7166: de bzhin gshegs pa yab btsun mo'i tshogs te yum
NK060(i)001:7167: rnams dang thabs shes gnyis su med pa lhun gyis
NK060(i)001:7168: grub pa'i dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi nyams su
NK060(i)001:7169: myong dka' ba'i gsang ba 'di nyid sku dang gsung
NK060(i)001:7170: dang thugs dang yon tan dang phrin las dbyer mi
NK060(i)001:7171: phyed pa'i rdo rje las bsdu ba'i tshig 'di dag
NK060(i)001:7175: zhes pa ni snod bcud sku dang ye shes su gsal ba la mnyes pa'i tshig go //
NK060(i)001:7176: dmigs bya chos kyi dbyings dang /
NK060(i)001:7177: dmigs byed rig pa'i ye shes gnyis su mi dmigs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:7178: blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa'i ting nge 'dzin dpag med yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa/
NK060(i)001:7179: gang du bsdu na 'dir bsdu la/
NK060(i)001:7180: gang bsdu na ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor/
NK060(i)001:7181: ya ki na ye shes zhes pas nas/
NK060(i)001:7182: spyod ces pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:7183: thams cad sku dang ye shes su lhun gyis grub
NK060(i)001:7184: pa la dbang sgyur bas rang rig pa nyid lhag
NK060(i)001:7185: pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor sna tshogs brjod
NK060(i)001:7186: kyi mi lang bar snang ba/
NK060(i)001:7188: gang na gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:7189: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor/
NK060(i)001:7190: ya ki na de nas zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:7191: lhun gyis grub ces pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:7192: gdul bya las dag pa la mnyam pa dang ma dag pa la mi mnyam pa/
NK060(i)001:7193: gnyis ka la kun tu khyab par don mdzad kyang /
NK060(i)001:7194: khyab bya khyab byed gnyis med du khyab pa snang stong gnyis su med pa'i dbyings/
NK060(i)001:7196: gang na rang bzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor/
NK060(i)001:7197: ya ki na sku'i zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:7198: bsam yas mchog ces pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:7199: ye gdod ma nas sku lnga po kun kyang gnyis
NK060(i)001:7200: su med pa lhun gyis grub par gsal ba'i dkyil
NK060(i)001:7201: 'khor du rang snang ba rnams rnam par 'phros kyang
NK060(i)001:7202: spros pa'i mtshan ma med pa/
NK060(i)001:7203: gang du bsdu na 'dir bsdu la/
NK060(i)001:7204: gang bsdu na sngags kyi sku lnga bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:7205: sku'i dkyil 'khor byung ba'i byin rlabs/
NK060(i)001:7206: ya ki na skye shi zhes pa nas/
NK060(i)001:7207: gsal bar gyur to zhes pa'i bar de sdud/
NK060(i)001:7209: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi don la mnyes pa'o //
NK060(i)001:7210: bka' gsang sngags mtshon pa'i tshig go //
NK060(i)001:7212: zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o zhes pa 'bru mthun no //
NK060(i)001:7215: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las mtshan gyi gzhi 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:7218: rang bzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor spros pa'i gcod cing mtshams
NK060(i)001:7219: 'dzin pas na le'u ste yas bgrangs drug pa'i don
NK060(i)001:7220: du gada'o////da ni le'u bdun pa ston par byed pa
NK060(i)001:7221: la/ chos tshoms ngos bzung ba ni/
NK060(i)001:7222: rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las/
NK060(i)001:7223: lam dang 'bras bu gtso bor ston/
NK060(i)001:7226: lam la thabs grol gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:7229: lam dang 'bras bu'i snang ba ston/
NK060(i)001:7232: 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las rgyud don/
NK060(i)001:7235: dkyil 'khor gyi zhor la dbang sngags ting nge 'dzin phrin las rnams ston/
NK060(i)001:7236: tha ma'i chos tshoms bcu las/
NK060(i)001:7237: ldem dgongs man ngag /tshad ma bkag gzhung /
NK060(i)001:7240: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:7241: de ltar ston pa'i le'u bdun pa 'di la 'di chings gsum/
NK060(i)001:7243: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:7245: le'u drug par sku'i dkyil 'khor bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:7246: da gsung gi dkyil 'khor ston pas na de nas zhes 'brel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:7247: de bzhin gshegs pa yab btsun mo'i tshogs te/
NK060(i)001:7248: yum rnams dang bcas pa thams cad kyi sku dang
NK060(i)001:7249: gsung dang thugs gnyis su med pa'i rdo rje las
NK060(i)001:7250: le'u'i gzhung don 'og nas 'byung ba 'di dag phyung
NK060(i)001:7251: ngo // le'u'i gzhung la spyi don gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:7252: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)001:7253: dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlabs pa'i sngags dang /
NK060(i)001:7254: rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK060(i)001:7255: de yang dang po lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor ston pa'i skabs 'dir/
NK060(i)001:7256: mngon par rtogs pa'i go rim sdebs ma shes na
NK060(i)001:7257: bdud rtsi'i ro nyams lta bu'i bshad pa'i skyon yod
NK060(i)001:7260: lta ba brgal brtag gi bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:7261: dam tshig rnam grangs kyi bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:7262: phrin las chog sdebs kyi bshad pa gsum las/
NK060(i)001:7263: 'dir zhi ba'i mngon par rtogs pa'am/
NK060(i)001:7264: phrin las kyi rim pa sdebs la bshad do //
NK060(i)001:7265: de yang rgyas par las gzhung las shes pas/
NK060(i)001:7266: 'dir bsdus pa tsam zhig sdebs pa'i dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:7277: nang dang phyi'i mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa rnams sgrub thabs kyi las byang ltar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7278: dngos gzhi las gzhung la brgyad yod pa las/
NK060(i)001:7279: dang po sems bskyed pa ni le'u gnyis pa ltar bskyed do //
NK060(i)001:7280: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa le'u lnga pa ltar ro //
NK060(i)001:7281: dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa sgrub ltar la/
NK060(i)001:7282: gzhal yas khang dang lha bskyed pa'i sngags le'u 'di nas bshad pa ltar ro //
NK060(i)001:7283: tshig gi gsal gdab pa drug pa ltar ro //
NK060(i)001:7284: dbang bskur byin rlabs 'di nas bshad pa ltar ro //
NK060(i)001:7285: spyan drang pa la sogs pa yang 'di ltar ro //
NK060(i)001:7286: gsum pa snyan gsan dbab cing /
NK060(i)001:7288: phyag nas brtsams te rol mo ye shes kyi bar du dbul lo //
NK060(i)001:7290: drug pa dngos grub blang ba dang /
NK060(i)001:7291: bdun pa smon lam gdab pa dang /
NK060(i)001:7292: brgyad pa 'dzab bzlas pa rnams sgrub thabs ltar ro //
NK060(i)001:7293: mjug gi las kyi rim pa/
NK060(i)001:7297: dkyil 'khor bsdu ba yan chad sgrub thabs nas byung ba bzhin bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7298: spyi don dang po lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gsung
NK060(i)001:7299: gi dkyil 'khor ston par byed pa 'di la bzhi
NK060(i)001:7300: ste/ rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i sngags dang /
NK060(i)001:7301: brten pa lha bskyed pa'i sngags dang /
NK060(i)001:7302: spyan drang pa la sogs pa las kyi rim pa'i sngags dang /
NK060(i)001:7306: b+h+r+aum cir yang 'gyur ba'i sa bon yin kyang /
NK060(i)001:7307: skabs 'dir gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i sa bon du 'gyur la/
NK060(i)001:7308: bi shwa bi shud+d+he ni 'byung ba lngar 'dzin gyi
NK060(i)001:7309: rtog pa sna tshogs dag pa gzhal yas khang bskyed
NK060(i)001:7310: pa'i sngags te/ de yang thal rgyud las/
NK060(i)001:7311: b+h+r+aum dbyibs b+ha gar sna tshogs 'dus //
NK060(i)001:7312: las dang ngo bo dag pa nyid //
NK060(i)001:7313: sangs rgyas rin chen za ma tog /byin rlabs skyon phyir sngags su brjod //
NK060(i)001:7315: gnyis pa brten pa lha bskyed pa'i sngags la drug ste/
NK060(i)001:7317: rigs lnga yab yum bcu bskyed pa'i sngags/
NK060(i)001:7320: badz+ra d+h+rika ni bskyed pa'i sngags te/
NK060(i)001:7322: rdor sems mthing ga rdo rje rtse lnga 'dzin pa'o //
NK060(i)001:7323: rtsa sngags dang bskyed sngags sgril ba ni bzlas pa las kyi sngags su shes par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:7324: 'chad par 'gyur ba'i sngags thams cad des 'agre'o //
NK060(i)001:7327: dz+ai na dzika rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags/
NK060(i)001:7329: rat+na d+h+rika rin 'byung ser po rin po che 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7331: a ro lika snang ba mtha' yas dmar po pad+ma 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7333: pradz+ny+aa d+h+rika don grub ljang gu ral gri 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags te/
NK060(i)001:7334: thams cad kyang phyag g.yas pa rang rig gi phyag mtshan thugs kar 'dzin cing /
NK060(i)001:7335: g.yon pa dril bu 'dzin pas yum la 'khyud pa bskyed do //
NK060(i)001:7337: tsit+ta'i khams lnga'i shi ra la //
NK060(i)001:7338: rdo rje rgyal po rin chen chos //
NK060(i)001:7339: shes rab rigs ldan bcud kyi gzugs //
NK060(i)001:7340: nges par 'dzin pa gsang ba'i sngags //
NK060(i)001:7343: d+h+aa t+w+ai shwa r+ai zhe sdang dga' ma ste rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma bskyed pa'i sngags/
NK060(i)001:7345: dwe sha ra ti gti mug dga' ma ste de bzhin dbyings phyug ma'i/
NK060(i)001:7347: mo ha ra ti nga rgyal dga' ma ste rin chen dbyings phyug ma'i/
NK060(i)001:7349: r+aa ga ra ti 'dod chags dga' ma ste pad+ma dbyings phyug ma'i/
NK060(i)001:7351: badz+ra ra ti phrag dog dga' ma ste las kyi dbyings phyug ma'i bskyed sngags so //
NK060(i)001:7352: de ltar dbyings phyug lnga gar yang sku mdog yab dang thun pa la/
NK060(i)001:7353: phyag g.yas pa dril bu 'dzin pa yab kyi mgul nas 'khyud pa/
NK060(i)001:7354: g.yon par rang rtags kyi phyag mtshan thugs kar 'dzin par bskyed do //
NK060(i)001:7356: de nyid dwangs ma'i ye shes lnga //
NK060(i)001:7357: ma rig gnyis sogs bzhi po dang //
NK060(i)001:7358: mi phyed phrag dog rdo rje sngags //
NK060(i)001:7359: dbyings su skyob pa dga' mar brjod //
NK060(i)001:7361: nang sems yab yum brgyad kyi bskyed sngags/
NK060(i)001:7364: hi r+aa dza ya sa snying dkar po myu gu 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags/
NK060(i)001:7366: +aa gar+b+h+ya ya nam snying ser po ral gri 'dzin pa/
NK060(i)001:7368: ha h+aum pad+ma pa da ma spyan ras gzigs dmar po pad+ma dkar po 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7370: ku ru p+aa na hri phyag rdor mthing kha rdo rje 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7372: l+aa s+ye ma sa ya s+t+wam l+aa s+ye dkar mo me long 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7374: m+aa le sa ma ye ho m+aa le ser mo phreng ba 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7376: gi rti ra go ham g+ai rti dmar mo pi wang 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7378: ni rti t+aa ga ya mi ni rti ljang gu gar gyi phu dung 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags so //
NK060(i)001:7380: las kyi bde bas sgeg pa ni //
NK060(i)001:7381: chags pa'i dam tshig dus yin no //
NK060(i)001:7382: slar yang lan gyis 'brel ba ni //
NK060(i)001:7383: gnyis ka dgyes pa'i mchog tu bshad //
NK060(i)001:7384: ha dang si yi bde sgra dang //
NK060(i)001:7385: bdag gis chags pa thob pa'o //
NK060(i)001:7386: shin tu bskyod pa'i bde ba dag /kun nas bskyod pa rlung zhes bya //
NK060(i)001:7388: phyi sems yab yum brgyad kyi bskyed sngags/
NK060(i)001:7391: d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa byams pa dkar ser glu shing 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags/
NK060(i)001:7393: sa ram pa ya s+w+aa h+aa sgrib sel dmar ser chos kyi 'khor lo 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7395: sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa kun bzang dmar ljang rin chen snye ma 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7397: sh+ri am r+aa g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa 'jam dpal dkar ljang ut+pala 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7399: d+h+au pe pra pe sha ya d+h+au pe ma dkar ser sbos me dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7401: push+pe a be sha ya push+pe ma dmar ser me tog 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7403: d+ai ba su ki n+aa mar me ma dmar ljang ras kyi sdong bu 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7405: gan+d+he tsit+ta dri chab ma dkar ljang dung chos 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags so //
NK060(i)001:7408: de nyid phye ba las 'byung ba'o //
NK060(i)001:7409: me tog bsdus pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK060(i)001:7410: bdag po'i zhal du thim par bshad //
NK060(i)001:7411: shin tu bsdams pa'i rim la byung //
NK060(i)001:7412: gsal ba'i ye shes bde ba che //
NK060(i)001:7413: kun gsal brjod dang 'dra ba'i sgra //
NK060(i)001:7414: gnyis med thugs su chud par bya //
NK060(i)001:7416: sgo ba yab yum gyii bskyed sngags/
NK060(i)001:7419: ya m+aan+ta krita phata gshin rje smug nag mi mgo kha gdangs pa 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags/
NK060(i)001:7421: big+h+n+aan+ta krita phata bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang nag rgya gram gnon thabs su 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7423: pad+m+aan+ta krita phata rta mgrin dmar nag thod pa sbrul gyis dkris pa 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7425: pradz+ny+aan+ta krita phata stobs chen ser nag thod pa rdo rjes gnon thabs su 'dzin pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7427: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa
NK060(i)001:7428: r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata lcags kyu ma smug
NK060(i)001:7431: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa
NK060(i)001:7432: r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata zhags pa ma ser
NK060(i)001:7435: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa
NK060(i)001:7436: r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata lcags sgrogs ma dmar
NK060(i)001:7439: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa
NK060(i)001:7440: r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata dril bu ma ljang
NK060(i)001:7441: nag dril bu 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags so //
NK060(i)001:7442: kun bzang yab yum gyi bskyed sngags/
NK060(i)001:7444: h+aum h+aum h+aum rtsa ba'i sa bon/
NK060(i)001:7445: badz+ra tsit+ta +amo kun bzang mthing kha mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya can bskyed pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7446: a a a rtsa ba'i sa bon/
NK060(i)001:7447: badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a kun tu bzang mo yab las ldog pa'i mnyam gzhag gam/
NK060(i)001:7448: thal mo thugs kar sbyar ba'i bskyed sngags so //
NK060(i)001:7450: rnam shes gsum 'das rdo rje ni //
NK060(i)001:7451: ye shes lnga rdzogs thugs nyid do //
NK060(i)001:7452: dbyings gsum rnam dag 'dus ma byas //
NK060(i)001:7453: kun tu de bzhin gnas med pa'o //
NK060(i)001:7455: thub pa drug bskyed pa'i sngags so //
NK060(i)001:7457: +amo ye shes lnga ldan rtsa ba'i sa bon/
NK060(i)001:7458: mu ne krim s+w+aa h+aa snam bu'i shar lhor lha'i thub pa daka po pi wang 'dzin pa'i bskyed sngags/
NK060(i)001:7460: mu ne h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa snam bu'i byang phyogs
NK060(i)001:7461: su lha min gyi thub pa mthing kha go cha
NK060(i)001:7463: mu ne srum s+w+aa h+aa snam bu'i lho phyogs su mi'i thub pa ser po gseg par bsnams pa'i/
NK060(i)001:7465: mu ne bram s+w+aa h+aa snam bu'i nub byang du
NK060(i)001:7466: byol song gi thub pa dmar nag po ti bsnams
NK060(i)001:7468: mu ne k+sham s+w+aa h+aa snam bu'i lho nub tu
NK060(i)001:7469: yi dwags kyi thub pa ser nag rin cen sgrom
NK060(i)001:7470: bu bsnams pa'i/ +amo rtsa ba'i sa bon/
NK060(i)001:7471: mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa snam bu'i byang shar du
NK060(i)001:7472: dmyal ba'i thub pa dud kha me chu bsnams pa'i
NK060(i)001:7474: sa bon zung gsum de ba de ba //
NK060(i)001:7475: des skyes rang rig gyur pa yin //
NK060(i)001:7476: gnyis byung 'dul bas thub par gsungs //
NK060(i)001:7478: gsum pa spyan drang ba la sogs pa las kyi rim pa'i sngags la bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:7480: snyan gsan dbab cing spyan drang ba'i sngags/
NK060(i)001:7482: +amo ni ye shes lnga ldan gyi sngags kyi 'go 'dren pa'o //
NK060(i)001:7483: e h+ye hi na bod pa ste/
NK060(i)001:7484: kye kye zhes pa'i don no //
NK060(i)001:7485: b+ha ga w+aa na ni bcom ldan 'das/
NK060(i)001:7486: ma h+aa ka ru ni ka ni thugs rje chen po/
NK060(i)001:7487: dri sh+ya hohni gshegs shig /sa ma ya s+t+wam ni dam tshig gi dus la bab bo zhes pa ste/
NK060(i)001:7488: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la dam tshig gis bskul ba'o //
NK060(i)001:7489: de ltar snyan gsan phab nas dam tshig gi thugs
NK060(i)001:7490: ka nas 'phros pa'i yi ge dzahs dgug /h+aum gis
NK060(i)001:7492: hohs dgyes pa bskyed nas dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor dang me ri 'dab 'byor du bzhugs par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7493: rig pa'i me tog dor ba'i/
NK060(i)001:7496: +amo badz+ra sa ma ya zhes pas ni/
NK060(i)001:7497: bdag de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gnyis su med par/
NK060(i)001:7498: +aam badz+ra sa ma ya +aam gis gsung dang gnyis su med par/
NK060(i)001:7499: h'u badz+ra sa ma ya h'u gis thugs dang gnyis su med par/
NK060(i)001:7500: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa sa yon tan dang gnyis su med par/
NK060(i)001:7501: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa zhes pas phrin las dang gnyis su med par bsam mo //
NK060(i)001:7504: +amo ye shes lnga ldan gyi glu'i 'go 'dren pa'o //
NK060(i)001:7505: rang rig pa'i ye shes la rang dbang bsgyur ba'i
NK060(i)001:7506: rgyal po nyid kyi sku dang gsang dang thugs dang
NK060(i)001:7507: yon tan dang phrin las gzhan las khyad par du
NK060(i)001:7508: gyur pas na rmad po che ste/
NK060(i)001:7509: dus da lta nyid du ni sems can thams cad
NK060(i)001:7510: dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i thugs rje mnga' bas sku'i
NK060(i)001:7511: phyag rgya chen por bdag kyang sbyor cig /+amo ye
NK060(i)001:7512: shes lnga ldan 'gre/ badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum ni
NK060(i)001:7513: rdo rje dam tshig gi rang bzhin gnyis su med
NK060(i)001:7514: par bsdus shig /+amo badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam ni
NK060(i)001:7515: gnyis su med par byin gyis brlab pa'i dus la
NK060(i)001:7516: shes lnga ldan 'gre/ bab bo // badz+ra sa ma
NK060(i)001:7517: ya hohni bdag la mnyes par mdzod cig ces bskur
NK060(i)001:7518: shes lnga ldan 'gre/ bab bo // ba'o // 'dir
NK060(i)001:7519: dngos grub bskul ba la tshig gis bskul ba dang
NK060(i)001:7520: shes lnga ldan 'gre/ bab bo // ba'o // / sngags kyis bskul ba gnyis ldabs so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:7521: rje sgro phug pa'i bzhed kyis/
NK060(i)001:7523: gnad nas phab ste bskul ba dang gnyis yin te/
NK060(i)001:7524: dper na slob ma gcig la bya ba 'chol ba'i dus na/
NK060(i)001:7525: khyod kyis 'di gyis shig bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:7526: 'di dam tshig la dgongs las cis kyang bya dgos so zer ba lta bu yin gsung /
NK060(i)001:7527: lha rje nye'u ston na re/
NK060(i)001:7528: spyir gyis don dam gsal byed brjod pa tshig gi sgo/
NK060(i)001:7529: thugs dam gnad bskul gsang ba sngags kyi sgo/
NK060(i)001:7530: dmigs pa rtse gcig ting 'dzin yid kyi sgo/
NK060(i)001:7531: mtshon par brdar rtags phyag rgya gar gyi sgo/
NK060(i)001:7532: zhes bya ba gsang sngags lung gi sgo bzhi yin pa la/
NK060(i)001:7533: kun la bzhi ka tshang ba yang yod/
NK060(i)001:7534: gsum tshang ba dang gnyis tshang ba'ang yod pas kun la thams cad tshang ba'i nges pa med la/
NK060(i)001:7535: skabs 'dir tshig dang sngags dang ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis bskul ba yin gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:7538: dza h+aum bam hoh zhes phyag rgya bzhis dam tshig
NK060(i)001:7539: pa dang ye shes pa gnyis su med par bstim
NK060(i)001:7540: par bya'o // bzhi pa sngags kyi yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:7542: zhes sngags de dag brjod pas gsung sngags kyi dkyil
NK060(i)001:7543: 'khor 'di dag ni mthus 'jig rten drug gi phyogs
NK060(i)001:7544: bcu'i gdul bya thams cad la sngags nyid lus la
NK060(i)001:7545: gnas pas na khyab par grags so //
NK060(i)001:7546: lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bas na rab tu grags so //
NK060(i)001:7547: las dang dngos grub tu snang bas na kun tu grangs so //
NK060(i)001:7549: yang na rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags kyis khyab par grags so //
NK060(i)001:7550: bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags kyi rab tu grags so //
NK060(i)001:7551: bzlas pa las kyi sngags kyis kun tu grags so //
NK060(i)001:7552: gsung gi dkyil 'khor kun tu grags pa de nas
NK060(i)001:7553: bcom ldan 'das yid byed pa po rdo rje kun
NK060(i)001:7555: chos bya ba mo rdo rje kun tu bzang mo grol lam ltar thabs shes dgongs pa/
NK060(i)001:7556: thabs lam ltar nyi zla byang chub kyi sems gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin ni/
NK060(i)001:7557: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor la thim par mdzad do //
NK060(i)001:7558: spyi don gnyis pa dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa'i sngags la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:7559: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:7560: dbang bskur byin brlab dngos dang /
NK060(i)001:7564: dkyil 'khor bskyed pa bstan pas na de/
NK060(i)001:7565: dbang bskur byin brlab ston pas na nas/
NK060(i)001:7566: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i de bzhin gshegs
NK060(i)001:7567: pa thams cad dang mi dmigs pa'i bdag nyid chen
NK060(i)001:7568: po kun tu bzang po yab yum gyis bdag nyid
NK060(i)001:7569: chen po'i ye shes lngas dbang bskur ba dang sku
NK060(i)001:7570: gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs bsdu ba zhes bya ba
NK060(i)001:7571: 'di sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i
NK060(i)001:7572: rdo rje sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba yab yum zung du
NK060(i)001:7574: gnyis pa dbang bskur byin brlab dngos la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:7578: de yang dbang gang gis na/
NK060(i)001:7581: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:7583: ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur te/
NK060(i)001:7584: dgos ched gang gi phyir na/
NK060(i)001:7585: swa b+h+aa ba'i sgras dri ma dag par byas pas/
NK060(i)001:7587: theg pa 'og ma ltar spang gnyen gyi tshul gyis ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:7588: rang bzhin rtogs pa'i tshul gyis so //
NK060(i)001:7589: de yang gung mo gnyis sbyar nas gyen du brkyangs
NK060(i)001:7590: pa'i rdo rje bsdams pa'i phyag rgya spyi bor bzhag
NK060(i)001:7591: la/ +amo ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra
NK060(i)001:7592: swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham zhes pa'i sngags kyis
NK060(i)001:7593: spyir bor mi bskyod pa yab yum sbyor ba mdzad
NK060(i)001:7594: pas rjes chags kyi me zhu ba stong pa nyid
NK060(i)001:7595: kyi ye shes kyi chu rgyun dbang bskur bas/
NK060(i)001:7596: nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gi dri ma dag nas/
NK060(i)001:7597: chu lud pa las mi bskyod pa dbu brgyan par bsgom zhing /
NK060(i)001:7598: rnam shes rnam dag rdo rje'i rigs rdo rje sems
NK060(i)001:7599: dpa' 'am bdag yin no bar nga rgyal bar bya'o
NK060(i)001:7600: // de'i 'gros kyis 'og ma rnams la'ang shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7601: mdzub mo gnyis brkyangs pa dpral bar bzhag la/
NK060(i)001:7602: +amo ma h+aa a dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham zhes pa'i sngags kyis/
NK060(i)001:7603: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi chu rgyun gyi dbang bskur bas/
NK060(i)001:7604: nyon mongs pa gti mug gi dri ma dag nas
NK060(i)001:7605: chu lud pa las rnam par snang mdzad kyis dbu
NK060(i)001:7607: gzugs phung rnam dag de bzhin gshegs pa'i rim rnam par snang mdzad du nga rgyal bar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7608: mthe bong gnyis brkyang pa ltag par/
NK060(i)001:7609: +amo ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham zhes pa'i sngags kyis/
NK060(i)001:7610: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi chu rgyun gyi dbang bskur bas/
NK060(i)001:7611: nyon mongs pa 'dod chags kyi dri ma dag nas
NK060(i)001:7612: chu lud pa las snang ba mtha' yas kyis dbu
NK060(i)001:7614: 'du shes rnam dag pad+ma'i rigs snang ba mtha' yas su nga rgyal bar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7615: srin lag brkyangs pa rna ltag g.yas su/
NK060(i)001:7616: +amo ma h+aa sa ma ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham zhes pa'i sngags kyis/
NK060(i)001:7617: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi chu rgyun gyi dbang bskur bas/
NK060(i)001:7618: nyon mongs pa nga rgyal gyi dri ma dag nas
NK060(i)001:7619: chu lud pa las rin cen 'byung ldan gyis dbu
NK060(i)001:7621: tshor ba rnam dag rin po che'i rigs rig chen 'byung ldan du nga rgyal bar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7622: mathe'u chung brkyangs pa rna ltag g.yon du/
NK060(i)001:7623: +amo ma h+aa kri t+y+aa nush+th+aa na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham zhes pa'i sngags kyis/
NK060(i)001:7624: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi chu rgyun gyi dbang bskur bas/
NK060(i)001:7625: nyon mongs pa phrag dog gi dri ma dag nas
NK060(i)001:7626: chu lud pa las don yod grub pas dbu brgyan
NK060(i)001:7627: par bsgom zhing / 'du byed rnam dag las kyi rigs don yod grub par nga rgyal bar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7628: de yang mi bskyod pa yab yum gnyis dang /
NK060(i)001:7629: byed pa po yab yum gnyis dang /
NK060(i)001:7630: zla dang bral ba zhes pa ni yum med pas
NK060(i)001:7631: te dpa' bo gcig pa'i lha thub pa drug go
NK060(i)001:7632: // de ltar rdo rje'i rigs kyi lha bcu'i rigs bdag mi bskyod pa yin pas/
NK060(i)001:7633: de yab yum dbus su byas nas dbang bskur ba yin te/
NK060(i)001:7635: mi bskyod byed po yum dang bcas //
NK060(i)001:7636: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i phyag rgyar ldan //
NK060(i)001:7639: zla dang bral ba'i dpa' bo che //
NK060(i)001:7644: gshin rje gshed yab yum gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:7645: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi lha brgyad kyi rigs bdag ltag par rnam par snang mdzad yin pas/
NK060(i)001:7646: de yab yum dbus su byas nas dbang bskur ba yin te/
NK060(i)001:7648: byams pa sa snying de bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:7650: gshin rje gshed la ltag par bshad //
NK060(i)001:7652: de dag gi shugs la lha gzhan rnams kyi rigs kyang shes par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:7653: mi bskyod pa rdo rje'i rigs yin pa'i shugs la rnam snang de bzhin rigs/
NK060(i)001:7656: don grub las kyi rigs yin par shes so //
NK060(i)001:7657: byang chub sems dpa' sa snying dang byams pa de bzhin rigs yin pa'i shugs la/
NK060(i)001:7658: nam snying dang sgrib sel rin cen/
NK060(i)001:7659: spyan ras gzigs dang kun bzang pad+ma/
NK060(i)001:7660: phyag rdor dang 'jam dpal las kyi rigs yin par shes so //
NK060(i)001:7661: khro bo gshin rje gshed de bzhin rigs yin pa'i shugs la/
NK060(i)001:7664: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba las kyi rigs yin par shes so //
NK060(i)001:7666: gzhan dag rang gi phyag rgyas te //
NK060(i)001:7668: 'di'i skabs su snga rabs pa 'ga' zhig /byams pa sa snying de bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:7669: zhes pa'i tshig gis 'khrul gzhi byas nas/
NK060(i)001:7670: byams pa dang sa snying de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs yin no bar ma go bar/
NK060(i)001:7671: de bzhin no zhes pa sngar bshad pa'i rdo rje'i rigs la snyeg par go bas/
NK060(i)001:7672: byams pa dang sa snying rdo rje'i rigs su 'dod mod kyi/
NK060(i)001:7673: sngon gyi dpe rnying du ma dang bum lung rnams na/
NK060(i)001:7674: byams pa dang sa snying de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs su byas 'dug go //
NK060(i)001:7675: 'on kyang sgyu 'phrul bla ma'i gzhung la la na/
NK060(i)001:7676: sa snying dang byams pa rdo rje'i rigs su byas pa'ang 'dug ste/
NK060(i)001:7677: gang zag 'ga' zhig gis zhen yul dbang btsan du byas nas bcos pa yin min brtag par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7678: yang zla dang bral ba'i dpa' bo che //
NK060(i)001:7679: zhes pa'i tshig gis 'khrul gzhi byas nas/
NK060(i)001:7680: thub pa drug zla bo yum dang bral ba'i dpa' bo gcig pa yin par ma go bar/
NK060(i)001:7681: rigs bdag mi bskyod pa rkyang res dbu brgyan par 'dod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:7683: phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor gyi sgom pa la dgongs na/
NK060(i)001:7684: thub drug rab byung sprul sku'i phyir //
NK060(i)001:7685: byin brlab dbu rgyan ma gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:7686: zhes pa'i lung gis 'khrul gzhi byas nas/
NK060(i)001:7687: 'dir phyag rgya spros bcas kyi lha bsgom pa'i skabs su yang /
NK060(i)001:7688: thub drug dbu rgyan med par 'dod pa ni shin tu 'khrul te/
NK060(i)001:7689: 'chad par 'gyur pa'i le'u brgyad pa las/
NK060(i)001:7690: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan //
NK060(i)001:7691: de nyid yan lag spros bdag ste //
NK060(i)001:7693: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog gis //
NK060(i)001:7694: rgyal ba rgyal mchog de bzhin te //
NK060(i)001:7696: zhes gsungs pa'i don dang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:7697: mdor na rigs gang yin gyi lha la/
NK060(i)001:7698: rigs kyi bdag po dbus na gnas pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs lngas dbu brgyan pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:7699: de yang gang dbus su song ba de'i shul du mi bskyod par 'byung bar shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7700: byin gyis brlab pa'i sngags so //
NK060(i)001:7702: spyi bor klad pa dang khang gi nang du zla
NK060(i)001:7703: ba'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i +amo dkar po las
NK060(i)001:7704: 'od 'phros pas/ de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul bas/
NK060(i)001:7705: sku'i byin rlabs kyi bdag de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK060(i)001:7706: cad kyi sku dang gnyis su med par byin gyis
NK060(i)001:7707: brlabs/ rlobs pa'i rtags su spyi bo'i +amo zhu ba'i 'od phung las/
NK060(i)001:7708: sku rdo rje rnam par snang mdzad dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin pa tshon gang ba bsgom zhing /
NK060(i)001:7709: rdo rje'i phyag rgya dpral bar gtugs la/
NK060(i)001:7710: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya
NK060(i)001:7711: badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham zhes brjod cing
NK060(i)001:7712: / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku'i rang bzhin nga'am bdag yin no bar nga rgyal bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7713: de bzhin du mgrin par pad+ma la gnas pa'i +aam/
NK060(i)001:7714: snying gar nyi ma la gnas pa'i h+aum/
NK060(i)001:7715: lte ba'i g.yas dang g.yon gnyis su zla ba'i gdan
NK060(i)001:7716: re re la gnas pa'i s+w+aa sngon po dang h+aa
NK060(i)001:7717: ljang gu'i 'od zer gyi spro bsdu las/
NK060(i)001:7718: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi lha rnams
NK060(i)001:7719: go rim bzhin sgom tshul shes par byas la rdo
NK060(i)001:7720: rje'i phyag rgya mgrin par gtugs nas/
NK060(i)001:7721: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aaka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham zhes brjod cing /
NK060(i)001:7722: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung gi rang bzhin nga'am bdag yin no bar nga rgyal bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7723: rdo rje'i phyag rgya snying gar gtugs la/
NK060(i)001:7724: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra p+aa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ka& ham zhes brjod cing /
NK060(i)001:7725: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kyi rang bzhin nga'am bdag yin no bar nga rgyal bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7726: rdo rje'i phyag rgya lte ba'i g.yas su gtugs la/
NK060(i)001:7727: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu
NK060(i)001:7728: ra ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham
NK060(i)001:7729: brjod cing / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK060(i)001:7730: yon tan gyi rang bzhin nga'am bdag yin no bar
NK060(i)001:7731: brjod cing / nga rgyal bya'o // rdo rje'i phyag rgya lte ba'i g.yon du gtugs la/
NK060(i)001:7732: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza
NK060(i)001:7733: badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham zhes brjod cing
NK060(i)001:7734: / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi phrin las
NK060(i)001:7735: kyi rang bzhin nga'am bdag yin no bar nga rgyal
NK060(i)001:7736: / bya'o // de ltar yan lag bcu gcig tu bshad kyang /
NK060(i)001:7737: don la yon tan dang phrin las ni sku gsung thugs kyi zhar byung yin pas/
NK060(i)001:7738: lam bsgom pa'i dbang du ye shes sems dpa' dang
NK060(i)001:7739: dbang bskur gyi lha lnga dang byin rlabs kyii lha
NK060(i)001:7740: gsum ste/ lhag pa'i lha dgu bsgom par gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:7741: 'o na dbang bskur ba'i lha dang byin gyis rlobs
NK060(i)001:7742: pa'i lha gnyis ka rigs lngar 'dug pas khyad ci
NK060(i)001:7743: yod ce na/ dbang bskur gyi lha ni dag bya
NK060(i)001:7744: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad dam nyon mongs pa
NK060(i)001:7745: ngar 'dzin dri ma de nyid dag byed ye shes
NK060(i)001:7746: lnga'i chu rgyun gyis dag par byas pa'i rtags/
NK060(i)001:7747: dbu rgyan rigs kyi lha lnga yin la/
NK060(i)001:7748: byin rlabs kyi lha ni lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs gsum mam/
NK060(i)001:7749: de dag gi yon tan phrin las dang bcas pa
NK060(i)001:7750: lngar byin gyis rlobs pa'i rtags su lus kyi gnas
NK060(i)001:7752: de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lngar snang ba yin no/
NK060(i)001:7753: yang dbang bskur gyi lha'i gtso bo dang byin rlabs
NK060(i)001:7754: kyi sku'i lha gnyis ka spyi bor bsgom pa'i phyir
NK060(i)001:7755: gnas tha dad med dam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:7756: dbang bskur gyi lha'i gtso bo spyi bor bsgom pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:7757: sku'i lha klad pa dung khang gi nang du bsgom pas na gnas tha dad do //
NK060(i)001:7758: dbang bskur gyi lha rnam par snang mdzad dang byin rlabs kyi sku'i lha gnyis/
NK060(i)001:7759: rnam par rnam par snang mdzad dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin par mtshungs sa ma zhe na/
NK060(i)001:7761: dbang bskur gyi lha ni ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun
NK060(i)001:7762: gyis lus gang bar byas pa'i lhag ma lud pa
NK060(i)001:7763: las rigs lngar snang ba yin te/
NK060(i)001:7764: sprul sku'i cha byad can no //
NK060(i)001:7765: byin rlabs kyi lha ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK060(i)001:7766: cad kyi sku gsung thugs sam yon tan phrin las
NK060(i)001:7767: kyi rang bzhin can gyi rigs gsum mam lnga/
NK060(i)001:7768: longs sku'i cha byad can yin no //
NK060(i)001:7769: 'di ltar ma go ba rnams kyis ni la las
NK060(i)001:7770: bla med kyi lha'i dbu rgyan yo ga'i rigs lngas
NK060(i)001:7771: byas pa dang / la las dbu rgyan gyi lha yab yum 'khril sbyor can byas pa dang /
NK060(i)001:7772: la las sngags nang lugs kyi rigs lnga la yum
NK060(i)001:7773: med pa'i dbu rgyan yon pa byas nas snang mod
NK060(i)001:7774: kyi 'di dag thams cad shin tu'ang rigs pa ma
NK060(i)001:7775: yin te/ snga ma ltar na yo ga 'brog 'chol ba'i skyon du 'gyur la/
NK060(i)001:7776: phyi ma gnyis ltar na tshom bu stong gi dkyil
NK060(i)001:7777: 'khor dang nyi khri bzhi stong gi dkyil 'khor bsgom
NK060(i)001:7779: dbu rgyan la yang dbu rgyan/
NK060(i)001:7781: dbu rgyan la yang dbu rgyan bsgoms na tshi chad par 'gyur ba dang /
NK060(i)001:7782: tshul 'di dag sngags gsar rnying gi rgyud 'grel man
NK060(i)001:7783: ngag khungs ma gang du'ang ma gsungs pa'i phyir ro
NK060(i)001:7785: dbu rgyan gyi lha rigs lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:7786: byin rlabs kyi lha rigs lnga ngo bo rang gcig gam mi gcig ce na/
NK060(i)001:7787: ngo bo ye shes rang snang gi lha yin pas gcig dang tha dad kyi mtha' las grol la/
NK060(i)001:7788: gnas dang rnam pa tha dad pa'i tshul sngar bshad zin no //
NK060(i)001:7789: yang ye shes sems dpa' dang thugs kyi lha gnyis gcig gam tha dad ce na/
NK060(i)001:7791: ye shes sems dpa' snying gi nang srog pa rtsa'i sgo ru bsgom la/
NK060(i)001:7792: thugs kyi lha brang gi nang snying gi phyi ru bsgom mo //
NK060(i)001:7793: rnam pa gang tha dad de/
NK060(i)001:7794: ye shes sems dpa' ni rtsa ba'i lha gang yin
NK060(i)001:7795: dang spyi rnams 'dra ba la rgyan dang cha lugs
NK060(i)001:7796: spangs pa/ phyag mtshan 'dzin 'dzin 'dra la mi 'dzin pa'o //
NK060(i)001:7797: thugs kyi lha ni rtsa ba'i lha gang yin kyang
NK060(i)001:7798: thugs kyi lha rdo rje mi bskyod pa sku mdog
NK060(i)001:7799: mthing kha/ phyag mtshan rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa 'dzin pa'o //
NK060(i)001:7800: ngo bo ni gcig dang tha dad las grol ba'i tshul sngar bshad zin to //
NK060(i)001:7801: mdor na lhag pa'i lha dgu/
NK060(i)001:7802: rtsa ba'i lha gang yin nyid dang bcu ste/
NK060(i)001:7803: lha thams cad kyang snang la rang bzhin med pa
NK060(i)001:7804: me long gi gzugs brnyan nam chu nang gi zla
NK060(i)001:7805: ba lta bur shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7806: gsum pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:7809: ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun ltar thim par gyur/
NK060(i)001:7810: dbang bskur gyi lha gsal bar gyur/
NK060(i)001:7811: byin rlabs kyi lha 'bar bar gyur to //
NK060(i)001:7813: yang na dbang gi lha rigs lngar thim par gyur/
NK060(i)001:7814: sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsal bar gyur/
NK060(i)001:7815: yon tan phrin las kyi lha 'bar bar gyur to //
NK060(i)001:7816: spyi don gsum pa rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:7824: e ma hohzhesa pa skye med don gyi gsung la ngam/
NK060(i)001:7825: rmad kyi chos zhes pa gsungs gzhan las khyad par du gyur pa la ngam pa'o //
NK060(i)001:7826: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku lnga po
NK060(i)001:7827: kun gyi gsung gi rang bzhin ni grags pa'i sgra
NK060(i)001:7828: dang btags pa'i ming dang brjod pa'i tshig dang yi
NK060(i)001:7829: ge la sogs pa kun las 'das pas na don
NK060(i)001:7830: gyi gsungs ste/ brjod med de nyid brjod bya kun
NK060(i)001:7831: gyi gzhir gyur pa'i phyir sna tshogs pa'i sgra dang
NK060(i)001:7832: tshig rnams kyi don gsal bar 'byung ba'o //
NK060(i)001:7835: de bzhin gshegs pa'i don gyi gsung gcig pu de
NK060(i)001:7836: ka gsung gi dkyil 'khor brjod bya thams cad gsal
NK060(i)001:7838: gsung de dbyangs kyi yan lag gi bcu gnyis sam/
NK060(i)001:7839: yang na 'gro ba rigs drug re re'i gnas su
NK060(i)001:7840: yang gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu drug cu ste
NK060(i)001:7841: sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa bsam gyis mi
NK060(i)001:7842: khyab pa gdul bya la kun tu khyab pa'i sgra
NK060(i)001:7843: dang ming tshig so sor grags pa thams cad kyang
NK060(i)001:7844: tshig res don re mtshon pa las mi 'da' bas
NK060(i)001:7845: na gsung gi phyag rgya'i mchog go //
NK060(i)001:7848: rgyud kun gyi mchog lha yab yum zung du 'brel
NK060(i)001:7849: bas na sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rgyud gsang ba snying
NK060(i)001:7850: po 'di nyid nyams su len ba las rnam rtog
NK060(i)001:7851: nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu med pas na bde ba
NK060(i)001:7852: dang ldan pa'i gsung gi don byung ba'ang 'khor 'das
NK060(i)001:7853: kyi sgra skad thams cad la 'dzin pa med pa
NK060(i)001:7854: ste/ des na pad+ma 'dam na gnas kyang 'dam gyi
NK060(i)001:7855: nyes skyon gyis mi gos pa lta bu'i ngang du
NK060(i)001:7856: gyur na grol ba ni mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK060(i)001:7857: ste/ chos dang / thar pa'i gnas su bgrod pa ni lam gyi chos dang /
NK060(i)001:7858: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang bcas pa ni 'khor ba'i chos so //
NK060(i)001:7859: gzhan yang sems can gyi rgyud kyis zin pa dang
NK060(i)001:7860: ma zin pa'i sgra skad ji ltar brjod pa thams
NK060(i)001:7861: cad kyang mtshan ma'i skyon gyis mi gos pas na
NK060(i)001:7862: gsung gi mchog ste rig pa byin gyis brlabs kyi
NK060(i)001:7865: theg pa mtho ba sngags dang dman pa mtshan nyid la sogs pa thams cad dang /
NK060(i)001:7866: log par mu stegs rtag chad dang /
NK060(i)001:7867: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sems can ma lus pa
NK060(i)001:7868: thams cad kyi sgra skad sems nyid du gsal bas
NK060(i)001:7869: ni mngon par byang chub pa'i gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:7870: de nyid grags stong dbyer mi phyed pas na rdo rje'i gsung du bsdus la/
NK060(i)001:7871: de ltar bsdus pa'i dus nyid na'ang rdo rje'i gsung
NK060(i)001:7872: las ma g.yos par phyogs bcur gdul bya'i snang ba
NK060(i)001:7873: dang mthun par rnam par grags so //
NK060(i)001:7874: sgra skad grags pa nyid na ma chags mi 'dzin pa gnyis med kyi ngang du gsungs la/
NK060(i)001:7875: de ltar gsungs pa'i dus nyid na skye ba med pa'i don la tshig tu brjod pa med pa'o //
NK060(i)001:7876: tshangs pa dbyangs kyi gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:7878: don gyi gsung brjod du med pa de nyid tshig
NK060(i)001:7879: sna tshogs pa'i sgra gdul bya kun la grags shing
NK060(i)001:7880: brda so sor 'jal bar byed do //
NK060(i)001:7881: dper na de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pas sprid pa sangs pa la lha rje dang /
NK060(i)001:7883: chung ma dang gsum la go tshul re re byung
NK060(i)001:7884: ba bzhin du don gyi gsung gcig gi sgra yis
NK060(i)001:7885: bye brag tu gdul bya thams cad la rang rang
NK060(i)001:7886: gi bsam pa dang mthun pas so sor go ba
NK060(i)001:7887: ste/ tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyi gsung 'di ni tshig gcig
NK060(i)001:7888: gis don tha dad pa du ma dus gcig la
NK060(i)001:7889: go bar byed pas na gsung mchog rgyal po yin
NK060(i)001:7890: ste/ no // skabs 'dir kha cig na re/
NK060(i)001:7891: 'dir longs sku brda'i gsung ma byung bas chad la
NK060(i)001:7892: sprul sku'i gsung lan gnyis byung bas ldabs so zhe
NK060(i)001:7893: na/ lha rje drings pa na re/
NK060(i)001:7894: longs sku brda'i gsung le'u drug par bstan pas 'dir ma byung ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:7895: sprul sku'i gsung gnyis ma ldabs te/
NK060(i)001:7896: sprul sku brjod pa tshig gi gsung ni tshig re res don re re mtshon pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:7897: sprul sku tshangs pa dbyangs kyi gsung ni tshig gcig gis don du ma mtshon pa yin te/
