NK060(i)001:7898: gzhung tshigs gis gsal lo gsung /
NK060(i)001:7899: gtsang pa byi ston na re/
NK060(i)001:7900: longs sku'i gsung chad pa med de/
NK060(i)001:7901: ji ltar gsung rab kun brjod kyang //
NK060(i)001:7902: de bzhin nyid las gsungs pa med //
NK060(i)001:7903: ces pa 'di brda'i gsung du 'gro gsung /
NK060(i)001:7904: rgya gab gong pa na re/
NK060(i)001:7905: bla ma rnams de ltar gsung yang /
NK060(i)001:7908: las dang rnam grangs rnams thun mong du bdun du bzhag pas longs sku'i gsung ma chad gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:7911: theg pa mtho ba sngags dang dman pa mtshan nyid
NK060(i)001:7912: la sogs pa bsam yas pa gdul bya'i ngo la
NK060(i)001:7913: ji ltar snang yang bcom ldan 'das kyis gzugs kyi
NK060(i)001:7914: de bzhin nyid kho na las ma gsungs te/
NK060(i)001:7915: gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabs su tshangs pa'i dbyangs gcig la'ang go tshul so sor thos te/
NK060(i)001:7916: mdo ting 'dzin rgyal po las kyang /
NK060(i)001:7917: koo d+ai nya ngas ni gzugs kyi de bzhin nyid 'ba' zhig gsungs na/
NK060(i)001:7918: la las ni gzugs stong zhes bya bar thos/
NK060(i)001:7919: la las ni gzugs mi stong zhes bya bar thos/
NK060(i)001:7920: la las ni gzugs bde zhes bya bar thos/
NK060(i)001:7921: la las ni gzugs sdug bsngal zhes bya bar thos/
NK060(i)001:7922: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:7923: gsum pa gsung gi rnam grangs so //
NK060(i)001:7925: ji ltar sgra'am brda'i sgo nas gsung rab kyi don
NK060(i)001:7926: kun tshig tu brjod pa thams cad kyang bsdu na
NK060(i)001:7927: gsung gi rnam grangs lnga'am drug tu 'dus te de
NK060(i)001:7928: bzhin nyid kyi don brjod du med pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:7929: tshig tu gsungs pa med pa ni chos sku skye med don gyi gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:7930: de nyid mtshon byed kyi yi ge med pa dang
NK060(i)001:7931: ljags kyi rtse mor sgra tshig tu ma byung yang
NK060(i)001:7932: brda don 'jal bar byed pas na longs sku'i dgongs
NK060(i)001:7934: de nyid kyang rang rig pa kho na'i phyir rig
NK060(i)001:7935: pa ye shes kyi gsung de ni spros pa dang
NK060(i)001:7936: bral yang brtse ba chen pos thams cad la khyab
NK060(i)001:7937: pa'i thugs rjes chos thams cad dang /
NK060(i)001:7938: sgra thams cad chos nyid kyi ngang du lhun gyis
NK060(i)001:7939: grub pa gsung gi byin rlabs cir yang mi 'gag
NK060(i)001:7940: pa ni rig pa byin gyis brlabs kyi gsung ngo
NK060(i)001:7941: // 'gro don sna tshogs gdul bya'i bsam pa dang
NK060(i)001:7942: mthun par so sor brda'i don dus gcig tu gsal
NK060(i)001:7943: bar ston pa sprul sku brjod pa tshig gi gsung
NK060(i)001:7944: // ngo // gsung lnga yang ma 'chags pa gsal
NK060(i)001:7945: ba'i dus nyid na'ang rang bzhin las g.yos pa med
NK060(i)001:7946: pas gsung gi mchog ste dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung
NK060(i)001:7947: // ngo // ngo // de bzhin tshig tu ma
NK060(i)001:7948: brjod par gsal bar go ba la sogs pa'i gsung
NK060(i)001:7949: gi sgo nas 'gro ba sems can gyi don rnams
NK060(i)001:7950: kyang de bzhin gyi ngang las ma g.yos par sgra'i
NK060(i)001:7951: bye brag tha dad pa sna tshogs su grags kyang
NK060(i)001:7952: // ngo // ngo // / dper na brag gis
NK060(i)001:7953: ma smras bzhin du brag ca'i sgra ka dang ki
NK060(i)001:7954: la sogs pa ngang gis ji ltar brjod pa ltar
NK060(i)001:7955: // ngo // ngo // / 'byung bzhin no // le'u'i mtshan no //
NK060(i)001:7957: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las mtshan gyi gzhi 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:7958: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gsung gi dkyil 'khor te/
NK060(i)001:7961: rnam grangs rnams bsdus te bstan pa dang lha bskyed
NK060(i)001:7962: pa la sogs pa'i gsang ba sngags kyi don rnams
NK060(i)001:7963: gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas na le'u ste yas bgrangs
NK060(i)001:7964: bdun pa'i don du gada'o////da ni le'u brgyad pa 'chad
NK060(i)001:7965: par byed de/ de la rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las/
NK060(i)001:7966: lam dang 'bras bu gtso cher ston/
NK060(i)001:7967: lam la thabs grol gnyis las gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:7971: 'bras bu mthar phyiin zur tsam ston/
NK060(i)001:7973: rang bzhin dang lam snang gnyis ston/
NK060(i)001:7974: lam la rim cig car gnyis las gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:7975: 'bring gi lnga las rgyud don ston/
NK060(i)001:7976: de la bcu las thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ston/
NK060(i)001:7977: zhor la lta ba spyod pa ting nge 'dzin ston/
NK060(i)001:7981: ldem dgongs man ngag /mtshon pa dpe/
NK060(i)001:7982: tshad ma bka' gzhung rnams ston/
NK060(i)001:7983: spyi don bsdu ba zur tsam ston/
NK060(i)001:7984: gzhan yang spyi 'gro rnams kyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:7985: de ltar ston pa'i le'u brgyad pa la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:7987: gsung pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:7989: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin sku dang gsung gi dkyil 'khor bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:7990: da thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ston par byed pas na de nas zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:7991: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid ston
NK060(i)001:7992: pa drug pa nyid kyis lus dang rtogs pa'i yan
NK060(i)001:7993: lag thams cad rigs lnga la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:7994: du ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub par ye nas
NK060(i)001:7995: gnas pa ni rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:7996: gnas pa la gnas pa ltar shes pa lta ba'i phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:7997: de don mngon du byas pa ni lhag pa'i phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:7998: de ltar thabs 'dis lha'i rang bzhin du byin gyis
NK060(i)001:7999: rlob pa zhes bya ba 'og nas 'byung ba'i don
NK060(i)001:8003: dang po rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8004: drang rtogs tshogs lha yab yum zung du 'brel bar
NK060(i)001:8005: ye nas gsal bas na sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon
NK060(i)001:8006: du rdzogs pa rtog pa thams cad lha'i ngo bor
NK060(i)001:8007: ye nas gnas pa rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8008: de ltar rtogs pa lta ba'i phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8009: mngon du byed pa 'bras bu'i phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8010: de gsum dang ldan pa ni byang chub mchog gi
NK060(i)001:8011: phyag rgya ste de ni phyag rgya'i mchog kho na'o
NK060(i)001:8013: rang bzhin phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK060(i)001:8014: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad kun //
NK060(i)001:8015: rigs lnga bde gshegs yab yum gyi //
NK060(i)001:8016: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK060(i)001:8018: mdor na phyag rgya zhes pa ni rgyas 'debs par byed pa'i tha tshig ste/
NK060(i)001:8019: de yang 'da' bar dka' ba dang /
NK060(i)001:8022: chos gsum ldan zhig yin no //
NK060(i)001:8023: de dag gi dpe ni go rim bzhin/
NK060(i)001:8026: nyo tshong mkhan gyi phu dud bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8027: gnyis pa phyag rgya'i khungs nges tshig dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:8029: rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya rtogs dka' bas na gsang ba de nyid gzhung gang gis ston na/
NK060(i)001:8030: de kho na nyid nges pa'i don mtshon par byed
NK060(i)001:8031: pa gsang ba snying po'i gzhung gis ston pa'i phyag
NK060(i)001:8032: rgya 'di ni 'da' bar dka' ba ste rgyal po'i
NK060(i)001:8034: gsum pa lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:8038: lag pa g.yas pa mi bskyod pa'i rigs kyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la/
NK060(i)001:8039: ma s+aur+ya man+da la zhes pa'i sngags kyis nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor lnga bkod la/
NK060(i)001:8040: de'i steng du yab kyi sa bon yi ge 'bru lnga bkod de/
NK060(i)001:8042: mdzub mo la +amo srin lag pa s+w+aa/
NK060(i)001:8044: mthe chung la h+aa rnams so //
NK060(i)001:8045: lag pa g.yon pa rin cen rigs kyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la/
NK060(i)001:8046: a tsan+d+ra man+dala zhes pa'i sngags kyis zla ba'i dkyil 'khor lnga/
NK060(i)001:8047: de'i steng du yum gyi yi ge 'bru lnga bkod de/
NK060(i)001:8052: mthe chung la t+aam rnams so //
NK060(i)001:8053: de nas lag pa g.yas g.yon gyi sor mo lnga
NK060(i)001:8054: gnyis zung du sprad pa las thal mo sbyar ba
NK060(i)001:8055: las lha so so'i phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu'o //
NK060(i)001:8057: mi bskyod rdo rje rtse lnga las //
NK060(i)001:8058: nyi ma'i theg le yi ge lnga //
NK060(i)001:8059: rat+na par bu'i nyi lnga la //
NK060(i)001:8060: zla ba'i thig le yi ge dngos //
NK060(i)001:8061: thig le thabs shes lnga gnyis rnams //
NK060(i)001:8062: phrad pa'i dus na rang snang ba //
NK060(i)001:8063: phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub 'byung //
NK060(i)001:8068: rigs lnga spyi'i dam tshig gi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8070: lag pa g.yas kyi mdzub mo'i +amo dang /
NK060(i)001:8071: g.yon gyi gung mo'i m+aum gnyis rtse sbyar te rigs
NK060(i)001:8072: bzhi'i yi ge 'bru brgyad po yab yum brang ma
NK060(i)001:8073: sprad par bsnol te rtse mo sprad pa ni/
NK060(i)001:8074: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor
NK060(i)001:8075: ba'i dbang du dngos grub bde ba chen po rang
NK060(i)001:8076: gi rgyud la sbyin par byed pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8077: de yang ye shes rngam pa glog gi 'khor lo'i rgyud las/
NK060(i)001:8078: +amo dang m+aum du rtse sbyar te //
NK060(i)001:8079: de bzhin h+aum dang l+aam du sbyar //
NK060(i)001:8080: h+aa dang pyam yang de bzhin te //
NK060(i)001:8081: +aam dang t+aam du sbyar ba las //
NK060(i)001:8082: rgyab sbyar s+w+aa dang m+aam bsgreng ba //
NK060(i)001:8083: 'di ni yab kyi spyi rgya yin //
NK060(i)001:8084: lag pa thal mo sbyar ba las //
NK060(i)001:8085: +amo dang mum sbyar h+aum dang ni //
NK060(i)001:8086: l+aam sbyar s+w+aa dang pyam du sbyar //
NK060(i)001:8087: +aam dang m+aam sbyar h+aa t+aam bsgreng //
NK060(i)001:8088: yum gyi spyi rgya yin par bshad //
NK060(i)001:8089: ces gsungs pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8090: sgyu 'phrul man ngag 'od kyi rim pa las/
NK060(i)001:8091: mthe bong gnyis la s+w+aa m+aam dang /
NK060(i)001:8092: srin lag gnyis la +aam pyam dgod par bshad cing /
NK060(i)001:8093: bla ma gong ma rnams kyang phyag len de ltar du mdzad mod kyi/
NK060(i)001:8094: rgyud rngam pa glog gi 'khor lo'i lung 'di dang mi mthun par snang zhing /
NK060(i)001:8095: rgyud rtsa bshad gnyis ka phyag rgya bca' lugs gung mthun dgos pas 'di bzhin du rig par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8097: dbyings dang ye shes bdag po gnyis //
NK060(i)001:8098: +amo dang m+aum du rang bzhin gnas //
NK060(i)001:8099: rwa dang 'dab ma'i thig le rnams //
NK060(i)001:8100: rang rang gnas kyi bsnol mar 'gyur //
NK060(i)001:8101: rab tu 'dres par gyur pa las //
NK060(i)001:8102: rgyal ba'i ye shes bde chen po //
NK060(i)001:8103: myong 'gyur thob pa zhes su bshad //
NK060(i)001:8108: dang po rigs lnga yab yum gyi phyag rgya la nang brtsegs lnga las/
NK060(i)001:8109: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8111: bdag rdo rje sems dpa' dbu'i gtsug tor nas zhabs
NK060(i)001:8112: gdan khri yan chod sku ra'i dang khyam khyom med
NK060(i)001:8113: par gsal ba ni sku'i phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK060(i)001:8114: de ltar gsal ba'i lag pa g.yas kyi nyi ma'i
NK060(i)001:8115: dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhi po
NK060(i)001:8116: sbas nas gung mo gyen du bsgreng ba thugs kar
NK060(i)001:8117: bkan thabs su bca' ba ni bca' ba dam tshig
NK060(i)001:8118: gi phyag rgya/ de'i rtse mor h+aum mthing kha bsam pa ni bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8119: de yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje rtse lnga
NK060(i)001:8120: 'od 'bar ba bsam pa ni bsam pa dam tshig
NK060(i)001:8121: gi phyag rgya/ lag pa g.yon pa'i zla ba'i dkyil
NK060(i)001:8122: 'khor lnga brtul yum gyi yig 'bru rnams sbas nas
NK060(i)001:8123: dril bu gsil zhing yum la 'khril ba'i tshul gyis
NK060(i)001:8124: barla g.yon pa chos kyi rigs la bstan pa'i phyag
NK060(i)001:8125: rgya dngos su bca' ba ni bca' ba las kyi
NK060(i)001:8126: gi phyag rgya/ phyag rgya/ de ltar yid kyis bsam pa ni bsam pa las kyi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8127: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika ces phyag rgya g.yas nas bcas te/
NK060(i)001:8128: mdun du bsgyur nas g.yon du yum gyi thugs kar
NK060(i)001:8129: dkrol ba ni shes rab la thabs kyis rgyas 'debs
NK060(i)001:8130: pa ste brjod pa chos kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8131: de'i g.yon phyogs su yum nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma
NK060(i)001:8132: gsal bar bsgom pa ni sku phyag rgya chen po'o
NK060(i)001:8133: // lag pa g.yon pa'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la
NK060(i)001:8134: gnas pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhi sbas nas gung mo
NK060(i)001:8135: bsgreng ba thugs kar bkan thabs su bca' ba ni
NK060(i)001:8136: bca' ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8137: de'i rtse mor m+aum mthing kha bsam pa ni bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8138: de yongs su gyur pa las dril bu gsil ba'i
NK060(i)001:8139: sgra can 'od 'bar ba bsam pa ni bsam pa
NK060(i)001:8141: lag pa g.yas pa'i nyi ma la gnas pa'i yab
NK060(i)001:8142: kyi 'bru lnga dang bcas pa las su yab kyi
NK060(i)001:8143: mgul la 'khril zhing yum gyi dbu yab kyi mdun
NK060(i)001:8144: na btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis yab kyi zhal
NK060(i)001:8145: blta ba'i tshul du phyag rgya dbus su bca' ba
NK060(i)001:8146: ni bca' ba las kyi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8147: de ltar yid kyis bsam pa ni bsam pa las kyi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8148: m+aum d+h+aa t+we shwa r+ai zhes brjod cing /
NK060(i)001:8149: phyag rgya g.yon du bcas shing thugs kar bsgyur nas
NK060(i)001:8150: g.yas su yab kyi thugs kar dgrol ba ni thabs
NK060(i)001:8151: la shes rab kyi rgyas 'debs pa ste brjod pa'i
NK060(i)001:8153: 'di la bdag gi bla ma dngul ston glang mkhal ba ni/
NK060(i)001:8154: yab yum gnyis kar gyi phyag rgya rdzogs pa'i rjes su/
NK060(i)001:8155: yab yum gyi snyings pos phan tshun thabs kyis shes rab la rgyas gdab pa dang /
NK060(i)001:8156: shes rab kyis thabs la rgyas gdab pa mdzad kyi/
NK060(i)001:8157: yum ma bskyed gong du yab kyi snying po mi brjod de thabs kyis rgyas gdab bya'i/
NK060(i)001:8158: yum shes rab ma bskyed pa'i phyir ro zhes gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:8159: mdor na phyag rgya bdun gsungs kyang bca' ba las kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK060(i)001:8160: bsam pa las kyi phyag rgya gnyis ka las kyi phyag rgya gcig tu bgrangs/
NK060(i)001:8161: bca' ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK060(i)001:8162: bsam pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya gnyis ka dam tshig gi phyag rgya gcig tu bgrang /
NK060(i)001:8163: bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK060(i)001:8164: brjod pa chos kyi phyag rgya gnyis ka chos kyi
NK060(i)001:8165: phyag rgya gcig tu bgrangs te de ltar sku phyag
NK060(i)001:8168: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK060(i)001:8169: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po bzhi //
NK060(i)001:8171: 'di'i 'gros kyis 'chad par 'gyur ba'i lha thams cad
NK060(i)001:8172: la phyag rgya bdun ldan sbyar ba shes par bya'o
NK060(i)001:8173: // rnam snang yab yum gyi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8175: rnam par snang mdzad kyi sku yongs su rdzogs par gsal ba ni sku'i phyag rgya chen po/
NK060(i)001:8176: lag pa g.yas pa'i 'bru bzhi sbas nas mdzub mo'i
NK060(i)001:8177: gyen du bsgreng ba thugs kar bkan thabs su bcas
NK060(i)001:8178: pa'i rtse mor +amo dkar po yongs su gyur pa
NK060(i)001:8180: lag pa g.yon pa'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor brtul yum
NK060(i)001:8181: gyi yig 'bru rnams sbas nas dril bu gsil zhing
NK060(i)001:8182: yum la 'khril ba'i tshul gyis barla g.yon pa chos
NK060(i)001:8183: kyi rigs la bstan pa ni yab kyi phyag rgya'o
NK060(i)001:8184: // lag pa g.yon pa'i yum gyi 'bru bzhi sbas
NK060(i)001:8185: nas mdzub mo gyen du bsgreng ba thugs kar bkan
NK060(i)001:8186: thabs su bcas pa'i rtse mor l+aam dkar po yongs
NK060(i)001:8187: su gyur pa las dril bu gsil ba'i sgra dang
NK060(i)001:8189: lag g.yas pa'i nyi ma la gnas pa'i yab kyi
NK060(i)001:8190: yig 'bru lnga dang bcas pa las su yab kyi
NK060(i)001:8191: mgul la 'khril nas/ dbu yab kyi mdun na btud
NK060(i)001:8192: de zhal 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis yab kyi zhal du
NK060(i)001:8193: blta ba'i tshul ni yum gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8194: rin cen 'byung ldan yab yum gyi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8196: rin cen 'byung ldan du gsal ba'i lag pa g.yas
NK060(i)001:8197: pa'i nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i yab kyi
NK060(i)001:8198: yig 'bru bzhi sbas nas srin lag gyen du bsgreng
NK060(i)001:8199: ba thugs kar bkan thabs su bcas pa'i rtse mor
NK060(i)001:8200: s+w+aa ser po bsam/ de yongs su gyur pa las rin cen 'od 'bar ba bsam zhing /
NK060(i)001:8201: g.yon zla ba'i dkyil 'khor brtul yum gyi yig 'bru
NK060(i)001:8202: sbas nas dril bu gsil zhing yum la 'khril ba'i
NK060(i)001:8203: tshul gyis barla g.yon pa chos kyi rigs la bstan
NK060(i)001:8204: pa ni yab kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8205: de'i g.yon du yum m+aa ma k+air gsal ba'i lag
NK060(i)001:8206: pa g.yon pa'i yum gyi yig 'bru bzhi sbas nas
NK060(i)001:8207: srin lag gyen du bsgreng ba thugs kar bkan thabs
NK060(i)001:8208: su bcas pa'i rtse mor m+aam ser po yongs su
NK060(i)001:8209: gyur pa las dril bu gsil ba'i sgra dang bcas
NK060(i)001:8211: g.yas pa'i nyi ma la gnas pa'i yab kyi yig
NK060(i)001:8212: 'bru lnga dang bcas pa las su yab kyi mgul
NK060(i)001:8213: la 'khril zhing / dbu mdun nas btud de zhal
NK060(i)001:8214: 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis yab kyi zhal du blta ba'i
NK060(i)001:8215: tshul ni yum gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8216: mtha' yas yab yum gyi phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8218: snang ba mtha' yas su gsal ba'i lag pa g.yas
NK060(i)001:8219: pa'i nyi ma la gnas pa'i yab kyi 'bru bzhi
NK060(i)001:8220: sbas nas mthe bong gyen du bsgreng ba thugs kar
NK060(i)001:8221: bkan thabs su bca' zhing de'i rtse mor +aam dmar
NK060(i)001:8222: po yongs su gyur pa las pad+ma 'od 'bar ba
NK060(i)001:8223: bsam zhing / g.yon pa'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams
NK060(i)001:8224: brtul yum gyi yig 'bru sbas nas dril bu gsil
NK060(i)001:8225: zhing yum la 'khril ba'i tshul gyis barla g.yon pa'i
NK060(i)001:8226: chos kyi rigs la bstan pa ni yab kyi phyag
NK060(i)001:8227: bsam zhing / rgya'o // de'i g.yon du yum na
NK060(i)001:8228: bza' dkar mo sku yongs su rdzogs pa'i gsal ba'i
NK060(i)001:8229: g.yon pa'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i yum
NK060(i)001:8231: mthe bong gyen du bsgreng ba thugs kar bkan thabs
NK060(i)001:8232: su bca' zhing de'i rtse mor pyam dmar po yongs
NK060(i)001:8233: su gyur pa las dril bu gsil ba'i sgra can
NK060(i)001:8235: g.yas pa'i nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i yab
NK060(i)001:8236: kyi yig 'bru lnga dang bcas pa las yab kyi
NK060(i)001:8238: dbu yab kyi mdun nas brgyud de zhal 'dzum pa'i
NK060(i)001:8239: mdangs kyis yab kyi zhal blta ba'i tshul ni yum
NK060(i)001:8240: gyi phyag rgya'o // don grub yab yum gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8242: don grub kyi sku gsal ba'i lag pa g.yas pa'i
NK060(i)001:8243: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i yab kyi yig
NK060(i)001:8244: 'bru bzhi sbas nas mathe'u chung gyen du bsgreng ba
NK060(i)001:8245: thugs kar bkan thabs su bcas pa de'i rtse mor
NK060(i)001:8247: de yongs su gyur pa las ral gri 'od 'bar ba bsam zhing /
NK060(i)001:8248: g.yon pa'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor brtul yum gyi yig
NK060(i)001:8249: 'bru bzhi sbas nas dril bu gsil zhing yum la
NK060(i)001:8250: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis barla g.yon pa chos kyi rigs
NK060(i)001:8251: la bstan pa ni yab kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8252: de'i g.yon du yum dam tshig sgrol mar gsal ba'i
NK060(i)001:8253: lag pa g.yon pa'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la gnas
NK060(i)001:8254: pa'i yum gyi yig 'bru bzhi sbas nas mathe'u chung
NK060(i)001:8255: gyen du bsgreng ba thugs kar bkan thabs su bca'
NK060(i)001:8256: zhing de'i rtse mor t+aam ljang gu bsam/
NK060(i)001:8257: de yongs su gyur pa las dril bu gsil ba'i sgra can 'od 'bar ba bsam zhing /
NK060(i)001:8258: g.yas pa'i nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i yab
NK060(i)001:8259: kyi yig 'bru lnga dang bcas pa las su yab
NK060(i)001:8260: kyi mgul nas 'khril zhing mdun na btud de zhal
NK060(i)001:8261: 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis yab kyi zhal du blta ba'i
NK060(i)001:8262: tshul ni yum gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8263: sems dpa' yab yum gyi phyag mtshan/
NK060(i)001:8265: 'di dag la'ang 'og nas gong gi phyag rgya chen po bzhi zhes pa las/
NK060(i)001:8266: phyag rgya bdun bdun gong gi rigs lnga dang mthun par 'chad de/
NK060(i)001:8267: sa snying la sogs pa sku yongs su rdzogs par bsgom pa ni sku phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK060(i)001:8268: lag pa g.yas pa'i sbom po ma gtogs sor mo bre kha bzhi la/
NK060(i)001:8269: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor sran chung slebs pa tsam re'i steng du sor mo'i rtse mo nas brtsams te/
NK060(i)001:8270: k+sh+aim tram hri dzim bzhi dgod/
NK060(i)001:8271: g.yon du zla ba'i steng du/
NK060(i)001:8272: h+aum tram hri a bzhi dgod/
NK060(i)001:8273: de nas lag pa g.yas pa'i 'bru gsum sbas nas/
NK060(i)001:8274: mdzub mo gyen du bsgrengs nas thugs kar bkan pa ni bca' ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8275: de'i rtse mor k+sh+aim dkar po bsam pa ni bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8276: de yongs su gyur pa las rin po che'i myu
NK060(i)001:8277: gu 'od 'bar ba bsam pa ni bsam pa dam
NK060(i)001:8279: lag pa g.yon pa'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor brtul yum
NK060(i)001:8280: gyi 'bru rnams sbas nas yum la 'khyud pa'i phyag
NK060(i)001:8281: rgya dngos dang bcas pa ni bca' pa las kyi
NK060(i)001:8282: phyag rgya'o // yid kyis kyang der ltar bsam pa ni bsam pa las kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8283: k+shi hi r+aa tsa ya zhes brjod cing /
NK060(i)001:8284: phyag rgya g.yas nas bcas shing mdun du bsgyur nas/
NK060(i)001:8285: g.yon du yum l+aa s+ye'i thugs kar dkrol ba ni
NK060(i)001:8286: shes rab la thabs kyis rgyas gdab pa ste brjod
NK060(i)001:8288: de'i 'gros kyis sems dpa' sems ma dang /
NK060(i)001:8289: khro bo khro mo thams cad la shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8290: 'o na ut+pala klu shing la sogs mtshan //
NK060(i)001:8291: zhes ut+pala thog mar smos pa ci yin zhe na/
NK060(i)001:8292: thams cad mkhyen pas gzhan don byed pa mngon du 'gro bas sam/
NK060(i)001:8293: yang na tshad med pa bzhi sngon du 'gro bas so //
NK060(i)001:8294: yang phyogs dang mtshams kyi dang po byang shar yin
NK060(i)001:8295: pas kyang byung ba yin no gsung ste brtag par
NK060(i)001:8296: bya'o // mdor na 'jam dpal gyi phyag mtshan ut+pala
NK060(i)001:8297: yin pa la sogs khongs nas gzhan rnams kyi phyag
NK060(i)001:8298: bya'o // mtshan yang ston te/ klu shing byams pa'i phyag mtshan yin la/
NK060(i)001:8299: de bzhin du sa snying gi rin chen myu gu/
NK060(i)001:8300: nam snying gi ral gri 'od 'bar ba/
NK060(i)001:8301: spyan ras gzigs kyi pad+ma dkar po/
NK060(i)001:8302: phyag rdor gyi rdo rje 'od 'bar ba/
NK060(i)001:8303: sgrib sel gyi chos kyi 'khor lo/
NK060(i)001:8304: kun tu bzang pos rin cen sna tshogs kyi snye ma 'khyil ba/
NK060(i)001:8305: l+aa s+ye ma'i gzugs mdzes par byed pa'i me long /
NK060(i)001:8306: m+aa le ma'i rin cen phreng ba dang /
NK060(i)001:8308: n+airti ma'i gar mkhan mchog gi phu dung nyid de/
NK060(i)001:8309: de bzhin du push+pe'i me tog gi phreng ba dang /
NK060(i)001:8310: d+h+au pe spos sna tshogs kyi mchod par byed la/
NK060(i)001:8312: gan+d+he ma'i byug pa ste dri'i dung chos/
NK060(i)001:8313: de la sogs pa rang rtags kyi phyag mtshan rnams 'dzin zhing /
NK060(i)001:8314: yab yum rnams las kyi phyag rgya phan tshun gcig la gcig 'khril zhing /
NK060(i)001:8315: yab kyi barla g.yon pa chos kyi rigs la bstan
NK060(i)001:8316: pa'i tshul gyis yab kyi dbu rnams yum la 'byor
NK060(i)001:8317: zhing yum gyi dbus 'dud pa'i tshul/
NK060(i)001:8318: gong gi rigs lnga'i phyag rgya chen po bzhin du
NK060(i)001:8319: thabs shes rab gnyis med mnyam pa'i dbyings kyi ngang
NK060(i)001:8320: du 'khril lo // sgo ba yab yum gyi phyag mtshan/
NK060(i)001:8322: sgo bzhir gnas pa'i khro bo bzhi'i phyag rgya ni
NK060(i)001:8323: gshin rje gshed po'i phyag mtshan n+rir mgo gdengs pa'i
NK060(i)001:8325: stobs po che rdo rje gnon thabs su 'dzin pa dang /
NK060(i)001:8326: rta mgrin thod sbrul chen po gnon thabs su 'dzin pa dang /
NK060(i)001:8327: rdo rje rgya gram ni khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba las kyi rigs kyi gnon thabs su 'dzin la/
NK060(i)001:8328: yum rnams ni lcags kyu ma lcags kyu dang /
NK060(i)001:8329: zhags pa ma zhags pa dang /
NK060(i)001:8330: lcags sgrog ma s+pho ta ste lcags sgrog dang /
NK060(i)001:8331: hohn dgyes pa bskyed pa ste dril bu ma dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK060(i)001:8332: sgo bzhir gnas pa'i khro bo khro mo de dag kyang yab yum phan tshun 'dud pa'i tshul dang /
NK060(i)001:8333: 'khril ba'i tshul ni gong ma rigs lnga bzhin du 'dir yang bsgom par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8334: thub pa drug gi phyag rgya'i rnam grangs bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:8336: 'gro 'dul thub drug gi phyag rgya ni gcig tu
NK060(i)001:8337: ma nges pas gdul bya mos pa sna tshogs dang
NK060(i)001:8338: mthun par bstan te/ mdor bsdus na 'gro ba rigs
NK060(i)001:8339: drug 'dul ba'i thabs su phyag rgya yang drug tu
NK060(i)001:8343: pi wang dang ni gseg par dang //
NK060(i)001:8344: go cha po ti rin chen sgrom //
NK060(i)001:8345: me dang chu ni rab tu bstan //
NK060(i)001:8347: rtags kyi yum ni dmigs su med la/
NK060(i)001:8348: don gyi yum ni chos kyi dbyings dang 'du 'bral med pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:8349: kun bzang yab yum gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:8351: kun tu bzang po phyag g.yon gyi thog tu g.yas
NK060(i)001:8352: mnyam par bzhag pa la ye shes 'od zer 'phro
NK060(i)001:8353: ba dang / yum yab kyi phyag rgya las 'gyur
NK060(i)001:8354: na g.yas kyi thog tu g.yon mnyam par bzhag pa
NK060(i)001:8355: la chos thams cad rdzogs pas mthe bong gnyis bkug
NK060(i)001:8356: nas pad+mo'i dkyil 'khor ltar byas pa dang /
NK060(i)001:8357: de las gzhan yang chos nyid cir yang snang ba'i
NK060(i)001:8358: phyir phyag rgya gcig tu ma nges pa sna tshogs
NK060(i)001:8359: pa ste/ yang na de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu bzang po dang rjes su mthun pa nyid dam/
NK060(i)001:8360: yang na rdo rje thal mo rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'am gsum pa nyid do //
NK060(i)001:8361: bzhi pa lta ba'i phyag rgya/
NK060(i)001:8363: rtog pa thams cad lha yab yum sku'i phyag rgya
NK060(i)001:8364: chen po sku gsung thugs su snang ba'i tshogs mchog
NK060(i)001:8365: ni/ thabs snang ba mi 'gog par gsal ba dang /
NK060(i)001:8366: shes rab 'dzin pa med par ldan pa'i don blo
NK060(i)001:8367: la 'byor na lus ma bskyod cing ma bsgul ba
NK060(i)001:8368: la sogs pa sgo gsum gyis ci byas thams cad
NK060(i)001:8369: kun kyang sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya chen po'i
NK060(i)001:8370: ngang du gnas pa la mi 'da' ba ni lta
NK060(i)001:8371: ba'i phyag rgya ste/ phyag rgya'i nang nas mchog yin no //
NK060(i)001:8372: lnga pa phyag rgya spros pa dang bcas pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:8374: snang ba rnam 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin la bslab pa'i thabs/
NK060(i)001:8376: yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu tham pa rtsa ba'i lha yab yum gnyis la ldan par bsgom ste/
NK060(i)001:8377: de yang bdag rtsa ba'i lha mi bskyod pa yab
NK060(i)001:8378: yum yin pa dbang btsan du byas nas de ltar
NK060(i)001:8379: du gsal ba la/ gzhan yan lag gi lha yab
NK060(i)001:8380: nyi shu rtsa gsum rtsa ba'i lha yab la dgod
NK060(i)001:8381: du gsal ba la/ de/ dbu la rnam par snang mdzad/
NK060(i)001:8382: lag pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la kun tu bzang po dang /
NK060(i)001:8383: g.yon gyi cha la rin cen 'byung ldan/
NK060(i)001:8384: rkang pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la don grub/
NK060(i)001:8385: g.yon gyi cha la mtha' yas/
NK060(i)001:8386: mig rna ba sna lce rnams kyi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha rnams su go rim bzhin/
NK060(i)001:8391: g.yon gyi cha rnams su byams pa/
NK060(i)001:8405: sum mdo rnams su lha la sogs pa'i thub pa drug dgod do //
NK060(i)001:8406: de bzhin du yan lag gi lha yum bcu bdun rtsa ba'i lha yum la dgod de/
NK060(i)001:8407: dgod tshul yab dang mtshungs so //
NK060(i)001:8408: rtsa ba'i lha rnam snang yab yum dbang btsan du byas nas/
NK060(i)001:8409: yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu dgod na/
NK060(i)001:8410: lag pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la mi bskyod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:8411: g.yon gyi cha la kun tu bzang mo dgod/
NK060(i)001:8412: de bzhin du rin 'byung yab yum la sogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:8413: rtsa ba'i lha yab yum rang rang gi go sa
NK060(i)001:8414: gang yin du kun bzang yab yum dgod la/
NK060(i)001:8415: de las gzhan rnams sngar mi bskyod pa la yan lag gi lha bkod pa dang mtshungs so //
NK060(i)001:8416: yang thub drug re re'ang rtsa ba'i lha yin pa dbang btsan du byas na/
NK060(i)001:8417: thub pa drug la yum med pas g.yas kyi cha la yab nyi shu rtsa gsum dang /
NK060(i)001:8418: g.yon gyi cha la yum bcu bdun dgod de/
NK060(i)001:8419: spyi bo'i g.yas kyi cha la rnam snang dang /
NK060(i)001:8420: g.yon gyi cha la spyan ma/
NK060(i)001:8421: lag pa g.yas kyi 'dom rtsa'i mdun dang rgyab la mi bskyod pa dang rin 'byung /
NK060(i)001:8422: rkang pa g.yas kyi 'dom rtsa'i mdun dang rgyab la mtha' yas dang don grub/
NK060(i)001:8425: sna/ lce rnams kyi rtsa'i nang du/
NK060(i)001:8426: nang gi sems dpa' bzhin dang /
NK060(i)001:8427: phyi ru phyi'i sems dpa' bzhi lag mthil g.yas kyi
NK060(i)001:8428: mdun dang rgyab tu gshin rje gshed dang stobs po
NK060(i)001:8429: che/ rkang mthil g.yas kyi mdun dang rgyab tu bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang rta mgrin dgod/
NK060(i)001:8430: de yang rtsa ba'i lha lha'i thub pa yin na/
NK060(i)001:8431: mtshog mar kun tu ba zang po/
NK060(i)001:8432: sta zur la sogs pa la lha ma yin la
NK060(i)001:8433: sogs pa'i thub pa dgod pa sngar dang mtshungs so
NK060(i)001:8434: // mdor na rtsa ba'i lha gang yin yang yum
NK060(i)001:8435: dang bcas pa rnams rtsa ba'i lha yab yum gnyis
NK060(i)001:8436: ka la yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu dgod pa
NK060(i)001:8437: // yin la/ yum med thub pa rnams rtsa ba'i
NK060(i)001:8438: lha re re la yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu
NK060(i)001:8439: bzhi bcu dgod pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:8440: yan lag gi lha kun bzang yab yum ni/
NK060(i)001:8441: rtsa ba'i lha gang dang gang yin pa de dang
NK060(i)001:8442: de'i gnas su dgod pa ni kun mthun pa yin
NK060(i)001:8443: no // de ltar yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu ni/
NK060(i)001:8444: rags pa'i cha nas thabs kyi lhar bzhag la/
NK060(i)001:8445: de nyid yan lag spros zhes pas/
NK060(i)001:8446: mi gcig grub na snying cig grub pa'i tshul du/
NK060(i)001:8447: thabs kyi lha re re'i yang srog gi gor ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang ba re re bsgom ste/
NK060(i)001:8448: phra ba'i cha nas shes rab kyi lhar bzhag pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:8449: de ltar thabs dang shes rab kyi lha brgyad cu la/
NK060(i)001:8450: shes rab kyi lha bzhi bcu ni bu mos pha'i
NK060(i)001:8451: rabs mi zin pa'i tshul du rgyan dang cha lugs
NK060(i)001:8452: rnam par spangs pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:8453: thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu po rtsa ba'i lha yab
NK060(i)001:8454: yum gnyis la bkod pa rnams re re la yang
NK060(i)001:8456: dpral mgrin snying gar sku gsung thugs kyi lha re re ste brgya nyi shu'o //
NK060(i)001:8457: de ltar thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu dang bcas pas
NK060(i)001:8458: brgya drug cu po re re la'ang gong gi bdag
NK060(i)001:8459: ste zhes pas/ rang rang gi rigs kyi bdag pos
NK060(i)001:8460: gtso byas pa'i dbu rgyan rigs kyi lha lnga lnga
NK060(i)001:8461: ste zhes pas/ ste brgyad bargya'o // mdor na thabs dang shes rab kyi lha brgyad cu/
NK060(i)001:8462: sku gsung thugs mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i lha brgya nyi shu/
NK060(i)001:8463: dbu rgyan gyi lha brgyad brgya ste/
NK060(i)001:8464: kun dril bas rtsa ba'i lha yab yum gnyis la yan lag dang lhag pa'i lha stong bsgom pa ni/
NK060(i)001:8465: tshom bu stong gi dkyil 'khor la bslab pa zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8466: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog rdo rje sems dpa'
NK060(i)001:8467: yab yum gyi gtso byas pa la yan lag gi
NK060(i)001:8468: lha ji ltar bkod pa bzhin/
NK060(i)001:8469: gzhan yang rgyal ba rigs bzhi rgyal mchog kun bzang
NK060(i)001:8470: yab yum ste drug po la'ang yan lag gi lha
NK060(i)001:8471: mi bskyod pa yab yum la bkod pa de bzhin
NK060(i)001:8472: du brtsis pa yab yum zung re re la'ang stong
NK060(i)001:8473: tsho re re/ sems dpa' yab yum brgyad sgo ba
NK060(i)001:8474: yab yum bzhi ste zung bcu gnyis la stong tsho
NK060(i)001:8475: tsho re re/ bcu gnyis/ thub pa drug po re re la stong tsho re re ste/
NK060(i)001:8476: de ltar thub drug gi stong tsho drug dang bcas
NK060(i)001:8477: pas stong tsho nyi shu rtsa bzhi po thams cad
NK060(i)001:8478: kyang 'od 'phro zhing gzi brjid 'bar ba bsgom pa
NK060(i)001:8479: ni nyi khri bzhi stong gi dkyil 'khor la bslab
NK060(i)001:8480: pa zhes bya'o // de la sogs pa snod bcud
NK060(i)001:8481: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor bsam gyis mi
NK060(i)001:8483: bsam yas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor la bslab pa zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:8484: snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i rim pa'o //
NK060(i)001:8485: 'di dag kyang lam mthar chags pa phyag rgya spros bcas la slob pa'i dbang du yin gyis/
NK060(i)001:8486: lam thod rgal ba'i rten gyi gang zag tshogs bsgrub
NK060(i)001:8487: pa'i mi dgos par mthong lam la sbyor ba'ang yod
NK060(i)001:8488: do // yang kha cig na re/
NK060(i)001:8489: gong nas ma bsgul ma bskyod thams cad kun //
NK060(i)001:8492: mdor na bsgul bskyod thams cad kun //
NK060(i)001:8493: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK060(i)001:8496: gong ma ni blo che ba la lta ba gtso che ba'i ngos na smos la/
NK060(i)001:8497: 'og ma ni blo chung ba la spyod pa gtso
NK060(i)001:8498: che ba'i ngos nas smos pa'i zhes bla ma rnams
NK060(i)001:8499: gsung ngo // des 'gro ba'i don byed tshul lo //
NK060(i)001:8501: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa gdul bya'i gnas
NK060(i)001:8502: bsam yas pa rnams su gong ltar lha'i ting nge
NK060(i)001:8503: 'dzin gyi gyis gdul bya gdul ba'i don rnams ji
NK060(i)001:8504: ltar mos pa ltar so sor ston cing re bskong
NK060(i)001:8505: ba'o // 'o na dkyil 'khor kho na'o snyam pa la/
NK060(i)001:8506: theg pa ma thob gsang sngags dang dman pa mtshan nyid la sogs pa'i theg pa thams cad dang /
NK060(i)001:8507: mu stegs rtags chad la sogs pa phyin ci log
NK060(i)001:8508: rnams kyang so so'i bsam pa mtha' yas pa dang
NK060(i)001:8509: mthun pas 'dul ba'i gnyen por so so'i ston pa
NK060(i)001:8510: dang lha dang bdud srin la sogs pa'i zhi ba
NK060(i)001:8511: dang / khro bo'i tshogs chen po thams cad la
NK060(i)001:8512: rang rang gi mos pa ltar so sor bsam pa
NK060(i)001:8513: dang mthun par byas pa kun tu snang yang de
NK060(i)001:8514: dag la rtsol ba med de/
NK060(i)001:8515: dper na gar mkhan nyid dang 'dra bar lus ma
NK060(i)001:8516: g.yos par gar gyi bkod pa sna tshogs su ston
NK060(i)001:8517: pa ltar ro // de yang sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las/
NK060(i)001:8518: sa gsum thams cad kun tu ni //
NK060(i)001:8519: byang chub chen po ston byed pa //
NK060(i)001:8521: res 'ga' zhi ba res 'ga' drag /res 'ga' gdon chen bgegs mdzad de //
NK060(i)001:8522: de la sogs pa bsam yas mchog /ri dang skye bo thams cad do //
NK060(i)001:8524: drug pa phyag rgya'i rnam grangs bsdu ba dang bcas pa'i/
NK060(i)001:8526: phyag rgya thams cad tshig gis mdor bsdu na lus
NK060(i)001:8527: kyi yan lag gi phyag rgya thams cad ni 'di
NK060(i)001:8528: kho na'o zhes sam gcig kho na'o zhes brjod du
NK060(i)001:8529: mtha' gcig tu nges pa med de/
NK060(i)001:8530: lus kyi yan lag gi dbang du zhabs gnyis dang dbu gcig phyag gnyis te gsum mo //
NK060(i)001:8531: de ltar du lus kyi yan lag lnga po re
NK060(i)001:8532: re la'ang rigs lnga yab yum bcu bcu'i ting nge
NK060(i)001:8533: 'dzin gyi rnam par 'byung ba las phyag rgya lnga
NK060(i)001:8534: bcu 'phro ba'am/ yang na rtog pa'i yan lag gi
NK060(i)001:8535: dbang du thabs dang shes rab gnyis kyi lha brgyad
NK060(i)001:8536: bcu 'phro ba'am/ cu dang / thabs kyi lha la
NK060(i)001:8537: sku gsung thugs gsum gsum du byas pas brgya nyi
NK060(i)001:8538: bcu 'phro ba'am/ cu dang / shu dang / de
NK060(i)001:8539: dag kyang rnam par 'phro ba dbu rgyan gyi lha
NK060(i)001:8541: de'i phyir lus bskyod pa dang ting nge 'dzin spro
NK060(i)001:8542: ba dang lha'i phyag rgya'i de bzhin nyid kyang shes
NK060(i)001:8543: par bya ste/ mdor na lus bsgul zhing bskyod pa thams cad kun rang bzhin dang /
NK060(i)001:8544: lta ba dang 'bras bu'i phyag rgyar gsal ba'i dus na/
NK060(i)001:8545: de nyid kyi sku gsung thugs kho na las mi
NK060(i)001:8546: 'da' bas na phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas
NK060(i)001:8547: la/ de tsam du gnas pa nyid na der yang
NK060(i)001:8548: blos mi 'dzin pas mi gnas pa dang gnas pa'i
NK060(i)001:8549: tha snyad bya ba'ang min no zhes so //
NK060(i)001:8550: de skad du spyod yul dag pa'i mchog kun tu bzang po nyid kyis bshad do //
NK060(i)001:8551: de ltar phyag rgya'i rim pa nyams su len tshul ni/
NK060(i)001:8552: zur chung shes rab grags pa'i bzhed kyis/
NK060(i)001:8553: blo chung nyams rim dang po pa la/
NK060(i)001:8554: sa zin sko 'thas su bslab pa spang la be phur btab pa lta bu ste/
NK060(i)001:8555: rigs dang sku mdog phyag mtshan rnams nges pa can du bsgom pa dang /
NK060(i)001:8556: blo 'bring nyams rim bar pa la/
NK060(i)001:8557: don mi 'gyur la gnas skabs 'gyur pa la bslab thabs mkha'i 'bab chu lta bu ste/
NK060(i)001:8558: rigs nges la sku mdog dang phyag mtshan nges med du bsgom pa dang /
NK060(i)001:8559: blo rab nyams rim tha ma pa la/
NK060(i)001:8560: nges med chen po'i bslab thabs nam mkha' la mdung bskor ba lta bu ste/
NK060(i)001:8561: rigs dang sku mdog phyag mtshan nges med du bsgom pa'i tshul dang gsum du bzhed do //
NK060(i)001:8563: de skad dag mchog nyid kyis bshad //
NK060(i)001:8565: gsang ba'i snying po 'di ston pa kun tu bzang pos gsungs pa'i rgyud ma yin no zhe na/
NK060(i)001:8568: 'di ni sdud pa po'i tshig yin pas so //
NK060(i)001:8569: gal te de ltar yin kyang skyon du 'gyur na/
NK060(i)001:8570: 'phags pa sdud pa 'di yang de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsungs ma yin par thal/
NK060(i)001:8571: de dag ma rig las byung bde bar gshegs pas gsungs/
NK060(i)001:8572: bya ba 'dug pa'i phyir ro zhes basgre'o //
NK060(i)001:8573: zhes bla ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:8576: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las mtshan gyi gzhi 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:8577: lus dang rtogs pa'i yan lag thams cad phyag rgya
NK060(i)001:8578: gsum gyi dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub par byin
NK060(i)001:8579: gyis brlabs nas rang bzhin dang /
NK060(i)001:8581: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya spros pa'i
NK060(i)001:8582: mtshams 'dzin par byed pas na le'u ste yas bgrangs
NK060(i)001:8583: brgyad pa'i don du gada'o////da ni le'u dgu pa'i chos
NK060(i)001:8584: tshoms ngos bzung na/ rab kyi chos tshom sa gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las/
NK060(i)001:8587: lam la thabs grol gnyis las gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:8588: mtshan nyid gsum las rkyen 'jug pa dang 'bras bu mthar phyin ston/
NK060(i)001:8589: snang ba bzhi las lam dang 'bras bu'i snang ba ston/
NK060(i)001:8590: rim cig car gnyis las gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:8591: 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las rgyud don/
NK060(i)001:8592: de la dngos po bcu yod pa las dkyil 'khor dang dbang dang sgrub pa gsum ston/
NK060(i)001:8593: zhor la spyod pa dang lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa ston/
NK060(i)001:8594: phrin las dang ting nge 'dzin dang phyag rgya zur tsam ston/
NK060(i)001:8596: ldem dgongs man ngag /mtshon pa dpe/
NK060(i)001:8598: gzhan yang spyi 'gro rnams kyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:8599: de ltar ston pa'i le'u dgu pa 'di la gsum/
NK060(i)001:8601: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:8603: de yan chad du lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:8604: da lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ston pas na de nas zhes 'brel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:8605: de bzhin gshegs pa ni ngo bo la mtshan du btags pa ste 'bru sngar bshad zin la/
NK060(i)001:8606: dgyes pa ni longs spyod la mtshan du btags pa ste dga' ba'i sde pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:8607: dga' ba la rnam dbye bzhi las/
NK060(i)001:8608: gzhi thun mong gi dga' ba ni/
NK060(i)001:8609: 'dod pa khams pa 'dod chags kyi bde ba la nye bar spyod pa'o //
NK060(i)001:8611: khams gong ma gnyis kyi bsam gtan gyi bde ba la nye bar spyod pa'o //
NK060(i)001:8613: sa dang po bden pa mthong ba'i dga' ba ste
NK060(i)001:8614: zag pa med pa'i bde ba la nye bar spyod
NK060(i)001:8615: pa'o // bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dga' ba ni/
NK060(i)001:8616: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad chos nyid mnyam pa
NK060(i)001:8617: nyid pas blang dor med pa'i bde ba la longs
NK060(i)001:8618: spyod pa ste/ de nyid dga' ba snga ma gsum las khyad par du gyur bas na chen po ste/
NK060(i)001:8619: sku gsung thugs ye shes rdo rjer lhun gyis grub
NK060(i)001:8620: pa de phal gyi yul ma yin pas na gsang
NK060(i)001:8621: ba'i mtshams sbyor las mi 'da' bas na dam tshig
NK060(i)001:8622: go // dkyil 'khor dang dbang dang grub pa gsum
NK060(i)001:8623: gyi las kyi rim pa la bkod pa'i ting nge
NK060(i)001:8624: 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas ched du brjod pa
NK060(i)001:8629: gzhung dngos la spyi don gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:8630: dkyil 'khor ye shes rdo rje dang /
NK060(i)001:8632: grub pa ye shes rdo rje'o //
NK060(i)001:8633: spyi don dang po la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:8635: phra mo la blo sbyang ba'i slob dpon gyis bsnyen pa bya ba las mi 'da' ba/
NK060(i)001:8637: gzhan don gnyer bar byed pa'i bla mas thog mar ting nge 'dzin gsum bsgom zhing yi ge dang /
NK060(i)001:8639: sku rnams shin tu phra ba la blo sbyangs pa
NK060(i)001:8640: yis sku gsung thugs kyi ting nge 'dzin shin tu
NK060(i)001:8641: phra ba'i sgo nas bzlas brjod rdzogs par bya ba
NK060(i)001:8642: las mi 'da' bas na dam tshig gi mchog go
NK060(i)001:8643: // dkyil 'khor gyi las kyi rim pa'o //
NK060(i)001:8647: mchog gi dkyil 'khor zhi ba ltar shes par gdams pa'o //
NK060(i)001:8650: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang //
NK060(i)001:8651: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang //
NK060(i)001:8652: rab gnas sbyin sreg dkyil 'khor du //
NK060(i)001:8653: 'jug dang zhugs pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:8656: dang po sa chog bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:8658: yang na zhes pa dgar ba'i tshig ste/
NK060(i)001:8659: dgar gzhi gang la dgar na/
NK060(i)001:8662: brgyad pa gsum du lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:8664: gal te der 'jug par mi nus na yang /
NK060(i)001:8665: thog mar gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:8666: dang pos gzhi rab tu mnyam par bya ba'i sa'i cho ga la/
NK060(i)001:8668: gzhi dang rang mtshan blang dbang dang //
NK060(i)001:8669: sbyang byin bsrung dang bzung ba ni //
NK060(i)001:8670: dang po'i nying lag nyid du bshad //
NK060(i)001:8673: kho bos sgyu 'phrul gyi dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga'i
NK060(i)001:8674: lag len khrigs ma byas yod pas der shes par
NK060(i)001:8675: bya'o // gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gyi tshad la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:8676: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyiil 'khor gyi tshad dang /
NK060(i)001:8677: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor tshad gsum bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:8682: de yang gnas khang dog cing slob ma 'byor pa
NK060(i)001:8683: chung na dkyil 'khor logs re la khru gang re
NK060(i)001:8684: yod pa'i tshad du bya ba'am/
NK060(i)001:8685: yang na lus gang ba'i tshad du ste/
NK060(i)001:8686: logs re la khru bzhi bzhi yod pa'o //
NK060(i)001:8689: yang zhes pa ba sdus pa'i tsha las dkar na
NK060(i)001:8690: logs re la khru bcu gnyis bcu gnyis te lus
NK060(i)001:8691: ni gsum cha'i tshad du bya ba'am/
NK060(i)001:8692: yang na logs re la khru ni bcu drug bcu
NK060(i)001:8693: drug dang ldan pa ste lus bzhi pa'i tshad du
NK060(i)001:8696: yang gnas khang yangs shing slob bu 'byor pa che na/
NK060(i)001:8697: dkyil 'khor gyi logs re la khru nyi shu nyi shu 'am/
NK060(i)001:8698: yang na logs re la khru nyi shu rtsa lnga lngar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8699: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad gsum/
NK060(i)001:8701: yang gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor gyi tshad bshad pa de
NK060(i)001:8702: dag la dgar na gzhu 'dom lnga brgya ni rgyang
NK060(i)001:8704: rnal 'byor pa ting nge 'dzin rtsal zhan na de tsam du bsgom mo //
NK060(i)001:8705: rgyang grags brgyad ni dpag tshad kyi tshad de/
NK060(i)001:8706: ting nge 'dzin rtsal 'bring na de tshod dam/
NK060(i)001:8707: ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsal rab kyis nam mkha'i dbyings
NK060(i)001:8708: ni bsam gyis mi khyab cing mtha' yas par khyab
NK060(i)001:8709: pa de bzhin du sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor sna
NK060(i)001:8710: tshogs pa'ang bsam gyis mi khyab par bsgom pa'o //
NK060(i)001:8711: de yang lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la tshad drug byung ba ni/
NK060(i)001:8712: slob dpon phyag bzo mi bzo dang /
NK060(i)001:8713: slob bu 'byor pa che chung dang /
NK060(i)001:8714: gnas khang yang dog gi dbang gis ji ltar rigs par bya ba'i tshad yin la/
NK060(i)001:8715: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin nam mchog gi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad gsum ni/
NK060(i)001:8716: slob dpon dgongs pa zab mi zab dang /
NK060(i)001:8717: slob bu las dag tshabs che chung gi dbang gi 'byung ba yin no //
NK060(i)001:8718: 'o na lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi skabs su lhag
NK060(i)001:8719: pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad smos
NK060(i)001:8720: pas skabs 'chol ba'i skyon du 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:8722: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyis mtshon nas lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pas/
NK060(i)001:8723: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor mngon du byed pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:8724: gsum pa thig la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:8728: gzhan sel phung po lnga dag pa/
NK060(i)001:8729: don gnyer sku lnga thob par bya ba'i phyir 'bru lnga/
NK060(i)001:8730: de bzhin du dbang po lnga phrin las lngar dag byed spos lnga/
NK060(i)001:8731: yon tan lngar dag byed rin chen lnga/
NK060(i)001:8732: rnam shes lnga ye shes lngar dag byed kyi snying po lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:8733: 'dod yon lnga gsung lngar dag byed sman lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:8734: khams lnga rigs lngar dag byed bdud rtsi lnga yin pas/
NK060(i)001:8735: de dag ni cha rab tu mnyam pa'i lde gus
NK060(i)001:8736: byugs la rig pa ma yes pas thig ni rim
NK060(i)001:8739: de las bcad nang tshegs drug las/
NK060(i)001:8740: thig skud kyi rgyu bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:8742: spyir gyis thig ni mi 'gyur bar byed pa cig yin la/
NK060(i)001:8743: de'i rgyu phur bu zhes pa 'gying phur bskor phur gnyis sta gon bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8744: srad bu ni thig skud de/
NK060(i)001:8745: dam tshig gi skud rgyu ras bal 'jam po dang /
NK060(i)001:8746: ye shes kyi skud rgyu me tog pad ma'i rgyus pa la bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8749: dar gyi chos gos lnga dang rin po che'i rgyan chas brgyad de/
NK060(i)001:8750: bcu gsum gyis mdzes par brgyan pa'i bu mo lo
NK060(i)001:8751: bcu drug ma yid du 'ong ba'i grogs mo dkyil
NK060(i)001:8752: 'khor che chung gi tshad dang sbyar ba'i skud pa
NK060(i)001:8753: sbom srid tshad dang ldan pa 'khal du gzhug go
NK060(i)001:8756: dam tshig gi thig skud tshon gyi kha dog gi phye ba'i gsum bsgrib lam dgu bsgril dang /
NK060(i)001:8757: ye shes kyi thig skud lnga bsgril lam nyi shu rtsa lngar bsgril bar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8760: ye shes kyi skud pa ye shes lngar/
NK060(i)001:8762: dam tshig gi skud pa sku gsung thugs su brlabs pa'i cho ga dang /
NK060(i)001:8769: bstim/ mchod/ bstod/ gsol ba gdab pa la sogs pa phun sun tshogs par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8772: rdo rje rgyal po yab yum gnyis lha skur gsal
NK060(i)001:8773: ba'i sbyor mtshams nas dam tshig gi thig sku gsung
NK060(i)001:8774: thugs kyi rang bzhin btab pa de'i steng du ye
NK060(i)001:8775: shes kyi thig gdab par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:8776: sku gsung thugs re re yang ye shes lnga lnga'i ro dang ldan par bsgom par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8779: thig 'debs thabs kyi man ngag dang ldan pa'i mkha'
NK060(i)001:8780: ldan pa'i mkhas ldan chen po des rig pa ma
NK060(i)001:8781: yengs par bsgrims te thig skud ma chad par/
NK060(i)001:8784: thig la ma 'goms par gdab par bya dgos so //
NK060(i)001:8785: de yang rdo rje las rim las/
NK060(i)001:8786: thig skud chad na slob dpon 'grongs //
NK060(i)001:8787: phyogs 'khrul bas ni gnyis ka nyams //
NK060(i)001:8788: rgyun chad lam la gnod pa ste //
NK060(i)001:8789: de phyir mkhas ldan bsgrims te bya //
NK060(i)001:8792: rab gnas ldan pa'i thig 'goms na //
NK060(i)001:8793: bde gshegs skur pa btab dang mtshungs //
NK060(i)001:8794: sangs rgyas chos las ring 'gyur bas //
NK060(i)001:8795: hri sgra'i phyag rgyas 'dzul bar bya //
NK060(i)001:8797: bzhin pa tshon gyi cho ga la lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:8801: 'og nas 'chad bzhin pa'i tshon rnams snod gtsang mar blug la/
NK060(i)001:8803: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor yab yum cha lnga'am/
NK060(i)001:8804: rgyas par rigs chung yab yum dang bcas pa rnams te lha lnga bcu bsgom pa yang rung ngo //
NK060(i)001:8805: de yang rdo rje las rim las/
NK060(i)001:8806: snod rim ma 'dres dag byas la //
NK060(i)001:8807: h+aum sogs yig 'bru gcig kyang lngar //
NK060(i)001:8808: kha dog rjes su mthun byas la //
NK060(i)001:8809: yongs 'gyur nyi shu rtsa lnga'i lhar //
NK060(i)001:8810: thabs dang shes rab ldan par bsgom //
NK060(i)001:8811: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pas mngon no //
NK060(i)001:8814: sems can rnams kyi rang gi sems ye shes lngar
NK060(i)001:8815: gnas kyang ma mthong zhing blo rmongs pa rnams la
NK060(i)001:8816: rang la yod pa'i don bstan par bya ba'i phyir
NK060(i)001:8818: tshon gyi kha dog gi grangs dur nges she na/
NK060(i)001:8819: rgyas par nyi shu rtsa lnga'am/
NK060(i)001:8820: bsdus par kha dog lnga yis kyang rung ste/
NK060(i)001:8821: mtshams sems khro bo la sogs phyir //
NK060(i)001:8822: kha dog nyi shu rtsa lngar gsungs //
NK060(i)001:8826: rab rin po che sna lnga'i tshon gyis bya bar gsungs te/
NK060(i)001:8828: push+pa r+aa ga byu ru zangs //
NK060(i)001:8829: mrgad ta las byas pa dgye //
NK060(i)001:8831: 'bring sman lnga kha dog bsgyur ba dang /
NK060(i)001:8832: tha ma sa tshon kha dog lnga la bya ste/
NK060(i)001:8834: 'bras dang s+aa lu la sogs pa //
NK060(i)001:8835: kha dog bsgyur ba de bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:8836: sman dang 'byor pa chung ba yis //
NK060(i)001:8837: 'byung khungs lnga yis bri bar bya //
NK060(i)001:8839: tshon gyi bkye lugs nyes dmigs dang bcas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:8841: thog mar tshon pra brtag pa'i don du/
NK060(i)001:8842: rdo rje rgyal po kha shar du phyogs pa'i khu tshur g.yon gyis dbang ldan gyi mtshams nas brtsams te/
NK060(i)001:8843: pany+tsa re kha'i sar mdzub gang ba'i pany+tsa re kha bri'o //
NK060(i)001:8844: de la ka p+aa la mtshan ldan bkab la tshon pra brtag par bya zhing /
NK060(i)001:8845: slob bu rnams dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gang
NK060(i)001:8846: gis 'dul ba'i cho ga bzhin du rdul tshon bkye
NK060(i)001:8847: bar bya ste/ 'chad par 'gyur pa'i dkyil 'khor bri ba'i skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8848: de yang bag dang ldan pas tshul bzhin ma bris na nyes dmigs ni/
NK060(i)001:8849: spyir thig gi skabs dang yang rjes su mthun pa
NK060(i)001:8850: las khyad par du tshon rtsi srab na dbul por
NK060(i)001:8852: tshon thal shor na nad rims 'byung ba'i nyes dmigs yod gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:8853: bye brag tshon pra la nyes skyon byung na/
NK060(i)001:8854: de bsal ba'i cho ga bzhin du bsal bar ma byas na bar chad 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:8858: lte ba rtsibs dang bcas pa'i 'khor lo chung ba
NK060(i)001:8859: cha re re dang ldan pa'i rtsibs bzhi po'i 'khor
NK060(i)001:8860: lo mu khyud zlum po gnyis dang bcas pa'am/
NK060(i)001:8861: bsdus 'bring ltar na ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa/
NK060(i)001:8862: bden pa bzhi mtshon pa'i gru chad bzhi dang che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa gru bzhi'i dbyibs can/
NK060(i)001:8863: bsdus pa ltar na bar khyams med kyang rgyas 'bring
NK060(i)001:8864: gtso che ba'i dbang du byas na bar khyams sgo
NK060(i)001:8865: bzhi sgo khyud dang bcas pa bri bar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:8866: drug pa rnam pa dgod pa/
NK060(i)001:8868: khru gang pa la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la sku tsaka li gsung yig 'bru thugs phyag mtshan te/
NK060(i)001:8869: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gang rung dang ldan
NK060(i)001:8870: pa'i gzugs kyang ji ltar 'byor pa dgod par bya'o
NK060(i)001:8871: // de yang rdo rje las rim las/
NK060(i)001:8872: dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum dag tu //
NK060(i)001:8873: gzhung nyid kyis ni gsal bar gsungs //
NK060(i)001:8874: yan lag gzugs sku snying po nyid //
NK060(i)001:8875: nyi zla pad+ma'i rim bzhugs pa //
NK060(i)001:8876: dkyil 'khor sku yi mtshan nyid ni //
NK060(i)001:8877: phyag rgya gsal bkod thugs dkyil 'khor //
NK060(i)001:8878: tha ma yang na h+aum m+aum ni //
NK060(i)001:8879: mchog dang 'bring pos phye ba ni //
NK060(i)001:8880: dkyil 'khor gsum du bshad par bya //
NK060(i)001:8883: sngar gyi gsung sgros la bum pa la sogs pa yan lag gi rab gnas dang /
NK060(i)001:8885: dkyil 'khor rab gnas dang gsum du gsungs/
NK060(i)001:8886: dkyil 'khor rab gnas la'ang sngon du bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:8888: rjes kyi bya ba dang gsum du gsungs mod kyis/
NK060(i)001:8889: kho bos dbang dang rab gnas kyi phyag len khrigs
NK060(i)001:8890: chags yod pas zhib par der shes par bya zhing
NK060(i)001:8891: / 'dir gzhung bshad kyi dbang du drug ste/
NK060(i)001:8895: bcos bu'i ras ni dkar dmar la sogs pa'i kha dog dang /
NK060(i)001:8896: bla bre 'phan gdugs la sogs pa'i dbyibs kyi bye brag rigs mi mthun pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:8897: rin po che'i rgyan chun 'phyang dang phreng ba la
NK060(i)001:8898: sogs pa rgyan gyi bye brag sna tshogs pa dang
NK060(i)001:8900: bza' btung dang g.yos kyi bye brag ro bro bas kyang bskor zhing /
NK060(i)001:8903: dar sna bzhi la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:8906: chu bdun dbang po'i skyon bsal/
NK060(i)001:8907: sku dang rgyan chas kyi mnga' gsol gyi chas/
NK060(i)001:8908: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa'i yo byad dang bcas
NK060(i)001:8909: pa bkod pa phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par
NK060(i)001:8910: bya'o // stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba/
NK060(i)001:8912: de yang mtshams bcad nas brtsams nas/
NK060(i)001:8913: 'dod don gsol ba yan chad gzhung bsrang zhing /
NK060(i)001:8916: thugs phyag mtshan gang yin gyi phyag rgya dkyil 'khor la bkod pa rnams dang /
NK060(i)001:8917: rnal 'byor pa'i lus ngag sems dang /
NK060(i)001:8918: der ma zad 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das
NK060(i)001:8919: pa'i bsdus pa'i chos thams cad sems kyi snang ba
NK060(i)001:8920: tsam las gzhan gang na'ang mi gnas shing sems kyi
NK060(i)001:8921: snang ba tsam du'ang mi dmigs par/
NK060(i)001:8922: dper na mig yor snang yang ngo bo ma grub
NK060(i)001:8923: pa'i tshul du sems nyid spyir yang mi dmigs pa'i
NK060(i)001:8924: ngang du mnyam par sbyor ba yis/
NK060(i)001:8925: sh+au nya ta'i sngags kyis kyang dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa sbyangs pas/
NK060(i)001:8926: mtha' bral stong pa nyid nam mkha' lta bu la
NK060(i)001:8927: ni blos dmigs su med par rang gsal bar sems
NK060(i)001:8928: nyid mtha' dbus dang bral ba nam mkha' lta bu
NK060(i)001:8929: bsgom mo // rol mo lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa/
NK060(i)001:8931: thog mar 'og nas rol mo zhes pa dper blangs te/
NK060(i)001:8932: gzhi ma nges pa las thabs kyis sna tshogs su snang ba bzhin du/
NK060(i)001:8933: stong pa nyid kyi ngang las rol mo lta bu'i
NK060(i)001:8934: ting nge 'dzin gyis rang dbang sgyur ba ni mtha'
NK060(i)001:8935: yas pa'i mchog ste/ mi rtog pa'i ye shes las 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor/
NK060(i)001:8936: yi ge tha tha la sogs pa'am yang na nyi
NK060(i)001:8937: zla la sogs pa'i gdan nam h+aum m+aum la sogs
NK060(i)001:8938: pa'i snying po'am sku yongs su rdzogs pa phyag rgya
NK060(i)001:8939: chen po'am gang yang rung bar bskyed cing /
NK060(i)001:8940: sku gsung thugs dang ldan par byin gyis brlabs na
NK060(i)001:8941: dngos grub ya mtshan can thun mong ma yin pa
NK060(i)001:8942: 'byung bas na rmad po che de nyid/
NK060(i)001:8945: yang yang bsgoms na 'grub par 'gyur te/
NK060(i)001:8946: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)001:8947: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)001:8948: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gsum 'tshogs pas/
NK060(i)001:8949: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes 'grub pa las mi
NK060(i)001:8950: 'da' ba'i phyir sangs rgyas kun gyi dam tshig ces
NK060(i)001:8951: bya'o // ting nge 'dzin gnyis kyis sbyangs shing bskyed pa'i yon tan/
NK060(i)001:8953: sa la lde gu dang la sogs pa'i sogs khongs nas gser dngul rag zangs la lugs su blugs pa'am/
NK060(i)001:8954: rwa shing la sogs pa la rkos su bskos pa'am/
NK060(i)001:8955: ras sam gro shog la ris su bris pa'i sku
NK060(i)001:8956: gsung thugs kyis phyag rgya'i dbyibs su byas shing mchod
NK060(i)001:8957: pa dang bstod pa byas pa tsam gyis kyang /
NK060(i)001:8959: sems dag tshabs che chung gi dbang gis rnam grol gyi rim pa gnas skabs mtho ris dang /
NK060(i)001:8960: mthar thug thar pa thob par 'gyur na dag pa'i
NK060(i)001:8961: ye shes stong nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyangs
NK060(i)001:8962: shing / rol mo lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK060(i)001:8963: lhar bskyed pas 'bras bu thob pa smos ci dgos
NK060(i)001:8964: shing / te/ sems kyi rnam pa lha'i skur gsal ba de nyid rang 'bras bu yin no //
NK060(i)001:8965: ye shes spyan drang zhing gzhug pa/
NK060(i)001:8967: de yang gang spyan drang na phyogs bcu dang dus
NK060(i)001:8968: bzhis bsdus pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi bdag nyid
NK060(i)001:8971: sems nyid spyi'i ngo bor yang mi dmigs pa thugs
NK060(i)001:8972: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi ngang la ye
NK060(i)001:8973: shes lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor de las
NK060(i)001:8974: so // mang nyung gi tshad ji tsam na dkyil
NK060(i)001:8975: 'khor de nyid cig kyang ye shes lnga lngar gsal
NK060(i)001:8976: bar thams cad du rang snang ba'i phyir blos tshad
NK060(i)001:8977: so // gzung du med de/ chos kyi dbyings kyi mtha' klas pa spyan drang ngo //
NK060(i)001:8978: gang la brten nas na sems nyid rang snang ba'i
NK060(i)001:8979: ye shes su dbyer med pa'i dkyil 'khor de la'o
NK060(i)001:8980: // de ji ltar bstim na phyag rgya bzhis gnyis su med par ro //
NK060(i)001:8981: de'i dgos ched ci zhe na rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan
NK060(i)001:8982: nyid ting nge 'dzin nyams su lon par bsgom zhing
NK060(i)001:8983: / dam tshig dang ye shes mnyam par sbyor bas
NK060(i)001:8984: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi kun nas bdag don du
NK060(i)001:8986: gzhan don du sems can gyi don la gshegs pa'i
NK060(i)001:8987: yon tan lngar bsnyen pa yi yi dam gyi lha
NK060(i)001:8988: dang / lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:8989: la sogs pa thams cad kyang rang rig pa'i ye
NK060(i)001:8990: shes kyi ngang du rab tu rdzogs par byed do
NK060(i)001:8991: dang / // dus nam na nye bar gyur pa'i dus te/
NK060(i)001:8992: de nyid rang du sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub
NK060(i)001:8993: 'grub pa las mi 'da' bas na dam tshig gi
NK060(i)001:8994: mchog ste/ bslu ba med pa'i 'bras bu thob pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:8995: 'o na dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo zhes pas/
NK060(i)001:8996: rnam pa thams cad spyan 'dren pa yin nam/
NK060(i)001:8997: grang thams cad spyan 'dren pa yin/
NK060(i)001:8998: snga ma ltar na zhi ba'i skabs su khro bo yang spyan 'dren par 'gyur la/
NK060(i)001:8999: phyi ma ltar na bsdus pa bco brgyad po'i skabs
NK060(i)001:9000: su rgyas pa brgyad cu rtsa gnyis pa yang spyan
NK060(i)001:9002: rnam pa zhi khro gang yin la grangs rgyas 'bring
NK060(i)001:9003: bsdus pa gang yin thams cad spyan 'dren pa yin
NK060(i)001:9004: gsung mod kyang / don la dkyil 'khor re re yang dkyil 'khor kun gyi bdag nyid yin la/
NK060(i)001:9005: bsgom pa'i dbang du rnam pa zhi khro dang /
NK060(i)001:9006: grangs rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gyi dkyil 'khor du dgos
NK060(i)001:9007: ched kyis bstan pa yin pas gang ltar byas kyang
NK060(i)001:9014: phyi'i mchod pa rnam pa lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:9018: 'phan/ gdugs/ rol mo'i bye brag sna tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:9019: nang gi mchod pa dam rdzas dang /
NK060(i)001:9021: glu tshig ste glu ye shes kyi mchod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:9023: lag pa'i gar te gar ye shes kyi mchod pa su ra to bcu drug dang /
NK060(i)001:9024: gzhan yang rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa la
NK060(i)001:9025: sogs pa du ma'i sprin dpung gi tshogs kyis nam
NK060(i)001:9026: mkha'i khams rab tu gang bas mchod de/
NK060(i)001:9027: gsang ba'i yum bzhi dang 'joms ma sgo ma bzhi
NK060(i)001:9028: dang sems ma nang gi bzhi dang phyi'i bzhi yis
NK060(i)001:9029: mchod de/ bskul tshig dang bsam pa zhi rgyas la
NK060(i)001:9030: sogs pa'i dngos grub ji ltar 'dod pa'i phrin las
NK060(i)001:9031: bzhi'i gzhung bzhin du mchod do //
NK060(i)001:9032: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa/
NK060(i)001:9034: mnyes par byed pa'i don gyis na mchod pa/
NK060(i)001:9035: snang grags mchod rdzas las mi 'da' ba'i phyag rgya
NK060(i)001:9036: mchod pa gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas na
NK060(i)001:9037: chen po 'di ni/ sems kyi cho 'phrul yid bzhin
NK060(i)001:9038: gyi nor bu rin po che lta bu las ma
NK060(i)001:9039: g.yos par mchod sprin bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i tshogs
NK060(i)001:9041: de yang bdag gi thugs ka nas yi ge b+h+r+aum
NK060(i)001:9042: phyogs bcur 'phros pas thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK060(i)001:9043: khams rnam par dag par byin gyis brlabs te/
NK060(i)001:9044: mnyen pa 'jam pa reg na shin tu bde ba dang ldan pa/
NK060(i)001:9045: 'og gzhi sna tshogs pa'i rin po che'i sa gzhi
NK060(i)001:9046: mnan na nem pa bteg na 'phar ba mdzes par
NK060(i)001:9047: byed pa'i re'u mig mang ris su bris shing /
NK060(i)001:9048: d+r+wa mig rin po che du mas spras pa dang
NK060(i)001:9049: ri dang ri phran thams cad la yi ge tram
NK060(i)001:9050: 'phros pa las yon tan kun 'byung ba nor bu
NK060(i)001:9051: rin cen gyi phung po 'od 'bar bar byin gyis
NK060(i)001:9052: brlab/ chu bo chu phran thams cad la yi ge a 'phros pas/
NK060(i)001:9053: dbyibs legs shing bang rim dang ldan pa'i rdzing bu chu yan lag brgyad ldan gyis gang ba/
NK060(i)001:9054: ro bro ba'i mchog tu gyur pa bsil zhing dwangs par byin gyis brlab/
NK060(i)001:9055: khang khyim dang sbra gur la sogs pa thams cad la yi ge b+h+r+aum 'phros pas/
NK060(i)001:9056: gnas khang thams cad rin chen gyi khang pa sna tshogs par byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK060(i)001:9057: gzhan yang rtsi shing nags tshal thams cad la yi ge tram 'phros pas/
NK060(i)001:9058: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten rin po che'i rgyan dang
NK060(i)001:9059: rtsi shing dang nags tshal thams cad dpag bsam gyi
NK060(i)001:9060: ljon shing rgyas pa'i tshul du byin gyis brlab/
NK060(i)001:9061: sems kyis zin pa dang ma zin pa'i sgra skad thams cad la yi ge tram 'phros pas/
NK060(i)001:9062: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la
NK060(i)001:9063: bstod pa'i glu dbyangs dang sems can la chos ston
NK060(i)001:9064: pa'i tshigs su bcad pa'i sgrar byin gyis brlab/
NK060(i)001:9065: gos rgyan thams cad la yi ge mam 'phros pas/
NK060(i)001:9068: rgyal mtshan lha'i na bza' dang gdugs la sogs par byin gyis brlab/
NK060(i)001:9069: sems can gyi rgyan thams cad la yi ge tram 'phros pas/
NK060(i)001:9070: rin po che'i do shal dpung rgyan dang se mo do ru byin gyis brlab/
NK060(i)001:9071: longs spyod thams cad la yi ge a 'phros pas/
NK060(i)001:9072: bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin bza' ba dang btung ba dang ro bro ba'i mchog sna tshogs pa rnams dang /
NK060(i)001:9073: 'gro ba thams cad kyang rang la mdzes par rgyan
NK060(i)001:9074: khyad par can du mas brgyan pa'i mchod rdzas 'dod
NK060(i)001:9075: yon sna tshogs thogs pa'i lha dang lha mo re
NK060(i)001:9076: re yang bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhing gi rdul
NK060(i)001:9077: snyed rnams kyis rkang pa'i bro dang /
NK060(i)001:9078: lag pa'i gar la sogs pa bsam yas pa sna
NK060(i)001:9079: tshogs kyis mang nyung gi tshad phyogs bcu nam mkha'i
NK060(i)001:9081: sngar spyan drangs pa'i dkyil 'khor kun la rgyas par dbul lo //
NK060(i)001:9082: skal ba dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa blo mi
NK060(i)001:9083: gsal ba dang gsal ba'i khyad par gyi rim gyis
NK060(i)001:9084: sam/ yang na cig car du skad cig dran rdzogs kyis chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam par sbyor zhing /
NK060(i)001:9085: chos nyid la chos nyid thim pa'i tshul du snang
NK060(i)001:9086: srid thams cad mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po las
NK060(i)001:9090: yum ting nge 'dzin gsal ba dang ldan pa can yin na yum rang gis bsgom pa'am/
NK060(i)001:9091: mi ldan na yab kyis byin gyis brlabs la dper
NK060(i)001:9092: na byang chub sems dpa' rdzu 'phrul can gyis stong
NK060(i)001:9093: gsum yungs 'brur 'jug pa'i tshul du dbyings phyug gi
NK060(i)001:9094: sna rtse yungs 'bru tsam la gzhal yas khang rdzogs
NK060(i)001:9095: par bskyed nas/ dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gang rung gi lha bkod la/
NK060(i)001:9096: 'og min gyi gnas nas rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ram/
NK060(i)001:9097: lus kyi rtsa gnas na byang chub kyi sems spyan
NK060(i)001:9098: drang zhing dam tshig gi lha la ye shes sems
NK060(i)001:9099: dpa' bstim pa'am/ byang chub kyi sems nyi zla gnyis
NK060(i)001:9100: med du bstim zhing yum dang rol pa'i bde ba'i
NK060(i)001:9101: dpa' bstim pa'am/ mchod pas/ thams cad bde bas mnyes
NK060(i)001:9102: nas tshim zhing grub pa las mi 'da' ba'i dam
NK060(i)001:9103: tshig 'di ni mchod pa gzhan las khyad par du
NK060(i)001:9105: bdag nyid chen po lha'i dkyil 'khor yab yum byang chub sems kyi mchod pa yis/
NK060(i)001:9106: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa rang rig
NK060(i)001:9107: pa'i ye shes las tha mi dad pas na mnyes
NK060(i)001:9108: shing de'i byin rlabs kyis srid pa ni/
NK060(i)001:9109: snod kyi dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:9112: bcud kyi dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:9115: gzugs/ gzugs med gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'gro ba rigs drug dang /
NK060(i)001:9122: su/ tri/ pre/ duh thams cad la byang chub kyi sems bde ba'i ro dga' ba chen po'i khyab par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:9123: sgyu ma mtshon pa lha yum/
NK060(i)001:9125: d+r+wa ba mtshon pa zung du 'brel ba'i ting nge
NK060(i)001:9126: 'dzin brtan pa'i tshad gsal ba yul gyis mi 'phrogs
NK060(i)001:9127: pa yis phyogs bcu dang dus bzhir yang dag pa'i
NK060(i)001:9129: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa dang /
NK060(i)001:9130: khams gsum gyi 'gro ba sems can rnams kyi khams dang /
NK060(i)001:9131: bsam pa rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal bar 'gyur pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:9133: 'di la rdo rje las rim las/
NK060(i)001:9134: sa dang rab gnas rnam gnyis dang //
NK060(i)001:9135: bde ba sbyin pa'i dus nyid do //
NK060(i)001:9137: sa chog gi dus su sa ngan na zhi ba'i
NK060(i)001:9138: sbyin sreg /rab gnas kyi dus su rgyas pa'i sbyin
NK060(i)001:9139: sreg /dbang bskur ba'i dus dbang gi sbyin sreg /slob
NK060(i)001:9140: bu rab gnas kyi nub mo kun rmis ltas log
NK060(i)001:9141: na drag po'i sbyin sreg bya ste/
NK060(i)001:9142: de yang sbyin sreg rtsa ba las/
NK060(i)001:9143: gnas rdzas thab kyi rnam pa dang //
NK060(i)001:9144: gzungs dang gtso sems bsgrub bya dang //
NK060(i)001:9145: phur pa lha dus las rim dang //
NK060(i)001:9146: lhag ma bcu gcig shes par bya //
NK060(i)001:9147: zhes pas dang po gnas ni zhi rgyas gnyis bkra shis pa'i gnas su/
NK060(i)001:9148: dbang drag gnyis gnyan pa'i gnas su bya ba'am yang na zhi ba ri bo 'dus pa'i rtse/
NK060(i)001:9149: rgyas pa nags tshal sman ljongs kyi tshal/
NK060(i)001:9150: dbang chu bo 'dus pa'i sum mdo/
NK060(i)001:9151: drag po dur khrod chen po'i gnas su bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9153: las bzhi gang byed kyi sreg shing /
NK060(i)001:9158: gsum pa thab kyi rnam pa ni/
NK060(i)001:9159: dbyibs zhi ba la zlum po/
NK060(i)001:9163: thams cad kyang khrug gang ba bang rim gsum gsum
NK060(i)001:9164: go rim bzhin 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa dkar po
NK060(i)001:9165: dang / rin po che zur brgyad ba ser po dang /
NK060(i)001:9167: khro zhal lam rdo rje rgya gram nag po'i lte ba la gnas pa dang /
NK060(i)001:9168: kha dog ni zhi ba dkar/
NK060(i)001:9172: zhi ba la 'khor lo +amo gyis mtshan pa/
NK060(i)001:9173: rgyas pa la rin po che tram gis mtshan pa/
NK060(i)001:9174: dbang la pad+ma h+r+aihs mtshan pa/
NK060(i)001:9175: drag po la rdo rje'am kha t+w+aam ga h+aum gis mtshan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:9180: rgyas pa la bzhin gru bzhi/
NK060(i)001:9188: drag po la bzhin gru gsum/
NK060(i)001:9191: lnga pa gtso bo'i sems ni/
NK060(i)001:9192: don gyi sems bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba rtog shing /
NK060(i)001:9194: zhi ba la zhi zhing dwangs pa/
NK060(i)001:9195: rgyas pa la spro zhing dga' ba/
NK060(i)001:9196: dbang la chags shing zhe na pa/
NK060(i)001:9197: drang po la zhe sdang khro ba'i sems kyis bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9199: zhi ba la gtum zhing rngam pa/
NK060(i)001:9200: rgyas pa la tshe dang bsod nams rgyas pa/
NK060(i)001:9201: dbang la gang dbang du bya bar 'dod pa/
NK060(i)001:9202: drag po la bsgral ba'i zhing bcu'o //
NK060(i)001:9203: de dag gang yin gyi dri ma drug gam rkang rjes kyi sa la byas pa'i ling+ga'i dpral bar rus/
NK060(i)001:9206: 'doms su las bzhi gang byed kyi sngags spu gri dang bcas pa bris la/
NK060(i)001:9207: las bzhi gang yin gyi brub khung du gzhug go //
NK060(i)001:9209: zhi ba la dngul lam shing dkar po'i phur pa
NK060(i)001:9210: dbal zlum por byas pa drug /rgyas pa la gser
NK060(i)001:9211: ram shing ser po'i phur pa dbal gru bzhir byas
NK060(i)001:9212: pa bzhi/ dbang la zangs sam shing dmar po'i phur pa dbal zla gam du byas pa lnga/
NK060(i)001:9213: drag po la lcags sam shing nag po'i phur pa dbal zur gsum byas pa gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:9214: de dag kyang grub na las byed kyi phur pa nyi shu rtsa re dang bcas pa bsham mo //
NK060(i)001:9216: las sbyor gyi lha zhi khro'i gzhung bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:9217: sbyin sreg gi lha las bzhi gang yin gyi sku mdog phyag mtshan can gyi me lha ste/
NK060(i)001:9218: zhi ba la me lha dkar po phyag g.yas pas na gun+d+he bsnams pa/
NK060(i)001:9219: rgyas pa la ser po rin chen sgrom bu/
NK060(i)001:9220: dbang la dmar po zhags pa/
NK060(i)001:9221: drag po la mthing nag tri shu la/
NK060(i)001:9222: kun kyang phyag g.yon pa na bgrang phreng 'dzin pa/
NK060(i)001:9223: drang srong gi cha byad can ra skyes la chibs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9225: zhi ba la rnam snang dang bud+d+ha he ru kas
NK060(i)001:9226: gtso byas pa'i zhi khro'i lha kun sku mdog dkar
NK060(i)001:9227: po/ rgyas pa la rin 'byung dang rat+na he ru kas gtso byas pa'i lha kun ser po/
NK060(i)001:9228: dbang la snang ba mtha' yas dang pad+ma he ru kas gtso byas pa'i lha kun dmar po/
NK060(i)001:9229: drag po la rdo rje sems dpa' dang badz+ra he
NK060(i)001:9230: ru kas gtso byas pa'i lha kun mthing khar bskyed
NK060(i)001:9240: nam gung drag po'i sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9241: bcu pa sbyin sreg gi las kyi rim pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:9248: las bzhi'i yo byad bsags la sa gzhi skyang nul bya/
NK060(i)001:9249: las bzhi gang byed kyi thab brtsig /dkyil 'khor bri/
NK060(i)001:9253: rigs dang mthun pa'i me dar dag pa/
NK060(i)001:9256: las bzhi gang byed kyi ling+ga bcas pa brub khung
NK060(i)001:9257: du gzhug /kha khyer la las bzhi gang yin gyi
NK060(i)001:9264: h+aum bzhis byin bsdus la rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa byin gyis brlab/
NK060(i)001:9265: de nas sreg rdzas byin gyis brlab pa ni/
NK060(i)001:9266: nyi zla ga'ura 'bru lnga bkod la bzhu brtul gyis bdud rtsir brlab/
NK060(i)001:9267: las bzhi'i gtor ma yang 'bru gsum mam lnga yis las gang yin 'grub par byin gyis brlab/
NK060(i)001:9268: las rim dngos la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:9269: dang po las sbyor gyi phrin las zhi khro gzhung bsrang /
NK060(i)001:9270: 'dzab kyi 'phro 'du las bzhi'i kha dog bzhin byas la bstod pa yang bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9271: gnyis pa ling+ga dgug gzhug bya ba ni/
NK060(i)001:9272: tshogs tha ma dang ling+ga brub khung du brubs la dgug gzhug bya/
NK060(i)001:9273: gtor bskul byas la gtor thun dbab/
NK060(i)001:9274: phur bskul byas la phur pa gdab/
NK060(i)001:9276: gris gtubs la sreg rdzas dang bsres la gzhag go //
NK060(i)001:9277: gsum pa sbyin sreg gi las rim la me lha dang sreg lha gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:9278: me lha ni las bzhi gang byed kyi me lha dam tshig par bskyed/
NK060(i)001:9281: lha thams cad kyi zhal du gyur pa'i ye shes kyi me lha snyan gsan dbab/
NK060(i)001:9282: mda' dar dmar pos g.yab cing /
NK060(i)001:9283: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK060(i)001:9284: zhes sogs kyis bos la dam tshig gi me lha la bstim/
NK060(i)001:9285: mchod bstod byas la las bzhi gang yin gyi smon lam gdab bo //
NK060(i)001:9286: sreg lha ni las bzhi gang byed bzhin dam tshig par bskyed/
NK060(i)001:9288: ye shes kyi me lha dbab/
NK060(i)001:9291: bstim/ kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod la/
NK060(i)001:9292: bza' btung bro ba'i tshogs sreg rdzas rnams las bzhi gang byed kyi tshig dang /
NK060(i)001:9293: sngags kyis las bzhi gang byed pa'i skabs dang sbyar
NK060(i)001:9294: la mchod pa dbul zhing bden pa dang smon lam
NK060(i)001:9295: brjod nas/ phyogs bcu dus bzhi bstod/
NK060(i)001:9296: de nas khro bor bsgyur la dbab/
NK060(i)001:9299: bstim/ kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod la/
NK060(i)001:9300: sngar bzhin las bzhi gang yin gyi sbyin sreg gi
NK060(i)001:9301: mchod pa rab tu sbyin par bya zhing gtum chen
NK060(i)001:9303: bcu gcig pa'i lhag ma'i las ni/
NK060(i)001:9306: yi ge brgya pas lhag chad bskang /
NK060(i)001:9307: sreg lha dang me lha ye shes pa gshegs/
NK060(i)001:9308: dam tshig pa rang la bsdu/
NK060(i)001:9310: las rjes mi mngon par byas la bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa brjod par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:9311: rgyas par sbyin sreg gi las bsgom khrigs ma na gsal bas der shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9312: dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:9315: slob ma la lha sgom par nan tan bya ba'o //
NK060(i)001:9319: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang /
NK060(i)001:9321: thog mar slob dpon 'jug pa'i cho ga gnyis ni/
NK060(i)001:9322: dkyil 'khor gyi las kun byas shing phyi nang gsang
NK060(i)001:9323: ba'i dbang gis phyug pa'i rdo rje slob dpon gyis
NK060(i)001:9324: khrus byas dbang gos gyon nas dkyil 'khor gyi shar
NK060(i)001:9327: dngos grub bskul zhing rig pa'i me tog dor nas
NK060(i)001:9328: dad pas dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga dag
NK060(i)001:9329: gis slob ma la ji tsam dbang bskur bar 'dod
NK060(i)001:9330: pa de/ rang nyid dkyil 'khor gyi lha la dbang
NK060(i)001:9331: blangs shing slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug par gsol
NK060(i)001:9333: bzod par gsol bar dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams dgyes
NK060(i)001:9334: bzhin du gnang ba byin par bsam pa ni slob
NK060(i)001:9336: gnyis pa slob ma gzhug pa/
NK060(i)001:9338: slob dpon dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa de nas slob
NK060(i)001:9339: ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug par bya ba la chos
NK060(i)001:9343: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang //
NK060(i)001:9344: bgegs bskrad lhar brlab dam tshig sbyin //
NK060(i)001:9345: de nyid dbog dang chu nan dang //
NK060(i)001:9346: bsgrag dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK060(i)001:9347: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang //
NK060(i)001:9348: tshogs mchog yon dang rnam bco brgyad //
NK060(i)001:9351: rgyas par dbang chog tu shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9352: slob ma la lha bsgom par nan tan bya ba'o //
NK060(i)001:9354: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsungs thugs su lhun gyis grub bas/
NK060(i)001:9355: lha dang khyad par med cing skal ba mnyam pa'i
NK060(i)001:9356: ye shes can de ni yi dam gyi lha sgrub
NK060(i)001:9358: dus nye bar 'byung ba'i dngos grub ya mtshan chen
NK060(i)001:9359: po 'byung bar nges bas yi dam gyi lha bsgom
NK060(i)001:9360: pa dang mi 'bral bar gces so //
NK060(i)001:9361: gal te lha bsgom pa'i dad pa med na yi dam lha'i dam tshig nyams par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:9362: dam tshig nyams kyang skyon ci yod ce na/
NK060(i)001:9363: rdo rje gnod sbyin gyis snying khrag zho bzhin du 'jibs nas 'dir yang tshe thung zhing /
NK060(i)001:9364: phyi ma ngan 'gro'i gnas su ltung ba'i phyir na phung bar 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:9365: bcu pa dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:9367: rigs lnga yab yum zung du 'brel ba bde ba
NK060(i)001:9368: chen po'i dkyil 'khor ni bsdus pa'i dbang du byas
NK060(i)001:9369: na stangs ni yab/ dpyal ni yum ste gtso bo yab yum gnyis sam/
NK060(i)001:9370: yang na dkyil 'khor 'bring po dang rgyas pa'i gtso bo rigs lnga rab gnas dang ldan par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:9371: der slob bu dad pa dang ldan pas gong bzhin
NK060(i)001:9372: dkyil 'khor du rab tu zhugs par gyur na 'dod
NK060(i)001:9373: pa'i don dbang dang dngos grub yin du 'ong ba
NK060(i)001:9374: thob pas na/ sngon 'og min du mthar lam pa zhugs pa dang skal ba mnyam par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:9375: de yang sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las/
NK060(i)001:9376: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK060(i)001:9377: 'khor lo sngon du mthong ba yis //
NK060(i)001:9378: bsod nams brtag pa gang yin pa //
NK060(i)001:9379: phyis byas pa yang de bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:9383: 'dir sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dkyil la yang sa gzhi
NK060(i)001:9384: mnyam pa la sogs pa spyi don bcus ston kyang
NK060(i)001:9385: / spyir zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su bshad pa de bzhin du byas te/
NK060(i)001:9386: 'on kyang dang po sa gzhi mnyam pa la brgyad yod pa'i/
NK060(i)001:9387: sa brtag pa'i skabs su gnas ma mo 'du ba'i dur khrod shis so //
NK060(i)001:9388: drug pa byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK060(i)001:9389: brgyad pa sa bzung ba khro bos bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9392: gsum pa thig la ye shes kyi thig skud rgyus chen la bya/
NK060(i)001:9394: gdab pa'i thabs kyang khro bo'i lugs su gdab bo //
NK060(i)001:9395: bzhi pa tshon la thal chen bsres la rab gnas khro bos bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9396: lnga pa bri thabs la khro bo'i dkyil 'khor khyams gnyis la bya/
NK060(i)001:9397: drug pa rnam pa dgod pa khro bo'i sku gsung thugs dgod/
NK060(i)001:9398: bdun pa rab gnas la las sbyor khro bo'i gzhung bsrang /
NK060(i)001:9399: mnga' gsol skabs su thog mar bum pa/
NK060(i)001:9400: de nas rol pa nyi shu/
NK060(i)001:9404: mnga' gsal brgyad cus mnga' gsol lo //
NK060(i)001:9405: chu bdun la dam rdzas lnga'i steng du thal chen dang zhun chen no //
NK060(i)001:9406: tshig kyang zhi ba dang mi mthun no //
NK060(i)001:9407: sku phyi ba yang dur khrod ras chen gyis so //
NK060(i)001:9408: phyi nang gsang ba'i p+au dza khro bo ltar ro //
NK060(i)001:9409: bdun pa bden pas brtan par bzhugs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:9410: brgyad pa bskor ba dang smon lam yang khro ba'i rab gnas nas bshad pa ltar ro //
NK060(i)001:9411: dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga la/
NK060(i)001:9412: lhar brlab pa dang lha dbab pa khro bos bya/
NK060(i)001:9413: de las gzhan pa rnams dang /
NK060(i)001:9414: bcu pa zhugs pa'i yon tan zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:9415: mchog gi dkyil 'khor zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor ltar shes par gdams pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9417: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor dag la'ang
NK060(i)001:9418: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su bshad pa de
NK060(i)001:9419: bzhin du spyi don bcur shes par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:9420: dang po sa gzhi mnyam pa ni chos thams cad mnyam par rtogs shing de'i ngang du 'jog pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9421: gnyis pa tshad ni rang gi rig pas dpags shing
NK060(i)001:9422: ji tsam dpog pa'i tshad tsam du bsgom par bya'o
NK060(i)001:9423: // gsum pa thig ni rang rig pa nyid dkyil 'khor du gsal ba las mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK060(i)001:9424: bzhi pa tshon ni sems rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar mtshon pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9425: lnga pa bri ba ni sems nyid mnyam pa nyid
NK060(i)001:9426: la sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor mnyam pa
NK060(i)001:9427: nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su gsal ba'o //
NK060(i)001:9428: drug pa rnam pa dgod pa ni snang ba sku'i dkyil 'khor/
NK060(i)001:9430: dran rig thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du ma 'gags par dgod pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9431: bdun pa rab gnas ni rgyun bshags ltar/
NK060(i)001:9436: bstim/ mchod pa'i rim pa rnams bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9437: brgyad pa sbyin sreg ni bde ba chen po'i don
NK060(i)001:9438: rgyud la sbyin zhing rnam rtog rang rgyud pa sreg
NK060(i)001:9439: pa'o // dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa ni
NK060(i)001:9440: rgyun bshags kyis gsal btab nas rgyun chad med par
NK060(i)001:9442: bcu pa zhugs pa'i yon tan ni sngon 'og min
NK060(i)001:9443: du mthar lam pa zhugs pa dang skal pa mnyam
NK060(i)001:9444: pa sngar dang rjes su mthun no //
NK060(i)001:9445: spyi don gnyis pa dbang ye shes rdo rje la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:9447: dbang gi sngon du rgyu yon dbul ba/
NK060(i)001:9449: dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba rdzogs pa de nas dkyil
NK060(i)001:9450: 'khor du zhugs pa'i rigs kyi bu mchog dbang thob
NK060(i)001:9451: par 'dod pa des sngon du rgyu yon dbul bar
NK060(i)001:9452: bya ste/ yi dam de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la me tog phog pa yin na rgyal srid dang /
NK060(i)001:9453: rdo rje rigs yin na ni rang gi lus dbul lo //
NK060(i)001:9454: rgyas srid med pa rnam yon mi dbul lam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:9455: rang dbang ba'i dngos po ci yin dbul gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:9456: yi dam pad+ma'i rigs la me tog phog na bu dang chung ma dbul/
NK060(i)001:9457: rin po che'i rigs la rin po che dngos sam nor gyi dbyig dbul/
NK060(i)001:9458: las kyi rigs la rang la gang rab tu gces pa dbul/
NK060(i)001:9459: yi dam rigs thams cad kyi bdag po yin na bla ma'i yid la gang 'thad dbul te/
NK060(i)001:9460: thugs la 'thad na rang gi gzungs ma yang dbul lo //
NK060(i)001:9462: dbang phyug la gong du bshad pa'i yon rnams dang
NK060(i)001:9463: bzang bca' la sogs pa'i longs spyod lngas nye bar
NK060(i)001:9464: mchod na dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod par 'gyur ba
NK060(i)001:9465: yin te/ dbang phyug dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi bdag
NK060(i)001:9466: nyid yin pas sam dgongs pa tha mi dad pa'i
