NK060(i)001:9467: yin te/ phyir ro // de mchod pa la dgos ched ci yod ce na/
NK060(i)001:9468: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor dbang phyug rdo rje slob dpon
NK060(i)001:9469: mchod pas dkyil 'khor thams cad mnyes pa smos ci
NK060(i)001:9475: gzhan yang sngags kyi dam tshig nyams pa la sogs pa'i nyes pa thams cad 'dag par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:9476: snod dang sbyar la bskur ba/
NK060(i)001:9478: slob bu'i mtshan nyid brtag pa la mkhas pa'i slob dpon gyis/
NK060(i)001:9480: slob bu snod dang ldan mi ldan gyi mtshan nyid rab tu brtags nas/
NK060(i)001:9481: snod dang mi ldan pa'i slob ma spangs la/
NK060(i)001:9482: snod ldan gyi slob bu dad pa can la phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu sbyin zhing /
NK060(i)001:9483: brtson 'grus can la nang nus pa'i dbang lnga sbyin par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:9484: de yang bdag don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la nyan bsgom gnyis/
NK060(i)001:9485: gzhan don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la 'chad phrin gnyis/
NK060(i)001:9486: gnyis ka'i don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la rdo
NK060(i)001:9487: rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang sbyin no
NK060(i)001:9488: // brtul zhugs can la gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum sbyin te/
NK060(i)001:9489: de yang spyod pa'i brtul zhugs can la gsang ba'i dbang /
NK060(i)001:9490: rig pa'i brtul zhugs can la shes rab ye shes kyi dbang /
NK060(i)001:9491: mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can la dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang sbyin te/
NK060(i)001:9492: snod kyi rim pa bzhin du rang rang gi blo dang 'tshams tshod du sbyin par bya zhing /
NK060(i)001:9493: rdo rje slob dpon gyis slob bu la don du mi 'gyur ba'i dbang byin na/
NK060(i)001:9494: rdza rnod du seng zho blug pa dang mtshungs pas/
NK060(i)001:9495: snying rjes kun nas bslangs pa'i sems kyis snod dang
NK060(i)001:9496: 'tshams par sbyin la slob bu chud ma zos par
NK060(i)001:9498: gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad do //
NK060(i)001:9501: de la gdan dang sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma dgod pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9506: spyir gsang bsgyu 'phrul gyi lugs kyi dkyil 'khor bzhi ru dbang lnga bskur bar byed pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:9507: phyi rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor du phan dbang /
NK060(i)001:9508: nang lus kyi dkyil 'khor du nus dbang /
NK060(i)001:9509: gsang ba b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor du gsang dbang dang shes rab kyi dbang /
NK060(i)001:9510: de kho na nyid sems kyi dkyil 'khor du dbyer
NK060(i)001:9511: med bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur ba yin pa
NK060(i)001:9512: la/ skabs 'dir gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor gsang gnas gnyis yin zhing de dag mtshon byed du/
NK060(i)001:9513: gser dngul zangs lcags la sogs pa la lugs su blug pa'am/
NK060(i)001:9514: ras sam gro shog la sogs pa la ris su bris pa'am/
NK060(i)001:9515: tsan+dana gor+shi sha la sogs pa la rkos su brkos pa'ang rung ste/
NK060(i)001:9516: sngar gyis dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gyi tshad
NK060(i)001:9517: la bltos na 'di la chung tshad gzhan med pas
NK060(i)001:9518: shin tu phra ba'i dkyil 'khor te/
NK060(i)001:9519: spyod pa'i brtul zhugs can gyi slob bu la bde
NK060(i)001:9520: ba'i ye shes mtshon zhing sbyor ba las mi 'da'
NK060(i)001:9521: bas na dam tshig gi mchog go //
NK060(i)001:9523: rdo rje slob dpon sku'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom pa'i phyag mnyam gzhag gi mthin du'o //
NK060(i)001:9525: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ngam pa bde ba'i ye shes skye ba'i yul gsang ba'i pad+ma yin pas/
NK060(i)001:9526: de mtshon byed pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma bzhi pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9528: yum gyi gsang gnas mtshon pa yin pas sor ni bzhi pa'i tshad du bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9530: phyag rgya chen po nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK060(i)001:9531: sor bzhi'i tshad du rang bzhin gnas //
NK060(i)001:9532: bde ba'i ye shes thugs dkyil 'khor //
NK060(i)001:9533: kha dog dbyibs dang ldan par bya //
NK060(i)001:9534: thabs kyi rab gnas cho gar ldan //
NK060(i)001:9535: 'jug pa pos kyang gsol ba gdab //
NK060(i)001:9537: rdo rje'i tshad mdzub gang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:9539: pad+ma'i tshad de las gzhan yang rdo rje'i tshad byed pa na/
NK060(i)001:9541: thal mo rab tu bsnol na sku'i phyag rgya chen po bsgom pa'i dbang du na'o //
NK060(i)001:9543: bde ba'i ye shes skye ba'i rten gsang ba'i rdo
NK060(i)001:9544: rje de mtshon par byed pa rdo rje sngon po
NK060(i)001:9545: rtse lnga pa'o // dkyil 'khor de'i tshad ji tsam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:9546: yab kyi gsang gnas mtshon pa yin pas mdzub gang ba'i tshad du yab bya ste/
NK060(i)001:9547: lag len la bzo bo mkhas pas rdo rje rtse
NK060(i)001:9548: lnga po cho ga ji lta ba bzhin du bzo
NK060(i)001:9549: bar bya'o // de yang thal rgyud las/
NK060(i)001:9550: thal mo zhes bya rdebs pa'i sgra //
NK060(i)001:9551: dbang po'i yul du rab sbyor bas //
NK060(i)001:9552: phyag rgya chen po nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK060(i)001:9553: brtul zhugs gnyis kyis pang du blangs //
NK060(i)001:9554: rdo rje mdzub mo'i rtse dag tu //
NK060(i)001:9555: til 'bru nam mkha'i gzhal yas su //
NK060(i)001:9556: ri rab tsam gyi phyag rgya dgod //
NK060(i)001:9557: thabs kyi cho ga rab gnas dang //
NK060(i)001:9558: gsang ba'i sbyin sreg lugs su dbul //
NK060(i)001:9560: gnyis pa la de la gdan dang sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma dgod pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9562: sor bzhi pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi pad+ma'i dbus kyi lte
NK060(i)001:9563: ba dang phyogs kyi 'dab ma rnams la nyi ma
NK060(i)001:9564: dang / mdzub gang ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi rdo rje'i
NK060(i)001:9565: rwa dbus ma dang phyogs kyi rwa rnams la zla
NK060(i)001:9566: dang / ba dgod de/ che chung gi tshad ni
NK060(i)001:9567: sen zlum tsam gyi nyi ma dang zla ba'i dkyil
NK060(i)001:9568: 'khor la sran ma tsa na ka'i 'bru slebs pa
NK060(i)001:9569: tsam gyis pad+ma'i gdan gyi steng du yung 'bru tsam
NK060(i)001:9571: sor bzhi'i dkyil 'khor gyi nyi ma la gnas pa'i
NK060(i)001:9572: pad+ma rnams kyi steng du yum gyi 'bru lnga dang
NK060(i)001:9573: / mdzub gang ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi zla ba la
NK060(i)001:9574: gnas pa'i pad+ma rnams la yab kyi 'bru lnga yongs
NK060(i)001:9575: su gyur pa las byung ba'i phyag rgya til 'bru
NK060(i)001:9578: yi ge yungs 'bru tsam la sku nas 'bru tsam dgod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:9579: yi ge til 'bru tsam la sku yungs 'bru tsam dgod pa'o zhes gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:9580: de ltar mtshon byed rtags kyi dkyil 'khor gnyis la
NK060(i)001:9581: gdan dang sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma ji ltar
NK060(i)001:9582: bkod pa bzhin du/ yab yum gnyis snyoms par 'jug
NK060(i)001:9583: pa'i sngon du'ang mkha' gsang gnyis la gdan dang sku
NK060(i)001:9584: gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma yab kyi dang yum gyis
NK060(i)001:9586: spyi don gsum pa sgrub pa ye shes rdo rje la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:9588: tshogs kyi sgrub pa po'i mtshan nyid/
NK060(i)001:9592: phyag rgya gcig pa la phra rags gnyis/
NK060(i)001:9593: phyag rgya spros pa dang bcas pa'i cho ga lnga ni sngon du rdzogs par byas shing /
NK060(i)001:9598: +aa li k+aa li'i yo byad dang lnga ni rdzogs par byas nas/
NK060(i)001:9599: gnas 'khor khang phyi nang bar gsum dang ldan par sngags ni/
NK060(i)001:9601: yid skyob pa dang byin gyis brlabs kyi phyir sngags
NK060(i)001:9602: te lha'o zhes pas sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum
NK060(i)001:9603: ye shes sems dpa' dang bzhi/
NK060(i)001:9604: dbu rgyan rigs kyi lha gcig tu byas pas yan
NK060(i)001:9605: lag lnga lnga ste de dag rdzogs pa gsal ba'i
NK060(i)001:9606: rnal 'byor pas rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:9607: yan lag gi bcu la sogs pa ma nyams par
NK060(i)001:9608: tshogs bsgrub pa'i spyod pa la 'jug cing sgrub ba
NK060(i)001:9609: nyams su len pa la rab tu brtson par byas
NK060(i)001:9610: na sgrub pa pos tshogs 'grub bo //
NK060(i)001:9611: 'bras bu rigs 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:9613: yang rab zhag ni sum cu phrag drug ste zla ba drug gam/
NK060(i)001:9614: rab zla ba bcu gnyis te lo gcig gam/
NK060(i)001:9615: 'bring zla ba bcu bzhi ste lo gcig zla ba gnyis sam/
NK060(i)001:9616: tha ma zla ba bcu drug gis te lo gcig
NK060(i)001:9617: zla ba bzhi yis dbang po rtul na rnam par
NK060(i)001:9619: rno na tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i rig 'dzin mthong
NK060(i)001:9620: lam gyi dam pa lam mchog yongs rdzogs kyi tshe
NK060(i)001:9622: de ltar bsgrub pa'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob tshul lo //
NK060(i)001:9628: 'grub tshul rang snang du bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:9630: gal te tshe dbang thob na de'i tshe lo brgya
NK060(i)001:9631: tshan bcu drug ste stong drug brgya tshun tshad kyis
NK060(i)001:9632: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa sngon du rdzogs par
NK060(i)001:9633: gyur pa ni/ lhun grub rigs 'dzin gyi dgongs pa
NK060(i)001:9634: spros bral du gsal ba ye shes thig le de
NK060(i)001:9635: nyid la mnyam bzhag gi dus su rgyal ba'i dgongs
NK060(i)001:9636: pa spros bral ye shes thig le de nyid snang
NK060(i)001:9637: gyur pa ni/ ba ste/ thal rgyud las/
NK060(i)001:9638: bde 'das ye shes thig le las //
NK060(i)001:9639: mtha' yas ye shes rang snang ba //
NK060(i)001:9640: ma btsal lhun grub rig 'dzin mchog /ces pas tshe
NK060(i)001:9641: dbang thod rgal ba lhun grub rig 'dzin la sbyor
NK060(i)001:9642: ba'am/ de bas kyang blo chen mthar thug sangs rgyas kyis la sbyor ba'ang yang yod de/
NK060(i)001:9644: tshe ni bcu dang drug pa yis //
NK060(i)001:9645: brgya brgyad dag tu bsnur zhing gnas //
NK060(i)001:9646: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas sa //
NK060(i)001:9647: zhes gsungs pas dgongs pa'i ngo bo bsam gyis mi
NK060(i)001:9648: khyab pa yi ge 'khor lo'i sa mtha' yas yon
NK060(i)001:9649: tan brjod pa las 'das pa'i mchog /phyogs bcu dus
NK060(i)001:9650: bzhis bsdus pa thams cad mngon du rdzogs pa'i rgyal
NK060(i)001:9651: ba'i zhing khams su rnam par dag ste bsnyen sgrub
NK060(i)001:9652: bzhi mthar phyin pa'i yon tan bsam yas pa dang
NK060(i)001:9653: / rig pa nyid rang shar rgya dang bral ba'i
NK060(i)001:9654: phyir blos gzhal ba las yas pa'i khang pa 'khor
NK060(i)001:9655: lo rtsibs bzhi gdan khri dang bcas pa rgyan dang
NK060(i)001:9656: rol mo'i bye brag 'dod yon gyi lha mo sna
NK060(i)001:9657: / tshogs pa dang / rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma
NK060(i)001:9658: lus pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'am
NK060(i)001:9659: nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs pa bsam yas pa
NK060(i)001:9660: / tshogs pa dang / kun kyang / skad cig
NK060(i)001:9661: dang po mnyam bzhag la mthong nas skad cig gnyis
NK060(i)001:9662: pa rjes thob la nye bar brnyes pa ste/
NK060(i)001:9663: de thob pa dang gsung lnga lhun gyis grub pas
NK060(i)001:9664: na rgya chen gsung las chos ston pa la sogs
NK060(i)001:9665: pa'i don 'byung ba'ang gzhi rang byung gi ye shes
NK060(i)001:9666: dang / lam rim pa'i ye shes dang /
NK060(i)001:9667: 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes gsum tshul
NK060(i)001:9668: gcig tu gyur pas na mthun pa'i ye shes rang
NK060(i)001:9670: de ltar 'grub pa'i dus dpe'i sgo nas rang snang du bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9672: gong du bstan pa 'i 'bras bu 'bras bu thob tshul de rang ji lta bu zhe na/
NK060(i)001:9673: dper na lha ma yin gyi yul na dpag bsam gyii shing dang /
NK060(i)001:9674: mi'i yul na yid bzhin gyi nor bu dang /
NK060(i)001:9675: lha'i yul na rin po che'i bum pa bzang po
NK060(i)001:9676: dang gsum po de la rang rang gi dgos 'dod
NK060(i)001:9677: 'byung ba kun snang tshul la dngos po rdzas grub
NK060(i)001:9678: ltar snang yang / don la de dag rdzas su grub pa rdul tsam yang yod pa ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:9679: 'gro ba rang rig sems kyi snang ba bsod nams cha mthun gyis mthus bstan pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:9680: dpe gsum po de bzhin du sems nyid ci yang
NK060(i)001:9681: ma yin pa la cir yang snang bas na ngo
NK060(i)001:9682: mtshar zhing sems kyi cho 'phrul sku gsung thugs yon
NK060(i)001:9683: tan phrin las lnga'am/ nyi shu rtsa lngar shar bas na rmad kyi chos so //
NK060(i)001:9684: de dag gzhan nas bkug pa'am gzhan na yod pa
NK060(i)001:9685: cig gsar du 'ongs pa lta bu ni ma yin
NK060(i)001:9686: te/ thabs snang la 'gag pa med pa la blos
NK060(i)001:9687: brtan pa thob pa'i shes rab rang bzhin med pa
NK060(i)001:9688: nyid 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:9689: te/ du rang snang bas/ gong gi dpe gsum po
NK060(i)001:9690: de lta bu rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa' ngang
NK060(i)001:9691: du rang byung ba'o zhes tha snyad du 'dogs so
NK060(i)001:9692: te/ du rang snang bas/ // gnyis pa 'bras bu'i ngo bo'o //
NK060(i)001:9695: rgyu rkyen las ma bskyed cing don byed nus par bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:9697: mi dmigs pa'i shes rab mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings
NK060(i)001:9698: de nyid kyi ngang la blo ma bcos pa'i de
NK060(i)001:9699: bzhin nyid de/ lhun gyis grub pa'i thabs kyi phyag
NK060(i)001:9700: rgya lha'i skur gyur pa'i phyir gzhi lhun gyis grub
NK060(i)001:9701: pa'i ye shes de la ni 'bras bu bsam gyis
NK060(i)001:9702: mi khyab pa'i ye shes rol pa zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9703: 'o na de'i dus na mtshan ma'am rang rgyud du grub pa'i 'bras bu yod dam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:9704: ye shes rol pa de nyid kyang yang dag par
NK060(i)001:9705: na bden pa'i dngos po 'di 'dra bar cir yang
NK060(i)001:9706: gzung du med pas na gsog ces bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9707: 'o na ye shes des don byed mi nus sam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:9708: rgyal ba sprul pa'i sku mngon du 'byung zhing 'gro ba sdug bsngal las skyob pa dang /
NK060(i)001:9709: longs sku'i byin gyis brlabs kyis chos ston pa'ang de bzhin te/
NK060(i)001:9710: thabs kyi phyag rgya gyur pa'i phyir don bya byed
NK060(i)001:9711: nus pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi
NK060(i)001:9712: gzi byin gyis don byed pa'i tshul ni/
NK060(i)001:9713: dper na sgyu ma'i rta dang glang po la sogs bden par grub pa med kyang /
NK060(i)001:9714: gzhan snang brid sdigs kyi don byed nus pa bzhin
NK060(i)001:9715: du ye shes sgyu ma'i rol pa sku gsung thugs
NK060(i)001:9716: lnga'am nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs par snang yang
NK060(i)001:9717: de dag rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed cing ngo bo'i
NK060(i)001:9718: 'dus ma byas pas na rdo rje/
NK060(i)001:9719: mtshan nyid skye 'jig dang bral bas na btsan po
NK060(i)001:9720: yum can las khyad par du gyur na mchog go
NK060(i)001:9721: // gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i don rang gi ye shes rang snang du bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:9723: 'khor 'das kun gyi bdag nyid rang rig pa rang
NK060(i)001:9724: byung gi ye shes dngos po thams cad du rang
NK060(i)001:9725: snang ba'i phyir gcig gi mtha' dang /
NK060(i)001:9726: ji ltar snang yang nyid kyi rang bzhin las ma
NK060(i)001:9727: 'das pa'i phyir du ma'i mtha' dang bral ba'i sems
NK060(i)001:9728: nyid 'di ni/ yod med rtag chad 'gro 'ong skye
NK060(i)001:9729: 'gag dran ltos kyi mtha' kun las 'das pa dang
NK060(i)001:9730: nyid 'di ni/ / de ltos kyi dbus kyang grub pa med de/
NK060(i)001:9731: ngo bo nyid 'di 'drar bstan du med pa ni
NK060(i)001:9732: 'khor 'das thams cad kyi ngo bor lhun gyis grub
NK060(i)001:9733: pa'o // de nyid mngon du byed pa ni de
NK060(i)001:9734: bzhin nyid du gshegs pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:9735: pa'o // sangs rgyas so // de nyid kyi kyang
NK060(i)001:9736: dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad yul
NK060(i)001:9737: dang yul can du'am brten can du mi gzigs te
NK060(i)001:9738: gzigs par byar med pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:9739: 'on kyang mu stegs chad pa'ang dbu ma ye shes rgyun chad pa lta bu ni ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:9740: rang byung gi ye shes gnas bya gnas byed med par rang snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:9741: de'i phyir sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs pa ni chu la chu thim pa ltar ro gcig tu gyur pa'am/
NK060(i)001:9742: shin du ma spungs pa'i me dpung ltar rgyud tha dad pa yang ma yin la/
NK060(i)001:9743: gnyis med kyi mtha' las kyang 'das pas na brjod du med pa zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9744: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi gdul bya la gzigs tshul bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9746: gnyis med kyi ye shes rang ngo ma shes pa lhan skyes kyi ma rig pa dang /
NK060(i)001:9747: der ma zad log par rtog pa bzung 'dzin kun
NK060(i)001:9748: brtags kyi ma rig pa glo bur gyi dri ma
NK060(i)001:9749: gnyis ye nas rnam par dag cing /
NK060(i)001:9750: ye shes dang dbyings gnyis su med pa las gdul
NK060(i)001:9751: bya sems can rnams kyang mi gzhan pa'i phyir na
NK060(i)001:9752: yul yul can gnyis su med pa'i thugs rje chen
NK060(i)001:9753: po sangs rgyas kyi ye shes dang /
NK060(i)001:9754: sems can gyi sems kyi chos nyid ngo bo bdag
NK060(i)001:9755: nyid gcig par 'brel bas na 'gro ba rigs drug
NK060(i)001:9756: gi snang ba rang rgyud du ma grub pa la
NK060(i)001:9757: ma grub pa ltar mkhyen pa ni ji lta ba
NK060(i)001:9759: gshis de ltar yin kyang 'khrul ngor dus snga phyi
NK060(i)001:9760: dang gnas mtho dman la sogs par snang ba kun
NK060(i)001:9761: lhag ma ma lus par mkhyen pa ni ji snyed
NK060(i)001:9763: mdor na 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad snang la
NK060(i)001:9764: rang bzhin med par mkhyen pa ni dbyer med mkhyen
NK060(i)001:9765: pa'i ye shes zhes tha snyad du 'dogs so //
NK060(i)001:9768: zhes dkyil 'khor dbang dang sgrub pa'i don de dag ched du brjod do //
NK060(i)001:9771: gsang ba'i zhes pa rgyud kyi rang bzhin snying po
NK060(i)001:9772: rgyud kyi che ba de kho na nyid rgyud kyi
NK060(i)001:9773: mtshan nyid nges pa rgyud kyi nges don las mtshan
NK060(i)001:9774: gyi gzhi ru gda'/ dkyil 'khor dang dbang dang sgrub pa ye shes rdo rje gsum bkod pa'i don/
NK060(i)001:9775: rtogs dka' bas na gsang ba de nyid 'da' bar dka' ba'i phyir dam tshig go //
NK060(i)001:9776: de dag gi mtshams 'dzin par byed pas na le'u
NK060(i)001:9777: ste yas bgrangs dgu pa'i don du gada'o////da ni le'u
NK060(i)001:9778: bcu pa 'chad par byed pa la chos tshoms kyi
NK060(i)001:9779: dbang du byas na/ gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las/
NK060(i)001:9781: lam la thabs grol gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:9784: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid dang 'bras bu mthar phyin zur tsam ston/
NK060(i)001:9793: dbang gi zhor la spyod pa ston/
NK060(i)001:9794: rin chen gsal 'khor gsal spro thim //
NK060(i)001:9795: zhes pas dkyil 'khor dang ting nge 'dzin ston/
NK060(i)001:9798: ldem dgongs man ngag /bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud/
NK060(i)001:9799: gzhan yang spyi 'gro rnams kyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:9800: de ltar ston pa'i le'u bcu pa 'di la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:9802: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:9804: le'u dgu par lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i rim pa dang /
NK060(i)001:9805: dbang gi rgyu yon dbul ba dang /
NK060(i)001:9806: gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad dang /
NK060(i)001:9807: snod kyi rim pa dang sbyar nas bskur tshul rnams song nas/
NK060(i)001:9808: da 'di na mar bskur thabs dngos ston pas na de nas zhes 'brel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:9809: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos zhes pa 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:9810: dbang gi che ba thob pas sam chos thams cad la dbang sgyur bas na rgyal po/
NK060(i)001:9811: snod gsum la rang rang gi skal ba dang 'tsham
NK060(i)001:9812: par sbyin pa zhes bya ba ting nge 'dzin la
NK060(i)001:9813: dgongs pa mngon du bzhag pas na snyoms par zhugs
NK060(i)001:9814: nas dbang chog bco brgyad kyi don ched du brjod
NK060(i)001:9817: dbang bskur ba'i rim pa dang /
NK060(i)001:9820: dang po la spyi don gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:9823: zab mo'i dbang bskur ba'i rim pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9826: 'di la yang rdo rje las rim las/
NK060(i)001:9827: rgyu rkyen ngo bo 'bras bu dang //
NK060(i)001:9828: rim las skyon yon brgyad ces bya //
NK060(i)001:9829: zhes pas sa dpyad nang tshegs brgyad kyis ston pa las dang po rgyu la gnyis/
NK060(i)001:9832: dang po ni rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad/
NK060(i)001:9833: dbu rgyan gyi dbang gi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu'o //
NK060(i)001:9834: ro rkyang gnyis cod pan gyi mtshungs ldan dang /
NK060(i)001:9835: thig le sum cu so gnyis phreng ba'i mtshungs ldan dang /
NK060(i)001:9836: de bzhin du lus rtsa'i d+r+wa bas khyab pa go cha'i/
NK060(i)001:9837: pho mo'i dbang po rgyal mtshan gyi/
NK060(i)001:9838: rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis phyag rgya'i dang /
NK060(i)001:9839: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo gdugs kyi dang /
NK060(i)001:9840: rtsa gnas thig les gang ba bum pa'i lce la gnas pa'i ro 'bab ma bza' btung gi dang /
NK060(i)001:9841: khams lnga'i bcud dam rdzas su lnga ni snying po lnga'i dbang gi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu yin no //
NK060(i)001:9842: dbang bskur na zhes pa ni/
NK060(i)001:9843: 'chad par 'gyur ba'i nus dbang dang gsang dbang la'ang sbyar ste/
NK060(i)001:9844: dbang bskur ba'i yon tan dang sbrel ba'o //
NK060(i)001:9845: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:9846: de yang dbu rgyan la rin cen 'byung ldan gyis rab gnas bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9847: de bzhin du cod pan la rdo rje sems dpa' dang snang ba mtha' yas kyis/
NK060(i)001:9849: go cha la don yod grub pas/
NK060(i)001:9850: rgyal mtshan la rdor sems kyis/
NK060(i)001:9851: phyag rgya la lha rang rang gis/
NK060(i)001:9853: bum pa la rigs lnga gar gyis/
NK060(i)001:9854: bza' btung la rnam snang gis/
NK060(i)001:9855: snying po lnga la rang rang gi rigs kyis rab tu gnas pa bya pa rnams so //
NK060(i)001:9856: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi las/
NK060(i)001:9857: phan dbang bskur du rung ba'i slob bu rgyu'i rkyen/
NK060(i)001:9858: bskur nus pa'i slob dpon bdag po'i rkyen/
NK060(i)001:9859: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa dmigs pa rkyen/
NK060(i)001:9860: dbang snga mas go phyed nas phyi ma 'byung ba de ma thag pa'i rkyen no //
NK060(i)001:9861: gsum pa ngo bo ni phye phan pa'i dbang bcu po yin no //
NK060(i)001:9863: dper na rno la ngar btags pa ltar/
NK060(i)001:9864: dbang bskur bas nus pa dngos su skyes pa ste rang la gnas pa'i don mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9865: de yang dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las/
NK060(i)001:9866: dbang mchog rang la med gyur na //
NK060(i)001:9867: bskur bas thob par ga la 'gyur //
NK060(i)001:9868: bra sran 'bras bu dbang bskur kyang //
NK060(i)001:9869: de la 'bras bu dngos snang med //
NK060(i)001:9882: drug pa dbang bskur ba'i las rim ni re re la'ang lnga lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:9886: sgrib pa gang dag nas nus pa gang skye ba'i tshul smon lam dang bcas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:9887: zhib par kho bos dbang chog tu bris pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9889: brgyad pa yon tan ni 'og tu ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:9890: spyi don gnyis pa nus pa'i dbang lnga po re re la yang don brgyad brgyad sngar dang mtshungs te/
NK060(i)001:9891: dang po mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni/
NK060(i)001:9892: slob bu'i rna ba gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa na sgra
NK060(i)001:9893: nyan pa'i reg shes kyi thig le gnas pa nyan
NK060(i)001:9894: dbang gi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu'o //
NK060(i)001:9895: de bzhin du snying gi reg shes kyi thig le bsgom dbang gi/
NK060(i)001:9896: lag pa'i 'dom rtsa na skyod byed kyi thig le phrin las kyi/
NK060(i)001:9897: lce'i smra byed kyi thig le 'chad dbang gi/
NK060(i)001:9898: yan lag lnga'i thig le lnga ni rdo rje rgyal
NK060(i)001:9899: po bka' rab 'byams gyi dbang gi mtshungs ldan gyi
NK060(i)001:9900: rgyu'o // lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni/
NK060(i)001:9901: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa ste/
NK060(i)001:9902: ka p+aa li glegs bam can rin 'byung gi rab gnas byas pa nyan dbang gi/
NK060(i)001:9903: phreng ba yi dam gang yin gyi rab gnas can bsgom pa'i/
NK060(i)001:9904: rdo rje rgya gram don grub kyi rab gnas can phrin las kyi/
NK060(i)001:9905: dung dang phyags shing 'khor lo gsum la mtha' yas kyi rab gnas byas pa 'chad pa'i/
NK060(i)001:9906: rdo rje dang dril bu kun bzang yab yum gyi
NK060(i)001:9907: rab gnas can ni rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab
NK060(i)001:9908: 'byams kyi dbang gi lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu'o //
NK060(i)001:9909: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi las/
NK060(i)001:9910: nus dbang bskur du rung ba'i slob bu rgyu'i rkyen/
NK060(i)001:9911: bskur nus pa'i slob dpon bdag po'i rkyen/
NK060(i)001:9912: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa dmigs pa'i rkyen/
NK060(i)001:9913: dbang snga mas go phye nas phyi ma 'byung ba de ma thag pa'i rkyen no //
NK060(i)001:9915: nyan dbang la sogs pa'i nus pa'i dbang lnga po yin no //
NK060(i)001:9917: dbang bskur bas nus pa dngos su skyes pa de'o //
NK060(i)001:9919: nyan pa sgom pa phrin las 'chad pa rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang rnams go rim bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:9920: drug pa nus dbang bskur ba'i las rim ni/
NK060(i)001:9921: nus dbang lnga po re re la'ang bsam rgyud/
NK060(i)001:9924: sgrib pa gang dag nas nus pa gang skye ba dang lnga lnga las/
NK060(i)001:9925: dang po nyan dbang gi bsam rgyud/
NK060(i)001:9927: slob bu rnams kyi nyan byed de rna ba gnyis 'dom rtsa ru/
NK060(i)001:9928: rdo rje slob dpon kun bzang yab yum du gsal
NK060(i)001:9929: ba'i thugs ka nas yi ge b+h+r+aum 'phros pa las
NK060(i)001:9930: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa sgo dang bcas pa'i gzhal
NK060(i)001:9931: yas su bskyed la/ sgra gsal bar byed pa'i thig
NK060(i)001:9932: le'am reg shes kyi ngo bo nyid yi ge tram
NK060(i)001:9933: zung lnga ya bcu las rin cen 'byung ldan yab
NK060(i)001:9934: yum gyis gtso byas pa'i rigs chung gi sems dpa'
NK060(i)001:9935: yas su bskyed la/ yab yum brgyad/ sgo ba yab
NK060(i)001:9936: yum dang bcas pa lha bco brgyad kyi phyag rgya'i
NK060(i)001:9937: tshogs mchog tu gyur pa bskyed pa las ye shes
NK060(i)001:9938: yas su bskyed la/ yab yum brgyad/ lngas dbang bskur/ sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs/
NK060(i)001:9939: rin cen 'byung ldan gyis gtso byas pa'i dkyil 'khor snyan gsan dbab/
NK060(i)001:9941: dam tshig pa dang gnyis su med par bstim/
NK060(i)001:9942: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod/
NK060(i)001:9943: slob dpon yab yum kun bzang yab yum du gsal
NK060(i)001:9944: ba'i sbyor mtshams nas 'od 'phros pas sngar bskyed pa'i
NK060(i)001:9945: lha thams cad kyang mkha' gsang brlab/
NK060(i)001:9946: sbyor ba'i brda bskul nas snyoms par zhugs pas rjes
NK060(i)001:9947: chags kyi mes 'od du zhu nas slob bu la
NK060(i)001:9948: thim pas slob bu yang 'od du zhu ba'i 'od
NK060(i)001:9949: phung ser po la rin chen 'byung ldan du bskyed
NK060(i)001:9950: do // de bzhin du bsgom pa'i dbang la sogs
NK060(i)001:9951: pa rna ba la'ang lha bskyed tshul shes par bya'o
NK060(i)001:9953: tram zhes pa'i glus 'go drangs la/
NK060(i)001:9954: gsang ba ma h+aa yo ga /gsang chen a nu
NK060(i)001:9955: yo ga /gsang mchog a ti yo ga'i bstan pa
NK060(i)001:9956: dang theg pa gang yang rung ba'ang gsang ba kun
NK060(i)001:9957: la'ang ma nyan par bya zhing /
NK060(i)001:9958: gsang ba'i don de nyid rang gi rig pas brtag
NK060(i)001:9959: par bya ba las 'chad dbang ma thob kyi bar
NK060(i)001:9960: du gzhan du smra zhing bshad par bya ba min
NK060(i)001:9962: bskur gnas ni lag tu pu ti gtad la/
NK060(i)001:9963: bstim gnas ni mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu la bstim pas
NK060(i)001:9964: dbang bka' phyi nang gi chos la thogs pa med
NK060(i)001:9965: par nyan mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas nyan
NK060(i)001:9966: nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsam zhing
NK060(i)001:9967: / de dang rjes su mthun pa'i smon lam yang gdab bo //
NK060(i)001:9968: gnyis pa bsgom dbang gi bsam rgyud/
NK060(i)001:9970: dran pa gsal bar byed pa'i rten snying gi rtsa'i
NK060(i)001:9971: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi sgo dang bcas pa'i gzhal yas
NK060(i)001:9972: su bskyed cing / dran pa gsal bar byed pa'i
NK060(i)001:9973: thig le'i ngo bo nyid yi dam lha gang yin
NK060(i)001:9975: ya bcu'i phreng ba'i tshogs mchog las yi dam gang
NK060(i)001:9976: yin gyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor lha bco brgyad du
NK060(i)001:9977: gsal ba la 'od spro ba la sogs pas rjes
NK060(i)001:9978: chags kyi mes zhu ba slob bu la thim pa'i
NK060(i)001:9979: 'od phung las slob bu yi dam gang yin du
NK060(i)001:9981: +amo yi ge cha lnga pa glus 'go drangs pa
NK060(i)001:9982: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sras chen po bu khyod yin
NK060(i)001:9983: pas/ khyod kyi lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku gsung
NK060(i)001:9984: thugs kyi ngo bo mi phyed pas na rdo rje
NK060(i)001:9985: zhes bya ba ste de mi 'bral bar zung zhig
NK060(i)001:9986: /yi dam gyi lha mnyes pas rgyal ba thams cad
NK060(i)001:9987: mnyes pa'i phyir na mchod pa ste/
NK060(i)001:9988: yi dam gyi lha gcig dang tha dad las grol
NK060(i)001:9989: bas rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor ba yin
NK060(i)001:9991: bskur gnas lag tu phreng ba gtad/
NK060(i)001:9992: bstim gnas mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu la bstim mo //
NK060(i)001:9993: yi dam lha'i ting nge 'dzin rgyud la mi skye
NK060(i)001:9994: ba'i sgrib pa dag nas skyes ba'i nus pa dngos
NK060(i)001:9995: su skyes par bsam zhing smon lam yang bya'o //
NK060(i)001:9996: gsum pa phrin las kyi dbang gi bsam rgyud/
NK060(i)001:9998: lag pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi sgo dang bcas pa'i gzhal yas su bskyed cing /
NK060(i)001:9999: lag pa'i bya byed gsal bar byed pa'i thig le'i
NK060(i)001:10000: ngo bo nyid yi ge h+aam gi tshogs zung lnga
NK060(i)001:10001: ya bcu'i phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las lha bskyed pa
NK060(i)001:10002: ni/ lam kyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor lha bco brgyad du gsal ba la 'od 'phros pas/
NK060(i)001:10003: rjes chags kyi mes 'od du zhu nas slob bu
NK060(i)001:10004: la thim pas 'od phung ljang khu las slob bu
NK060(i)001:10007: +amo bu khyod ni phrin las kyi dbang thob pas rdo rje las mkhan yin gyis/
NK060(i)001:10008: phrin las bzhi la sogs pa rnams ma lus pa
NK060(i)001:10009: kun khyod kyis byos shig /thugs rje sprul pa dang
NK060(i)001:10011: mngag pa las kyi pho nya mang po nang du
NK060(i)001:10012: 'du ba dang phyir 'gro ba kun kyang las dbang
NK060(i)001:10013: thob pa'i bu khyod kyi dgos pa'i bya ba gang
NK060(i)001:10014: yin byed pa yin no zhes bsgrag go //
NK060(i)001:10015: bskur gnas lag tu rdo rje rgya gram gtad la/
NK060(i)001:10016: bstim gnas mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu la bstim mo //
NK060(i)001:10017: phrin las bzhis 'gro ba 'dul mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas/
NK060(i)001:10018: da 'dul nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsam zhing smon lam yang bya'o //
NK060(i)001:10019: bzhi pa 'chad dbang gi bsam rgyud/
NK060(i)001:10021: smra byed de lce'i 'dom rtsar b+h+r+aum 'phros pa las
NK060(i)001:10022: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i gzhal yas su sgra gsal
NK060(i)001:10023: ba'i reg shes kyi thig le'i ngo bo nyid yi
NK060(i)001:10024: ge h+r+ai zung lnga ya bcu'i phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog
NK060(i)001:10025: las gsung chos kyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK060(i)001:10026: tshogs/ snang ba mtha' yas kyis gtso byas pa bco brgyad du gsal ba la 'di spros pas/
NK060(i)001:10027: lha rnams rjes chags kyang mes zhu ba slob bu
NK060(i)001:10028: la thim pa'i 'od phung las snang ba mtha' yas
NK060(i)001:10030: +amo chos nyid don gyi bdud rtsi bla med kyi
NK060(i)001:10031: dad pa dang ldan pa'i skyes bu ngoms par byos
NK060(i)001:10032: shig /rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can gang yin brtags
NK060(i)001:10033: la snod dang mthun par gsang ba bsgrag par bya'o
NK060(i)001:10034: // gzhan du blo dang mi 'tshams pa bstan par bya ba nam yang min no zhes bsgrag go //
NK060(i)001:10035: bskur gnas lag tu dung dang phyags shing gtad la/
NK060(i)001:10036: bstim gnas mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu lce'i thig le la bstim mo //
NK060(i)001:10037: sngar phan chad sems can gyi rgyud la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas/
NK060(i)001:10038: da bskor nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsam zhing smon lam yang gdab bo //
NK060(i)001:10039: lnga pa rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams gyi dbang gi bsam rgyud/
NK060(i)001:10041: bskyod chen yan lag bzhi mgo dang lnga la/
NK060(i)001:10042: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i gzhal yas su gsal ba'i
NK060(i)001:10043: lha gnas rnams su skyed byed reg shes kyi thig
NK060(i)001:10045: lag pa g.yas pa'i mthing ga'i dkyil 'khor la h+aum zung lnga/
NK060(i)001:10046: de bzhin du mgo bo la +amo/
NK060(i)001:10047: lag pa g.yon pa la s+w+aa/
NK060(i)001:10049: g.yas la h+aa rnams zung lnga lnga ste ya bcu bcu'o //
NK060(i)001:10050: de ltar yi ge'i tshogs las dkyil 'khor cha lnga la lha yab yum lnga bcu dang /
NK060(i)001:10051: khro bo yab bcu khro mo yum bcu'i phreng ba
NK060(i)001:10052: rjes chags kyi mes zhu ba slob bu la thim
NK060(i)001:10053: pa'i 'od phung las slob bu kun tu bzang por
NK060(i)001:10056: +amo phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i de bzhin
NK060(i)001:10057: gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi rdo
NK060(i)001:10058: rje bdag nyid chen po khyod/
NK060(i)001:10059: rgyud dang dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed pa po yin
NK060(i)001:10060: pas dkyil 'khor kun gyi bdag po khyod kyis gyis
NK060(i)001:10061: la/ snod dang 'tshams par sbyin par bya ba dang longs spyod par yang gyis shig ces bsgrag go //
NK060(i)001:10062: bskur gnas lag tu rdo rje dril bu gtad la/
NK060(i)001:10063: bstim gnas mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu yan lag lnga'i thig le la bstim mo //
NK060(i)001:10064: sngar gzhan don byed pa'i mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas/
NK060(i)001:10065: da gzhan don byed par nus pa'i nus pa dngos
NK060(i)001:10066: su skyes par bsam zhing smon lam yang gdab bo
NK060(i)001:10067: // skyon yon spyir shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:10068: spyi don gsum pa zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur ba'o //
NK060(i)001:10070: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum po 'di la yang /
NK060(i)001:10071: dbang snga ma rnams dang tshul mtshungs par sa bcad nang tshegs re re la'ang brgyad brgyad las/
NK060(i)001:10074: don dam dkor bdun rang chas su yod pa ni gsang dbang gi/
NK060(i)001:10075: kun rdzob sku dang ye shes rang chas su yod pa ni shes rab ye shes kyi/
NK060(i)001:10076: bden gnyis dbyer med rang chas su yod pa ni
NK060(i)001:10077: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang gi mtshungs ldan
NK060(i)001:10078: gyi rgyu'o // lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni/
NK060(i)001:10079: phyag rgya mo nyi shu ma mtshan dang ldan pa ni gsang dbang gi/
NK060(i)001:10080: bcu drug ma shes rab ye shes kyi/
NK060(i)001:10081: bcu gnyis ma dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang gi lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu yin no //
NK060(i)001:10082: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi las/
NK060(i)001:10083: zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur du rung ba'i slob bu rgyu'i/
NK060(i)001:10084: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma bdag po'i //
NK060(i)001:10085: phyag rgya mtshan dang ldan pa dmigs pa'i/
NK060(i)001:10086: dbang snga ma go phyed nas phyi ma 'byung ba de ma thag pa'i rkyen no //
NK060(i)001:10088: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum po yin no //
NK060(i)001:10090: nus pa dngos su skyees pa'o //
NK060(i)001:10093: de nas shes rab ye shes/
NK060(i)001:10094: de'i rjes la bde ba chen po'o //
NK060(i)001:10095: drug pa dbang bskur ba'i las rim ni/
NK060(i)001:10096: zab mo'i dbang gsum gzhung gcig gi steng du sbrags nas 'chad de/
NK060(i)001:10097: ye shes dngos su rgyud la skye bar byed pa mthar thug gi dbang yin pas/
NK060(i)001:10098: bsam rgyud dang bsgrag tshig la ltos pa ni ma yin no //
NK060(i)001:10099: de yang thog mar gsang dbang bskur ba'i dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:10100: shes rab ma mtshan ldan lo nyi shu lon pa/
NK060(i)001:10104: thabs rdo rje slob dpon kun tu bzang po'am mi
NK060(i)001:10105: bskyod pa'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas yab yum gnyis
NK060(i)001:10106: kyi mkha' gsang bsnol mar brlab cing /
NK060(i)001:10107: sbyor ba'i brda bsnol mar bskur nas/
NK060(i)001:10108: dza h+aum bam ho phyag rgya bzhis rol pa las/
NK060(i)001:10109: yab kyi bde ba'i ye shes yi ge h+aum gis
NK060(i)001:10110: 'bru tshogs su gsal ba'i byang chub sems kyi chu
NK060(i)001:10111: rgyun gsang ba rdo rje'i lam nas byung nas yum
NK060(i)001:10112: gyi pad+mora 'khyil ba'i byang chub kyi sems yungs 'bru'i
NK060(i)001:10113: tshad tsam ste/ rdo rje sems dpa' sha stag tu byin gyis brlabs la gsang dbang bskur ro //
NK060(i)001:10115: thabs kyi gsang dbang ba dang be'u'i tshul du bskur ba ni/
NK060(i)001:10116: rdo rje slob dpon gyis yum gyi mkha' nas byang
NK060(i)001:10117: chub kyi sems gsang ba'i rdo rje'i rtses blangs nas
NK060(i)001:10118: slob bu'i lce thog tu bzhag pa'am/
NK060(i)001:10119: shes rab kyi gsang dbang me tog dang bung ba'i tshul du bskur ba ni/
NK060(i)001:10120: yum gyi pad+ma'i sna rtse nas slob bus 'jibs nas byang chub kyi sems lce thog tu blangs pa'am/
NK060(i)001:10121: thabs shes rab gnyis med kyi gsang dbang bya dang byi'u'i tshul du bskur ba ni/
NK060(i)001:10122: rdo rje slob dpon gyi ljags kyis yum gyi mkha'
NK060(i)001:10123: nas byang chub kyi sems blangs nas slob bu'i lce
NK060(i)001:10125: la la dag byang chub gyi sems dkar po byin pa thabs kyi gsang dbang /
NK060(i)001:10126: dmar po byin pa shes rab kyi gsang dbang /
NK060(i)001:10127: gnyis 'dres byin pa thabs shes gnyis med kyi gsang dbang zhes kyang 'dod do //
NK060(i)001:10128: mdor na bskur thabs gsum po gang rung gis/
NK060(i)001:10129: bzhag lce la bzhag kyang bstim snying la bstim zhing
NK060(i)001:10130: dbang bskur bas snying gi rtsa ba'i rtsa chen bzhi
NK060(i)001:10131: la gnas pa'i 'gro ba rigs drug tu skye bar
NK060(i)001:10132: byed pa'i sa bon/ a su n+ri tri pre duhzunga gsum ya drug gnyid dang bcas pa sbyangs te/
NK060(i)001:10133: bde ba'i ye shes su gsal bas/
NK060(i)001:10134: dper na sa bon tshig pa la myu gu mi 'byung ba bzhin du/
NK060(i)001:10135: ngan song dang 'khor ba kar dag pas don dam spros med kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba ste/
NK060(i)001:10136: don dam gyi bden pa mngon du byas pa ni gsang ba'i dbang thob pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:10137: de yang thal ba'i rgyud las/
NK060(i)001:10138: mi bskyod yab yum rol pa yis //
NK060(i)001:10139: bde ba gsal zhing mi dmigs pa //
NK060(i)001:10140: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK060(i)001:10141: rdo rje ye shes h+aum tshogs kyis //
NK060(i)001:10143: yungs kar tshad tsam rdo rje sems //
NK060(i)001:10144: rtse nas rtse ru phyin pa yis //
NK060(i)001:10145: rang bzhin chos khams dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK060(i)001:10146: sa bon zung gsum gnyis dang bcas //
NK060(i)001:10147: gnas ngan len pa gsum sbyangs te //
NK060(i)001:10148: dmigs med sems kyi ye shes lnga //
NK060(i)001:10149: gsal ba'i sa bon tshig pa bzhin //
NK060(i)001:10150: mi skye thabs kyi dbugs dbyung ba'o //
NK060(i)001:10152: gnyis pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur ba ni/
NK060(i)001:10153: sngar bzhin chas su btsud pa'i shes rab ma lo bcu drug lon pa/
NK060(i)001:10154: nyi ma byang sems 'dzag pa'i dus su thabs slob bu rdo rje sems dpa' bskyed pa la gtad de/
NK060(i)001:10155: slob bu yab yum gnyis kyi mkha' gsang bsnol mar brlab cing sbyor ba'i brda bsnol mar bskul nas/
NK060(i)001:10156: dza h+aum bam hoh phyag rgya bzhis rol pa las
NK060(i)001:10157: bde ba'i byang shes h+aum gis 'bru tshogs su gsal
NK060(i)001:10158: ba'i chu rgyun 'bab pa ni yas bab kyi dga'
NK060(i)001:10159: ba ste/ de yang klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo nas mgrin par bab pa dga' ba/
NK060(i)001:10162: gsang ba rdo rje'i lam nas 'byung ba'i tshe dga'
NK060(i)001:10163: bzhi'i mthar thug lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba nyams
NK060(i)001:10164: su myong zhing / rten byang chub sems kyi thig
NK060(i)001:10165: le yum gyi pad+mara reg pa'i gnas su 'khyil bas
NK060(i)001:10166: yum gyi nyi ma byang chub kyi sems dang rtse
NK060(i)001:10167: 'phrad nas thig le phyed shor phyed ma shor te
NK060(i)001:10168: drag thung lta bur gnas pa de/
NK060(i)001:10169: yab yum gnyis kyi gsang rtsa phan tshun du bstim
NK060(i)001:10170: zhing dbang bskur bas nyon mongs par rang sar grol
NK060(i)001:10171: nas/ kun rdzob bde chen gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang
NK060(i)001:10172: bskur ba ste kun rdzob kyi bden pa mngon du
NK060(i)001:10173: nas/ byas pa ni/ shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:10175: rjes su 'jug pa'i phyag rgya nyid //
NK060(i)001:10176: zil pa'i thig le sngon lam bzhin //
NK060(i)001:10177: bcu drug phyed phyed thig le gcig /phan tshun 'god pa'i stobs kyis bstim //
NK060(i)001:10178: bde ba gnyis pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK060(i)001:10179: gsum pa ye shes dkyil 'khor du //
NK060(i)001:10180: gsal bar shar bas gyur ba'i sgra //
NK060(i)001:10183: gsum pa dbyer med bde chen gyi dbang ni/
NK060(i)001:10184: sngar bzhin chas su bcug pa'i shes rab ma mtshan dang ldan pa lo bcu gnyis lon pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10185: thabs slob bu rdo rje sems dpa'i nga rgyal dang
NK060(i)001:10186: ldan pa'i yab yum gnyis kyi mkha' gsang brlabs sbyor
NK060(i)001:10187: ba'i brdas bskul nas phyag rgya bzhi rol pa las/
NK060(i)001:10188: yab yum gnyis kyi bde ba'i ye shes byang chub
NK060(i)001:10189: sems kyi thig le yi ge h+aum gi 'bru tshogs
NK060(i)001:10190: su gsal ba'i chu rgyun gsang ba rdo rje'i lam
NK060(i)001:10191: nas yum gyi pad+mara 'khyil bas yab yum gnyis kyi
NK060(i)001:10192: dga' ba bzhi bzhi ste brgyad po dus gcig tu
NK060(i)001:10193: ro mnyam zhing / re re yang bzhi bzhi'i dbye bas mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis rdzogs la/
NK060(i)001:10194: yab kyi dga' ba bcu drug po re re yang
NK060(i)001:10195: ye shes lnga lnga'i ro dang ldan pas dpe byad
NK060(i)001:10196: bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan zhing mngon par shes
NK060(i)001:10198: yum gyi rtsa kha kha mu kha'i sna rtse nas
NK060(i)001:10199: lhan cig skyes dag'i ye shes kyi bdag nyid thig
NK060(i)001:10201: 'gro 'ong byang chub sems kyi kyis tshur log nas gsang ba rdo rje'i bu gar bstim zhing /
NK060(i)001:10202: thig le rdo rje'i lam nas yar log pa ni mas brtan gyi dga' ba ste/
NK060(i)001:10203: lte bar brtan pa dga' ba/
NK060(i)001:10206: spyi bor brtan pa ni lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba'o //
NK060(i)001:10207: de tsam na brda gcig kun tu 'od kyis rdzogs shing /
NK060(i)001:10208: de'i yon tan gyi thig les lus thams cad du
NK060(i)001:10209: khyab cing brtan pas 'khor ba'i skyon gyis ma gos
NK060(i)001:10210: pas bcu gnyis pad+ma can gyi sa dang /
NK060(i)001:10211: rtogs tshogs thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK060(i)001:10212: 'khor du rang snang bas bcu gsum yi ge 'khor
NK060(i)001:10213: lo tshogs chen gyi sa rdzogs pas na/
NK060(i)001:10214: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang sgyur ba ste/
NK060(i)001:10215: dbyer med kyi bden pa mngon du byas pa ni bde ba chen po'i dbang thob pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:10217: rdo rje nyi ma thabs kyi rgya //
NK060(i)001:10218: phung tshogs phyag rgya'i tshogs dang ldan //
NK060(i)001:10219: de zla ba'i sil byed shes rab dngos //
NK060(i)001:10220: dus gcig ro mnyam thig le che //
NK060(i)001:10221: sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan rdzogs shing //
NK060(i)001:10222: zla ba'i ye shes lnga bcu drug /dpe byad la sogs dpag tu med //
NK060(i)001:10223: sems shes mngon par shes dang ldan //
NK060(i)001:10225: gnas nas log pa thim pa'i sgras //
NK060(i)001:10226: mtha' gnyis ma gos pad+ma'i can //
NK060(i)001:10227: sprul pa'i gnas nas skyes ba yi //
NK060(i)001:10228: bzhi bcu lnga shogs mtha' yas kun //
NK060(i)001:10229: rang bzhin nyid las rang gsal ba //
NK060(i)001:10230: bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lor brjod //
NK060(i)001:10235: slob dpon gyi rnam grangs drug gsungs kyang /
NK060(i)001:10236: 'dir dam tshig dbang gi slob dpon nye bar bzung ste/
NK060(i)001:10237: slob bu rab kyi shes rab dang sgrub pas/
NK060(i)001:10238: 'bring gis dad pa dang spyod lam gyis/
NK060(i)001:10239: tha mas kyang zang zing dang zhabs 'bring gis mnyes par ma byas shing /
NK060(i)001:10240: phan nus zab mo'i dbang rnams thob par ma byas par nyan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10243: phrin las sgrub pa dang la sogs pa'i sogs khongs
NK060(i)001:10244: nas dkyil 'khor gyi thig gdab pa la sogs pa
NK060(i)001:10245: rdo rje slob dpon gyi las rab 'byams rtsom pa
NK060(i)001:10246: rnams tshe 'dir yang 'bras bu mchog dang thun mong
NK060(i)001:10248: tshe phyi mar yang bka' zab mo rang dgar bardzabasa
NK060(i)001:10249: pa'i rkyen gyis ngan song du skyes nas bde 'bras
NK060(i)001:10251: dbang bskur ba'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:10253: dbang thob pa'i dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i gdung
NK060(i)001:10254: 'dzin pa'i sras yin pas ngan song gsum gyi sdug
NK060(i)001:10255: bsngal thams cad kyang med pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10256: skye ba 'dir yang tshe ring zhing bde ba phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10257: skye ba phyi mar yang phan dbang gi 'bras bu
NK060(i)001:10258: mtho ris kyi nang nas kyang lha mi'i rgyal po
NK060(i)001:10259: dang / nus dbang gi 'bras bu thar pa'i lam ston pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang /
NK060(i)001:10260: zab dbang gi 'bras bu rigs thams cad kyi bdag
NK060(i)001:10261: por rgyal ba drug pa nyid du 'gyur ro zhes
NK060(i)001:10264: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:10265: snod gsum la dbang gsum rim pa bzhin sbyin pa'i
NK060(i)001:10266: le'u ste yas bgrangs bcu pa'i don du gada'o////da ni
NK060(i)001:10267: le'u bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa bsdebs nas
NK060(i)001:10268: ston pa la chos tshoms kyi dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:10269: rab gi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las gsum ka ston/
NK060(i)001:10270: snang ba bzhi las gzhi zur tsam ston/
NK060(i)001:10271: lam dang 'bras bu'i snang ba gtso cher ston/
NK060(i)001:10272: lam la thabs grol gnyis las gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:10273: rim cig car gnyis las gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:10274: mtshan nyid gsum las gsum ka ston/
NK060(i)001:10275: 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las rgyud don/
NK060(i)001:10276: de la bcu las gzhung hril po tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang sgrub pa ston/
NK060(i)001:10278: h+aum du shes bas rab spyad na //
NK060(i)001:10280: sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa ston/
NK060(i)001:10281: phyag rgya dang ting nge 'dzin ston/
NK060(i)001:10282: tha ma'i chos tshoms bcu las rang bzhin lta ba/
NK060(i)001:10283: ldem dgongs man ngag /bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud/
NK060(i)001:10285: gzhan yang spyi 'gro rnams kyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:10286: de ltar le'u bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa
NK060(i)001:10287: bsdebs nas tshogs sgrub pa ston pa byed pa la
NK060(i)001:10289: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa gnyis bsdebs te ston pa/
NK060(i)001:10291: le'u dgu par tshogs sgrub pa med par bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:10293: le'u dgu par dkyil 'khor du zhugs/
NK060(i)001:10295: bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa sdebs nas tshogs
NK060(i)001:10296: sgrub pa ston pas na de nas zhes 'grel byar
NK060(i)001:10297: ro // de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa chen pos
NK060(i)001:10298: lha yab yum zung du 'brel ba sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK060(i)001:10299: ba'i rgyal po rtog pa la rang dbang sgyur ba
NK060(i)001:10300: zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin nam dgongs pa la
NK060(i)001:10301: mngon du bzhag pas na snyoms par zhugs nas 'og
NK060(i)001:10302: nas 'byung ba tshogs sgrub pa'i ched du brjod pa
NK060(i)001:10303: ro // 'di brjod do // de nas de bzhin
NK060(i)001:10304: gshegs pa dgyes pa chen po zhes pa ni 'bru
NK060(i)001:10305: ro // 'di brjod do // mthun la/ sems nyid
NK060(i)001:10306: gzhi ma ngos pa la yo byad lngar snang nas
NK060(i)001:10307: tshim par byed pa ni ye shes kyi rol mo'i
NK060(i)001:10308: sprin rnam par snang ba sna tshogs su spros te/
NK060(i)001:10309: 'khor 'das gnyis med sgrub pa'i thabs su mdzes pas
NK060(i)001:10310: rgyan bkod pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK060(i)001:10311: dgongs pa mngon du bzhag pas na snyoms par zhugs
NK060(i)001:10312: nas tshogs sgrub pa'i ched du brjod pa 'di brjod
NK060(i)001:10313: do // gzhung gnyis tshogs sgrub par bsdebs te bstan pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:10314: gzhung dngos gnyis bsdebs te bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10315: bka' gsang sngags mtshon pa'i tshig dang gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan gnyis ba sdebs te bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:10318: mtshan nyid gsum mdor bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:10320: 'di la lam rim gyis pa ltar du bshad na
NK060(i)001:10321: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba nyams su lon
NK060(i)001:10322: pa dang rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin
NK060(i)001:10323: las su rung bas lta spyod mgo 'byor zhing de'i
NK060(i)001:10324: don bsgom pa ni 'khor bar mi gtong ba'i gzungs
NK060(i)001:10325: so // de la rgyun du goms nas lam nus
NK060(i)001:10326: pa'i mthu can du gang gyur pa des ni 'bras
NK060(i)001:10329: gnas skabs lam gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi
NK060(i)001:10330: dang mthar thug rgyal ba sku lnga'i 'bras bu thob
NK060(i)001:10331: nas/ de dag gi 'dul bya'i zhing khams kun tu grags so zhes pa'am/
NK060(i)001:10332: yang lam cig car ba ltar du bshad na/
NK060(i)001:10333: rgyu lta ba dang rkyen ting nge 'dzin te/
NK060(i)001:10334: lta sgom cig car du mgo 'byor ba'i spyod pas
NK060(i)001:10335: lam log dang 'khor ba'i g.yang sar mi 'gro ba'i
NK060(i)001:10336: gzungs ting nge 'dzin nus pa'i mthu can du gyur
NK060(i)001:10337: te/ de'i nyer rdzogs su lhun grub rig 'dzin thob
NK060(i)001:10338: nas sku lnga'i zhing du grags shing sku lnga'i 'bras
NK060(i)001:10340: mtshan nyid gsum rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK060(i)001:10341: de la spyi don gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:10342: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba/
NK060(i)001:10343: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin/
NK060(i)001:10344: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK060(i)001:10345: spyi don dang po la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:10346: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10347: grub mtha' dang 'bras bu gzhan du tshol ba'i zhen pa dgag pa'o //
NK060(i)001:10352: 'di la rim gyis pa ltar du bshad pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10353: cig car ba ltar du bshad pa gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:10354: dang po rim gyis pa ltar du bshad na 'khor 'das kyi chos gzhal bya dang /
NK060(i)001:10355: rgyu gcig pa gtan tshig dang /
NK060(i)001:10356: skye med du rtogs pa grub mtha' ste/
NK060(i)001:10357: des dngos po mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i zhen pa 'gro ba'o //
NK060(i)001:10358: skye med du zhen pa gzhal bya dang yig 'bru'i tshul gtan tshigs dang /
NK060(i)001:10359: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor rtogs pa grub mtha' ste/
NK060(i)001:10360: des stong pa phyang chad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa 'grol ba'o //
NK060(i)001:10361: rtogs pa snga ma gnyis su zhen pa gzhal bya dang /
NK060(i)001:10362: byin gyis brlabs pa gtan tshigs dang /
NK060(i)001:10363: dbyer med du rtogs pa grub mtha' ste/
NK060(i)001:10364: bden gnyis tha dad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa 'grol ba'o //
NK060(i)001:10365: bden gnyis dbyer med du zhen pa gzhal bya dang /
NK060(i)001:10366: mngon sum par gtan la 'bebs pa gtan tshigs dang /
NK060(i)001:10367: spyod yul dang bral bar rtogs pa grub mtha' ste/
NK060(i)001:10368: lta ba bden pa dbyer med blo'i yul du byed pa'i zhen pa 'grol ba'o //
NK060(i)001:10369: bzhi po 'di sbyor ngag tu bkod na ma rig
NK060(i)001:10370: pa dang log rtog gi rgyun las 'khor bar snang
NK060(i)001:10371: ba dang / sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor las myang 'das su snang ba 'di chos can/
NK060(i)001:10372: de dag rang bzhin skye med kyi dbyings las g.yos pa med pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:10373: brgyud du sems nyid rang byung ye shes su gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:10374: dper na rgyal po'i phrug gu dmangs su 'khyams pa bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:10376: chos nyid dbyings su tshul gcig pas //
NK060(i)001:10377: ma lus rang snang chos thams cad //
NK060(i)001:10378: ma lus byang chub sems su rtogs //
NK060(i)001:10380: sems nyid skye med kyi gdangs chos can/
NK060(i)001:10381: rol pa 'gag med lha'i sku gsung thugs su rang snang ba yin te/
NK060(i)001:10382: mtshon du med pa'i yi ge a nyid mtshon byed yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa lngar snang ba'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:10384: sku gsung thugs su snang ba yis //
NK060(i)001:10385: ma lus gsung gi rgyan du rtogs //
NK060(i)001:10386: thams cad gsung gi yi ge ste //
NK060(i)001:10387: thabs dang ldan pas rgyas gdab bo //
NK060(i)001:10389: rang bzhin skye med dang rol pa 'gag med gnyis chos can/
NK060(i)001:10390: tshig la snga phyi yod kyang don la dbyer med de/
NK060(i)001:10391: dkor bdun ngo bo nyid kyi rgyud lhun gyis grub
NK060(i)001:10392: pas snod bcud sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:10393: du ye nas sangs rgyas par byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK060(i)001:10394: phyir/ de yang rgya mtsho las/
NK060(i)001:10395: de nyid dbyer med byin brlabs las //
NK060(i)001:10396: de nyid de'i byin brlabs te //
NK060(i)001:10397: gnyis med tshul gyis rang snang ba //
NK060(i)001:10398: byin brlabs ngo mtshar bsam mi khyab //
NK060(i)001:10400: bden pa dbyer med chos can/
NK060(i)001:10401: blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:10402: rang rig pa'i mngon sum gyis yul med rang gsal du rtogs pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:10404: rang byung rang snang chos 'di dag /gnyis med rang rig ma skyes par //
NK060(i)001:10405: gsal bar mngon sum the tshom med //
NK060(i)001:10406: rtogs pa kun gyi mchog tu bshad //
NK060(i)001:10408: de ltar gtan tshigs bzhis gtan la phab pa'i grub
NK060(i)001:10409: mtha' rab tu rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi yis chos
NK060(i)001:10410: thams cad rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal bar
NK060(i)001:10411: rdzogs shing rig pa la rang dbang sgyur bas na
NK060(i)001:10412: rgyal po ste/ sngags kyi rgyud dang dbu sems las
NK060(i)001:10413: khyad par du gyur pas na 'di las che ba'i
NK060(i)001:10415: yang cig car ba ltar du bshad na/
NK060(i)001:10416: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad don dam skye 'gag
NK060(i)001:10417: gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong dang bral bar rgyu gcig /kun
NK060(i)001:10418: rdzob skyes 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong ltar snang bar
NK060(i)001:10419: rgyu gcig /bden pa dbyer med du skyes pa nyid
NK060(i)001:10420: na skye ba med pa la sogs pa lngar rgyu
NK060(i)001:10421: gcig pa'o // 'o na yig 'bru'i tshul gyi gtan tshigs mi dgos sam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10422: dgos te rgyu gcig par rtogs pa de yig 'bru'i tshul gyi gtan tshigs kyis mtshon nas rtogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:10423: 'o na byin gyis rlabs mi dgos sam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10424: dgos te yig 'bru'i tshul la brten nas rtogs kyang mthu byin gyis rlabs la yod pas so //
NK060(i)001:10425: 'o na mngon sum pa ni mi dgos sam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10426: dgos te dbyer med du zhen pa las kyang grol bar byed pas so //
NK060(i)001:10427: de yang bzhi po de rim par rtogs pa ni ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:10428: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rgyu gcig par yig
NK060(i)001:10429: 'bru'i tshul gyis mtshon nas byin gyis brlabs pa'i mthus
NK060(i)001:10430: dbyer med du gtan la phebs pas rang rig pa'i
NK060(i)001:10431: mngon sum gyis blo'i spyod yul las grol ba ni
NK060(i)001:10434: rim gyis pa ltar bshad pa'i dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:10435: gzhal bya gtan tshigs grub mtha' gsum mtshon tshul 'dren pa'i skyon du 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10436: rdo rje drings pa nye'u ston na re/
NK060(i)001:10438: rgyu gcig pa'i gtan tshigs kyis ston par rtog pa
NK060(i)001:10439: dang yig 'bru'i tshul gyis gtan tshigs kyis sgyu mar
NK060(i)001:10440: rtogs pa'i ngos nas grub mthar 'gro yang /
NK060(i)001:10441: stong pa dang snang ba gnyis la zhen pa'i cha
NK060(i)001:10442: nas byin gyis brlabs kyi gtan tshigs kyis gzhal byar
NK060(i)001:10443: 'gro gsung ngo // gtsang nag 'od 'bar na re/
NK060(i)001:10444: bden gsum rang sa'i gzhal bya gtan tshigs grub mtha' gsum mtshon tshul 'dres na skyon du che yang /
NK060(i)001:10445: gtan tshigs snga ma snga ma'i grub mtha' phyi ma phyi ma'i gzhal byar song ba la skyon med de/
NK060(i)001:10446: khyod kyi mar 'dod gang yin pa //
NK060(i)001:10447: de ni nga yi chung ma yin //
NK060(i)001:10449: yang na kun tu 'od mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu yin yang /
NK060(i)001:10450: sngags kyi lam stegs su bshad de/
NK060(i)001:10453: pad+ma can du gyur pas na //
NK060(i)001:10456: khyod kyi mthar phyin kun tu 'od //
NK060(i)001:10457: thabs chen theg pa'i bsti gnas sa //
NK060(i)001:10458: zhes gsungs pa bzhin no zhes gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:10459: yang mngon sum pa ni grub mtha' yin pa la gtan tshigs su ci 'gro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10460: zhor sel zhor bsgrub kyi cha nas 'gro ste/
NK060(i)001:10461: dper na mi ngan zhig gi bud med la bu skyes na/
NK060(i)001:10462: bu des dgra gnyen la phan gnod gang yang ma byas kyang pha ma'i dgra rnam mi dga' la/
NK060(i)001:10463: gnyen rnams dga' ba bzhin du mngon sum par rtogs pas dbyer med kyi zhen cha zhor la sel la/
NK060(i)001:10464: spyod yul dang bral ba zhor la bsgrub pas de'i
NK060(i)001:10465: cha nas gtan tshigs dang grub mtha' gnyis kar du
NK060(i)001:10466: yang 'gro zhes bla ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:10467: yang le'u gsum par rtogs pa bzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:10469: mnyam pa nyid kyi gtan tshigs byung /
NK060(i)001:10470: 'dir yang rtogs pa bzhi dag mnyam gyi gtan tshigs byung bas ldabs so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10472: le'u gsum pa ni las dang po pa la brtag
NK060(i)001:10473: gzhi 'khor ba'i chos gtan la 'beb pa'i gtan tshigs
NK060(i)001:10474: yin la/ 'dir tshogs sgrub pa'i sngon 'gro yin pas ldabs skyon med gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:10475: dag mnyam gyi gtan tshigs so //
NK060(i)001:10477: le'u gsum par rtogs pa bzhi dang dag mnyam gyi gtan tshig kyis gtan la phab pa bzhin du/
NK060(i)001:10478: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten 'byung ba lngas bsdus pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10479: nang bcud kyi sems can phung po lngas bsdus pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10480: de dag gi rgyud rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad
NK060(i)001:10481: kyis bsdus pa rnams ye gdod ma nas 'byung ba
NK060(i)001:10483: phung po lnga rigs kyi yab lnga/
NK060(i)001:10484: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar dag
NK060(i)001:10485: pa las dag pa ltar gtan tshigs kyis gzhigs pa'i
NK060(i)001:10486: sgo nas rtogs shing gzhan yang mnyam pa gnyis kyi
NK060(i)001:10487: dbang du byas nas mdo sdee pa dang sgo bstun
NK060(i)001:10488: pa thun mong gi mnyam pa gnyis ni/
NK060(i)001:10489: snang tsam du don byed nus pa yang dag pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK060(i)001:10490: snang tsam du'ang don byed nus pas stong pa log
NK060(i)001:10491: pa'i kun rdzob gnyis ka'ang snang yang bden dngos kyis
NK060(i)001:10492: stong pa tsam du mnyam zhing /
NK060(i)001:10493: spros pa phyogs te chod pa rnam grangs kyi don dam pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10494: spros pa mtha' dag chod pa rnam grangs ma yin
NK060(i)001:10495: don dam gnyis ka'ang spros pa 'gag pa'i stong nyid
NK060(i)001:10497: lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis ni/
NK060(i)001:10498: ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs kyis ma dag pa las snang log pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK060(i)001:10499: dag pa lha snang yang dag pa'i kun rdzob gnyis
NK060(i)001:10500: ka'ang rang bzhin dang thun mong ma yin pa dang
NK060(i)001:10501: / kar dag pa thugs su chud pa na sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du mnyam la/
NK060(i)001:10502: rnam grangs kyi don dam med dgag gi stong nyid dang /
NK060(i)001:10503: rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam ma yin dgag
NK060(i)001:10504: gi stong nyid gnyis ka'ang dkor bdun ngo bo nyid
NK060(i)001:10505: du lhun gyis grub par mnyam mo //
NK060(i)001:10506: de ltar dag mnyam kyi gtan tshigs kyis kun rdzob
NK060(i)001:10507: kyi bden pa ma dag pa las kyi snang ba
NK060(i)001:10508: 'di 'khrul ngo tsam du mi bslu yang /
NK060(i)001:10509: gshis la ma grub par gtan la phab pas bden
NK060(i)001:10510: gnyis tha dad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa grol kyang
NK060(i)001:10511: / tshu rol mthong ba'i blos chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du 'dzin na yang 'khrul pa'i blos te/
NK060(i)001:10512: de'i phyir gzhal bya sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK060(i)001:10513: 'khor spyod yul yongs su dag pa kun tu bzang
NK060(i)001:10514: po'i ngang du 'jal byed kyi blo ngo bo nyid
NK060(i)001:10515: du grol zhing / lus ngag yid gsum gyi byed
NK060(i)001:10516: spyod ma 'gags pa'i cha nas bsod nams kyi tshogs
NK060(i)001:10517: du grol zhing / dang / ma dmigs pa'i cha nas ye shes kyi tshogs te/
NK060(i)001:10518: de ltar tshogs chen gnyis su gyur pa ni rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:10519: de don nyams su len par byed pa rkyen 'jug
NK060(i)001:10520: pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin gyi 'go 'dren pas
NK060(i)001:10522: grub mtha' dang 'bras bu gzhan du tshol ba'i zhen pa dgag pa'o //
NK060(i)001:10524: dus bzhi dang phyogs bcu gang gi gnas nas lam
NK060(i)001:10525: gyi 'bad rtsol gyi btsal bar gyur kyang rang gi
NK060(i)001:10526: sems nyid las gzhan pa'i 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK060(i)001:10527: rgyas zhes bya ba cig brnyes par mi 'gyur ro
NK060(i)001:10529: rang gi sems nyid de ka rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas yin pa ste/
NK060(i)001:10530: de las gzhan pa'i sangs rgyas med phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:10531: 'o na lam bgrod pa la dgos pa med dam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10532: rang gi sems nyid sangs rgyas yin pa la yin pa ltar/
NK060(i)001:10533: de mngon du byed pa la lam bgrod pa'i ba zhes tha snyad du byas kyi/
NK060(i)001:10534: de las gzhan du sangs rgyas zhes pa'i 'bras bu
NK060(i)001:10535: bzang bzang po gcig ma tshol zhig /spyi don gnyis
NK060(i)001:10536: pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin la
NK060(i)001:10537: gnyis te/ sgrub pa'i gzhi phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10538: sgrub pa'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:10541: dang po sgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa/
NK060(i)001:10543: sngags kyi yan lag lnga zhes pa lhag pa'i lha
NK060(i)001:10544: dgu'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK060(i)001:10545: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams
NK060(i)001:10546: shing / sngar bshad pa'i bza' dang btung ba la sogs pa yo byad lnga dang ldan pa/
NK060(i)001:10547: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa
NK060(i)001:10548: cho ga lnga rdzogs par shes pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK060(i)001:10549: tshom bu lnga pa la pho mo bdun bcu/
NK060(i)001:10550: tshom bu gsum pa pho mo zhe drug /tshom bu
NK060(i)001:10551: gcig pa la bco brgyad kyi 'tshogs pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:10552: gyis tshogs bsgrubs na nges par 'grub ste/
NK060(i)001:10554: legs pa'i dgongs pa gnas skabs rig 'dzin bzhi yi
NK060(i)001:10555: go 'phang dang mthar thug sangs rgyas kyis 'grub par
NK060(i)001:10556: 'gyur ro // gnas dang yo byad thun mong du
NK060(i)001:10557: bstan pa rang bdag dbang bar chad med pa'i gnas
NK060(i)001:10558: phyi nang bar gsum dang ldan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10559: nye bar dgos pa'i longs spyod ldabs thang du bsags te/
NK060(i)001:10560: bza' btung dang rkyen bzlog dang sgrub rdzas la sogs pa phun sum tshogs par bsag cing /
NK060(i)001:10561: ci bde bar longs spyad rgyu dang ldan par byas la sgrub pa'i dam tshig rnams ma nyams shing /
NK060(i)001:10562: lta spyod dang ting nge 'dzin 'brel ba'i blo dang
NK060(i)001:10563: ni rab tu ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pho mo 'tshogs
NK060(i)001:10564: pas/ dang po tshom bu gang yin gyi lha grangs
NK060(i)001:10565: dang dus ji tsam sgrub par khas blangs shing dam
NK060(i)001:10566: nos pa bzhin du byas te/
NK060(i)001:10567: le lo dang sgyid snyoms med pa yis blo la
NK060(i)001:10568: the tshom med pa'i sgo nas bsgrub cing nyams len
NK060(i)001:10569: gzhung bzhin byas na tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:10570: gcig gsum lnga pa gang bsgrubs kyang gnas skabs su
NK060(i)001:10571: thun mong dang mthar thug tu mchog gi dngos grub
NK060(i)001:10574: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'am nyi shu
NK060(i)001:10575: lnga dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje gsang mchog sangs
NK060(i)001:10576: rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa dam pa gcig dang
NK060(i)001:10577: du ma dang bral ba thob par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:10578: 'o na tshom bu tshogs sgrub pa'i thabs le'u lnga pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10580: 'di dang gsum ka ru byung ba ldabs so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10582: le'u lnga pa'i ni sgrub pa'i rgyu dang thun mong gi sgrub pa yin/
NK060(i)001:10583: dgu pa'i ni 'grub pa'i dus dang thob tshul yin/
NK060(i)001:10584: 'di ni phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung /
NK060(i)001:10585: bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ste/
NK060(i)001:10586: sgrub thabs dngos ston pa yin pas na ma ldabs so //
NK060(i)001:10587: bsgrub pa'i dus phun sum tshogs pa bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:10589: sgrub pa'i dus kyi zhag grangs ni/
NK060(i)001:10591: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK060(i)001:10592: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10593: tshes grangs ni yar ngo'i tshe brgyad la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10594: gzhan yang dus tshod gza' skar bzang po la grub pa la 'jug ste/
NK060(i)001:10595: rgyud kun 'dus le'u dang po las spros pa bzhin du bya bar bshad pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:10597: rgyud las smos pa bzhin du bshad //
NK060(i)001:10599: 'di rgyud min par 'dug pa la rgyud du bshad pas rgyud log pa'i skyon du 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10601: tshogs sgrub pa'i dus 'di nyid rang gi le'u dgu par bstan tshar ba dang /
NK060(i)001:10602: dus tshod dang tshes grangs la sogs ba kun 'dus
NK060(i)001:10603: la sogs pa'i rgyud sde gzhan na gsal ba la
NK060(i)001:10604: kha 'phangs pas 'di rgyud ma yin par mi 'gyur
NK060(i)001:10605: te/ 'di lta bu'i tshul sngags phyi nang gsar rnying
NK060(i)001:10606: gi rgyud sde du ma na mang du snang ngo
NK060(i)001:10607: te/ // des kyang mi go na/
NK060(i)001:10608: 'o na 'phags pa sdud pa 'di yang de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung ma yin par 'gyur te/
NK060(i)001:10609: de dag ma rig las byung bde bar gshegs pas gsungs //
NK060(i)001:10610: zhes bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung gzhan la 'phangs pa'i phyir ro zhes bya ba la mgo mtshungs basgre'o //
NK060(i)001:10611: gnyis pa sgrub pa'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis/
NK060(i)001:10612: zhi ba'i tshogs sgrub pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10615: bgrang bsnyen sgrub bzhir mdor bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:10618: lam dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:10619: stong pa chen po dang kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin gnyis ni bsnyen pa'i yan lag dang /
NK060(i)001:10620: phyag rgya gcig pa dang spros bcas ni nye bar bsnyen pa'i yan lag dang /
NK060(i)001:10621: yo byad lngas tshogs sgrub pa ni sgrub pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10622: de'i dus su +aa li k+aa li nyams su lon pa ni sgrub pa chen po ste/
NK060(i)001:10623: mthar chags rim gyis pa lam bgrod pa'i dbang du'o //
NK060(i)001:10624: sgrub pa'i dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi ni/
NK060(i)001:10625: shoms yan lag dang 'brel ba bsnyen pa/
NK060(i)001:10626: sgrub pa ji tsam byed pa'i zhag grangs kyi phyed
NK060(i)001:10627: yan chad 'od zer dkar po phyir spro ba'i ting
NK060(i)001:10628: nge 'dzin gyis snod dag par byed pa ni nye
NK060(i)001:10629: bsnyen/ nub mtha' ma ma gtogs pa'i phyed phan chod
NK060(i)001:10630: 'od zer dmar po 'phro 'du'i ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK060(i)001:10631: bcud dag par byed pa ni sgrub pa/
NK060(i)001:10632: nub mtha' ma la 'od zer mthing kha tshur bsdus
NK060(i)001:10633: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis rgyud dag par byed pa
NK060(i)001:10634: ni sgrub pa chen po ste/
NK060(i)001:10635: bar chad med pa'i lam pa tshogs sgrub pa'i dbang du'o //
NK060(i)001:10636: sbyor ba'i dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi ni/
NK060(i)001:10637: yum mtshan nyid dang ldan pa khrus gsum byas rgyan
NK060(i)001:10638: gsum btags chos gsum bshad nas sta gon du gnas
NK060(i)001:10639: pa ni bsnyen pa'i yan lag go //
NK060(i)001:10640: mkha' gsang brlabs sbyor ba'i brda bskul 'dod pa'i bstan
NK060(i)001:10641: bcos brgyad dam drug cu rtsa bzhis bde ba rgyas
NK060(i)001:10642: par byed pa ni nye bsnyen/
NK060(i)001:10643: phyag rgya bzhis rol pa ni sgrub pa/
NK060(i)001:10644: nyi zla rdo rje'i lces longs pa ni sgrub pa chen pos te/
NK060(i)001:10645: nub mtha' ma la mthong lam gyi ye shes chen
NK060(i)001:10646: po rgyud la skye bar byed pa dngos grub chen
NK060(i)001:10647: po yum gyi mkha' la blang ba'i dbang du'o //
NK060(i)001:10648: bsnyen sgrub bzhi rgyas par bstan pa la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:10651: sgrub pa thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10655: sngon du bya ba'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10657: nam mkha'i dkyil ltar sems nyid sgrib g.yogs med pa
NK060(i)001:10658: dwangs pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi gzhal yas khang nyi
NK060(i)001:10659: zla'i gdan dang bcas pa la rang byung gi ye
NK060(i)001:10660: shes 'khor 'das kyi chos la dbang sgyur ba'i rgyal
NK060(i)001:10661: po rdo rje sems dpa' stangs dpyal te yab yum
NK060(i)001:10662: bsgom mo // de bsgom pa la dgos pa ci yod ce na/
NK060(i)001:10663: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kun kyang lhag ma
NK060(i)001:10664: ma lus par ni bsgom par 'gyur ba'i dgos ched
NK060(i)001:10665: yod de/ rgyal ba thams cad gcig dang du ma'i mtha' las grol ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:10666: bya ba las rim gyi bsnyen pa'o //
NK060(i)001:10671: sngar le'u dgu par bshad pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi
NK060(i)001:10672: sgrub pa po gtso bo yab lnga dang gtso mo
NK060(i)001:10673: yum lnga zhal sbyor da bzhugs pa la/
NK060(i)001:10674: rang rang gi rigs chung gi rnal 'byor pa yab
NK060(i)001:10675: yum brgyad brgyad zhal sbyor gyis bskor ba'i dbus su
NK060(i)001:10676: tshom bu'i rnal 'byor pho mo lnga bcu'i sbyor pa'i
NK060(i)001:10678: steng gi cha shar gyi shar dang /
NK060(i)001:10679: 'og gi cha nub kyi nub tu rnal 'byor pa yab yum zhal sbyor bcu dang bcas pa ste/
NK060(i)001:10680: rnal 'byor pho mo bdun cu la tshom bu cha
NK060(i)001:10681: lnga'i lha rigs lnga yab yum gyis gtso byas pa
NK060(i)001:10682: lnga bcu tham pa bkod la/
NK060(i)001:10683: mthar gnas pa'i rnal 'byor pho mo cha bcu la
NK060(i)001:10684: khro bo yab bcu dang khro mo yum bcu bkod
NK060(i)001:10685: pas lha yab yum bdun cu tham pa dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:10686: gyii 'khor lo'i tshul du bsnyen pa'i dus su bris
NK060(i)001:10687: la/ nye bsnyen gyi dus su rnam par bsgom mo zhes 'brel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:10690: shar gyi phyogs su de bzhin rigs kyi tshom bu yab yum cha lnga ste ya bcu dang /
NK060(i)001:10691: dbus su rdo rje'i rigs ya bcu dang /
NK060(i)001:10692: rgyab tu pad+ma'i rigs ya bcu ste/
NK060(i)001:10693: de ltar sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor cha gsum gyi mthar/
NK060(i)001:10694: phyogs mtshams brgyad du khro bo yab brgyad dang khro
NK060(i)001:10695: mo yum brgyad zhal sbyor ba'i tshogs dang ldan pa'i
NK060(i)001:10696: gtso bo rigs gsum gyis byas pa tshom bu gsum
NK060(i)001:10697: pa'i lha bzhi bcu zhe drug gi tshogs rnams bsnyen
NK060(i)001:10699: nye bsnyen gyi dus su bsgom mo yang 'brel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:10702: rigs ji snyed pa thams cad kyi 'du tshul ni rigs lngar 'du ba yin te/
NK060(i)001:10703: de yang bsdus na thugs kyi sgyu 'phrul gyi lugs
NK060(i)001:10704: kyi rigs kyi gtso bo rdo rje'i rigs su 'dus
NK060(i)001:10705: pa yin no // de ci'i phyir zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10706: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs mkhyen pa'i
NK060(i)001:10707: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab brjod kyis ming lang
NK060(i)001:10708: ba yang / rigs bsdu na thugs ye shes lngar 'dus pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:10709: de yang thugs kyi mchog stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kho nar 'du ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:10710: des na rdo rjes sems dpa' yab yum rigs chung
NK060(i)001:10711: gi sems dpa' yab yum dang bcas pa zung lnga
NK060(i)001:10712: ya bcu ste khro bo'i tshogs yab bzhi yum bzhi
NK060(i)001:10713: dang ldan pa'i rigs gcig gis gtso byas pa tshom
NK060(i)001:10714: bu gcig pa'i lha bco brgyad kyi tshogs rnams bsnyen
NK060(i)001:10716: nye bsnyen gyi dus su bsgom mo bar 'brel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:10718: 'dir yang tshom bu rgyas 'bring bsdus pa gsum byung la/
NK060(i)001:10720: rdo rje rigs su thams cad dkyil //
NK060(i)001:10721: zhes pa la sogs pa tshom bu gsum pa sgrub pa'i thabs byung bas ldabs so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10723: gong ma ni bsnyen pa'i dus su bris nas nye
NK060(i)001:10724: bsnyen gyi dus su bsgom mo bar 'brel 'dogs pa
NK060(i)001:10725: yin la/ 'og ma ni dngos su bsgrub pa yin pas so //
NK060(i)001:10726: gnyis pa nye bsnyen dang sgrub pa thun mong du bstan pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:10728: rnal 'byor pas lha spyi'am so so bsgom pa/
NK060(i)001:10730: rnal 'byor pa thabs yab dang shes rab yum rnams kyi go rim bzhin/
NK060(i)001:10731: yab rnams kyis de bzhin gshegs pa rigs kyi yab lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:10732: yum rnams kyis rigs kyi yum du bsgom/
NK060(i)001:10733: 'khor yab rnams kyis rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab dang /
NK060(i)001:10734: yum rnams kyis rigs chung gi sems ma yum nyid du bsgom/
NK060(i)001:10736: lha rang rang gi phyag rgya dang ting nge 'dzin
NK060(i)001:10737: rnams ma 'dres par yang dag pa so sor gsal
NK060(i)001:10738: bar bsgom mo // tshom bu gsum la bsgrub pa'i thabs so //
NK060(i)001:10741: tshom bu gcig pa la bsgrub pa'i thabs/
NK060(i)001:10743: rdo rje'i rigs su rigs bzhi po thams cad 'dus
NK060(i)001:10744: pas na tshom bu gcig pa'i dkyil 'khor de bsgom
NK060(i)001:10745: pa'i tshul ni rtsa ba'i lha bco brgyad/
NK060(i)001:10746: yan lag gi lha dang bcas pa 'od zer 'phro
NK060(i)001:10747: ba gzi brjid 'bar ba rab tu bsgom par bya'o
NK060(i)001:10748: // yo byad la spyad pa'i thabs ni chags pa
NK060(i)001:10749: med pa'i tshul gyis spyad bya spyod byed spyod do
NK060(i)001:10750: ba gsum du 'dzin pa med pa'i ngang du bstim
NK060(i)001:10751: // par bya'o // de'i 'bras bu ni lta spyod
NK060(i)001:10752: gnyis su med par gyur nas phyag rgya chen po'i
NK060(i)001:10755: yo byad bzhi po lta spyod gnyis su med pas
NK060(i)001:10756: ni sku'i phyag rgya chen po'i rigs 'dzin thob bo
NK060(i)001:10757: // yo byad lnga pa nyi zla gnyis su med
NK060(i)001:10758: pas ni thabs dang shes rab kyi phyag rgya chen
NK060(i)001:10760: yo bya lnga pa nyi zla gnyis su med pas
NK060(i)001:10761: ni thabs dang shes rab kyi phyag rgya chen po'i
NK060(i)001:10762: dngos grub ste/ lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin 'grub bo zhes kyang bshad do //
NK060(i)001:10763: tshom bu gsum pa la bsgrub pa'i thabs/
NK060(i)001:10765: yang zhes pa tshom bu gcig pa la bkar ba ste/
NK060(i)001:10766: gsum pa bsgrub pa'i thabs ston par byas pas na
NK060(i)001:10767: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs su 'dus pa nyid
NK060(i)001:10768: de/ rgyal ba thams ca da lhag ma ma lus
NK060(i)001:10769: pa kun sku'i tshom bu dang gsung gi tshom bu
NK060(i)001:10770: dang thugs kyi tshom bu dang gsum mo //
NK060(i)001:10772: lha zhe drug gi dkyil 'khor yan lag gi lha
NK060(i)001:10773: dang bcas pa'i ting nge 'dzin gsal zhing 'bar ba'i
NK060(i)001:10774: 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phro bar bsgom par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:10775: yo byad la spyad pa'i thabs ni/
NK060(i)001:10776: spyod bya spyod byed gnyis su med pa mnyam pa
NK060(i)001:10777: nyid kyi dbyings 'dzin med kyi ngang du thim par
NK060(i)001:10779: rig 'dzin bzhi yi nang nas kyang dngos grub kyi
NK060(i)001:10780: mchog brnyes pa lhun grub rig 'dzin thob par 'gyur
NK060(i)001:10781: la/ de'i yon tan ni dkyil 'khor lhag ma ma
NK060(i)001:10782: lus pa yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa'i
NK060(i)001:10783: yon tan 'bar bar byed pa 'grub cing /
NK060(i)001:10784: des gzhan don byed tshul ni nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:10785: sdug bsngal brgyad dam bcu gcig sel bar mdzad pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10786: sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs dbyer mi phyed pa
NK060(i)001:10787: rdo rje'i rigs su skye ba'i gnas kho na yin
NK060(i)001:10788: no // tshom bu lnga pa la bsgrub pa'i thabs so //
NK060(i)001:10790: sngags ni yid skyob pa ste lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:10791: de rnams 'byor gyi mngon sum du 'chang ba dngos
NK060(i)001:10792: grub yang dag pa thob par byed pa ni thabs
NK060(i)001:10793: yab sum cu so lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:10794: shes rab yum sum cu so lnga po thams cad
NK060(i)001:10795: kyis lha bsgom par bya ba'i tshul ni dbus su
NK060(i)001:10796: dkyil 'khor cha lnga'i lha yab yum lnga bcu dang
NK060(i)001:10797: / sgo khyams la khro bo nyi shu'i phreng ba bsgom ste/
NK060(i)001:10798: lha yab yum bdun cu rnal 'byor pho mo bdun
NK060(i)001:10799: cus mtshan 'dzin dang chags pa med pa'i tshul gyis
NK060(i)001:10800: yan lag lhag pa'i lha dang bcas pa rnams ni
NK060(i)001:10801: 'od zer rnam pa mang po 'phro ba dang bcas
NK060(i)001:10803: yo byad la spyad pa'i thabs ni/
NK060(i)001:10804: spyad bya spyod byed gnyis su med par 'dzin med kyi ngang du bstim par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:10806: dngos grub kyi mchog lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi bsgrub bya'i snying po sku lnga 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:10807: 'o na tshom bu gcig pa'i skabs na/
NK060(i)001:10808: gnyis med gyur nas phyag rgya che //
NK060(i)001:10809: zhes gsungs pas 'bras bu phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK060(i)001:10814: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'grub //
NK060(i)001:10815: ces pa 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob par bshad 'dug pas ji ltar bshad pa bzhin thob bam mi thob/
NK060(i)001:10816: thob na tshogs sgrub nas thod rgal 'byung bar thal/
NK060(i)001:10821: lam mchog dbye sa gcig yin no //
NK060(i)001:10822: zhes pas zag med kyi lam gyi 'dus dang dbye sa mthong lam yin par bshad pas gsal lo //
NK060(i)001:10823: mi thob na thob par bshad pa'i lung dang 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10826: 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan dang gsum las/
NK060(i)001:10827: dang po thod rgal 'byung sa ni/
NK060(i)001:10828: zag bcas kyi lam gyi skabs su phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10829: spros bcas gnyis nas 'byung ba srid kyis/
NK060(i)001:10831: zag med kyi lam gyi skabs su tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK060(i)001:10832: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gnyis kyi sa nas 'byung ba srid kyis/
NK060(i)001:10834: gnyis pa thod rgal gyi go ba ni/
NK060(i)001:10836: grangs kyi 'og ma don gyi gong ma la sbyor ba zhig yin no //
NK060(i)001:10837: gsum pa thod rgal 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ni lam
NK060(i)001:10838: rim gyis pa gang zhig /lam bar nas bor du
NK060(i)001:10839: yod pa dang gcig /ngang gi blo che ba dang
NK060(i)001:10840: gnyis/ stong pa dang snying rje dbyer med bsgom pa'i
NK060(i)001:10841: lam pa yin pa dang gsum po gzhi gcig la
NK060(i)001:10842: gnyis/ 'tshogs na 'byung gis/ de las gzhan du ni mi 'byung ngo //
NK060(i)001:10843: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir stong pa chen po bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK060(i)001:10844: snying rje sgyu ma bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor gnyis ngang gis blo che ba cig yin gyis/
NK060(i)001:10845: lam phyag rgya gcig spros tshom bu tshogs sgrub dang gsum bar nas bor du yod kyang /
NK060(i)001:10846: stong nyid snying rje dbyer med bsgom pa'i lam pa ma yin pa'i phyir thod rgal mi 'byung la/
NK060(i)001:10847: zag bcas bar chad med pa'i lam tshom bu tshogs sgrub pa blo che shos dang /
NK060(i)001:10848: zag med mthar lam lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin
NK060(i)001:10849: blo che shos gnyis kyi ngang gis blo che ba
NK060(i)001:10850: yang yin/ stong pa dang snying rje dbyer med bsgom pa'i lam pa'ang yin kyang /
NK060(i)001:10851: lam bar nas bor du med pa'i phyir thod rgal mi 'byung ngo //
NK060(i)001:10852: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin ni stong par dang snying rje dbyer med bsgom pa'i lam pa yang yin/
NK060(i)001:10853: lam bar nas bar du yang sgom lam du mthar
NK060(i)001:10854: lam gnyis yod kyang ngang gi blo chung ba yin
NK060(i)001:10855: pa'i phyir thod rgal mi 'byung ngo //
NK060(i)001:10856: 'o na tshom bu gcig pa'i 'bras bur phya rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK060(i)001:10857: gsum pa'i 'bras bu lhun grub rig 'dzin dang /
NK060(i)001:10858: lnga pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas 'grub par bshad pa'i gong gi lung dang 'gal lo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10860: lung 'di dag ni zhor grub zhor sel gyi lung yin pas 'dir ltar go bar bya ste/
NK060(i)001:10861: de yang tshom bu gcig pa bsgrubs pas thob pa'i
NK060(i)001:10862: tshe dbang de phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la
NK060(i)001:10863: sbyor/ tshom bu gsum pa bsgrubs pas thob pa'i tshe dbang de lhun grub rig 'dzin la sbyor/
NK060(i)001:10864: tshom bu lnga pa bsgrubs pas thob pa'i tshe dbang
NK060(i)001:10865: de mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas la sbyor
NK060(i)001:10866: bar gsungs pa'i lung yin gyis/
NK060(i)001:10867: tshogs bsgrubs nas thod rgal 'byung ba'i lung ni ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:10868: tshe dbang nas thod rgal 'byung ba lung gis grub
NK060(i)001:10869: pas rnam smin nas thod rgal 'byung bar 'dod pa
NK060(i)001:10870: zhor la sel ba yin no //
NK060(i)001:10872: tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi 'bras bu rnam smin dang tshe dbang gnyis gang rung yin na/
NK060(i)001:10873: tshogs bsgrub pa'i dus su phyag rgya gcig gsum lnga pa'i 'bras bu sgom lam/
NK060(i)001:10875: sangs rgyas dang gsum bshad pa mi rigs so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10877: 'di nyid kyi le'u dgu pa las/
NK060(i)001:10878: byas te dad ldan rab zhugs na //
NK060(i)001:10882: sngon 'og min du zhugs pa dang mnyam par bstan te zhes/
NK060(i)001:10883: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du las dang po pa zhugs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10884: mthar lam pa skal pa mnyam par bshad pa yang mi rigs so byas pas/
NK060(i)001:10886: dus phyis 'grub pa la dgongs pa yin no zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10887: 'dir yang tshogs sgrub kyi dngos 'bras mthong lam yin kyang /
NK060(i)001:10888: tshom bu gcig pa yo byad bzhi la spyod pa'i dus su/
NK060(i)001:10889: lta spyod gnyis su med pa gyur pa'i rgyu 'bras phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK060(i)001:10890: +aa li k+aa li spyod pa'i dus su thabs shes
NK060(i)001:10891: rab gnyis su med par gyur pa'i rgyu 'bras lhun
NK060(i)001:10892: gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob pa la sogs pa
NK060(i)001:10893: yang / dus phyis tshe dbang rig 'dzin gyis thob
NK060(i)001:10894: pa la dgongs pa yin no zhes mgo mtshungs basgre'o
NK060(i)001:10895: yang / // 'o na tshe dab nga gi 'bras bu la bzang ngan byung bas/
NK060(i)001:10896: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i lha la bzang ngan yod par 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10897: tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha la bzang ngan med kyang /
NK060(i)001:10898: lam pa'i blo la che chung yod pas/
NK060(i)001:10899: rgyu tshogs bsgrub pa'i dus su lha mang nyung gi
NK060(i)001:10900: khyad par gyi 'bras bu lam gong ma la sbyor
NK060(i)001:10901: ba'i dus su mtho dman byung ba yin no //
NK060(i)001:10902: 'o na tshom bu gcig gsum lngar bsgrubs pa'i rnam
NK060(i)001:10903: smin rig 'dzin la yang blo rab 'bring tha ma
NK060(i)001:10904: gsum yod par thal zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10906: 'o na rnam smin nas kyang thod rgal 'byung bar thal zhe na/
