NK060(i)001:10908: rnam smin rig 'dzin gyi dngos 'bras phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin kho na las mi thob kyang /
NK060(i)001:10909: rgyu 'bras lam gong ma la sbyor ba dus myur bul yod pas khyad par shin tu che'o //
NK060(i)001:10910: zhes zur thams cad mkhyen pa gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:10912: lam rang sa nas blo chen mthar lam ma yin pa kun nas thod rgal 'byung gsung lo //
NK060(i)001:10913: rgya gab gong pa na re/
NK060(i)001:10914: tshogs sgrub mtshan nyid pa blo che ba nas thod rgal 'byung ba mi skyon te/
NK060(i)001:10916: nus pa thob dang ma thob pa'i //
NK060(i)001:10917: mthong lam gnyis su 'gyur ba yin //
NK060(i)001:10918: zhes gsungs pas bar chad med pa'i lam pa blo
NK060(i)001:10919: che shos kyis zag bcas su chos nyid kyi bden
NK060(i)001:10920: pa mthong na/ zag med kyi mthong lam rnam smin dang /
NK060(i)001:10921: tshe dbang gnyis ka la ltos mi dgos pa'ang yod gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:10922: 'khor bo'i go tshad la lam chung gi lung ni
NK060(i)001:10923: nus pa ma thob pa'i mthong lam rnam par smin
NK060(i)001:10924: pa'i rig 'dzin yin par go ste/
NK060(i)001:10925: lus rang dbang med par 'dor ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:10926: de ya nga lam rim las/
NK060(i)001:10927: stobs chung rkyen smon zhan pa'i phyir //
NK060(i)001:10928: rnam rtog 'byung ba'i lhag lus bzhag /ces gsungs pas mngon no //
NK060(i)001:10929: nus pa thob pa'i mthong lam ni tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin te/
NK060(i)001:10930: rdo rje'i lus su gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:10932: rdo rje'i lus gyur tshe yi rigs //
NK060(i)001:10933: mthong ba'i chos la mya ngan 'da' //
NK060(i)001:10934: lus ma bor bar rgyal ba'i sa //
NK060(i)001:10937: yang tshom bu dang dkyil 'khor gyi khyad par gang yin zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10938: bsgom bya lha'i khyad par ni/
NK060(i)001:10939: gtso bo'i ngos nas bzhag pa tshom bu ste/
NK060(i)001:10940: gtso bor rigs gcig gis byas pa tshom bu gcig pa/
NK060(i)001:10941: gtso bo rigs gsum gyis byas pa tshom bu gsum pa/
NK060(i)001:10942: gtso bo rigs lngas byas pa tshom bu lnga pa ste/
NK060(i)001:10943: de dag kyang gtso 'khor lha grangs dang gral nges pa can yin no //
NK060(i)001:10944: lha rnams grangs byung rdzogs kyi ngos nas gzhag pa dkyil 'khor te/
NK060(i)001:10945: lha grangs dang gral ma nges pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:10946: yang rigs 'gyur kyang ye shes mi 'gyur ba tshom bu dang /
NK060(i)001:10947: rigs dang ye shes gnyis ka 'gyur ba dkyil 'khor du bzhed pa'ang yod de/
NK060(i)001:10948: de'i go don ni sku'i sgyu 'phrul gyi skabs su dbus kyi gtso bo rnam snang gis byed la/
NK060(i)001:10949: gsung gi sgyu 'phrul gyi skabs su dbus kyi gtso
NK060(i)001:10950: bo mthas yas kyis byed pa la sogs pa ni
NK060(i)001:10952: rigs ji ltar 'gyur yang dbus kyi gtso bo'i thugs
NK060(i)001:10953: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes yin pa la sogs
NK060(i)001:10954: pa ni rigs 'gyur yang ye shes mi 'gyur ba
NK060(i)001:10955: zhes bya la/ dbus kyi gtso bo rnam snang gis
NK060(i)001:10956: byed na de'i thugs me long lta bu'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:10957: yin pa la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:10958: dbus kyi gtso bo mtha' yas kyis byed na de'i
NK060(i)001:10959: thugs so sor rtog pa'i ye shes yin pa la
NK060(i)001:10960: sogs pa ni rigs dang ye shes gnyis ka 'gyur
NK060(i)001:10961: ba zhes bya'o // de'i phyir na/
NK060(i)001:10962: thugs kyi sgyu 'phrul gyi skabs 'dir tshom bu gcig
NK060(i)001:10963: gsum lnga pa kun gyi gtso bo rdo rje'i rigs
NK060(i)001:10964: yin pa bzhin du/ sku'i sgyu 'phrul gyi skabs su
NK060(i)001:10965: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa kun gyi gtso bo
NK060(i)001:10966: de bzhin rigs yin pa la sogs pa bzhed pa'ang
NK060(i)001:10967: yin pa bzhin du/ yod do // sgom byed rnal 'byor pa'i khyad par ni/
NK060(i)001:10968: lha dang rnal 'byor pa brang sprod du bsgom pa tshom bu yin la/
NK060(i)001:10969: rnal 'byor pa pho mo gang rung zhig gis kyang
NK060(i)001:10970: lha'i dkyil 'khor byung rdzogs su bsgom pa ni dkyil
NK060(i)001:10971: 'khor ro // yang na pho mo zung du sbrel ba'i sgo nas bsgrub pa ni tshom bu/
NK060(i)001:10972: pho rkyang mo rkyang gis bsgrub tu rung ba ni dkyil 'khor ro zhes bzhed pa'ang yod do //
NK060(i)001:10973: 'o na tshom bu tshogs sgrub pa 'di zag bcas yin nam zag med yin/
NK060(i)001:10974: ldog bcas yin nam ldog med yin zhe na/
NK060(i)001:10975: spyir gyi zag ldog yod med kyi mu bzhi yod pa las/
NK060(i)001:10976: zag ldog gnyis ka yod pa'i lam pa ni stong pa chen po/
NK060(i)001:10979: phyag rgya spros bcas dang bzhi te/
NK060(i)001:10981: de phyir lam bzhir ldog zag yod //
NK060(i)001:10983: zag pa yod la ldog pa med pa'i lam pa ni tshom bu tshogs sgrub bo //
NK060(i)001:10984: zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i lam pa ni rigs 'dzin bzhi'o //
NK060(i)001:10985: zag pa med la ldog pa yod pa'i lam pa
NK060(i)001:10986: ni theg pa chung ngu'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK060(i)001:10987: zag med dgra bcom pa thob par gang zhig /sngags
NK060(i)001:10988: kyi theg pa la zhugs nas tshogs sbyor gyi lam
NK060(i)001:10990: 'on kyang ldog bcas 'di rnams srid pa la dgongs kyi khyab pa ni med do //
NK060(i)001:10992: nyon yid mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su ma
NK060(i)001:10993: log pa de srid du ldog bcas kyi lam du
NK060(i)001:10995: ji srid sa brgyad ma non par //
NK060(i)001:10996: de srid theg pa dman pas 'jig /ces gsungs so zhes na/
NK060(i)001:10997: lung des ma dag sa bdun gyi byang chub sems dpa' sems bskyed nyams par dogs pa'i lung yin gyi/
NK060(i)001:10998: lam pa de 'khor bar phyir ldog pa'i lung ni ma yin no //
NK060(i)001:10999: yang zag bcas su chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid mthong ngam mi mthong zhe na/
NK060(i)001:11000: chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid zag bcas su mi mthong la/
NK060(i)001:11001: zag med kyis mthong zin pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:11002: zag pa 'dzad pa dang chos nyid rang mtsham mthong ba dus gcig go //
NK060(i)001:11003: des na zag bcas kyi bsam gtan gyis chos nyid
NK060(i)001:11004: kyi don mthong bar bshad pa'i lung rnams mi spyi'i
NK060(i)001:11005: rnam par mthong ba la dgongs pa yin gyis/
NK060(i)001:11006: rang gi mtshan nyid mthong ba la dgongs pa ma yin no //
NK060(i)001:11007: de yang mdo don bsdus las/
NK060(i)001:11008: de dag zag bcas bsam gtan te //
NK060(i)001:11009: gnyis med yul bral de mthong min //
NK060(i)001:11013: gsum pa bden gnyis rang mtshan du //
NK060(i)001:11014: mgo mthong gnyis med bzod ma thob //
NK060(i)001:11015: ces pa'i lung zag bcas su chos nyid rang mtshan mthong ba'i lung du 'dod kyang /
NK060(i)001:11016: ma mthong ba'i lung yin te/
NK060(i)001:11017: mgo mthong zhes pa'i tshig gis gsal lo //
NK060(i)001:11018: de ka rang mtshan mthong ba'i lung yin zer na/
NK060(i)001:11019: 'o na gyang gi phag na mi yod pa'i mgo
NK060(i)001:11020: bo mthong bas kyang mi de'i rang mtshan mthong bar
NK060(i)001:11023: 'dod par nus pa ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:11024: mi de'i gos dang lus kyi rnam pa dang sha
NK060(i)001:11025: mtshan dang gtam smra lugs dang blo gros che chung
NK060(i)001:11026: la sogs pa gang yang ma mthong ba tshad mas
NK060(i)001:11027: gsal lo // yang lam gong 'og la chos nyid gsal mi gsal kyi khyad par yod dam med/
NK060(i)001:11028: yod na zag bcas su chos nyid rang mtshan ma mthong bar thal //
NK060(i)001:11029: 'dod na skabs 'grel gyi lung gis gsal lo //
NK060(i)001:11030: gsal mi gsal med na lam rim las/
NK060(i)001:11031: gsal ba'i bye brag rim pas 'gro //
NK060(i)001:11033: 'di la gtsang pa byi ston na re/
NK060(i)001:11035: chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:11036: gnas yun ring thung yod de/
NK060(i)001:11037: lam gong ma gong mar bgrod pa'i dus na/
NK060(i)001:11038: brtan pa je thob je thob song ba yin no gsung /
NK060(i)001:11039: rje drings pa nye'u ston na re/
NK060(i)001:11040: lam gyi khyad par gsal mi gsal yin gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:11041: rgya gab gong pa na re/
NK060(i)001:11042: gsal mi gsal dang yun ring thung gnyis ka yod de/
NK060(i)001:11043: snga ma ni lam rim las/
NK060(i)001:11044: gsal ba'i bye brag rim pas 'gro //
NK060(i)001:11046: phyi ma ni spyi mdo las/
NK060(i)001:11047: skad cig dang thang cig dang yud tsam dang de
NK060(i)001:11048: ma thag pa dang thun phyed dang thun dang zhes
NK060(i)001:11049: pa la sogs pa gsungs pas gsal lo //
NK060(i)001:11051: bzhed pa 'di dag lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin shan ma phyed pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:11052: chos nyid spyi'i rnam pa mthong ba ni lta ba don spyi yin la/
NK060(i)001:11053: rang gi mtshan nyid mthong ba ni lta ba rang mtshan yin te/
NK060(i)001:11054: de ltar lta ba'i ngos nas gsal mi gsal dang yun ring thung med la/
NK060(i)001:11055: de dag yod pa'i lung rnams ni mthong don bsgom
NK060(i)001:11056: pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gsal mi gsal dang yun
NK060(i)001:11057: ring thung gi lung yin no //
NK060(i)001:11058: 'o na ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs kyi lta sgom tha dad par thal/
NK060(i)001:11059: lta ba gsal mi gsal dang yun ring thung med la/
NK060(i)001:11060: sgom pa la yod pa'i phyir ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:11061: de tshod du lam dang 'bras bu'ang tha dad par thal/
NK060(i)001:11062: thob bya 'bras bu nas thob byed lam yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:11066: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yis //
NK060(i)001:11067: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK060(i)001:11069: gsum pa bsgrub pa chen po'o //
NK060(i)001:11071: yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i thabs dang /
NK060(i)001:11075: yo byad bzhi la spyad pa'i thabs/
NK060(i)001:11077: lhab lhub dar gyi chos gos lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:11078: zhing glang stag lpags la sogs pa ste zhi khro'i gos dang /
NK060(i)001:11079: sil khrol rin po che'i rgyan brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:11080: thal chen khrag zhag sbrul dang thod pa skam rlon
NK060(i)001:11081: la sogs pa ste zhi khro'i rgyan gyi yod byad
NK060(i)001:11082: dang / gzhan yang bzang dang btung ba'i glu dang
NK060(i)001:11083: sgra tshigs gi rigs so so'i bro gar 'du 'phro'i
NK060(i)001:11084: yo byad kyi tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyi mang
NK060(i)001:11085: ba'i tshad ni sprin phung tsam la rang rig pa'i
NK060(i)001:11086: ye shes yi ge h+aum gi rang bzhin du shes
NK060(i)001:11087: pas yo byad rnams la spyod cing /
NK060(i)001:11088: ma chags pa 'i tshul gyis rab tu spyad na
NK060(i)001:11089: ngo mtshar ba'i 'bras bu tshogs chen gnyis 'byung ba'i
NK060(i)001:11090: dkyil 'khor thams cad bdag nyid chen po'i mchod pas
NK060(i)001:11091: mnyes pa'o // yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i thabs so //
NK060(i)001:11096: sbyor sgrol la rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:11101: 'di la lo grangs kyi sgo nas dbye na lo bcu gnyis ma mtshan dang ldan pa lha mo/
NK060(i)001:11103: nyi shu ma rigs ngan mo/
NK060(i)001:11105: rtsa dung can ma yod pa lha mo/
NK060(i)001:11107: zhar ma can rigs ngan mo/
NK060(i)001:11108: byang sems kyi sgo nas dbye na/
NK060(i)001:11109: nyi zla gnyis ka 'dzag pa lha mo/
NK060(i)001:11112: sbyor thabs kyi sgo nas dbye na/
NK060(i)001:11113: bdag gzhan gnyis ka bde ba'i sbyor thabs shes pa ni lha mo/
NK060(i)001:11115: bdag bde tsam rigs ngan mo/
NK060(i)001:11116: yang na lha mo na lha mo dngos/
NK060(i)001:11117: klu mo na klu mo dngos te/
NK060(i)001:11118: sngags dang ting nge 'dzin gyis dngos su dgug pa'am/
NK060(i)001:11119: de ma nus na rigs ngan mo ste mi'i bu mo yang rung bas/
NK060(i)001:11120: slob dpon nus pa chung na phyag rgya bzang ngan dbye ste/
NK060(i)001:11122: yang nus pa che na mi dbye ste/
NK060(i)001:11123: ngan yang skyon gyis gnod mi nus pa'i phyir gang rnyed bsten par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:11124: de yang yum mtshan ldan gyi gsang ba'i pad+ma'i nang
NK060(i)001:11125: du tshom bu gang yin gyi dkyil 'khor rten dang
NK060(i)001:11126: brten par bcas pa bskyed la/
NK060(i)001:11127: bde ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor yab kyi byang chub
NK060(i)001:11128: kyi sems spros zhing sangs rgyas sprin tshogs ma lus
NK060(i)001:11129: pa tshom bu gang yin gyi dkyil 'khor du rigs
NK060(i)001:11130: bsdus pa de la dgyes pa chen po'i mchod pa
NK060(i)001:11131: phul bas/ bdag dang sangs rgyas dang sems can thams
NK060(i)001:11132: cad rang rig pa'i ngo bor mnyam pa'i phyir yab
NK060(i)001:11133: yum rol pa'i bde bas bdag mchod pas rgyal ba
NK060(i)001:11134: mnyes te 'gro ba tshim pa ni mchog gi sbyin
NK060(i)001:11135: phul bas/ pa yin pas na/ bdag dang rgyal ba
NK060(i)001:11136: sems can gsum gnyis su med pa'i bde ba chen
NK060(i)001:11138: dngos grub chen po yum gyi mkha' la blang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:11140: bde ba'i ye shes chen po sgrub pa'i thabs yab
NK060(i)001:11141: yum gnyis su med pa'i rol pa las byung ba'i
NK060(i)001:11142: thig le nyi zla gnyis 'dres yon tan thams cad
NK060(i)001:11143: kyi bcud 'dus pa'i snying po de dkyil 'khor thams
NK060(i)001:11144: cad kyi bdag nyid ye shes lngar rang gsal bar
NK060(i)001:11145: byed pa'i rten yin pas na de blang bar bya'o
NK060(i)001:11146: // su yis na bar chad med pa'i lam pas //
NK060(i)001:11147: dus nam gyi tshe na tshogs sgrub kyi nub mtha' ma'i tho rangs kyi dus su/
NK060(i)001:11148: gang nas blang na yum gyi mkha' nas/
NK060(i)001:11149: gang gis blang na rdo rje'i lce yis te gsang ba'i rdo rje nyid do //
NK060(i)001:11150: yang na lce rdo rje rtse lnga par bsgoms pa de yis so //
NK060(i)001:11151: tshul ji ltar na bung ba me tog 'jib pa'i tshul gyis blang ngo //
NK060(i)001:11152: dgos ched ci'i phyir blang na/
NK060(i)001:11153: dngos grub gnyis bde blag tu thob pa'i phyir du'o //
NK060(i)001:11154: gang zhe na thun mong gi dngos grub nam mkha'
NK060(i)001:11155: la bya bzhin du 'gro zhing lha'i bu mor spyod
NK060(i)001:11156: pa dang / kha dog gsal ba dang /
NK060(i)001:11158: tshe lo grangs med pa thub pa la sogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:11159: sogs khong nas sa la byi ba bzhin du 'dzul
NK060(i)001:11160: nas klu'i bu mo la spyod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:11161: gzhan yang mngon par shes pa dang rdzu 'phrul du ma 'thob bo //
NK060(i)001:11162: mchog gi dngos grub ni yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che las ma g.yos bzhin du/
NK060(i)001:11163: dgos 'dod char bzhin du 'byung bas na sprin gyi tshogs te/
NK060(i)001:11164: dpe de dang 'dra ba'i rigs thams cad kyi bdag
NK060(i)001:11165: po rgyal ba drug pa yang thob par 'gyur ro
NK060(i)001:11166: // yang na snga ma gsang ba'i rdo rjes blangs
NK060(i)001:11167: pa'i yon tan ni yid bzhin gyi sprin gyi bdag
NK060(i)001:11168: po mchog gi dngos grub thob par 'gyur la/
NK060(i)001:11169: phyi ma lce rdo rje rtse lngar bsgoms nas blangs
NK060(i)001:11170: pa'i yon tan nam mkha' 'gro gsal 'bar tshe la
NK060(i)001:11171: sogs pa thun mong gi dngos grub thob par 'gyur
NK060(i)001:11174: de yang bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pa ni gnyis yin te/
NK060(i)001:11175: bkra shis dag pa'i zhing dang /
NK060(i)001:11176: thugs rjes bzung ba'i zhing ngo //
NK060(i)001:11177: snga ma ni bram ze skye ba bdun pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:11178: de'i sha rus la sogs pa dngos grub kyi rdzas khyad par can yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK060(i)001:11179: phyi ma ni gsal bkra las/
NK060(i)001:11180: dkon cog slob dpon sku dgra gnyis //
NK060(i)001:11181: dam nyams lon dang 'khu ba dang //
NK060(i)001:11183: dam dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can //
NK060(i)001:11184: ngan song gsum dang bcu po ni //
NK060(i)001:11185: rnal 'byor chen pos rtag tu bsgral //
NK060(i)001:11187: bcu po de dag ni shin tu snying rje bas na phan gdags pa'i phyir du'o //
NK060(i)001:11188: de yang mchog ni mi brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:11189: mchog phran ni ngan song gsum mo //
NK060(i)001:11190: yang na mchog gi bsgral bya gang yin te/
NK060(i)001:11191: mchog phran tsa ra dang shel chen la bkug nas sgrol zhes bzhed pa yang yod do //
NK060(i)001:11192: mdor na bsgral bya bcu gcig po de rnams bdag gzhan chos gsum gyi don du bsgral bar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:11193: su yis na bar chad med pa'i lam pas/
NK060(i)001:11194: dus nam gyi tshe na tshogs sgrub kyi nub mtha' ma'i nam gung gi dus/
NK060(i)001:11195: thabs gang gis na mngon du phyung ba'i sgrol ba'i thabs kyis te/
NK060(i)001:11196: e ram gyis drag po'i dkyil 'khor bskyed la nyi
NK060(i)001:11197: zla'i gdan gyi steng du sgrol ba'i thabs la mkhas
NK060(i)001:11198: pa bdag nyid gying dang bcas pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK060(i)001:11199: la ma yengs pas bsgral bya sngags dang ting nge
NK060(i)001:11200: 'dzin gyis nus pas dngos su bkug la/
NK060(i)001:11201: grub gsum gyi steng du mgo lho nub dang rkang
NK060(i)001:11202: pa byang shar te 'khor ba ru ldog gi tshul
NK060(i)001:11203: du gan rkyal du bsgyel ba'i snying gar rdo rjes
NK060(i)001:11205: tshul ji ltar na nga rgyal rnam pa lnga dang ldan pa'i tshul gyis te/
NK060(i)001:11207: bsgral bya ru dra te bdag 'dzin gsum/
NK060(i)001:11210: lag sor dpa' bo 'bru lngar nga rgyal ba'i tshul gyis lag gi 'du byed kyis bsgral lo //
NK060(i)001:11211: sgrol ba'i ting nge 'dzin gang bsgom na/
NK060(i)001:11212: gri 'jam dpal rnon por gsal ba des/
NK060(i)001:11213: bsgral bya'i byang khog shags kyis gshags pas/
NK060(i)001:11214: ma rig pa dbugs kyi rgya bral bar bsgom/
NK060(i)001:11215: lag sor dpa' bo 'bru lnga gsal ba des/
NK060(i)001:11216: snying tshir gyis bzung bas snying gi rtsa chen bzhi
NK060(i)001:11217: la gnas pa'i sa bon zung gsum gnyid dang bcas
NK060(i)001:11218: pa dpa' bo 'bru lnga'i 'od zer gyis bsregs nas/
NK060(i)001:11219: yig 'bru h+aum drug tu gyur pas 'khor bar skye
NK060(i)001:11220: ba'i sa bon drug bag chags dang bcas pa rnam
NK060(i)001:11221: par dag cing / h+aum drug po de yang thugs
NK060(i)001:11222: rang rig pa'i ye shes gcig las ma 'das pas
NK060(i)001:11223: na h+aum dkar la rtsa dmar ba gcig tu gyur
NK060(i)001:11224: par dag cing / pa bsgom te/ de ni shes pa chos nyid du bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:11225: de nas h+aum dkar po de sgrol byed rnal 'byor pa'i shangs bug g.yon gyi rngubs pas/
NK060(i)001:11226: klad pa'i rgyas su thim pas sku'i dbyibs brgyud srog dag pa'i lam nas byung /
NK060(i)001:11227: sgal tshigs kyi rta brgyud de gsang ba rdo rje'i
NK060(i)001:11228: lam nas yum gyi mkha' la bab pas gsang ba'i
NK060(i)001:11229: dbyings su thim par bsgom mo //
NK060(i)001:11230: de ni shes pa yum gyi mkha' la bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:11231: de nas yum gyi mkha'i gsung yig 'bru h+aum de yongs su gyur pa las/
NK060(i)001:11232: thugs phyag rgya rdo rje 'od 'bar ba gcig tu gyur/
NK060(i)001:11233: de yang yongs su gyur pa las/
NK060(i)001:11234: sku yongs su rdzogs pa rdo rje sems dpa'i skur gyur te/
NK060(i)001:11235: de yang nyon mongs pa lnga ma spangs gnas su
NK060(i)001:11236: dag pa 'khor 'das gnyis med du longs spyod pas
NK060(i)001:11237: na/ longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mtshan dpe dang ldan pa 'od zer 'phro bas rab tu brjid pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11238: de'i gtsug tu 'khor ba las rnam par rgyal ba
NK060(i)001:11239: mtshon pa rigs kyi bdag po mi bskyod pa tshon
NK060(i)001:11241: de ni rdo rje sems dpa' mtshan yongs su rdzogs pa'i sa la bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:11242: rdo rje sems dpa' de yang zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:11243: gyi steng na gnas pa rlung gi dkyil 'khor gyis
NK060(i)001:11244: bteg nas/ e yam s+pha ra na phata ces 'og min gyi gnas su 'phangs par bsgom mo //
NK060(i)001:11245: de ni shes pa 'og min du bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:11246: de nas sha khrag rus pa'i tshogs rnams skos btab nas/
NK060(i)001:11247: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs la mchod par phul bas mnyes par bsgom mo //
NK060(i)001:11248: de ni phung po dur khrod du bsgral ba bzhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:11249: dgos ched gang gi phyir bsgral na/
NK060(i)001:11250: bdag la sgrib pa mi gsog cing gzhan la sdug bsngal mi bskyed pas na ngo mtshar zhing /
NK060(i)001:11251: gnas ngan len gyi 'gro ba'i rgyu bstan pa'i spyi dgra la sogs pa bdun dang /
NK060(i)001:11252: 'bras bu ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal las thar ba'i thabs khyad par can yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:11253: sbyor sgrol la rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:11255: gong gi ga na sbyor ba dang /
NK060(i)001:11256: ta na sgrol ba'i tshul de dag la/
NK060(i)001:11258: sbyor ba'i rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu ro myags kyi 'dam gyi dmyal ba dang /
NK060(i)001:11259: rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu mngal gyi srin bur skye bar bshad/
NK060(i)001:11260: sgrol ba'i rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu yang shi yang sos kyi dmyal ba dang /
NK060(i)001:11261: rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu las kyi srin bur skye bar bshad pas/
NK060(i)001:11262: 'di dag log pa lam du 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:11264: nyon mongs pas kun nas bslangs nas 'dod chags tha mal du spyad pa dang /
NK060(i)001:11265: sems can gyi srog la 'tshe ba byas pa dang /
NK060(i)001:11266: byed du bcug na 'bras bu de ltar yin mod/
NK060(i)001:11267: 'dir gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba ye gdod ma
NK060(i)001:11268: nas skye ba med pa don dam pa'i bden pa
NK060(i)001:11269: de nyid rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta bas de
NK060(i)001:11270: bzhin nyid kho nar rtogs shing /
NK060(i)001:11271: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin gyis nyams su blangs pas/
NK060(i)001:11272: kun rdzob tu sgyu mar snang ba 'di yang dpe tho yor la mir 'dzin pa grol ba bzhin/
NK060(i)001:11273: snang ba thams cad mig yor gyi tshul du shes
NK060(i)001:11274: nas dngos grub gnyis kyi don du spyod pa dang
NK060(i)001:11275: sgrol ba'i bya ba kun byas kyang tha mal pa'i
NK060(i)001:11276: sbyor sgrol rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med do
NK060(i)001:11277: // gnyis pa yo byad la spyad pa'ii dngos grub bo //
NK060(i)001:11282: spyir chos nyid rang bzhin gyi mngon du byed pa lam gyi/
NK060(i)001:11283: lhun gyis grub pa 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor dang gsum las/
NK060(i)001:11284: 'dir ye shes dang phyag rgya mi 'byed pa ni lam gyi rnal 'byor ro //
NK060(i)001:11285: sngags ni yid skyob pa dang byin gyis rlob pa'i phyir lha bsgom pa ste/
NK060(i)001:11286: de 'chang ba ni rnal 'byor gyi mngon sum dang /
NK060(i)001:11287: shin tu 'chang ba ni rang rig pa'i mngon sum gyis so //
NK060(i)001:11288: bcangs pa la dgos pa ci yod ce na/
NK060(i)001:11289: thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub gnyis 'thob bo //
NK060(i)001:11290: de nas gzhi gang las byung zhe na/
NK060(i)001:11291: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sku dang ye shes
NK060(i)001:11292: su mnyam par rdzogs pa ni lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK060(i)001:11293: lta ba/ de nyid kyi ngang la gnas shing ma yengs pa ni bsgom du med pa'i sgom la/
NK060(i)001:11294: blang dor dang bral ba'i spyod pa gang yang ma
NK060(i)001:11295: bkag pas cig la yang thog pa med pa ni
NK060(i)001:11296: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa'i khyad par te/
NK060(i)001:11297: de ltar lta sgom spyod gsum po thams cad ye
NK060(i)001:11298: gdod ma nas dbyer med du rtogs pa mchog dang
NK060(i)001:11299: thun mong gi dngos grub 'byung ba ni 'bras bu'o
NK060(i)001:11300: // dngos grub blang ba'i thabs so //
NK060(i)001:11302: yan lag lnga dang dbang po lnga dang rnam shes
NK060(i)001:11303: lnga po kun rang rig pa'i nyid rang snang bar
NK060(i)001:11304: shes pas ni de dag gi rnam pa ye shes
NK060(i)001:11305: lnga'i ngo bor smin pa ste de mtshon byed yi
NK060(i)001:11307: des mtshon pa'i sku dang ye shes lnga ma 'gags
NK060(i)001:11308: pa'i rtsal yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu rigs lnga
NK060(i)001:11309: la sogs pa lha yab kyi dkyil 'khor nyid du
NK060(i)001:11310: bsgom pa'am/ yang zhi ba las bkar bas na khros pa khro bo rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor bsgom mo //
NK060(i)001:11315: reg la sogs pa yul gyi rnam pa kun dbyings
NK060(i)001:11316: lnga'i ngo bor smin pa ste de mtshon pa yi
NK060(i)001:11317: ge m+aum du shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:11318: des mtshon pa'i dbyings lnga ma 'gags pa'i rtsal lha yum gyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom mo //
NK060(i)001:11319: yang zhes pa zhi ba las bkar bas na khro bo yum lnga'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom mo //
NK060(i)001:11322: rigs kyi khro bo yab lnga khroo mo yum lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:11323: bcu'i tshogs chen pos gtso byas pa'i 'khor gnas yul sgo ma nyi shu ste/
NK060(i)001:11325: phyag brnyan sing ha ma brgyad/
NK060(i)001:11326: bka' nyan sgo ma bzhi rnams sprul pa yang sprul gyi tshogs dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:11327: gzhan yang las ci bgyi zhes rang rang stan dang
NK060(i)001:11328: lag char chas pa'i dbang mo nyer brgyad la sogs
NK060(i)001:11329: pa'i sogs khongs nas khro bo khro mo nyi shu
NK060(i)001:11330: ste/ bdun cu don brgyad kyi tshogs rnams dang res
NK060(i)001:11331: su mthun pa'i rnal 'byor rnams kyis khro bo'i tshogs
NK060(i)001:11332: bsgrubs na dngos grub gnyis sam/
NK060(i)001:11333: las bzhi la sogs pa ji ltar 'dod pa'i 'bras bu rnams rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:11334: spyi don gsum pa 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid la bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:11335: yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i 'bras bu/
NK060(i)001:11336: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi cha lugs/
NK060(i)001:11338: de dag gi yon tan bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11341: bro gar 'du 'phro'i yo byad la spyad pa'i 'bras bu/
NK060(i)001:11343: tshom bu gsum gyi lha yab yum zung du 'brel ba ni sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste/
NK060(i)001:11344: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal bar rdzogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:11345: tshom bu gsum po gang rang gi lha'i dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:11346: bsgom pas brtan pa'i tshad gsal ba yul gyis mi
NK060(i)001:11347: 'phrogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin thob pa des yan lag
NK060(i)001:11351: 'od zer sprul pa'i 'du 'phro sna tshogs dang bcas pa'i sgo nas/
NK060(i)001:11352: sgo gsum sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya'i ngang las mi 'da' ba yis sa la 'dzul lam/
NK060(i)001:11353: yang na nam mkhar 'gro bas klu dang lha'i bu mo la sogs pa la spyod cing /
NK060(i)001:11354: de dag thams cad bran du 'khol bar 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:11355: klu tshig sgra'i yo byad kyi 'bras bu/
NK060(i)001:11357: ngag gi sgo nas glu tshig dang sgra'i yo byad
NK060(i)001:11358: la sogs pa sgo gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi
NK060(i)001:11359: phyag rgya las mi 'da' ba yis gdul bya so
NK060(i)001:11360: so la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dngos grub
NK060(i)001:11362: rgyan dang bgo ba'i yo byad kyi 'bras bu/
NK060(i)001:11364: zhi ba'i rgyan chas bcu gsum dang /
NK060(i)001:11365: khro bo'i ko rlon la sogs pa bgo ba'i yo
NK060(i)001:11366: byad dang yang ldan pas sgo gsum lha'i sku gsung
NK060(i)001:11367: thugs kyi phyag rgya yis 'bar ba'i rgyal po sus
NK060(i)001:11368: kyang thub pa med pa 'grub par 'gyur te dpung
NK060(i)001:11369: bzhi'i dmag gis kyang mi tshugs so //
NK060(i)001:11370: bza' dang btung ba'i yo byad kyi 'bras bu/
NK060(i)001:11372: bza' ba dang btung ba'i yo byad/
NK060(i)001:11373: sgo gsum sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyas longs spyod na ni/
NK060(i)001:11374: gdul bya rnams la ji ltar bsam pa yid bzhin
NK060(i)001:11375: du 'byung ba'i sku rin po che mtshon shel du
NK060(i)001:11377: bdud rtsi'i bcud zad pa med pas 'gro ba thams cad tshim par byed pa 'grub bo //
NK060(i)001:11378: +aa li k+aa li'i yo byad kyi 'bras bu'o //
NK060(i)001:11381: k+aa li sgrol ba'i yo byad la sgo gsum sku
NK060(i)001:11382: gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya las mi 'da' ba yis
NK060(i)001:11383: thun mong gi dngos grub thams cad 'grub par 'gyur
NK060(i)001:11384: ro // gnyis pa tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi cha lugs/
NK060(i)001:11387: 'dod khams kyi lha rigs drug dang /
NK060(i)001:11388: gzugs khams kyi lha tshangs pa'i cha lugs kyi skye
NK060(i)001:11389: ba rnam par dag pa 'dzin mod kyang lha mi
NK060(i)001:11390: gzhan dang khyad par che ste/
NK060(i)001:11391: skye ba rang dbang can yin pas so //
NK060(i)001:11392: khyad par du rgyu'i theg pa'i mthong lam dang /
NK060(i)001:11393: mthong lam tsam du skal ba mnyam yang dgongs pa
NK060(i)001:11394: sa brgyad pa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK060(i)001:11395: dang mnyam par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK060(i)001:11396: des mtshon nas rgyu'i theg pa'i sa brgyad pa dang
NK060(i)001:11397: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gnyis sgom lam tsam
NK060(i)001:11399: dgongs pa rgyu'i mthar lam dang mnyam mo //
NK060(i)001:11400: rgyu'i theg pa'i sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK060(i)001:11401: lhun grub rig 'dzin gnyis mthar lam tsam du skal
NK060(i)001:11402: ba mnyam yang dgongs pa kun tu 'od dang mnyam
NK060(i)001:11404: de yang dang po dang po dang //
NK060(i)001:11405: skal mnyam gnyis pa'i rigs mchog ste //
NK060(i)001:11406: brgyad pa'i sems dpar skal ba mnyam //
NK060(i)001:11407: gsum pa bcu dang skal mnyam mod //
NK060(i)001:11408: dgongs spyod rgya mtsho khyad par 'phags //
NK060(i)001:11410: gsum pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu/
NK060(i)001:11412: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba rtogs/
NK060(i)001:11413: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin sgom/
NK060(i)001:11414: de ltar lta sgom mgo 'byor pas tshogs gnyis rdzogs
NK060(i)001:11415: pa'i 'bras bu ni pha rol tu phyin pa bcu
NK060(i)001:11416: dang / rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa'i sa dang lam thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:11418: gang la yang mi 'dzin pas sbyin pa/
NK060(i)001:11420: don la mi skrag pas bzod pa/
NK060(i)001:11421: gnyis med las mi g.yo bas bsam gtan/
NK060(i)001:11422: de nyid la mi g.yeng bas brtson 'grus/
NK060(i)001:11423: rang rig tu gsal bas shes rab/
NK060(i)001:11424: mngon du gyur pas smon lam/
NK060(i)001:11425: 'bras bu gzhan nas mi tshol bas thabs/
NK060(i)001:11426: lta ngan zil gyis gnon pas stobs/
NK060(i)001:11427: ye nas gnas pa'i don shes pas ye shes kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ste/
NK060(i)001:11428: de ltar bcu po kun kyang rab tu rdzogs la/
NK060(i)001:11429: mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings rang mtshan mthong bas sa dang po rab tu dga' ba/
NK060(i)001:11430: mtha'i lta ba ngan pa dag pas gnyis pa dri ma med pa/
NK060(i)001:11431: sems nyid rang gsal zhing 'gro don mi 'gog pas gsum pa 'od byed pa/
NK060(i)001:11432: rang rig thams cad du 'od gsal bas bzhi pa 'od 'phro ba/
NK060(i)001:11433: don gnyis su dus gcig la byed pas lnga pa sbyang dka' ba/
NK060(i)001:11434: mtha'i lta ba las ring du song ba drug pa mngon du gyur ba/
NK060(i)001:11435: sems nyid du yul med du rang gsal bas bdun pa ring du song ba/
NK060(i)001:11436: g.yeng ba'i las med pas brgyad pa mi g.yo ba/
NK060(i)001:11437: yon tan lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes mnga' bas dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros/
NK060(i)001:11438: de dag gi 'byung gnas su gyur pas bcu pa chos kyi sprin no //
NK060(i)001:11439: gzhan yang shes rab gsum gyi nang nas rang rig
NK060(i)001:11440: spyir yang ma dmigs pa gsal bas na sa bcu
NK060(i)001:11441: pa chos kyi sprin las kyang mchog tu gyur pa'i
NK060(i)001:11442: rgyu'i theg pa'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu kun tu
NK060(i)001:11443: 'od kyi sa'o // 'khor ba'i chos ma spangs par
NK060(i)001:11444: spyod pa'i thabs dang de la mi 'dzin pas shes
NK060(i)001:11445: 'od kyi sa'o // rab ste/ de gnyis gnyis su med pa ni thabs kyi khyad par ro //
NK060(i)001:11446: de ltar spyad kyang skyon gyis mi gos pas na
NK060(i)001:11447: kun tu 'od las kyang mchog tu gyur pa pad+ma
NK060(i)001:11448: can gyi sa'o // thams cad sku dang ye shes
NK060(i)001:11449: kyi dkyil 'khor du gsal bas na pad ma can
NK060(i)001:11450: las kyang mchog tu gyur pa'i yi ge 'khor lo
NK060(i)001:11452: de ltar sa'i khyad pa ni rab dga' la sogs pa lam gyi bcu dang /
NK060(i)001:11453: gzhan yang 'bras bu'i sa gsum ni rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i mthar thug kun tu 'od dang /
NK060(i)001:11454: 'bras bu rdo rje'i theg pa'i mthar thug pad+ma can dang /
NK060(i)001:11456: de dag gi khyad par ma 'dres pa yod kyang /
NK060(i)001:11457: 'og ma'i yon tan rnams gong ma la ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub cing yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11461: mthar thug rgyal ba'i yon tan/
NK060(i)001:11463: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyiil 'khor rtogs goms mthar phyin
NK060(i)001:11464: pas ni dkyil 'khor kun tu rab tu sbyor bas
NK060(i)001:11465: te/ rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:11466: thams cad ma btsal lhun gyis grub par 'gyur ro
NK060(i)001:11467: te/ // gnas skabs lam la mi gnod pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:11469: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pa la sogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:11470: cho ga lnga ni cig car ba'i rten gyi gang
NK060(i)001:11471: zag la dus gcig tu rdzogs pas na/
NK060(i)001:11472: rim gyis pa ltar bsgom mi dgos bzhin du gal te bsgom pas lhag gam/
NK060(i)001:11473: thod rgal ba'i rten gyi gang zag gis lam bar
NK060(i)001:11474: nas bor bas ma tshang yang dngos grub gnyis thob
NK060(i)001:11475: pa'i phyir na cho ga lhag chad kyi skyon nyid
NK060(i)001:11476: dag ste nyes pa med do //
NK060(i)001:11477: bka' gsang sngags mtshon pa'i tshig dang /
NK060(i)001:11478: gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan gnyis bsdebs te bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11480: le'u'i don dril nas byung ba 'di ni gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje'i tshig tu'o //
NK060(i)001:11481: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa nyid 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched du gleng ngo //
NK060(i)001:11482: zhes ched du brjod pas gzhi ma nges pa la
NK060(i)001:11483: sna tshogs su snang ba rol mo'i sprin gyis gnyis
NK060(i)001:11484: su med par gnas su stobs pas mnyes par gyur
NK060(i)001:11485: to // le'u'i mtshan gnyis bsdebs te bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11487: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las zhes pa gnyis 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:11490: dgyes ldan lha'i tshogs dang gsum yin te/
NK060(i)001:11492: skye bo mdza' ba kun 'tshogs pa //
NK060(i)001:11494: 'byor pa longs spyod tshang ba ni //
NK060(i)001:11495: bde ba'i longs spyod tshogs su bshad //
NK060(i)001:11496: lha dang dam can kun 'dus pa //
NK060(i)001:11497: 'dus pa chen po'i tshogs su gsungs //
NK060(i)001:11498: thams cad spyod la mi 'dzin pa //
NK060(i)001:11499: tshogs gnyis rgyun du rdzogs byed pas //
NK060(i)001:11500: tshogs chen po ru nges par bshad //
NK060(i)001:11502: tshogs kyi gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum dkyil yin pa de la/
NK060(i)001:11503: rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum khro bo dang
NK060(i)001:11504: bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor gyis bskor nas tshogs sgrub pa'i
NK060(i)001:11505: gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas na le'u ste yas bgrangs
NK060(i)001:11506: bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa'i don du gada'o////da
NK060(i)001:11507: ni le'u bcu gsum pa ston par byed pa la
NK060(i)001:11509: rab kyi gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las gsum ka ston/
NK060(i)001:11510: snang ba bzhi las bzhi ka ston/
NK060(i)001:11511: mtshan nyid gsum las gsum ka ston/
NK060(i)001:11512: lam la thabs grol gnyis las gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:11513: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa gtso bor ston/
NK060(i)001:11514: 'bring gi chos lnga las rgyud don/
NK060(i)001:11515: de la bcu las gzhung hril po byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ston/
NK060(i)001:11516: de'i zhor la lta ba ston/
NK060(i)001:11518: ting nge 'dzin dang phrin las zur tsam ston no //
NK060(i)001:11519: tha ma'i chos bcu las rang bzhin lta ba/
NK060(i)001:11520: ldem dgongs man ngag /gtar ka gegs sel/
NK060(i)001:11521: gzhan yang spyi 'gro rnams kyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:11522: de ltar ston pa'i le'u bcu gsum pa 'di la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:11524: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:11526: le'u bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis par tshom bu'i lha bsgom pa bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:11527: 'dir 'khor lo bsgom pa ston pas na de nas zhes 'brel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:11528: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi phyogs bcu dang
NK060(i)001:11529: dus bzhis bsdus pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi ye shes
NK060(i)001:11530: rang rig par mi phyed pas na/
NK060(i)001:11531: rdo rje'i dkyil 'asemakhora sa nyid du rang snang bas
NK060(i)001:11532: thams cad gcig tu 'dus nas dgongs pa bsam gyis
NK060(i)001:11533: mi khyab pa'i dgyes pa chen pos 'khor 'das kyi
NK060(i)001:11534: chos thams cad ye'am gdod ma nas rdzogs pas na
NK060(i)001:11535: rang byung gi ye shes chen por rang snang ba
NK060(i)001:11536: ste/ lhun gyis grub pa las mi 'da' ba'i dam
NK060(i)001:11537: tshig phal gyi yul ma yin pa'i phyir na shin
NK060(i)001:11538: ste/ tu gsang ba'o // gang zhe na/
NK060(i)001:11539: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po de'o //
NK060(i)001:11541: rang gsang thabs kyis chod pa'i tshul gyis so //
NK060(i)001:11542: de nyid ma tshon par byed pa'i sgo/
NK060(i)001:11544: mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu la sogs pa'i sprin
NK060(i)001:11545: yongs su bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin la dgongs pa
NK060(i)001:11546: mngon du bzhag pas na snyoms par zhugs nas 'og
NK060(i)001:11547: nas 'byung ba'i don ched du brjod pa 'di dag
NK060(i)001:11548: brjod do // le'u'i gzhung la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:11555: 'bras bu de byas pa ma yin pa rang byung du bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:11556: rgyud la mthong mos byas pa'i yon tan/
NK060(i)001:11557: snod dang ldan pa'i yul du bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:11560: snod ngan la sbyin pa'i nyes dmigs so //
NK060(i)001:11563: 'di las bcad nang tshegs su phye na gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:11564: 'jig rten pa'i lta ba mtshon par byed pa'i sgo dang /
NK060(i)001:11565: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba mtshon pa'i sgo dang /
NK060(i)001:11566: de gnyis ka'i tha snyad mtshon par byed pa'i sgo'o //
NK060(i)001:11568: ma rtogs pa skye bo tha mal pa dang /
NK060(i)001:11569: log par rtogs pa mu stegs so //
NK060(i)001:11570: de yang skye bo ni las rgyu 'bras dang /
NK060(i)001:11571: tshe snga phyi la sogs pa yod par yang ma rtogs/
NK060(i)001:11572: med par yang ma rtogs te/
NK060(i)001:11573: de gnyis ka gang la yang blo rten mi 'cha'
NK060(i)001:11574: ba kun tu rmongs pa rnams ni phyal ba zhes
NK060(i)001:11575: bya'o // tshe snga phyi dang las rgyu 'bras yod pa tsam rtogs kyang /
NK060(i)001:11576: phyi ma rgyab tu bor nas tshe 'di'i btsan phyug bsgrub pa ni rgyang 'phen zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:11577: de gnyis ka yang grub mthas blo ma bsgyur ba yin no //
NK060(i)001:11578: grub mthas blo bsgyur ba la gnyis/
NK060(i)001:11580: log pa ma yin par bsgyur ba'o //
NK060(i)001:11581: 'dir grub mthas blo bsgyur ma bsgyur gyi khyad par
NK060(i)001:11582: ni rten gyi gang zag gang zhig /phyi pa mu
NK060(i)001:11583: stegs pa dang nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i grub mtha'i
NK060(i)001:11584: rjes su zhugs ma zhugs so //
NK060(i)001:11586: phyi ma'i grub mtha' rtag chad gnyis dang /
NK060(i)001:11587: nang pa'i grub mtha' theg chung gi bye brag pa dang mdo sde pa gnyis/
NK060(i)001:11588: theg chen gyi sems tsam dang dbu ma gnyis so //
NK060(i)001:11589: dang po phyi pa mu stegs pa ni yang dag
NK060(i)001:11590: pa'i lta ba 'gal 'du btsugs nas yin lugs las
NK060(i)001:11591: log pa ste/ rtag par lta ba dang chad par lta ba'o //
NK060(i)001:11592: rtag lta ni chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i 'khrul gzhi byas nas/
NK060(i)001:11593: bdag dang dbang phyug la sogs pa rtag pa gcig pu bde ba rang dbang can dang 'dod pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11594: de la yang phye na phyi dang /
NK060(i)001:11595: dbang phyug rgyur smra ba dang /
NK060(i)001:11596: ril por rgyur smra ba dang /
NK060(i)001:11597: rig byed kyi mtha' gsang bar smra la sogs pa rnams so //
NK060(i)001:11598: chad lta ni chos nyid ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub par 'khrul gzhi byas nas/
NK060(i)001:11599: las rgyu 'bras dang tshe snga phyi med par lta bas te/
NK060(i)001:11601: mdzes ma zhim par g.yos la ci dgar spyod //
NK060(i)001:11602: shi nas de yi spyod yul min/
NK060(i)001:11603: me shi thal ba rlung khyer ltar //
NK060(i)001:11604: slar 'tsho ba dag ga la yod //
NK060(i)001:11605: gang zhig rgyu 'bras yod smra ba //
NK060(i)001:11606: yi dwags spyang ki'i rjes dang mtshungs //
NK060(i)001:11608: de dag ni 'jig rten pa'i lta ba mtshon par byed pa'i sgo'o //
NK060(i)001:11609: gnyis pa 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba mtshon pa'i sgo //
NK060(i)001:11610: nang pa sangs rgyas pa yang gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:11613: rgyu theg pa la chung ngu dang chen po gnyis las/
NK060(i)001:11614: chung ngu ni sems nyid gnas lugs kyi phyogs gang
NK060(i)001:11615: zag gi bdag med dam bdag med phyed dang gnyis
NK060(i)001:11616: rtogs pa ste/ snga ma ni nyan thos dang /
NK060(i)001:11617: phyi ma ni rang sangs rgyas so //
NK060(i)001:11618: de yang nyan thos pa chos bdag gzung yul rdul phra rab dang /
NK060(i)001:11619: 'dzin sems skad cig ma don dam du 'dod kyang /
NK060(i)001:11620: gang zag gi bdag gzung yul rags pa dang /
NK060(i)001:11621: 'dzin sems rgyun dang bcas pa kun rdzob tsam du snang ba las rang bzhin med par rtogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11622: de yang bye brag pa ni 'dir ltar snang ba
NK060(i)001:11623: sgo lnga'i yul rnams phyi rol gyi don du bden
NK060(i)001:11624: par 'dod/ mdo sde pa ni 'di ltar snang ba ni sems kyi rnam par snang ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:11625: de'i lkog na de dang rigs 'dra'i don bden rdzas grub cig yod par 'dod do //
NK060(i)001:11626: rang rgyal ni gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa nyan thos dang mthun la/
NK060(i)001:11627: de'i steng du chos kyi bdag gi gzung cha rdul phra rab kyang rang bzhin med par rtogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11628: de ltar gnyis pa ni phyogs rtogs so //
NK060(i)001:11629: 'dir phyi pa mu stegs pa dang nang pa sangs
NK060(i)001:11630: rgyas pa'i khyad par ni lta ba gang zag gi
NK060(i)001:11631: bdag 'dod cing / rtag gcig bde ba rang dbang can dngos por smra ba'am/
NK060(i)001:11632: yang na las rgyu 'bras dang tshe snga phyi med par lta ba dang /
NK060(i)001:11633: skyabs gnas dkon chog gsum la skyabs su mi 'gro zhing /
NK060(i)001:11634: chos rtogs kyi phyag rgya bzhi khas mi len pa ni phyi pa mu stegs pa/
NK060(i)001:11635: de las ldog pa nang pa sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11636: yang bdag nyid ma rtogs pa ni sems tsam dang dbu ma ste/
NK060(i)001:11637: sems tsam pa rnam bcad bkag nas yongs gcod sems su 'dod de/
NK060(i)001:11638: de yang rnam bden pa ni don du snang ba
NK060(i)001:11639: thams cad don du mi bden kyang shes ngor bden
NK060(i)001:11640: par 'dod/ de'i nang nas kyang rnam rig pa/
NK060(i)001:11641: don sems gnyis na yin pa gcig yin pa/
NK060(i)001:11642: yod pa tha dad du yod pa/
NK060(i)001:11643: rnam pa mtshungs pa ste rnam rig gnyis sgo nga bkas pa ltar 'dod do //
NK060(i)001:11645: rnam pa ni sems kyis sgro btags pa'i sgro btags
NK060(i)001:11646: tsam snang ba yin pa'i phyir bden med du 'dod
NK060(i)001:11647: do // dbu ma pa ni rnam bcad bkag nas yongs gcod spros bral las khas mi len pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11648: de yang dbu ma rang rgyud pa ni yang dag pa'i kun rdzob pa dang /
NK060(i)001:11649: log pa'i kun rdzob khyad par 'byed la/
NK060(i)001:11650: thal 'gyur ba ni yang log khyad par med par 'dod do //
NK060(i)001:11651: 'dir theg pa chung ngu dang chen po gnyis kyi
NK060(i)001:11652: khyad par na shes rab dang snying rjes phye ba
NK060(i)001:11653: ste/ shes rab chung bas bdag med gnyis ka rnal mar rtogs mi nus/
NK060(i)001:11654: snying rje chung bas gzhan don spyod par mi nus pa ni thig pa chung ngu'o //
NK060(i)001:11655: shes rab che bas bdag med gnyis rnal mar rtogs nus/
NK060(i)001:11656: snying rje che bas gzhan don 'ba' zhig spyod nus pa ni theg pa chen po ste/
NK060(i)001:11658: theg pa'i khyad par shes rab snying rjes te //
NK060(i)001:11659: de min theg pa chen por khas 'ches pa //
NK060(i)001:11660: bong bus seng ge'i pags pa gyon dang mtshungs //
NK060(i)001:11664: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud do //
NK060(i)001:11665: snga ma phyi rgyud ni sgo gsum gyi bya bas
NK060(i)001:11666: rgyud 'dul gtso bor byed pa kri ya dang u
NK060(i)001:11667: pa'o // ting nge 'dzin gyi dgongs pas 'bras bu bsgrub pa gtso bor byed pa yo ga'o //
NK060(i)001:11668: 'dir rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:11669: 'bras bu sngags kyi theg pa'i khyad par ni sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rgyu ru 'dod cing /
NK060(i)001:11670: don dam bsgrub byar byas nas kun rdzob spang byar byed pa ni mtshan nyid kyi theg pa/
NK060(i)001:11671: sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bur 'dod cing kun
NK060(i)001:11672: rdzob kyang mi spong bar lam du byed pa ni
NK060(i)001:11674: phyi ma nang rgyud ni sngags kyi rgyud man chad
NK060(i)001:11675: la med pa'i lta spyod dang ldan pa gsang ba
NK060(i)001:11676: ma h+aa/ a nu gnyis dang /
NK060(i)001:11677: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i rang bzhin
NK060(i)001:11678: rang byung gi ye shes ye nas 'bras bu'i ngo
NK060(i)001:11679: bor 'dod pa a ti yo ga ste/
NK060(i)001:11680: de ltar bskyed rdzogs gsum mo //
NK060(i)001:11681: 'dir sngags phyi nang gi khyad par gang zhe na/
NK060(i)001:11682: lta spyod ting nge 'dzin gsum dbyer med du 'dod pa sngags nang pa/
NK060(i)001:11684: 'o na sngags phyi pa dang mtshan nyid pa la khyad par med dam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:11686: kun rdzob lam du byed mi nus pa dang nus pa'i khyad par yod do //
NK060(i)001:11687: sngags nang pa gsum gyi khyad par ni spyod pa gtso che ma h+aa/
NK060(i)001:11688: ting nge 'dzin gtso che a nu/
NK060(i)001:11689: lta ba gtso che a ti'am/
NK060(i)001:11692: zung 'jug gtso gang che'i ngos nas kyang btags so //
NK060(i)001:11693: de dag rtogs par dka' bas na gsang ba'i don
NK060(i)001:11694: de 'jig rten las 'das pa mtshon par byed pa'i
NK060(i)001:11695: sgo'o // de ltar 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las
NK060(i)001:11696: 'das pa'i sgo de rnams ji lta bar mtshon pa
NK060(i)001:11697: ni yi ge dang ming tshig la sogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:11698: rtogs ma rtogs gnyis ka'i tha snyad mtshon par byed pa'i sgo'o //
NK060(i)001:11699: de yang yi ge a'i sgra las btags pa ka
NK060(i)001:11700: kha la sogs pa gsal byed sum cu rtsa bzhi
NK060(i)001:11701: dang / a +aa la sogs pa dbyangs yig bcu gnyis dang /
NK060(i)001:11702: sgra dbyangs gnyis ka'i cha la sgrims pa thung ring ri r+ai gnyis/
NK060(i)001:11703: glod pa thung ring li l+ai gnyis ma ning gi yi ge bzhi'o //
NK060(i)001:11704: de ltar gsal byed dang dbyangs kyi yi ge 'dus pa las ming /
NK060(i)001:11705: ming 'dus pa las tshig gi tshogs byung la/
NK060(i)001:11706: de dag la brten pa'i tshig tshogs glegs bam gyis don rab tu mtshon te/
NK060(i)001:11707: bstan pa dang theg pa du mar snang ba ni mtshon par byed pa'i sgo zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:11709: mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud khong nas khong du
NK060(i)001:11710: gab pa rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po zhes bya
NK060(i)001:11711: ba/ mtshon byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud kyi khong du sbas pa'i rgyud don de'o //
NK060(i)001:11712: de gang gis 'byin par byed na ston pa gnyis kyis te/
NK060(i)001:11714: mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud don sems can thams
NK060(i)001:11715: cad la rang chas su gnas pa rtog pas bsgribs
NK060(i)001:11716: te ngo ma shes kyang ston pa kun tu bzang
NK060(i)001:11718: mtshon byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud don rdo rje 'dzin pa'i slob dpon gyi thugs la gnas pas na/
NK060(i)001:11719: de ltar ston pa gnyis kyis 'byin par byed do //
NK060(i)001:11721: ston pa kun tu bzang po'i thugs la gab cing /
NK060(i)001:11722: lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud kyi nang du sbas pa'i don 'di dag rgyal ba rnams dgongs pa/
NK060(i)001:11724: gang zag rnams snyan khung du brgyud nas rdo rje
NK060(i)001:11725: 'dzin pa'i slob dpon gyis rgyud kyi don rnams dkrugs
NK060(i)001:11727: gab pa mngon du 'byung ba'i tshul gyis 'byin no //
NK060(i)001:11729: gzu lum can dang ras chod can la/
NK060(i)001:11730: gab cing sbas pa'i don de dag snod dang ldan
NK060(i)001:11731: pa'i slob bu la bla ma brgyud pa'i man ngag
NK060(i)001:11732: gis rgyud kyi don phyin ci ma log par rtogs
NK060(i)001:11733: shing khong du chud par byed pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11735: phyir gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa/
NK060(i)001:11737: yang sgos su le'u bcu gsum pa 'adi'ang tshig brgyud dang /
NK060(i)001:11739: snyan brgyud gsum 'dzom par bar ma chad pa'i rdo
NK060(i)001:11740: rje slob dpon la rag las par shes par bya'o
NK060(i)001:11741: // gnyis pa myong bar byed pa'i thabs/
NK060(i)001:11743: 'di la gzhung 'di'i steng du sngon gyi bshad srol
NK060(i)001:11744: rnying pa la bskyed pa'i rim pa'i dbang du bstan
NK060(i)001:11745: pa dang / rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i dbang du bstan pa'i bshad lugs gnyis gsung /
NK060(i)001:11749: gsang ba rdzogs pa'i rdzogs rim dang bshad lugs gsum du gsung /
NK060(i)001:11751: dkyil 'khor bcu gnyis dang sbyar ba'i bshad lugs gcig gsung /
NK060(i)001:11752: rje sgro phug pa'i bzhed kyis sgyu 'phrul lam rim
NK060(i)001:11753: gyis rgyab byas nas grol lam rim gyis par ltar
NK060(i)001:11754: du bshad // man ngag lta phreng gis rgyab byas nas grol lam cig car ba ltar du bshad/
NK060(i)001:11755: thabs lam rim gyis pa steng sgo ltar bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:11756: thabs lam cig car ba 'og sgo ltar bshad pa bshad lugs bzhi ru 'thad dam gsum mod kyi/
NK060(i)001:11757: phyag len du bshad lugs gsum du mdzad de/
NK060(i)001:11758: grol lam rim gyis pa dang sbyar te phyi ltar du bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:11759: thabs lam steng sgo dang sbyar te nang ltar bshad pa/
NK060(i)001:11760: thabs lam 'og sgo dang sbyar te gsang ba ltar bshad pa dang gsum las/
NK060(i)001:11761: dang po phyi ltar bshad na/
NK060(i)001:11762: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor bden gsum ris med du ldan pa'i rang rig de/
NK060(i)001:11763: 'khor 'das thams cad la khyab par gnas pa ni lta ba dang rang gi ngo bo'o //
NK060(i)001:11764: de ltar gnas lugs kyi dkyil 'khor bden gsum ris med du ldan pa de/
NK060(i)001:11767: mnyam pa gnyis kyi gtan tshigs kyi sgo nas rtogs
NK060(i)001:11768: par gyis shig ces lta ba rtogs par gdams pa'o
NK060(i)001:11769: // de ltar gnyis ni rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba yin no //
NK060(i)001:11770: rang bzhin gnas lugs chos nyid don gyi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:11771: de la ni rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge
NK060(i)001:11772: 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i
NK060(i)001:11773: chos thams cad stong zhing bdag med par bsgom pa
NK060(i)001:11774: ni de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK060(i)001:11775: don dam spros bral gyi dkyil 'khor de ltar yin
NK060(i)001:11776: kyang kun rdzob sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor snying rje chen
NK060(i)001:11777: po nam mkha' dang mnyam par bsgoom pa las byung
NK060(i)001:11778: ba ni kun tu snang gi ting nge dzin no
NK060(i)001:11779: // stong pa dang snying rje rgya mi 'bral bar
NK060(i)001:11780: bya ba'i phyir yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gsum la
NK060(i)001:11781: // sems sbyang zhing / de thams cad kyang thugs
NK060(i)001:11782: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo yi ge
NK060(i)001:11783: h+aum gi dkyil 'khor du gsal bar bsgom pa ni
NK060(i)001:11784: phra ba yi 'bru la bslab pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11785: gsung yig 'bru h+aum de yongs su gyur pa las thugs phyag mtshan rdo rje rtse lnga pa/
NK060(i)001:11786: de yang yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje sems
NK060(i)001:11787: dpa' sku'i dkyil 'khor yongs su rdzogs par bsgom pa
NK060(i)001:11788: ste/ phra ba yig 'bru bsgom pa la ltos na mchog go //
NK060(i)001:11789: de gnyis ni phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK060(i)001:11790: de ltar stong pa dang snying rje gnyis su med
NK060(i)001:11791: pa'i lha'i sku snang la rang bzhin med pa de
NK060(i)001:11792: nyid phal gyis rtogs dka' zhing /
NK060(i)001:11793: gcig tu zlum pas na gsang ba'i thig le zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:11794: de ka dkyil 'khor gyi lha du ma'i 'byungs khungs su gyur pas na dbyings so //
NK060(i)001:11795: de yang 'byung ba lnga ni shes rab ste cha phra ba rigs kyi yum lngar bsgom zhing /
NK060(i)001:11796: chen po phung po lnga ni thabs te rags pa rigs kyi yab lngar bsgom pa'ang de bzhin te/
NK060(i)001:11797: gzhan yang dbang po lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:11800: rig pa ste rnam par shes pa lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:11801: shugs la gsum 'dus kyi reg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:11802: gya phyi log bzhi rnams kyi rtog pa ni byang chub sems dpa' sems ma dang /
NK060(i)001:11803: khro bo dang khro mo rnams te/
NK060(i)001:11804: lha rtogs dbyer mi phyed pa ni rdo rje'i tshogs zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:11805: yid dang chos kyi rtog pa'i spyod yul yongs su
NK060(i)001:11806: dag pas na kun tu bzang po dang bzang mo
NK060(i)001:11807: thub pa drug dang bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK060(i)001:11808: tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po rtsa ba'i lha yin
NK060(i)001:11809: no // rtsa ba'i lha yab yum cha re la yang yab la yab dang /
NK060(i)001:11810: yum la yum bkod pa thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu
NK060(i)001:11811: la bdag nyid chen po ye shes sems dpa' rtsa
NK060(i)001:11812: ba'i lha ci 'dra/ man 'dra phyag mtshan 'dzin 'dzin 'dra la mi 'dzin pa/
NK060(i)001:11813: rgyan dang cha lugs rnam par spangs pa re re bsgom pa ni shes rab kyi lha bzhi bcu'o //
NK060(i)001:11814: thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu po re re la yang
NK060(i)001:11815: lhag pa'i lha sku gsung thugs kyi gnas su rnam
NK060(i)001:11817: mi bskyod pa'i cha lugs can re re bsgom zhing /
NK060(i)001:11818: lha sum stong brgyad brgyad bzhi bcu po re re
NK060(i)001:11819: la yang thugs rig pa rang byung ye shes kyi
NK060(i)001:11820: snang cha ye shes lnga mtshon pa dbu rgyan rigs
NK060(i)001:11821: kyi lha lnga lngar blta zhing /
NK060(i)001:11822: de ltar yan lag gi lha lhag pa'i lha dang
NK060(i)001:11823: bcas pa nyi khri bzhi stong po thams cad gsal
NK060(i)001:11824: bar yul gyis mi 'phrogs par bsgom pa ni snang
NK060(i)001:11825: ba rnam par 'byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya
NK060(i)001:11826: ste/ de ni phyag rgya spros bcas so //
NK060(i)001:11827: lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin mgo 'byor pas sems
NK060(i)001:11828: nyid yo byad lngar zlum pas na snying po'i thig
NK060(i)001:11829: le zhes bya'o // de yang bsnyen sgrub kyi don
NK060(i)001:11830: la mnyam par sbyor bas yo byad lnga la spyod
NK060(i)001:11831: bzhin ma chags pa bde ba'i ye shes so //
NK060(i)001:11832: thabs kyis sna tshogs snang nas tshim par byed pa'i
NK060(i)001:11833: rol mo yis rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes su
NK060(i)001:11834: gsal ba ni dgyes pa'i mchog yin la/
NK060(i)001:11835: de ka la bdag nyid chen po'i mchod pa zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:11836: lha la lha thim par mchod/
NK060(i)001:11837: chos nyid la chos nyid rol pa'i tshul du dbul
NK060(i)001:11838: ba ni bar chad med pa'i lam tshom bu tshogs
NK060(i)001:11839: sgrub pa ste/ de rnams ni rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin yin no //
NK060(i)001:11840: zag pa gsum med pa'i bsod nams dang ye shes
NK060(i)001:11841: kyi tshogs kyis gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin
NK060(i)001:11842: bzhi thob cing ye shes sgyu ma'i sku dang cha
NK060(i)001:11843: mthun par rang snang ba ni sems nyid gzhi ma
NK060(i)001:11844: nges pas na rol mo'i dkyil 'khor te yon tan
NK060(i)001:11845: mtha' yas pa dang ldan pas na zag bcas kyi
NK060(i)001:11846: lam las mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11847: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor snang stong dbyer mi
NK060(i)001:11848: phyed pa de ni phal gyi yul ma yin zhing
NK060(i)001:11849: spros pa dang bral bas na gsang ba'i thig le'o
NK060(i)001:11850: // de nyid kyi don mtshan nyid gsum gyis mngon
NK060(i)001:11851: du byas pa ni dbyings rnam par dag pa zung
NK060(i)001:11853: de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos gzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:11854: de'i yon tan gyi cha la sku lnga lhun gyis
NK060(i)001:11855: grub pas phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi'i rgyal ba thams
NK060(i)001:11856: cad kyang mngon du rdzogs par 'gyur pas na/
NK060(i)001:11857: sku lnga gsung lnga yon tan lnga phrin las lnga
NK060(i)001:11858: thugs lnga ste nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs pa
NK060(i)001:11859: ma lus pa thob pa ni bdag nyid kyi zhal
NK060(i)001:11860: bdag nyid kyis mthong ba'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:11861: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK060(i)001:11862: la dbang sgyur ba'i mchog nyid dam pa yi ge
NK060(i)001:11863: 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa thob pa yin te/
NK060(i)001:11864: de dag ni 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid yin no //
NK060(i)001:11865: yang bshad lugs gnyis pa thabs lam steng sgo dang sbyar te bshad na/
NK060(i)001:11866: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo bsgom pa'ang kun tu bzang po'i man ngag ni/
NK060(i)001:11867: dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i zhes pas snying ga chos kyi
NK060(i)001:11868: 'khor lo tsit+ta smug po gur phub pa 'dra ba'i
NK060(i)001:11869: nang na rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ye nas gnas
NK060(i)001:11870: pa'i rtags su dwangs ma lnga/
NK060(i)001:11873: sku lnga rang bzhin gyis gnas te/
NK060(i)001:11874: de yang rtsa'i dwangs ma dar dkar gyi skud pa lta bu/
NK060(i)001:11876: yum dang sbyar na sangs rgyas spyan/
NK060(i)001:11877: ye shes dang sbyar na me long lta bu/
NK060(i)001:11878: sku dang sbyar na mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK060(i)001:11879: de na khrag gi dwangs ma mtshal cog la ma bcag pa'i khu ba lta bu/
NK060(i)001:11882: ye shes na mnyam pa nyid/
NK060(i)001:11883: sku na longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o //
NK060(i)001:11884: de na me'i dwangs ma me long nyi ma la bzhag pa'i ngad tsam zhig gnas te/
NK060(i)001:11887: ye shes na so sor rtog pa/
NK060(i)001:11889: de na rlung gi dwangs ma gser sa 'og bzhag pa'i rlangs tsam zhig gnas te/
NK060(i)001:11891: yum na dam tshig sgrol ma/
NK060(i)001:11892: ye shes na bya ba grub pa/
NK060(i)001:11894: de na nam mkha'i dwangs ma bar snang sang seng
NK060(i)001:11895: du yod pa ni 'byung ba dang sbyar na nam
NK060(i)001:11896: mkha'/ yum dang sbyar na nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma/
NK060(i)001:11897: ye shes na stong pa nyid/
NK060(i)001:11898: sku dang sbyar na chos kyi sku'o //
NK060(i)001:11899: g.yas na chos nyid kyi rtsa dkar po zlum po/
NK060(i)001:11900: sbyang ba'i sa bon a n+ri/
NK060(i)001:11901: de'i bar na sbyong byed kyi snying po +amo/
NK060(i)001:11903: rgyab phyogs su ye shes kyi rtsa ser po gru bzhi/
NK060(i)001:11907: g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa dmar po zla gam/
NK060(i)001:11908: sa bon pre duh snying po am/
NK060(i)001:11909: shes pa nyon mongs pa can gyi yid/
NK060(i)001:11910: mdun na rang rgyud kyi rtsa dmar nag gru gsum/
NK060(i)001:11911: de na sbyang bya dang sbyong byed kyi yig 'bru ni med de/
NK060(i)001:11912: shes pa ni sgo lnga gnyid dang bcas pa gnas so //
NK060(i)001:11913: dkyil 'khor de dag bsgoms pa'i stobs kyis gsal bar snang yang /
NK060(i)001:11914: mu stegs rtag pa'i 'dod pa ltar byed pa pos byas pa ni ma yin gyis/
NK060(i)001:11915: sgra gnas bdun pa lta bu'i ye shes lnga'i ngo
NK060(i)001:11916: bo la tsit+ta dkyil 'khor gyi dbus na ye shes
NK060(i)001:11917: snying po'i thig le me tog kun da lta bu
NK060(i)001:11918: 'od sna tshogs cir yang ma nges pa mtha' thams
NK060(i)001:11919: cad las grol ba yungs kar 'bring tshad tsam du
NK060(i)001:11920: gnas pa de/ rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal ba yul gyis mi 'phrogs pa bsgoms par byas pas/
NK060(i)001:11921: dwangs ma lnga ye shes snying po dang drug gi
NK060(i)001:11922: dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba ni phyin ci ma
NK060(i)001:11923: log par yongs su grub pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11924: de las byung ba ni spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu
NK060(i)001:11925: ga na mar ye shes snying po'i thig le la
NK060(i)001:11927: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le la phog ste mgal
NK060(i)001:11928: dum la has btab pa'i tshul du dkar sal le
NK060(i)001:11929: song ba las sa bon drug gnyid dang bcas pa
NK060(i)001:11930: sbyangs nas/ dwangs ma lnga ye shes kyi snying po la bsdus te bde ba'i ye shes 'byung ba'o //
NK060(i)001:11931: bde ba'i ye shes de nyid kyi ngo bo ni
NK060(i)001:11932: dmigs su med pa mtha' thams cad dang bral ba
NK060(i)001:11934: ye shes lnga'i ngo bor rang gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor de'i gong na gzhan med pas na mchog go //
NK060(i)001:11935: de ni rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa kun tu bzang po'i man ngag go //
NK060(i)001:11936: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo'am kun tu bzang po'i man ngag ni/
NK060(i)001:11937: lte ba'i rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi'i dbus na
NK060(i)001:11938: dbyings phyug lnga'i thig le zhes bya ba yi ge
NK060(i)001:11939: a thung gi dbyibs su gnas te/
NK060(i)001:11940: yum gyi gsang ba'i mkha'i sna rtse'i thig le dang 'brel nas gnas so //
NK060(i)001:11941: snying ga na mar la a la sems gtad de
NK060(i)001:11942: bsgoms pas rtsa a wa d+h+au ti na mar me
NK060(i)001:11943: sna dmar nar gyis song bas dbyings phyug lnga'i thig
NK060(i)001:11944: le la phog ste 'od du zhu bas/
NK060(i)001:11945: rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi'i rtog tshogs kyi thig le rnams zhu ste/
NK060(i)001:11946: zhag dkar 'o mas bus pa bzhin song tsa na
NK060(i)001:11947: sku dang ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gsal
NK060(i)001:11948: zhing / de dag 'byung ba'i rgyur gyur pas dkyil 'khor gyi dbyings so //
NK060(i)001:11949: 'byung lugs ni 'byung ba cha phra ba shes rab ste rigs kyi yum du gsal zhing /
NK060(i)001:11950: chen po phung po lnga rigs kyi yab lngar gsal bas na de bzhin te zhes sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:11951: byang chub sems ni rdo rje'i tshogs //
NK060(i)001:11953: dbang po bzhi phyi'i byang chub sems dpa' bzhi/
NK060(i)001:11954: yul bzhi nang gi sems ma bzhi/
NK060(i)001:11955: dus bzhi phyi'i sems ma bzhi/
NK060(i)001:11956: rig pa rnam shes bzhi nang gi sems dpa' bzhi'o //
NK060(i)001:11957: rnams zhes pa'i sgras gsang ba'i dbang po dang /
NK060(i)001:11960: gsum 'dus kyi reg pa dang bzhi ni sgo ba bzhi/
NK060(i)001:11961: rtag chad bdag mtshan ma yin pa'i gya phyi log bzhi ni sgo ma bzhir gsal ba'o //
NK060(i)001:11962: kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK060(i)001:11964: rtog tshogs thams cad bde ba'i ye shes kyi spyod yul du dag pa'o //
NK060(i)001:11965: des na 'khor 'das thams cad yid rang byung gi
NK060(i)001:11966: ye shes kho na'i phyir bdag nyid chen po zhes
NK060(i)001:11967: bya'o // de yang snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo
NK060(i)001:11968: la yang dang yang du bsgoms pa'i stobs kyis rang
NK060(i)001:11969: la rang gsal ba'i lhag pa'i ye shes so //
NK060(i)001:11970: ye shes lnga'i ngo bo yang thugs stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su 'dus pas/
NK060(i)001:11971: 'khor lo gnas dang bcas pa bsgom pa'i las kyis tha dad ltar snang yang /
NK060(i)001:11972: rang rig pa'i ye shes la blta bya lta byed
NK060(i)001:11973: med pa'i tshul gyis ye shes lnga'i ngo bo la
NK060(i)001:11974: lta zhing nyams su len pa ni lte ba sprul
NK060(i)001:11975: pa'i 'khor lor bsgom pa'i man ngag go //
NK060(i)001:11976: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo bsgom pa'am sbyor ba dag pa'i man ngag ni/
NK060(i)001:11977: mgrin pa'i rtsa 'dab bcu drug gi dbus na mkha'
NK060(i)001:11978: 'gro ma rngam ma zhes bya ba yi ge +aam
NK060(i)001:11979: gi dbyibs su gnas pa de la bza' baca'i bcud
NK060(i)001:11981: snying ga nas 'od zer gyen du song bas longs
NK060(i)001:11982: spyod kyi thig le la phog pas rtog tshogs kyi
NK060(i)001:11984: zhag dkar po 'o mas bus pa ltar song ba
NK060(i)001:11985: la mnyam bzhag gi sbyor bas thig le de dag
NK060(i)001:11986: zhu ba las ro drug po bde ba'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:11987: su gsal zhing / yid tshim par byed pas na rol mo'i ye shes zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:11988: sdug bsngal gyis gdung ba med pa'i dgyes pa chen po de la/
NK060(i)001:11989: bde ba'i ye shes myong bya myong byed med par
NK060(i)001:11990: gnas su stobs pas na mchod pa dbul ba zhes
NK060(i)001:11991: bya'o // de ltar spyod la mi 'dzin pa ni sbyor ba dag pa'i man ngag go //
NK060(i)001:11992: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo bsgom pa'am khyab gdal chen po'i man ngag ni/
NK060(i)001:11993: klad pa'i rtsa 'dab sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi dbus
NK060(i)001:11994: na kun tu bzang po'i thig le yi ge ham
NK060(i)001:11996: de bsgoms pa'i stobs kyis zag pa med pa'i bde
NK060(i)001:11997: ba nyams su myong ba'i bsod nams kyi tshogs kyis
NK060(i)001:11998: dngos po dang mtshan mar dngos po dang mtshan mar
NK060(i)001:11999: 'dzin pa'i dri ma dag nas ye shes su sgyu
NK060(i)001:12001: snying ga me sna yar song ste longs spyod kyi
NK060(i)001:12002: thig le la phog /de nas yar spyi bo tshangs
NK060(i)001:12004: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la phog pas 'od du zhu nas/
NK060(i)001:12005: bde chen gyi 'khor lo na thig le ham yod pa la thim pas/
NK060(i)001:12006: ham zhu ba las rtsa 'dab so gnyis kyi rtog tshogs kyi thig le 'od du zhu ste/
NK060(i)001:12007: zhag dkar 'o mas brgyangs pa bzhin du song ba dang /
NK060(i)001:12008: rol mo'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas mchog /ces pas/
NK060(i)001:12009: zag med kyi bde bas lus mgo mjug la khyab
NK060(i)001:12010: tsa na rtog tshogs thams cad sku dang ye shes
NK060(i)001:12011: su gsal ba'o // de yang rtogs dka' bas na gsang bas te/
NK060(i)001:12012: bcud 'dus pa'i thig le de nyid kyi 'byung khungs su gyur pas na dbyings zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:12013: bde ba'i ye shes de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa'i dngos gazhi'o //
NK060(i)001:12014: des na phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i chos
NK060(i)001:12015: thams cad rang rig pa'i mngon sum du rdzogs pas
NK060(i)001:12016: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku dang gsung dang yon tan
NK060(i)001:12017: dang phrin las dang thugs rnam lnga'am/
NK060(i)001:12018: nyer lnga ma lus par bdag nyid kyi zhal bdag nyid kyis mthong ba'o //
NK060(i)001:12019: des ni rig pa la rang dbang sgyur ba'i phyir
NK060(i)001:12020: na lam gyi nang nas mchog nyid dang thabs kyi
NK060(i)001:12021: nang nas dam pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:12022: gsang ba ltar bshad pa la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:12023: dang po thabs nyid shes rab tu sbyor ba ni
NK060(i)001:12024: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor bde ba'i ye shes kyi ro
NK060(i)001:12025: dang ldan pa'i don de gsang ba'i lung man ngag
NK060(i)001:12026: rig pa gsum gyis gtan la phab ste/
NK060(i)001:12027: rtogs par byed pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bzhi
NK060(i)001:12028: bsgom pa'i dkyil 'khor la ni bde ba'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:12029: skyed par byed pa'i dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12030: de yang yum gyi mkha' skye mched byin gyis brlabs te/
NK060(i)001:12031: sbyor ba'i brda bsnol mar bskul zhing yab thabs kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)001:12032: yum shes rab kyi dkyil 'khor gnyis su med pa las bde ba'i ye shes 'byung ba'o //
NK060(i)001:12033: yab kyi zla ba byang chub kyi sems la don
NK060(i)001:12034: dam gyi ye shes skye ba ni mi dmigs mtha'
NK060(i)001:12035: dang bral bas thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK060(i)001:12036: yab kyi thig le rdo rje bum pa'i nang na gnas pa'i dus na khams lnga'i bcud 'dus shing /
NK060(i)001:12037: ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas dkyil 'khor gyi mchog go //
NK060(i)001:12038: de ni thabs nyid ye shes rab tu sbyor ba'i/
NK060(i)001:12039: shes rab nyid thabs su sbyor ba ni nyi ma
NK060(i)001:12040: byang chub kyi thig le la rtsa gnas thams cad
NK060(i)001:12041: kyi bcud 'dus pa de rtogs dka' bas gsang ba'i
NK060(i)001:12042: thig le de nyid thabs kyis ma zin pa las
NK060(i)001:12044: thabs kyis zin na rtog tshogs dang sku dang ye shes su 'byung bas dkyil 'khor gyi dbyings so //
NK060(i)001:12046: phra ba ni shes rab ste rigs kyi yum mo //
NK060(i)001:12047: chen po ni phung po lnga ste rigs kyi de bzhin gshegs pa yab lnga'o //
NK060(i)001:12048: 'khor gyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni lta ba'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir rdo rje'i tshogs so //
NK060(i)001:12049: de yang dbang po bzhi ni phyi'i byang chub sems dpa'/
NK060(i)001:12050: rig pa rnam shes bzhi ni nang gi sems dpa'/
NK060(i)001:12051: yul bzhi ni nang gi sems ma/
NK060(i)001:12052: dus bzhi ni phyi'i sems ma'o //
NK060(i)001:12053: rnams kyi sgras gsang ba'i dbang po/
NK060(i)001:12056: gsum 'dus kyi reg pa dang bzhi ni sgo ba bzhi/
NK060(i)001:12057: rtag chad mu bzhi gya phyi log ni sgo ma bzhi/
NK060(i)001:12058: yid chos kun bzang yab yum/
NK060(i)001:12059: nyon mongs pa drug thub pa drug tu gsal bas/
NK060(i)001:12060: rtog tshogs kyi thig le sku dang ye shes kyi
NK060(i)001:12061: dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas te spyod yul yongs su
NK060(i)001:12062: dag pas na/ kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor de
NK060(i)001:12063: la rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes zag
NK060(i)001:12064: pa med pa'i bdag nyid chen po de nyams su
NK060(i)001:12065: blangs pa'i dus su bde ba'i ye shes khyad par
NK060(i)001:12066: can myong bas na lhag pa'i thugs sam sangs rgyas
NK060(i)001:12067: kyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo ye shes lnga blta bya
NK060(i)001:12068: lta byed med pa'i tshul gyis lta zhing /
NK060(i)001:12069: yum gyi nyi ma byang sems pad+ma'i ze 'brur gnas pa'i tshe/
NK060(i)001:12070: nyi ma byang sems de nyid sku dang ye shes
NK060(i)001:12071: dkyil 'khor du gsal bas shes rab nyid thabs su
NK060(i)001:12072: sbyor ba'o // thabs shes rab gnyis med du sbyor
NK060(i)001:12073: ba ni nyi zla gnyis su med pa'i thig le
NK060(i)001:12074: la yab yum gyi rtsa thams cad kyi bcud 'dus
NK060(i)001:12076: yab kyi zla ba byang chub kyi sems dang yum
NK060(i)001:12077: gyi nyi ma byang sems gnyis ro mnyam zhing gnyis
NK060(i)001:12078: med du sbyor bas/ mtha' gnyis las grol ba'i dngos po lhan cig skyes pa bde ba'i ye shes de/
NK060(i)001:12079: lam pas nyams su myong zhing tshim pas ni rol mo'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:12080: dga' ba bcu drug gi rim pas mas bzlog pa'i bde ba nyams su myong bas dgyes pa ste/
NK060(i)001:12081: de ka la thig le bde ba'i ye shes mchod pa dbul ba zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:12082: de la nyon mongs pa dang rnam rtog gi zag
NK060(i)001:12083: pa med pa'i ye shes med pa'i ye shes ro
NK060(i)001:12084: ma 'gags par myong ba bsod nams kyi tshogs kyis/
NK060(i)001:12085: bde ba'i ye shes snang la 'dzin med sgyu ma
NK060(i)001:12086: lta bu nyams su myong bas 'dod chags nyid bde
NK060(i)001:12087: ba'i ye shes su rang snang la/
NK060(i)001:12088: de nyid sku dang ye shes su gsal bas yid tshim par byed pas na rol mo'i dkyil 'khor te/
NK060(i)001:12089: de nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pas na mtha' yas pa'i mchog go //
NK060(i)001:12090: nyi zla gnyis med kyi ye shes rtogs dka' ba
NK060(i)001:12091: gsang ba'i thig le de nyid sku dang ye shes
NK060(i)001:12092: kyi 'byung khungs su gyur pas na dbyings so //
NK060(i)001:12093: de ka la thabs shes rab gnyis med du sbyor ba zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:12094: bde ba'i ye shes de ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa dngos so //
NK060(i)001:12095: de ltar gyur tsam na phyogs bcu dus bzhi rang
NK060(i)001:12096: rig pa'i mngon sum du rdzogs pas sku dang gsung
NK060(i)001:12097: dang yon tan dang phrin las dang thugs rnam lnga'am/
NK060(i)001:12098: nyer lngar lhun gyis grub pa de mngon du byas
NK060(i)001:12099: tsam na 'bras bu lhag ma ma lus pa grub
NK060(i)001:12100: ste bdag nyid kyi zhal mthong ba med pa'i tshul
NK060(i)001:12101: gyi mthong ba'o // de ni 'dod chags bde ba'i
NK060(i)001:12102: ye shes su dbang sgyur ba'i lam gyi nang nas
NK060(i)001:12103: gyi mthong ba'o // mchog nyid yin la/ thabs kyi nang nas dam pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:12104: gsum pa mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu/
NK060(i)001:12106: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang byang
NK060(i)001:12107: chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la blo brtan par gnas
NK060(i)001:12108: pa'i stobs kyis/ rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor gzhi
NK060(i)001:12109: dngos po'i gnas lugs de nyid mngon du rdzogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:12110: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor du
NK060(i)001:12111: pa'i stobs kyis/ rang snang ba'i phyir/ dkyil 'khor bdun
NK060(i)001:12112: gyis bsdus pa thams cad ma 'dres la yongs su
NK060(i)001:12113: rdzogs par lhun gyis grub pas na/
NK060(i)001:12114: rgyan du dkyil 'khor ma lus thogs //
NK060(i)001:12116: de ltar dkyil 'khor ma lus pa rdzogs pa'i phyir na rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)001:12117: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis
NK060(i)001:12118: rang rig pa'i bdag nyid du mnyam par sbyor bas
NK060(i)001:12119: 'gro ba drug gi sems can thams cad kyang nyid
NK060(i)001:12120: las mi gzhan pa ni gnyis su med pa'i thugs
NK060(i)001:12121: rje'i dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas na/
NK060(i)001:12122: dus gnas thams cad du ma 'gags par ma btsal lhun grub tu yongs kyis 'byung ba yin te/
NK060(i)001:12124: phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:12125: du rang snang bas gdul bya mi 'dor bar 'dul
NK060(i)001:12126: ba'i phyir sdug bsngal las skyob pa'i mgon zhes bya'o
NK060(i)001:12128: dpe sgyu ma mkhan gyis sprul pa'i rta glang snang yang bden dngos kyis stong pa bzhin/
NK060(i)001:12129: ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor gzugs sku gnyis su
NK060(i)001:12130: snang nas 'gro ba sgrol bar byed pa yis don
NK060(i)001:12131: bya ba'i yul byed pa'i mkhan po don byas pa'i
NK060(i)001:12132: dngos po dang gsum du 'dzin pa med par rang
NK060(i)001:12133: rig pa'i dkyil 'khor du spyod do //
NK060(i)001:12134: bzhi pa 'bras bu de byas pa ma yin par rang byung du bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:12136: rang byung gi ye shes la 'bras bu'i chos thams
NK060(i)001:12137: cad ye nas rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor sems can thams
NK060(i)001:12138: cad la ye nas gnas kyang /
NK060(i)001:12139: rang gi gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pas bsgribs nas ma rtogs pa de rtogs par byed pa'i thabs/
NK060(i)001:12140: thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab gsum gyis gnas lugs
NK060(i)001:12141: kyi don la blo mnyam par sbyor ba'i thabs kyis
NK060(i)001:12142: rang byung ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rang rig pa'i
NK060(i)001:12143: mngon sum du gsal ba ni 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK060(i)001:12145: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:12146: lam gyi tshul 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK060(i)001:12147: ngo bo nyid thob pa ra byed pa las 'da'
NK060(i)001:12148: bar mi mdzad pas na dam tshig gi mchog ces
NK060(i)001:12149: bya'o // lnga pa rgyud la mthong mos byas pa'i yon tan/
NK060(i)001:12151: sdig pa'i grogs dang bral bas blo phyin ci ma
NK060(i)001:12152: log pa'i gang zag gang zhig gis rgyud sde zab
NK060(i)001:12153: mo 'adi'am lam nyams su len tshul 'di la mos
NK060(i)001:12154: par gyur ba tsam kyang sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:12155: lhag ma ma lus pa thams cad kyis/
NK060(i)001:12156: phyogs bcu kun nas dus bzhin thams cad du dkyil
NK060(i)001:12157: 'khor ma lus pa nye bar bsnyen par byed pa
NK060(i)001:12158: yi nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur ba yin
NK060(i)001:12159: no // drug pa snod dang ldan pa'i yul du bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:12161: bskal pa chen po zhing gi rdul snyed du shes
NK060(i)001:12162: rab rnam pa gsum la shin tu blo sbyangs pa
NK060(i)001:12163: la rab tu gnas shing dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
NK060(i)001:12164: mchod nas bsnyen cing bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu ni/
NK060(i)001:12165: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po bsgrub bya kun gyi
NK060(i)001:12166: mthar thugs tu gyur pas na chen po 'di yin
NK060(i)001:12167: no // te zhes pa ni 'chad par 'gyur ba'i che ba dang 'brel ba'o //
NK060(i)001:12168: bdun pa man ngag gi che ba la yang gsum/
NK060(i)001:12170: rgyal ba'i gshegs shul yin pa'i che ba/
NK060(i)001:12172: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i gnas na 'das pa
NK060(i)001:12173: dang da ltar byung ba'i rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma
NK060(i)001:12174: lus pa kun kyang gsang ba'i snying po 'di mnyan
NK060(i)001:12175: pa la brten nas rgyal ba sku lnga lhun gyis
NK060(i)001:12176: rdzogs pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:12177: ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi lam yin pa'i che ba/
NK060(i)001:12179: de ltar 'byung ba'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang ma
NK060(i)001:12180: 'ongs pa nas 'byung bar 'gyur pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK060(i)001:12181: thams cad kun kyang rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i
NK060(i)001:12182: don rtogs pa 'di yis sku lnga lhun gyis 'grub
NK060(i)001:12184: dgongs pa'i zhe phugs yin pa'i che ba'o //
NK060(i)001:12186: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di ni ye nas gnas pa'i cha nas gzhi/
NK060(i)001:12187: de nyid nyams su len pa'i cha nas lam/
NK060(i)001:12188: de mngon du gyur pa'i cha nas 'bras bu ste/
NK060(i)001:12189: de ltar mtshan gsum du btags kyang ngo bo tha
NK060(i)001:12190: mi dad pa ni theg pa thun mong pa rnams
NK060(i)001:12191: kyi blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur pas na gsang
NK060(i)001:12192: chen zhes bya'o // de na nges pa'i don mthar
NK060(i)001:12193: thug pa 'di ni 'bras bu yang yin la 'di
NK060(i)001:12194: ka nyams su len pa'i cha nas lam du yang
NK060(i)001:12196: de'i phyir rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa rnams
NK060(i)001:12197: la yang thugs kyi brnag byar gyur pa 'di las
NK060(i)001:12198: gsang ba'i nges don gzhan med de/
NK060(i)001:12199: des na gzhan nas btsal kyang rtogs pa mngon du
NK060(i)001:12200: gyur pa'i rgyal bas kyang thob par byar med pas
NK060(i)001:12203: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i ba'i lugs kyis 'bras bu la lam du byed dam mi byed/
NK060(i)001:12205: byed na smin pa la lam du byed dam ma smin pa la lam du byed/
NK060(i)001:12206: snga ma ltar na thug pa med pa thal/
NK060(i)001:12207: smin na'ang smin pa la lam du bya dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:12210: mthar thug gsum cha las brjod //
NK060(i)001:12211: ces mthar thug yod par bshad pas gsal lo //
NK060(i)001:12212: phyi ma ltar na 'bras bu rang ma yin par thal/
NK060(i)001:12214: rtags khyab gang ma grub kyang dam bca' 'bud do zhe na/
NK060(i)001:12216: bskyed bya skyed byed kyi rgyu 'bras kyi dbang du byas na de ltar yin kyang /
NK060(i)001:12217: 'dir ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu 'bras kyi dbang du 'bras bu ni ye nas smin zin yin la/
NK060(i)001:12218: yin pa la yin pa ltar nyams su len pa ni lam du byed pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12219: de'i dgos ched ni yin pa la yin pa ltar mngon du 'gyur ba'o //
NK060(i)001:12220: de'i phyir na gzhi lam 'bras bu ngo bo tha
NK060(i)001:12221: mi dad par rtogs shing nyams su len pa ni
NK060(i)001:12222: 'bras bu rdo rje theg pa'i khyad chos yin no
NK060(i)001:12223: // gal te brgal lan gyis mi lo na/
NK060(i)001:12224: tshes brgyad kyi zla ba 'di zla ba yin nam ma yin/
NK060(i)001:12226: bu chung mi yin nam min zhes mgo basgre'o zhes rgya gab gong pa gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:12227: brgyad pa snod ldan la sbyin pa/
NK060(i)001:12229: rgyal ba kun gyi dgongs pa dang phyag rgya chen
NK060(i)001:12230: po'i mchog rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di su'i
NK060(i)001:12232: thos pa'i shes rab rngam po zan za ba lta bu dang /
NK060(i)001:12233: bsam pa'i shes rab gzob mo sha za ba lta bu dang /
NK060(i)001:12234: sgom pa'i shes rab bu chung zhun mar za ba lta bu ste/
NK060(i)001:12235: de ltar shes rab gsum la blo rab tu sbyangs
NK060(i)001:12236: pa'i stobs kyis dngos po thams cad kyi de kho
NK060(i)001:12237: na nyid mthong ba'i shes rab kyi mig dang ldan
NK060(i)001:12238: pa'i skyes bu rnams kyis 'di zungs shig /snod kha
NK060(i)001:12241: dug can gyi skyon dang bzhi bral ba/
NK060(i)001:12242: shes rab dang snying rje nogs thub pas snod kyi yon tan lnga dang ldan pa ste/
NK060(i)001:12244: ngang chu bo chen po'i rgyun bzhin ring ba/
NK060(i)001:12245: tshul dge slong gsar bu ltar zhib ba/
NK060(i)001:12246: bsam pa rin po che gser ltar bzang ba la blo ri rab ltar brtan cing mi 'gyur ba'am/
NK060(i)001:12247: yang na cis kyang sems mi 'khrug pas ngang bzang /
NK060(i)001:12248: skye bo rnams kyi spyod pa las log pas tshul shis/
NK060(i)001:12249: blo mi 'gyur bas rab tu brtan cing lus dang
NK060(i)001:12250: longs spyod chos phyir gtong phod pa la sbyin par
NK060(i)001:12251: bya'o // dgu pa snod ngan la mi sbyin zhing byin pa'i nyes dmigs bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12253: bshad ma thag pa'i snod ldan de las gzhan du nam yang sbyin par mi bya ste/
NK060(i)001:12254: snod dang mi ldan pa'i slob ma rmongs pa la
NK060(i)001:12255: slob dpon rmongs pa mi chos kyi lcam 'phyar che
NK060(i)001:12256: bas gal te byin par gyur na/
NK060(i)001:12257: tshe 'dir yang dus min par ni srog zad nas 'chi bar 'gyur la/
NK060(i)001:12258: shi ma thag pa sreg pa tsha ba'i dmyal ba brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:12259: sbrebs pa grang ba'i dmyal ba brgyad la sogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:12260: sdug bsngal la yun ring du gnas par 'gyur ro
NK060(i)001:12262: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas shing //
NK060(i)001:12265: 'dir/ snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la bstan //
NK060(i)001:12266: zhes pa gnyis ldabs so zhe na/
NK060(i)001:12268: gong ma ni theg pa 'og ma rnams la sbyangs
NK060(i)001:12269: pa'i 'bras bu 'di nyid 'grub tshul gyi sgo nas
NK060(i)001:12270: smos la/ skabs 'di ni snod kyi skyon dang yon tan bstan pa yin pas so //
NK060(i)001:12271: yang la la dag na re/
NK060(i)001:12272: gsang ba'i snying po 'di sbyangs rno'i yul yin gyis
NK060(i)001:12273: rang rno'i yul ma yin no zhes smra ba dag
NK060(i)001:12275: de tshod du zag med kyi chos nyid de mthong lam pa'i yul yin gyis/
NK060(i)001:12276: mthar lam pa'i yul ma yin no byas pas/
NK060(i)001:12278: mthong lam pas mthar lam blo chung bar thal zer na/
NK060(i)001:12279: 'o na sbyangs rno bas rang rno blo chung bar thal/
NK060(i)001:12283: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan mchog 'chang //
NK060(i)001:12284: zhes pas gsal lo zer na/
NK060(i)001:12286: ma sbyangs grub pa gsum phyir gyis //
NK060(i)001:12289: gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:12291: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa nyid ston 'khor dgongs pa
NK060(i)001:12292: khyad par med pas na de bzhin gshegs pa nyid
NK060(i)001:12293: la gong du bstan pa'i gzhung don de dag ched
NK060(i)001:12294: du brjod do // le'u'i mtshan no //
NK060(i)001:12296: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:12297: phal gyi yul ma yin zhing rtogs dka' bas na
NK060(i)001:12298: shin tu gsang ba bya sla tshegs chung don chen
NK060(i)001:12299: po ton pas na man ngag gi gcod cing mtshams
NK060(i)001:12300: 'dzin par byed pas na le'u ste yas bgrangs bcu
NK060(i)001:12301: gsum pa'i don du gada'o////da ni le'u bcu bzhi pa
NK060(i)001:12303: chos tshoms kyi dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:12304: rabs kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam dang 'bras bu ston/
NK060(i)001:12305: snang ba bzhi las lam snang dang 'bras bu'i snang ba ston/
NK060(i)001:12306: mtshan nyid gsum las 'bras bu mthar phyin/
NK060(i)001:12307: lam la thabs grol gnyis las grol lam/
NK060(i)001:12308: rim cig car gnyis las gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:12309: 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga rgyud don/
