NK060(i)001:12310: de la bcu las bstod pa'i mchod pa ston/
NK060(i)001:12311: zhor la dkyil 'khor dang phrin las ston/
NK060(i)001:12312: tha ma'i chos bcu las spyi 'gro rnams kyis ston no //
NK060(i)001:12313: de ltar ston pa'i le'u bcu bzhi pa 'di la gsum/
NK060(i)001:12315: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:12317: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan nas da bstod pa ston par byed pas na de nas zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:12318: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid kyi dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis yin pa la/
NK060(i)001:12319: de las gzhan pa'i sel med pa dgyes pa chen
NK060(i)001:12320: po'i glu drug 'di dbyangs su bsnyad nas blangs so
NK060(i)001:12326: dang po sku lnga la bstod pa/
NK060(i)001:12328: +amo yi ge cha lnga pas glu'i 'go 'dren pa ste ye shes lnga mtshon pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12329: phyogs cu dang dus bzhi'i sku bzhir snang ba thams
NK060(i)001:12330: cad kyang rang rig pa'i ye shes gcig gi ngo
NK060(i)001:12331: bo la lhun gyis grub par rdzogs pa ni mngon
NK060(i)001:12333: ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK060(i)001:12334: ngang du gsal ba'i thig le khyab gdal chen po
NK060(i)001:12336: zag pa med pa'i bsod nams kyi dkyil 'khor du snang ba longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o //
NK060(i)001:12337: gdul bya thams cad la sku'i snang ba sna tshogs su snang ba sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK060(i)001:12338: snang stong gnyis med du zlum pas na thig le
NK060(i)001:12339: ste chos kun dbyer med du rdzogs pa ni rdo
NK060(i)001:12340: rje'i sku'o // hohzhesa bstod pa'i don la mnyes pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12344: rdo rje ni gsung lnga skye 'jigs med par dbyer mi phyed pas so //
NK060(i)001:12345: bsod nams kyi ngo bo sgra thams cad ma spangs
NK060(i)001:12346: par rang snang ba brjod pa'i tshig gi gsung ngo
NK060(i)001:12347: // spros pa med pas na thig le chen po'i
NK060(i)001:12348: rang bzhin brjod pa bral ba skye med don gyi
NK060(i)001:12349: // gsung ngo // rdo rje ye shes lnga'i dkyil
NK060(i)001:12350: 'khor ni rang rig pa la ldan pas na de
NK060(i)001:12351: nyid gsal bar brda sprod pa mnyam nyid rig pa'i
NK060(i)001:12352: // gsung ngo // gsung ngo // rdo rje sgra
NK060(i)001:12353: chen ni tshig gcig gis don mtha' yas pa go
NK060(i)001:12354: bar byed pa tshangs par dbyangs kyi gsung dang /
NK060(i)001:12355: rdo rje rgyal po ni tshig tu brjod pa med
NK060(i)001:12356: pa nyid brjod pa dang 'dra bar gsal bar dgongs
NK060(i)001:12358: thig le chen po grags stong dbyer mi phyed pa ste yi ge med pa rdo rje'i gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:12365: thugs stong pa nyid kyi ye shes gsum rdzogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:12366: bdag nyid chen po de la yon tan mnyam pa
NK060(i)001:12367: nyid dang phrin las bya ba grub pa ye shes
NK060(i)001:12369: ye gdod ma nas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las ye shes lnga'i ngo bor lhun gyis rdzogs te/
NK060(i)001:12370: spyod yul yongs su dag pas na kun tu bzang po'o //
NK060(i)001:12371: ye shes re re la yang lnga lnga 'dus pa'i
NK060(i)001:12372: tshogs chen rang byung gi ye shes gcig ngor zlum
NK060(i)001:12373: pas na thig le chen po'o //
NK060(i)001:12375: yon tan lnga la bstod pa/
NK060(i)001:12378: cir yang mi dmigs pa'i rig pa nyid sgyu ma
NK060(i)001:12379: lta bur 'khrul pa snang stong gnyis su med par
NK060(i)001:12380: mnyam pa'i dbyings gzhal yas khang gi yon tan no
NK060(i)001:12381: // rgyal ba drug pa'i zhing khams mtha' yas pa
NK060(i)001:12382: kun tu snang nas don mdzad pa zhing khams kyi
NK060(i)001:12383: // yon tan no // ba spu'i bu ga re
NK060(i)001:12384: re nas kyang 'od zer sna tshogs pa 'phro ba
NK060(i)001:12385: ni 'od zer gyi yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:12386: 'dod yon lnga'i lha mo re re yang mtha' yas
NK060(i)001:12387: pa'i 'dod pa'i yon tan kun nas lhun gyis grub
NK060(i)001:12388: cing / gzugs kyi lha mo la sogs pa spyan
NK060(i)001:12389: la sogs pa la thim pa ni longs spyod kyi
NK060(i)001:12390: cing / yon tan no // de las gzhan yang
NK060(i)001:12391: yon tan ni sna tshogs pa ste seng ge la
NK060(i)001:12392: sogs pa'i sems can lngas bteg pa'i khri'i steng du
NK060(i)001:12393: sku zla ba gsung nyi ma thugs nyes pa'i skyon
NK060(i)001:12394: yis ma gos pas pad+ma dang /
NK060(i)001:12395: yon tan lhun gyis grub pas rin po che'i khri
NK060(i)001:12396: rkang chen por rang snang ba gdan khri'i yon tan
NK060(i)001:12398: phrin las lnga la bstod pa/
NK060(i)001:12401: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul phra mo snyed kyi dag pa chos sku'i/
NK060(i)001:12403: bar ma longs sku'i zhing khams dang gsum du rgyal
NK060(i)001:12404: bas mdzad pas sems can gyi don mdzad pa'i phrin
NK060(i)001:12405: las rdul phran snyed rnams kyang zhi ba'i/
NK060(i)001:12408: drag po'i phrin las dang bzhir 'du la/
NK060(i)001:12409: de dag mdzad pa'i mkhan po sprul pa'i sku zhing
NK060(i)001:12410: gi rdul phran las 'das pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK060(i)001:12411: pa mtha' yas pa rnams kyis dus skad cig gam
NK060(i)001:12412: yud tsam la rtsol ba la rag ma las par
NK060(i)001:12413: phrin las bzhis don mdzad pa ni lhun gyis grub
NK060(i)001:12416: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga la spyir bstod pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12419: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pas bsdus pa'i
NK060(i)001:12420: chos thams cad lhag ma ma lus par sku gsung
NK060(i)001:12421: thugs dang yon tan phrin las lngar ye nas gnas
NK060(i)001:12422: pa yin te/ gnas tshul ji ltar zhe na/
NK060(i)001:12423: gangs chen po lnga'i dbus na mtsho gcig yo na
NK060(i)001:12424: de'i nang du gangs chen po'i gzugs brnyan lnga 'char
NK060(i)001:12425: ba bzhin du/ sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin
NK060(i)001:12426: las ni mdzad pa ji ltar snang yang gcig gi
NK060(i)001:12427: bdag nyid du 'dus pas na chen po'o //
NK060(i)001:12428: yang mtsho chen po lnga'i dbus na gangs chen po gcig yod na/
NK060(i)001:12429: mtsho re re'i nang du yang gangs chen po'i gzugs brnyan re re snang ba bzhin/
NK060(i)001:12430: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin las lnga car
NK060(i)001:12431: gyis re re la'ang kun tu khyab pa yin no
NK060(i)001:12432: // de'i phyir dpe mtsho gcig tu gangs lnga 'char la/
NK060(i)001:12433: gangs gcig mtsho lngar 'char ba'i bzhin sku gsung thugs
NK060(i)001:12434: dang yon tan phrin las kyi snang tshul kun gcig
NK060(i)001:12435: tu bsdus pa/ gcig kun tu 'char bas na gcig dang du ma'i mtha' las grol ba'i yin te/
NK060(i)001:12436: de'i phyir thig le chen po'i rang bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:12440: zhes glu drug gi 'di dag ched du bsgrags so //
NK060(i)001:12441: 'di la bla ma rnams kyi gsung sgros ni/
NK060(i)001:12442: dper na stod mnga' ris bskor gsum gyi bdag po mnga' bdag rtse lde yin bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:12443: mnga' ris bskor gsum la mnga' bdag rtse lde'i bka' drin gyis ma khyab pa med bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:12444: mnga' ris bskor gsum la mnga' bdag rtse lde'i 'bangs
NK060(i)001:12445: min pa gzhan med bya ba lta bu yin gsung
NK060(i)001:12446: ngo // de dag kyang sgro btags pa'am bskur pa btab pa ni ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:12447: yon tan yod pa la yod pa ltar du che ba'i chen por bstod pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:12448: de'i phyir yon tan med bzhin bstod pa ni sgro btags pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:12449: yod bzhin mi bstod pa ni skur pa btab pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:12452: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:12453: bstod pa'i sgo nas mnyes pa'i glu drug gi gcod
NK060(i)001:12454: cing mtshams 'dzin pas na le'u ste yas bgrangs bcu
NK060(i)001:12456: 'o na mnyes pa'i le'u bya ba 'dug pas/
NK060(i)001:12457: rgyal bas mnyes mi mnyes mnga' na gzung 'dzin can du 'gyur ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:12458: rgyal ba la mnyes mi mnyes mi mnga' yang /
NK060(i)001:12459: gdul bya rnams kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs par bya ba'i
NK060(i)001:12460: ched du mnyes pa ltar snang ba la 'gal ba
NK060(i)001:12461: med do // de ltar le'u bcu bzhi pa yan
NK060(i)001:12462: chad ni rtogs pas bdag bsgral ba zhes kyang bya
NK060(i)001:12463: ste thugs rje zhi ba'i chos rdzogs so////da ni le'u
NK060(i)001:12464: bco lnga pa 'chad pa la chos tshoms gyi dbang
NK060(i)001:12465: med do // du byas na/ gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las/
NK060(i)001:12467: ru dra'i ngo la rgyal ba khro bor snang bas 'bras bu dang /
NK060(i)001:12468: ru dra lam bgrod pas lam ston/
NK060(i)001:12472: mtshan nyid gsum las rkyen 'jug pa dang 'bras bu mthar phyin pa ston/
NK060(i)001:12473: thabs grol gnyis las gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:12474: rim cig car gnyis las gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:12475: 'bring gi chos lnga las gleng gzhi dang rgyud don ston/
NK060(i)001:12476: rgyud don la bcu las gzhung hril po khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ston/
NK060(i)001:12477: de'i zhor la spyod pa ston/
NK060(i)001:12478: ru dra la dbang bskur bas dbang ston/
NK060(i)001:12479: ru dral dam 'bogs pas dam tshig ston/
NK060(i)001:12480: tha ma'i chos bcu las ldem dgongs man ngag /mtshon pa dpe/
NK060(i)001:12482: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:12483: de ltar ston pa'i le'u bco lnga pa 'di la gnyis/
NK060(i)001:12485: le'u'i gzhung la spyi don gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:12488: spyi don dang po la gsum/
NK060(i)001:12491: de la thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs rjes 'dul ba'i dus la bab par gzigs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12494: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs nas khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ston pas na de nas zhes 'brel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:12495: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad rigs lngar 'dus la/
NK060(i)001:12496: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po kun tu bzang po'o //
NK060(i)001:12497: zhi khro'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa gcig
NK060(i)001:12498: dang du ma dang bral ba ngo bo nyid kyis
NK060(i)001:12499: khroo bo'i dkyil 'khor sku'i phyag rgya chen por mngon
NK060(i)001:12500: par 'du mdzad de/ gang zhe na/
NK060(i)001:12501: spyir gyis khro bo la gsum las/
NK060(i)001:12502: shes rab chen po'i khro bo ni bdag med rtogs pa'i shes rab ste/
NK060(i)001:12503: des rnam par rtog pa'i mtshan ma 'joms pas so //
NK060(i)001:12504: de yang sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las/
NK060(i)001:12505: yang dag shes rab chen po ni //
NK060(i)001:12506: mtshan ma 'joms phyir khro bo'i mchog /ces gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:12507: ye shes chen po'i khro bo ni rang rig pa'i ye shes te/
NK060(i)001:12508: des dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos la mnga' mdzad cing /
NK060(i)001:12509: srid zhi gnyis kyi sa bon drungs nas 'joms so //
NK060(i)001:12510: de yang sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa las/
NK060(i)001:12511: rang rig ye shes rgyal po yis //
NK060(i)001:12512: phyogs bcu khams rnams dbang bsdus nas //
NK060(i)001:12513: kun kyang mi dmigs dbyings su thim //
NK060(i)001:12514: thams cad khro bo'i tshogs su 'gyur //
NK060(i)001:12516: phyag rgya chen po'i khro bo ni gdul bya gdug
NK060(i)001:12517: pa can gdul ba'i phyir sku mdog dang rgyan chas
NK060(i)001:12518: su snang ba ste/ de yang drang srong khros pa'i cha byad dang /
NK060(i)001:12519: mi'u thung byis pa'i cha byad dang /
NK060(i)001:12520: dpal chen rngam brjid kyi cha byad can te 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgu dang ldan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12521: de ltar khro bo gsum las/
NK060(i)001:12523: de dgos ched ci'i phyir zhe na/
NK060(i)001:12526: rgyu bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtog pa lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12527: rkyen kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pa gzung 'dzin
NK060(i)001:12528: gnyis la mngon par zhen pas spyi mtshan la rang
NK060(i)001:12529: mtshan du mthong bas yang dag pa'i lam bskyed rdzogs
NK060(i)001:12530: gnyis dang bral ba dag go //
NK060(i)001:12531: khyad par du sngon bskal pa kun bkod kyi dus su byung ba'i dge slong thar pa nag po de/
NK060(i)001:12532: gol gzhi de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab tshig bzhi pa la sgra ji bzhin par spyad pas/
NK060(i)001:12533: gab pa'i gsang ba rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po
NK060(i)001:12534: ji bzhin pa de nyid ma rtogs par yi ge'i
NK060(i)001:12535: rgyud du barda'am sgra'i tshul du sbas pa'i gsang ba
NK060(i)001:12536: 'khor ba'i chos dngos po bzhi la mngon par 'chel
NK060(i)001:12537: nas de dag la 'jol nyog tu spyod cing /
NK060(i)001:12538: rgyu las dge sdig dang 'bras bu mtho ris dang ngan song gi don la rmongs pas so //
NK060(i)001:12539: gnyis pa gol ba'i 'bras bu la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:12540: rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu sdug bsngal myong ba dang /
NK060(i)001:12541: rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu ru drar smin pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12546: srid pa gsum du skye ba'i sa bon las dang
NK060(i)001:12547: nyon mongs pa rang kha ma'i bag chags rtsub mo
NK060(i)001:12548: yis 'phangs nas sdug bsngal bar mtshams med pa'i rab
NK060(i)001:12549: tu tsha ba'i dmyal bar skyes so //
NK060(i)001:12550: der rab tu tsha ba'i sdug bsngal drag pos lus sems shin tu gdungs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12551: 'di las shin tu grang yang ci ma rung snyam
NK060(i)001:12552: pa'i mod la grang ba'i sdug bsngal gyis rab tu
NK060(i)001:12553: sbrebs pa dang / pad+ma ltar gas pa'i sdug bsngal
NK060(i)001:12554: drag po dag gis lus sems rab tu gdungs pa
NK060(i)001:12555: de lta bu'i sdug bsngal rab tu tsha ba'i dmyal
NK060(i)001:12556: ba'i gnas rigs ni yang sos dang /
NK060(i)001:12562: rab tu tsha ba chen po dang /
NK060(i)001:12563: mnar med pa la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:12564: shin tu grang ba'i gnas rigs chu bur can dang /
NK060(i)001:12565: chu bur rdol ba can dang /
NK060(i)001:12571: gas pa chen po la sogs pa brgyad po dag tu bskal pa chen po re 'jig pa'i dus su/
NK060(i)001:12572: 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan gyi dmyal ba'i gnas su skad cig gi yun la 'phos nas/
NK060(i)001:12573: dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal kha brgyud cing bar bskal brgyad cu la bskal pa chen po gcig tu byas pa'i/
NK060(i)001:12574: de'ang stong phrag bcu gnyis su tsha grang gi sdug bsngal mi ba zod pa nyams su myong ngo //
NK060(i)001:12577: dmyal ba'i gnas su skyes pa de nas yi dwags kyi gnas su skye ba ston te/
NK060(i)001:12580: rang kha ma'i phrin las tshad du ma phyin pa'i sbyor sgrol dang /
NK060(i)001:12582: dam tshig can la ngan du sems pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12583: che ba'i nga rgyal gyis dregs pa la sems pa'i rnam par smin pa de rnams zad pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12584: yi dwags kyi gnas su skyes nas ltogs pa dang
NK060(i)001:12585: skom pa'i sdug bsngal gyis rab tu gdungs nas nyen
NK060(i)001:12586: pa dang / phyi'i 'dod pa'i dngos po bza' btung
NK060(i)001:12587: rnams ngan skyugs la sogs par mthong nas yid du
NK060(i)001:12588: mi 'ong ba phyi'i sgrib pa can dang /
NK060(i)001:12589: gdug cing rtsub pa'i dngos po khro chu khol ma
NK060(i)001:12590: dang lcags tshan la sogs pa sna tshogs su 'gyur
NK060(i)001:12591: pa me lce'i 'khor lo can dang /
NK060(i)001:12592: bza' baca'i dngos po'i mthong nas bgrod pas sleb tsam
NK060(i)001:12593: na yod med par 'gyur zhing lus shin tu rid
NK060(i)001:12595: mgo lus ri bo tsam dang yan lag byi thur tsam dang dbang po mi 'tshams pa ste/
NK060(i)001:12596: kha mig tsam la sogs par 'gyur ba de lta bur bskal ba chen po drug tu skyes so //
NK060(i)001:12598: de nas rnam par smin pa de zad pa dang
NK060(i)001:12599: bya ba 'dug pas rnam par smin pa spyad pas
NK060(i)001:12601: spyad pas zad na yang dag pa'i lam la dgos pa med par thal/
NK060(i)001:12602: rnam smin spyad pas zad pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:12603: gnyen po bstem pas zad na ngan song gsum mi khoms pa'i gnas ma yin par thal/
NK060(i)001:12604: gnyen po bsten du 'dug pa'i phyir ro zhe na/
NK060(i)001:12605: lan ni spyir gyis las 'dag tshul bzhin yin te/
NK060(i)001:12606: rtogs pas 'dag pa ni bdag med rtogs pa'i shes
NK060(i)001:12607: rab kyis 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad snang yang
NK060(i)001:12608: bden dngos kyis stong pa rmi lam mam/
NK060(i)001:12609: sgyu ma lta bur rtogs na las kyi 'bras bu myong yang gnod par mi nus so //
NK060(i)001:12610: bshags pas 'dag pa ni stobs bzhi yongs su rdzogs
NK060(i)001:12611: pa'i bshags pas mtshams med pa'i las byas pa yang
NK060(i)001:12613: gnyen pos 'dag pa ni mi dge ba chung ngu'i gnyen por dge ba chen po spyad pas/
NK060(i)001:12614: mi dge ba'i 'bras bu bag la zha nas gnod par mi nus pas so //
NK060(i)001:12615: gal te de gsum ka dang mi ldan na myong
NK060(i)001:12616: 'gyur gyi las yin pas de ni myong bas 'dag
NK060(i)001:12617: ste/ de'i phyir du ru dra thar pa nag pos
NK060(i)001:12618: ni gsang sngags sgra ji bzhin par spyad pas yang
NK060(i)001:12619: dag pa'i lam las gol ba'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:12620: las kyi 'bras bu myong ba'i stobs kyis zad pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:12623: yi dwags su skyes pa de nas las kyi sgrib pa rtsub mo zas nor la brkam pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12626: mchod pa'i yo byad la rngam pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12627: gsog 'jog byas pa'i rnam par smin pa de khad kyis bsrabs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12628: sngon gyi dus su phra men la sogs pa'i khro bo rang rgyud pa bsgom pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12629: las barlanga bo byas pa'i srid pa'i mtshams sbyar nas
NK060(i)001:12630: yi dwags kyi rigs kyi las kyi srin por skyes
NK060(i)001:12631: so // de yang yul lang ka pu rangs kyi smad 'tshong ma'i mngal du chags pa las/
NK060(i)001:12632: mngal nas skyes nas zhag bdun lon pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12633: ma shi nas dwa bu de mi rnams kyis dug
NK060(i)001:12634: shing nal bya'i rtsar ma'i ro'i mchan du bcug nas
NK060(i)001:12635: bskyal lo // der dwa bu des ma'i nu zho
NK060(i)001:12636: dang khrag dang sha dang rus pa'i bar du zos
NK060(i)001:12637: bskyal lo // so // zos pas kho cher brtas
NK060(i)001:12638: nas dur khrod kyi ro rnams zas su za zhing
NK060(i)001:12639: bskyal lo // so // / ro gos rnams gos
NK060(i)001:12640: su gyon pas yi dwags kyi rigs kyi srin po
NK060(i)001:12641: chen po bya'i gshog pa can du gyur to //
NK060(i)001:12642: de yang lus rab tu gdug pa sems shin tu
NK060(i)001:12643: gtum pa dbu mang por rang rgyud du bsgoms pa'i
NK060(i)001:12644: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu lus gcig la mgo bo
NK060(i)001:12645: brgya pa dang / stag dang seng ge la sogs pa mgo bo sna tshogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12646: lus mang po rang rgyud du bsgoms pa'i rgyu mthun
NK060(i)001:12647: gyi 'bras bu lus brgya la mgo bo gcig pa
NK060(i)001:12648: dang / stag dang seng ge la sogs pa lus sna tshogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12649: phyag mang rang rgyud du bsgoms pa'i rgyu mthun gyi
NK060(i)001:12650: 'bras bu yan lag mang po dang yan lag rigs
NK060(i)001:12651: mi mthun pa sna tshogs pa dang gdug pa'i lag
NK060(i)001:12652: cha mda' dang mda' bo che dang /
NK060(i)001:12653: kha t+w+aam ral gri la sogs pa sna tshogs thogs pa/
NK060(i)001:12658: dur bya la sogs pa gdug pa can gyi 'khor rab tu mang po dang /
NK060(i)001:12659: sdig pa dang dug sprul la sogs pa 'jigs pa'i gzugs sna tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:12660: ra la ra la la sogs pa'i 'jigs pa'i sgra sna tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:12661: ru dra ma dra ma ra dra la sogs pa
NK060(i)001:12662: 'jigs pa'i nga ro sna tshogs sgrogs pa gdug pa'i
NK060(i)001:12663: gzugs dang ngag gi nga ro dang lus kyi dri
NK060(i)001:12664: dang kha rlang gis nad 'byung bar byed cing /
NK060(i)001:12665: lus can thams cad skyi bung zhes byed pa dbugs
NK060(i)001:12666: rab tu 'jigs pa'i rlung nag tu 'tshubs pa dang
NK060(i)001:12667: / sna nas grang ba'i nad dang kha nas tsha
NK060(i)001:12668: ba'i nad 'byung ba'i dbugs kyis phyogs kun tu lus
NK060(i)001:12669: can thams cad khams 'khrug par byed pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12670: rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa re re yang brgya
NK060(i)001:12671: rtsa gcig brgya rtsa gcig ste nad bzhi brgya rtsa
NK060(i)001:12673: bdag sems myos shing dran pa nyams par byed pa'i mthus klu'i rigs dang /
NK060(i)001:12674: lha ma yin gyi rigs dang /
NK060(i)001:12679: 'bras bu che ba man chad dbang du bsdus so //
NK060(i)001:12680: thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs rjes 'dul bar dus la bab par gzigs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12682: las kyi srin po mthu rtsal can de sngon bskal pa kun bkod kyi dus su/
NK060(i)001:12683: dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu bsten pa'i stobs kyis
NK060(i)001:12684: thub dka' gzhon nu de rdo rje sems dpar sangs
NK060(i)001:12685: rgyas pa dang / mched dan 'bag sa bcu'i byang
NK060(i)001:12686: chub sems dpa' gsang ba'i bdag por gyur pa'i thugs
NK060(i)001:12687: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gzigs nas/
NK060(i)001:12688: yul dang 'phrad pa'i thugs rjes mngon spyod kyi phrin
NK060(i)001:12689: las kyis 'dul bar gyur pa'i dus la bab par
NK060(i)001:12690: mkhyen to // te zhes pa ni lhag ma can
NK060(i)001:12691: te 'og nas 'dul bar byed pa dngos dang sbrel
NK060(i)001:12692: mkhyen to // lo // spyi don gnyis pa gleng gzhi rang gi ngo bo la bcu bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:12694: dang po ting nge 'dzin gyi cho 'phrul bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:12696: gdul bya bstan pa la de/
NK060(i)001:12698: de bzhin bshegs pa che ba'i rdo rje bkod pa
NK060(i)001:12699: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba lha yab
NK060(i)001:12701: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyi
NK060(i)001:12702: bdag po bdud ru drar 'dul ba'i thabs yang dag
NK060(i)001:12703: pa'i nga rgyal chen pos ru dra zil gyis gnon
NK060(i)001:12704: pa'i gzi brjid ston pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:12705: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK060(i)001:12706: rdo rje'i bdag po rgyal ba kun tu bzang po
NK060(i)001:12707: de bcom ldan 'das chos thams cad bsam gyis mi
NK060(i)001:12708: khyab pas na dgyes pa chen po de nyid khro
NK060(i)001:12709: bo rgyal po rigs lnga'i he ru ka'i yang rgyal
NK060(i)001:12710: por gyur pa/ che mchog he ru kas gtso byas
NK060(i)001:12711: pa'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin chen po rnam
NK060(i)001:12712: par 'phro ba'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyal po'i ting
NK060(i)001:12713: nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas so //
NK060(i)001:12714: gnyis pa che mchog longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor/
NK060(i)001:12716: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings kun tu bzang mo'i ngang
NK060(i)001:12717: nyid las khro mo'i dbang phyug chen mo mngon du
NK060(i)001:12718: phyug ste/ hi hi zhes pas dgyes shing tshim pa'i
NK060(i)001:12719: gad mo dang gzi mdangs kyis 'dod rgu 'byung ba
NK060(i)001:12720: rin cen yum gyi gsang ba'i pad+ma bde bas dgyes
NK060(i)001:12721: phyug ste/ par mdzad nas/ thabs shes rab gnyis su
NK060(i)001:12722: med par 'khril ba'i dgyes pas byang chub kyi sems
NK060(i)001:12723: nyi zla gnyis su med par thim nas dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:12724: thams cad bskyed pa'i rgyud gyur pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12725: gsum pa kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul/
NK060(i)001:12727: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems kyi ye
NK060(i)001:12728: shes lnga'i sprin las sku gsung thugs sna tshogs rdo
NK060(i)001:12729: rje khro bo 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyis sgrol cig
NK060(i)001:12732: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la
NK060(i)001:12733: man+da la phata phata phata ha la ha la ha
NK060(i)001:12734: la h+aum zhes pa'i sngags brjod pas/
NK060(i)001:12735: yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams nas khro bo 'chol ba dpag tu med pa 'phros nas/
NK060(i)001:12736: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad mer mer shig shig tu gyur te/
NK060(i)001:12737: ru dra 'khor dang bcas pa zil gyi gnon cing bag 'khums par byed do //
NK060(i)001:12740: khro bo'i sprul pa spro ba ni gnas gang du
NK060(i)001:12741: na 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas khyab
NK060(i)001:12742: par/ gang spro na khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs de rnams so //
NK060(i)001:12743: che chung gi tshad ji tsam na/
NK060(i)001:12744: stong gsum gyi stong chen po 'jig rten khams tsam mo //
NK060(i)001:12745: mang nyung gi tshad ji tsam na/
NK060(i)001:12746: phyogs bcu'i rdul phra mo snyed 'thon par gyur nas so //
NK060(i)001:12747: lnga pa byin rlabs kyi cho 'phrul/
NK060(i)001:12749: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad phyogs cha drug tu g.yos tshabs che bas rab tu g.yos/
NK060(i)001:12750: khyab cing tshabs ches che bas kun tu g.yos so //
NK060(i)001:12751: de yang nang dang sbyar na de bzhin nyid kyi
NK060(i)001:12752: ting nge 'dzin las g.yo thob goms pa'i nyams gsum
NK060(i)001:12753: bogs thon pa'o // de bzhin du 'ur 'ur/
NK060(i)001:12756: nang du kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin la bogs gsum thon pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12760: nang du phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin la bogs gsum thon pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12761: shig shig /rab tu shig shig /kun tu shig shig go //
NK060(i)001:12762: nang du phyag rgya spros bcas kyi ting nge 'dzin la bogs gsum thon pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12766: nang du tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi ting nge 'dzin la bogs gsum thon pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12767: drug pa chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul/
NK060(i)001:12769: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i stong khams thams cad
NK060(i)001:12770: na gnas pa'i dbang che ba ma h+aa de ba
NK060(i)001:12771: dang / gzi brjid che ba tshangs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12772: mthu che ba'i lha khyab 'jug dang /
NK060(i)001:12773: dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa thams cad khams 'khrugs nas dran pa nyams shing brgyal/
NK060(i)001:12776: sems myos shing kun tu brgyal bar gyur to //
NK060(i)001:12777: bdun pa sprul pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor/
NK060(i)001:12779: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul bstan pa de nas bcom
NK060(i)001:12780: ldan dgyes pa chen po che mchog he ru ka
NK060(i)001:12781: de nyid 'jigs byed chen po zhal shin tu rngams
NK060(i)001:12782: pa/ bdud dang log 'dren thams cad skyi bung zhes
NK060(i)001:12783: byed pa'i me dpung 'bar ba chen po'i klong na
NK060(i)001:12784: 'dod chags zad par byed pa'i rtags su khrag 'thung
NK060(i)001:12785: pa/ zhing / dbang drag gi las mthar phyin pa'i
NK060(i)001:12786: rtags su sku mdog smug nag /gdul bya 'dul thabs
NK060(i)001:12787: gcig tu ma nges pa'i rtags su mdzad pa cir
NK060(i)001:12788: pa/ zhing / yang 'gyur la/ dbu dang phyag dang zhabs stong khams kyi rdul snyed tsam yod pa/
NK060(i)001:12789: rdo rje dang 'khor lo la sogs pa'i mtshon cha
NK060(i)001:12790: sna tshogs 'dzin pa de dag kyang stong pa nyid
NK060(i)001:12791: kyi ye shes las 'phros pa'i khro bo thams cad
NK060(i)001:12792: rnam thar gsum dang ldan pa'i rtags su dbu gsum/
NK060(i)001:12793: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i rtags su phyag drug
NK060(i)001:12794: /rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags
NK060(i)001:12796: dur khrod chen por yab yum gnyis su med par
NK060(i)001:12797: rol pas dgyes nas khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:12798: na keng rus chen po'i ri rab kyi steng gi
NK060(i)001:12799: me ri 'bar ba chen po'i klong dkyil na/
NK060(i)001:12800: gzhal yas khang gi dbus kyi lte ba la dbang phyug chen po dang /
NK060(i)001:12801: dur khrod kyi bdag po dregs pa chen po ru
NK060(i)001:12802: dra pho mo byi chings su bsnol ba'i khyo shugs
NK060(i)001:12803: kyi gdan la zhabs brkyang bskum du bzhugs so //
NK060(i)001:12804: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor byang chub kyi sems ye shes lnga las 'phros pa'i sprin phung de dag kyang /
NK060(i)001:12805: la la me long lta bu'i ye shes las 'phros
NK060(i)001:12806: pa'i khro bo thams cad ni dpal khrag 'thung chen
NK060(i)001:12807: po bud+d+ha he ru kar gyur te shar phyogs su
NK060(i)001:12808: bzhugs so // la la mnyam pa nyid kyi ye
NK060(i)001:12809: shes las 'phros pa'i khro bo thams cad ni dpal
NK060(i)001:12810: khrag 'thung chen po rin po cher gyur te lho
NK060(i)001:12812: la la so sor rtog pa'i ye shes las 'phros
NK060(i)001:12813: pa'i khro bo thams cad ni dpal khrag 'thung chen
NK060(i)001:12814: po pad+ma he ru kar gyur te nub phyogs su
NK060(i)001:12815: bzhugs so // la la bya ba grub pa'i ye
NK060(i)001:12816: shes las grub pa'i khro bo thams cad ni dpal
NK060(i)001:12817: khrag 'thung chen po kun tu las su gyur te
NK060(i)001:12819: de dag kun kyang 'jigs byed chen po'i cha lugs dpal gyi chas brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:12820: zhal nas h+aum h+aum phata phata la sogs pa'i gsung
NK060(i)001:12821: rngam pa'i nga ro dang bcas pas me dpung 'bar
NK060(i)001:12822: ba'i klong na/ dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis shar du dri za pho mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12823: de bzhin du byang du gnod sbyin dang /
NK060(i)001:12825: lhor gshin rje pho mo la sogs pa la khyo shugs pho kha sbub dang /
NK060(i)001:12826: mo gan rkyal gyi gdan la zhabs brkyangs bskum du bzhugs so //
NK060(i)001:12827: btsun mo khrag 'thung chen mo'i tshogs rnams kyang badz+ra
NK060(i)001:12828: kro ti shwa ri ma badz+ra he ru ka'i sku
NK060(i)001:12829: la 'khril ba bzhin/ rigs so so'i khro bo'i sku
NK060(i)001:12830: la rang rang gi rigs kyi yum rnams 'khril ba'i
NK060(i)001:12832: brgyad pa phrin las rmad du byung ba'i ngo bo/
NK060(i)001:12834: sprul pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa la de/
NK060(i)001:12835: phrin las rmad du byung ba sgrol ba ston pas na nas/
NK060(i)001:12836: dregs pa chen po ru dra la sogs pa gtum
NK060(i)001:12837: pa'i sems kyis gdug pa'i rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs bstan
NK060(i)001:12838: nas/ 'khor rnams dang mgrin gcig tu gdug pa'i nga ros ngag barlanga po'i gtum tshig gis smras pa/
NK060(i)001:12839: thong thog khyod snying rje'i bdag po yin na ci
NK060(i)001:12840: de ltar byed dam zhes 'dzer zhing shin tu gdug
NK060(i)001:12841: pa'i sems kyis khros nas da rung rngam mo //
NK060(i)001:12842: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po he ru ka de dbu dgu/
NK060(i)001:12844: zhabs brgyad du gnas nas thugs rjes 'dul ba'i thabs kyis shin tu khros nas/
NK060(i)001:12845: rngam pa'i gyad kyis pho rnams kyi lus ngag yid
NK060(i)001:12846: gsum sku gsung thugs su sdud pa'i phyir h+aum h+aum
NK060(i)001:12847: h+aum dgyes pa'i gad mos srog dbugs la rngam pa'i
NK060(i)001:12848: phyir ha ha ha/ lhag ma ma lus par zhal du gsol ba'i phyir kh+aa hi kh+aa hi kh+aa hi/
NK060(i)001:12849: zhes brjod pa dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa
NK060(i)001:12850: gdug pa chen po'i tshogs de dag gi bdag 'dzin
NK060(i)001:12851: rtsad gcad pa'i phyir snying dang /
NK060(i)001:12852: 'byung ba'i sgo dgag pa'i phyir dbang po kun phyung /
NK060(i)001:12853: mngon par zhen pa dag par bya ba'i phyir nang khrol kun drangs/
NK060(i)001:12854: las ngan gyi bag chags rtsad nas gcad pa'i phyir yan lag kun gcad gtubs nas/
NK060(i)001:12855: gti mug zad par bya ba'i phyir sha kun zos/
NK060(i)001:12856: 'dod chags zad par bya ba'i phyir khrag kun 'thung /
NK060(i)001:12857: zhe sdang zad par bya ba'i phyir rus pa kun 'chos so //
NK060(i)001:12860: pho rnams bsgral nas btul bas na de/
NK060(i)001:12861: mo rnams sbyor nas 'dul bas na nas/
NK060(i)001:12862: h+aum h+aum h+aum gsum ni mo rnams kyi lus ngag yid gsum dbang du sdud pa'o //
NK060(i)001:12863: dbang phyug ma g.yog yang g.yog dang bcas pa dbang du sdud pa'i sngags/
NK060(i)001:12864: b+h+yo e a ra li dzahdzahzhesa brjod pas/
NK060(i)001:12865: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams nam mkha' dang bcas
NK060(i)001:12866: par yungs 'bru gcig tsam du chud par bsdus so
NK060(i)001:12867: // don du na dregs pa can rnams kyi rnam shes h+aum du bsdus te/
NK060(i)001:12868: rgyu des chos thams cad sems su gcig par mthong ba'o //
NK060(i)001:12869: bsdus pa de nas 'byung po ma lus pa'i rgyal po'i yang rgyal po/
NK060(i)001:12870: dregs pa chen po la sogs pa'i chung ma/
NK060(i)001:12871: 'byung po thams cad kyi rje mo'i yang rje mo/
NK060(i)001:12872: srin po d+ha sha gri ba'i chung ma srin mo chen mo srin mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12873: lha tshangs pa'i chung ma tshangs ma dang /
NK060(i)001:12874: lha chen po'i chung ma 'khrug mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12875: brgya byin gyi chung ma dbang mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12876: khyab 'jug chung ma 'jug sred ma dang /
NK060(i)001:12877: gdong drug gi chung ma gzhon nu ma dang drug ni shar gyi ma mo rnams so //
NK060(i)001:12878: 'jug sred kyi chung ma dmar mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12879: lha'i bu nyi ma'i chung ma bdud rtsi mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12880: zla ba'i chung ma zhi ba mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12881: srin po rdo rje'i chung ma be con ma dang /
NK060(i)001:12882: srin po skya ring khrag mig gi chung ma srin mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12883: lha za byed kyi chung ma za ba mo dang drug ni lho'i ma mo rnams so //
NK060(i)001:12884: dga' byed dbang phyug gi chung ma dga' ba mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12885: stobs bzang gi chung ma ra ro khrag 'thung myos ma dang /
NK060(i)001:12886: b+h+ring gi ri ti'i chung ma gcig pur spyod ma dang /
NK060(i)001:12887: 'dod lha'i chung ma yid 'phrog ma dang /
NK060(i)001:12888: nor srungs kyi chung ma grub mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12889: rlung lha'i chung ma rlung mo dang drug ni nub kyi ma mo rnams so //
NK060(i)001:12890: lha gsod rkyen gyi chung ma gsod byed mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12891: me lha'i chung ma me mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12892: sa bdag chen po'i chung ma phag mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12893: gshin rje rgan byed kyi chung ma dang rgan byed mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12894: bgegs kyi rgyal po bi na ya ka'i chung ma sna chen mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12895: klu'i chung ma chu lha mo dang drug ni byang gi ma mo rnams so //
NK060(i)001:12896: lha nag po chen po'i chung ma nag mo chen mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12897: ra gdong chen po'i chung ma ra mgo dmar ser chen mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12898: srin po bum sna'i chung ma bum sna sngo nag chen mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12899: lha gsus po che'i chung ma gsus 'dzin ser nag
NK060(i)001:12900: chen mo dang bzhi ni sgo bzhir gnas pa'i ma
NK060(i)001:12901: mo rnams so // de la sogs pa ma mo'i tshogs las byed pa bran dang /
NK060(i)001:12902: de'i yang las byed pa yang bran dang /
NK060(i)001:12903: bkur stir byed pa g.yog dang /
NK060(i)001:12904: de la yang bkur sti byed pa yang g.yog dang
NK060(i)001:12905: bcas pa 'khor zhing gi rdul snyed rnams kyang bsdus
NK060(i)001:12906: so // bcu pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor/
NK060(i)001:12908: 'khor dbang du bsdus nas da yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:12909: dkyil 'khor ston pas na de nas zhes 'brel sbyar
NK060(i)001:12910: ro // bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal
NK060(i)001:12911: khrag 'thung che mchog he ru ka chen po des
NK060(i)001:12913: yang rigs lnga'i 'jigs byed chen po lngar ma mo rnams kyi ngor snang bar byas nas/
NK060(i)001:12914: de dag kun dgyes pas rol pa las khro bo'i
NK060(i)001:12915: dkyil 'khor gyi sprin 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i ting
NK060(i)001:12916: nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas sku dang gsung
NK060(i)001:12917: dang thugs rdo rje las 'di phyung ngo //
NK060(i)001:12918: sku gsung thugs kyi snying po +amo +aahh+aum gsum dang /
NK060(i)001:12919: gsang ba'i rdo rjes gsang ba'i pad+ma kha phyed bas
NK060(i)001:12920: bde bas dgyes pa'i sngags badz+ra pra be sha a
NK060(i)001:12924: zhes brjod pas 'khor bsdus pa'i cho 'phrul gyis 'byung
NK060(i)001:12925: po'i rgyal mo rnams shin tu chags pa'i yid g.yos
NK060(i)001:12926: nas/ pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor sdud cing bde bar rgyas par gyur nas/
NK060(i)001:12927: dper na rdo khab len la lcags 'du ba'i tshul du/
NK060(i)001:12928: dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad bcom ldan 'das dgyes
NK060(i)001:12929: pa chen po dpal khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i sku la
NK060(i)001:12930: 'khril te/ dbus kyi gtso bo la phyogs kyi gtso mo bzhi dang sgo ma bzhi ste brgyad/
NK060(i)001:12931: rigs kyi he ru ka bzhi la sogs kyi ma mo lnga lnga 'khril lo //
NK060(i)001:12932: de yang bcom ldan 'das khrag 'thung chen po rdo
NK060(i)001:12933: rje'i sku badz+ra he ru ka la shar gyi dbang
NK060(i)001:12934: mo'i gtso mo srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo
NK060(i)001:12936: nub kyi dga' ba mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12937: byang gi gsod byed mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12938: sgo ma bzhi la shar sgo'i nag mo chen mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12939: lho sgo'i dmar ser chen mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12940: nub sgo'i sngo nag chen mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12941: byang sgo'i ser nag chen mo rnams 'khril to //
NK060(i)001:12942: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po bud+d+ha he ru ka'i sku la shar gyi ma mo lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:12948: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po rin po
NK060(i)001:12949: che'i sku rat+na he ru ka la lho'i ma mo
NK060(i)001:12950: lnga ste/ bdud rtsi mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12955: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung pad+ma chen po'i sku
NK060(i)001:12956: pad+ma he ru ka la nub kyi ma mo lnga
NK060(i)001:12957: ste/ khrag gi myos ma dang /
NK060(i)001:12962: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po kun tu
NK060(i)001:12963: las kyi sku karma he ru ka la byang gi
NK060(i)001:12964: ma mo lnga ste/ me mo dang /
NK060(i)001:12969: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de dag gis h+aum zhes brjod pas/
NK060(i)001:12970: dbang mo'i pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs rdo rjes bsdus
NK060(i)001:12971: nas shin tu rol pa la bcum par gyur to
NK060(i)001:12972: // bcu gnyis pa ngo mtshar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor la bzhi/
NK060(i)001:12977: ngo mtshar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ston pas na de nas zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:12978: rigs kyi he ru ka dang /
NK060(i)001:12979: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad sbyor ba mdzad pas/
NK060(i)001:12980: dgyes te ha zhes brjod pas sbyor mtshams nas byang chub kyi sems kyi sprin ha'i tshogs 'phros pa las/
NK060(i)001:12981: dbang phyug ma re re'i mkha' nas gnas ma brgyad
NK060(i)001:12982: po yang re re 'thon nas phrin las bsgrub pa
NK060(i)001:12983: ni/ dkar mo'i tshogs koo r+ai ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis zhi ba'i las bsgrub pa dang /
NK060(i)001:12984: rkun mo'i tshogs tsoo r+ai ma sa dbang gi las dang /
NK060(i)001:12985: rmongs mo'i tshogs pra mo has zhi ba'i las dang /
NK060(i)001:12986: thal byed ma'i tshogs bee ta lis drag po'i las dang /
NK060(i)001:12987: sbos mo'i tshogs puk+ka sis rgyas pa'i las dang /
NK060(i)001:12988: gtum mo'i tshogs kasma ris drag po'i las dang /
NK060(i)001:12989: sme sha can gyi tshogs sme sha nis las gang 'dod dang /
NK060(i)001:12990: ma tshogs ma'i tshogs tsan+d+ha lis 'phel ba'i las bsgrub pa ste/
NK060(i)001:12991: de rnams re re yang tshogs zhes pa'i sgras nyi
NK060(i)001:12992: shu rtsa brgyad brgyad rang rang gi lag cha dang
NK060(i)001:12993: bcas pa ste/ koo r+ai ban dmar byin dbyug sngo //
NK060(i)001:12994: zhes pa la sogs pa bzhin/
NK060(i)001:12995: rngam zhing rngam pa rgyan chas dang ldan pa/
NK060(i)001:12996: ngo mtshar ba'i tshul du ma dang bcas nas dbang
NK060(i)001:12997: phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad po re re'i mkha'
NK060(i)001:12998: nas gnas ma brgyad po re re sras kyi tshul
NK060(i)001:12999: du 'thon to // 'thon nas kyang 'bar ba chen
NK060(i)001:13000: po'i 'khor lo'i rtsibs mchan la dkar mo la sogs
NK060(i)001:13001: du 'thon to // pa bzhi dang / gru chad la sbos mo la sogs pa bzhi ste brgyad/
NK060(i)001:13002: shar phyogs nas g.yas bskor gyis 'khor bar za za
NK060(i)001:13003: 'cha' 'cha' 'dra ba 'jigs pa'i gzugs don rtags dang
NK060(i)001:13004: mthun par rang rang gi lag cha dang bcas nas
NK060(i)001:13005: 'khod do // yul ma brgyad gdon pa/
NK060(i)001:13007: koo r+ai 'thon pa de nas slar yang shin tu
NK060(i)001:13008: dgyes nas he zhes brjod pas sbyor mtshams byang chub
NK060(i)001:13009: sems kyi sprin las/ he'i tshogs 'phros pa las dbang
NK060(i)001:13010: phyug ma re re'i mkha' nas yul ma brgyad po
NK060(i)001:13012: thams cad zil gyis gnon pa seng gdong chen mo'i tshogs nyer brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:13013: dpa' brtul gyis drag po'i las byed pa stag gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:13014: thabs mkhas pas phung po'i bdud dag par byed pa wa gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:13015: lha'i bu'i bdud 'joms par byed pa khyi gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:13016: shes bya la thogs pa med pa bzhad gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:13017: 'khor ba dang du len pa dur bya'i gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:13018: nyon mongs pa zad par byed pa khwa gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:13019: gdul bya phra ba yang mi 'dor ba 'ug gdong
NK060(i)001:13020: chen mo'i tshogs rnams re re yang nyer brgyad nyer
NK060(i)001:13021: brgyad/ sid+ha kha ro bsnol ser seng //
NK060(i)001:13022: zhes pa la sogs pa bzhin rang rang gi lag
NK060(i)001:13023: cha ngo mtshar dang bcas nas dbang phyug ma nyi
NK060(i)001:13024: shu rtsa brgyad kyi mkha' nas 'thon par gyur to
NK060(i)001:13025: // 'thon nas kyang 'bar ba chen mo'i 'khor lo'i phyi rol gser gyi snam bu la/
NK060(i)001:13026: shar la sogs pa'i phyogs bzhir seng gdong ma la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13027: shar lho nas mtshams bzhir bzhad gdong ma la sogs pa bzhis 'khor bar/
NK060(i)001:13028: ro rlon pa mgo g.yon du bstan pa dang nyi ma'i gdan la rngam pa'i mdangs kyis 'khod do //
NK060(i)001:13031: yul ma 'thon pa de nas shin tu dgyes pas
NK060(i)001:13032: phyogs bcu'i zhing ma lus par khyab nas phata ces
NK060(i)001:13033: brjod pas/ dbang rtags rdo rje rtse lnga pas dbu
NK060(i)001:13034: brgyan pa 'khor ba mi gtong ba sring 'gro stag
NK060(i)001:13036: phrin las gdong tshugs su byed pa rdo rje gdong mo phag gdong ma'i tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:13037: thams cad sreg par byed pa rdo rje 'jig rten dred gdong ma'i tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:13038: khams gsum slar 'tsho ma rdo rje ro langs spyang gdong ma'i tshogs rnams/
NK060(i)001:13039: stag gdong sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK060(i)001:13040: zhes pa la sogs pa bzhin rang rang gi lag
NK060(i)001:13041: cha dang rgyan chas dang ngo mtshar du bcas nas
NK060(i)001:13042: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi mkha' nas 'thon
NK060(i)001:13043: par gyur to // 'thon nas kyang 'bar ba'i dkyil
NK060(i)001:13044: 'khor gyi shar la sogs pa'i sgo bzhir shin tu
NK060(i)001:13045: rngam pa'i gzugs kyis ro dang nyi ma'i gdan la
NK060(i)001:13046: zhal phyir bstan nas gnas so //
NK060(i)001:13048: rgyud kyi skabs nas dbang phyug ma la sras tshogs bskyed par 'dug la/
NK060(i)001:13049: nyams len gyi dus su rigs lnga yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams nas sras tshogs bskyed pas/
NK060(i)001:13050: rgyud sgrub thabs kha gam mo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:13052: rgyud kyi skabs su mo rnams sbyar te btul ba dang /
NK060(i)001:13053: bu mos ma 'dul ba'i dgos pa yod pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:13054: dbang mo dang sbyor ba'i sbyor mtshams nas bskyed pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:13055: nyams len gyi dus su las kyi srin mo la mos pa mi skye bas/
NK060(i)001:13056: rigs kyi yum lnga dang sbyor ba'i sbyor mtshams nas bskyed pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:13057: yang ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad la sras tshogs khro
NK060(i)001:13058: mo nyi shu las med pas ma bu ma 'cham
NK060(i)001:13059: mo zhe na/ skyon med de/
NK060(i)001:13060: ma dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad mo re re la yang /
NK060(i)001:13061: sras khro mo nyi shu nyi shu 'thon par 'bru bsnon gyi skabs su bshad zin no //
NK060(i)001:13062: de dag gis phata ces brjod pas thams cad khros par bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13064: sras kyi tshogs 'thon pa de nas dgyes pa chen
NK060(i)001:13065: po'i byang chub sems kyi sprin las phyogs bcu nas
NK060(i)001:13066: phata ces bsgrags pas/ khro mo thams cad shin tu
NK060(i)001:13067: yang khros nas ma mo thams cad kyang rang rang
NK060(i)001:13068: gi gnas ga la ba der yud tsam gyis phyin
NK060(i)001:13070: bcu gsum pa phrin las kyi 'bras bu dregs pa can gnas bstabs pa la yang gsum/
NK060(i)001:13072: gnas bstabs pas snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin thob pa/
NK060(i)001:13075: mo rnams dang sbyor ba de nas bcom ldan 'das
NK060(i)001:13076: dgyes pa chen po dpal khrag 'thung chen po de
NK060(i)001:13077: dag kun kyang gcig tu thim nas badz+ra he ru
NK060(i)001:13078: kar gyur pa/ thugs rje chen po bdud rtsi 'byung
NK060(i)001:13079: ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK060(i)001:13080: zhugs nas sku dang gsung thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i
NK060(i)001:13081: rdo rje las byung ba dbang rdzas/
NK060(i)001:13082: phyi bdud rtsi dri chen rlon sbyor/
NK060(i)001:13083: nang nyi zla byang chub kyi sems 'di byung ngo //
NK060(i)001:13084: gong du dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa'i dregs
NK060(i)001:13085: pa can thams cad kyi yan lag kun bcad gtubs
NK060(i)001:13086: khrag 'thung sha zos rus pa kun 'chos nas/
NK060(i)001:13087: lto ba kyi dbyings kyi pho brang na yod pa la/
NK060(i)001:13088: bcom ldan 'das khro bo chen po de dag gis
NK060(i)001:13089: bsnam zhes pa'i 'og sgo nas dar sgong gi tshul
NK060(i)001:13090: du bton te/ spyan sngar 'dug pa de la slar
NK060(i)001:13091: yang bsnam zhes pa 'og sgo nas phyi ltar khro
NK060(i)001:13092: bo uts+tshush+ma kro d+ha rme ba brtsegs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13093: nang ltar dam rdzas dri chen rlon sbyor phyung nas
NK060(i)001:13094: dbang bskur ba'i sngags +amo ni ye shes lnga dang
NK060(i)001:13095: ldan pa'o // badz+ra ma h+aa a mri ta ma
NK060(i)001:13096: h+aa kro ta zhes pa rdo rje khro bo 'chi
NK060(i)001:13097: ldan pa'o // med chen po ste/ nang ltar bdud rtsi gcig kyang lnga lngar byin gyis brlabs/
NK060(i)001:13098: am am am zhes lan gsum brjod cing lce'i steng du dam rdzas lan gsum bzhag pas/
NK060(i)001:13099: sngar mi gtsang ba'i 'dam gyi rgya mtshor chud pa
NK060(i)001:13100: de las mi gtsang ba'i 'dam kun khro bo rme
NK060(i)001:13101: brtsegs kyis 'thung te/ dbang thob pa'i byin rlabs kyis
NK060(i)001:13102: dran pa slar rnyed nas rtog tshogs thams cad sku
NK060(i)001:13103: dang ye shes su gsal bar gyur te khro bo
NK060(i)001:13104: bsam yas lhun grub kyi ting nge 'dzin thob bo
NK060(i)001:13105: brtsegs kyis 'thung te/ // de'i tshe dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs de dag thams cad kyang dbu brgya/
NK060(i)001:13108: sku 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor na bzhugs pa mthong ngo //
NK060(i)001:13109: snang ba rnam 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin thob pa'i
NK060(i)001:13110: de'i dus su 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i srid
NK060(i)001:13111: pa kun tu dregs pa'i dbang phyug thams cad 'dul
NK060(i)001:13112: ba'i thabs mi mthun pa sna tshogs bsam gyis mi
NK060(i)001:13113: khyab par so sor snang bas dus gcig tu btul
NK060(i)001:13114: lo // dam bcas nas lus gdan du phul ba/
NK060(i)001:13116: gnas bstabs pa de nas dregs pa can de dag
NK060(i)001:13117: shin tu lus 'dar zhing yid bred pas sems rab
NK060(i)001:13118: tu zhum pas nga ros 'bangs su mchi/
NK060(i)001:13120: gal te 'bangs su nan tan ma bgyis na mgo dang lus ni tshal pa brgyar 'gas shing /
NK060(i)001:13121: de bzhin du snying yang 'gas shing dum bur gtub
NK060(i)001:13122: par gyur cig /lus rul myags tshig nas sems ngan
NK060(i)001:13124: dmyal bar ltung nas sdug bsngal zhing 'o 'dod 'bod
NK060(i)001:13125: par shog cig ces 'bangs su mchi bar mna' bor
NK060(i)001:13126: nas lus dkyil 'khor gyi gdan du phul nas gzhag
NK060(i)001:13129: dregs pa'i bdag po thams cad kyis ngag mthun par
NK060(i)001:13130: mgrin gcig tu lus phul nas yang 'khor 'bul ba
NK060(i)001:13131: smras pa/ bdag cag rnams kyi mchis brang dang /
NK060(i)001:13132: ma dang srin mo bu mo rnams dkyil 'khor chen por bzhes su gsol lo //
NK060(i)001:13133: nyam nga med pa'i dpa' bo lha chen po nyi
NK060(i)001:13134: shu rtsa brgyad kyi yang rje bo 'khor bzhes su
NK060(i)001:13135: gsol lo // zhes 'khor rnams phul nas/
NK060(i)001:13136: phyi rabs kyi rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi dgongs pa
NK060(i)001:13137: 'grub par dam bcas pa ni bdag cag so so'i
NK060(i)001:13138: 'khor bcas rnams kyis/ khro bo'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:13139: chen po 'di'i ming tsam 'dzin par byed pa'i rnal
NK060(i)001:13140: 'byor pa yang dper na lha'i dbang po dang /
NK060(i)001:13141: klu'i dbang po'i spyi bo na gtsug gi nor bu rin po che 'bar ba de lha bran dang /
NK060(i)001:13142: klu bran rnams kyis mthong ma thag phyag ma byas
NK060(i)001:13143: na mgo bo 'gas pas mi bkur ba'i kha stabs
NK060(i)001:13144: med pa ltar/ sems la g.yo sgyu med cing gus
NK060(i)001:13145: pa dang ldan par sems kyis blangs te spyi bo'i
NK060(i)001:13146: gtsug tu bzhag nas bkur bar bagyi'o //
NK060(i)001:13149: rab lta ba dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa gtsug gi nor bur ltar du mthong zhing 'khur/
NK060(i)001:13150: 'bring ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa rje dpon dbang po che ltar du mthong zhing 'khur/
NK060(i)001:13151: tha ma spyod lam dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK060(i)001:13152: de spyan 'dren ngo chen ltar du mthong zhing 'khur
NK060(i)001:13153: la/ yang tha dam la mi gnas pa'i rnal 'byor
NK060(i)001:13154: pa ni bka' chad kyi gnas su mthong zhing 'khur
NK060(i)001:13155: ba lta ga la srid do //
NK060(i)001:13156: zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:13157: des na dam la gnas pa'i rnal 'byor pa de'i
NK060(i)001:13158: dgos pa ci yang rung ba ma lus rdzogs par
NK060(i)001:13159: bdag cag rnams kyis bsgrub bo //
NK060(i)001:13160: gal te dpa' bo dpal chen he ru ka'i spyan
NK060(i)001:13161: sngar 'dir smras pa khas blangs bzhin du ma bsgrubs
NK060(i)001:13162: na/ bdag cag rnams kyi mgo 'gas lus gtubs snying dum bur gyur nas rul bar mchi'o //
NK060(i)001:13163: zhes mna' bor ba'i tshig de dag smras so //
NK060(i)001:13164: bcu bzhi pa phrin las kyi 'bras bu 'khor dam la btags pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13166: mna' bor ba de nas de dag gi chung ma'i tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:13168: ma dang bu mo'i tshogs thams cad dkyil 'khor du
NK060(i)001:13169: yud tsam gyis 'ongs nas thams cad kyis mgrin gcig
NK060(i)001:13170: tu smras pa/ bdag cag ru dra 'khor tshogs thams
NK060(i)001:13171: cad kun kyang dpa' bo chen po'i 'bangs su mchi'o
NK060(i)001:13172: tu smras pa/ // dpa' bo chen pos bdag cag
NK060(i)001:13173: rnams la phrin las kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol
NK060(i)001:13174: tu smras pa/ // zhes smras so // de nas
NK060(i)001:13175: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po 'khor rnams kyi
NK060(i)001:13176: lag tu rdo rje byin nas rdo rje mi srin
NK060(i)001:13177: mo la sogs pa ming gi dbang bskur te/
NK060(i)001:13178: dkyil 'khor gyi khyams kyi phyi rol du bkod do //
NK060(i)001:13179: 'o na le'u bco lnga pa 'dir gsungs pa'i ru
NK060(i)001:13180: dra 'di rang rgyud pa yin nam sprul pa ba
NK060(i)001:13181: yin/ rang rgyud pa yin na lung man ngag rig pa gsum dang 'gal ba'i skyon yod de/
NK060(i)001:13182: lung dang 'gal ba'i skyon ni 'di nyid las/
NK060(i)001:13183: khro bo'i tshogs chen po de dag kyang dbu dgu brgya/
NK060(i)001:13186: sku 'bar ba chen po'i klong na bzhugs pa mthong ngo zhes gsungs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13187: man ngag ni 'grel pa lung bstan las/
NK060(i)001:13188: mthu 'di dag rang rgyud pa la yod pa ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:13189: sprul pa ba yin pa la som nyi mi bya'o zhes pa dang 'gal la/
NK060(i)001:13190: rigs pa ni sdig pa gang che che bas 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur/
NK060(i)001:13191: ci ste na ru dra rang rgyud par 'dug pas so //
NK060(i)001:13192: yang ru dra sprul pa ba yin na lung man ngag rig pa gsum dang 'gal te/
NK060(i)001:13193: lung dang 'gal ba'i skyon ni 'di nyid las/
NK060(i)001:13194: bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtog pas btags pa la mngon par zhen pa zhes pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13195: man ngag ni spar khab las/
NK060(i)001:13196: las ngan pa dang nyon mongs pa rang kha ma'i bag chags rnams so //
NK060(i)001:13198: rig pa ni sprul pa ba de rang la dgos ched med par 'gyur/
NK060(i)001:13199: ci ste na gdul bya rang rgyud pa med pas so //
NK060(i)001:13200: yang phyis 'byung bar dogs nas sdigs bskur ba yin no zhes na/
NK060(i)001:13201: de la dgos ched med de/
NK060(i)001:13202: sngar dngos su ma byung na phyis kyang 'byung bar mi 'gyur te/
NK060(i)001:13203: rgyu rkyen la khyad par med pa'i phyir ro zer na/
NK060(i)001:13204: 'di la rgya gab gong pa na re/
NK060(i)001:13205: 'dir dngos su byung ba ni sprul pa ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:13206: 'di dag cha lugs mthun pa'i rang rgyud pa mthu
NK060(i)001:13207: 'di tsam med par yang yod pas gnyis ka ltar
NK060(i)001:13208: shes par bya'o zhes gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:13209: gtsang pa byin ston na re/
NK060(i)001:13210: dngos su byung ba 'di rang sprul pa rang rgyud gnyis ka yin te/
NK060(i)001:13211: mthar lam nas mdzad pa bcu gnyis ston pas sprul pa yang yin la/
NK060(i)001:13212: bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa yod pas rang rgyud pa yang yin gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:13213: rje sgro phug pa ni 'grel pa lung bstan phyag
NK060(i)001:13214: tu ma byung gi bar du rang rgyud par bzhed
NK060(i)001:13215: la/ phyag tu byung tshun chod sprul pa bar bzhed mod kyis/
NK060(i)001:13216: kho bo ni 'di ltar sems te/
NK060(i)001:13217: spyir gyis sprul pa dang rang rgyud kyi mtshan nyid gang la byed brtag par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:13218: sngar mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas zin pa zhig
NK060(i)001:13219: sems can gyi don du thugs rjes las sprul pa
NK060(i)001:13220: ba la sprul pa bar byed/
NK060(i)001:13221: lam mas rim gyis rgyud sbyangs pa'i lam la gnas
NK060(i)001:13222: pa dang sangs rgyas pa zhig mas sbyangs rang rgyud
NK060(i)001:13223: par byed na/ snga rabs pa rnams kyi bzhed pa
NK060(i)001:13224: dang 'gal spong thams cad nyung ma'i g.yos lta bur
NK060(i)001:13225: par byed na/ gsal/ yon tan gyi snang tshul can la sprul par byed/
NK060(i)001:13226: skyon gyi snang tshul can la rang rgyud par byed na/
NK060(i)001:13227: sems can gyi don du sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i rnam par 'phrul par rngon pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13228: smad 'tshong ma la sogs par sprul pa rnams kyang rang rgyud pa yin par thal ba dang /
NK060(i)001:13229: zag bcas kyi bsod nams cha mthun las grub pa'i bdud srin gyi rigs mngon shes dang /
NK060(i)001:13230: rdzu 'phrul du ma dang ldan pa rnams kyang sprul pa ba yin par thal ba'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK060(i)001:13231: gal te sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i sprul
NK060(i)001:13232: pa sdig can dang nyam thag pa la sog par
NK060(i)001:13233: sprul pa ni dgos ched kyi dbang gis de lta
NK060(i)001:13234: bu'i tshul bstan pa yin no zhe na/
NK060(i)001:13235: 'o na tshul bstan pa de dag dang rjes su
NK060(i)001:13236: mthun par gsungs pa'i lung rnams la gang zag gi
NK060(i)001:13237: blos dpags par mi nus te/
NK060(i)001:13238: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams
NK060(i)001:13239: kyi mdzad pa ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i phyir
NK060(i)001:13240: ro // 'on kyang lung la rjes su dpags pa'i
NK060(i)001:13241: dbang du byas na bskal pa bzang po 'di 'das
NK060(i)001:13242: ro // pa'i 'og tu/ 'jig rten gyi khams thal bas khebs ba pa zhes bya bar/
NK060(i)001:13243: de bzhin gshegs pa thal ba'i dbang po'i dbyangs su
NK060(i)001:13244: mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar spyi mdo dgongs
NK060(i)001:13245: pa 'dus pa nas lung bstan pa nges lung du
NK060(i)001:13246: byas nas/ 'chad bzhin pa'i mdo sde myang 'das kyi lung rang bzhin la dgongs pa'am/
NK060(i)001:13247: dus gzhan la dgongs pa'i lung du byas nas ru dra rang rgyud pa kho na yin la/
NK060(i)001:13248: yang mdo sde mya ngan 'das pa las/
NK060(i)001:13249: rigs kyi bu de'i tshe de'i dus na bdud sdig to can ni nga nyid de/
NK060(i)001:13250: gzhan du ma rtog cig ces pa'i lung nges lung du byas nas/
NK060(i)001:13251: dgongs 'dus kyi lung bstan drang lung du byas nas sprul pa kho na yin gyis/
NK060(i)001:13252: shes rgyud gcig gi steng du sprul pa rang rgyud
NK060(i)001:13253: gnyis dus gcig la tshang bar 'dod pa ni blun
NK060(i)001:13254: po ti thug pa rnams kyi 'dod rgyal du rig
NK060(i)001:13255: par bya'o // yang kha cig /dngos su byung ba
NK060(i)001:13256: 'di sprul pa rang rgyud gang rung du khas len
NK060(i)001:13257: par bya'o // zhing / de dang cha mthun gyi
NK060(i)001:13258: gcig shos kyang yod par 'dod pa ni mi rigs
NK060(i)001:13262: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:13263: khro bo rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi sprin rnam
NK060(i)001:13264: par spros pa'i gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pas
NK060(i)001:13265: na le'u ste yas bgrangs bco lnga pa'i don du
NK060(i)001:13266: gada'o////da ni le'u bcu drug pa 'chad par byed pa
NK060(i)001:13267: la/ chos tshoms kyi dbang du byas nas/
NK060(i)001:13268: rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam ston/
NK060(i)001:13269: snang ba bzhi las lam snang ston/
NK060(i)001:13270: lam la thabs grol gnyis las grol lam ston/
NK060(i)001:13271: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa ston/
NK060(i)001:13272: mtshan nyid gsum las rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ston/
NK060(i)001:13274: de la bcu las khro bo gsung gi dkyil 'khor ston/
NK060(i)001:13278: tha ma'i bcu las bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud dang /
NK060(i)001:13279: gzhan yang spyi 'gro rnams kyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:13280: de ltar ston pa'i le'u bcu drug pa 'di la gsum/
NK060(i)001:13282: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:13284: khro bo rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:13285: da de dag gi sngags kyi dkyil 'khor ston pas na de nas zhes 'brel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:13286: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos khro bo'i dkyil
NK060(i)001:13287: 'khor gyi tshogs chen po 'di dag sngags kyi dam
NK060(i)001:13288: tshig gi tshul bsgrub par bya ba'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:13289: de bzhin bshegs pa khro bo khrag 'thung chen po
NK060(i)001:13290: rigs lnga btsun mo dang bcas pa'i tshogs de dag
NK060(i)001:13291: gi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang rdo rje ye
NK060(i)001:13292: shes rngam pa'i nga ro dang bcas pa bsgrags pa
NK060(i)001:13293: las lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:13294: gyi don 'og nas 'byung ba'i 'di dag phyung ngo
NK060(i)001:13296: gsung gi dkyil 'khor dang de'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:13297: dang po la spyi don gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:13298: lha rnams kyi sngags sam snying po dang /
NK060(i)001:13299: spyan drang pa la sogs pa las kyi rim pa'i sngags so //
NK060(i)001:13300: spyi don dang po la yang gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:13302: dang po khrag 'thung yab yum bcu'i rtsa ba bskyed pa las sngags dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:13304: 'dir mngon par rtogs pa'i go rim sdebs ma shes
NK060(i)001:13305: na bdud rtsi ro nyams lta bu'i bshad pa'i skyon
NK060(i)001:13306: yod pas/ khro bo'i chog khrigs bsdus pa tsam sdebs pa'i dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:13311: gzhung dang mthun pa'i gnas su mchod shoms gzhung bzhin byas la/
NK060(i)001:13316: byin dbab mchod pa byin gyis brlab bo //
NK060(i)001:13317: dngos gzhi gzhung don la khro bo 'byung ba'i gleng gzhi bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13318: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang zhing bstim pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13319: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul ba/
NK060(i)001:13324: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i
NK060(i)001:13325: skabs su dang po rtsa ba ltar ting nge 'dzin
NK060(i)001:13326: gsum bsgom/ de nas gzhal yas khang bsgoms la/
NK060(i)001:13327: le'u bcu bdun pa nas 'byung ba ltar tshig gi gsal gdab/
NK060(i)001:13328: bdag sras le'u bco lnga pa bzhin du ngo mtshar tshogs kyi lha tshogs sum cu bskyed/
NK060(i)001:13329: gzhan sras 'di nas bshad pa'i sngags kyis bskyed/
NK060(i)001:13330: le'u bcu bdun pa bzhin tshig gis gsal gdab dbang bskur byin brlab rtsa ba ltar bya/
NK060(i)001:13331: 'di nas bshad pa bzhin ye shes pa spyan drang ba nas brtsams te/
NK060(i)001:13332: gzhung bsrang la bstod cing 'dzab bzlas so //
NK060(i)001:13340: spyod lam rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin la gnas par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:13341: de yang bdag sras kyi lha tshogs rnams ting nge
NK060(i)001:13342: 'dzin gyi 'ju 'dul gyis so so'i gdan thog tu
NK060(i)001:13343: 'od kyi rang bzhin du gnas pa la cho ga
NK060(i)001:13344: gsum gyis he ru ka yab yum du bskyed la/
NK060(i)001:13345: mkha' gsang brlabs sbyor ba'i brda bskul nas rol pa byas pas/
NK060(i)001:13346: yab yum gyi mkha' las khrag 'thung sum cu tham
NK060(i)001:13347: pa yig 'brur gnas pa la bskyed sngags rnams brjod
NK060(i)001:13348: pa lhar bskyed cing phyir bton la dkyil 'khor la
NK060(i)001:13349: dgod/ dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni sbyor mtshams nas mi bskyed de/
NK060(i)001:13350: thugs ka nas b+h+yo nyi shu rtsa brgyad 'phros nas
NK060(i)001:13351: phyi khyams la gnas pa la ma nu rak+sha si
NK060(i)001:13352: zhes pa la sogs pa bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags
NK060(i)001:13353: kyis bskyed de/ phata dza zhes pa'i sngags kyis phyi
NK060(i)001:13354: ru bton nas rang rang gi gnas su 'khod pa
NK060(i)001:13355: kyis bskyed de/ la/ +amo +aahh+aum zhes brjod pas/
NK060(i)001:13356: sku gsung thugs nus ldan du byin gyis brlab cing /
NK060(i)001:13357: +amo ye shes lnga dang ldan pa ste rtsa ba'i sngags so //
NK060(i)001:13358: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka zhes pa ni snying po'i sngags te sku bskyed pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13359: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da
NK060(i)001:13360: ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata ces pa ni
NK060(i)001:13361: gtum po chen pos sdang ba thams cad rtogs shig
NK060(i)001:13362: /sbyor cig /choms shig /tshoms shig /sku gsung thugs su
NK060(i)001:13363: bsdus la/ gnyis su med par sgrol cig pa ste bzlas pa las kyi sngags so //
NK060(i)001:13365: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kroti shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata ces pa ste/
NK060(i)001:13366: nyams len gyi skabs su yab yum gyi sngags sdebs pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:13367: de bzhin du bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum gyi sngags ni/
NK060(i)001:13368: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he
NK060(i)001:13369: ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha
NK060(i)001:13370: na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata/
NK060(i)001:13371: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa kro ti shwa kro ti shwa r+ai sarba dush+tana h+aum phata/
NK060(i)001:13372: rat+na he ru ka yab yum gyi sngags ni/
NK060(i)001:13373: +amo rat+na ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa
NK060(i)001:13374: tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK060(i)001:13376: +amo ma h+aa s+au r+ya rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa r+ai b+hi d+ha ma h+aum phata/
NK060(i)001:13377: pad+ma he ru ka yab yum gyi sngags ni/
NK060(i)001:13378: +amo pad+ma ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa
NK060(i)001:13379: tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK060(i)001:13381: +amo hri shwa ta sa man+ta pad+ma ma h+aa kro ti shwa r+ai kh+aa hi h+aum phata/
NK060(i)001:13382: karma he ru ka yab yum gyi sngags ni/
NK060(i)001:13383: +amo karma ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa
NK060(i)001:13384: tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK060(i)001:13386: +amo sarba a mo ga kar+m+aa d+ha ra ma h+aa
NK060(i)001:13387: kro ti shwa r+ai bi shwa h+aum phata zhes pa
NK060(i)001:13388: rnams so // gnyis pa gnas yul sgo ma nyi shu bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags la gsum/
NK060(i)001:13390: gnas ma brgyad bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags/
NK060(i)001:13392: +amo ye shes lnga dang ldan pa/
NK060(i)001:13393: badz+ra ni rdo rje ste dbang rtags rdo rje rtse lnga pas dbu brgyan pa kun la 'agre'o //
NK060(i)001:13395: ha rtsa ba'i sa bon no //
NK060(i)001:13396: de bzhin du badz+ra tsoo r+ai ha/
NK060(i)001:13404: yul ma brgyad kyi bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags/
NK060(i)001:13406: sngar bzhin dbang rtag rdo rje rtse lnga pas dbu
NK060(i)001:13407: brgyan pa'i khro mo'i lus la phra men gyi gdong
NK060(i)001:13408: pa can rnams te/ badz+ra sing ha mu kh+ai he/
NK060(i)001:13409: badz+ra bya gri mu kh+ai he/
NK060(i)001:13410: badz+ra sh+r+ai g+aa la mu kh+ai he/
NK060(i)001:13411: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai he/
NK060(i)001:13412: badz+ra g+h+ri d+ha mu kh+ai he/
NK060(i)001:13413: badz+ra kam ka mu kh+ai he/
NK060(i)001:13414: badz+ra kh+aa kha mu kh+ai he/
NK060(i)001:13415: badz+ra u lu ka mu kh+ai he/
NK060(i)001:13417: sgo ma bzhi bskyed pa rkyen gyis sngags so //
NK060(i)001:13419: dbang rtags rdo rje rtse lngas dbu brgyan pa'i sgo skyong ma bzhi bskyed pa'i sngags ni/
NK060(i)001:13420: badz+ra ar+ya te dza teng dza/
NK060(i)001:13423: badz+ra basmi ba la ya ba to hoh gsum pa
NK060(i)001:13424: dbang mo rnams kyi rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i
NK060(i)001:13426: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i thugs ka nas dbang mo rnams kyi rtsa ba'i sngags sam sa bon/
NK060(i)001:13427: phyi khyams dmar po la shar gyi ma drug gi rtsa sngags/
NK060(i)001:13428: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo/
NK060(i)001:13429: lho'i ma drug gi rtsa sngags/
NK060(i)001:13430: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo/
NK060(i)001:13431: nub kyi ma drug gi rtsa sngags/
NK060(i)001:13432: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo/
NK060(i)001:13433: byang gi ma drug gi rtsa sngags/
NK060(i)001:13434: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo/
NK060(i)001:13438: 'di dag la ma nu rak+sha si b+h+yo zhes pa la sogs pa bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags kyis/
NK060(i)001:13439: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK060(i)001:13440: zhes pa la sogs pa'i sku mdog phyag mtshan can
NK060(i)001:13441: rgyan chas dang ldan pa'i skur bskyed pa yin no
NK060(i)001:13442: // spyi don gnyis pa spyan drang ba la sogs pa'i las kyi rim pa'i sngags la drug /bgrang /
NK060(i)001:13443: dang po snyan gsan dbab pa'i sngags/
NK060(i)001:13445: chos sku skye ba med pa'i ngang la ri dwags la rdzi ba skyod pa'i tshul du/
NK060(i)001:13446: lha tshogs lnga bcu rtsa brgyad gzugs skur rongs kyis
NK060(i)001:13447: bzhengs nas byon la ma reg par mos pas se
NK060(i)001:13449: ru lu ru lu ru lu h+aum zhes pa'i sngags kyis nyan gsan dbab pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13453: mathe'u chung sbrel ba'i lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas e h+ye
NK060(i)001:13454: hi zhes bod pa'i sgras a na ya zhes pas
NK060(i)001:13455: skye ba med pa'i dbyings rnam par dag pa rang
NK060(i)001:13456: bzhin gyi gnas nas/ chos sku las gzugs sku rongs kyi bzhengs pa de rnams/
NK060(i)001:13458: h+aum byams pa'i zhags pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13459: bam dga' ba'i lcags sgrog dang /
NK060(i)001:13460: hohbatanga snyoms kyi dril bus mdun gyi nam mkha' la rim par spyan drangs nas/
NK060(i)001:13461: ram zhes pas dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor dang me ri 'dab 'byor du gnas par bsgom mo //
NK060(i)001:13462: rig pa'i me tog dor ba'i/
NK060(i)001:13464: ye shes rdo rje khro bo'i dam tshig gis bsdus shig ces pa'i sngags/
NK060(i)001:13465: +amo badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya h+aum zhes brjod cing /
NK060(i)001:13466: ye shes dang dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor sku gsung
NK060(i)001:13467: thugs yon tan phrin las dbyer mi phyed pa cig
NK060(i)001:13468: gi ngo bor gsal la rtog pa med par bsgom
NK060(i)001:13469: pa ni rig pa'i me tog dor ba zhes bya'o
NK060(i)001:13472: +amo yi ge cha lnga pas ni glu'i 'go 'dren pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:13473: dregs pas khro bo'i gdul bya la mthun pa 'dul
NK060(i)001:13474: ba'i tshul gyis thugs rjes khros pa'i tshul bstan pas
NK060(i)001:13475: dregs pa can gyi gdul bya zhi bar mdzad pa
NK060(i)001:13476: ni thugs rje chen po gzhan gyi dpal lo //
NK060(i)001:13477: thugs rjes khros pa'i tshul gyi dpal chen rngam pa'i
NK060(i)001:13478: tshogs khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi byin rlabs
NK060(i)001:13479: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las gzhan las khyad
NK060(i)001:13480: par du gyur pas na rmad po che de nyid
NK060(i)001:13481: dus da lta nyid du ni bdag la stsal du
NK060(i)001:13482: gsol cig ces gsol ba btab nas/
NK060(i)001:13483: slar yang gnad nas bskul ba na /
NK060(i)001:13484: +amo badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya s+t+wam/
NK060(i)001:13485: +amo badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya hoh +amo badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya phata/
NK060(i)001:13486: ces pa'i sngags brjod pa'i don ni/
NK060(i)001:13487: ye shes rdo rje khro bo'i dam tshig gis bdag
NK060(i)001:13488: dang gnyis su med par mdzod cig /mnyes par mdzod
NK060(i)001:13489: cig /bdag gi gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa sgrol cig
NK060(i)001:13490: pa ste/ sngags des thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul bas
NK060(i)001:13491: dgyes nas lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs ka nas yig
NK060(i)001:13492: 'bru phata nag po grangs med pa 'phros nas bdag
NK060(i)001:13493: pa ste/ la phog pas/ gnyis 'dzin gyi sgrib pa
NK060(i)001:13494: bral nas lha rtog gnyis med kyi dngos grub thob
NK060(i)001:13495: pa ste/ la phog pas/ par bsam mo // drin lan gyi tshul du mchod pa/
NK060(i)001:13497: mchod par dbul rgyu gang zhe na/
NK060(i)001:13498: +aa li u li zhes pa la sogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:13502: ta pa li na bca' ba'i tshogs rnams so //
NK060(i)001:13503: dbul ba'i gnas gang la zhe na/
NK060(i)001:13504: damsh+ta zhes pas mche ba can rgyal ba rigs lnga'i tshogs dang /
NK060(i)001:13505: go na roo tri zhes pas yon tan dra mo'i tshogs khro mo nyi shu dang /
NK060(i)001:13506: kha ram yo gi ni zhes pas zhal 'bar ba'i
NK060(i)001:13507: tshogs rnal 'byor nyer brgyad la sogs pa la dbul
NK060(i)001:13508: lo // tshul ji ltar dbul zhe na/
NK060(i)001:13509: kh+aa hi ho zhes pa ni gsol cig /mnyes par mdzod cig pa'i tshul gyis so //
NK060(i)001:13510: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la bstim pa'i sngags so //
NK060(i)001:13515: phata kyis sgo ma rnams rim pa bzhin bstim mo //
NK060(i)001:13516: de yang lha la lha thim/
NK060(i)001:13517: gzhal yas khang la gzhal yas khang thim ste/
NK060(i)001:13518: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang dam tshig gi dkyil
NK060(i)001:13519: 'khor gnyis chu dang 'o ma 'dres pa bzhin dbyer
NK060(i)001:13520: med du gyur par bsam mo //
NK060(i)001:13523: zhes gsung gi dkyil 'khor gyi don de dag brjod
NK060(i)001:13524: pas 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad bzlas
NK060(i)001:13525: pa las kyi sngags kyi mathu'am byin rlabs kyis kun
NK060(i)001:13526: tu btags pa'i rnam par rtog pa thams cad mi
NK060(i)001:13527: gnas par byas pas na tshig /tshabs che bas na
NK060(i)001:13528: rab tu tshig /khyab cing tshabs che bas kun tu
NK060(i)001:13529: tshig go // bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags kyi mathu'am
NK060(i)001:13530: byin rlabs kyis rtog tshogs lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal
NK060(i)001:13531: tshig go // zhing 'bar/ tshabs che bas rab tu 'bar/
NK060(i)001:13532: khyab cing tshabs che bas kun tu 'bar ro //
NK060(i)001:13533: spyan drang ba la sogs pa'i sngags kyi mathu'am byin
NK060(i)001:13534: rlabs kyis dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor thams cad du
NK060(i)001:13535: 'bar ba khro bo'i lha ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:13537: tshabs che bas na rab tu gang /
NK060(i)001:13538: khyab cing tshabs che bas na kun tu gang bar gyur to //
NK060(i)001:13541: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las mtshan gyi gzhi ru gda'/
NK060(i)001:13542: le'u bco lnga pa'i skabs su bshad pa'i khro bo'i
NK060(i)001:13543: tshogs chen po'i gsung sngags kyi dkyil 'khor rtsa ba
NK060(i)001:13544: bskyed pa las rim gyi sngags la sogs pa spros
NK060(i)001:13545: pa'i gcod cing 'tshams 'dzin par byed pas na le'u
NK060(i)001:13546: ste yas bgrangs bcu drug pa'o////da ni le'u bcu bdun
NK060(i)001:13547: pa 'chad par byed pa la chos tshoms kyi dbang
NK060(i)001:13548: du byas na/ rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam ston/
NK060(i)001:13549: lam la thabs grol gnyis las grol lam/
NK060(i)001:13550: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa ston/
NK060(i)001:13551: snang ba bzhi las lam snang /
NK060(i)001:13552: mtshan nyid gsum las rkyen 'jug pa ston no //
NK060(i)001:13553: 'bring gi chos lnga las rgyud don/
NK060(i)001:13554: de la bcu las khro bo'i sku dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ston/
NK060(i)001:13556: lha sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin ston/
NK060(i)001:13558: tha ma'i chos bcu las spyi don bsdu ba dang spyi 'gro gsum ston no //
NK060(i)001:13559: de ltar ston pa'i le'u bcu bdun pa la gsum/
NK060(i)001:13561: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:13563: le'u bcu drug par lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor sngags kyi rim pa rnams bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:13564: da lhag pa ting nge 'dzin sku dang thugs kyi
NK060(i)001:13565: dkyil 'khor ston pas na de nas zhes 'brel sbyar
NK060(i)001:13566: ro // bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos ni 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:13567: gsang sngags kyi dkyil 'khor de dag gis sku dang
NK060(i)001:13568: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa bstan pa'i phyir 'og
NK060(i)001:13569: nas 'byung ba'i don ched du brjod pa 'di dag
NK060(i)001:13570: brjod do // le'u'i gzhung la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:13571: sku'i dkyil 'khor dang sku'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:13573: rten gzhal yas khang dang brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13574: rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa la yang gnyis/
NK060(i)001:13576: ngo bo rgyan dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:13578: 'bar ba chen po khro bo'i gzhal yas khang ni ye shes lnga dang ldan pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:13579: rtags 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dbus kyi lte ba dang lnga pa/
NK060(i)001:13580: bden pa bzhi dang ldan pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:13581: rtags gru chad bzhi'i rnam pas mdzes par brgyan pa/
NK060(i)001:13582: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:13583: rtags phyi'i dbyibs gru bzhi pa/
NK060(i)001:13584: rnam thar bzhi dang ldan pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:13585: rtags sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan pa/
NK060(i)001:13586: bden pa gnyis dang ldan pa don yin la/
NK060(i)001:13587: rtags phra men dang dbang phyug ma'i 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis kyis mdzes pa/
NK060(i)001:13588: thod pa sna tshogs pa brtsigs pa'i kha bad sbrul
NK060(i)001:13589: chen gyi zhags pas mgul nas drangs pa'i d+r+wa ba
NK060(i)001:13590: d+r+wa phyed kyi tshugs su byas pa chu srin chun
NK060(i)001:13591: po'i kha nas 'dzag pa'i ta ra na dang /
NK060(i)001:13592: sna tshogs thod pa'i bar nas nyi ma 'od zer
NK060(i)001:13593: 'phro bas brjid pa me'i 'od rdo rje rtse lnga
NK060(i)001:13594: pa'i dbyibs su 'bar ba sprul pa'i khro chung phyi
NK060(i)001:13595: nang du 'phro ba mang po 'khrug pa'i gzhal yas
NK060(i)001:13598: gti mug ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags shar
NK060(i)001:13599: gyi 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du khyu mchog /nga rgyal
NK060(i)001:13600: ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags/
NK060(i)001:13601: lho'i 'khor lo'i rtsib steng du ma he/
NK060(i)001:13602: 'dod chags ma spang gnas su dag pa'i rtags nub kyi 'khor lo'i rtsib steng du gzig dang /
NK060(i)001:13603: phrag dog ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags/
NK060(i)001:13604: byang gi 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du stag /zhe sdang ma spang gnas su dag pa'i rtags/
NK060(i)001:13605: dbus kyi lte ba la gtum pa dom rnams kyi
NK060(i)001:13606: sbar bas ni phrin las nan tur du bstan par
NK060(i)001:13607: bya ba'i phyir 'khor lo dbus su/
NK060(i)001:13608: 'jig rten gyi dbang phyug lha chen po dregs pa
NK060(i)001:13609: ru dra pho mo byi chings su bsnol ba dang
NK060(i)001:13610: la sogs pa'i sogs khongs nas shar du dri za/
NK060(i)001:13613: byang du gnod sbyin pho mo/
NK060(i)001:13614: de rnams kyang pho kha sbub dang /
NK060(i)001:13615: mo gan rkyal du bsgyel ba'i pho rnams kyi sog phrag dang /
NK060(i)001:13616: mo rnams kyi nu phrag nas bzung ba ste/
NK060(i)001:13617: de dag ni dreg pa can zil gyis gnon pa'i gdan zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:13618: yon tan gyi che ba rang snang ba'i gdan ni nyi zla pad+ma gsum brtsegs so //
NK060(i)001:13619: gnas yul sgo ma nyi shu'i gnas su ro dang nyi ma'i gdan no //
NK060(i)001:13620: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni rang rang stan
NK060(i)001:13621: dang lag cha dang zhes pas gdan rang chas so
NK060(i)001:13622: // gnyis pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa la gsum/
NK060(i)001:13624: dang bo sku mdog sku'i tshul dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:13626: le'u bcu drug pa'i skabs su bdag sras rgyu'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)001:13627: gzhan sras 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor sngags kyis bskyed pa de dag gi tshul rgyas par le'u 'dir ston te/
NK060(i)001:13629: rigs mi 'gyur zhing phrin las drag po mdzad pa'i
NK060(i)001:13630: phyir bud+d+ha he ru ka sku mdog smug nag /badz+ra
NK060(i)001:13631: he ru ka sngo nag /rat+na he ru ka ser
NK060(i)001:13632: nag dang / pad+ma he ru ka dmar nag /karma
NK060(i)001:13633: he ru ka ljang nag /thams cad kyang shin tu
NK060(i)001:13634: 'jigs pa'i sku rnam par thar pa gsum dang ldan
NK060(i)001:13636: ye shes drug gis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i rtags
NK060(i)001:13637: su phyag drug /rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang
NK060(i)001:13638: ldan pa'i rtags su zhabs bzhi gyad kyi dor thabs
NK060(i)001:13639: su bgrad pa/ gzhan yang nyi zla bye ba'i 'od
NK060(i)001:13640: zer dus gcig la 'phro ba lta bus brjid cing
NK060(i)001:13641: rngam pa'i sgra chen gshe zhing myur bar bzhad pas
NK060(i)001:13642: 'jigs pa'i nga ro ha ha dang phata phata dang
NK060(i)001:13643: su bgrad pa/ / ru lu ru lu la sogs pa sna tshogs par sgrogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13646: 'bar ba chen po'i lha tshogs de dag kyang dur
NK060(i)001:13647: khrod kyi chas brgyad dang dpal gyi chas brgyad kyis
NK060(i)001:13651: byugs pa'i rdzas gsum dang brgyad las/
NK060(i)001:13652: bgo ba ko rlon gyi gos ni sna tshogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:13653: thabs mkhas phrin las kyi gos zhing gi g.yang gzhi/
NK060(i)001:13654: khyab pa thugs rje'i gos glang chen gyi ko rlon/
NK060(i)001:13655: phyi nang gsang ba sdud pa'i gos stag lpags kyi sham thabs rnams gyon pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13656: gdags pa sprul gyi rgyan dang thod phreng gi rgyan gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:13658: klu rgyal rigs dkar khras dbu brgyan pa/
NK060(i)001:13659: rje rigs ser khra'i snyan cha/
NK060(i)001:13660: bram ze'i rigs dmar khri'i mgur chu/
NK060(i)001:13661: dmangs rigs nag khra'i sku rags/
NK060(i)001:13662: gdol pa'i rigs ljang khri'i phyag gdub dang /
NK060(i)001:13665: thod pa skam po'i dbu rgyan/
NK060(i)001:13669: dpral ba'i g.yas su thal chen gyi tshom bu/
NK060(i)001:13670: smin dbrag tu rak+ta'i thig le/
NK060(i)001:13671: o la ko la zhag gi zo ris so //
NK060(i)001:13672: de dag ni rgyal byed dpa' rtags kyi rgyan zhes
NK060(i)001:13673: bya ba sngon du ru dra btul ba'i tshe ru
NK060(i)001:13674: dra'i rgyan rnams dpal chen po'i rgyan du mdzad pa
NK060(i)001:13675: ste/ dper na dpa' bos dgra bsad na de'i gos rgyan rang gis gyon pas bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:13677: gzi brjid 'bar ba chu srin brjid pa'i chas //
NK060(i)001:13678: thabs dang shes rab zung 'brel nyi zla'i chas //
NK060(i)001:13679: gdug pa can bsreg ye shes me yi chas //
NK060(i)001:13680: skye shi rtsad gcod mche ba zla tshes chas //
NK060(i)001:13681: khyab mdzad re skong rdo rje gshog pa'i chas //
NK060(i)001:13682: mnga' thang yongs rdzogs rdo rje lhag pa'i chas //
NK060(i)001:13683: sangs rgyas sar bgrod dbang gi bse khrab chas //
NK060(i)001:13684: gnod gdug zlog byed rgya gram lcags kyi chas //
NK060(i)001:13686: de dag la thugs rig pa rang snang gi rgyan zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:13687: don dang rtags su mi 'gal ba'o //
NK060(i)001:13688: gsum pa phyag mtshan bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13690: stong gi 'jig rten khor yug dang bcas pa ni/
NK060(i)001:13691: badz+ra he ru ka'i phyag g.yon mtha' ma'i phyag mtshan yin la/
NK060(i)001:13692: khrag 'thung rigs lnga char gyi phyag bar pa rnams g.yas rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'dzin pa/
NK060(i)001:13693: g.yon pa ni dung chen khrag gis gang ba 'khrug pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13694: karma he ru ka'i phyag g.yon gyi dang po na ral gri/
NK060(i)001:13695: rat+na he ru ka'i g.yon gyi mtha' ma na dgra s+t+wa/
NK060(i)001:13696: karma he ru ka'i g.yon gyi mtha' ma na thong
NK060(i)001:13697: gshol dang la sogs pa'i sogs khong nas rigs lnga
NK060(i)001:13698: rang rang gi lag cha mi mthun pa sna tshogs
NK060(i)001:13699: pa ste/ phyag g.yas kyi dang po rnams na rang rtags kyi phyag mtshan/
NK060(i)001:13700: badz+ra he ru ka'i rdo rje rtse dgu/
NK060(i)001:13701: bud+d+ha he ru ka'i 'khor lo rtsibs stong /
NK060(i)001:13702: rat+na he ru ka'i rin chen zur brgyad/
NK060(i)001:13703: pad+ma he ru ka'i pad sngon/
NK060(i)001:13704: gzhan yang bud+d+ha he ru ka'i g.yon gyi mtha' ma na kha t+w+aam ka dang /
NK060(i)001:13705: pad+ma he ru ka'i g.yon gyi mtha' ma na rnge'u
NK060(i)001:13706: chung sgra dang bcas pa bsnams shing rang rang rigs
NK060(i)001:13707: kyi btsun mo'i 'jigs pa'i tshogs rnams dang 'khril nas/
NK060(i)001:13708: yum gyi phyag g.yas pa shes rab kyi rtags dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK060(i)001:13709: g.yon pa dung khrag zhal du stob pa/
NK060(i)001:13710: sku mdog yab dang mthun pa/
NK060(i)001:13711: gzig gi sham thabs can no //
NK060(i)001:13712: gnas ma koo r+ai ma brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:13713: yul ma sing ha ma brgyad ni/
NK060(i)001:13714: rgyu ming 'bras bu la btags pa'am/
NK060(i)001:13715: gdul bya'i ming 'dul byed la btags pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:13717: koo ri ba na dmar byis dbyug sngo //
NK060(i)001:13718: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13719: yul ma brgyad kyi phyag rgya ni/
NK060(i)001:13720: sing ha kha ro bsnol seng ser //
NK060(i)001:13721: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13723: stag gdong sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK060(i)001:13724: zhes pa la sogs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:13725: khro mo nyi shu'i 'khor gyis rab tu mdzes shing /
NK060(i)001:13726: gzhan yang slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs ni
NK060(i)001:13727: dbang phyug ma bcu mtshan gnyis dang ya gyal ni
NK060(i)001:13728: brgyad de nyid shu rtsa brgyad kyis mdzes pa/
NK060(i)001:13729: mdza' mo'i 'khor rnams rang rang gi gdan zhing skam po re dang /
NK060(i)001:13730: sku mdog deng lag cha ni/
NK060(i)001:13731: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK060(i)001:13732: zhes pa la sogs pa dang mthun pa'i cha lugs
NK060(i)001:13733: can rnams bdag cag rnams kyis ci bgyi zhes zer
NK060(i)001:13734: bas ni las la chas te gnas so //
NK060(i)001:13735: 'di ni sgrub thabs dam pa rgyan dang mthun mod kyi/
NK060(i)001:13736: gzhan yang sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las/
NK060(i)001:13737: rdo rje rdo rje dril bu dang //
NK060(i)001:13739: de bzhin 'khor lo dgra s+t+wa dang //
NK060(i)001:13741: nor bu rin chen rgyu zhags dang //
NK060(i)001:13742: rdo rje dgra s+t+wa rab tu sdebs //
NK060(i)001:13743: chags mchog pad+ma chen po dang //
NK060(i)001:13744: dril bu rnga yi sgra sgrogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13745: las ni ral gri gshol chen dang //
NK060(i)001:13747: bar ma rdo rje dung dmar 'khrug /ti ra chen po rab sdebs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13750: g.yas dang po rang rtags su/
NK060(i)001:13756: zhes bshad kyang thugs rje la phyogs ris med pa la ji ltar mos pa ltar snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:13757: 'o na sku mdog dang phyag mtshan la sogs pa
NK060(i)001:13758: la nges pa med na nyams su ji ltar len
