NK060(i)001:13759: zhe na/ rgyud gzhung re re'i dbang du byas nas
NK060(i)001:13760: nges pa can du nyams su len zhes bla ma
NK060(i)001:13762: sku'i dkyil 'khor gyi yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:13764: zhes gzhung gi don de dag brjod pas 'jig rten
NK060(i)001:13765: drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa thams cad du
NK060(i)001:13766: dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad khrag
NK060(i)001:13767: 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du kun tu gsal bar
NK060(i)001:13770: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:13771: 'bar ba khro bo'i lhag pa ting nge 'dzin sku
NK060(i)001:13772: dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar bstan pa'i gcod
NK060(i)001:13773: cing mtshams 'dzin pas na le'u ste yas bgrangs bcu
NK060(i)001:13774: bdun pa'i don du gada'o////da ni le'u bco brgyad pa
NK060(i)001:13776: chos tshoms kyi dbang du byas na rab kyi chos
NK060(i)001:13777: tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las gzhi 'bras zur
NK060(i)001:13778: tsam ston/ lam gtso cher ston/
NK060(i)001:13779: snang ba bzhi las bzhi ka ston/
NK060(i)001:13780: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa/
NK060(i)001:13781: 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las rgyud don/
NK060(i)001:13782: de la bcu las mchod pa ston/
NK060(i)001:13787: tha ma'i chos bcu las rang bzhin lta ba/
NK060(i)001:13788: ldem dgongs man ngag /gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston no //
NK060(i)001:13789: de ltar ston pa'i le'u bco brgyad pa 'di la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:13791: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:13793: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa la de/
NK060(i)001:13794: khyad par gyi mchod pa ston pas na nas zhes bya la/
NK060(i)001:13795: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos zhes pa 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:13796: gnas su stob pa mnyes pa'i mchod pa phyi rgyud
NK060(i)001:13797: man chod kyi yul ma yin zhing rmad du byung
NK060(i)001:13798: bas na chen po 'di 'khor rnams kyi don gyi
NK060(i)001:13802: mchod pa'i 'bras bu de'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:13803: dang po mchod pa dngos la bzhi/
NK060(i)001:13805: zhe sdang sgrol ba'i mchod pa/
NK060(i)001:13807: sngar bstan pa'i lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil
NK060(i)001:13808: 'khor de la de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mchod cing
NK060(i)001:13809: / ma mo dang mkha' 'gro ma min pa 'di
NK060(i)001:13810: ni mchod sbyin gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas
NK060(i)001:13811: / na dam pa'o // de ni tshul ji lta bu zhe na/
NK060(i)001:13812: 'chad bzhin pa'i sbyor sgrol gnyis ka la rang bzhin
NK060(i)001:13813: gyi dbang po yul dus kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK060(i)001:13814: mngon du phyung ba'i thabs chen po'i sbyor sgrol dang
NK060(i)001:13815: lnga lngas ston te/ thog mar sgrol ba'i tshul lnga las/
NK060(i)001:13816: 'dir mtha' ma gnyis gtso bor bzung ste/
NK060(i)001:13817: de yang sgrol ba'i mchod pa'i dbang du thog mar rtogs pas bdag bsgral ba ni/
NK060(i)001:13818: bdag nyid kyis rtogs pa bzhi dang dag pa gsum
NK060(i)001:13819: dang mnyam pa gnyis kyi gtan tshigs kyi sgo nas
NK060(i)001:13820: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba rtogs shing nyams
NK060(i)001:13821: su lon/ cho ga lnga'i sgo nas ting nge 'dzin
NK060(i)001:13822: bsgom zhing stobs su byas nas gzung 'dzin gyi rnam
NK060(i)001:13823: rtog chos nyid kyi klong du bsgral lo //
NK060(i)001:13824: thugs rjes gzhan bsgral ba ni sngon du bdag bsgral ba/
NK060(i)001:13825: de nas sems nyid kyi gshis la bsgral bya sgrol
NK060(i)001:13826: byed gnyis su med par rtogs pa'i blo gdengs dang
NK060(i)001:13827: ldan pa de yis ni rgyu 'bras kyi don la
NK060(i)001:13828: rmongs pa'i blo ngan gyi 'jig rten pa bsgral ba'i
NK060(i)001:13829: zhing bcur gyur pa de dag ma bsgral na snying
NK060(i)001:13830: re rje bas/ thugs rjes gzung ba'i don du gnyis
NK060(i)001:13831: su med par chos kyi dbyings su bsgral bar bya
NK060(i)001:13832: re rje bas/ ste/ 'di dag gi tshul rgyas par
NK060(i)001:13833: le'u bcu gcig par bshad zin pas 'dir ma spros
NK060(i)001:13834: re rje bas/ ste/ so // 'dod chags sbyor ba'i mchod pa/
NK060(i)001:13836: sbyor ba'i tshul la yang lnga las/
NK060(i)001:13838: thabs lam steng sgo las su rung zhig log pa'i chags yid spangs pa'i rnal 'byor pas/
NK060(i)001:13839: pad+ma can la sogs pa'i bu mo mtshan nyid dang
NK060(i)001:13840: ldan pa yongs su sbyang ba dang gnyis po mkha'
NK060(i)001:13841: gsang bsnol mar brlab/ sbyor ba'i brda bsnol mar bskul nas/
NK060(i)001:13842: thabs shes rab phan tshun 'khril ba'i tshul gyi bsrub
NK060(i)001:13843: pa'i sbyor bas bde ba nyams su myong ba'i mchod
NK060(i)001:13844: pa chen po 'di ni bdag gzhan chos gsum gyis
NK060(i)001:13846: yab yum gnyis kyi byang sems dkar dmar dus mnyam
NK060(i)001:13847: du sbyor bas dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kun gyi
NK060(i)001:13848: bdag nyid rnal 'byor pa yab yum bde ba chen
NK060(i)001:13849: pos mnyes pas rgyal ba thams cad kyang mnyes par
NK060(i)001:13850: bya'o // 'di dag gi tshul rgyas par le'u dgu pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13851: bcu gcig par bshad zin pas 'dir ma spros so //
NK060(i)001:13852: gti mug dam rdzas kyi mchod pa/
NK060(i)001:13855: rang bzhin gyis mnyam pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13856: spyad pa las kyis mnyam pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13858: dam rdzas lnga dang ye shes lnga la bzang ngan
NK060(i)001:13859: med pa snang stong gnyis med kyi rang bzhin du
NK060(i)001:13860: mnyam pa ni rang bzhin gyi mnyam pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13863: sems can rtog pa bzlog phyir sman //
NK060(i)001:13864: gtso ru dang du blang bar bya //
NK060(i)001:13866: gtsang rme'i rtog pa bzlog nas mnyam pa nyid du
NK060(i)001:13867: longs spyod pa ni mnyam pa las kyi mnyam pa'o
NK060(i)001:13868: // de lta bu'i grub pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i
NK060(i)001:13869: rdzas chen bdud rtsi lnga po 'di dag grub tshul
NK060(i)001:13870: // ni bzhi ste/ chos nyid rang bzhin gyis chos
NK060(i)001:13871: can rang gi ngo bos mthus byin gyis brlabs kyis
NK060(i)001:13872: // ni bzhi ste/ grub pa'o // dang po ni/
NK060(i)001:13874: dngos po ma lus sems nyid phyir //
NK060(i)001:13875: mtshan nyid bral ba chos kyi dbyings //
NK060(i)001:13877: dam rdzas lnga'i rang bzhin sems nyid las mi gzhan
NK060(i)001:13878: pa'i phyir ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin las ma g.yos
NK060(i)001:13879: pa ni chos nyid rang bzhin gyis grub pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13881: rang bzhin bde ba'i ye shes lnga //
NK060(i)001:13882: byed po med par rang snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:13884: de dag kyang byed pa pos ma byas par ye
NK060(i)001:13885: shes lnga'i ngo bor rang snang ba ni chos can
NK060(i)001:13886: rang gi ngo bor grub pa'o //
NK060(i)001:13888: shes rab ting 'dzin thabs dag gis //
NK060(i)001:13889: nus mthus nges par 'byung ba yin //
NK060(i)001:13891: lta sgom ldan pa'i thabs kyi dam rdzas lnga la
NK060(i)001:13892: longs spyad pas mchog thun mong gi dngos grub 'grub
NK060(i)001:13895: 'di lta'i lam la gang gnas pa //
NK060(i)001:13896: phyogs dus kun nas byin gyis rlobs //
NK060(i)001:13898: dam rdzas lnga la longs spyod pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK060(i)001:13899: de la sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' ma
NK060(i)001:13900: mo dang mkha' 'gro thams cad kyi byin rlabs phyogs
NK060(i)001:13901: dus kun tu 'byung ba ni byin gyis brlabs kyis
NK060(i)001:13902: grub pa'o // des na bdag dam tshig sems dpa' dang /
NK060(i)001:13903: lha ye shes sems dpa' gnyis su med par mnyam
NK060(i)001:13904: pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs la 'khor gsum yongs
NK060(i)001:13905: dag gi mchod pa dbul ba ni 'bul byed 'bul
NK060(i)001:13906: rgyu'i dngos po gsum du 'dzin pa las grol pa
NK060(i)001:13907: ste/ phyi khang zhing nor rdzas bran khol la sogs pa la chags shing zhen pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13908: nang rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad yul gyi rjes su 'jug cing zhen pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13909: gsang ba lta sgom la mchog tu 'dzin pa'i zhen
NK060(i)001:13910: pa las grol nas ye shes chen por byed pa
NK060(i)001:13911: med pa'i ngang gnas par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:13914: bza' dang bca' dang btung ba ni ro'i bye brag rnams te/
NK060(i)001:13915: shin tu ro bro ba'i mchog tu gyur pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13916: bgo ba ni reg bya'i bye brag rnams te/
NK060(i)001:13917: 'jam zhing yang la bde ba rnams dang /
NK060(i)001:13918: de la sogs pa gzugs sdug pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13920: dri zhim po'i bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK060(i)001:13921: longs spyod lnga po ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pas
NK060(i)001:13922: thams cad 'dod yon gyi lha mor byin gyis brlabs
NK060(i)001:13923: pa rnams ni chu la chu thim pa'i tshul du
NK060(i)001:13924: dam tshig ye shes gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK060(i)001:13925: de la ni mchod pa'i lha mor byin gyis brlabs
NK060(i)001:13926: pa'i 'dod yon gyi dkyil 'khor de nyid gnyis su
NK060(i)001:13927: med par thim par rol lo //
NK060(i)001:13928: gnyis pa mchod pa'i 'bras bu la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:13932: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhir bdag don du yang dag pa'i sa dang /
NK060(i)001:13933: gzhan don du sems can gyi don la gshegs pa
NK060(i)001:13934: yi bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung
NK060(i)001:13935: thugs yon tan phrin las theg pa gzhan gyi 'bras
NK060(i)001:13936: bu las khyad par du gyur pa'i rmad po che
NK060(i)001:13937: de nyid/ rang sems sgrib pa dang bral ba las
NK060(i)001:13938: gzhan nas btsal du yod pa'am gzhan nas 'ongs pa
NK060(i)001:13939: de nyid/ ma yin te/ lha dang srin po la
NK060(i)001:13940: sogs pa'i mthu las byung ba ni smos kyang ci
NK060(i)001:13941: de nyid/ ma yin te/ dgos so // mchog gi 'bras bu'o //
NK060(i)001:13943: rnal 'byor pa ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba
NK060(i)001:13944: rnams kyis phyag rgya chen po lha'i sku rang rig
NK060(i)001:13945: pa'i mngon sum du rdzogs par 'gyur zhing /
NK060(i)001:13946: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal ba'i tshad yul
NK060(i)001:13947: gyis mi 'phrogs pa la brtan pa thob nas yid
NK060(i)001:13948: gnyis dang the tshom med par gyur pa na rgyal
NK060(i)001:13949: ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi dngos grub chen po 'bar bar
NK060(i)001:13950: 'gyur ro // gsum pa mchod pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:13952: zhes mchod pa 'bras bu dang bcas pa'i don de
NK060(i)001:13953: dag brjod pas gnas su stob cing mnyes par byed
NK060(i)001:13954: pa'i mchod pa don gnyis grub pas na chen po
NK060(i)001:13955: 'dis ni/ 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad du mchod pa'i sprin gyis khyab par gyur to //
NK060(i)001:13958: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las mtshan gyi gzhi ru gda'/
NK060(i)001:13959: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud man chod kyi mchod sbyin las khyad par du gyur pas na dam pa/
NK060(i)001:13960: dug gsum gyi mchod pa bstan pa'i gcod cing mtshams
NK060(i)001:13961: 'dzin par byed pas na le'u ste yas bgrangs bco
NK060(i)001:13962: brgyad pa'o////da ni le'u bcu dgu pa 'chad par byed
NK060(i)001:13963: pa la/ chos tshoms ngos bzung na/
NK060(i)001:13964: rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las gsum ka ston/
NK060(i)001:13965: snang ba bzhi las bzhi ka ston/
NK060(i)001:13967: mtshan nyid gsum las gsum ka /rim cig car gnyis
NK060(i)001:13968: las gnyis ka /thabs grol gnyis las gnyis ka /'bring
NK060(i)001:13969: gi chos lnga las rgyud don/
NK060(i)001:13970: de la bcu las dam tshig ston/
NK060(i)001:13973: tha ma'i chos bcu las rang bzhin lta ba/
NK060(i)001:13974: ldem dgongs man ngag /mtshon pa dpe/
NK060(i)001:13976: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:13977: de ltar ston pa'i le'u bcu dgu pa la gsum/
NK060(i)001:13979: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:13981: le'u bco brgyad pa khyad par gyi mchod pa bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:13982: le'u 'dir dam tshig gi bsrung mtshams ston pas na de nas zhes 'brel sbyar ro //
NK060(i)001:13983: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos zhes pa ni 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:13984: gsang sngags 'chad pa'i lam pa rnams lam la 'bad
NK060(i)001:13985: pa don yod pa'i bya ba'i phyir ma h+aa yo
NK060(i)001:13986: ga'i bsrung bya dam tshig chen po gzhan theg pa
NK060(i)001:13987: 'og ma'i 'dul sdom la sogs pa las khyad par
NK060(i)001:13988: du gyur pa 'di dag ched du brjod do //
NK060(i)001:13993: dam tshig gi che ba 'dul ba rnam par dag pa bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13994: dam tshig gi rnam grangs mdor bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13995: mnyam pa chen po dam tshig skyon yon dang bcas pa bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13996: dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon dang /
NK060(i)001:13997: dam tshig gi rang bzhin dang /
NK060(i)001:13998: dam tshig gi rnam grangs rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:13999: dam tshig gi yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:14004: lam dang 'bras bu gnyis ka gong na gzhan med
NK060(i)001:14005: pas bla na med pa'i theg par rtsa ba'i dam
NK060(i)001:14006: tshig lnga dang / yan lag gi dam tshig bco
NK060(i)001:14007: lnga nyams su lon cing don rab tu nges na
NK060(i)001:14008: nyon mongs pa lnga dang mi dge ba bcu/
NK060(i)001:14011: log pa brgyad la sogs pa'i las ngan rnams ma
NK060(i)001:14012: lus pa kun spyod pa ltar snang yang bsam pa
NK060(i)001:14014: thabs khyad pa can gyi gnad dang /
NK060(i)001:14015: rtogs pa lta ba'i gdengs gsum gyis zin pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:14016: las ngan pa byas pa la 'bras bu ngan song
NK060(i)001:14017: gsum gyi sdug bsngal mi gsog pa tsam lta ci
NK060(i)001:14018: smos/ bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis kyang rdzogs par 'gyur te/
NK060(i)001:14020: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa/
NK060(i)001:14021: sngags phyi rgyud kyi dam tshig rnams ched du ma
NK060(i)001:14022: bsrungs kyang 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin yon tan yar
NK060(i)001:14023: ldan du rdzogs pas na phun sum tshogs pa'i sdom
NK060(i)001:14024: pa zhes bya'o // de'i phyir lam 'bras gong na
NK060(i)001:14025: med pa bla med mchog gi dam tshig 'di dag
NK060(i)001:14026: tu gdul bya 'dul ba'i dbang gis so sor thar
NK060(i)001:14027: pa nyan thos kyi tshul khrims rtsa ba bzhi yan
NK060(i)001:14028: lag dang bcas pa'i bsrung bya kun dang /
NK060(i)001:14029: gzhan yang ji snyed pa'i sdom pa byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK060(i)001:14030: sngags phyi rgyud pa'i bsrung sdom bsam yas pa lhag
NK060(i)001:14031: ma ma lus pa kun kyang bla na med pa'i
NK060(i)001:14032: theg pa 'dir 'dus shing rnam par dag pa ste/
NK060(i)001:14033: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig chen po dang ldan pa'i
NK060(i)001:14034: rnal 'byor pas nyon mongs pa lnga la sogs pa
NK060(i)001:14035: spyod pa ltar snang yang 'dzin pa med par ltung
NK060(i)001:14036: bar mi 'gyur ba ni mi dge sdom pa'i tshul
NK060(i)001:14037: khrims gzhan don du 'gyur na srog gcod pa la
NK060(i)001:14038: sogs pa'i tshul mi 'dor ba ni sems can don
NK060(i)001:14039: byed kyi tshul khrims/ gang ltar spyod kyang sgo gsum
NK060(i)001:14040: sku'i phyag rgya chen po las mi 'da' ba ni
NK060(i)001:14041: dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims yin no //
NK060(i)001:14045: dang po srog gcod pa la srog gcod pa spong ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i man ngag /drang /
NK060(i)001:14046: bdag gzhan gnyis ka sems nyid kyi ngang du gsal
NK060(i)001:14047: ba'i dus na yod med dbu ma gsum gyi mtha'
NK060(i)001:14048: gang du'ang mi dmigs shing blo'i spyod yul las 'das
NK060(i)001:14049: pa ni don dam pa'i bden pa'o //
NK060(i)001:14050: 'o na bdag dang gzhan du snang ba 'di ci zhe na/
NK060(i)001:14051: kun rdzob rgyu rkyen 'dus pa log rtog gi ngo
NK060(i)001:14052: bo tsam du snang yang bden dngos kyis stong pa
NK060(i)001:14053: dper na sgyu ma'am mig shes 'khrul pas tho yor
NK060(i)001:14054: la mir 'dzin pa lta bu'i tshul lo //
NK060(i)001:14055: de'i phyir srog gcad bya gcod byed ka nas dag pa ste/
NK060(i)001:14056: gcad bya srog dmigs su med pas srog gcod byed
NK060(i)001:14057: kyi skyes bu dang gcod do ba'i 'du shes kyang
NK060(i)001:14058: dmigs su med pas na don dam par srog gcad
NK060(i)001:14059: du med kyang / kun rdzob tu gcad bya srog
NK060(i)001:14060: dang gcod byed skyes bur snang ba 'di ni log
NK060(i)001:14061: rtog rten 'brel gyi snang ba tsam du rtogs shing
NK060(i)001:14062: du med kyang / / de ltar bden pa gnyis
NK060(i)001:14063: kyang de nyid dang gzhan du brjod du med par
NK060(i)001:14064: rtogs nas thugs rjes zhing bcu'i srog gcad kyang bdag
NK060(i)001:14065: la sgrib pa mi bsog cing /
NK060(i)001:14066: gzhan la sdug bsngal mi bskyed pas na de la
NK060(i)001:14067: ni theg pa 'og ma bas srog gcod pa spangs
NK060(i)001:14068: pa'i yon tan zhor la rdzogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:14069: ma byin par len pa la ma byin par len
NK060(i)001:14070: pa spong ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i man ngag /drang
NK060(i)001:14071: / don dam pa dang kun rdzob kyi bden pa
NK060(i)001:14072: gnyis ka sems gnyis ka sems nyid kyi ngo bor
NK060(i)001:14073: dbyer med pas bdag dang gzhan du mi dmigs shing
NK060(i)001:14074: / / dper na lha 'phrul dag'i longs spyod rang la sprul nas rang gis spyod pa'i tshul te/
NK060(i)001:14075: blang bya dang len byed len no ba'i 'du shes
NK060(i)001:14076: gsum ka sems nyid kyi ngo bor tha dad min
NK060(i)001:14077: pas blang bya rdzas dang gzhan bdag po dang ma
NK060(i)001:14078: byin par len pa po bdag rnams dmigs su med
NK060(i)001:14079: pa'i phyir/ kun rdzob tu ma byin par len pa
NK060(i)001:14080: ltar snang yang don dam par blang bya blang byed
NK060(i)001:14081: pa'i phyir/ med de/ thams cad bdag nyid chen po
NK060(i)001:14082: mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings las ma 'das par rtogs
NK060(i)001:14083: nas gzhan don bsgrub pa'i phyir ma byin par len
NK060(i)001:14084: pa'i phyir/ med de/ pas ni/ theg pa 'og ma
NK060(i)001:14085: pas ma byin par len pa spong ba'i yon tan
NK060(i)001:14087: rdzun du smra ba la rdzun du smra ba spong ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i man ngag /drang /
NK060(i)001:14088: dngos po phyi nang gi bsdus pa'i chos rnams snang
NK060(i)001:14089: yang bden dngos kyis stongs pa sgyu ma lta bu
NK060(i)001:14090: la bdag tu lta ba ni ngo bo nyid med
NK060(i)001:14091: bzhin du btags pa/ ngo bo nyid kyi brdzun dang
NK060(i)001:14092: dngos po med bzhin zhen pas ming dang tshig tu
NK060(i)001:14093: bzhin du btags pa/ btags pa 'di la/ ming tshig
NK060(i)001:14094: gi rjes su spyod cing mngon par zhen pa rjes
NK060(i)001:14096: de dag las kyang 'gal bar smra ba ni log pa'i brdzun no //
NK060(i)001:14097: rdzun gsum po de nyid la ni bden pa'i gzhi ma grub pa'i phyir na rdzun spyod pa ste/
NK060(i)001:14098: des na rdzun zhes btags pa tsam yang dmigs su yod pa ma yin no //
NK060(i)001:14099: de ltar rtogs nas bdag gzhan chos gsum gyi don du brdzun du smras pas ni/
NK060(i)001:14100: theg pa 'og ma bas brdzun smra ba spangs pa'i yon tan zhor la rdzogs pa'o //
NK060(i)001:14101: mi tshangs par spyod pa la mi tshangs par spyod
NK060(i)001:14102: pa spong ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i man ngag go
NK060(i)001:14104: dngos po thams cad sems nyid du rang snang bas
NK060(i)001:14105: yul sems gnyis med du gsal ba ni ma chags
NK060(i)001:14107: de la pho mo gnyis su zhen cing chags pa ni log pa'i 'dod chags so //
NK060(i)001:14108: chags pa rang kha ma dang tshul mthun par spyad
NK060(i)001:14109: kyang de dag sems nyid kyi ngo bor shes pa'i
NK060(i)001:14110: lta ba dang / 'du shes gsum ldan gyi sgom pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14111: thabs kyis zin pa'i spyod pa dang gsum ldan gyi
NK060(i)001:14112: sgo nas chags pa ma 'gags par spyod pa'i dus
NK060(i)001:14113: nyid na chags pa tha mal pa'i dri ma med
NK060(i)001:14114: pa de ni tshangs par spyod pa'i mchog bde ba'i
NK060(i)001:14115: ye shes la dbang sgyur ba'i rgyal po yin te/
NK060(i)001:14116: de ni shin tu chags pa chen po spang gnyen
NK060(i)001:14117: ro gcig tu gyur pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i dgongs
NK060(i)001:14118: pa'i ngo bo nyid yin no //
NK060(i)001:14119: de ltar shes nas 'dzag med kyi ye shes bsgrub
NK060(i)001:14120: pa'i don du chags pa spyad pas theg pa 'og
NK060(i)001:14121: ma bas mi tshangs par spyod pa spangs pa'i yon
NK060(i)001:14123: gnyis pa dam tshig gi rnam grangs mdor bstan pa la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:14127: ngo bo nyid dang lam 'bras gong na gzhan med pa ni bla na med pa'i dam tshig ste/
NK060(i)001:14128: don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14129: kun rdzob sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du mnyam par rdzogs pa gnyis snang na snang mnyam/
NK060(i)001:14130: stong na stong mnyam du rtogs nas/
NK060(i)001:14131: sgo gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya las
NK060(i)001:14132: mi 'da' ba ni mi spang ba ste byang chub
NK060(i)001:14134: 'di la lta spyod lhas ma khrel ba cig dgos gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:14135: bla ma zhes pa ni spar khab ltar bzhi 'am/
NK060(i)001:14137: spyi dang 'dren dang dam tshig dbang //
NK060(i)001:14138: nyams chag skong dang shes rgyud dgrol //
NK060(i)001:14139: man ngag lung gi slob dpon drug /ces gsungs pas/
NK060(i)001:14140: de rnams bkur ba ni sgo gsum zol zog med pas mnyes par bya ba ste/
NK060(i)001:14141: 'di la sri zhu slob dpon gyis ma khrel ba cig dgos gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:14142: gzhan yang 'chad par 'gyur ba'i mched ni spar khab ltar gsum mam/
NK060(i)001:14144: spyi'i mched dang nye ba'i mched //
NK060(i)001:14145: ring ba'i mched dang 'dres pa'i mched //
NK060(i)001:14147: yang dag pa bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gi lam du
NK060(i)001:14148: zhugs pa rnams la sgo gsum gyis phan pa'i rtsal
NK060(i)001:14150: 'di la brtse gdung mched lcam gyis ma khrel ba cig dgos gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:14151: de gnyis su sku'i dam tshig go //
NK060(i)001:14154: bzlas pa las te sngags gsum dang /
NK060(i)001:14158: sku'i phyag rgya chen po dang bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:14159: de dag ni brtson pa rab kyis rgyun mi gcad par chu bo'i gzhung bzhin nam/
NK060(i)001:14160: nyin zhag gcig la thun bzhi'am/
NK060(i)001:14161: thun drug gi rnal 'byor du bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:14162: 'bring gis zla ba gcig la dus tshigs drug gam/
NK060(i)001:14164: nya stong gnyis la rnal 'byor dang ldan par bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:14165: tha mas kyang zla dus sam/
NK060(i)001:14167: lo dus su yid dam gyi sgom bzlas dang tshogs gtor bya ba ni gsung gi dam tshig go //
NK060(i)001:14170: gsal bkra gnyis mthun par bcu ste/
NK060(i)001:14171: sgrub pa'i gnas dus grogs dang rdzas //
NK060(i)001:14174: lta zab spyod pa barlanga po dang //
NK060(i)001:14175: lha ming gzungs dang grub rtags gsang //
NK060(i)001:14178: mchod rdzas dang gsang spyod la sogs pa gsang bar 'os pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14179: gzhan yang slob dpon dang mched kyis gsang gnyer gtad pa rnams te/
NK060(i)001:14180: bdag gzhan chos sgrogs kyi don du mi 'gyur ba rnams spang ba'i phyir dam tshig med pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14182: ma 'dres pa rnams lta smros kyang ci dgos/
NK060(i)001:14183: dam 'dres pa la yang skabs dang sbyar la gsang
NK060(i)001:14184: bcu gzhan du smra bar mi bya ni thugs kyi
NK060(i)001:14185: dam tshig go // de yang ji skad du/
NK060(i)001:14186: gsang sngags gsang zhes bya ba ni //
NK060(i)001:14187: chos la skyon yod ma yin te //
NK060(i)001:14188: sems can don phyir rab tu gsang //
NK060(i)001:14190: 'di rnams la g.yo sgyu rang sems kyis ma khrel ba cig dgos gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:14191: de ltar lnga po 'di dag ni lam dang 'bras
NK060(i)001:14192: bu'i yon tan mtha' dag gi gzhi rten yin pas
NK060(i)001:14193: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga zhes gsung pa rnams te/
NK060(i)001:14194: de yang bla med mi spang bar dang /
NK060(i)001:14195: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad pa gnyis ni sgrub pa'i dam tshig yin pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14198: gsang ba gzhan la mi spel ba dang gsum ni bsrung ba'i dam tshig yin la/
NK060(i)001:14199: de dag yan lag gi dam tshig khyad par du gyur bas na mchog ces bya'o //
NK060(i)001:14200: yan lag gi dam tshig bcu'o //
NK060(i)001:14203: mi spang ba'i dam tshig lnga/
NK060(i)001:14205: spyir yang dag pa'i dug lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:14206: log pa'i dug lnga gnyis su rgyas pa'i le'u bdun cu don gcig pa nas gsungs te/
NK060(i)001:14207: de la yang dag pa'i dug lnga ni 'khor 'das mnyam nyid du rtogs nas/
NK060(i)001:14208: 'byed pa med pa ni gti mug dang /
NK060(i)001:14209: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can la thugs rjes chags pa'i 'dod chags dang /
NK060(i)001:14210: log par rtogs pa'i ru dra sgrol ba'i zhe sdang dang /
NK060(i)001:14211: mnyam nyid rtogs pa'i lta ba shong mi 'babs pa'i nga rgyal dang /
NK060(i)001:14212: gnyis 'dzin can gyi lta spyod mnyam nyid kyi klong
NK060(i)001:14213: du mi shong ba'i phrag dog rnams ni spangs na
NK060(i)001:14214: don gsum mi 'grub pa'i phyir mi spang ngo //
NK060(i)001:14216: spyi'i mtshan nyid mi rtag pa dang sdug bsngal ba dang bdag med pa dang stong pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:14217: rang gi mtshan nyid sems kun nas blun zhing rmongs
NK060(i)001:14218: pa gti mug /phyi rdzas dang nang sems can la
NK060(i)001:14220: kun nas mnar sems pa zhe sdang /
NK060(i)001:14221: khong khengs shing gyong ba nga rgyal/
NK060(i)001:14222: gzhan gyi phun sum tshogs pa phrag tu mi shong ba phrag dog gi mtshan nyid yin la/
NK060(i)001:14223: de dag spangs na lta ba'i klungs las nyams nas
NK060(i)001:14224: nyan thos kyi theg pa gol bar 'gyur ba'i phyir
NK060(i)001:14225: mi spang ngo // 'o na log pa'i dug lnga mi spong bar bshad pa 'di/
NK060(i)001:14226: gsang ba yin nam bsgrag pa yin/
NK060(i)001:14227: drang don yin nam nges don yin/
NK060(i)001:14228: mi spong ba'i rgyu mtshan nam gtan tshigs gang yin/
NK060(i)001:14229: ma spangs pa la dgos ched ci yod/
NK060(i)001:14230: lam du byed na tshul ji ltar du byed ce na/
NK060(i)001:14231: dri ba dang po'i lan ni/
NK060(i)001:14232: blo chung gsang sngags sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa la gsang zhing /
NK060(i)001:14233: blo ldan yang dag pa'i lam du zhugs pa la bsgrag pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:14234: dri ba gnyis pa'i lan ni/
NK060(i)001:14235: nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin dang ye shes gnyis spang gnyen du lta ba la drang don yin la/
NK060(i)001:14236: gnyis med du lta ba la nges don yin te/
NK060(i)001:14238: rnam rtog nyid na rang byung ye shes te //
NK060(i)001:14239: rnam rtog mi skye ye shes brjod du med //
NK060(i)001:14240: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs pas mngon no //
NK060(i)001:14241: dri ba gsum pa'i lan ni/
NK060(i)001:14242: log pa'i dug lnga mi spong ba'i gtan tshigs lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:14243: spang bar bya ba'i gzhi ma grub pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14244: rnam par byang ba'i lam yin pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14245: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub yin pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14246: thabs dang shes rab kyi rang bzhin yin pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14247: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid yin pas na mi spang ngo //
NK060(i)001:14249: log pa'i dug lnga chos can/
NK060(i)001:14250: spang bar bya ba'i gzhi ma grub ste/
NK060(i)001:14251: shes bya'i gshis la nyon mongs pa rang kha ma med pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:14252: dper na thag khra sbrul du snang yang /
NK060(i)001:14253: gshis la sbrul med pa bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:14255: ma rig pa nyid spang du med //
NK060(i)001:14256: rig pa ye shes bsgrub tu med //
NK060(i)001:14259: log pa'i dug lnga chos can/
NK060(i)001:14260: thabs kyis zin na rnam par byang ba'i lam yin te/
NK060(i)001:14261: dug lnga spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid rtogs pa las gzhan pa'i 'bras bu bsgrub bya med pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:14262: dper na dug gi sman mar gyis dug nad 'joms shing ro rtsa'i mchog tu 'gyur pa bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:14264: nyon mongs rang dang spyir bstan pa //
NK060(i)001:14265: mtshan nyid ma nor don rtogs na //
NK060(i)001:14266: rnam par byang ba'i lam du 'gyur //
NK060(i)001:14269: 'dod chags zhes sdang gti mug kyang //
NK060(i)001:14270: byang chub chen po'i lam las byung //
NK060(i)001:14271: kun spyod yon tan lnga rnams kyang //
NK060(i)001:14272: chos nyid dbyings kyi rgyan zhes gsungs //
NK060(i)001:14275: log pa'i dug lnga chos can //
NK060(i)001:14276: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub tu 'gyur te/
NK060(i)001:14277: dug lnga'i yi ge a yis mtshon nas sku/
NK060(i)001:14279: +amo gyis mtshon nas thugs su brda sprad pas/
NK060(i)001:14280: sgo gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs las mi 'da' ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:14281: dper na dug la sngags kyis btab ba bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:14283: nyon mongs dug ltar snang ba'i rang bzhin rnams //
NK060(i)001:14284: rnam grol ye shes lnga yi ngang du snang //
NK060(i)001:14287: log pa'i dug lnga chos can/
NK060(i)001:14288: thabs dang shes rab kyi rang bzhin yin te/
NK060(i)001:14289: dug lngar snang ba thabs dang /
NK060(i)001:14290: de la rang bzhin med pa shes rab yin te/
NK060(i)001:14291: de gnyis ye shes dbyer mi phyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:14292: dper na tshad nad can dang /
NK060(i)001:14293: rlung nad can la ga bur sman dang dug tu snang yang /
NK060(i)001:14294: ga bur la sman dug dbyer med pa bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:14296: ma 'gags snang ba thabs yin te //
NK060(i)001:14297: rang bzhin med pa shes rab yin //
NK060(i)001:14300: log pa'i dug lnga chos can/
NK060(i)001:14301: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid yin te/
NK060(i)001:14302: zhe sdang mi bskyod pa rdo rje'i rigs dang stong pa nyid kyi ye shes/
NK060(i)001:14303: de bzhin du gti mug de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang me long lta bu/
NK060(i)001:14304: nga rgyal rin chen rigs dang mnyam nyid/
NK060(i)001:14305: 'dod chags pad+ma'i rigs dang so sor rtog pa/
NK060(i)001:14306: phrag dog las kyi rigs dang bya ba grub pa'i ye shes yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:14307: dper na 'khyags pa'i bdag nyid chu yin pa bzhin no //
NK060(i)001:14309: zhe sdang rang byung ye shes chen po dang //
NK060(i)001:14310: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:14311: dri ba bzhi pa'i lan ni/
NK060(i)001:14312: log pa'i dug lnga ma spangs pa'i dgos ched la yang don gnyer dang /
NK060(i)001:14315: dngos po'i zhen pa ldog pa'i/
NK060(i)001:14316: spros pa'i bag chags nye bar zhi ba'i/
NK060(i)001:14317: chos nyid kyi don la blo myur ba'i/
NK060(i)001:14318: bka' zab mo la gus pa skye ba'i/
NK060(i)001:14319: spyod lam tshogs su 'gyur ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK060(i)001:14320: de la dgos pa dang po ni/
NK060(i)001:14321: pha mes thams cad mes tshig nas shi ba'i mi zhig gis bsams pas/
NK060(i)001:14322: me ni tsha zhing bsreg pa kho na'o snyam du
NK060(i)001:14323: mngon par zhen pa zhig /dus nam zhig gi tshe
NK060(i)001:14324: 'brog dgon pa zhig tu phyin pas de na drang
NK060(i)001:14325: srong me'i gtsang sbra can dang /
NK060(i)001:14326: ri dwags me byi dkar po bya ba me la gnas bcas nas/
NK060(i)001:14327: zas su me za skom du me 'thung ba cig mthong nas/
NK060(i)001:14328: 'o na me 'di tsha zhing sreg pa kho nar 'dug snyam pa'i mngon par zhen pa log go //
NK060(i)001:14329: dpe de bzhin du theg pa 'og ma ba nyon mongs pa 'khor ba'i chos kho nar bzung ste/
NK060(i)001:14330: spong 'gegs sbyor sgyur byed pa la/
NK060(i)001:14331: gsang sngags pas nyon mongs pa nyid rang rig pa
NK060(i)001:14332: byang chub kyi sems yin pas ma spangs par lam
NK060(i)001:14333: du byas na/ sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu tshe gcig
NK060(i)001:14334: lus gcig la 'thob bo zhes brjod pas theg pa
NK060(i)001:14335: 'og ma ba dug lnga 'khor ba'i chos kho na
NK060(i)001:14336: yin snyam pa'i mngon par zhen pa las grol lo
NK060(i)001:14337: du byas na/ // gnyis pa ni/
NK060(i)001:14338: spang blang la sogs pa gnyis byung phan chod spros pa ste/
NK060(i)001:14339: gnyis su zhen pa las log tsa na spros pa'i bag chags zhi ba'o //
NK060(i)001:14341: nyon mongs pa nyid chos nyid yin pas de ltar
NK060(i)001:14342: rtogs na lam dang 'bras bu gzhan nas btsal mi
NK060(i)001:14343: dgos par thag chod pas chos nyid la blo myur
NK060(i)001:14345: nyon mongs pa ma spangs par byang chub thob pa'i
NK060(i)001:14346: thabs khyad par can dang ldan pa sngags kyi bka'
NK060(i)001:14347: brgyud 'di ni theg pa gzhan las khyad par du
NK060(i)001:14348: 'phags pas shin tu zab pa'o snyam pa'i gus pa
NK060(i)001:14350: sgo gsum gyi byed spyod thams cad ma 'gags par shes pas rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs te/
NK060(i)001:14351: de'i gnad kyis nyon mongs pa dang rnam rtog ye shes su 'char ba'o //
NK060(i)001:14352: yang dgos ched gnyis pa gzhan sel gyi dgos ched ni/
NK060(i)001:14353: zhe sdang med na rang byung gi ye shes gsal mi thebs/
NK060(i)001:14354: 'dod chags med na bde ba'i ye shes rgyud la mi skye/
NK060(i)001:14355: gti mug med na rnam par rtog pa'i ngang la blo mi gnas/
NK060(i)001:14356: nga rgyal med na chos nyid du la mi bzla/
NK060(i)001:14357: phrag dog med na mnyam pa nyid du khod mi snyoms pas so //
NK060(i)001:14358: dri ba lnga pa'i lan ni/
NK060(i)001:14359: dug lnga lam du byed tshul la brtag pa bzhi ste/
NK060(i)001:14360: de yang chos can zhe sdang lta bu gcig la sbyar na/
NK060(i)001:14361: rgyud la zhe sdang drag po skam gyis skyes pa'i rang ldog de ka la lam du byed dam/
NK060(i)001:14362: de gtan tshigs kyis gzhigs pas rang bzhin ma grub pa de la lam du byed dam/
NK060(i)001:14363: zhe sdang la brten nas gnyen po byams pa bsgom pa la lam du byed dam/
NK060(i)001:14364: zhe sdang 'gags pa'i rjes thob kyi shes pa gsal la rtog med de la lam du byed/
NK060(i)001:14366: pha bsad kyi bus mtshams med kyi las kyi mi gos par rnam grol thob par thal/
NK060(i)001:14368: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang khyad par med par thal/
NK060(i)001:14370: 'dod nyon mongs pa lam byed du 'dod gnyen po lam byed du thal/
NK060(i)001:14372: ma rig pa dang ye shes tha dad du thal/
NK060(i)001:14373: de thams cad rtags khas blangs/
NK060(i)001:14375: 'dod par nus pa ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:14376: lung rig gis gsang ba 'bab bo zhe na/
NK060(i)001:14378: rje go bu ba skyo ston sh+aaka yes kyi zhal nas/
NK060(i)001:14379: skad cig ma dang po la nyon mongs pa thol gyis skyes pa la/
NK060(i)001:14380: skad cig ma gnyis par chos nyid du shes par lam du byed gsung ste/
NK060(i)001:14381: des kyang brtag pa mtha' ma'i skyon mi spongs so //
NK060(i)001:14382: rje sgro phug pa'i bzhed kyis/
NK060(i)001:14383: nyon mongs pa skam skyes pa la lam du byed de/
NK060(i)001:14384: de yang rtogs pa lta ba'i rtsis zin pa rang rgyud du ma shor ba/
NK060(i)001:14385: nyon mongs pa rang gi mtha' la ma zhen pa
NK060(i)001:14386: dang chos gsum ldan cig la lam du byed gsung
NK060(i)001:14387: mod kyi/ de ltar na chos gsum ldan dang /
NK060(i)001:14388: skam skyes pa la khyad yod dam med/
NK060(i)001:14389: yod na lam du bya rgyu de nyon mongs pa skam skyes pa ma yin par thal/
NK060(i)001:14390: chos gsum ldan yin pa'i phyir skam skyes yin kyang /
NK060(i)001:14393: 'on te khyad par med na brtag pa dang po'i skyon gyis gnod do //
NK060(i)001:14394: des na kho bo ni 'di ltar sems te/
NK060(i)001:14395: nyon mongs pa skam skyes la lam du byed la/
NK060(i)001:14396: 'o na pha bsad kyi bu rang grol bar thal zhe na/
NK060(i)001:14397: de la brtags ste ma h+aa yo ga'i lam tshang
NK060(i)001:14398: la ma nor ba lam du byed pa'i pha bsad
NK060(i)001:14400: de las gzhan pa'i pha bsad kyi bu la zer/
NK060(i)001:14401: snga ma ltar na 'dod thog /phyi ma ltar na khyab pa med de/
NK060(i)001:14402: pha bsad kyi bu de la zhe sdang skam skyes
NK060(i)001:14403: yod kyang ma h+aa yo ga'i lam pa ma yin
NK060(i)001:14404: pa'i phyir ro // 'o na ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK060(i)001:14405: lam tshang la ma nor ba gang yin snyam na
NK060(i)001:14406: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba'i gdengs dang ldan
NK060(i)001:14407: pa'i phyir ro // pas/ rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i thabs kyis/
NK060(i)001:14408: nyon mongs pa spyad kyang mi 'ching ba rma bya
NK060(i)001:14409: dug gis 'tsho ba lta bu'i rnal 'byor pas nyon
NK060(i)001:14410: mongs pa skam gyis skyes pa'i dus na skye bo
NK060(i)001:14411: tha mal pa ltar nyon mongs pa'i dbang du mi
NK060(i)001:14412: gtong / nyan thos ltar mi spong /
NK060(i)001:14414: byang chub sems dpa' ltar mi spyod/
NK060(i)001:14415: sngags phyi rgyud ltar mi bsgyur bar dpe nya lam
NK060(i)001:14416: du chu bde ba lta bu ni ma h+aa yo
NK060(i)001:14417: ga'i lam pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa yin no
NK060(i)001:14418: // de ltar ma yin pa'i gsang sngags par khas 'ches pa/
NK060(i)001:14419: gab pa'i gsang ba chos nyid ji bzhin nyid kyi don ma rtogs shing sbas pa'i gsang ba/
NK060(i)001:14421: ga na la sogs pa la mngon par 'chel nas
NK060(i)001:14422: gsang sngags sgra ji bzhin pa ltar spyod pa rnams
NK060(i)001:14423: ni/ mnar med pa'i sems can dmyal ba chen por
NK060(i)001:14424: skye bar sngags gsar rnying gi rgyud sde du mar
NK060(i)001:14425: ni/ gsungs so // mi dor ba lnga/
NK060(i)001:14427: dkar rtsi byang chub kyi sems/
NK060(i)001:14431: sha chen dang lnga ni sngar bshad pa'i grub pa
NK060(i)001:14432: bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir na yang dag pa'i snod
NK060(i)001:14433: bcud 'di dag la longs spyod par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:14434: gtsang rme'i rtog pa sbyang ba dang /
NK060(i)001:14435: thun mong gi yon tan gnyis gnyis 'byung ba dang /
NK060(i)001:14436: rigs lnga bsgrub pa'i rdzas khyad par can yin pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:14437: dang du blang zhing mi dor ro //
NK060(i)001:14438: mjug bsdus ba yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:14440: de ltar mi spang ba dang mi dor ba ni yan lag bcu'i dam tshig ste/
NK060(i)001:14441: ye gdod ma nas dag pa gsum dang /
NK060(i)001:14442: mnyam pa bzhi'i ngo bor gnas pa la gnas pa ltar rtogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14443: rtogs par 'dod pa'i rnal 'byor pas spyad par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:14444: nyams na skyon yod pas 'da' bar dka' ba'o //
NK060(i)001:14446: sngar bshad pa'i bsrung zhing bsgrub pa'i dam tshig lnga ni/
NK060(i)001:14447: lam dang 'bras bu'i chos thams cad kyi gazhi'am rtsa ba yin te/
NK060(i)001:14448: de nyams na mi dang lha'i rigs kyang med par
NK060(i)001:14449: 'gyur na theg pa chen po'i rigs lta smos kyang
NK060(i)001:14450: ci dgos te mkhar gyi 'gram zhig pa dang mtshungs
NK060(i)001:14451: so // mi spang ba dug lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:14452: mi dor ba bdud rtsi lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:14453: lnga mtshan gnyis po 'di ni yan lag gi dam tshig yin yang /
NK060(i)001:14454: log pa'i dug lnga spangs na lta ba'i klungs las nyams na nyan thos su gol la/
NK060(i)001:14455: yang dag pa'i dug lnga spangs na rgyud la byin rlabs mi 'jug cing bdag gzhan gyi don mi 'grub/
NK060(i)001:14456: dam rdzas lnga spangs na spyod pa kri yog tu
NK060(i)001:14457: gol bas lta bas yod ma 'brel ba'i skyon du
NK060(i)001:14459: gsum pa mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig skyon yon dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:14461: dngos po thams cad kyi rang bzhin bden gsum ris
NK060(i)001:14462: med du mnyam pa la mnyam pa ltar shes rab
NK060(i)001:14463: dang ting nge 'dzin gyis mnyam par sbyor ba'i dus
NK060(i)001:14464: na gang yang bdag nyid chen po las mi 'da'
NK060(i)001:14465: ba ni mnyam pa'i dam tshig yin la/
NK060(i)001:14466: de'i don la gnas na mnyam rdzogs chen po kun
NK060(i)001:14467: tu bzang po dbye ba med pa'i sa thob par
NK060(i)001:14468: 'gyur bas so // gal te de las 'das shing
NK060(i)001:14469: mnyam pa'i dam tshig ma bsrungs na thabs gzhan gyis
NK060(i)001:14470: sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu thob pa ma yin no
NK060(i)001:14471: 'gyur bas so // // bzhi pa dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon la gsum/
NK060(i)001:14475: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po yang sku gsung thugs
NK060(i)001:14476: kyi dam tshig gsum du 'dus pas sku'i dam tshig
NK060(i)001:14477: slob dpon dang / mched la nyams na gang nyams pa'i gnas su gso ste/
NK060(i)001:14478: 'byor ba pa dang sri zhu la sogs kho nas zhi bar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:14479: gsung gi dam tshig sngags dang phyag rgya nyams na
NK060(i)001:14480: sgrub pa chen po lan gsum gyis bshags nas bzlas
NK060(i)001:14482: thugs kyi dam tshig gang bcu nyams na shes rab
NK060(i)001:14483: dang ting nge 'dzin gyi gso bar byed dgos pa
NK060(i)001:14484: la/ gal te nyams pa 'i phyal ba dag gso
NK060(i)001:14485: ba'i cho ga la dus nye bar mi brtson pa
NK060(i)001:14486: de dag dus skad cig tsam mam yud tsam du
NK060(i)001:14487: yang smra bar ma byed cig /smras na nyes pa
NK060(i)001:14488: la/ ci yod ce na/ dper na sbal pa rma
NK060(i)001:14489: can gcig gi zhor la sbal dong gang rmas par
NK060(i)001:14490: la/ ci yod ce na/ 'gyur pa dang / thu
NK060(i)001:14491: ru rdo can gcig gis rta khyu rngos 'khyer ba
NK060(i)001:14492: la/ ci yod ce na/ 'gyur pa dang / dang
NK060(i)001:14493: / 'o ma rul ba thig pa gcig gis 'o
NK060(i)001:14494: ma khol zangs gang rul bzhin du dam tshig nyams
NK060(i)001:14495: pa dang 'grogs par 'gyur ba'i nyes pa brjod kyis
NK060(i)001:14496: la/ ci yod ce na/ 'gyur pa dang / dang
NK060(i)001:14497: / mi lang ste/ nyams pa gcig gi zhor la
NK060(i)001:14498: de dang dam 'dres pa'i rnal 'byor pa kun dmyal
NK060(i)001:14499: bar ltung ba'i skyon 'dug pas na lung pa gcig
NK060(i)001:14500: gi chu la'ang btung bar mi bya'o //
NK060(i)001:14501: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon/
NK060(i)001:14503: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po nyams par gyur na
NK060(i)001:14504: tshe 'dir yang sgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur
NK060(i)001:14505: te/ las ci brtsams par mi 'grub cing bar chad mang ba dang /
NK060(i)001:14506: phyi ma yang yid du mi 'ong ba'i sdug bsngal
NK060(i)001:14507: sna tshogs pa'i 'bras bu ngan song gsum mi 'dod
NK060(i)001:14508: bzhin du rang dbang med par 'du bar 'gyur ro
NK060(i)001:14509: // yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon no //
NK060(i)001:14511: yan lag gi dam tshig mi spang lnga dang mi dor lnga nyams te/
NK060(i)001:14512: nyan rang dang kri yog tu gol bar gyur na
NK060(i)001:14513: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa nyams su blangs pa'i
NK060(i)001:14514: 'bras bu thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub med
NK060(i)001:14515: cing / lam mchog tu gyur pa spangs pa'i nyes
NK060(i)001:14516: pas slar ngan song gi gnas su ltung bar 'gyur
NK060(i)001:14517: cing / ro // lnga pa dam tshig gi rang bzhin bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:14519: gong du bshad pa'i rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig de dag rnams ni lta spyod gnyis sam/
NK060(i)001:14520: rang bzhin dang lam dang 'bras bu dbyer mi phyed pa'i phyir rdo rje che zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:14521: de dag dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi lam
NK060(i)001:14522: yang yin la ngo bo yang yin pas na bdag
NK060(i)001:14523: nyid ces brjod pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:14524: drug pa dam tshig gi rnam grangs rgyas par bstan pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:14526: sum brgya drug cur dbye ba/
NK060(i)001:14528: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po de la nang tshegs
NK060(i)001:14529: su dbye ba'i grangs ni rtsa ba lnga po'i ya
NK060(i)001:14530: gyal gcig la'ang shes rab lta bas rtogs pa dang
NK060(i)001:14531: / thabs kyis ma 'gags par spyod pa gnyis gnyis su phye bas rtsa ba la bcu dang /
NK060(i)001:14532: de dag spyi ru bzhag nas bye brag tu rtsa
NK060(i)001:14533: ba re re la yang bcu phrag gsum gsum du
NK060(i)001:14534: phye na/ dang po bla na med pa byang chub kyi sems mi spang ba la bcu phrag gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:14535: yi dam gyi lha zhi khro gnyis re re la'ang
NK060(i)001:14536: rtsa ba'i lha re la lhag pa'i lha dgu dgu
NK060(i)001:14537: bkod pas lhag pa'i lha dgu nyid dang bcu ste
NK060(i)001:14539: theg pa thun mong ba ltar byams pa/
NK060(i)001:14543: thun mong gi tshad med pa bzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:14544: khro bo rtog pa lha rgyud ltar khro gtum gyi
NK060(i)001:14545: tshul gyis gdug pa can rjes su 'dzin par byams
NK060(i)001:14546: pa/ brtse ba chen pos myur du sgrol ba'i snying rje/
NK060(i)001:14547: shes pa gnas spar zhing phung po tshogs su stobs pa dga' ba/
NK060(i)001:14548: gdul bya rnams yal bar mi 'dor ba btang snyoms te/
NK060(i)001:14549: thun mong ma yin pa'i tshad med pa bzhi ste brgyad/
NK060(i)001:14551: kun rdzob sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK060(i)001:14552: mnyam par rdzogs pa gnyis te bcu kun dril bas
NK060(i)001:14553: bla med mi spang ba sum cu'o //
NK060(i)001:14554: gnyis pa bla ma bkur ba sum cu ni/
NK060(i)001:14555: bla ma drug la lus kyi sgo nas brdeg btsog spang /
NK060(i)001:14564: ma rabs kyi spyod pa spang zhing /
NK060(i)001:14565: bag zon dang ldan par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:14573: lkog tu tshul ngan brjod pa dang brgyad spang zhing /
NK060(i)001:14576: sems kyi sgo nas bla ma'i rdzas la rkam zhing yum la chags pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14577: bla ma dang bla ma'i 'khor gyi skyon la mnar sems pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14578: yon tan la rmongs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14579: rang che'o snyam pa'i dregs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14580: bla ma'i phun sum tshogs pa phrag tu mi shong ba dang /
NK060(i)001:14581: ngan du sems pa rnams spang ba dang /
NK060(i)001:14582: bla ma'i gsung gnyan zhing lci bar sems pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14583: pha ma ltar sems pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14584: yi dam ltar sems pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14585: gdung sems rgyun mi gcad pa dang bcu ste/
NK060(i)001:14586: dril bas bla ma bkur tshul sum cu'o //
NK060(i)001:14587: gsum pa sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad pa sum cu ni/
NK060(i)001:14588: phyogs mtshams bcing ba 'bar ba mtshams kyi sngags dang
NK060(i)001:14589: gcig /'byung ba rim brtsegs bskyed pa la rtsa sngags
NK060(i)001:14590: dang bskyed sngags gnyis/ rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa la rtsa sngags dang bskyed sngags gnyis te lnga/
NK060(i)001:14591: brten pa lha bskyod pa la rtsa ba bskyod pa las sngags dang gsum/
NK060(i)001:14592: dbang bkur ba dang byin bsdu ba'i sngags gnyis te lnga/
NK060(i)001:14595: brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK060(i)001:14597: mchod pa 'bul ba'i sngags dang lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:14598: de ltar sngags la bco lnga dang /
NK060(i)001:14599: zhi khro gnyis po re re la yang dam tshig dang /
NK060(i)001:14600: las dang chos dang sku'i phyag rgya chen po ste/
NK060(i)001:14601: de yang dam tshig gi phyag rgya la bca' ba dang bsam pa gnyis/
NK060(i)001:14602: las kyi phyag rgya la bca' ba dang bsam pa gnyis/
NK060(i)001:14603: chos kyi phyag rgya la brjod pa dang bsam pa gnyis so //
NK060(i)001:14604: de ltar zhi khro gnyis la phyag rgya bdun bdun te bcu bzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:14605: zhi khro zung 'jug gi sku drug pa spyi'i gzugs can dang bco lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:14606: dril bas sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad pa sum cu'o //
NK060(i)001:14607: bzhi pa mched la byams pa sum cu ni/
NK060(i)001:14608: mched bzhi la lus kyi sgo nas brdeg pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14610: gzungs ma la spyod pa spang /
NK060(i)001:14611: lta spyod mtho ba khyad du mi bsad/
NK060(i)001:14612: dbang thob pa snga ba dang rdzogs pa gong du bkur/
NK060(i)001:14613: dam tshig can la gus par bya/
NK060(i)001:14614: mched kyi thugs dang 'gal ba'i spyod lam spang /
NK060(i)001:14617: dus kun tu dga' zhing spro bar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:14618: ngag gi sgo nas brdzun dang /
NK060(i)001:14625: zhe sa dang bcas pa smra/
NK060(i)001:14627: sri zhu'i sgra dang bcas te smra bar bya'o //
NK060(i)001:14628: sems kyi sgo nas 'dod chags dang /
NK060(i)001:14632: phrag dog gis kun nas blangs pa'i sems spang zhing /
NK060(i)001:14636: mig 'bras ltar blta zhing gdung sems dang ldan par
NK060(i)001:14637: bya ste dril bas mched la bkur tshul sum cu'o
NK060(i)001:14638: // lnga pa gsang ba'i don phyir mi smra ba sum cu ni/
NK060(i)001:14639: spyir gsang bzhi bar gsang bzhi ste brgyad/
NK060(i)001:14641: gsang bar gnyer gtad pa gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:14642: bcu po de dag gzhir byas nas yongs su ma
NK060(i)001:14643: smin pa rnams la sems kyis bstan par mi bsam
NK060(i)001:14644: pa bcu dang / ngag gis tshig tu mi brjod pa bcu dang /
NK060(i)001:14645: lus kyi brdas mi mtshon pa bcu ste/
NK060(i)001:14646: dril bas gsang ba mi bsgrag pa sum cu'o //
NK060(i)001:14647: de ltar sum cu pa phrag lnga la brgya lnga
NK060(i)001:14648: bcu de'i steng du gong gi spyir bzhag bcu po
NK060(i)001:14649: bsnan pas brgya drug cu ni rtsa ba'i dam tshig
NK060(i)001:14651: yan lag gi dam tshig mi spang ba dang mi dor ba lnga tshan gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:14652: bcu po la gcig la'ang bcu phrag gnyis gnyis su dbye ba'i tshul ni/
NK060(i)001:14654: dang du blang ba'i dam grub rdzas //
NK060(i)001:14655: sgrub rdzas rnam lnga'ang rtsa ba brgyad //
NK060(i)001:14656: brgya cha re zhing dwangs snyigs gnyis //
NK060(i)001:14657: re re'ang rnam pa bcu ru 'gyur //
NK060(i)001:14658: zhing bcu'i bdud rtsis de bzhin pas //
NK060(i)001:14659: rnam par dbye ba nyi shu'o //
NK060(i)001:14660: bdag gzhan rang bzhin zhing dang gnyis //
NK060(i)001:14661: rdzas bcu thabs spyod shes rab spyod //
NK060(i)001:14662: bcu gnyis nyi shur 'gyur ba'ang rigs //
NK060(i)001:14663: zhes mi dor ba'i dam tshig gi rnam dbye dang /
NK060(i)001:14665: mi spang lnga las bcu gnyis te //
NK060(i)001:14666: zhing bcu thabs kyi mdzad pas 'joms //
NK060(i)001:14667: shes rab rang bzhin med par bsgom //
NK060(i)001:14668: thabs dang shes rab zhe sdang gis //
NK060(i)001:14669: bdag gzhan don rnams rdzogs par byed //
NK060(i)001:14670: yan lag bcu yi dam tshig la //
NK060(i)001:14671: thabs kyi mdzad pas mi 'byed cing //
NK060(i)001:14672: shes rab gnyis med mi 'byed pa'i //
NK060(i)001:14673: gti mug bcu gnyis 'da' mi bya //
NK060(i)001:14674: de ltar thabs dang shes rab bcu //
NK060(i)001:14675: gnyis ni gdeng du gyur pa yi //
NK060(i)001:14676: lhag pa'i nga rgyal 'da' mi bya //
NK060(i)001:14677: nga rgyal chen po'i dam tshig go //
NK060(i)001:14678: zhing bcu thugs rjes mi gtong ba //
NK060(i)001:14679: rigs lnga'i yum la thabs kyis rol //
NK060(i)001:14680: ting 'dzin thabs dbang rang bzhin sbyar //
NK060(i)001:14682: ma rtogs gnyis dang log rtogs gnyis //
NK060(i)001:14683: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems //
NK060(i)001:14684: gsang sngags phyi pa'i theg pa gsum //
NK060(i)001:14685: gsang sgor mdzad pa mi chud cing //
NK060(i)001:14686: shes rab lta ngan mi chud pa //
NK060(i)001:14687: phrag dog chen po'i dam tshig go //
NK060(i)001:14688: zhes mi spang ba'i dam tshig lnga'i rnam dbye gsung mod kyi/
NK060(i)001:14689: 'di la slob dpon h+aum ka ra/
NK060(i)001:14693: dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra rnams kyis bzhed gzhung mi 'dra ba lnga yod do zhes grags kyang /
NK060(i)001:14694: gzhan rnams ni kho bos ma mthong la/
NK060(i)001:14695: dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra'i bzhed gzhung yin zer ba phra rgyas kyi mchan bu dang /
NK060(i)001:14696: sngon gyi t+ai ka rnying pa rnams na bris 'dug
NK060(i)001:14697: pas 'di dag dbang btsan du byas na dang po
NK060(i)001:14698: mi spang ba'i dam tshig lnga po re re la'ang
NK060(i)001:14699: nyi shu nyi shur dbye ste/
NK060(i)001:14700: de yang zhe sdang gi nyi shu ni/
NK060(i)001:14701: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu thabs kyis mdzad spyod kyi dngos su bsgral ba bcu dang /
NK060(i)001:14702: shes rab lta bas rang bzhin med par shes nas
NK060(i)001:14703: skye med kyi ngang du sgrol ba bcu ste nyi
NK060(i)001:14704: shu'o // gti mug gi nyi shu ni/
NK060(i)001:14705: yan lag bcu'i dam tshig la thabs kyi mdzad spyod kyis mi 'byed par spyod pa bcu dang /
NK060(i)001:14706: shes rab lta bas mi 'byed pa bcu ste nyi shu'o //
NK060(i)001:14707: nga rgyal gi nyi shu ni/
NK060(i)001:14708: yan lag bcu'i dam tshig la yang dag pa'i dug
NK060(i)001:14709: lnga dang log pa'i dug lnga la thabs kyis ma
NK060(i)001:14711: lta ba rang bzhin med par rtogs pa bcu ste nyi shu'o //
NK060(i)001:14713: rigs lnga'i yum la thabs kyis dngos su rol pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14714: shes rab kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis rol par la ste bcu/
NK060(i)001:14715: zhing bcu lta bas rang bzhin med par shes na
NK060(i)001:14716: thugs rjes mi 'bral bar chags pas rjes su 'dzin
NK060(i)001:14718: phrag dog gi nyi shu la/
NK060(i)001:14719: ma rtogs phyal ba rgyang 'phen gnyis/
NK060(i)001:14720: log rtogs mu stegs rtag chad gnyis/
NK060(i)001:14721: theg chung nyan thos rang rgyal gnyis/
NK060(i)001:14722: theg chen byang chub sems dpa' dang phyi rgyud sde
NK060(i)001:14723: gsum dang bcu po'i lta spyod thabs kyi spyod pa'i
NK060(i)001:14724: klong du mi chud pa bcu dang /
NK060(i)001:14725: shes rab lta ba'i gor mi chud pa bcu ste nyi shu'o //
NK060(i)001:14726: gzhan yang mi dor ba'i dam tshig lnga po re re la'ang nyi shu nyi shur dbye ste/
NK060(i)001:14727: de yang byang sems kyi nyi shu ni/
NK060(i)001:14728: byang sems mthar phyin pa mig /chu rgyus mthar phyin pa sen mo/
NK060(i)001:14729: khrag dang chu ser mthar phyin pa skra/
NK060(i)001:14730: rus pa mthar phyin pa so ste mngon pa phyi'i bzhi'o //
NK060(i)001:14733: gshegs shul rdo rje chu ba/
NK060(i)001:14734: pho brang snying ste sbas pa nang gi bzhi ste brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:14735: phyi nang gi dwangs snyigs gnyis te bcu/
NK060(i)001:14736: zhing bcu'i byang sems la bcu ru phye bas nyi shu'o //
NK060(i)001:14737: dri chen gyi nyi shu ni/
NK060(i)001:14741: byin pa'i dri chen te mngon pa'i phyir bzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:14745: shi ba bam gyi dri chen te sbas pa nang gi bzhi ste brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:14747: zhing bcu'i dri chen dang nyi shu'o //
NK060(i)001:14752: gshegs lam mkhal ma'i rtsa khrag ste mngon pa phyi'i bzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:14753: gzungs ma la dang po 'dzag pa'i khrag /'dzag pa dang sbyar ba'i/
NK060(i)001:14755: rgyud lnga bsgral ba'i khrag ste sbas pa nang gi bzhi ste brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:14757: zhing bcu bsgral ba'i khrag bcu ste nyi shu'o //
NK060(i)001:14762: skye bo'i dri chu ste mngon pa phyi'i bzhi dang /
NK060(i)001:14766: shi ba bam gyi dri chu rnams ni sbas pa nang gi bzhi ste brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:14768: zhing bcu'i dri chu dang nyi shu'o //
NK060(i)001:14769: sha chen gyi nyi shu ni/
NK060(i)001:14770: nywa sha bzhi ni mngon par phyi'i bzhi/
NK060(i)001:14772: mkhar mtshos gnyis ni sbas pa nang gi bzhi ste brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:14774: zhing bcu bsgral ba'i sha chen bcu ste nyi shu'o //
NK060(i)001:14775: de ltar nyi shu tshan bcu la nyis bargya'o zhes bshad mod kyi/
NK060(i)001:14776: mang du thos pa rnams kyis ji ltar rigs brtag par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:14777: mdor na rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig bsrung mtshams kyi rnam grangs ni/
NK060(i)001:14778: rtsa ba la brgya drug cu dang /
NK060(i)001:14779: yan lag la nyis brgya ste sum brgya drug cu
NK060(i)001:14780: gsungs pa 'di ni rgyud gzhung 'di nyid kyi dbang
NK060(i)001:14781: du yin gyi gzhan du ni nges pa med par
NK060(i)001:14782: shes par bya'o // gdul bya la dgongs nas dbye ba'o //
NK060(i)001:14784: theg pa'i chen po gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK060(i)001:14785: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig 'di dag
NK060(i)001:14786: ni yon tan khyad par can mnga' bas/
NK060(i)001:14787: rgyal khrims chags pa'i sa dang 'dra'o //
NK060(i)001:14788: de yang rgya chad med pa gdul bya ji ltar
NK060(i)001:14789: 'dul ba ltar ston pas na rmad po che zhes
NK060(i)001:14790: bya ste/ gnas 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na
NK060(i)001:14791: gdul bya srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'gro ba
NK060(i)001:14792: ji snyed pa'i rnam par rtogs pa 'dul ba'i gnyen
NK060(i)001:14793: por dam tshig gi rnam grangs kyang /
NK060(i)001:14799: rang ngo shes pa la sogs pa 'dul thabs kyi
NK060(i)001:14800: bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa de snyed cig
NK060(i)001:14801: spros nas sems can gyi don mdzad do //
NK060(i)001:14802: bdun pa dam tshig gi yon tan/
NK060(i)001:14804: gong du bshad pa'i mnyam rdzogs chen po cig car
NK060(i)001:14805: ba'i dam tshig las gzhan pa rim gyis pa'i yang
NK060(i)001:14806: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams
NK060(i)001:14807: par bsrungs na/ rgyal mchog rigs thams cad kyi bdag
NK060(i)001:14808: po kun tu bzang po'i sku gsung thugs kyi ngang
NK060(i)001:14809: du 'khor ba'i chos thams cad dang mya ngan las
NK060(i)001:14810: 'das pa'i chos ma lus pa ye nas lhun gyis
NK060(i)001:14811: grub pas na phyag rgya'i mchog ste/
NK060(i)001:14812: de las gzhan pa'i 'bras bu bsgrub tu med pa
NK060(i)001:14813: ni 'bras bu'i mchog dam pa kun tu bzang po'i
NK060(i)001:14814: yon tan ma lus pa 'grub cing /
NK060(i)001:14815: de la sogs pa'i yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab
NK060(i)001:14816: cing brjod kyis mi lang bas na mtha' yas pa'i
NK060(i)001:14817: mchog go // yon tan de dag kyang mdor bsdus na lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:14818: 'jig rten gyi gtso bos 'khur 'os su mthong ba'i
NK060(i)001:14819: yon tan ni de lta bu'i dam tshig rnams dang
NK060(i)001:14820: ldan na rgyal ba'i rigs mchog 'dzin pa ste/
NK060(i)001:14821: de yang lta spyod tshang bar 'byor pa ni sar chud pa/
NK060(i)001:14822: de la rgyun du gnas pa ni sar gnas pa/
NK060(i)001:14823: de stobs su gyur pa'i sar yongs su smin pa'i rig 'dzin yin no //
NK060(i)001:14824: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po de la ni 'jig rten gyi gtso bo lha srin sde brgyad dang /
NK060(i)001:14825: de dag gi 'khor g.yog rnams kyis kyang dgos pa sgrub cing bkur sti byed pa'o //
NK060(i)001:14826: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpas byin gyis rlob pa'i yon tan ni/
NK060(i)001:14827: dam pa mchog ni sangs rgyas dang /
NK060(i)001:14828: dam pa ni rig 'dzin dang byang chub sems dpa' ste/
NK060(i)001:14829: de dag gis kyang sangs rgyas rnams kyi sras dang
NK060(i)001:14830: rig 'dzin dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi spun
NK060(i)001:14831: du dgongs shing byin gyi rlob bo //
NK060(i)001:14832: 'di na med kyis kyang lung gra chad la nyal
NK060(i)001:14833: ba slang ba bshad pa mkhan po'i gnyer bya ba
NK060(i)001:14834: yin pas/ ma mo dang mkha' 'gro rnams kyis ming por dgongs nas stongs dang grogs byed do //
NK060(i)001:14835: dam can chos skyong ba'i srung ma rnams kyis kyang
NK060(i)001:14836: rje dpon dam par dgongs nas phrin las bsgrub po
NK060(i)001:14837: zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:14838: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa dang gnyis su med par sbyor ba'i yon tan ni/
NK060(i)001:14839: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig gzhung bzhin
NK060(i)001:14840: dubasrunga ba de ni bde bar gshegs pa nyid kyi
NK060(i)001:14841: ngo bo dang tha mi dad pas byed spyod thams
NK060(i)001:14842: cad kyang de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul la zhugs
NK060(i)001:14843: pa zhes bya'o // de'i phyir dam tshig dang ldan
NK060(i)001:14844: pa'i byed spyod gang yang ltung bar 'gyur ba'i 'jigs
NK060(i)001:14845: pa med pas spyod yul yongs su dag pa kun
NK060(i)001:14847: 'og ma'i 'dul sdom yongs su rdzogs pa'i yon tan ni/
NK060(i)001:14848: chos thams cad ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid mngon byed
NK060(i)001:14849: pa gsang sngags bla na med pa'i dam tshig phan
NK060(i)001:14850: yon dang bcas pa'i 'dir thun mong gdul bya 'dul
NK060(i)001:14851: ba'i thabs su bstan pa'i nyan thos kyi 'dul khrims
NK060(i)001:14853: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14854: sngags phyi rgyud kyi dam tshig la sogs pa bsam yas pa rnams 'dus pa'i phyir/
NK060(i)001:14855: 'dir rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma
NK060(i)001:14856: nyams na theg pa 'og ma rnams kyi dgag bya
NK060(i)001:14857: ma lus pa rnam par dag cing /
NK060(i)001:14858: dgos pa ma lus pa ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK060(i)001:14859: nyams kyang bskang du rung ba'i yon tan ni/
NK060(i)001:14860: gal te sngags kyi dam tshig nyams par gyur na
NK060(i)001:14861: yang nyan rang ltar bskang thabs med pa ma yin
NK060(i)001:14862: te/ bskang pas skong ba'i thabs khyad par can yod
NK060(i)001:14863: pas nyams pa gso ba la rab tu brtson pa
NK060(i)001:14864: ni dam tshig gi yon tan yongs su rdzogs par
NK060(i)001:14865: te/ 'gyur ba dang / de la sogs pa'i yon tan mtha' yas pas na mchog ces bya'o //
NK060(i)001:14866: gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:14868: zhes le'u'i gzhung don de dag brjod pas rgyal ba
NK060(i)001:14869: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid dam tshig gi rang bzhin
NK060(i)001:14870: las 'da' bar mi byed pas na de bzhin gshegs
NK060(i)001:14871: pa nyid la 'da' bar mi byed pa'i dam tshig
NK060(i)001:14875: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las mtshan gyi gzhi ru gda'/
NK060(i)001:14876: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig gi rnam
NK060(i)001:14877: par bzhag pa bstan pa'i gcod cing mtshams 'dzin pas
NK060(i)001:14878: na le'u ste yas bgrangs bcu dgu pa'i don du
NK060(i)001:14879: gada'o////da ni le'u nyi shu pa 'chad par byed pa
NK060(i)001:14880: la chos tshoms kyi dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:14881: rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam ston/
NK060(i)001:14882: de la thabs grol gnyis las gnyis ka ston/
NK060(i)001:14883: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa ston/
NK060(i)001:14884: snang ba ba zhi las snang ston/
NK060(i)001:14885: mtshan nyid gsum las rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ston/
NK060(i)001:14886: 'bring gi lnga las rgyud don ston/
NK060(i)001:14887: de la bcu las gzhung hril pos phrin las ston/
NK060(i)001:14891: dug gsum gyi mchod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14892: phrin las bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin ston/
NK060(i)001:14893: tha ma'i chos bcu las rang bzhin lta ba/
NK060(i)001:14895: ldem dgongs man ngag /gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:14896: de ltar ston pa'i le'u nyi shu pa 'di la gsum/
NK060(i)001:14898: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:14900: le'u bcu dgu par dam tshig bstan nas/
NK060(i)001:14901: da dam tshig ldan pa'i sgrub pa pos phrin las
NK060(i)001:14902: bya ba ston pas na de nas zhes 'brel sbyar
NK060(i)001:14903: ro // de bzhin gshegs pa bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po ni 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:14904: sems nyid la phrin las bzhi lhun gyis grub pa
NK060(i)001:14905: las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig /cho ga bzhis byin
NK060(i)001:14906: gyis rlob pa zhes bya ba'i dgongs pa la mngon
NK060(i)001:14907: du bzhag pas na ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK060(i)001:14908: zhugs nas 'og nas 'byung ba'i don ched du brjod
NK060(i)001:14912: phrin las kyi yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:14914: rdzas dang lu gu rgyud kyi sgo nas phrin las bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:14916: bro gar glu tshig gi yon tan dang /
NK060(i)001:14921: rgyas/ zhi ba'i phrin las so //
NK060(i)001:14922: bzhi po de re re la'ang lnga lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:14924: drag po'i ling+ga bca' ba dang /
NK060(i)001:14929: drag po'i cha byad kyis kha lho ru phyogs nas
NK060(i)001:14930: khros pa'i sems kyis rang gi dri ma dang kha
NK060(i)001:14932: grib ma mi 'phog pa'i thabs dang ldan par byas la/
NK060(i)001:14933: dgra bgegs kyi bdud rtsi lnga'am/
NK060(i)001:14936: til dang zas lnga la rgyu byas pa'i ling+ga pho mo gang yin gyi mtshan ma can dpral bar rus/
NK060(i)001:14937: snying gar srog gang yin ming du bcas par bya ste/
NK060(i)001:14938: de yang gro shog la bris nas glan pa'am/
NK060(i)001:14939: yang na gro shog gi ling+ga la rjes kyi sa'am
NK060(i)001:14940: zag rdzas rnams kyis byugs pa yang rung bas lte
NK060(i)001:14942: 'doms su ch+gee mo ma ra ya phata bya ba bri/
NK060(i)001:14943: mtha' ma dzahs bskor la thod pa mtshan ngan gyi nang du bcug la mgo bo lho nub dang /
NK060(i)001:14944: rkang pa byang shar du bstan nas dkyil 'khor gyi
NK060(i)001:14945: byang phyogs kyi brub khung gru gsum du gzhug go
NK060(i)001:14948: sngags 'chad rnams drag po'i cha byad dang 'dug stangs
NK060(i)001:14949: kyis e ram la sogs pa'i sngags brjod pas phyi
NK060(i)001:14950: drag po'i e'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mthing nag gru
NK060(i)001:14952: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam/
NK060(i)001:14953: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram zhes brjod pas/
NK060(i)001:14954: nang drag po lha'i mchog badz+ra he ru kas gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad/
NK060(i)001:14955: kun kyang mthing nag 'jigs pa'i gzugs can/
NK060(i)001:14956: mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs pa/
NK060(i)001:14957: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa/
NK060(i)001:14958: sprul pa dang yang sprul du bcas pa grangs med bskyed do //
NK060(i)001:14961: gu gul la sogs pa lha dbye'i rdzas kyi dud pas ling+ga bdug cing 'go ba'i lha lnga dang dbye/
NK060(i)001:14962: de nas ba hu'i sngags kyis lha las la gzud/
NK060(i)001:14963: pho nya drug bskor btang la/
NK060(i)001:14964: bi shwa badz+ra'i sngags kyis sprul pa spros nas/
NK060(i)001:14965: gzas pa po gang yin rang dbang med par mdun du byung bar dmigs shing /
NK060(i)001:14967: bgegs yin na tri dzahzhesa brjod cing /
NK060(i)001:14968: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya lan gsum mam bdun gyis bkug
NK060(i)001:14969: nas dzahh+aum bam hos ling+ga dang gnyis su med par
NK060(i)001:14970: byas la/ lcags sam shing nag po la byas pa'i rdo rje phur pa mgo la rgya mdud dang /
NK060(i)001:14971: dbal zur gsum pa gsum brung khung gi zur gsum la 'god pa de/
NK060(i)001:14972: sras mchog badz+ra k+ai la ya mngon rtogs bzhin bskyed nas/
NK060(i)001:14973: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab pa la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14974: lag sor byin gyis brlab pa la sogs pa byas nas/
NK060(i)001:14975: sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i le'u lnga bcu rtsa bdun pa nas byung ba'i phur bskul gyi tshig dang /
NK060(i)001:14976: g+ha ta ya'i sngags kyis ling+ga'i dpral mgrin snying ga
NK060(i)001:14977: ste lus ngag yid gsum gyi gnas gsum du gdab
NK060(i)001:14978: par bya'o // de nas hrish+ti'i sngags kyi btub pa dang /
NK060(i)001:14979: +amo b+h+r+aum la sogs pa'i sngags kyis mtshon cha'i char phab pas/
NK060(i)001:14980: ling ro rnams rdul phran tsam du byas par bsam
NK060(i)001:14981: nas tsho gsum du byas la tsho gcig bstab zhal
NK060(i)001:14982: du blug la dkyil 'khor gyis lha rdo rje sems
NK060(i)001:14983: dpa' dang badz+ra he ru kas gtso byas ba'i tshogs
NK060(i)001:14985: tsho gcig gtubs la sbyin sreg gi bsreg rdzas dang basre'o //
NK060(i)001:14986: tsho gcig la bro brdung la lam rgya gram du
NK060(i)001:14987: dong gru gsum brus la ro g.yam la ro sol
NK060(i)001:14988: gyis rdo rje rgya gram bris la mnan pa bya'o
NK060(i)001:14989: // mchod sbyin byas pa'i yon tan/
NK060(i)001:14991: bcom ldan 'das badz+ra he ru kas gtso byas pa'i
NK060(i)001:14992: khrag 'thung 'bar ba drag po'i dkyil 'khor me lha'i
NK060(i)001:14993: lto ru bskyed pa'i lha gtum chen rngam pa'i tshogs
NK060(i)001:14994: rnams la/ stongs kyi sems zhe sdang khros pa'i yid
NK060(i)001:14995: kyis ye shes kyi lha mo dang mkha' 'gro la
NK060(i)001:14996: sbyin pa'i las byas pa'i yon tan ni/
NK060(i)001:14997: sangs rgyas rnams kyi bsod nams kyi tshogs las grub
NK060(i)001:14998: pa'i gzugs sku gnyis yang 'jig par nus na bsgral
NK060(i)001:14999: ba'i zhing bcu la sogs pa brlag nus par lta
NK060(i)001:15001: lu gu rgyud kyi bro yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15004: phyi drag po'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba/
NK060(i)001:15006: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+hi
NK060(i)001:15007: shwa ri s+t+wam h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram zhes
NK060(i)001:15008: pas/ badz+ra he ru kas gtso byas pa'i khro bo'i
NK060(i)001:15009: lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa
NK060(i)001:15010: brgyad du gsal ba'i sgrub pa po pho mo rnams
NK060(i)001:15011: kyis bro ra gru gsum du bcas pa'i dbus su
NK060(i)001:15013: lag pa g.yas pa steng dang g.yon pa 'og tu
NK060(i)001:15014: byas nas bsnol ba'i mathe'u chung lu gu rgyud du
NK060(i)001:15015: sbrel zhing bsdams nas phyag rgya bcing ngo //
NK060(i)001:15017: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK060(i)001:15018: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig dang sum b+ha ni'i sngags kyis bskul zhing /
NK060(i)001:15019: mig 'gyur ba dang bcas pas rkang stabs bskyod nas bro brdungs pas/
NK060(i)001:15020: rdo rje'i rigs kyi sprul pa mthing nag dpag tu
NK060(i)001:15021: med pa phyogs bcur g.yos nas gang la bya ba
NK060(i)001:15022: rdul du brlag par bsams la/
NK060(i)001:15023: ch+gee mo m+aa ra ya h+aum phata zhes pa'i sngags
NK060(i)001:15024: pa'i brjod cing phyag rgya sprugs nas bshig pas gzas
NK060(i)001:15025: pa'i rnam shes myos nas lus gas te snying 'tshig
NK060(i)001:15026: par 'gyur ro // dbang gi phrin las la lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:15030: rgyu bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la gang dbang du
NK060(i)001:15031: bya bar 'dod pa'i mtshan ma snying gar srog gang
NK060(i)001:15032: yin gyi mtha' ming gi yi ges bskor ba la
NK060(i)001:15033: sogs pa sngar bzhin du bcas pa dkyil 'khor gyi
NK060(i)001:15034: nub tu brub khung zla gam du bcug la bzhag
NK060(i)001:15035: par bya'o // dbang gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa/
NK060(i)001:15037: sngags 'chang rnams dbang gi cha byad dang 'dug stangs kyis/
NK060(i)001:15038: bam ram la sogs pa'i sngags brjod pas/
NK060(i)001:15039: phyi dbang mchog bam gyi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dmar nag zla gam me 'bar ba bskyed la/
NK060(i)001:15040: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+hi
NK060(i)001:15041: shwa ri s+t+wam h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram zhes
NK060(i)001:15042: brjod pas/ nang dbang gi lha mchog pad+ma he ru
NK060(i)001:15043: kas gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad
NK060(i)001:15044: kun kyang dmar nag rngam pa'i gzugs can lcags kyu
NK060(i)001:15045: brjod pas/ thogs pa/ me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa/
NK060(i)001:15046: sprul pa yang sprul dang bcas pa grangs med pa bskyed do //
NK060(i)001:15049: sngar bzhin bsgrub bya dgug /gzhug /bstim pa la sogs pa byas pa'i ling+ga la/
NK060(i)001:15050: zangs sam shing dmar po la mgo la rgya mdud dang /
NK060(i)001:15051: dpal zla gam du byas pa rdo rje chags pa
NK060(i)001:15052: ste sras mchog pad+ma k+ai la yar bskyed pa'i phur
NK060(i)001:15053: pa lnga brub khung gi kha khyer la bkod pa
NK060(i)001:15054: rnams la dbang bskur byin brlab la sogs pa dang
NK060(i)001:15055: / lag sor byin gyis brlab pa la sogs pa byas pas phur bskur gyi tshig dang /
NK060(i)001:15056: g+ha ta ya'i sngags kyi rjes la/
NK060(i)001:15057: che ge mo bdag gi dbang du sdus shig /pa
NK060(i)001:15058: sham ma na ye ho zhes ling+ga'i dbang po lnga'i
NK060(i)001:15060: chags pa ste dbang gi dkyil 'khor kyi lha snang
NK060(i)001:15061: ba mtha' yas dang pad+ma he ru kas gtso byas
NK060(i)001:15062: pa'i tshogs rnams la sngar drag po'i las kyi skabs
NK060(i)001:15063: su bshad pa'i cho ga rnams dang tshul mthun par
NK060(i)001:15065: mchod sbyin byas pa'i yon tan/
NK060(i)001:15067: pad+ma he ru kas gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung 'bar
NK060(i)001:15068: ba dbang gi dkyil 'khor me lha'i lto ru bskyed
NK060(i)001:15069: pa'i lha tshogs gzi brjid dang ldan pa lhun chen
NK060(i)001:15070: rnams la stongs kyi sems chags shing zhen pa'i yid
NK060(i)001:15071: kyis mchod sbyin byas pa'i yon tan ni/
NK060(i)001:15072: rdo rje gsung pad+ma dbang yang sgrub pa po'i dbang
NK060(i)001:15073: du 'gyur na bsgrub bya gzhan lta smos kyang ci
NK060(i)001:15074: dgos so // lu gu rgyud kyi las yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15077: phyi zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor dmar nag 'bar ba 'byams klas pa bskyed/
NK060(i)001:15078: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+hi
NK060(i)001:15079: shwa ri s+t+wam h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram zhes
NK060(i)001:15080: pad+ma he ru kas gtso byas pa'i khro bo'i lha
NK060(i)001:15081: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad
NK060(i)001:15082: du gsal ba'i sgrub pa po rnams kyis bro ra
NK060(i)001:15083: zla gam du bcas pa'i dbus su ling ro rnams
NK060(i)001:15084: spungs la/ lag pa sngar ltar bsnol ba'i srin lag lu gu rgyud du sbrel zhing bsdams nas/
NK060(i)001:15087: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig dang /
NK060(i)001:15088: sum+b+ha ni'i sngags kyis bskul zhing /
NK060(i)001:15089: sngar bzhin bro brdungs pas pad+ma rigs kyi sprul pa
NK060(i)001:15090: dmar nag dpag tu med pa rnams kyis gang la
NK060(i)001:15091: bya ba sgrub pa po yis dbang du bsdus par
NK060(i)001:15092: bsams la/ bsgrub bya che ge mo bdag gi dbang
NK060(i)001:15093: du gyur cig /wa sham ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa
NK060(i)001:15094: zhes brjod cing phyag rgya sprugs nas bshig pas bdag
NK060(i)001:15096: mi mdza' ba rnams 'gugs par 'gyur ba lta smos kyang ci dgos te/
NK060(i)001:15097: phyag na rdo rje'ang khyi la zan byin pa bzhin
NK060(i)001:15098: phyi bzhin du 'brang zhing rang ci 'dod pa'i bzhin
NK060(i)001:15100: rgyas pa'i phrin las la lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:15104: rgyu bsgrub bya'i bdud rtsi lnga'am yang na zas lnga la/
NK060(i)001:15105: 'jig rten na gang tshe dang bsod nams rgyas pa/
NK060(i)001:15106: mi dang mi ma yin pa'ang rung ste/
NK060(i)001:15107: de dag gi ling+ga bca' tshul rnam sngar bzhin du
NK060(i)001:15108: byas pa la yon tan dpag tu med pas na
NK060(i)001:15109: yid bzhin gyi gter du brtag cing /
NK060(i)001:15110: dkyil 'khor gyi lho phyogs kyi brub khung gru bzhir gzhug go //
NK060(i)001:15113: sngags 'changs rnams rgyas pa'i cha byad dang 'dug stangs kyis/
NK060(i)001:15114: ma ram la sogs pa'i sngags brjod pa'i phyis rgyas
NK060(i)001:15115: pa ma'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ser nag gru bzhi
NK060(i)001:15116: ma 'bar ba bskyed/ rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na
NK060(i)001:15117: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam h+aum ha he
NK060(i)001:15118: phata b+h+yo ram zhes brjod pas/
NK060(i)001:15119: nang rgyas pa'i lha'i mchog rat+na he ru kas gtso
NK060(i)001:15120: byas pa'i khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kun kyang
NK060(i)001:15121: ser nag rgyas pa'i gzugs can/
NK060(i)001:15122: rin po che zur brgyad pa thogs pa/
NK060(i)001:15123: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa/
NK060(i)001:15124: sprul pa yang sprul dang bcas pa grangs med pa bskyed do //
NK060(i)001:15127: sngar bzhin dgug gzhug bstim pa la sogs pa byas pa'i ling+ga la gser ram/
NK060(i)001:15128: shing ser po la mgo la rgya mdud dang /
NK060(i)001:15129: dbal zur bzhir byas pa nga rgyal dga' 'phro ste/
NK060(i)001:15130: sras mchog rat+na k+ai la yar bskyed pa'i phur pa
NK060(i)001:15131: bzhi brub khung gi zur bzhir bkod pa rnams la
NK060(i)001:15132: dbang bskur byin brlab la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15133: lag sor byin gyis brlab pa la sogs pa byas la phur bskul gyi tshig dang /
NK060(i)001:15134: g+ha ta ya'i sngags kyi rjes la/
NK060(i)001:15135: bdag che ge mo'i tshe dang /
NK060(i)001:15138: longs spyod thams cad push+tim ku ru ye zhes ling+ga'i
NK060(i)001:15139: yan lag bzhi la gdab cig rdo rje'i tshe dang
NK060(i)001:15140: bsod nams gzi byin rnams 'phel bar byed pa rin
NK060(i)001:15142: rat+na he ru kas gtso byas pa'i rgyas pa'i dkyil
NK060(i)001:15143: 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams la dbul ba la sogs
NK060(i)001:15144: pa'i tshul ni sngar dang rjes su mthun no //
NK060(i)001:15145: mchod sbyin bya ba yon tan dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:15147: rat+na he ru kas gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung 'bar
NK060(i)001:15148: ba rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor me lha'i lto ba ru
NK060(i)001:15149: bskyed pa'i lha tshogs/ sprul pa yang sprul dang bcas
NK060(i)001:15150: pa nang du 'du zhing phyir 'phro ba gzi brjid
NK060(i)001:15151: chen po dang ldan pa rnams la stongs kyi sems
NK060(i)001:15152: dga' ba'i yid kyis mchod sbyin byas pa'i yon tan
NK060(i)001:15153: ni tshad las 'das pa nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam
NK060(i)001:15155: lu gu rgyud kyi las yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15158: phyi gru bzhi rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor ser nag 'bar ba 'byams klas pa bskyed/
NK060(i)001:15159: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na ma h+aa kro d+hi
NK060(i)001:15160: shwa ri s+t+wam h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram zhes
NK060(i)001:15161: pa la sogs pas/ rat+na he ru kas gtso byas
NK060(i)001:15162: pa'i khro bo'i lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor khrag 'thung
NK060(i)001:15163: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad du gsal ba'i sgrub pa po
NK060(i)001:15164: rnams kyis bro ra grub bzhir byas pa'i dbus su
NK060(i)001:15165: ling ro lhag ma rnams spungs la/
NK060(i)001:15166: lag pa sngar bzhin bsnol ba'i gung mo lu gu rgyud du sbrel zhing bsdams nas rkang thabs bskyod la/
NK060(i)001:15168: nga rgyal rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK060(i)001:15170: sum+b+ha ni'i sngags kyis bskul zhing sngar bzhin bro brdungs
NK060(i)001:15171: pas gzi brjid 'bar ba rin po che'i rigs kyi
NK060(i)001:15172: sprul pa ser nag dpag tu med pa'i cho 'phrul
NK060(i)001:15173: chen po spros pas tshe dang /
NK060(i)001:15176: longs spyod la sogs pa dgos 'dod 'byung ba yid
NK060(i)001:15177: bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che ltar bsams la
NK060(i)001:15178: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa'i tshe dang /
NK060(i)001:15180: dbang thang dang longs spyod thams cad rgyas par gyur cig push+tim ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa/
NK060(i)001:15182: phyag rgya sprugs nas bshig pa'i yon tan ni/
NK060(i)001:15183: nam mkha'i khams gang ba dang mnyam par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:15184: zhi ba'i phrin las la lnga ste/
NK060(i)001:15188: ling+gi'i rgyu ni bsgrub bya'i bdud rtsi lnga'am yang na zas lnga la/
NK060(i)001:15189: 'jig rten la rgyud ma rungs pa lus gdug cing
NK060(i)001:15190: gtum pa ngag rngam zhing sems 'khrug pa mi dang
NK060(i)001:15191: mi ma yin pa gang yang rung ba'i ling+ga bca'
NK060(i)001:15192: tshul rnams sngar bzhin byas la/
NK060(i)001:15193: de dag gi ngo bor brtag cing dkyil 'khor gyi shar phyogs kyi brub khung zlum por gzhug go //
NK060(i)001:15196: sngags 'chang rnams zhi ba'i cha byad dang 'dug stangs kyis/
NK060(i)001:15197: ya ram la sogs pa'i sngags brjod pas/
NK060(i)001:15198: phyi zhi ba ya'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dkar zhing zlum pa me 'bar ba bskyed/
NK060(i)001:15199: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha ma h+aa kro d+hi
NK060(i)001:15200: shwa ri s+t+wam h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram zhes
NK060(i)001:15201: brjod pas/ nang gi zhi ba'i lha mchog bud+d+ha he
NK060(i)001:15202: ru kas gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa
NK060(i)001:15203: brgyad kun kyang sku mdog dkar po zhi ba'i tshul
NK060(i)001:15204: brjod pas/ can 'khor bsnams pa/ me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pas/
NK060(i)001:15205: sprul pa yang sprul dang bcas pa grangs med bskyed do //
NK060(i)001:15208: sngar bzhin dgug gzhug bstim pa la sogs pa byas pa'i ling+ga la dngul lam/
NK060(i)001:15209: shing dkar po la mgo la rgya mdud dang /
NK060(i)001:15210: dbal zlum por byas pa lhan ner gsal ba'i sras
NK060(i)001:15211: mchog bud+d+ha k+ai la yar bskyed pa'i phur pa drug
NK060(i)001:15212: brub khung gi kha khyer la bkod pa rnams la
NK060(i)001:15213: dbang bskur byin brlab la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15214: lag sor byin gyis brlab pa la sogs pa byas pas gzi brjid dang ldan pa/
NK060(i)001:15216: g+ha ta ya'i sngags kyi rjes la/
NK060(i)001:15217: gdug cing gtum pa rngam zhing 'khrug pa'i sems can
NK060(i)001:15218: thams cad sh+ain+tam ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa zhes ling+ga'i
NK060(i)001:15219: yan lag bzhi mgo dang lnga/
NK060(i)001:15220: snying ga dang drug tu gdab cing 'bar ba lhan ne ste rnams par snang mdzad dang /
NK060(i)001:15221: bud+d+ha he ru kas gtso byas pa'i zhi ba'i lha
NK060(i)001:15222: tshogs rnams la dbul bar bya ba'i tshul rnams ni
NK060(i)001:15223: snga ma rnams dang rjes su mthun no //
NK060(i)001:15224: mchod sbyin bya ba yon tan dang bcas pa/
NK060(i)001:15226: bud+d+ha he ru kas gtso byas pa'i dwangs shing gsal
NK060(i)001:15227: ba zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor me lha'i lto ba ru
NK060(i)001:15228: bskyed pa'i lha tshogs gzi byin 'bar zhing 'od 'tsher
NK060(i)001:15229: ba rnams la stongs kyi sems dang ba'i yid kyis
NK060(i)001:15230: mchod pa dang / sbyin pa byas pa'i yon tan ni/
NK060(i)001:15231: gtum chen rngam pa khro ba las kyi sbyor ba'ang zhi nas lhan ner 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:15232: lu gu rgyud kyi las yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15234: ya b+h+r+aum zhes brjod pas phyi zlum po zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor dkar po lham pa 'byams klas pa bskyed/
NK060(i)001:15235: bud+d+hash+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa
NK060(i)001:15236: ri s+t+wam h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram zhes pa
NK060(i)001:15237: la sogs pa bud+d+ha he ru kas gtso byas pa'i
NK060(i)001:15238: khro bo'i lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor khrag 'thung lnga
NK060(i)001:15239: bcu rtsa brgyad du gsal ba'i sgrub pa po rnams
NK060(i)001:15240: kyis bro ra zlum po byas pa'i dbus su ling
NK060(i)001:15241: ro lhag ma rnams spungs la lag pa sngar ltar
NK060(i)001:15242: bsnol ba'i mdzub mo lu gu rgyud du sbrel zhing
NK060(i)001:15244: gti mug rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK060(i)001:15245: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig dang /
NK060(i)001:15246: sum+b+ha ni'i sngags kyis bskul zhing bro brdungs pas 'bar
NK060(i)001:15247: ba lhan ne zhi ba'i rigs kyi sprul pa dkar
NK060(i)001:15248: po dpag tu med pa'i gzi byin gyis khyab nas/
NK060(i)001:15249: phyi dang nang gi gdug rtsub thams cad zhi bar bsams la/
NK060(i)001:15250: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa la sdang ba'i dgra/
NK060(i)001:15252: bar du gcod pa'i bdud thams cad kyi gdug rtsub
NK060(i)001:15253: zhi bar gyur cig sh+aan+tim ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa
NK060(i)001:15254: zhes brjod cing / phyag rgya sprugs nas bshig pa'i yon tan ni/
NK060(i)001:15255: zhe sdang gis kun nas bslangs pa'i phyi nang gi
NK060(i)001:15256: gdug rtsub thams cad g.yo ba med par byed do
NK060(i)001:15257: // las bzhi po 'di dag skabs 'dir gzhung gi 'bru bsnan pa tsam du zad kyis/
NK060(i)001:15258: rgyas par sbyin sreg rtsa ba dang lag len gyi skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:15259: gnyis pa lhag ma'i las la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:15260: dbang phyug ma lhag mas mchod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15261: dam tshig bsgrag cing las bcol ba'o //
NK060(i)001:15264: las bzhi gang byed kyi phrin las ling ro mnan pa yan chad tshar ba'i rjes la/
NK060(i)001:15267: dbang mo rnams sngags dang phyag rgyas spyan drangs la/
NK060(i)001:15268: sngar bsdus pa'i lhag gtor rnams kha chus bran la gtor mar bsre zhing /
NK060(i)001:15269: so sor mchod nas phrin las bcol ba ni/
NK060(i)001:15270: dpal gyi pho brang slas par byed pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15271: gzhan yang mdza' mo'i ngos nas byi mo/
NK060(i)001:15272: las byed pa'i ngos nas bran mo'i tshogs te/
NK060(i)001:15273: dbang phyug ma nyi shu brgyad la lhag ma'i mchod sbyin ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du sbyin no //
NK060(i)001:15274: dam tshig bsgrag cing las bcol ba la mdo rgyas gnyis las dang po/
NK060(i)001:15276: dpal gyi spyan sngar dam bcas pa'i rang rang gi
NK060(i)001:15277: dam tshig rnams rab tu bsgrags pas phrin las rnam
NK060(i)001:15278: bzhi gang 'dod kyi las de dag byed pa bka'
