NK060(i)001:15283: sngon ru dra 'dul ba'i tshe dpal chen po badz+ra
NK060(i)001:15284: he ru ka sku shin tu gdug cing gsung rngam
NK060(i)001:15285: pa thugs gtum bag can dregs pa can gyi tshogs
NK060(i)001:15286: thams cad lhag ma lus pa 'dul bar mdzad pa'i
NK060(i)001:15287: dbang dang / byin rlabs khyad par can mnga' bas
NK060(i)001:15288: na rmad po che ste de nyid kyis 'jig rten
NK060(i)001:15289: gyi gtso bo lha chen po nyi shu rtsa brgyad
NK060(i)001:15290: la sogs pa dbang du bsdus nas/
NK060(i)001:15291: de dag gi 'khor na gnas pa rnams kyang dbang
NK060(i)001:15292: phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad slas su byas nas
NK060(i)001:15293: zhi rgyas dbang drag so so'i las rnams la bskos
NK060(i)001:15294: pa de dag gis dpal gyi spyan sngar ji ltar
NK060(i)001:15295: dam bcas shing khas blangs pa'i las rnams ma thogs
NK060(i)001:15296: myur du mngon par phyungs shig /gal te dam bcas
NK060(i)001:15297: pa bzhin du ma byas na sngon dpal gyi spyan
NK060(i)001:15298: sngar ji ltar dam bcas shing mna' bor ba'i don
NK060(i)001:15299: dang 'gal tu mi rung bas sngar gyi sdom bcas
NK060(i)001:15300: de las 'da' bar ma byed cig /gal te dam
NK060(i)001:15301: tshig de las 'das par gyur na mgo lus snying
NK060(i)001:15302: yang tshal pa bdun du yak+sha khro bo rdo rje
NK060(i)001:15303: gnod sbyin gyis gtubs par 'gyur ro //
NK060(i)001:15306: mgo dang snying tshal pa bdun du gtubs par 'gyur
NK060(i)001:15307: ba de bas na rnal 'byor sngags 'chang gis las
NK060(i)001:15308: ji ltar bcol ba bzhin du byos shig /gal te
NK060(i)001:15309: las de mngon du ma byas na ni rang gi
NK060(i)001:15310: mna' bor zhing khas blangs pa bzhin du 'jig rten
NK060(i)001:15311: 'dir yang lus rul myags tshig nas/
NK060(i)001:15312: phyi ma dmyal bar 'gro dogs pa de 'dra'i nyen
NK060(i)001:15313: la ma bsdo ba rnal 'byor pa dam la gnas
NK060(i)001:15314: par gyur pa'i las rnams yongs su rdzogs par bya
NK060(i)001:15315: ba dang / de'i 'khor rnams kyang bu gcig pa
NK060(i)001:15316: la mas gdung ba bzhin du skyongs shig /phra men
NK060(i)001:15317: ni don rtags dpe gsum las/
NK060(i)001:15318: don dbyings ye shes gnyis med/
NK060(i)001:15319: rtags khro mo'i lus la dud 'gro'i mgo can/
NK060(i)001:15320: dpe gser yol dngul gyis spras pa lta bu yin la/
NK060(i)001:15321: 'dir rtags kyi phra men ma rnams kyis kyang dngos
NK060(i)001:15322: grub thob par byed pa bcol ba'i las rnams mngon
NK060(i)001:15323: du byos shig ces bka' basgo'o //
NK060(i)001:15324: gsum pa bro gar glu tshig gi yon tan la drug /bgrang /
NK060(i)001:15325: khrag 'thung yab yum gyi glu tshig gis phrin las bzhi ka 'grub par bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:15327: khro bo tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'i dus su
NK060(i)001:15328: phrin las kyi gtso bo ni bro gar glu tshig
NK060(i)001:15330: de yang khrag 'thung chen po rigs lnga yab yum
NK060(i)001:15331: la sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i rnal
NK060(i)001:15334: ngag gi glu tshig ni stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten du zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15335: sum b+ha ni dang las so so'i sngags smon lam
NK060(i)001:15336: dang bcas pas bro chen po brdungs pa 'dis ni
NK060(i)001:15337: las thams cad dang dngos grub thams cad ci 'dod
NK060(i)001:15338: par las thams cad dang dngos grub thams cad 'grub
NK060(i)001:15339: cing thob par byed pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:15340: ke'u r+ai la sogs pa phyogs kyi khro mo bzhis dbang rgyas 'grub par bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:15342: khro mo koo r+ai ma yon tan gyi mdzod dang
NK060(i)001:15343: ldan pas na chen mo yin pa la sogs pa'i
NK060(i)001:15346: be ta li rnams kyi ting nge 'dzin dang ldan
NK060(i)001:15347: pa'i rnal 'byor pas sngar bshad pa bzhin bro gar
NK060(i)001:15348: dang glu tshig chen mos bro brdungs pas ni dbang
NK060(i)001:15349: du 'du bar 'dod na dbang du 'du bar byed
NK060(i)001:15350: la/ tshe dang bsod nams la sogs pa rgyas shing
NK060(i)001:15351: 'phel bar 'dod na yang rgyas shing 'phel bar byed
NK060(i)001:15352: la/ do // puk+ka si la sogs pa mtshams kyi khro mo bzhis zhi drag 'grub par bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:15354: yon tan gyis mngon par mtho ba'i sbos mo chen mo puk+ka si dang la sogs pa'i sogs khongs nas/
NK060(i)001:15357: tsan+da li rnams kyi ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i
NK060(i)001:15358: rnal 'byor pas sngar bzhin bro gar dang glu tshig
NK060(i)001:15359: chen pos bro brdungs pas ni/
NK060(i)001:15360: phyi nang gi gdug rtsub thams cad zhi nas lhan ner 'dod na ni lhan ner byed la/
NK060(i)001:15361: drag pos rmugs par 'dod na ni rmugs par byed do //
NK060(i)001:15362: sid+ha ma la sogs pa phyogs kyi phra men bzhis drag po 'grub par bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:15364: phra men ma seng gdong chen mo dang la sogs pa'i sogs khongs na b+y+aa gri dang /
NK060(i)001:15366: shwa na ma rnams kyi ting nge 'dzin dang ldan
NK060(i)001:15367: pa'i rnal 'byor pas sngar bzhin bro gar dang glu
NK060(i)001:15368: tshig chen mos bro brdungs pas ni/
NK060(i)001:15369: drag po sgrol ba'i las kyi sha khrag thams cad
NK060(i)001:15370: kun la za bar byed cing lhag ma rdul cha
NK060(i)001:15371: tsam yang med par byed do //
NK060(i)001:15372: gri d+ha ma la sogs pa mtshams kyi phra men bzhis drag po 'grub par bstan pa/
NK060(i)001:15374: phra men bzhad gdong chen mo dang la sogs pa'i sogs khongs nas kam ka ma/
NK060(i)001:15376: hu lu ma rnams kyi ting nge 'dzin dang ldan
NK060(i)001:15377: pa'i rnal 'byor pas sngar bzhin bro gar dang glu
NK060(i)001:15378: tshig chen pos bro brdungs pas ni/
NK060(i)001:15379: drag po'i phrin las kyi mthu rtsal thams cad lhag
NK060(i)001:15380: ma ma lus pa 'byin par byed cing dgra bgegs
NK060(i)001:15381: kun la yod pa'i mthu rtsal rab tu nyams par
NK060(i)001:15382: byed do // dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad
NK060(i)001:15383: kyis pho nya mngag gzhug gi las 'grub par bstan
NK060(i)001:15385: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i 'bru sngar dang mthun la/
NK060(i)001:15386: tshogs ni du ma 'dus pa ste nyi shu rtsa brgyad do //
NK060(i)001:15387: de dag gi ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i rnal
NK060(i)001:15388: 'byor pas bro gar dang glu tshig chen pos bro
NK060(i)001:15389: brdungs pas ni/ rbad cing gtang bar bya ba ni
NK060(i)001:15390: pho nya ste de dag thams cad kyis mngag gzhug
NK060(i)001:15391: gi las thams cad byed pa yin no //
NK060(i)001:15392: bzhi pa gzungs sems bstan pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15394: phrin las 'grub pa'i cha rkyen gyi gtso bo gzungs ma dang /
NK060(i)001:15396: de yang gzungs ma'i mtshan nyid ni/
NK060(i)001:15398: shing dang chos mtshungs sbyor te/
NK060(i)001:15399: zhi ba'i gzungs ma shing ljon pa dang chos mthun pa ni/
NK060(i)001:15401: dkar mo bong chung skad che la //
NK060(i)001:15402: bzhin lus gtsug phud g.yas su 'khyil //
NK060(i)001:15403: yan lag phra 'jam skad gsal zhing //
NK060(i)001:15404: glu gar lci bas zhi ba bya //
NK060(i)001:15406: rgyas pa'i gzungs ma shing lcug phran rgyas pa'i tshal dang chos mthun pa ni/
NK060(i)001:15407: zla dang yan lag mang ba dang //
NK060(i)001:15408: phra zhing shed la gzabs su ring //
NK060(i)001:15409: bzhin lus ser zhing gru bzhir gnas //
NK060(i)001:15410: sna 'phyang sha dang nu ma rgyas //
NK060(i)001:15413: dbang gi gzungs ma shing sdong cig dang chos mthun pa ni/
NK060(i)001:15414: bzhin mdog pad 'dra sog kha ma //
NK060(i)001:15415: smin dkyus rings la stod smad phyed //
NK060(i)001:15416: lus la chu klung dri zhim zhing //
NK060(i)001:15417: bde ba ldan zhing yal ga med //
NK060(i)001:15420: drag po'i gzungs ma shing mes reg pa dang chos mtshungs pa ni/
NK060(i)001:15421: nag mo gru gsum rtsid mgo la //
NK060(i)001:15422: khro gnyer byis pa'i lus ldan zhing //
NK060(i)001:15423: gtum zhing barlanga tshig 'dzem bag med //
NK060(i)001:15424: gtsang rme'i rtog bral gsod par byed //
NK060(i)001:15426: 'di la 'grel chung pin tar+tha ltar na/
NK060(i)001:15427: phrin las bzhi bsgrub pa sbyin sreg bya ba'i phyir gnas su bshad de/
NK060(i)001:15429: zhi rgyas dbang drag phyi nang gsang ba'i gnas //
NK060(i)001:15430: ljon shing can dang lcug phran rgyas pa'i tshal //
NK060(i)001:15431: shing gcig drug dang mes tshig phyi yi yin //
NK060(i)001:15432: ma rmas pa dang pu tra mang 'phel dang //
NK060(i)001:15433: skye brgyud med dang bkra mi shis gsang ba //
NK060(i)001:15434: ting 'dzin rnam pa bzhi ni nang gir gsungs //
NK060(i)001:15436: 'o na las bzhi bsgrub pa'i cha rkyen du gzungs ma mi dgos sam zhe na/
NK060(i)001:15438: sbyin sreg bya ba'i gnas de nyid du gzungs ma'i
NK060(i)001:15439: mtshan nyid kyang bshad ma thag pa'i ma rmas pa
NK060(i)001:15440: dang pu tra mang 'phel la sogs pa'am/
NK060(i)001:15441: sgyu 'phrul rdo rje nas bshad pa'i mtshan nyid can
NK060(i)001:15442: gyi gzungs ma rnams dang snyoms par 'jug pa la
NK060(i)001:15444: gzungs ma de dag dang sbyor ba'i tshe gtso bo'i sems ni/
NK060(i)001:15445: las bzhi re re la'ang don dang /
NK060(i)001:15447: de yang chos thams cad dang yid du 'ong ba'i
NK060(i)001:15448: dngos po rnams rang bzhin gyi mi gnas te dwangs
NK060(i)001:15449: pas na zhi ba'i don gyis sems yin la/
NK060(i)001:15450: zhi ba'i phrin las kyis las la sbyar bas gnod
NK060(i)001:15451: pa dang gdug rtsub thams cad zhi bar bsam pa
NK060(i)001:15452: ni stongs kyi sems yin no //
NK060(i)001:15453: yon tan gyi dngos po rnams rang bzhin gyis gnas
NK060(i)001:15454: pa'i dga' ba chen po ni rgyas pa'i don gyi
NK060(i)001:15455: sems yin la/ rgyas pa'i phrin las kyis las la
NK060(i)001:15456: sbyar bas yon tan mngon sum du 'phel bar bsam
NK060(i)001:15457: pa ni stongs kyi sems yin no //
NK060(i)001:15458: bdag la mi gus pa dang mi mdza' ba la
NK060(i)001:15459: sogs pa'i gdul bya rang gi sems nyid las mi
NK060(i)001:15460: gzhan par chags pa ni dbang gi don gyi sems
NK060(i)001:15461: yin la/ de dang rjes su mthun par zhen cing
NK060(i)001:15462: chags pa'i sgo nas las la sbyar bas bsgrub bya
NK060(i)001:15463: dbang du bsdu bar bsam pa ni stongs kyi sems
NK060(i)001:15464: yin la/ yin no // dngos po'i rang bzhin dgos
NK060(i)001:15465: med du 'jigs par byed pa ni drag po'i don
NK060(i)001:15466: yin la/ yin no // gyi sems yin la/ zhe
NK060(i)001:15467: sdang khros pas k+aa li sgrol ba'i las la rab
NK060(i)001:15468: tu sbyar bar byas nas bsgral ba'i zhing bcu'i srog
NK060(i)001:15469: 'jig par mos pa'i bsam pa ni stongs kyi sems
NK060(i)001:15470: yin la/ yin no // gyi sems yin la/ yin no // phrin las kyi yon tan no //
NK060(i)001:15472: zhes brjod pas ma 'ongs pa dang 'byung bar ma
NK060(i)001:15473: nges pa'i dus gnyis kyi de bzhin gshegs pa nyid
NK060(i)001:15474: de/ sems can rnams la 'das pa da ltar gyi
NK060(i)001:15475: dus gnyis kyi de bzhin gshegs pa rtogs pa mngon
NK060(i)001:15476: gyur gyi sangs rgyas nyid brtse ba'i thugs rjes mdzad
NK060(i)001:15477: pa'i phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas rgyud sbyong
NK060(i)001:15478: de/ bar 'gyur ro // le'u'i mtshan no //
NK060(i)001:15480: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las mtshan gyi gzhi ru gda'/
NK060(i)001:15481: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las bzhis lhun
NK060(i)001:15482: gyis grub pa la grub pa ltar byin gyis rlob
NK060(i)001:15483: pa zhes bya ba'i gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed
NK060(i)001:15484: pas na le'u ste yas bgrangs nyi shu pa'i don
NK060(i)001:15485: du gada'o////da ni le'u nyi shu rtsa gcig pa ston
NK060(i)001:15486: par byed pa la/ chos tshoms kyi dbang du bgyis na/
NK060(i)001:15487: rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las lam dang 'bras bu ston/
NK060(i)001:15488: lam la thabs grol gnyis las grol lam ston/
NK060(i)001:15489: rim gyis pa dang cig char ba gnyis las rim gyis pa ston/
NK060(i)001:15490: snang ba bzhi las lam dang 'bras bu'i snang ba ston/
NK060(i)001:15491: mtshan nyid gsum las 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid ston/
NK060(i)001:15492: 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las rgyud don/
NK060(i)001:15493: de la bcu las bstod pa'i mchod pa ston/
NK060(i)001:15494: zhor la dkyil 'khor dang phrin las zur tsam ston no //
NK060(i)001:15495: tha ma'i chos tshoms bcu las mtshon pa dpe dang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston no //
NK060(i)001:15496: de ltar ston pa'i le'u nyi shu rtsa gcig pa 'di la gsum ste/
NK060(i)001:15498: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa/
NK060(i)001:15500: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin khro bo'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK060(i)001:15501: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa la de/
NK060(i)001:15502: de la bstod pa ston pas na nas zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:15503: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos ni 'bru mthun la/
NK060(i)001:15504: khro bo mang po'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor de dag
NK060(i)001:15505: gis zhal khro tshul dang ldan pas shin tu rngam
NK060(i)001:15506: zhing 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis nga ro dang bcas pas
NK060(i)001:15507: bstod pa'i glu 'og nas 'byung ba 'di dag blangs
NK060(i)001:15515: ye shes lnga re re yang ye shes lnga lnga'i
NK060(i)001:15516: bdag nyid du mtshon pa h+aum yi ge cha lnga
NK060(i)001:15518: 'chad par 'gyur ba'i bstod pa kun la shes pa bya'o //
NK060(i)001:15519: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de dag kun kyang rngam pa'i tshems/
NK060(i)001:15521: phrin las drag shul mdzad pa'i phyag rnams rab tu gtum zhing 'gran zla med pas na chen po'o //
NK060(i)001:15522: de lta bu'i sku la la bzod par dka' ba
NK060(i)001:15523: dus mtha'i me chen 'bar ba las sku me dpung
NK060(i)001:15527: thugs rje chen po'i 'od zer dang gsum ni go
NK060(i)001:15528: rim bzhin du gsal zhing mang ba kun la khyab
NK060(i)001:15529: che ba/ dpe nyi ma 'bum gyi 'od dus gcig la shar ba bas kyang gzi brjid che'o //
NK060(i)001:15532: thabs mkhas pa'i khro gnyer dang gsum ni/
NK060(i)001:15533: go rim bzhin smin mtshams sdud pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15535: sna tshogs su g.yo ba rnams glog stong dus gcig tu 'gyur ba bzhin du 'khyug pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15536: skye shi rtsad nas gcod pa'i/
NK060(i)001:15537: gdug pa can za bar byed pa'i/
NK060(i)001:15538: rab tu rngam pa'i mche ba dang gsum ni/
NK060(i)001:15539: go rim bzhin dkar la zangs ring ba dang /
NK060(i)001:15543: gdug pa can za bar byed pa 'gran pa'i zla med par che ba'o //
NK060(i)001:15544: ho zhes pa bstod pas mnyes pa'i don no //
NK060(i)001:15552: rngam pa'i tshul dang gsum gyis gsung gi nga ro drag po'i dbyangs 'jigs par sgrogs pa/
NK060(i)001:15553: dpe 'brug stong du gcig tu ldir ba tsam mo //
NK060(i)001:15556: sprul pa 'khrug pa'i gtum chen dang gsum ni dpe
NK060(i)001:15557: ri rab 'bum dus gcig tu snyil ba'i skad tsam
NK060(i)001:15558: du grags pa'o // a la na rngam pa'i/
NK060(i)001:15560: ha ha na dgyes pa'i gad rgyang dang gsum ni rab tu sgra che ba'o //
NK060(i)001:15563: byin 'bebs pa'i bshugs pa dang gsum ni/
NK060(i)001:15564: go rim bzhin snyan pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15566: byings che ba'i dbugs kyis khams gsum 'thor bar byed
NK060(i)001:15567: pa'i rlung chen pos g.yeng ba 'gran zla med par
NK060(i)001:15574: phyag rgya chen po'i khro bo dang gsum las 'dir shes rab kyi khro bo ste/
NK060(i)001:15575: lta ngan thams cad 'joms par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:15576: de nyid kyang mi sgrib yang gsal bas na 'od po che'o //
NK060(i)001:15577: thugs ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor na shes bya ma
NK060(i)001:15578: lus pa kun dus gcig tu yul med rang gsal
NK060(i)001:15579: gyi tshul gyis mkhyen pa ni 'bar ba'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:15580: zhes bya ste/ lta ngan thams cad kun tu 'jom
NK060(i)001:15581: pas na rdo rje lta bu'i ye shes kyi snang
NK060(i)001:15582: ba thams cad kyang nyid las mi gzhan par sbyor
NK060(i)001:15583: zhes bya ste/ ba'i phyir ro // stong pa nyid
NK060(i)001:15584: bco brgyad mngon du byas pa la sogs pa rtsis
NK060(i)001:15585: zhes bya ste/ ba'i phyir ro // las 'das pas
NK060(i)001:15586: na/ sna tshogs pa'i ye shes rnam pa tha dad
NK060(i)001:15587: du gsal ba kun kyang mi gnas pa'i ye shes
NK060(i)001:15588: chen por ro gcig pas na thig le che zhes
NK060(i)001:15589: zhes bya ste/ ba'i phyir ro // las 'das pas na/ bya'o // ho 'bru mthun/
NK060(i)001:15593: khro bo'i rgyal po yon tan gyi tshogs rab tu
NK060(i)001:15594: mang po 'khrigs pa'i sprin chen po las 'phrog pa'i
NK060(i)001:15595: dkyil 'khor so so'i sprul pa dang chas pa bsam
NK060(i)001:15596: yas pa/ gdul bya'i ngo la dgos 'dod kyi char chen po 'bebs pa/
NK060(i)001:15597: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de dag kyang yid bzhin gyi
NK060(i)001:15598: rin po che la dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i tshul du
NK060(i)001:15599: mi zad pa'i gter gyis gdul bya so so'i re
NK060(i)001:15601: de ltar yon tan sna tshogs dang bcas pa khros
NK060(i)001:15602: pa'i tshul ston pa'i khro bo thams cad kyang ye
NK060(i)001:15603: shes chen po'i khro bor ro gcig pas na thig
NK060(i)001:15609: nyon mongs pa la sogs pa'i bdud bzhi po ma
NK060(i)001:15610: lus pa kun gyi rang bzhin ma spangs par dbang
NK060(i)001:15611: du byed pa ni bdag nyid chen po badz+ra he
NK060(i)001:15612: ru ka'o // de ni bdud ru dra pho mo
NK060(i)001:15613: 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi yang bdud lhar snang
NK060(i)001:15614: ru ka'o // ba yin te/ pho rnams bsgral zhing gnas spar/
NK060(i)001:15615: mo rnams sbyar zhing byin gyis brlabs nas/
NK060(i)001:15616: phyi rol gzhan snang du pham par byas pas na bdud rnams 'joms pa zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:15617: de'i phyir 'jigs pa'i tshogs ru dra sde dang bcas pa rnams kyang 'jigs par byed pa/
NK060(i)001:15618: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung rol pa'i lha tshogs
NK060(i)001:15619: thams cad kyang ye shes kyi mdzad pa nyid las
NK060(i)001:15620: ma g.yos par rang snang bas na thig le che
NK060(i)001:15622: spyir bstod pa'am dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15624: h+aum ye shes lnga ldan yi ge lnga cha bas glu'i 'go 'dren pa yin la/
NK060(i)001:15625: rdo rje ni khro bo'i tshogs rnams ngo bor snang stong dbyer mi phyed pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15626: phrin las bdud bzhi 'joms pa'i phyir te tshul des 'og ma rnams kyang zhes par bya'o //
NK060(i)001:15627: brag chen sra ba po ni dpe yin la/
NK060(i)001:15628: don rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes de mtshan
NK060(i)001:15629: ma'i rnam par rtog pas mi shigs pa'i rtags su
NK060(i)001:15630: khro bo rnams kyi gnas 'og gzhi rdo rje'i brag
NK060(i)001:15631: tu yod pa'o // rdo rje chu bo sdud chen po ni dpe yin la/
NK060(i)001:15632: don 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du sdud cing /
NK060(i)001:15633: ma rtogs pa'i sems can la thugs rjes chags pa'i
NK060(i)001:15634: rtags su khrag gi rgya mtsho zhal du rngub cing
NK060(i)001:15635: gsol ba'o // rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che ba ni dpe yin la/
NK060(i)001:15636: don ye shes kyi mes mtshan ma'i bag chags mi
NK060(i)001:15637: gnas par sreg pa'i rtags su sku me dpung 'bar
NK060(i)001:15639: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che zhes pa ni dpe yin la/
NK060(i)001:15640: don ye shes kyi rlung gis rnam par rtog pa'i
NK060(i)001:15641: rgyu 'bras skye med kyi dbyings su 'thor bar byed
NK060(i)001:15642: pa'i rtags su zhal dang shangs nas bshugs rlung drag
NK060(i)001:15643: po 'byin pa'o // yang na 'di dag 'og gzhi 'byung ba rim brtsegs la bstod pa yang rung ste/
NK060(i)001:15644: tshig rkang dang pos keng rus kyi phung po dang /
NK060(i)001:15645: gnyis pas rak+ta'i rgya mtsho dang /
NK060(i)001:15646: gsum pas rta gdong gi me dang /
NK060(i)001:15647: bzhi pas rgod ma kha'i rlung gi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15648: de yang bu ngan la mas bstod pa la bu ni ma yin te/
NK060(i)001:15649: yon tan yod pa la yod pa ltar nyid kyis nyid la bstod pa ni/
NK060(i)001:15650: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba yin la/
NK060(i)001:15651: de'i rjes su lam pa'i rnal 'byor pas bstod pa ni/
NK060(i)001:15652: bstod pa'i mchod par shes par bya'o zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK060(i)001:15656: zhes khro bo'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK060(i)001:15657: la bstod pa'i klu 'di dag go phye ba'i 'khor
NK060(i)001:15658: gyi ched du bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po
NK060(i)001:15659: nyid kyis nyid la blangs so //
NK060(i)001:15662: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las mtshan gyi gzhi ru gda'/
NK060(i)001:15663: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK060(i)001:15664: las dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa la
NK060(i)001:15665: bstod pa'i gcod cing mtshams 'dzin par byed pas na
NK060(i)001:15666: le'u ste yas bgrangs nyi shu rtsa gcig pa'i don
NK060(i)001:15667: du gada'o////da ni le'u mtha' ma ston par byed pa
NK060(i)001:15668: la/ chos tshoms kyi dbang du byas na/
NK060(i)001:15669: rab kyi chos tshoms gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum las gsum ka ston/
NK060(i)001:15670: lam la thabs grol lam ston/
NK060(i)001:15671: rim cig car gnyis las rim gyis pa ston/
NK060(i)001:15672: snang ba bzhi las bzhi ka ston/
NK060(i)001:15673: mtshan nyid gsum las rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba dang /
NK060(i)001:15674: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid ston/
NK060(i)001:15675: 'bring gi chos tshoms lnga las gdams gtad ston/
NK060(i)001:15676: tha ma'i chos tshoms bcu las rang bzhin lta ba/
NK060(i)001:15679: gzhan yang spyi 'gro gsum gyis ston par byed do //
NK060(i)001:15680: de ltar ston pa'i le'u rtsa gnyis pa 'di la/
NK060(i)001:15681: rnam par dbye ba'i tshig stag gis mchongs pa ltar du bshad na/
NK060(i)001:15682: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15687: de yang 'brel mtshams sbyor ba'i tshig bya ngang mo'i 'gros ltar bshad na/
NK060(i)001:15688: le'u gsum pa'i smad nas nyi shu rtsa gcig pa'i
NK060(i)001:15689: bar gyi le'u phyed dang bcu dgus rgyud don bstan
NK060(i)001:15690: pa la de/ da gdams shing gtad pa ston pas na nas zhes bya ste/
NK060(i)001:15691: gang gis gdams shing gtad na/
NK060(i)001:15692: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos so //
NK060(i)001:15694: lhan cig pa'i 'khor dbang rdzogs pa rnams de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du gyur pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15695: go phyed ba'i 'khor gang zag chos kyi mig can
NK060(i)001:15696: rnams kyang ma 'ongs pa'i dus su de bzhin gshegs
NK060(i)001:15697: pa nyid du gyur pa la dgongs nas gtad do
NK060(i)001:15698: // gang gtad na gsang sngags kyi rgyal po ste/
NK060(i)001:15699: mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud bzhin gsang ba'i snying
NK060(i)001:15700: po zhes bya ba shes bya thun mong ba rnams
NK060(i)001:15701: las khyad par du gyur pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15702: de mtshon byed lam rkyen gyi rgyud yi ger bkod
NK060(i)001:15703: pa lta spyod gzhan las khyad par du 'gyur pa
NK060(i)001:15704: 'di dag go // dgos ched ci'i phyir gtad na/
NK060(i)001:15705: de dag gi don snga ma mi 'gyur zhing brtan par bya ba dang /
NK060(i)001:15706: phyi ma mi nub par gzung bar bya ba'i phyir
NK060(i)001:15707: gdams shing gtad pa'i don 'og nas 'byung ba 'di
NK060(i)001:15714: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba rtogs byar gdams pa/
NK060(i)001:15716: gzhi ni chos thams cad kyi 'byung gzhi rang bzhin ni bcos bslad dang bral ba/
NK060(i)001:15717: snang ba ni rang rig pa thams cad du rtsal ma 'gags par snang ba ste/
NK060(i)001:15718: de'i don 'khor rnams la gdams tshul ni kye zhes lhan cig pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15719: go phye ba'i 'khor gnyis la bos na phyogs bcu
NK060(i)001:15720: dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das gnyis kyiranga bzhin
NK060(i)001:15721: sku dang ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi ngo
NK060(i)001:15722: bor ye gdod ma nas gnas pa 'di ni de
NK060(i)001:15723: bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po ste/
NK060(i)001:15724: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i ngo bo nyid yin
NK060(i)001:15725: pas de nyid kyi don las mi 'gyur bar gnas
NK060(i)001:15727: log rtog 'khrul pa'i snang ba dag byar gdams pa/
NK060(i)001:15729: gnyis med las log cing gnyis su rtog pas na
NK060(i)001:15730: log rtog /de ma yin pa der gzung bas 'khrul
NK060(i)001:15731: pa/ las dang log rtog gi blor snang ba'o //
NK060(i)001:15732: 'o na chos thams cad rang bzhin bden pa dbyer
NK060(i)001:15733: med lhag pa'i chos skur chen por ye nas sangs
NK060(i)001:15734: rgyas pa ma yin nam zhe na yin mod kyi/
NK060(i)001:15735: ma rig pa'i bdag gnyis las byung ba'i gzung 'dzin
NK060(i)001:15736: kun brtags kyi spros pa la thog ma med pa'i
NK060(i)001:15737: dus na mngon par 'chel zhing goms pa'i mthus rnam
NK060(i)001:15738: par rtog pa'i zhags pas 'gro ba drug gi gnas
NK060(i)001:15740: las dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis sdug bsngal bar gyur pas na de las grol bar gdams pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15741: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba bgrod byar gdams pa/
NK060(i)001:15743: mchog dang thun mong gi sems lnga skyes sam skyer
NK060(i)001:15744: rung ba cig gdul bya 'jug cing grol bar byed
NK060(i)001:15745: pas na lam bstan pa blo dang 'tshams par snang
NK060(i)001:15746: ba'o // 'khrul snang de las thar bar bya ba'i phyir lam gyi rgyud rnams gsungs la/
NK060(i)001:15747: lam du ma la dgos pa med par dogs pa
NK060(i)001:15748: gsal ba'i phyir gong 'og gi sa dang lam gyi
NK060(i)001:15749: rim pa rnams khyad par du bkod pa nges 'byung
NK060(i)001:15751: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam stegs
NK060(i)001:15752: yin pas na mthar thug gi lam 'di nyams su
NK060(i)001:15754: 'bras bu bde gshegs kyi snang ba thob byar gdams pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15756: gang zhig smin pa zhig 'bras bu de bzhin nyid
NK060(i)001:15757: du nar son pa cig bde gshegs rtog tshogs sku
NK060(i)001:15758: dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'o
NK060(i)001:15759: // de yang lam nyams su blangs pa'i 'bras bu
NK060(i)001:15760: sku dang ye shes mngon du byas pa ni ngo
NK060(i)001:15761: // mtshar ba ste/ yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab
NK060(i)001:15762: pa sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor
NK060(i)001:15763: lo rab 'byams kyis gdul bya sems can gyi don
NK060(i)001:15764: du mi 'gyur ba yongs ma gsungs pa ste/
NK060(i)001:15765: de dag thob byar gdams pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15766: mdor na snang ba bzhi yang gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rgyud gsum du 'dus la/
NK060(i)001:15767: de gsum yang rang bzhin gyi rgyud rang bzhin bden
NK060(i)001:15768: pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por ye
NK060(i)001:15769: nas sangs rgyas pa las mi 'gyur bar gdams pa'o
NK060(i)001:15770: // gnyis pa gtad pa la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:15772: sdud pa po la gtad de rgyal tshab tu dbyung la/
NK060(i)001:15774: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid
NK060(i)001:15775: dang dgongs pa phyin cig ma log par mngon du
NK060(i)001:15776: bstan pa ni rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po yin
NK060(i)001:15777: la/ rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di las thugs kyi brnag bya gzhan mi mnga' ba'o //
NK060(i)001:15778: de'i phyir rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i ngo bo
NK060(i)001:15779: nyid la sgro 'dogs pa dang skur pa 'debs pa
NK060(i)001:15780: zhi ba'i lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud gsang ba'i snying
NK060(i)001:15781: po de kho na nyid de nges pa'i don 'di
NK060(i)001:15782: ni shes bya'i ming shes byed la btags pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15783: de ltar rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i dbyings nas
NK060(i)001:15784: mngon du phyung ba'i lung 'di yi bka' bsdu ba
NK060(i)001:15785: phyag na rdo rje khyod kyis gyis shig ces gtad
NK060(i)001:15786: nas rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur ba'o //
NK060(i)001:15787: gang zag chos kyi mig can la gtad de mi nub par bya ba'o //
NK060(i)001:15789: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rigs kyi bdag
NK060(i)001:15790: po drug pa kun tu bzang po'i gsung gi phyag
NK060(i)001:15791: rgya ste/ lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud 'dis rang bzhin
NK060(i)001:15792: gyi rgyud don mtshon pa las mi 'da' ba dang
NK060(i)001:15793: rgya ste/ / 'di rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i ngo bo nyid las kyang mi 'da' ba dang /
NK060(i)001:15794: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis kyang lam rkyen gyi rgyud 'di las ma 'das/
NK060(i)001:15795: da ltar ba rnams kyang mi 'da'/
NK060(i)001:15796: ma 'ongs pa rnams 'da' bar mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK060(i)001:15797: des na gsang chen snying po lam rkyen yi ge'i
NK060(i)001:15798: rgyud 'di'i tshig don phyin ci ma log par rtogs
NK060(i)001:15799: nas mi nub par bya ba'i phyir snod du gyur
NK060(i)001:15801: blo dang 'tshams par smra bar gang byed pa de
NK060(i)001:15802: nyid ni kun tu bzang po nga dang khyad med
NK060(i)001:15803: pa yin te/ phan nus zab gsum gyi dbang lnga
NK060(i)001:15804: yang ma bskur bar rdzogs pas na rig pa rtsal
NK060(i)001:15805: gyi dbang thob pa zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:15806: de lta bu'i rten gyi gang zag ni sa la
NK060(i)001:15807: gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' nges par lung bstan
NK060(i)001:15808: de rgyal ba'i sras zhes bya'o //
NK060(i)001:15809: de ni kun tu bzang po'i thugs kyi dgongs pa
NK060(i)001:15810: phyin ci ma log par rtogs pa las skyes pa
NK060(i)001:15811: yin pas na/ rgyu'i theg pa'i sa las mchog tu
NK060(i)001:15812: gyur pa sa rab rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa la
NK060(i)001:15813: yin pas na/ gnas pa yin te/ sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las/
NK060(i)001:15814: rang rig ye shes rgyud don phyir //
NK060(i)001:15815: rang snang rig pa mngon byas pas //
NK060(i)001:15816: rigs 'dzin mchog ste lhun grub pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15817: ting 'dzin nus pa'i mthu med kyang //
NK060(i)001:15818: sa sbyong sems dpa' bskyod du med //
NK060(i)001:15819: bder gshegs nyid dang spyod yul gcig /rig pa'i skyes bur lung thob pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15821: de lta bas na 'di'i don ji lta bar rtogs par gyis la/
NK060(i)001:15822: snod dang ldan par mi nub par bya ba'i phyir snod ldan rnams la sgrogs shig par gtad pa'o //
NK060(i)001:15823: zhor la phyogs bcur 'phel zhing byin che bar bya
NK060(i)001:15824: ba'i phyir ma mo dang mkha' 'khor la gtad pa
NK060(i)001:15826: sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa'i le'u lnga bcu pa dam tshig chen pos bud med btul ba'i le'u las/
NK060(i)001:15827: nga yi thugs kyi snying po 'di //
NK060(i)001:15828: phyogs bcu kun tu spel ba dang //
NK060(i)001:15829: de yi gzungs la gtad pa ni //
NK060(i)001:15830: yid bzhin mdzod 'byor bka' yi gnas //
NK060(i)001:15831: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK060(i)001:15833: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las mtshan gyi gzhi ru gda'/
NK060(i)001:15834: mdzad pa yongs su rdzogs shing ston 'khor dgongs pa
NK060(i)001:15835: dbyer med du gyur nas gdams pa la mnyes pa
NK060(i)001:15836: dang / gtad pa yongs su gzung ba'i gcod cing
NK060(i)001:15837: mtshams 'dzin par byed pas na le'u ste yas bgrangs
NK060(i)001:15838: nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa'i don du gada'o////spyi don mtha'
NK060(i)001:15839: ma mjug gi don la gnyis te/
NK060(i)001:15841: rgyud rdzogs nas mdzad pa chos nyid du bzhugs tshul/
NK060(i)001:15843: zhes brjod pas dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa
NK060(i)001:15844: thams cad chos nyid bde ba chen por ro gcig
NK060(i)001:15845: pas na/ dgongs pa dbyer med par gyur pa bsam
NK060(i)001:15846: gyis mi khyab pa la dgyes nas phyogs bcu dang
NK060(i)001:15847: dus bzhis bsdus pa thams cad rang rig pa las
NK060(i)001:15848: mi gzhan pas mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings te/
NK060(i)001:15849: snang stong dbyer mi phyed cing sku gsung thugs kyi phrin las ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa ste/
NK060(i)001:15850: dper na til gyi gang bu ltar chos kyi dbyings
NK060(i)001:15851: kyi mthas klas pa na stug po bkod pa'i rgyan
NK060(i)001:15853: ngo bo nyid med pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15854: lta bas mi ngoms pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15855: thams cad du cir yang snang ba'i phyir rang rig
NK060(i)001:15856: pa nyid du gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyis bzhengs
NK060(i)001:15857: pa dang bzhugs pa mi mnga' bar gnas shing rtag
NK060(i)001:15858: par bzhugs so // de yang ther zug dang rgyun
NK060(i)001:15859: gyi rtag pa ni ma yin te ngo bo nyid
NK060(i)001:15860: par bzhugs so // kyis so // 'di las bstan
NK060(i)001:15861: pa dang theg pa thams cad 'phros pas rgyud kyi
NK060(i)001:15864: gzhi shes bya'i gnas lugs bden pa dbyer med de
NK060(i)001:15865: nyid bden pa bya bral dang tha dad du 'dod
NK060(i)001:15866: pa las 'phags lam thabs shes zung 'jug de nyid/
NK060(i)001:15867: rgyu la lam du byed pa la 'phags/
NK060(i)001:15868: dus tshe gcig lus gcig de nyid skye ba bcu
NK060(i)001:15869: drug ma bskal pa grangs med gsum la sogs pa
NK060(i)001:15870: la 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa la 'phags/
NK060(i)001:15871: 'bras bu pad+ma can dang yi ge 'khor lo tshogs
NK060(i)001:15872: chen gyi sa de nyid bcu gcig kun tu 'od
NK060(i)001:15873: las 'phags pa'o // rtog pa'i rgyal po zhes pa ni/
NK060(i)001:15874: ngo bo nyid kyi rtog pa lhan skyes kyi ma rig pa/
NK060(i)001:15875: 'khrul pa'i rtog pa kun brtags kyi ma rig pa/
NK060(i)001:15876: log par rtog pa smig rgyu la chur 'dzin pa la sogs pa/
NK060(i)001:15877: rnam pa'i rtog pa yid 'das ma 'ongs kyi rjes su 'jug pa/
NK060(i)001:15878: yang dag pa'i rtog pa chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid rnam par 'byed pa las/
NK060(i)001:15879: 'di ni yang dag pa'i rtog pas te/
NK060(i)001:15880: rtog pa gzhan gong ma bzhi la dbang bskyur bas na rgyal po zhes spar khab nas bshad mod kyi/
NK060(i)001:15881: kho bo'i bla ma zur thams cad mkhyen pa ni/
NK060(i)001:15882: rtogs pa'i rgyal po zhes pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud kyi mtshan gyi rnam grangs su bzhed do //
NK060(i)001:15883: de lta bu'i rgyud mchog 'di ni sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK060(i)001:15884: ba le'u stong phrag brgya pa las bsdus pa'i snying
NK060(i)001:15885: por 'dug pas na/ rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po yin pa'i phyir nges par che/
NK060(i)001:15886: 'di nyid du mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi
NK060(i)001:15887: don dang 'bras bu thams cad 'dus pas na lung
NK060(i)001:15888: gi spyi 'grel yin pa'i phyir nges par che/
NK060(i)001:15889: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kyi gsang
NK060(i)001:15890: ba dam pa'i mthar thug 'di las mi 'da' bas
NK060(i)001:15891: na dgongs pa thams cad kyi zhe phugs yin pa'i
NK060(i)001:15892: phyir nges par che/ nges 'byung gi theg pa gzhi'i
NK060(i)001:15893: mthar thug gi bsgrub bya gsang ba'i snying po de
NK060(i)001:15894: kho na nyid nges pa las ma 'das pa na
NK060(i)001:15895: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse yin pa'i phyir
NK060(i)001:15896: phyir nges par che/ nges par che/ rgyud 'di nyid
NK060(i)001:15897: kyi byin rlabs las bstan pa thams cad dang theg
NK060(i)001:15898: pa ma lus par 'phros pas te de las gzhan
NK060(i)001:15899: pa'i sel med pas na bstan pa thams cad kyi
NK060(i)001:15900: 'byung gnas yin pa'i phyir nges par che/
NK060(i)001:15901: de yang rgyud 'di'i byin rlabs las/
NK060(i)001:15902: bka' dang po bden pa bzhi'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK060(i)001:15903: bskor bas nyon mongs pa dang srid pa'i zag pa
NK060(i)001:15905: bka' bar pa mtshan nyid med pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15906: mtha' ma nges pa don gyi chos kyi 'khor los
NK060(i)001:15907: lta ba dang ma rig pa'i zag pa gnyis kyi
NK060(i)001:15908: d+r+wa ba ma lus pa gcod par byed pas na/
NK060(i)001:15909: sngar 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi gshegs shul yin pa'i phyir nges par che la/
NK060(i)001:15910: ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi lam kyang yin pa'i phyir na nges par che'o //
NK060(i)001:15911: de dag rnams kyi 'bras bu'i nang nas kyang mchog
NK060(i)001:15912: tu gyur pa ni rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying por
NK060(i)001:15913: 'dug pas na 'bras bu thams cad kyi thugs yin
NK060(i)001:15917: tshig dang don la lhag ma ma lus pa'i tha tshig go //
NK060(i)001:15918: +thii zhes pa ni shin tu zab pa'i don no //
NK060(i)001:15919: rgyud rgyal rdo rje'i tshig la 'grel bshad rtsom pa'i gnyer //
NK060(i)001:15920: gnas lnga ma rig mngon shes lnga bral bdag lta bu //
NK060(i)001:15921: ji ltar 'os kyang rgyal rig gang zhig gsum brgyud pa'i //
NK060(i)001:15922: bshad rgyud 'grel tig mchan bu gsung sgros rjes 'brangs nas //
NK060(i)001:15923: bklags dang bltar pas bshad dang mnyan go chod pa 'di //
NK060(i)001:15924: bde blag rgyud don khong du chud par bya phyir bris //
NK060(i)001:15926: mkhas pa rnams kyi tshul min kyang //
NK060(i)001:15927: dri med 'od las ji skad du //
NK060(i)001:15928: yul gyi skad gyi don shes na //
NK060(i)001:15929: bstan bcos skad kyis ci zhig bya //
NK060(i)001:15930: 'di la nongs pa 'i tshogs gyur gang //
NK060(i)001:15931: ye shes shes rab chos kyi spyan //
NK060(i)001:15932: mnga' ba'i mkhyen ldan rnams kyis ni //
NK060(i)001:15933: rang gzhan don la dgongs nas kyang //
NK060(i)001:15934: bzod mdzad thugs rjes bzung bar rigs //
NK060(i)001:15935: 'di brtsams phal pa'i dge ba gang //
NK060(i)001:15936: mkha' khyab sems can don du bsngo //
NK060(i)001:15937: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i
NK060(i)001:15938: rgyud kyi 'grel bshad rgyud don gsal bar byed pa'i
NK060(i)001:15940: sh+aakya'i dge slong rdo rje dpal bzang pos chu mo
NK060(i)001:15941: lug gi lo'i dbyar gyi ngo g.yas ru chos ldings
NK060(i)001:15942: kyi ri khrod du sbyar ba 'dis kyang 'gro ba
NK060(i)001:15943: dpag tu med pa rdo rje 'dzin pa'i go 'phang
NK060(i)001:15944: la 'god par gyur cig /dri med lhag pa'i bsam
NK060(i)001:15946: snyigs dus bstan pa'i bcas su smon btsugs nas //
NK060(i)001:15947: dngos dang go phye'i 'khor la 'di yi lung //
NK060(i)001:15948: bdag gis byin no de la yid ches mdzod //
NK060(i)001:15949: 'grel bshad 'di mthong ba dag dang dngos 'phrad mtshungs //
NK060(i)001:15950: rtog spyod su gtong bdag dang gleng bas na //
NK060(i)001:15951: 'di don su rtogs bdag gi snying gi bu //
NK060(i)001:15952: yid ches skyes na bdag gi lung thob cing //
NK060(i)001:15953: 'di don rtogs na de ka snod ldan yin //
NK060(i)001:15954: gal te ma rtogs rang gsang thabs kyis mchod //
NK060(i)001:15955: sgro 'dogs skur 'debs slar gyi thugs rje'i yul //
NK060(i)001:15956: de phyir 'di yi snod du ma gyur med //
NK060(i)001:15957: kun gyis blta dang 'chad nyan nyams len dang //
NK060(i)001:15958: yi ger 'bri dang 'di ru gzhug par rigs //
NK060(i)001:15959: de la ma mgon lcam dral 'khor bcas kyis //
NK060(i)001:15960: sngon gyi tha tshig bzhin du stong grogs mdzod //
NK060(i)001:15961: gang gis 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK060(i)001:15963: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK060(i)001:15964: phyogs dus kun nas thams cad du //
NK060(i)001:15965: nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur //
NK060(i)001:15966: rgyal ba'i rig pa 'dzin pa de //
NK060(i)001:15969: dam pa mchog dang dam pa yi //
NK060(i)001:15970: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis rlobs //
NK060(i)001:15971: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK060(i)001:15973: phyag rgya gsang chen snying po 'di //
NK060(i)001:15974: rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa //
NK060(i)001:15975: de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK060(i)001:15979: +thii/ rje sgro phug pa'i bshad srol la gzhung las bcad btab nas mchan bus 'chad cing /
NK060(i)001:15980: dka' ba rnams dka' tshoms dang t+ai kas 'chad/
NK060(i)001:15981: gsung sgros kyi shog lde rnams lhan thabs su 'debs par 'dug na'ang /
NK060(i)001:15982: dka' tshoms dang sa bcad dang mchan bu rnams 'debs pa dang /
NK060(i)001:15984: gsung sgros rnams la'ang dag ther bya rgyu ci rigs pa 'dug cing /
NK060(i)001:15985: mchan bu rnams 'grel pa spar khab kyi lugs su btab 'dug na'ang /
NK060(i)001:15986: spar khab kyis ma khrol ba dang ma bkral ba rnams/
NK060(i)001:15989: 'ga' zhig bla ma gong ma rnams kyi sgros mchan du 'dug pa/
NK060(i)001:15990: de thams cad la bdag gis brtags shing dpyad nas/
NK060(i)001:15991: rmongs pa rnams kyi shes sla'i phyir t+ai ka bklags chog gu ru'i lugs su bris pa la/
